UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='为什麽我们需要这样的服务?荒弃的洞穴的盗贼霍夫丹·黑须已经给我们惹了一大堆麻烦，我是不是还要留意你一下?',Text0_1_loc4='为什麽我们需要这样的服务?荒弃的洞穴的盗贼霍夫丹·黑须已经给我们惹了一大堆麻烦，我是不是还要留意你一下?',Text1_0_loc4='为什麽我们需要这样的服务?荒弃的洞穴的盗贼霍夫丹·黑须已经给我们惹了一大堆麻烦，我是不是还要留意你一下?',Text1_1_loc4='为什麽我们需要这样的服务?荒弃的洞穴的盗贼霍夫丹·黑须已经给我们惹了一大堆麻烦，我是不是还要留意你一下?' WHERE entry=2774; /* Text0_0: Now why would ye be needing the services of one of those types?  We get enough trouble out of that rogue, Hulfdan Blackbeard, over in The Forlorn Cavern, do I need to be turning my eye to you as well? */ /* Text0_1: Now why would ye be needing the services of one of those types?  We get enough trouble out of that rogue, Hulfdan Blackbeard, over in The Forlorn Cavern, do I need to be turning my eye to you as well? */ /* Text1_0: All the roguish types hang out in The Forlorn Cavern, north of the gates of Ironforge.  I\'d wager ye\'ll find Fenthwick there, no doubt counting the coin of another cut purse.  I\'ll catch him one of these days!  $B$BIn the meantime I\'ll have my eye on you as well, $glad : lass;. */ /* Text1_1: All the roguish types hang out in The Forlorn Cavern, north of the gates of Ironforge.  I\'d wager ye\'ll find Fenthwick there, no doubt counting the coin of another cut purse.  I\'ll catch him one of these days!  $B$BIn the meantime I\'ll have my eye on you as well, $glad : lass;. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='没有什麽地方比铁炉堡最黑暗的荒弃洞穴那里更适合寻找那些阴暗的家伙了。你在那里肯定会找到瑟斯哈特，就像是召唤一个行径卑劣的动物去照他的吩咐办事。',Text0_1_loc4='没有什麽地方比铁炉堡最黑暗的荒弃洞穴那里更适合寻找那些阴暗的家伙了。你在那里肯定会找到瑟斯哈特，就像是召唤一个行径卑劣的动物去照他的吩咐办事。',Text1_0_loc4='没有什麽地方比铁炉堡最黑暗的荒弃洞穴那里更适合寻找那些阴暗的家伙了。你在那里肯定会找到瑟斯哈特，就像是召唤一个行径卑劣的动物去照他的吩咐办事。',Text1_1_loc4='没有什麽地方比铁炉堡最黑暗的荒弃洞穴那里更适合寻找那些阴暗的家伙了。你在那里肯定会找到瑟斯哈特，就像是召唤一个行径卑劣的动物去照他的吩咐办事。' WHERE entry=2775; /* Text0_0: Where better to look for a dark and brooding lot, than the dark section of Ironforge, aptly named The Forlorn Cavern.  Thistleheart is sure to be found there, likely summoning some manner of vile creature to do his bidding. */ /* Text0_1: Where better to look for a dark and brooding lot, than the dark section of Ironforge, aptly named The Forlorn Cavern.  Thistleheart is sure to be found there, likely summoning some manner of vile creature to do his bidding. */ /* Text1_0: A warlock, eh...  Well, if you\'ve got a mind to be doing that sort of thing around here then ye best keep yer demons on a leash $gboyo : girlie;.  I don\'t like demons, but I love putting mah axe to them.  Ye get me?  $B$BNow you just leave me be and go get lost in The Forlorn Cavern.  That\'s where you\'ll find that warlock, Thistleheart. */ /* Text1_1: A warlock, eh...  Well, if you\'ve got a mind to be doing that sort of thing around here then ye best keep yer demons on a leash $gboyo : girlie;.  I don\'t like demons, but I love putting mah axe to them.  Ye get me?  $B$BNow you just leave me be and go get lost in The Forlorn Cavern.  That\'s where you\'ll find that warlock, Thistleheart. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='哦!你想接受战士的训练，是吗?克斯塔姆·碎石会帮你实现梦想的!去铁炉堡东门的武器大厅吧。',Text0_1_loc4='哦!你想接受战士的训练，是吗?克斯塔姆·碎石会帮你实现梦想的!去铁炉堡东门的武器大厅吧。',Text1_0_loc4='哦!你想接受战士的训练，是吗?克斯塔姆·碎石会帮你实现梦想的!去铁炉堡东门的武器大厅吧。',Text1_1_loc4='哦!你想接受战士的训练，是吗?克斯塔姆·碎石会帮你实现梦想的!去铁炉堡东门的武器大厅吧。' WHERE entry=2776; /* Text0_0: Och! Ye seek training in the way of the warrior, do ye?  Kelstrum Stonebreaker will put ye through yer paces!  Just march yerself over to the Hall of Arms east of the gates of Ironforge. */ /* Text0_1: Och! Ye seek training in the way of the warrior, do ye?  Kelstrum Stonebreaker will put ye through yer paces!  Just march yerself over to the Hall of Arms east of the gates of Ironforge. */ /* Text1_0: Kelstrum is a loudmouth and a braggart... and if that weren\'t enough he\'s also one of the most skilled warriors ye\'ll ever meet!  $b$bI tell ye, if ye\'re looking to be trained in the ways of a warrior, that\'s who ye should be talking to.  I\'m sure he can be found over in the Hall of Arms east of the Gates of Ironforge. */ /* Text1_1: Kelstrum is a loudmouth and a braggart... and if that weren\'t enough he\'s also one of the most skilled warriors ye\'ll ever meet!  $b$bI tell ye, if ye\'re looking to be trained in the ways of a warrior, that\'s who ye should be talking to.  I\'m sure he can be found over in the Hall of Arms east of the Gates of Ironforge. */
