UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你在找炼金术训练师吗?嗯，我刚从那儿过来呢，真的。你可以在侏儒聚集的侏儒区找浆泡小姐。',Text0_1_loc4='你在找炼金术训练师吗?嗯，我刚从那儿过来呢，真的。你可以在侏儒聚集的侏儒区找浆泡小姐。',Text1_0_loc4='你在找链金术训练师吗?嗯，我刚从那儿过来呢，真的。你可以在侏儒聚集的侏儒区找浆泡小姐。',Text1_1_loc4='你在找链金术训练师吗?嗯，我刚从那儿过来呢，真的。你可以在侏儒聚集的侏儒区找浆泡小姐。' WHERE entry=2794; /* Text0_0: An Alchemy trainer is what you need?  Well, I just came from there, I did.  Ye\'ll find Ms. Berryfizz over in Tinker Town where the gnomes gather. */ /* Text0_1: An Alchemy trainer is what you need?  Well, I just came from there, I did.  Ye\'ll find Ms. Berryfizz over in Tinker Town where the gnomes gather. */ /* Text1_0: Yer looking for an Alchemy trainer are ye?  Just came from there, I did.  Ye\'ll find Ms. Berryfizz over in Tinker Town where the gnomes gather.  $B$B::sigh:: ...why o\' why didn\'t I take the blue potion. */ /* Text1_1: Yer looking for an Alchemy trainer are ye?  Just came from there, I did.  Ye\'ll find Ms. Berryfizz over in Tinker Town where the gnomes gather.  $B$B::sigh:: ...why o\' why didn\'t I take the blue potion. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你算来对地方了，$g小夥子:姑娘;!人们从世界各地来此学习成为一名铁匠。你会看到本古斯·深炉在我们漂亮的城市中央的大锻炉的铁砧上埋头工作。',Text0_1_loc4='你算来对地方了，$g小夥子:姑娘;!人们从世界各地来此学习成为一名铁匠。你会看到本古斯·深炉在我们漂亮的城市中央的大锻炉的铁砧上埋头工作。',Text1_0_loc4='你算来对地方了，$g小夥子:姑娘;!人们从世界各地来此学习成为一名铁匠。你会看到本古斯·深炉在我们漂亮的城市中央的大锻炉的铁砧上埋头工作。',Text1_1_loc4='你算来对地方了，$g小夥子:姑娘;!人们从世界各地来此学习成为一名铁匠。你会看到本古斯·深炉在我们漂亮的城市中央的大锻炉的铁砧上埋头工作。' WHERE entry=2795; /* Text0_0: Ye\'ve come to the right place $glad : lass;!  People come here from all o\'er the world to train to be a blacksmith.  Ye\'ll find Bengus Deepforge hammering away at an anvil in the middle of our fine city by The Great Forge itself. */ /* Text0_1: Ye\'ve come to the right place $glad : lass;!  People come here from all o\'er the world to train to be a blacksmith.  Ye\'ll find Bengus Deepforge hammering away at an anvil in the middle of our fine city by The Great Forge itself. */ /* Text1_0: Are ye really askin\' me where the Blacksmith is?  Have ye not heard of The Great Forge!?  All our best blacksmiths gather there to craft their weapons and armor!  $B$BIt\'s dead smack in the middle of Ironforge, and that\'s where you\'ll find one of our most brilliant blacksmiths, Bengus Deepforge. */ /* Text1_1: Are ye really askin\' me where the Blacksmith is?  Have ye not heard of The Great Forge!?  All our best blacksmiths gather there to craft their weapons and armor!  $B$BIt\'s dead smack in the middle of Ironforge, and that\'s where you\'ll find one of our most brilliant blacksmiths, Bengus Deepforge. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='一个烹饪训练师?那好吧，你到大锻炉东北方的铜壶铁罐店去。达瑞尔·瑞克努索会教你制作极好的菜肴，那肯定会让你获得新生的!',Text0_1_loc4='一个烹饪训练师?那好吧，你到大锻炉东北方的铜壶铁罐店去。达瑞尔·瑞克努索会教你制作极好的菜肴，那肯定会让你获得新生的!',Text1_0_loc4='一个烹饪训练师?那好吧，你到大锻炉东北方的铜壶铁罐店去。达瑞尔·瑞克努索会教你制作极好的菜肴，那肯定会让你获得新生的!',Text1_1_loc4='一个烹饪训练师?那好吧，你到大锻炉东北方的铜壶铁罐店去。达瑞尔·瑞克努索会教你制作极好的菜肴，那肯定会让你获得新生的!' WHERE entry=2796; /* Text0_0: A Cooking trainer is it?  Well then, get yerself over to the Bronze Kettle on the northeastern side of The Great Forge.  Daryl Riknussun will teach ye to make a mighty fine dish that\'s sure to put the life back in ye! */ /* Text0_1: A Cooking trainer is it?  Well then, get yerself over to the Bronze Kettle on the northeastern side of The Great Forge.  Daryl Riknussun will teach ye to make a mighty fine dish that\'s sure to put the life back in ye! */ /* Text1_0: Och!  That Daryl Riknussun is a brilliant cook!  He makes a chilli so hot ye could temper steel with it!  I don\'t think he\'ll teach ye the recipe, but he\'ll certainly help ye to become a good cook.  Ye\'ll find him at the Bronze Kettle o\'er on the northeastern side of The Great Forge. */ /* Text1_1: Och!  That Daryl Riknussun is a brilliant cook!  He makes a chilli so hot ye could temper steel with it!  I don\'t think he\'ll teach ye the recipe, but he\'ll certainly help ye to become a good cook.  Ye\'ll find him at the Bronze Kettle o\'er on the northeastern side of The Great Forge. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='啊，要是你想成为一名附魔师的话，我想你需要找吉布·草须。他在大锻炉狮鹫兽管理人右边的商店草须魔法用品店里。',Text0_1_loc4='啊，要是你想成为一名附魔师的话，我想你需要找吉布·草须。他在大锻炉狮鹫兽管理人右边的商店草须魔法用品店里。',Text1_0_loc4='啊，要是你想成为一名附魔师的话，我想你需要找吉布·草须。他在大锻炉狮鹫兽管理人右边的商店草须魔法用品店里。',Text1_1_loc4='啊，要是你想成为一名附魔师的话，我想你需要找吉布·草须。他在大锻炉狮鹫兽管理人右边的商店草须魔法用品店里。' WHERE entry=2797; /* Text0_0: Ah, I believe Gimble Thistlefuzz is who ye\'ll be needing if yer looking to learn the Enchanter\'s profession.  Ye\'ll find Gimble in his shop, Thistlefuzz Arcanery, right by the Gryphon Master at The Great Forge. */ /* Text0_1: Ah, I believe Gimble Thistlefuzz is who ye\'ll be needing if yer looking to learn the Enchanter\'s profession.  Ye\'ll find Gimble in his shop, Thistlefuzz Arcanery, right by the Gryphon Master at The Great Forge. */ /* Text1_0: Och!  Ye should be careful what ye get enchanted $glad : lass;.  I had me mug enchanted so it wouldn\'t spill a drop, but now I can\'t drink from it!  Such a tragedy.  $B$BYou be sure to heed me advice when ye see Gimble.  He\'ll be in his shop right by the Gryphon Master at The Great Forge. */ /* Text1_1: Och!  Ye should be careful what ye get enchanted $glad : lass;.  I had me mug enchanted so it wouldn\'t spill a drop, but now I can\'t drink from it!  Such a tragedy.  $B$BYou be sure to heed me advice when ye see Gimble.  He\'ll be in his shop right by the Gryphon Master at The Great Forge. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='急救是一种有价值的技能。我们的常驻的训练师，尼莎·火石，会教你该怎麽做。到大锻炉南边的铁炉堡医师协会可以找到她。',Text0_1_loc4='急救是一种有价值的技能。我们的常驻的训练师，尼莎·火石，会教你该怎麽做。到大锻炉南边的铁炉堡医师协会可以找到她。',Text1_0_loc4='急救是一种有价值的技能。我们的常驻的训练师，尼莎·火石，会教你该怎麽做。到大锻炉南边的铁炉堡医师协会可以找到她。',Text1_1_loc4='急救是一种有价值的技能。我们的常驻的训练师，尼莎·火石，会教你该怎麽做。到大锻炉南边的铁炉堡医师协会可以找到她。' WHERE entry=2799; /* Text0_0: A valuable skill First Aid is.  Our resident trainer, Nissa Firestone, can show ye how it\'s done.  Look for her on the southern side of The Great Forge at the Ironforge Physician. */ /* Text0_1: A valuable skill First Aid is.  Our resident trainer, Nissa Firestone, can show ye how it\'s done.  Look for her on the southern side of The Great Forge at the Ironforge Physician. */ /* Text1_0: First Aid?  Well ye don\'t look hurt to me.  If yer really interested in learning First Aid, then Nissa Firestone is the one to learn from.  Go see her over by The Great Forge in her shop, The Ironforge Physician. */ /* Text1_1: First Aid?  Well ye don\'t look hurt to me.  If yer really interested in learning First Aid, then Nissa Firestone is the one to learn from.  Go see her over by The Great Forge in her shop, The Ironforge Physician. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='格瑞诺尔·石印会告诉他曾经碰到许多脱钩的超级大鱼，但他仍是附近最好的渔夫之一。他在荒弃的洞穴开有一家叫做旅行渔具店的商店。',Text0_1_loc4='格瑞诺尔·石印会告诉他曾经碰到许多脱钩的超级大鱼，但他仍是附近最好的渔夫之一。他在荒弃的洞穴开有一家叫做旅行渔具店的商店。',Text1_0_loc4='格瑞诺尔·石印会告诉他曾经碰到许多脱钩的超级大鱼，但他仍是附近最好的渔夫之一。他在荒弃的洞穴开有一家叫做旅行渔具店的商店。',Text1_1_loc4='格瑞诺尔·石印会告诉他曾经碰到许多脱钩的超级大鱼，但他仍是附近最好的渔夫之一。他在荒弃的洞穴开有一家叫做旅行渔具店的商店。' WHERE entry=2800; /* Text0_0: Grimnur Stonebrand will tell ye some whoppers about the one that got away, but he\'s still one o\' the best fishermen around.  He\'s got a shop set up in The Forlorn Cavern called the Traveling Fisherman. */ /* Text0_1: Grimnur Stonebrand will tell ye some whoppers about the one that got away, but he\'s still one o\' the best fishermen around.  He\'s got a shop set up in The Forlorn Cavern called the Traveling Fisherman. */ /* Text1_0: I once heard ol\' Grimnur say he fished up a sword.  Or was it a swordfish?  Damn that Grimnur, he\'s told so many fish tales I can\'t remember which is which.  Well, why don\'t you go see him over in The Forlorn Cavern and have him tell you what it was. */ /* Text1_1: I once heard ol\' Grimnur say he fished up a sword.  Or was it a swordfish?  Damn that Grimnur, he\'s told so many fish tales I can\'t remember which is which.  Well, why don\'t you go see him over in The Forlorn Cavern and have him tell you what it was. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='花和种子以及类似的东西?那是雷纳·石枝的专业领域。你能在大锻炉南面的铁炉堡医师协会处看到她料理她的植物。',Text0_1_loc4='花和种子以及类似的东西?那是雷纳·石枝的专业领域。你能在大锻炉南面的铁炉堡医师协会处看到她料理她的植物。',Text1_0_loc4='花和种子以及类似的东西?那是雷纳·石枝的专业领域。你能在大锻炉南面的铁炉堡医师协会处看到她料理她的植物。',Text1_1_loc4='花和种子以及类似的东西?那是雷纳·石枝的专业领域。你能在大锻炉南面的铁炉堡医师协会处看到她料理她的植物。' WHERE entry=2801; /* Text0_0: Flowers and seeds and such?  That would be Reyna Stonebranch\'s area of expertise.  Ye can find her tending to her plants over at the Ironforge Physician on the southern side of The Great Forge. */ /* Text0_1: Flowers and seeds and such?  That would be Reyna Stonebranch\'s area of expertise.  Ye can find her tending to her plants over at the Ironforge Physician on the southern side of The Great Forge. */ /* Text1_0: Oh, ye want to learn to pick some daisies do ye?  Ha!  I\'m just teasing ye $gladdie : lass;.  $B$BA fine profession it is, and Reyna Stonebranch can show ye how it\'s done.  She works at the Ironforge Physician on the southern side of The Great Forge. */ /* Text1_1: Oh, ye want to learn to pick some daisies do ye?  Ha!  I\'m just teasing ye $gladdie : lass;.  $B$BA fine profession it is, and Reyna Stonebranch can show ye how it\'s done.  She works at the Ironforge Physician on the southern side of The Great Forge. */
