UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='达纳苏斯有许多熟练的训练师，他们拥有多年的训练经验。我会介绍一名导师给你，沿着你选择的道路前进吧。',Text0_1_loc4='达纳苏斯有许多熟练的训练师，他们拥有多年的训练经验。我会介绍一名导师给你，沿着你选择的道路前进吧。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=3022; /* Text0_0: Here in Darnassus you will find skilled trainers who have perfected the skills of their chosen class through ages of training and dedication.  I will guide you to one who can become your mentor, you have but to name your chosen path. */ /* Text0_1: Here in Darnassus you will find skilled trainers who have perfected the skills of their chosen class through ages of training and dedication.  I will guide you to one who can become your mentor, you have but to name your chosen path. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你很幸运来到达纳苏斯，因为你遇到了像祖卡斯特这样多才多艺的猎人作为你的训练师。我建议你到塞纳里奥区拜访她并寻求她的指导。',Text0_1_loc4='你很幸运来到达纳苏斯，因为你遇到了像祖卡斯特这样多才多艺的猎人作为你的训练师。我建议你到塞纳里奥区拜访她并寻求她的指导。',Text1_0_loc4='你很幸运来到达纳苏斯，因为你遇到了像祖卡斯特这样多才多艺的猎人作为你的训练师。我建议你到塞纳里奥区拜访她并寻求她的指导。',Text1_1_loc4='你很幸运来到达纳苏斯，因为你遇到了像祖卡斯特这样多才多艺的猎人作为你的训练师。我建议你到塞纳里奥区拜访她并寻求她的指导。' WHERE entry=3023; /* Text0_0: You are fortunate to have come to Darnassus where you can find such an accomplished Hunter as Jocaste among our trainers.  I encourage you to visit her over in the Cenarion Enclave and seek her tutelage. */ /* Text0_1: You are fortunate to have come to Darnassus where you can find such an accomplished Hunter as Jocaste among our trainers.  I encourage you to visit her over in the Cenarion Enclave and seek her tutelage. */ /* Text1_0: Jocaste was the greatest of Hunters of her time.  These days you can find her over in the Cenarion Enclave where she teaches those who are just starting down the Hunter\'s path. */ /* Text1_1: Jocaste was the greatest of Hunters of her time.  These days you can find her over in the Cenarion Enclave where she teaches those who are just starting down the Hunter\'s path. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='居住於塞纳里奥区的德鲁伊一直在大德鲁伊鹿盔的领导下警惕地保卫着自然界。你可以在达纳苏斯北部找到他和别的德鲁伊训练师。',Text0_1_loc4='居住於塞纳里奥区的德鲁伊一直在大德鲁伊鹿盔的领导下警惕地保卫着自然界。你可以在达纳苏斯北部找到他和别的德鲁伊训练师。',Text1_0_loc4='居住於塞纳里奥区的德鲁伊一直在大德鲁伊鹿盔的领导下警惕地保卫着自然界。你可以在达纳苏斯北部找到他和别的德鲁伊训练师。',Text1_1_loc4='居住於塞纳里奥区的德鲁伊一直在大德鲁伊鹿盔的领导下警惕地保卫着自然界。你可以在达纳苏斯北部找到他和别的德鲁伊训练师。' WHERE entry=3024; /* Text0_0: Ever vigilant in their protection of the natural world, the druids are guided by Arch Druid Fandral Staghelm who resides in the Cenarion Enclave.  You will find him and the other Druid trainers in the northern section of Darnassus. */ /* Text0_1: Ever vigilant in their protection of the natural world, the druids are guided by Arch Druid Fandral Staghelm who resides in the Cenarion Enclave.  You will find him and the other Druid trainers in the northern section of Darnassus. */ /* Text1_0: In grizzly times a druid can be a dear friend to those around them.  Ask any of the druids in the Cenarion Enclave and they will tell you the same. */ /* Text1_1: In grizzly times a druid can be a dear friend to those around them.  Ask any of the druids in the Cenarion Enclave and they will tell you the same. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='月神殿是伊露恩的祭司们的家园。你会在那儿找到贾德莉亚和拉瑞亚，她们会对你的牧师生涯做出进一步的指导。',Text0_1_loc4='月神殿是伊露恩的祭司们的家园。你会在那儿找到贾德莉亚和拉瑞亚，她们会对你的牧师生涯做出进一步的指导。',Text1_0_loc4='月神殿是伊露恩的祭司们的家园。你会在那儿找到贾德莉亚和拉瑞亚，她们会对你的牧师生涯做出进一步的指导。',Text1_1_loc4='月神殿是伊露恩的祭司们的家园。你会在那儿找到贾德莉亚和拉瑞亚，她们会对你的牧师生涯做出进一步的指导。' WHERE entry=3025; /* Text0_0: The Temple of the Moon is home to the priests of Elune.  There you will find Jandria and Lariia, who will provide you with further guidance in the path of priesthood. */ /* Text0_1: The Temple of the Moon is home to the priests of Elune.  There you will find Jandria and Lariia, who will provide you with further guidance in the path of priesthood. */ /* Text1_0: The power of Elune compels you!  The power of Elune compels you!  $B$BGo now!  Seek out Jandria in the central hall of the Temple of the Moon in the southern section of Darnassus! */ /* Text1_1: The power of Elune compels you!  The power of Elune compels you!  $B$BGo now!  Seek out Jandria in the central hall of the Temple of the Moon in the southern section of Darnassus! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='要是你想做盗贼的话，就该去找塞尤娜。她居住在西部森林盘旋山道下的塞纳里奥区。',Text0_1_loc4='要是你想做盗贼的话，就该去找塞尤娜。她居住在西部森林盘旋山道下的塞纳里奥区。',Text1_0_loc4='要是你想做盗贼的话，就该去找塞尤娜。她居住在西部森林盘旋山道下的塞纳里奥区。',Text1_1_loc4='要是你想做盗贼的话，就该去找塞尤娜。她居住在西部森林盘旋山道下的塞纳里奥区。' WHERE entry=3026; /* Text0_0: It is Syurna that you seek if you are to follow the rogue\'s path.  She dwells in the Cenarion Enclave down the spiraling path within the western most tree. */ /* Text0_1: It is Syurna that you seek if you are to follow the rogue\'s path.  She dwells in the Cenarion Enclave down the spiraling path within the western most tree. */ /* Text1_0: There are those that attempt to follow the path of the Rogue, but only the night elves are truly embraced by the night.  If you seek to walk the shaded path then find Syurna in the Cenarion Enclave. */ /* Text1_1: There are those that attempt to follow the path of the Rogue, but only the night elves are truly embraced by the night.  If you seek to walk the shaded path then find Syurna in the Cenarion Enclave. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你会在战士区的护卫队中找到希达奈尔，她敏锐的眼睛扫视着森林，寻找着胆敢进入我们美丽的城市的敌人。',Text0_1_loc4='你会在战士区的护卫队中找到希达奈尔，她敏锐的眼睛扫视着森林，寻找着胆敢进入我们美丽的城市的敌人。',Text1_0_loc4='你会在战士区的护卫队中找到希达奈尔，她敏锐的眼睛扫视着森林，寻找着胆敢进入我们美丽的城市的敌人。',Text1_1_loc4='你会在战士区的护卫队中找到希达奈尔，她敏锐的眼睛扫视着森林，寻找着胆敢进入我们美丽的城市的敌人。' WHERE entry=3033; /* Text0_0: You will find Sildinair at the Warrior\'s Terrace among the guards, her keen eyes scanning the forest for enemies that might dare to enter our fair city. */ /* Text0_1: You will find Sildinair at the Warrior\'s Terrace among the guards, her keen eyes scanning the forest for enemies that might dare to enter our fair city. */ /* Text1_0: Sildinair has trained many of the Sentinels who guard our beloved city.  I am certain she can make a warrior out of the likes of you.  Seek her out at the Warrior\'s Terrace near the entrance to our city. */ /* Text1_1: Sildinair has trained many of the Sentinels who guard our beloved city.  I am certain she can make a warrior out of the likes of you.  Seek her out at the Warrior\'s Terrace near the entrance to our city. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='达纳苏斯的工匠们可传授很多工艺知识给你。告诉我，你对哪种工艺最好奇?',Text0_1_loc4='达纳苏斯的工匠们可传授很多工艺知识给你。告诉我，你对哪种工艺最好奇?',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=3034; /* Text0_0: Here among the craftsmen of Darnassus, there is a millenium of knowledge for the benefit of your chosen craft.  Now tell me, which craft do you find the most intriguing? */ /* Text0_1: Here among the craftsmen of Darnassus, there is a millenium of knowledge for the benefit of your chosen craft.  Now tell me, which craft do you find the most intriguing? */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='如果你真的想学习这个专业技能，就去达纳苏斯北部的工匠区找一个技艺纯熟的链金师:安尼希尔。',Text0_1_loc4='如果你真的想学习这个专业技能，就去达纳苏斯北部的工匠区找一个技艺纯熟的链金师:安尼希尔。',Text1_0_loc4='如果你真的想学习这个专业技能，就去达纳苏斯北部的工匠区找一个技艺纯熟的链金师:安尼希尔。',Text1_1_loc4='如果你真的想学习这个专业技能，就去达纳苏斯北部的工匠区找一个技艺纯熟的链金师:安尼希尔。' WHERE entry=3035; /* Text0_0: If you truly have the desire to learn this profession, then I would point you in the direction of Ainethil, a skilled alchemist at the Craftsmen\'s Terrace in northern Darnassus. */ /* Text0_1: If you truly have the desire to learn this profession, then I would point you in the direction of Ainethil, a skilled alchemist at the Craftsmen\'s Terrace in northern Darnassus. */ /* Text1_0: An alchemist?  No trouble at all $c.  Ainethil, in all her labor and toil, has become the most accomplished alchemist in the Craftsmen\'s Terrace.  I would head over there on the double if I were you. On the double!  Now off with you! */ /* Text1_1: An alchemist?  No trouble at all $c.  Ainethil, in all her labor and toil, has become the most accomplished alchemist in the Craftsmen\'s Terrace.  I would head over there on the double if I were you. On the double!  Now off with you! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='阿雷贡是一名技艺精湛的厨师，数个世纪以来，他都在精进自己的厨艺。要是他愿意教你的话，你就得谢天谢地了。要是你相信自己的实力的话，就去工匠区找他吧。',Text0_1_loc4='阿雷贡是一名技艺精湛的厨师，数个世纪以来，他都在精进自己的厨艺。要是他愿意教你的话，你就得谢天谢地了。要是你相信自己的实力的话，就去工匠区找他吧。',Text1_0_loc4='阿雷贡是一名技艺精湛的厨师，数个世纪以来，他都在精进自己的厨艺。要是他愿意教你的话，你就得谢天谢地了。要是你相信自己的实力的话，就去工匠区找他吧。',Text1_1_loc4='阿雷贡是一名技艺精湛的厨师，数个世纪以来，他都在精进自己的厨艺。要是他愿意教你的话，你就得谢天谢地了。要是你相信自己的实力的话，就去工匠区找他吧。' WHERE entry=3036; /* Text0_0: Alegorn is a masterful chef who has had centuries with which to perfect his cooking.  You should consider yourself blessed should he decide to teach you.  If you believe you are worthy, you can find him in the Craftsmen\'s Terrace. */ /* Text0_1: Alegorn is a masterful chef who has had centuries with which to perfect his cooking.  You should consider yourself blessed should he decide to teach you.  If you believe you are worthy, you can find him in the Craftsmen\'s Terrace. */ /* Text1_0: The dishes that Alegorn whips up are to die for.  He\'s always busy preparing new delicacies over in the Craftsman\'s Terrace.  Be sure to try his Cenarion Green recipe if he has any left.  $B$BNow, if you don\'t mind, I must investigate this rash of missing deer. */ /* Text1_1: The dishes that Alegorn whips up are to die for.  He\'s always busy preparing new delicacies over in the Craftsman\'s Terrace.  Be sure to try his Cenarion Green recipe if he has any left.  $B$BNow, if you don\'t mind, I must investigate this rash of missing deer. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='当你没有医者来料理你的伤口时，急救知识可以救你的性命。我会请教工匠区的丹纳罗尔关於这门技艺的问题。',Text0_1_loc4='当你没有医者来料理你的伤口时，急救知识可以救你的性命。我会请教工匠区的丹纳罗尔关於这门技艺的问题。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=3037; /* Text0_0: When you have not a healer to tend to your wounds, the knowledge of First Aid can be a lifesaver.  I would consult Dannelor over at the Craftsmen\'s Terrace for instruction on this skill. */ /* Text0_1: When you have not a healer to tend to your wounds, the knowledge of First Aid can be a lifesaver.  I would consult Dannelor over at the Craftsmen\'s Terrace for instruction on this skill. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='它是一项耗时，但是会很有收获的技能。与贸易区的阿斯坦娅谈谈或许你能学到一些有用的东西。',Text0_1_loc4='它是一项耗时，但是会很有收获的技能。与贸易区的阿斯坦娅谈谈或许你能学到一些有用的东西。',Text1_0_loc4='它是一项耗时，但是会很有收获的技能。与贸易区的阿斯坦娅谈谈或许你能学到一些有用的东西。',Text1_1_loc4='它是一项耗时，但是会很有收获的技能。与贸易区的阿斯坦娅谈谈或许你能学到一些有用的东西。' WHERE entry=3038; /* Text0_0: A time consuming, yet rewarding skill.  Speak with Astaia in the Tradesman\'s Terrace and maybe you\'ll learn something useful. */ /* Text0_1: A time consuming, yet rewarding skill.  Speak with Astaia in the Tradesman\'s Terrace and maybe you\'ll learn something useful. */ /* Text1_0: Astaia has fished up some curious treasures over the ages she has spent fishing.  Why don\'t you go see her over in the Tradesman\'s terrace and have her show you some of them. */ /* Text1_1: Astaia has fished up some curious treasures over the ages she has spent fishing.  Why don\'t you go see her over in the Tradesman\'s terrace and have her show you some of them. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='草药的收集和与之相关的知识是菲罗迪恩·唤月的专长。去达纳苏斯西南部的神殿花园找他吧。',Text0_1_loc4='草药的收集和与之相关的知识是菲罗迪恩·唤月的专长。去达纳苏斯西南部的神殿花园找他吧。',Text1_0_loc4='草药的收集和与之相关的知识是菲罗迪恩·唤月的专长。去达纳苏斯西南部的神殿花园找他吧。',Text1_1_loc4='草药的收集和与之相关的知识是菲罗迪恩·唤月的专长。去达纳苏斯西南部的神殿花园找他吧。' WHERE entry=3039; /* Text0_0: The gathering and knowledge of herbs is a specialty of Firodren Mooncaller.  Seek him out in the Temple Gardens in the southwestern area of Darnassus. */ /* Text0_1: The gathering and knowledge of herbs is a specialty of Firodren Mooncaller.  Seek him out in the Temple Gardens in the southwestern area of Darnassus. */ /* Text1_0: A budding herbalist are we?  Then you should visit with Firodren Mooncaller over in the Temple Gardens.  He may have some tricks of the trade to impart with you. */ /* Text1_1: A budding herbalist are we?  Then you should visit with Firodren Mooncaller over in the Temple Gardens.  He may have some tricks of the trade to impart with you. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='泰龙尼斯制作武器的技能无与伦比。他不会收学生的钱，你该为此感到庆幸。去吧，去达纳苏斯东北部的工匠区找他吧。',Text0_1_loc4='泰龙尼斯制作武器的技能无与伦比。他不会收学生的钱，你该为此感到庆幸。去吧，去达纳苏斯东北部的工匠区找他吧。',Text1_0_loc4='泰龙尼斯制作武器的技能无与伦比。他不会收学生的钱，你该为此感到庆幸。去吧，去达纳苏斯东北部的工匠区找他吧。',Text1_1_loc4='泰龙尼斯制作武器的技能无与伦比。他不会收学生的钱，你该为此感到庆幸。去吧，去达纳苏斯东北部的工匠区找他吧。' WHERE entry=3040; /* Text0_0: The skill with which Telonis crafts armor is beyond compare.  You should be grateful that he does not charge more for the knowledge he passes to others.  Go now and seek him out in the Craftsmen\'s Terrace in the northeast section of Darnassus. */ /* Text0_1: The skill with which Telonis crafts armor is beyond compare.  You should be grateful that he does not charge more for the knowledge he passes to others.  Go now and seek him out in the Craftsmen\'s Terrace in the northeast section of Darnassus. */ /* Text1_0: We plant the vegetables.  Our vegetables are eaten by the rabbit.  The rabbit is devoured by the wolf.  The wolf is slain by us.  We take the meat and hide from the wolf\'s corpse.  It\'s that Magic Circle of life, or whatever you call it.  $B$BNow go see Telonis in the Cenarion Enclave to get started and let me return to my duties. */ /* Text1_1: We plant the vegetables.  Our vegetables are eaten by the rabbit.  The rabbit is devoured by the wolf.  The wolf is slain by us.  We take the meat and hide from the wolf\'s corpse.  It\'s that Magic Circle of life, or whatever you call it.  $B$BNow go see Telonis in the Cenarion Enclave to get started and let me return to my duties. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='世间动物死时会将它们的生命和兽皮赐予我们。要是你能尊重牠们的牺牲，或许剥皮这个专业技能会适合你的。去达纳苏斯北部的工匠区，找艾拉迪尔谈谈，学习更多知识。',Text0_1_loc4='世间动物死时会将它们的生命和兽皮赐予我们。要是你能尊重牠们的牺牲，或许剥皮这个专业技能会适合你的。去达纳苏斯北部的工匠区，找艾拉迪尔谈谈，学习更多知识。',Text1_0_loc4='世间动物死时会将它们的生命和兽皮赐予我们。要是你能尊重牠们的牺牲，或许剥皮这个专业技能会适合你的。去达纳苏斯北部的工匠区，找艾拉迪尔谈谈，学习更多知识。',Text1_1_loc4='世间动物死时会将它们的生命和兽皮赐予我们。要是你能尊重牠们的牺牲，或许剥皮这个专业技能会适合你的。去达纳苏斯北部的工匠区，找艾拉迪尔谈谈，学习更多知识。' WHERE entry=3042; /* Text0_0: In death, the animals of the world bestow both life and protection unto us.  If you feel that you can offer the appropriate respect for their sacrifice, then the skinner\'s profession may suit you.  Speak with Eladriel in the Craftsmen\'s Terrace in northern Darnassus to learn more. */ /* Text0_1: In death, the animals of the world bestow both life and protection unto us.  If you feel that you can offer the appropriate respect for their sacrifice, then the skinner\'s profession may suit you.  Speak with Eladriel in the Craftsman\'s Terrace in northern Darnassus to learn more. */ /* Text1_0: As a culture we believe in letting nothing go to waste.  When we are forced to slay a creature we take what we can to make sure its sacrifice was not in vain.  $B$BIf you wish to learn the proper way to take the skin of a slain beast, then seek out Eladriel in the Craftsmen\'s Terrace. */ /* Text1_1: As a culture we believe in letting nothing go to waste.  When we are forced to slay a creature we take what we can to make sure its sacrifice was not in vain.  $B$BIf you wish to learn the proper way to take the skin of a slain beast, then seek out Eladriel in the Craftsmen\'s Terrace. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='如果你有希望学成一位裁缝的话你当然应该去找玫琳恩。她住在达纳苏斯东北方的工匠区。',Text0_1_loc4='如果你有希望学成一位裁缝的话你当然应该去找玫琳恩。她住在达纳苏斯东北方的工匠区。',Text1_0_loc4='如果你有希望学成一位裁缝的话你当然应该去找玫琳恩。她住在达纳苏斯东北方的工匠区。',Text1_1_loc4='如果你有希望学成一位裁缝的话你当然应该去找玫琳恩。她住在达纳苏斯东北方的工匠区。' WHERE entry=3044; /* Text0_0: You would certainly be looking for Me\'Lynn if you have any hope of learning to be a tailor.  She resides at the Craftsmen\'s Terrace in northeastern Darnassus. */ /* Text0_1: You would certainly be looking for Me\'Lynn if you have any hope of learning to be a tailor.  She resides at the Craftsmen\'s Terrace in northeastern Darnassus. */ /* Text1_0: With the garments that Me\'Lynn tailors, one might think that her needle was blessed by Elune herself.  Unless your needle is so blessed, you best pay her a visit and listen to her teachings.  You can find her in The Craftsmen\'s Terrace in northeastern Darnassus. */ /* Text1_1: With the garments that Me\'Lynn tailors, one might think that her needle was blessed by Elune herself.  Unless your needle is so blessed, you best pay her a visit and listen to her teachings.  You can find her in The Craftsmen\'s Terrace in northeastern Darnassus. */
