UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='银行?哦，这附近最近的银行就是暴风城会计室。沿着暴风城大门不远的那条路向前走就是。',Text0_1_loc4='银行?哦，这附近最近的银行就是暴风城会计室。沿着暴风城大门不远的那条路向前走就是。',Text1_0_loc4='银行?哦，这附近最近的银行就是暴风城会计室。沿着暴风城大门不远的那条路向前走就是。',Text1_1_loc4='银行?哦，这附近最近的银行就是暴风城会计室。沿着暴风城大门不远的那条路向前走就是。' WHERE entry=4260; /* Text0_0: A bank?  Well, the closest bank around here is The Stormwind Counting House.  It\'s just up the road in Stormwind not far from the gates. */ /* Text0_1: A bank?  Well, the closest bank around here is The Stormwind Counting House.  It\'s just up the road in Stormwind not far from the gates. */ /* Text1_0: Oh, you must mean the Stormwind Counting House.  It\'s not far from the gates after you enter Stormwind. */ /* Text1_1: Oh, you must mean the Stormwind Counting House.  It\'s not far from the gates after you enter Stormwind. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='如果你想乘坐狮鹫兽的话，就去找暴风城的狮鹫兽管理员吧。当你进入英雄谷时，应该就能看见右边的狮鹫兽降落台。',Text0_1_loc4='如果你想乘坐狮鹫兽的话，就去找暴风城的狮鹫兽管理员吧。当你进入英雄谷时，应该就能看见右边的狮鹫兽降落台。',Text1_0_loc4='如果你想乘坐狮鹫兽的话，就去找暴风城的狮鹫兽管理员吧。当你进入英雄谷时，应该就能看见右边的狮鹫兽降落台。',Text1_1_loc4='如果你想乘坐狮鹫兽的话，就去找暴风城的狮鹫兽管理员吧。当你进入英雄谷时，应该就能看见右边的狮鹫兽降落台。' WHERE entry=4261; /* Text0_0: Well there\'s a gryphon master up in Stormwind if you need to fly somewhere.  You should be able to see the gryphons landing on your right as you walk through the Valley of Heroes. */ /* Text0_1: Well there\'s a gryphon master up in Stormwind if you need to fly somewhere.  You should be able to see the gryphons landing on your right as you walk through the Valley of Heroes. */ /* Text1_0: The gryphon master oversees the gryphon flights from within Stormwind.  If you\'re looking to take a ride, then that\'s where you should be headed. */ /* Text1_1: The gryphon master oversees the gryphon flights from within Stormwind.  If you\'re looking to take a ride, then that\'s where you should be headed. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我相信奥德文·拉弗林仍是暴风城的常驻公会注册员。当你进入暴风城的贸易区后，你的左手边就是他的居所。',Text0_1_loc4='我相信奥德文·拉弗林仍是暴风城的常驻公会注册员。当你进入暴风城的贸易区后，你的左手边就是他的居所。',Text1_0_loc4='我相信奥德文·拉弗林仍是暴风城的常驻公会注册员。当你进入暴风城的贸易区后，你的左手边就是他的居所。',Text1_1_loc4='我相信奥德文·拉弗林仍是暴风城的常驻公会注册员。当你进入暴风城的贸易区后，你的左手边就是他的居所。' WHERE entry=4262; /* Text0_0: I believe Aldwin Laughlin is still the resident Guild Master of Stormwind.  Look for his residence on your left as you pass the inner gate of Stormwind. */ /* Text0_1: I believe Aldwin Laughlin is still the resident Guild Master of Stormwind.  Look for his residence on your left as you pass the inner gate of Stormwind. */ /* Text1_0: All that official business is handled up in Stormwind these days.  You could stop by the Stormwind Visitor\'s Center if you want to start a guild. */ /* Text1_1: All that official business is handled up in Stormwind these days.  You could stop by the Stormwind Visitor\'s Center if you want to start a guild. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='到闪金镇的狮王之傲旅店去吧。那儿有麦芽酒和柔软的床铺供你尽情享用，没有比那里更好的休息场所了。',Text0_1_loc4='到闪金镇的狮王之傲旅店去吧。那儿有麦芽酒和柔软的床铺供你尽情享用，没有比那里更好的休息场所了。',Text1_0_loc4='到闪金镇的狮王之傲旅店去吧。那儿有麦芽酒和柔软的床铺供你尽情享用，没有比那里更好的休息场所了。',Text1_1_loc4='到闪金镇的狮王之傲旅店去吧。那儿有麦芽酒和柔软的床铺供你尽情享用，没有比那里更好的休息场所了。' WHERE entry=4263; /* Text0_0: Look no further than the Lion\'s Pride Inn in Goldshire.  With a wide selection of ales and soft down beds you, couldn\'t ask for a better place to rest. */ /* Text0_1: Look no further than the Lion\'s Pride Inn in Goldshire.  With a wide selection of ales and soft down beds you, couldn\'t ask for a better place to rest. */ /* Text1_0: The Lion\'s Pride Inn in Goldshire is as good as any inn you will find around these parts.  Drop in and let Innkeeper Farley make you feel at home. */ /* Text1_1: The Lion\'s Pride Inn in Goldshire is as good as any inn you will find around these parts.  Drop in and let Innkeeper Farley make you feel at home. */
