UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='一瓶雷酒牌麦芽酒外加格雷姆罗克做的菜就足以让你饱餐一顿。如果你想成为一名厨师的话，就该去参加他的培训。',Text0_1_loc4='一瓶雷酒牌麦芽酒外加格雷姆罗克做的菜就足以让你饱餐一顿。如果你想成为一名厨师的话，就该去参加他的培训。',Text1_0_loc4='一瓶雷酒牌麦芽酒外加格雷姆罗克做的菜就足以让你饱餐一顿。如果你想成为一名厨师的话，就该去参加他的培训。',Text1_1_loc4='一瓶雷酒牌麦芽酒外加格雷姆罗克做的菜就足以让你饱餐一顿。如果你想成为一名厨师的话，就该去参加他的培训。' WHERE entry=4303; /* Text0_0: A Thunderbrew ale and a bit of Gremlock\'s cooking makes for a nice meal indeed.  Ye really should hit him up for some training if ye want to be a cook. */ /* Text0_1: A Thunderbrew ale and a bit of Gremlock\'s cooking makes for a nice meal indeed.  Ye really should hit him up for some training if ye want to be a cook. */ /* Text1_0: Gremlock doesn\'t always have the best of luck with cooking, but he does have some tasty recipies worth learning.  Go chat him up in the Thunderbrew Distillery and see what he\'ll teach ye. */ /* Text1_1: Gremlock doesn\'t always have the best of luck with cooking, but he does have some tasty recipies worth learning.  Go chat him up in the Thunderbrew Distillery and see what he\'ll teach ye. */
