UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我看见一些有趣的人在港口进进出出。小心，$N。你永远不清楚谁值得信任以及跟这儿发生的所有事情的缘由……' WHERE entry=5753; /* Text0_0: I see some interesting characters come and go here at the port. Watch yourself, $N. It\'s never clear who to trust, what with all of the shady activity that goes on here... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你是为战歌之斧而来的吧。嗯，是时候了，$N。那木箱已经放了好长时间了。$B$B你可以随时拖走它。' WHERE entry=5754; /* Text0_0: So you\'re here for the Warsong axes. Well, it\'s about time, $N. That crate has been sitting out there for days, now.$B$BFeel free to haul it away whenever you are ready. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='石爪山脉在这片区域拥有许多危险的洞穴。若干冒险家愿意冒着生命的危险到这些洞穴中探险。$B$B$C，也许只要你全心全意地寻找，会找到财宝的。' WHERE entry=5773; /* Text0_0: Stonetalon Mountain has many perilous caves through out this region.  Exploring these caves can hold many adventures for those willing to risk life for glory.$B$B$C, perhaps you seek riches that only following your heart and soul can garnish. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='鱼肉真鲜美。你来学钓鱼的?还是来吃鱼的?呣...' WHERE entry=5793; /* Text0_0: Fish so delicious. You come learn fish? Eat fish? Mmmmm... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='好吧，我可以教你钓鱼。' WHERE entry=5794; /* Text0_0: Yap, I can teach ye to fish. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我们可能遇到强气流了，但是并不缺乏肉食!想看看我的货物吗?' WHERE entry=5798; /* Text0_0: We may have been suffering a drought but there\'s no shortage of meat! Care to browse my goods? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我会喂养它们的，孩子。达瑞尔·瑞克努索，愿为你服务。' WHERE entry=5800; /* Text0_0: I keep \'em fed, kid. Yep, Daryl Riknussun, at yer service. */
