UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你好，$c。现在正是收获节－一个感恩与追思的时间。我们举办盛宴感激所有我们应该感激的人，追忆我们的祖先和英雄，感谢他们给我们留下的宝贵遗产。$B$B请尽情享受这盛宴吧。我还提供一些烟火来庆祝这个美好的日子。' WHERE entry=7535; /* Text0_0: Greetings, $c.  It is the time of the Harvest Festival - a time of great bounties and a time of remembrance.  We partake of feasts to celebrate all we have to be thankful of, and we remember our ancestors and past heroes to give thanks to the legacy they gave us.$B$BPlease feel free to partake of the feast being offered here.  Also, I am offering some fireworks to help celebrate this joyous time of year. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你好，$c。现在正是收获节－一个感恩与追思的时间。我们举办盛宴感激所有我们应该感激的人，追忆我们的祖先和英雄，感谢他们给我们留下的宝贵遗产。$B$B请尽情享受这盛宴吧。我还提供一些烟火来庆祝这个美好的日子。' WHERE entry=7536; /* Text0_0: Greetings, $c.  It is the time of the Harvest Festival - a time of great bounties and a time of remembrance.  We partake of feasts to celebrate all we have to be thankful of, and we remember our ancestors and past heroes to give thanks to the legacy they gave us.$B$BPlease feel free to partake of the feast being offered here.  Also, I am offering some fireworks to help celebrate this joyous time of year. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='阿拉希盆地的战斗是一场谋略战。木材、矿石、食物……所有这些物资对战斗来说都是必需品。$B$B摧毁敌方的物资跟在战场上杀死他们一样重要。' WHERE entry=7555; /* Text0_0: The battle for Arathi Basin is a battle for resources.  Lumber, ore, food... all these are needed in order to wage a good war.$B$BDenying our enemies of their supplies is as good as killing them on the battlefield. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我眼睛虽然看不到，但是我还拥有洞察力。$B$B我主要跟猎人和盗贼打交道，$r。' WHERE entry=7556; /* Text0_0: Sightless I may be, but vision I have.$B$BMy primary dealings are with hunters and rogues, $r. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='冒险者，你好。我是赞达拉的商人林沃斯。我来自南海，从我的家乡带来了许多新奇的货物。$B$B如果你能证明自己的价值，我会乐意与你交换物品的。如果你有我们部族的荣誉勳章，我这里还有些更好的东西……' WHERE entry=7574; /* Text0_0: Hail, adventurer. I am Rin\'wosho, trader of Zuldazar. I come from the South Seas and bring many exotic goods and items from my homeland.$B$BPerhaps if you prove your worth to my tribe, I shall barter.  If you have any of my tribe\'s Honor Tokens, then perhaps we shall barter even more. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我是赞达拉的赞札。我用以太形态从赞达拉赶来帮助我的人民。哈卡不能控制我的灵魂。$B$B我是来帮助那些曾经有恩於赞达拉的朋友的。' WHERE entry=7594; /* Text0_0: I am Zanza, a Loa of Zandalar. I have come in this ethereal form from Zandalar to help my people. Hakkar has no dominion over my soul.$B$BI help those that have helped the Zandalarian people. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='赞达拉的朋友!你已经进入血神的巢穴深处，$c。你最好仔细听我说。$B$B数千年前，当祖阿曼帝国的食人妖与入侵的高等精灵异教徒作战时，高等精灵盗取了赞札强大的魔法，在自己的武器和护甲上附魔，以此征服当地的食人妖。' WHERE entry=7595; /* Text0_0: A friend of the Zandalrian! You have ventured deep into the lair of the Blood God, $c. You will do well to listen to what I have to say.$B$BMany thousands of years ago, while the indigenous trolls of the Zul\'Aman empire were battling the invading high elf heathens, great magic was stolen from Zanza. This magic was used by the high elves to enchant their weapons and armor to assist in conquering the trolls of the region. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='是吗?这麽说你已经知道高等精灵所掌握的食人妖魔法有多麽浅显了?$B$B高等精灵怎麽都想不明白，作为一个与魔法密切相关的种族，他们为何无法驾驭食人妖巫毒的力量。对这些白皮肤的生灵而言，这简直难以置信。他们只好使用一种不纯的食人妖法术来增强他们的魔法力量。我想他们称其为「秘纹」。' WHERE entry=7596; /* Text0_0: Have you? Then you know how weak and pathetic the high elf version of troll magic was?$B$BThe high elves could not understand why a people with their magical affinity could not contend with the powers of troll voodoo. This was an inconceivable notion for the pale skins to understand. They were resigned to using the bastardized version of troll enchantments. I believe they called them \'Arcanum.\'$b */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='只要有正确的材料，赞札就能制造古老的食人妖附魔。这种魔法能帮助你打败哈卡和他的爪牙。$B$B我只要你帮我找2种东西。' WHERE entry=7597; /* Text0_0: Zanza can create the ancient troll enchantments with the right components. This magic will help you in defeating Hakkar and his minions.$B$BI only ask that you bring me three items. I admit that one of these items is not entirely necessary but I wish to purge the world of the high elf magic. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='首先你得从强大的哈卡副官:金度和血领主那里获得一个原始的雕像。$B$B第二是打孔的巫毒人偶。你可以在散落此地的霉运巫毒垃圾堆中找到。$B$B把这些物品都给我找来，我会为你进行一次强效的附魔!' WHERE entry=7598; /* Text0_0: The first is a primal token that must be taken from the most powerful of the Hakkari.$B$BThe second is a punctured voodoo doll. These can be found in the piles of refuse that litter this foul place. Look inside the jinxed Hoodoo piles.$B$BThe last is the high elven facsimile of troll magic known as the Arcanum. I do not know where they can be found.$B$BBring me all three and I will create a powerful enchantment for you! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='很抱歉，$c，但是在你变得更加强大之前，我不能让你去战歌峡谷送死。',Text0_1_loc4='很抱歉，$c，但是在你变得更加强大之前，我不能让你去战歌峡谷送死。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=7599; /* Text0_0: I am sorry $c, but you are not seasoned enough yet to enter Warsong Gulch. */ /* Text0_1: I am sorry $c, but you are not seasoned enough yet to enter Warsong Gulch. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='欢迎参加藏宝海湾钓鱼比赛，每周我们都会选出一位最好的渔夫，授予他钓鱼大师的称号!$B$B在下午2点到4点之间，大群的可口鱼会出现在荆棘谷海岸。如果你的浮标落在可口鱼鱼群中，你肯定能钓上一些的，这比在荆棘谷一般的海域垂钓要有效得多。' WHERE entry=7614; /* Text0_0: Welcome to the Booty Bay fishing contest where each week we choose the finest fisherman to be the Master Angler!$B$BBetween 2pm and 4pm schools of tastyfish will appear up and down the coast of Stranglethorn.  While fishing if your fishing bobber lands in a tastyfish school then you will catch something from the school rather than the normal stranglethorn fishing fare.$B */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你好，$c。我是拉斯塔哈的仆从，伊克萨尔。' WHERE entry=7615; /* Text0_0: Greetings, $c.  I am Exzhal, Servitor of Rastakhan. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='很抱歉，$c，但是在你变得更有经验之前，我不能让你去奥特兰克山谷送死。',Text0_1_loc4='很抱歉，$c，但是在你变得更有经验之前，我不能让你去奥特兰克山谷送死。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=7616; /* Text0_0: I am sorry $c, but you need to be more experienced before you can survive in Alterac Valley. */ /* Text0_1: I am sorry $c, but you need to be more experienced before you can survive in Alterac Valley. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='权力珍宝是古代古拉巴什帝国的遗物。赞达拉部族正在寻找它们─它们不仅有着极大的收藏价值，而且我们相信它们还蕴藏着远古帝国的魔法。$B$B你可以在祖尔格拉布找到三种权力珍宝:硬币、珠宝和原始神灵的物品。收集到一定数量之后，把这些东西交给我们，我们就会送你一些赞达拉最好的工艺制品。',Text0_1_loc4='权力珍宝是古代古拉巴什帝国的遗物。赞达拉部族正在寻找它们─它们不仅有着极大的收藏价值，而且我们相信它们还蕴藏着远古帝国的魔法。$B$B你可以在祖尔格拉布找到三种权力珍宝:硬币、珠宝和原始神灵的物品。收集到一定数量之后，把这些东西交给我们，我们就会送你一些赞达拉最好的工艺制品。' WHERE entry=7634; /* Text0_0: The Paragons of Power are remnants from the ancient Gurubashi Empire.  We Zandalar seek them - not only are they of tremendous collectible value to us, but we believe that they also hold latent signatures of magic used by the old Empire.$B$BYou\'ll more than likely discover three kinds of Paragons in Zul\'Gurub: coins, bijous, and primal items.  Bring them to us in the quantities that we seek, and you\'ll be rewarded with some of the finest items we Zandalar have ever crafted. */ /* Text0_1: The Paragons of Power are remnants from the ancient Gurubashi Empire.  We Zandalar seek them - not only are they of tremendous collectible value to us, but we believe that they also hold latent signatures of magic used by the old Empire.$B$BYou\'ll more than likely discover three kinds of Paragons in Zul\'Gurub: coins, bijous, and primal items.  Bring them to us in the quantities that we seek, and you\'ll be rewarded with some of the finest items we Zandalar have ever crafted. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='石板上篆刻着古老的图案，上面的文字蕴涵着可怕的力量，但是你无法理解它们的意思。' WHERE entry=7635; /* Text0_0: The markings of this tablet show ancient diagrams and hold dire words of power, but their meaning is inscrutable to you. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='石板上篆刻着古老的图案，上面的文字蕴涵着可怕的力量，用来制造古拉巴什疯狂魔精……' WHERE entry=7636; /* Text0_0: The markings on this tablet show ancient diagrams and dire words of power, used to create  Gurubashi Mojo Madness... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='在我看来，钓鱼的美妙之处在於其缓慢的节奏。人们可以在钓鱼的过程中思考、回想过去和计画未来。$B$B哦，当然这也是用来大醉一场的绝佳理由。' WHERE entry=7638; /* Text0_0: If you ask me, the best part about fishing is its slow pace.  It gives one time to think, to reflect on past events and to plan for future ones.$B$BOh, and it\'s also a great excuse to drink.  Heavily. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='再次感谢你找回了我的幸运卷尺，$N。这东西能帮我捕到更大的鱼呢!' WHERE entry=7639; /* Text0_0: Thanks again for returning my lucky measuring tape, $N.  I swear it helps me catch bigger fish! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你需要一种特殊的臭泥鱼诱饵来捕捉加兹兰卡。这些鱼饵是我亲自制作的!$B$B但是除了鱼饵之外，你还需要臭泥鱼……你得把臭泥鱼放入诱饵，让它充满臭味!$B$B将做好的诱饵放到祖尔格拉布中的帕格渔场……然后就坐下来喝酒等待……你无需等太久，因为加兹兰卡肯定会迫不及待地上钩!' WHERE entry=7640; /* Text0_0: To catch Gahz\'ranka, you\'ll need a special Mudskunk lure.  I make \'em myself!$B$BBut you need more than just the lure; you need some mudskunks too... you need to place them in the lure to give it a rank old smell!$B$BWhen you have the mudskunks, throw the lure off Pagle\'s Point in Zul\'Gurub... and then grab a drink and wait... but not too long, because Gahz\'ranka is sure to come a\'stomping! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='很抱歉，$c，在你变得更加强大之前，我不能让你去阿拉希盆地送死。',Text0_1_loc4='很抱歉，$c，在你变得更加强大之前，我不能让你去阿拉希盆地送死。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=7642; /* Text0_0: I am sorry $c, but you need to be more powerful before I can allow you to enter Arathi Basin. */ /* Text0_1: I am sorry $c, but you need to be more powerful before I can allow you to enter Arathi Basin. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='钢铁之血格里雷克$B$B漫游者。愿他的力量和对战争的渴望生生不息。$B$B格里雷克正在遥远的地方徘徊。总有一天，他会回来的……' WHERE entry=7643; /* Text0_0: Gri\'lek, of the Iron Blood$B$BThe wanderer.  May his strength and lust for battle pierce the ages.  $B$BGri\'lek now dwells far from here.  One day, he may return... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='去勇者大厅找污染者迪兹・斯诺班，他会帮助你进入阿拉希盆地的。',Text0_1_loc4='去勇者大厅找污染者迪兹・斯诺班，他会帮助你进入阿拉希盆地的。',Text1_0_loc4='去勇者大厅找污染者迪兹·斯诺班，他会帮助你进入阿拉希盆地的。',Text1_1_loc4='去勇者大厅找污染者迪兹·斯诺班，他会帮助你进入阿拉希盆地的。' WHERE entry=7644; /* Text0_0: Go to the Hall of the Brave.  You will find The Defiler, Deze Snowbane there to assist you in getting to Arathi Basin. */ /* Text0_1: Go to the Hall of the Brave.  You will find The Defiler, Deze Snowbane there to assist you in getting to Arathi Basin. */ /* Text1_0: You wish to help the Forsaken with their fight against the humans in Arathi Basin?  Then go to the Hall of the Brave and speak with Deze Snowbane. */ /* Text1_1: You wish to help the Forsaken with their fight against the humans in Arathi Basin?  Then go to the Hall of the Brave and speak with Deze Snowbane. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='臭泥鱼是一种散发着特殊臭味的鱼，它们生活在热带水域中。祖利安臭泥鱼则是其中最臭的一种，只有在祖尔格拉布的水域中才能找到。$B$B我想一定是祖力安臭泥鱼引来了加兹兰卡，尽管食人妖会告诉你它是食人妖膜拜的众多神灵之一，但是……$B$B相信自己─用祖利安臭泥鱼制成的诱饵去捕捉加兹兰卡吧，那家伙肯定会上钩的!' WHERE entry=7645; /* Text0_0: Mudskunks are a particularly smelly breed of fish that likes tropical waters.  The Zulian Mudskunk - the smelliest of them all, can only be found in the steamy waters of Zul\'Gurub.$B$BThe Zulian Mudskunks are what I believe attracted Gahz\'ranka to the place, though trolls will probably tell you he\'s one of their gods...$B$BBelieve what you like, but mark me - fill one of my lures with Zulian Mudskunks and that old boy will come, for sure! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='去圣殿区找玛洛维尔爵士。',Text0_1_loc4='去圣殿区找玛洛维尔爵士。',Text1_0_loc4='去圣殿区找玛洛维尔爵士。',Text1_1_loc4='去圣殿区找玛洛维尔爵士。' WHERE entry=7646; /* Text0_0: You go Royal Quarter.  See Sir Malory Wheeler.  Him scary. */ /* Text0_1: You go Royal Quarter.  See Sir Malory Wheeler.  Him scary. */ /* Text1_0: Arathi Basin place to take from soft humans.  Sir Malory Wheeler send you there. */ /* Text1_1: Arathi Basin place to take from soft humans.  Sir Malory Wheeler send you there. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='去灵魂高地下面的预见之池找马丁・林塞。他会帮助你转至阿拉希盆地。',Text0_1_loc4='去灵魂高地下面的预见之池找马丁・林塞。他会帮助你转至阿拉希盆地。',Text1_0_loc4='去灵魂高地下面的预见之池找马丁·林塞。他会帮助你前往阿拉希盆地。',Text1_1_loc4='去灵魂高地下面的预见之池找马丁·林塞。他会帮助你前往阿拉希盆地。' WHERE entry=7648; /* Text0_0: You may seek out Martin Lindsey inside the Pools of Vision, underneath the Spirit Rise.  He will assist you on your way to Arathi Basin. */ /* Text0_1: You may seek out Martin Lindsey inside the Pools of Vision, underneath the Spirit Rise.  He will assist you on your way to Arathi Basin. */ /* Text1_0: You wish to aid The Defilers in their fight against The League of Arathor in Arathi Basin?  Very well, you should ask Martin Lindsey for his assistance then.  Look for him in the Pools of Vision. */ /* Text1_1: You wish to aid The Defilers in their fight against The League of Arathor in Arathi Basin?  Very well, you should ask Martin Lindsey for his assistance then.  Look for him in the Pools of Vision. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='在阿拉希盆地跟被遗忘者作战的人类需要你的帮助。去武器大厅找他们的代表杜纳尔・奥斯古德谈谈。',Text0_1_loc4='在阿拉希盆地跟被遗忘者作战的人类需要你的帮助。去武器大厅找他们的代表杜纳尔・奥斯古德谈谈。',Text1_0_loc4='在阿拉希盆地跟被遗忘者作战的人类需要你的帮助。去武器大厅找他们的代表杜纳尔·奥斯古德谈谈。',Text1_1_loc4='在阿拉希盆地跟被遗忘者作战的人类需要你的帮助。去武器大厅找他们的代表杜纳尔·奥斯古德谈谈。' WHERE entry=7649; /* Text0_0: The humans are in need of your assistance in their fight against The Forsaken at Arathi Basin.  Go to the Hall of Arms and speak with their representative, Donal Osgood. */ /* Text0_1: The humans are in need of your assistance in their fight against The Forsaken at Arathi Basin.  Go to the Hall of Arms and speak with their representative, Donal Osgood. */ /* Text1_0: The League of Arathor is trying to reclaim their ancestral holdings in Arathi Basin from the Forsaken.  If you would aid them $N speak to Donal Osgood in the Hall of Arms. */ /* Text1_1: The League of Arathor is trying to reclaim their ancestral holdings in Arathi Basin from the Forsaken.  If you would aid them $N speak to Donal Osgood in the Hall of Arms. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='阿拉索联军在阿拉希盆地所做的一切令人敬佩。可惜亡灵憎恶和他们的部落盟友挡住了去路。去暴风要塞国王的觎见室找到赫塔希姆吧，她会帮你转至阿拉希盆地的。',Text0_1_loc4='阿拉索联军在阿拉希盆地所做的一切令人敬佩。可惜亡灵憎恶和他们的部落盟友挡住了去路。去暴风要塞国王的觎见室找到赫塔希姆吧，她会帮你转至阿拉希盆地的。',Text1_0_loc4='阿拉索联军在阿拉希盆地所做的一切令人敬佩。可惜亡灵憎恶和他们的部落盟友挡住了去路。去暴风要塞国王的觎见室找到赫塔希姆吧，她会帮你前往阿拉希盆地的。',Text1_1_loc4='阿拉索联军在阿拉希盆地所做的一切令人敬佩。可惜亡灵憎恶和他们的部落盟友挡住了去路。去暴风要塞国王的觎见室找到赫塔希姆吧，她会帮你前往阿拉希盆地的。' WHERE entry=7650; /* Text0_0: In the King\'s audience chamber you will find the Lady Hoteshem.  She can assist you in getting to Arathi Basin where The League of Arathor is in need of assistance against The Defilers. */ /* Text0_1: In the King\'s audience chamber you will find the Lady Hoteshem.  She can assist you in getting to Arathi Basin where The League of Arathor is in need of assistance against The Defilers. */ /* Text1_0: It\'s admirable what The League of Arathor is attempting to do in Arathi Basin.  Too bad those undead abominations and their Horde friends are standing in the way.  Head over to Stormwind Keep.  Lady Hoteshem awaits you in the King\'s audience chamber.  She can help you to get to Arathi Basin. */ /* Text1_1: It\'s admirable what The League of Arathor is attempting to do in Arathi Basin.  Too bad those undead abominations and their Horde friends are standing in the way.  Head over to Stormwind Keep.  Lady Hoteshem awaits you in the King\'s audience chamber.  She can help you to get to Arathi Basin. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='(兽人语)你好，$c!你准备好要参加战歌峡谷的战斗了吗?为了部落!' WHERE entry=7652; /* Text0_0: Throm\'ka $c!  Are you ready to fight for the Horde at Warsong Gulch? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='$N，银翼哨兵必须被消灭!你做好进入战歌峡谷的准备了吗?' WHERE entry=7654; /* Text0_0: $N, the Silverwing Sentinels must be crushed!  Are you ready for Warsong Gulch? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你是来帮助我们在战歌峡谷作战的吗?为了部落，$c!' WHERE entry=7655; /* Text0_0: Are you here to fight for us at Warsong Gulch?  Lok\'tar Ogar $c! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='$g小夥子:姑娘;，你准备好动身前往奥特兰克山谷了吗?让部落尝尝失败的滋味!' WHERE entry=7657; /* Text0_0: Aye $g lad : lass; are ye ready to head to Alterac Valley and give the Horde a taste o\' what they been asking for? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='$N，你对我们在奥特兰克山谷的处境有什麽想法?你准备好跟霜狼氏族作战了吗?' WHERE entry=7658; /* Text0_0: $N, have ye any idea o\' what we\'re up against in Alterac Valley?  Are ye ready to fight the Frostwolf Clan? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='必须杀死雷矛卫兵!准备好要到奥特兰克山谷了吗，$c?' WHERE entry=7659; /* Text0_0: The Stormpike Guard must be destroyed!  Ready for Alterac Valley $c? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我们在奥特兰克山谷的军队需要运用谋略才能获胜，$c。你看起来是个不错的领导者。' WHERE entry=7661; /* Text0_0: Our forces in Alterac Valley need wisdom to achieve victory $c.  You look like the one to lead them. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='希望你是来奥特兰克山谷作战的，$N。我们会竭尽所能，利用一切援助。' WHERE entry=7662; /* Text0_0: I hope that you are here to go to Alterac Valley $N.  We can use all o\' the help that we can get. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='阿拉希盆地曾经是我们的家园，有了你的帮助，我们会收复失地的!你愿意帮助我们吗，$c?' WHERE entry=7664; /* Text0_0: Arathi Basin was once our home, and will be again with your aid!  Will you help us $c? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我希望你是来帮助我们从污染者手中夺回阿拉希盆地的。你说是吗，$N?' WHERE entry=7665; /* Text0_0: I hope that you\'re here to help us take back Arathi Basin from The Defilers.  What do you say $N? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你认为你能摧毁阿拉索联军吗，$c?希望如此。你究竟想要干什麽呢，还是你根本就是来浪费我的时间的?' WHERE entry=7667; /* Text0_0: You think you have what it takes to destroy The League of Arathor, $c?  I hope so.  What is it that you want, or are you simply here to waste my time? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='看看四周，$c。你身边的朋友并不多，我想你需要证明自己的价值。嗯，或许我应该同意你帮助我们在阿拉希盆地作战。你愿意吗?' WHERE entry=7668; /* Text0_0: Look around you $c.  You are in rare company to be certain, yet still I think you need to prove yourself.  Hmm, perhaps I shall allow you to aid us in our cause at Arathi Basin.  Would you like that? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='钢铁之血格里雷克$B$B漫游者。愿他的力量和对战争的渴望生生不息。$B$B格里雷克就在疯狂之缘那边……' WHERE entry=7669; /* Text0_0: Gri\'lek, of the Iron Blood$B$BThe wanderer.  May his strength and lust for battle pierce the ages.$B$BGri\'lek now lingers near the edge of madness... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='织梦者哈札拉尔。$B$B他拥有梦魇的力量，愿他的敌人永远沉睡。$B$B哈札拉尔正在遥远的地方徘徊。总有一天，他会回来的……' WHERE entry=7670; /* Text0_0: Hazza\'rah, the Dreamweaver.$B$BHis is the power of nightmares, and may his foes ever sleep.  $B$BHazza\'rah now dwells far from here.  One day, he may return... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='千刃之王雷纳塔基。$B$B痛苦是他的生命。恐怖是他的夥伴。愿他早日重返世间。$B$B雷纳塔基就在疯狂之缘那边。' WHERE entry=7673; /* Text0_0: Renataki, of the Thousand Blades.$B$BPain is his lifeblood.  Fear, his ally.  May he one day return and bring joyous bloodshed with him.$B$BRenataki now dwells near the edge of madness. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='『雷巫』乌苏雷。$B$B他拥有天空、雨水和大地的力量。愿他再次统治古拉巴什。$B$B乌苏雷正在遥远的地方徘徊。总有一天，他会回来的……' WHERE entry=7674; /* Text0_0: Wushoolay, the Storm Witch.$B$BHer power is the power of the sky, the rain, and the shattered earth.  May she once again reign mother to the Gurubashi.  $B$BWushoolay now dwells far from here.  One day, she may return... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='嘿嘿嘿!我是来这里推广荆棘谷的超棒钓鱼锦标赛的，不过你首先得有足够的生存能力在这里活下去，然后还需要足以在这里钓鱼的精湛技巧。$B$B当你更符合以上条件的时候再回到这里来吧!' WHERE entry=7676; /* Text0_0: Hey Hey Hey!  I am here to promote a fabulous fishing tournament in Stranglethorn but you need to be tough enough to survive there and have enough skill in fishing to fish those waters.$B$BCome back later when you are more qualified!$B$B */
