UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='当你将爱之硬币给人民，你将收到他们不同的礼物作为回礼。有些礼物你会想留着自己用，但其他的就可以收集在一起送给你最喜欢的英雄!拜访丘比特·传播者把礼物交给他。$B$B丘比特就在伯瓦尔，麦格尼和泰兰妲附近。',Text0_1_loc4='当你将爱之硬币给人民，你将收到他们不同的礼物作为回礼。有些礼物你会想留着自己用，但其他的就可以收集在一起送给你最喜欢的英雄!拜访丘比特·传播者把礼物交给他。$B$B丘比特就在伯瓦尔，麦格尼和泰兰妲附近。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=8317; /* Text0_0: When you give love tokens to townsfolk, you\'ll receive different gifts in return.  Some of those you\'ll want to keep and use, but others can be bundled together and given to your favorite hero!  Visit Kwee Q. Peddlefeet to turn them in.$B$BKwee can be found near Bolvar, Magni, or Tyrande. */ /* Text0_1: When you give love tokens to townsfolk, you\'ll receive different gifts in return.  Some of those you\'ll want to keep and use, but others can be bundled together and given to your favorite hero!  Visit Kwee Q. Peddlefeet to turn them in.$B$BKwee can be found near Bolvar, Magni, or Tyrande. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我注定永远被束缚在这个受诅咒的世界。你的慾望是什麽，凡人?' WHERE entry=8318; /* Text0_0: I am bound eternally to this cursed world. What is it you desire, mortal? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='当你将爱之硬币给人民，你将收到他们不同的礼物作为回礼。有些礼物你会想留着自己用，但其他的就可以收集在一起送给你最喜欢的英雄!拜访丘比特·传播者把礼物交给他。$B$B传播者就在凯恩，希瓦娜斯和索尔附近。',Text0_1_loc4='当你将爱之硬币给人民，你将收到他们不同的礼物作为回礼。有些礼物你会想留着自己用，但其他的就可以收集在一起送给你最喜欢的英雄!拜访丘比特·传播者把礼物交给他。$B$B传播者就在凯恩，希瓦娜斯和索尔附近。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=8319; /* Text0_0: When you give love tokens to townsfolk, you\'ll receive different gifts in return.  Some of those you\'ll want to keep and use, but others can be bundled together and given to your favorite hero!  Visit Kwee Q. Peddlefeet to turn them in.$B$BKwee can be found near Cairne, Sylvanas and Thrall. */ /* Text0_1: When you give love tokens to townsfolk, you\'ll receive different gifts in return.  Some of those you\'ll want to keep and use, but others can be bundled together and given to your favorite hero!  Visit Kwee Q. Peddlefeet to turn them in.$B$BKwee can be found near Cairne, Sylvanas and Thrall. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='这本秘典的内容就像潮水不断流出。你觉得好像你脑中的思绪被榨乾并被这本书消化掉。' WHERE entry=8321; /* Text0_0: The content on the pages of this tome appear to be in constant flux. You feel as if your thoughts are being bled from your mind and consumed by the book. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='索尔让我进入他领地中的圣域是对我释出相当大的善意。无论如何，我不求久留。给我们的领导者带来任何麻烦都是极大的侮辱。' WHERE entry=8332; /* Text0_0: Thrall has shown great kindness in granting me sanctuary within his domain.  I do not wish to overstay my welcome, at any rate.  It would be a great dishonor if I brought any trouble to our leader. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='丧命的危险是我常碰到的事。但失去亚希达是我不能容忍的事，就算我死了也是一样。' WHERE entry=8334; /* Text0_0: Losing my life was a danger I had come to terms with.  Losing Ysida is something I cannot endure, even after my own death. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你好，朋友!想不想看一些精华电容器?或是精细的全方位鬼灵吸收器?' WHERE entry=8335; /* Text0_0: Greetings, friend!  Can I interest you in some ectoplasmic capacitors?  Or perhaps a nice omni-directional spectral assimilator? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='什么事？你没看见我很忙吗？' WHERE entry=8336; /* Text0_0: What now?  Can\'t you see I\'m rather busy? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='当碰到危害这个世界的事物时，我们圣光兄弟会相较之下是不会手下留情的。' WHERE entry=8351; /* Text0_0: Watch your step, $r. We of the Brotherhood of the Light are not as lenient as our brethren when it comes to meting justice to those that would do this world wrong.$B$BWoe unto those that would anger Korfax.$B$BNow if you have no business with me or the other members of the Brotherhood, please leave so that we may continue our meeting. $B */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='巫妖王想让自己名扬四海。绝不能让他得逞。' WHERE entry=8352; /* Text0_0: The Lich King is attempting to make his presence known in our world. This must not be allowed to occur.$B */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='头衔是骗人的。你了解我后，你就知道我是个好人。' WHERE entry=8355; /* Text0_0: The title is misleading. I\'m really a very nice person once you get to know me. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='他们都派了我的兄弟，洛克希，到这个集会。他连他的猎犬都顾不好了，更别说有资格代表血色十字军。' WHERE entry=8356; /* Text0_0: They almost sent my brother, Loksey, to this gathering. He cannot even take care of his hounds, let alone represent the Scarlet Crusade in a competent manner. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我一直在期...$B$B<林布拉特咳嗽。>$B$B不好意思，老毛病。我是陶土议会的林布拉特。' WHERE entry=8357; /* Text0_0: I\'ve been expec...$B$B<Rimblat coughs.>$B$BExcuse me, old habit. I am Rimblat of the Earthen Ring. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你要什麽，鼠辈?知道为什麽大家都叫我施怒者?在我证明之前，你赶快给我滚。' WHERE entry=8359; /* Text0_0: What is it that you want, lemming? Get out of my sight before you find out why I am known as the Wrathcaster. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='第一套无畏护甲是专为血色大领主莫格莱尼订做的。完成时，大领主觉得自己活生生像是从冥府来的恶魔。$B$B没错，这的确是个绝佳机会亲见莫格莱尼精神饱满的率领血色十字军，齐声呐喊、高举挥舞着灰烬使者，眼看另一端敌军於燃火飞尘之中在他的双脚下慌张撤离。' WHERE entry=8363; /* Text0_0: The first suit of Dreadnaught armor was made exclusively for the Scarlet Highlord Mograine. Whilst donning the full suit, the Highlord looked himself to be a demon from the depths of the Nether.$B$BAye, \'twas quite a sight to behold as Mograine would wade into a hundred Scourge, Ashbringer held high, and come out on the other side in a cloud of dust and flames - enemies left in ashes beneath his feet." */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='在饱受争议的死亡事件之后，洛丹伦的骑士与战士为了向他们倒下的英雄表示敬意，纷纷都穿起类似的战袍。而莫格莱尼的死对科尔苏加德是伟大的胜利，最后殉难的结果要一直到战争结束才知分晓。$B$B一王倒下，他强必崛起…' WHERE entry=8364; /* Text0_0: It was not until after his controversial death that the knights and warriors of Lordaeron would wear similarly fashioned suits in honor of their fallen hero. While the death of Mograine was a great victory for Kel\'Thuzad, the resulting martyrdom would be felt until the end of the war.$B$BWhere one did fall, many would rise... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我就是你口中的资本家，$r。' WHERE entry=8366; /* Text0_0: I\'m what you call a capitalist, $r. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='喔，哈罗…嗯，你是?$B$B不要紧，是什麽风把你吹来我在这美丽乡村的离家之园啊?',Text0_1_loc4='无论萨尔是否存在，破碎之手氏族的秩序都将延续下去。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=8374; /* Text0_0: Oh, hello there.. um, what\'s your name?$B$BNo matter, what brings you to my home-away-from-home here out in the beautiful countryside? */ /* Text0_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text0: */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='嗨，$c。想必你们一定玩得很开心吧?你们觉得的派对好玩吗?希望我们派对上的东西都够供应。饮料跟开胃点心如果不够就是派对的致命伤啊，对吧?$B$B嗯，好啦，我要去招待其他宾客罗。尽兴玩。' WHERE entry=8375; /* Text0_0: Hello, $c. I trust that you are enjoying youself? What do you think of the party? I do so hope that we aren\'t running out of anything. Nothing kills a fete faster than running out of drinks and hors d\'oeuvres, wouldn\'t you say?$B$BYes, well, I must be about attending to my other guests. Do enjoy your stay. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='这就是权力，低能儿。<麦特斯眼眸加深。>$B$B这些傻瓜派了像你这样的白痴到纳克萨玛斯，取回玷污的护甲以便净化它，重组零件恢复昔日光采。$B$B<麦特斯啐了一口。>就是这种愚蠢至极的想法让我反胃想吐。$B$B我也去寻找护甲，我要找玷污以及被亵渎最深的护甲。' WHERE entry=8398; /* Text0_0: It is power, imbecile.$B$B<Mataus\'s eyes darken.>$B$BThese fools send idiots like you into Naxxramas to retrieve desecrated armor so that they may purify it and restore the pieces to their former glory.$B$B<Mataus spits.>$B$BJust the thought of such utter stupidity brings the bile up to my throat.$B$BI too seek that armor, but in its most foul and desecrated form. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我不会装模作样，蛆虫。这种黑暗物品所支配的力量可以把我们两个都摧毁。这就是为什麽价格如此高昂的原因。如果我就要死了，也会是个富翁。$B$B你死了我也不会对你吐一口豺狼人的口水，照我的话做就对了。把我要的东西带来，我们就能双方受惠 - 或者死;我已经解释过了……' WHERE entry=8399; /* Text0_0: I make no pretenses, maggot. The darkness such items hold could very well destroy the both of us. That is why the price is so high. If I\'m going to die, it\'s going to be as a rich man.$B$BAnd I don\'t give an ounce of gnoll spit how you die, only that you do as I ask. Bring me what I require and we will both benefit - or die, but I\'ve already explained this... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='您好，旅行者。我奉命在此接待主人的贵客，所有携带着卡拉赞钥匙的人都会被奉为上宾。如果您有什么疑问，请尽管开口。有什么需要我帮忙的吗？' WHERE entry=8401; /* Text0_0: Greetings, travelers. I have been instructed to treat any bearer of a key to Karazhan as an honored guest of the Master. Feel free to ask any questions you wish of me. How may I assist you? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我们对那些失心者太仁慈了，要我说，我们应该拔出剑刺向他们。$B$B他们在阳帆港的大胆行径是不可饶恕的。' WHERE entry=8402; /* Text0_0: We\'re too merciful with the Wretched.  We ought to drive a sword through each of them.$B$BTheir boldness in Sunsail Anchorage is unpardonable. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='啊，主人的贵客。希望您在这里没有到处乱走。' WHERE entry=8404; /* Text0_0: Ah, guests of the Master. I hope you\'ve been watching your step in here. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='这些该死的歹徒！我能指望你助我一臂之力吗？' WHERE entry=8406; /* Text0_0: Damn all these vermin! I don\'t suppose you could help me with this situation? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我不想教牛头人骑乘迅猛龙。',Text0_1_loc4='我不想教牛头人骑乘迅猛龙。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=8407; /* Text0_0: I cannot be teachin\' a Tauren to ride a Raptor. */ /* Text0_1: I cannot be teachin\' a Tauren to ride a Raptor. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='那些污秽的野兽充斥此地。$B$B如果你喜欢在户外狩猎的话，你可以在病木林跟恐惧谷寻获牠们大部分的踪迹，也请特别留意恶蛛隧道。牠们也可能出没在东瘟疫之地的天谴军团紮营处。$B$B假如你热衷於地城，你在斯坦索姆会发现更多牠们的踪影，另外，在通灵学院可以找到一些通灵魔。' WHERE entry=8408; /* Text0_0: Those filthy beasts are all over the place.$B$BIf you prefer hunting outdoors, you\'ll find most of them around Plaguewood and Terrordale, with a good concentration of them in the Terrorweb tunnel. They are also likely to appear at almost any Scourge encampment in the Eastern Plaguelands.$B$BIf you\'re a hearty dungeon crawler, you\'ll find a good lot of them in Stratholme and a few of the necrofiend variety in Scholomance. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你是笨蛋吗?遗失了你回程时那堆散乱路旁的骷髅类生物?<洛汉叹气。>$B$B如果你是户外型的人，你可在东、西瘟疫之地找到骷髅生物。相信我，你不能搞丢牠们－如果他们可以的话，他们一定不会放过你。倘若你是地城冒险型，斯坦索姆和通灵学院正是寻找为骨头碎片的地方。' WHERE entry=8409; /* Text0_0: Are you daft? Did you miss the BONY SKELETAL CREATURES littering the landscape on your way over here?$B$B<Rohan sighs.>$B$BIf you\'re the outdoor type, you\'ll find skeletal creatures all over both the Western and Eastern Plaguelands. Trust me, you can\'t miss \'em - they certainly won\'t miss you if they get the chance.$B$BIf you\'re a dungeon type, Stratholme and Scholomance are definitely the place to be for bone fragments. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='没有什麽是比翱翔天空更自由的事，$c。有什麽需要我帮忙的吗?' WHERE entry=8411; /* Text0_0: No greater freedom than to soar through the skies, $c. What can I do for you today? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='哈罗，朋友。需要什麽吗?',Text0_1_loc4='无论萨尔是否存在，破碎之手氏族的秩序都将延续下去。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=8412; /* Text0_0: Hello, friend. How may I be of service to you today? */ /* Text0_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text0: */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='这是很严肃的问题?你真的不知道?$B$B如果你是懦弱型的深怕脏了手，你可以在燃烧平原与灼热峡谷，找找生物身上的黑铁碎块。$B$B如果你是嗜血如命的冒险型，你到黑石塔和黑石深渊的地城，会发现有数以万计的黑铁碎块等着你。' WHERE entry=8415; /* Text0_0: Is this a serious question? You really don\'t know?$B$BIf you are the cowardly sort, afraid to get their hands too dirty, you will find Dark Iron scraps on the creatures in the Burning Steppes and Searing Gorge.$B$BIf you\'re the bloodthirsty adventuring type, the dungeons of Blackrock Spire and Blackrock Depths hold quite a large supply of the scraps. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='$C，看看他们对我们可爱的土地做了什麽。天谴军团一定要被消灭!' WHERE entry=8417; /* Text0_0: $C, look what they\'ve done to our beloved land. The Scourge must be destroyed! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我…不行了…我失败了。' WHERE entry=8419; /* Text0_0: Who are you?  I feel... so... cold. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我没那时间跟你玩猜谜游戏，$r。说出你的来意，然后消失在我眼前吧!' WHERE entry=8422; /* Text0_0: I\'m far too busy to be playing \'guess the smell\' with you, $r. State your business or get out of my sight! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='高阶执行官和阿莉法娜奥丝夫人让我在哪边枯等，但我真的没时间!我朋友正在垂死边缘挣扎啊，$c!',Text0_1_loc4='无论萨尔是否存在，破碎之手氏族的秩序都将延续下去。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=8423; /* Text0_0: The high executor and Dame Auriferous are making me wait, but I don\'t have time for this! My friends are out there dying, $c! */ /* Text0_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text0: */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='有时候我觉得我好像永远也无法回归到简单正常的生活来效忠阿莉法娜奥丝夫人。我永远也离不开战争。$B$B幸好总是有像你这样的人热切於见到奎尔萨拉斯回到它原来的样貌。摧毁天谴军团，$c!不管你在何方都要摧毁他们!',Text0_1_loc4='无论萨尔是否存在，破碎之手氏族的秩序都将延续下去。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=8425; /* Text0_0: Sometimes it feels like I\'ll never go back to being a simple functionary in service to Dame Auriferous. I\'m not cut out for war.$B$BThankfully there are those like you who burn to see Quel\'Thalas restored to its former beauty. Crush the Scourge, $c! Crush them wherever you can! */ /* Text0_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text0: */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我得到消息说你帮助了游侠瓦兰娜和派往塞布索雷的上尉。$B$B感谢你，$c。我想我现在应该回远行者营地了。' WHERE entry=8428; /* Text0_0: I received word that you were able to help Ranger Valanna and the lieutenant at Zeb\'Sora.$B$BThank you, $c. I suppose I should make my way back to Farstrider Enclave now. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='是什麽风把你吹到这里来，$c?',Text0_1_loc4='无论萨尔是否存在，破碎之手氏族的秩序都将延续下去。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=8429; /* Text0_0: What business brings you here, $c? */ /* Text0_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text0: */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='啊，你好，$r。如你所见，我还没开始营业。所以，如果你不介意，我要先忙了。',Text0_1_loc4='无论萨尔是否存在，破碎之手氏族的秩序都将延续下去。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=8431; /* Text0_0: Ah, hello there, $r. As you can see, I\'m not open for business quite yet. Now, if you\'ll excuse me, I\'m very busy. */ /* Text0_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text0: */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='很高兴再见到你，$c。不，真的。你是我会在这里赚钱，掌管一切的原因。$B$B那麽，你今天想跟我买些什麽?' WHERE entry=8432; /* Text0_0: Such a delight to see you again, $c. No, really. You\'re the reason that I\'m making money here, hand over fist.$B$BNow, what can I sell to you today? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='该是部落和联盟注意北裂境和巫妖王入侵的时候了。最近这些日子，整个卡林多和东部王国都遭到攻击。你是否会开始全副武装保护你的土地免於他们的摧毁呢?' WHERE entry=8434; /* Text0_0: The time has come for Horde and Alliance to look towards the north and the invasion of the Scourge. In recent days, territories across Kalimdor and the Eastern Kindgoms have come under attack. Will you take up arms to save your land from destruction at their hands? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='剑而已，不用害怕。要小心羊肉才是真的！' WHERE entry=8435; /* Text0_0: Don\'t be afraid of the sword, nubling. It\'s the mutton that gets ya! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='恐怖的事情是，发生在那些骡身上的事…这次失败，梅兹一定需要我的掩护。' WHERE entry=8438; /* Text0_0: Terrible thing, what happened to them mules... Metz is gonna have my hide for this failure. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你是援军吗?夜精灵已被击溃了!',Text0_1_loc4='无论萨尔是否存在，破碎之手氏族的秩序都将延续下去。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=8441; /* Text0_0: Are you the reinforcements? The night elves have been routed! */ /* Text0_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text0: */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你将安欧恩的月水晶能源关闭是一件好事，$c!如果你想为我这里的研究提供一点贡献欢迎你随时过来。' WHERE entry=8442; /* Text0_0: Good thing that you deactivated the moon crystal at An\'owyn when you did, $c! Come around any time you feel like pitching in with my research here. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='在这样的情况之下我要怎麽工作?!还有全部这些恶心的被遗忘者!我为安宁地和奎尔萨拉斯悲叹!' WHERE entry=8445; /* Text0_0: How can I work under these conditions?! And all of these disgusting Forsaken around here! I weep for Tranquillien and Quel\'Thalas! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='嗯……你想要什么，$r？你没看到我这里正忙着吗？' WHERE entry=8446; /* Text0_0: Yes... what do you want, $r? Can\'t you see I am busy here? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='$R，报告!你带了什麽重要的消息来?快点说吧……我和阿莉法娜奥丝夫人正在做策略的商讨。',Text0_1_loc4='无论萨尔是否存在，破碎之手氏族的秩序都将延续下去。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=8447; /* Text0_0: $R, report! What news of significance do you bring? Be quick about your business... Dame Auriferous and I are in the middle of a strategic discussion. */ /* Text0_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text0: */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我们的商队大约一天出队2次，万一天谴军团又去阻止迪笛儿，还有要送往前线的那些骡，那到时我就会被指责。这还是我前所未见最疯狂的事情。但愿我们有英勇的冒险精神能保护这运送过程...' WHERE entry=8452; /* Text0_0: Our caravans go out \'bout twice a day, but I\'ll be damned if the Scourge haven\'t gone out of their way to stop Didier and his mules from getting shipments to the front lines. Craziest thing I\'ve ever seen. If only we had the heroic adventurin\' types to help protect the shipments... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我事情太多，时间根本不够用，$r!拜托，别挡我路。',Text0_1_loc4='我事情太多，时间根本不够用，$r!拜托，别挡我路。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=8454; /* Text0_0: I\'ve got too much to do and not enough time to do it in, $r! Please, get out of my way. */ /* Text0_1: I\'ve got too much to do and not enough time to do it in, $r! Please, get out of my way. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我事情太多，时间根本不够用，$r!拜托，别挡我路。$B$B万一你被蛆虫粘液跟腐烂食屍鬼感染的话，我有能力治疗各种疾病。',Text0_1_loc4='我事情太多，时间根本不够用，$r!拜托，别挡我路。$B$B万一你被蛆虫粘液跟腐烂食屍鬼感染的话，我有能力治疗各种疾病。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=8455; /* Text0_0: I\'ve got too much to do and not enough time to do it in, $r! Please, get out of my way.$B$BIf you\'re infected with the maggot slime or ghoul rot, I might be able to help you. */ /* Text0_1: I\'ve got too much to do and not enough time to do it in, $r! Please, get out of my way.$B$BIf you\'re infected with the maggot slime or ghoul rot, I might be able to help you. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='<当你将恢复药剂倒入他嘴里后血精灵很快恢复意识。>$B$B我欠你一命，$c。没有你的帮忙，我就得屈服於天谴军团的痛苦折磨了。' WHERE entry=8456; /* Text0_0: <The blood elf quickly regains consciousness as you pour the draught into his mouth.>$B$BI owe you my life, $c.  Without your help I would\'ve succumbed to the Scourge\'s painful torture. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='<血精灵倒在地上看起来变的很迟缓。>',Text0_1_loc4='无论萨尔是否存在，破碎之手氏族的秩序都将延续下去。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=8457; /* Text0_0: <The blood elf lies on the floor in some manner of induced torpor.> */ /* Text0_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text0: */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你好，$R。我是辛多雷——也就是血精灵一族的大使欧诺·炎伤。我忠心希望我们与部落新建立起来的友好关系对双方都有好处。' WHERE entry=8458; /* Text0_0: Greetings, $r.  I am Ambassador Sunsorrow of the sin\'dorei, or blood elves as we are commonly known.  I have high hopes that this new bond between us and the Horde will be mutually beneficial. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='<血精灵毫无生气地躺在桌上。虽然他还有呼吸，但他明显地中了高效的镇静毒素。>' WHERE entry=8461; /* Text0_0: <The blood elf lies limp on the table.  While he\'s still breathing, he appears to have been the victim of potent sedative toxins.> */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你好，$r。我是听从高阶执行官的建议来到这里。我有信心只要我们团结一致就能打造一个前所未有的强大部落并消灭所有的天谴军团威胁。' WHERE entry=8462; /* Text0_0: Well met, $r. I am here as a resource of advice for the High Executor to make use of as he will. I am confident that together we can forge the Horde into something that is even stronger than before and turn back the Scourge menace once and for all! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='<当恢复药剂开始生效瓦尼司激烈地咳嗽。>$B$B谢谢你救了我。我一定要立刻回到安宁地!' WHERE entry=8463; /* Text0_0: <Varnis coughs violently as the restorative draught takes effect.>$B$BThank you for rescuing me.  I must go back to Tranquillien at once! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='从永歌森林三不五时吹来的风真让我作呕，你懂我的意思吧。',Text0_1_loc4='无论萨尔是否存在，破碎之手氏族的秩序都将延续下去。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=8464; /* Text0_0: The drafts of fresh air that blow from Eversong from time to time really upset my stomach, if you know what I mean. */ /* Text0_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text0: */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='这块告示写着许多宣布事项和奖励办法。',Text0_1_loc4='无论萨尔是否存在，破碎之手氏族的秩序都将延续下去。',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=8469; /* Text0_0: This sign contains various announcements and notices of rewards. */ /* Text0_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text0: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='战争浪潮又再度袭来。巫妖王的亡域军队已经从寒冷的北方，包围了我们的土地。他派出了飞行的亡域入侵全世界。' WHERE entry=8471; /* Text0_0: The tides of war have come again. From the cold north, the Lich King\'s necropolises have laid siege to our lands.  He and his cursed general, Kel\'Thuzad, send flying necropolises to invade across the world. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='她会在哪?我满早以前就派我的学徒，莎夏莉雅去西边的光底矿坑了。我们需要把那些矿石样本带回来，要快，否则我们的实验就会失败!',Text0_1_loc4='无论萨尔是否存在，破碎之手氏族的秩序都将延续下去。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=8474; /* Text0_0: Where could she possibly be? I sent my apprentice, Shatharia, to the Underlight Mines to the west quite some time ago. We need those ore samples back, and fast or our experiment is going to fail! */ /* Text0_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text0: */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='如果没有那个光底矿石，这样的情况下，我们的研究一定会失败。$B$B等莎夏莉雅回来这里再说吧。我有一些有趣的任务要交给她，你可以相信我!' WHERE entry=8475; /* Text0_0: Without delivery of the Underlight ore in such a timely fashion, our research would have failed.$B$BJust wait until Shatharia shows her head here again. I\'ve got some interesting tasks for her, you can be sure of it! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='在我们战胜像天谴军团和阿曼尼这些外患之前，一定要先克服内忧。鄙恶者已经惹人厌够久了，是时候消灭他们了。' WHERE entry=8477; /* Text0_0: Before we can overcome external obstacles like the Scourge and the Amani trolls, we must overcome obstacles from within.  The Wretched have been a nuisance for long enough; it is time we vanquished them. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='在那几张羊皮纸里有核对清单和其他远行者的资料，其中有一张特别抢眼。那是一张丑陋的食人妖素描，可能是你见过最可怕的生物!' WHERE entry=8479; /* Text0_0: Amongst the various pieces of parchment containing checklists and other information from the Farstriders, one stands out. It is a drawing of a hideous troll, perhaps the most fearsome creature that you have ever seen! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='的确，冬泉谷山丘一带正尝试要抵挡重生的天谴军团攻击。你的帮忙对他们来说很重要。$B$B剩余的亡域:$2284W' WHERE entry=8480; /* Text0_0: Indeed, the hills of Winterspring are currently attempting to withstand a renewed Scourge assault. Your assistance would help them greatly.$B$BNumber of Necropolises remaining: $2284W */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='这地方目前暂时脱离天谴军团的威胁了。我担心他们很快又要回来了。' WHERE entry=8481; /* Text0_0: For the time being, that area is free of Scourge influence. I fear it will only be a matter of time before they return. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='似乎天灾军团的士兵正在进攻塔纳利斯。大量浮空城和其他部队还在陆续正向这里涌来。$B$B剩余浮空要塞数量：$2283W' WHERE entry=8482; /* Text0_0: It seems the army of the Scourge has come to Tanaris. A significant number of their necropolises and other forces have been dispatched there.$B$BNumber of Necropolises remaining: $2283W */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='天灾军团的势力已经蔓延到了诅咒之地。所有的士兵都要集结起来，击退他们的进攻之潮。$B$B剩余浮空要塞数量：$2280W' WHERE entry=8483; /* Text0_0: The Scourge infestation grows in the Blasted Lands. Every able bodied warrior is needed to stem the tide of their invasion.$B$BNumber of Necropolises remaining: $2280W */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='如果援军不能及时赶到燃烧平原，我怕天谴军团会在那里建立指挥基地。如果你可以，就应该赶快到那边协助防卫部队。$B$B剩余的亡域:$2281W' WHERE entry=8484; /* Text0_0: If additional support is not soon sent to the Burning Steppes, I fear the Scourge will establish a base of operations there. If you can, you should go there to aid the defenders.$B$BNumber of Necropolises remaining: $2281W */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='天谴军团正在攻击地区设置火力点，接收横跨天际的亡域的通讯协助，和其他方面的军援，我们知道，将他们根除的方法就是杀掉所有地面基地的军力。' WHERE entry=8486; /* Text0_0: The Scourge are establishing small staging points in the places under attack, receiving communications and other assistance from the necropolises that fly overhead. From what we can tell, the only way to root them out is by killing the ground forces that surround the points. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='流散的秘法力量会对大地，元素，甚至亡者的灵魂做出奇怪的事情。',Text0_1_loc4='无论萨尔是否存在，破碎之手氏族的秩序都将延续下去。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=8488; /* Text0_0: Stray arcane forces can do strange things to the land, the elements and even the spirits of the dead. */ /* Text0_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text0: */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='高阶执行官是个很忙的人，$c。有什麽事我可以帮你吗?',Text0_1_loc4='无论萨尔是否存在，破碎之手氏族的秩序都将延续下去。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=8489; /* Text0_0: The High Executor is a very busy man, $c.  Maybe I can help you with whatever you need? */ /* Text0_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text0: */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你是我们的楷模，$N。在对付光底矿坑的豺狼人和阿曼尼地下墓穴的屍化食人妖之后，你对我们的敌人击出了致命的一击!$B$B$G做得好!:我们应该找个时间好好喝一杯，你觉得怎麽样?;' WHERE entry=8490; /* Text0_0: You\'ve done us exemplary service, $N. Between dealing with the gnolls at the Underlight Mines, and the mummified trolls in the Amani Catacombs, you\'ve dealt a mighty blow to our enemies!$B$B$G Good job! : We should get together for drinks sometime, what do you say?; */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='很高兴再见到你，$g老兄!:美女!;我们合作愉快;$g下回再见。:我希望我们还有机会合作。;',Text0_1_loc4='无论萨尔是否存在，破碎之手氏族的秩序都将延续下去。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=8491; /* Text0_0: Good to see you again, $g man! : gorgeous!; We work well together; $g see you around. : I hope we get to continue to do so.; */ /* Text0_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text0: */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='人们对你将项链归还给希尔瓦娜斯女王一事议论纷纷。我坚持认为你做了件好事，不要担心女王会对此做何反应。$B$B去做你自己的事好了。' WHERE entry=8492; /* Text0_0: Word got back to me through channels concerning Lady Sylvanas\'s reaction to you and the recovery of her necklace. I still think you did the right thing; don\'t worry too much about how the lady reacted.$B$BNow, state your business. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我能说什麽，$c?你是个真正的$g英雄:女英雄;!你不仅个人救了我许多的游侠，还帮助我们对影松食人妖击出致命一击。你确定你不要留下来成为我手下的远行者之一吗?$B$B再见了，$N。' WHERE entry=8493; /* Text0_0: What can I say, $c? You\'re a true $g hero : heroine;! Not only have you personally saved many of my rangers, but you\'ve dealt a decisive blow against the Shadowpine trolls. Are you sure that you don\'t want to stay here and be one of my Farstriders?$B$BFare well, $N. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你对我们对抗影松食人妖的帮助可说是无法比拟，$c。继续保持我们或许就能将注意力转回来对付天谴军团。',Text0_1_loc4='无论萨尔是否存在，破碎之手氏族的秩序都将延续下去。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=8495; /* Text0_0: Your help with the Shadowpine trolls is proving invaluable, $c. Keep this up and maybe we\'ll be able to turn our attention back to dealing with the Scourge. */ /* Text0_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text0: */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你给了影松食人妖重重一击，$N。我只希望我们可以在他们从祖阿曼获得援军前召集我的军队铲除他们。$B$B如果安宁地愿意给我们支援会非常好。' WHERE entry=8496; /* Text0_0: You\'ve dealt the decisive blow against the Shadowpine trolls, $N. I only hope that we can muster our forces quickly enough to finish them off before they receive reinforcements from Zul\'Aman.$B$BIt would be nice if Tranquillien were to reinforce us. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='情况比许多人所想的还要严重。被遗忘者是我们在这里的盟友，帮助我们对抗共同的敌人，天谴军团。$B$B当我这样说的时候请相信我，没有他们的话就不会有鬼魂之地，而且天谴军团也会早已进入永歌森林!$B$B但更重要的是，我们需要你的帮助来重拾我们曾经骄傲的土地!' WHERE entry=8501; /* Text0_0: The situation is more grim than many have been led to believe. The Forsaken are here as allies in the fight against our common enemy, the Scourge.$B$BTrust me when I say this, without them the Ghostlands would be lost and the Scourge would already have overrun all of Eversong Woods!$B$BBut more than anything else, we need your help in reclaiming our once proud lands! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='这些符文石保护永歌森林的大地不受天谴军团污染。西边的符文石很久前就失去作用了，逼迫我们燃烧它周围的土壤。$B$B只要我还活着我就绝不允许剩下的符文石再次失效。我发誓。' WHERE entry=8504; /* Text0_0: These Runestones protect the lands in Eversong from becoming tainted by the Scourge.  The Western Runestone failed long ago, forcing us to burn the ground around it.$B$BAs long as I live I won\'t allow the remaining Runestones to fail us.  That is my oath. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='有些人认为银色黎明已经是明日黄花。我也持相同的观点，但不是因为天灾军团的威胁已经消除。$b$b不……真正的原因是他们因循守旧的行事风格。他们变得和其努力摆脱的教会越来越像——太过刻板，太过受制于荣耀与秩序。总之，这正是我想要说给巴萨罗梅听的。$b$b当然，这听起来有些过于激进，不过应该会激发一次有意义的辩论。' WHERE entry=8506; /* Text0_0: There are those who would say that the Argent Crusade is a thing of the past.  I am one of them, but not because the Scourge have fallen.$b$bNo... it is because of their stubborn ways.  They\'ve become too much like the church that they seceded from: too rigid, too governed by honor and order.  This is what I\'m trying to tell Barthalomew, anyhow.$b$bSure, it may sound a bit jingoistic, but it makes for a good debate. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='在某个夜里工匠大师欧玛利安突然消失了。就像风中的号角声...咻!消失了!呸，现在只剩下我一个人帮前线的战士们铸造东西了。' WHERE entry=8513; /* Text0_0: Master craftsman Omarion just vanished one night. Like a toot in the wind... Poof! Gone! Bah, now I\'m the only one left to craft the goods for the boys on the front lines. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='$n，辛多雷和被遗忘者在幽魂之地的目标是一致的。我们将共同击败亡灵天灾，或许在我们进军外域的过程中，被遗忘者也将成为最有价值的盟友……谁知道呢。' WHERE entry=8515; /* Text0_0: Sin\'dorei and Forsaken share a common goal in the Ghostlands, $N.  Together we shall defeat the Scourge and who knows... perhaps the Forsaken will be valuable allies in our quest to reach Outland. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='<塔希斯呻吟。>$B$B或许还有时间……仔细听好，凡人。$B$B我在时间与空间里搜索。和一个极度邪恶的恶魔主人打过交道……$B$B<塔希斯在手中咳出血来。>$B$B你会……你会相信就连伊露恩也不理我了吗，$r?死在这里，现在这样的情势之下……' WHERE entry=8517; /* Text0_0: <Tarsis groans.>$B$BThere may still be time... Listen closely, mortal.$B$BThrough time and across the Nether I have searched. Deals made with a host of evil and villainy so wretched...$B$B<Tarsis coughs blood into his hands.>$B$BWould you... would you believe that even Elune has turned her back on me, $r? To die here, in this manner now... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我做过的事……这样恐怖的事……$B$B<塔希斯开始啜泣。>' WHERE entry=8518; /* Text0_0: The things I have done... such horrible things...$B$B<Tarsis begins to sob.> */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我是个精灵贵族，$r。现在已经没有意义了。虽然，曾有一段时间，这个世界是被精灵贵族所统治的。一万年过去了……' WHERE entry=8519; /* Text0_0: I am Highborne, $r. It has no meaning now. There was a time, though, when this world was ruled by Highborne. Ten thousand years past... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我会把它拿回来的，凡人。阿泰丝……我会用它来使精灵贵族获得新生。我会让他们全都复原。就连我们的女王也是……' WHERE entry=8520; /* Text0_0: I would have it back, mortal. Atiesh... From it I would create the Highborne anew. I would have it all back. Even the Queen... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='<塔希斯虚弱地抓住你的衣领。即使濒临死亡你也在他的眼中看到难以想像的力量。>$B$B我是吗?那麽仔细听好，因为有更多的疯言疯语要从我嘴里说出来了。在堡垒里面你会发现我毕生的杰作:每一块碎裂的法杖碎片的所在位置。' WHERE entry=8521; /* Text0_0: <Tarsis grabs you weakly by the collar. Even in death you see power unimaginable in his eyes.>$B$BAm I? Then listen closely, for more nonsense is about to escape my lips. Within this citadel you will find my life\'s work: The exact location of every fragment of the splintered staff. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='阿泰丝，守护者之杖。那个法杖一直以来都在每个提瑞斯法的守护者间流传着。法杖后来被萨格拉斯腐败。最后一名守护者的法杖。麦迪文的法杖。' WHERE entry=8522; /* Text0_0: Atiesh, Greatstaff of the Guardian. The staff handed down through the ages to each of the Guardians of Tirisfal. The staff corrupted by Sargeras. The staff of the last Guardian. The staff of Medivh. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='<塔希斯的眼神发亮。>$B$B我曾经拥有它……我不顾肯瑞托的警告拥有它。我曾经拥有它，凡人……无尽的力量。做我想做的事的力量，随心所慾。就在那个时候，它从我手中被夺走了。但是我尝过那种滋味……而那滋味值得你付出那样的代价。' WHERE entry=8523; /* Text0_0: <Tarsis\'s eyes light up.>$B$BI held it once... I held it despite the warnings of the Kirin Tor. I held it, mortal... Power unending. Power to do what I desired, as I desired. And just as quickly, it was taken from me. But I had tasted... And that taste was all that it took. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='<塔希斯伤的很重。>' WHERE entry=8524; /* Text0_0: <Tarsis is badly injured.> */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='战役进行良好。天灾军团的实力已经被大大削弱了。我相信我们完全能够把他们都赶进海里，这只是时间问题了。我会尽可能地帮助你进行战斗。',Text0_1_loc4='战役进行良好。天灾军团的实力已经被大大削弱了。我相信我们完全能够把他们都赶进海里，这只是时间问题了。我会尽可能地帮助你进行战斗。' WHERE entry=8526; /* Text0_0: The battle goes well. The Scourge forces seem weakened. I believe it will only be a matter of time before we drive them from our shores. I will turn my magics to you, to aid in this struggle. */ /* Text0_1: The battle goes well. The Scourge forces seem weakened. I believe it will only be a matter of time before we drive them from our shores. I will turn my magics to you, to aid in this struggle. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我们对抗天谴军团的第一步进行的很好。我们有了一些成就，希望我们的协助能帮你们获得未来的胜利。',Text0_1_loc4='我们对抗天谴军团的第一步进行的很好。我们有了一些成就，希望我们的协助能帮你们获得未来的胜利。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=8527; /* Text0_0: The first steps of our fight against the Scourge go well. We have had some successes, and hopefully my assistance can aid you in bringing future success to the battle. */ /* Text0_1: The first steps of our fight against the Scourge go well. We have had some successes, and hopefully my assistance can aid you in bringing future success to the battle. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='它是在紫罗兰堡垒陷落之后不见的……碎成了四十二个碎片。' WHERE entry=8529; /* Text0_0: It was lost when the Violet Citadel fell... splintered into forty-two pieces. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='科尔苏加德付出了相当大的努力在尝试重组法杖。这些碎片又再次散落在世界各地，从卡林多到南海都有。我曾经一次拥有二十个碎片 - 直到科尔苏加德的爪牙从我手中将它们偷走。这就是为什麽我会在这里的原因。' WHERE entry=8530; /* Text0_0: Kel\'Thuzad has put forth considerable effort in attempting to reform the staff. The pieces were once scattered across this world, from Kalimdor to the South Seas. I myself held twenty of the pieces at one point in time - until they were stolen from me by Kel\'Thuzad\'s minions. It is why I am here. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你没在听吗?不，我很怀疑如果科尔苏加德组合了法杖我们还能有这段谈话。科尔苏加德握有那个杖头。他的手下拥有四十个阿泰丝之杖的碎片。最后一块 - 杖柄 - 被布莱恩·铜须发现。他最后一次被人看到是在希利苏斯的沙漠;毫无疑问地，离科尔苏加德派遣到这世界的残酷追寻者越远越好。' WHERE entry=8531; /* Text0_0: Haven\'t you been listening? No, I very much doubt we would be having this conversation had Kel\'Thuzad formed the staff. Kel\'Thuzad holds the head. His underlings hold forty splinters of Atiesh. The last piece - the base - was uncovered by Brann Bronzebeard. He was last seen in the Silithus desert; undoubtedly doing his best to stay as far away as possible from the relentless seekers Kel\'Thuzad has dispatched into the world. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='横跨这片土地上有肉眼不能见到的能量界线洪流，我们的圣所就是从那里虹吸秘法能量。$B$B在太阳之井消逝之后，它们提供了我们稳定可靠的能量来源。' WHERE entry=8534; /* Text0_0: Our Sanctums syphon arcane power from ley-line currents that traverse our lands invisible to the naked eye.$B$BWith the Sunwell gone, they provide us with a steady and reliable source of energy. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='晴风村仍然存在，这是对我们种族坚韧不屈的精神的证明。我们绝不让步，直到永远地击败天灾军团。' WHERE entry=8535; /* Text0_0: It\'s a testament to our race\'s tenacity that Fairbreeze Village still stands.  We shall never concede defeat to the Scourge ever again. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='肯威，你这下流的家伙!里维加兹让我免於绞刑架的惩罚但我的刑罚也好不到哪里去。',Text0_1_loc4='肯威，你这下流的家伙!里维加兹让我免於绞刑架的惩罚但我的刑罚也好不到哪里去。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=8536; /* Text0_0: Gangway, ye scurvy dog!  Revilgaz has spared me from the gallows but my punishment might be nearly as bad. */ /* Text0_1: Gangway, ye scurvy dog!  Revilgaz has spared me from the gallows but my punishment might be nearly as bad. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我能为你做些什麽，$N?快点说，我很忙!' WHERE entry=8538; /* Text0_0: What can I do for you, $N?  Make it quick, I don\'t have all day! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我能为你做些什麽?不，等等!你能为我做些什麽?' WHERE entry=8539; /* Text0_0: What can I do for you?  No, wait!  What can you do for me? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你对我们的事业付出了相当大的忠诚，$N。请让我带你瞧瞧我们永无止尽的元素精华来源。' WHERE entry=8541; /* Text0_0: You\'ve served our cause with great loyalty, $N.  Allow me to present you with an unending source of our elemental quintessence. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='欢迎回来，$N。你是个对付拉格纳罗斯的忠诚盟友，我们永远欢迎你。' WHERE entry=8542; /* Text0_0: Welcome back, $N.  You\'ve proven a worthy ally against Ragnaros and your presence is always welcome among us. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='达克汗认为我们会还没开战就被天谴军团给击败。我们一定要让他知道他是错的，$N。',Text0_1_loc4='无论萨尔是否存在，破碎之手氏族的秩序都将延续下去。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=8548; /* Text0_0: Dar\'Khan thinks we\'ll roll over for the Scourge without putting up a fight.  We shall prove him wrong, $N. */ /* Text0_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text0: */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='那是萨瑟里避难所的清单吗?没问题，他的身分地位可以获得一瓶最好的酒。当然，任何萨瑟里领主的朋友都可以特殊的价格买到这样上好的葡萄酒。' WHERE entry=8550; /* Text0_0: Is that a list from Saltheril\'s Haven?  No doubt, his lordship will require a bottle of my finest.  And, of course, any friend of Lord Saltheril deserves a special price on such a fine vintage. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我们赢了天谴军团$2219W场战役。做好准备，$N，这场战争要结束还差的远了。' WHERE entry=8551; /* Text0_0: We have won $2219W battles against the Scourge.  Gird yourself, $N, for this war is far from over. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我们已经赢得了$2219W场对天灾军团战役的胜利。坚持住，$n！我们一定能活下来的！' WHERE entry=8555; /* Text0_0: We have won $2219W battles against the Scourge.  Stand firm, $N!  We must persevere! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我出售各式各样的物品，$c。随意看看。' WHERE entry=8556; /* Text0_0: I have all manner of goods for sale, $c.  Browse at your leisure. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='一个清单……好奇怪。啊对了，萨瑟里领主的烟火。他还没付帐;你是代表他来这里的吗，$c?' WHERE entry=8557; /* Text0_0: A list... how intriguing.  Ah yes, the shipment of fireworks for Lord Saltheril.  He hasn\'t paid for them; are you here to purchase them on his behalf, $c? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='$C，你不会刚好在来这里的路上看到一个信差吧?我们在等待银月城的消息而他们的信差迟到了!',Text0_1_loc4='无论萨尔是否存在，破碎之手氏族的秩序都将延续下去。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=8561; /* Text0_0: $C, you didn\'t happen to see a courier on your way here? We are awaiting word from Silvermoon City and their messenger is late! */ /* Text0_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text0: */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='有时候我站在这里，望着湖后面的森林，然后我就会看到大地又变的……绿意盎然充满生机。' WHERE entry=8564; /* Text0_0: Sometimes I stand here, looking into the forest beyond the lake, and I see the land as it once was... green and full of life. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我们一定得想出个完美的办法来对付那些臭燻燻的影松食人妖!' WHERE entry=8565; /* Text0_0: We really must perfect a way to deal with those smelly Shadowpine trolls! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='投毒成功，那些巨魔要倒大霉了，$C。你真是个有前途的$G小伙子:姑娘;！' WHERE entry=8566; /* Text0_0: I must say, you delivered my poison and dealt with those trolls most ruthlessly, $c. You\'ve got the makings of quite a talented young $g man : lady;! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='巫妖王只派了一小批军力来应付艾泽拉斯的每个主城，他们的主力部队周期性地攻击以下的土地:$B$B艾萨拉，诅咒之地，燃烧平原，塔纳利斯沙漠，东瘟疫之地和冬泉谷。' WHERE entry=8573; /* Text0_0: The Scourge brought only small forces to bear against each of Azeroth\'s capital cities, while their main forces periodically attack the following lands:$B$BAzshara, the Blasted Lands, the Burning Steppes, the Tanaris Desert, the Eastern Plaguelands and Winterspring. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我们的道路是一条贞洁与公正的圣光之路。我今天能为你做些什麽?',Text0_1_loc4='我们的道路是一条贞洁与公正的圣光之路。我今天能为你做些什麽?',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=8582; /* Text0_0: Ours is the path of purity and righteousness in the Light. */ /* Text0_1: Ours is the path of purity and righteousness in the Light. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='在圣光中我们都是一体的，$g兄弟:姐妹;。',Text0_1_loc4='在圣光中我们都是一体的，$g兄弟:姐妹;。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=8584; /* Text0_0: We are one in the Light, $g brother : sister;, but I cannot train you. */ /* Text0_1: We are one in the Light, $g brother : sister;, but I cannot train you. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我能帮你什麽忙，猎人?',Text0_1_loc4='我能帮你什麽忙，猎人?',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=8585; /* Text0_0: You come in search of training, hunter? */ /* Text0_1: You come in search of training, hunter? */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我是个猎人训练师。你要找一个$c训练师。',Text0_1_loc4='我是个猎人训练师。你要找一个$c训练师。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=8586; /* Text0_0: I\'m a hunter trainer. You\'ll want to find the $c trainer. */ /* Text0_1: I\'m a hunter trainer. You\'ll want to find the $c trainer. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你是来寻找战士更深层的启蒙吗?',Text0_1_loc4='你是来寻找战士更深层的启蒙吗?',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=8587; /* Text0_0: Do you seek further training in the ways of the warrior? */ /* Text0_1: Do you seek further training in the ways of the warrior? */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我会训练你，但你不是个战士。',Text0_1_loc4='我会训练你，但你不是个战士。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=8588; /* Text0_0: I would train you, but you are no warrior. */ /* Text0_1: I would train you, but you are no warrior. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我们学习秘法和元素的实践者跟随着一条永无止尽的发现之路。这是为什麽你找我谘询的原因吗?你想受进一步的训练?',Text0_1_loc4='我们学习秘法和元素的实践者跟随着一条永无止尽的发现之路。这是为什麽你找我谘询的原因吗?你想受进一步的训练?',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=8589; /* Text0_0: We practitioners of the arcane and elemental ways follow a never ending path of discovery. Is that why you seek my counsel? You wish further training? */ /* Text0_1: We practitioners of the arcane and elemental ways follow a never ending path of discovery. Is that why you seek my counsel? You wish further training? */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='以纳鲁的名义，你不是个法师！如果你在寻求训练，你必须找$c训练师才行。',Text0_1_loc4='以纳鲁的名义，你不是个法师！如果你在寻求训练，你必须找$c训练师才行。' WHERE entry=8590; /* Text0_0: By the Naaru, you are no mage! If you are looking for training, you must seek out a $c trainer. */ /* Text0_1: By the Naaru, you are no mage! If you are looking for training, you must seek out a $c trainer. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='虽然我不能提供你训练，年轻的$c，我仍会给你我的祝福。大胆地走进圣光。',Text0_1_loc4='虽然我不能提供你训练，年轻的$c，我仍会给你我的祝福。大胆地走进圣光。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=8592; /* Text0_0: Though I cannot offer you training, young $c, I can give you my blessing. Walk boldly in the Light! */ /* Text0_1: Though I cannot offer you training, young $c, I can give you my blessing. Walk boldly in the Light! */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='天灾军团的势力正在艾萨拉迅速滋长。所有能参加战斗的人都必须并肩战斗，阻止他们的侵略大潮席卷世界！$B$B剩余浮空要塞数量：$2279W' WHERE entry=8593; /* Text0_0: The Scourge infestation grows in Azshara. Every able bodied warrior is needed to stem the tide of their invasion.$B$BNumber of Necropolises remaining: $2279W */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='天灾军团的势力正在东瘟疫之地迅速滋长。所有能参加战斗的人都必须并肩战斗，阻止他们的侵略大潮席卷世界！$B$B剩余浮空要塞数量：$2282W' WHERE entry=8594; /* Text0_0: The Scourge infestation grows in the Eastern Plaguelands. Every able bodied warrior is needed to stem the tide of their invasion.$B$BNumber of Necropolises remaining: $2282W */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='圣光为我们指引了许多道路，$C。你必须决定要走哪一条。' WHERE entry=8616; /* Text0_0: Many are the paths of the Light, $c.  You must decide which to follow on this world, or any other. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='如果你能在我们的城镇获得越多名声，我就能让你得到越多的东西，$N。由於我们的装备短缺所以只能提供给我们信任的人。' WHERE entry=8617; /* Text0_0: As you gain renown with our town, I can make more goods available to you, $N.  With equipment in such short supply we can only afford to provide it to those we trust. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我尽可能的在我们破碎的大地提供避难所。',Text0_1_loc4='我尽可能的在我们破碎的大地提供避难所。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=8618; /* Text0_0: I offer what shelter I can in our shattered lands. */ /* Text0_1: I offer what shelter I can in our shattered lands. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='很高兴看到你，$g兄弟:姐妹;!这个地方令我很不自在。当你在这里，记得要好好利用这些所谓被遗忘者所提供的许多机会。' WHERE entry=8619; /* Text0_0: It is so good to see you, $g brother : sister;!  This place gives me the creeps.  While you\'re here, be sure to avail yourself of the many opportunities that these so-called Forsaken are providing. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='不是我的错……那不是我的错!!!$B$B如果他们照着我的话做一切都不会有事。但是不!他们根本不听。$B$B现在他们都死了。$B$B我只想回家。回到银月城的家。我累垮了。' WHERE entry=8620; /* Text0_0: It\'s not my fault... IT\'S NOT MY FAULT!!!$B$BIf they\'d just done what I told them to do everything would have been fine. But no! They wouldn\'t listen.$B$BNow they\'re all dead.$B$BI just want to go home. Home to Silvermoon. I\'m so tired. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我提供舒适的环境...舒缓你的野性冲动，$r。我的旅店就是你的家...' WHERE entry=8634; /* Text0_0: I deal in comfort... Soothe your savage impulse, $r. My inn is your home... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='如果你弄丢了一件赞达拉护甲，我或许可以帮你。' WHERE entry=8642; /* Text0_0: If you have lost a piece of your Zandalarian armor, I may be able to help. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我非常感激你的帮助，$c!',Text0_1_loc4='无论萨尔是否存在，破碎之手氏族的秩序都将延续下去。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=8650; /* Text0_0: I am most grateful for your help, $c! */ /* Text0_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text0: */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='啊，你就是找到信的那个人。谢谢你的……消息，我想应该这麽说，有关我家人的消息。欢迎你享用我提供的食物和饮料。',Text0_1_loc4='啊，你就是找到信的那个人。谢谢你的……消息，我想应该这麽说，有关我家人的消息。欢迎你享用我提供的食物和饮料。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=8653; /* Text0_0: Ah, you\'re the one who found the letter. Thank you for the... news, I suppose, about my family. You\'re welcome to what food and drink I can offer. */ /* Text0_1: Ah, you\'re the one who found the letter. Thank you for the... news, I suppose, about my family. You\'re welcome to what food and drink I can offer. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='哎！排队好不好？我一点都吃不惯外域的东西。',Text0_1_loc4='哎！排队好不好？我一点都吃不惯外域的东西。' WHERE entry=8656; /* Text0_0: OY! Wait in line, would ya? Outland food doesn\'t agree with me at all. */ /* Text0_1: OY! Wait in line, would ya? Outland food doesn\'t agree with me at all. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='希德是名字。在这附近还能看到新面孔真好。我能为你做些什麽?' WHERE entry=8658; /* Text0_0: Sid\'s the name. It\'s nice to see some new faces around here. What can I do you for? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='虽然我们抵达了乐土，$N，还有很多事等着要做。除非我们拼了命地穿过外域，否则我们的人民接近不了凯尔萨斯。$B$B一定要找到安全的路线，保护好资源，避开我们的敌人或杀了他们。' WHERE entry=8659; /* Text0_0: Though we\'ve arrived at the promised land, $N, much work remains to be done.  Our people won\'t reach Kael\'thas if we lunge desperately across Outland.$B$BSafe routes must be found, resources must be secured and our enemies must be avoided or destroyed. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='现在为了治疗水晶我什麽都愿意给!' WHERE entry=8662; /* Text0_0: What I wouldn\'t give for a healing crystal right about now! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='谢谢你帮忙递交清单！我的腿差不多已经痊愈，这样我就可以自己走回坠毁点了。' WHERE entry=8663; /* Text0_0: Thank you for delivering that list!  My leg is almost recovered enough that I\'ll be able to walk back to the crash site. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='看到你还活得好好的真好，$N!' WHERE entry=8667; /* Text0_0: It is good to see you alive and well, $N! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='再次感谢你补充了我们的治疗水晶。我听说你到处在帮忙人们。保持下去!' WHERE entry=8669; /* Text0_0: Thank you again for replenishing our healing crystals. I hear that you\'re helping out all over the place. Keep up the good work! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='无论是在黑暗之门的那边还是这边，米伦和我都是非常优秀的猎人。到处晃晃，你也许可以学到点什么的。' WHERE entry=8672; /* Text0_0: Mirren and I are two of the very best hunters on either side of the Dark Portal.  Stick around, you might learn a thing or two. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我希望你不是为我们的啤酒而来的。不要想了，我们是不会把啤酒分给你的！$B$B除了我们之外居然没有人会有这么好的远见，想到把啤酒带到外域来，嘿，这可不是我们的过错。' WHERE entry=8673; /* Text0_0: I hope yer not here for our ale.  We\'re not sharing and that\'s final!$B$BIt\'s not our fault no one had the good sense to bring beer to Outland but us. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='外域里存在着比我们以前见过还强大很多的恶魔势力。$B$B强大的力量应该给予那些不会畏惧的人，但能学着驾驭和控制它的力量。' WHERE entry=8675; /* Text0_0: There exist in Outland demonic presences much more powerful than anything we\'d ever seen in the old world.$B$BGreat power shall come to those who do not shy away from it, but learn to harness and master its strength. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我出生在这里，$r。这是我的世界，我所了解的一切……当我还是个小孩子的时候，我的父母经常向我讲述你们那个世界的故事，你们那个世界的荣光。我是多么渴望离开这个地方啊。$B$B唉，命运是残酷的。我的父母已经去世很久了，长眠在这个坟墓里。我留在这里，为他们的荣耀而战，也为我的家族——洛萨之子的荣耀而战。' WHERE entry=8676; /* Text0_0: I was born here, $r. This is my world - all that I know... As a boy, my mother and father would regale me with tales of your world and the splendor it held. How I longed to leave this place.$B$BAlas, fate is a cruel mistress. My mother and father have long since passed, buried in this very graveyard. I remain to uphold their honor and the honor of my family - the Sons of Lothar. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我能帮你什麽忙?',Text0_1_loc4='我能帮你什麽忙?',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=8678; /* Text0_0: How may I serve? */ /* Text0_1: How may I serve? */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='外域散发着魔法能量，就在那空气中。你能感觉到吗，$N?我想不到比这更适合我们种族的地方了。很快辛多雷就有自己的新土地了!' WHERE entry=8680; /* Text0_0: Outland just oozes with magical energy, it\'s in the very air.  Can you feel it, $N?  I can\'t think of a place better suited to our race.  Soon the sin\'dorei shall have a new land to call our own! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='别...担心...我...' WHERE entry=8683; /* Text0_0: Don\'t... worry... about me... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='和逐日者交朋友各有各的好处;我用只能在外域找到的实验品来进行研究，而他们则获得...我迷人的个性和粗犷的帅脸蛋。' WHERE entry=8685; /* Text0_0: Befriending the Sunstriders has paid off; I get to conduct research with subjects I can only find in Outland and they get... my charming personality and rugged good looks. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='当我父亲被派来这片荒地时我只是个婴儿。所有我知道关於他的事都是别人告诉我的。$B$B你的梦会变吗，$N?我的不会。我只有一个梦:一条赤红的军团地平线包围着我，数量庞大无法计算，在远处作战。我在一个人的躯体前跪下，他大概就是我的父亲，然后哭泣。当他喘着气时，他的身体整个被压碎，他虚弱的说着一些话。尽管我再怎麽努力;还是听不到他要和我说的话。' WHERE entry=8688; /* Text0_0: I was only an infant when my father was deployed to this wasteland. All that I have ever known of him is what others have told me.$B$BDo your dreams change, $N? Mine do not. I have one dream: A crimson skyline envelops me as Legion, numbering beyond comprehension, battle in the distance. I kneel before the body of a man, presumably my father, and weep. As he is gasping for air, his body wholly crushed, he whispers something. Despite every effort, I am unable to hear what he is trying to tell me. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你认为我对这个小人太残忍了吗?$B$B他们这个月已经杀了我手下两个人!我们对这些鄙恶人渣太仁慈了。' WHERE entry=8698; /* Text0_0: You think I\'m being cruel to this worm?$B$BThey\'ve killed two of my men this month!  We\'re too kind to this Wretched scum. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='如果你在找工作，$C，拿起一个工具开始挖吧。这里所见都是废墟!',Text0_1_loc4='无论萨尔是否存在，破碎之手氏族的秩序都将延续下去。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=8712; /* Text0_0: If you\'re looking for work, $c, grab yourself a pick and get to digging. There\'re ruins out there as far as the eye can see! */ /* Text0_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text0: */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='外域的腐败程度真的相当惊人，$c。塞纳里奥远征队想了解这土地的生物如何在这麽艰难的环境下生存。研究这块破碎，受尽折磨的土地和它的居民，或许能教我们如何治疗这生病的世界。' WHERE entry=8716; /* Text0_0: It is sad to see what has happened to this land.  The Cenarion Expedition will do what it can to understand and heal the damage that has been done. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你看起来若有所失，$c。不要逼我让你和那些苦工一样到墙上去工作。' WHERE entry=8717; /* Text0_0: You look lost, $c. Don\'t make me put you to work on the walls with the other peons. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='索尔玛需要你，$c。大酋长需要你。准备好履行你的职责。',Text0_1_loc4='无论萨尔是否存在，破碎之手氏族的秩序都将延续下去。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=8719; /* Text0_0: Thrallmar needs you, $c. The warchief needs you. Stand ready to do your duty. */ /* Text0_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text0: */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='靠着蛮力赢了几场比赛。那很奸诈，最后靠着你在武器上的本能反应和知识获得胜利。',Text0_1_loc4='靠着蛮力赢了几场比赛。那很奸诈，最后靠着你在武器上的本能反应和知识获得胜利。' WHERE entry=8724; /* Text0_0: Few bouts are won by sheer strength.  It is cunning, reflexes and knowledge of your weapon that wins the day in the end. */ /* Text0_1: Few bouts are won by sheer strength.  It is cunning, reflexes and knowledge of your weapon that wins the day in the end. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='另一个英雄?命运今天对我们微笑，$N。',Text0_1_loc4='无论萨尔是否存在，破碎之手氏族的秩序都将延续下去。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=8733; /* Text0_0: Another hero? The fates smile upon us on this day, $N. */ /* Text0_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text0: */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我听说过你的一些功绩，$N。我知道当你在这被遗忘者的土地时你会带着尊严行动，像个辛多雷真正的英雄。' WHERE entry=8740; /* Text0_0: I\'ve heard something of your exploits, $N.  I know that while you\'re here in Forsaken lands that you\'ll comport yourself with dignity and as a true hero of the sin\'dorei! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我没时间闲聊，$c。我一定要照料那些朝圣者确保他们为前方漫长的旅途做好准备。' WHERE entry=8751; /* Text0_0: I haven\'t time for idle chatter, $c. I must see to the pilgrims and ensure they are prepared for the long journey ahead. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='欢迎来到猎鹰岗哨，$c。我留意着那些朝圣者的需求，并帮助他们继续走完漫长的旅程。如果你还没有开始朝圣，我可以给你提供一些你需要的信息。' WHERE entry=8752; /* Text0_0: Welcome to Falcon Watch, $c. I see to the needs of the pilgrims and help them in continuing their long journey. If you haven\'t yet undertaken the pilgrimage, I can provide you with the information you will need. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你好，$c。' WHERE entry=8753; /* Text0_0: Greetings, $c. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='喔……我认识你吗 ?',Text0_1_loc4='喔……我认识你吗 ?',Text1_0_loc4='喔……我认识你吗 ?',Text1_1_loc4='喔……我认识你吗 ?' WHERE entry=8759; /* Text0_0: Oh... do I know you? */ /* Text0_1: Oh... do I know you? */ /* Text1_0: Sorry, I don\'t speak with the help. */ /* Text1_1: Sorry, I don\'t speak with the help. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text2_0_loc4='喔……我认识你吗 ?',Text2_1_loc4='喔……我认识你吗 ?',Text3_0_loc4='喔……我认识你吗 ?',Text3_1_loc4='喔……我认识你吗 ?' WHERE entry=8759; /* Text2_0: And you would be? */ /* Text2_1: And you would be? */ /* Text3_0: I\'m afraid you have me confused with someone who wants to talk to you. */ /* Text3_1: I\'m afraid you have me confused with someone who wants to talk to you. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='嗨，$N!派对好玩吗?',Text0_1_loc4='嗨，$N!派对好玩吗?',Text1_0_loc4='嗨，$N!派对好玩吗?',Text1_1_loc4='嗨，$N!派对好玩吗?' WHERE entry=8760; /* Text0_0: Hi, $N!  Enjoying the party? */ /* Text0_1: Hi, $N!  Enjoying the party? */ /* Text1_0: Hey everyone, it\'s $N! */ /* Text1_1: Hey everyone, it\'s $N! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text2_0_loc4='嗨，$N!派对好玩吗?',Text2_1_loc4='嗨，$N!派对好玩吗?',Text3_0_loc4='嗨，$N!派对好玩吗?',Text3_1_loc4='嗨，$N!派对好玩吗?' WHERE entry=8760; /* Text2_0: Word travels fast in this circle.  Thanks for restocking the supplies! */ /* Text2_1: Word travels fast in this circle.  Thanks for restocking the supplies! */ /* Text3_0: This party is just the best!  Don\'t you agree? */ /* Text3_1: This party is just the best!  Don\'t you agree? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text4_0_loc4='你应该试试泉爪开胃菜，他们好吃死了！',Text4_1_loc4='你应该试试泉爪开胃菜，他们好吃死了！',Text5_0_loc4='嗯……我认为今年的特殊美酒不怎么特别。你同意吗，$N?',Text5_1_loc4='嗯……我认为今年的特殊美酒不怎么特别。你同意吗，$N?' WHERE entry=8760; /* Text4_0: You should try the springpaw appetizers, they\'re to die for! */ /* Text4_1: You should try the springpaw appetizers, they\'re to die for! */ /* Text5_0: Hmm... I think this year\'s Suntouched Special isn\'t so special afterall.  Wouldn\'t you agree, $N? */ /* Text5_1: Hmm... I think this year\'s Suntouched Special isn\'t so special afterall.  Wouldn\'t you agree, $N? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text6_0_loc4='我听说我们今晚都要去边界观看和天谴军团的战斗。真棒！',Text6_1_loc4='我听说我们今晚都要去边界观看和天谴军团的战斗。真棒！',Text7_0_loc4='你相信那个艾莉萨·击日者的胆量吗?觉得她可以吸引到萨瑟里领主的目光?你有看到她穿的衣服吗?早就过时了。真悲哀，真的。',Text7_1_loc4='你相信那个艾莉萨·击日者的胆量吗?觉得她可以吸引到萨瑟里领主的目光?你有看到她穿的衣服吗?早就过时了。真悲哀，真的。' WHERE entry=8760; /* Text6_0: I heard a rumor that we\'re all going to go watch the battle with the scourge at the border tonight.  How delightfully wicked! */ /* Text6_1: I heard a rumor that we\'re all going to go watch the battle with the scourge at the border tonight.  How delightfully wicked! */ /* Text7_0: Can you believe the nerve of that Elisara Sunstriker?  Thinking that she can catch the eye of Lord Saltheril?  And did you see what she\'s wearing?  So last season.  It\'s sad, really. */ /* Text7_1: Can you believe the nerve of that Elisara Sunstriker?  Thinking that she can catch the eye of Lord Saltheril?  And did you see what she\'s wearing?  So last season.  It\'s sad, really. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='啊……滚开！',Text0_1_loc4='啊……滚开！',Text1_0_loc4='什么？发生什么事了？',Text1_1_loc4='什么？发生什么事了？' WHERE entry=8761; /* Text0_0: Ugh... go away! */ /* Text0_1: Ugh... go away! */ /* Text1_0: Huh, what?  What happened? */ /* Text1_1: Huh, what?  What happened? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text2_0_loc4='走开……我试着在这里睡觉。',Text2_1_loc4='走开……我试着在这里睡觉。',Text3_0_loc4='我感觉不太舒服！',Text3_1_loc4='我感觉不太舒服！' WHERE entry=8761; /* Text2_0: Go away.. I\'m tryin\' to shleep here. */ /* Text2_1: Go away.. I\'m tryin\' to shleep here. */ /* Text3_0: Ack, I don\'t feel so good. */ /* Text3_1: Ack, I don\'t feel so good. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我让我自己成了一个笑柄。先知瑞卡酷试着警告我，但我的粗心最后还是让我哉了个跟斗。$B$B我来这里研究札斯可废墟，但却在路上与燃烧军团发生冲突。现在，我所有的一切就是腿上一个讨厌的伤口。' WHERE entry=8767; /* Text0_0: I\'ve managed to work myself into quite a spot here. Far Seer Regulkut tried to warn me, but my carelessness has finally caught up with me.$B$BI came down here to study the ruins of Zeth\'Gor, but ran afoul of the Legion on my way. Now, all I have to show for it is a nasty gash on my leg. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='虽然我无法提供你训练，年轻的$c，但我可以给你我的祝福。勇敢地走进圣光里!$B$B还有别的事吗?',Text0_1_loc4='虽然我无法提供你训练，年轻的$c，但我可以给你我的祝福。勇敢地走进圣光里!$B$B还有别的事吗?',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=8768; /* Text0_0: Though I cannot offer you training, young $c, I can give you my blessing.  Walk boldly in the Light!$B$BIs there anything else? */ /* Text0_1: Though I cannot offer you training, young $c, I can give you my blessing.  Walk boldly in the Light!$B$BIs there anything else? */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='就在不久之前，此地才发生了一场惨烈的战斗。我们守望堡与银色黎明抵抗着一波波从黑暗之门中涌出的恶魔。$B$B那些黑暗的日子，充满的血腥与绝望...$B$B但是艾泽拉斯王国很快地加入我们，把那些怪物给逼退了!战斗持续在传送门边进行着...$B$B这个营地现在虽然很平静，但我害怕此地的宁静只是在掩饰着那座地狱之门后的狂暴。' WHERE entry=8770; /* Text0_0: Not long ago, this place was the site of a terrible battle.  We of Nethergarde and the Argent Dawn held at bay a wave of demons, surging relentlessly from the Dark Portal.$B$BThose were dark days, full of bloodshed and despair...$B$BBut the Kingdoms of Azeroth soon joined us and pushed the monsters back!  The fighting continues on the far side of the Portal...$B$BThis camp is now calm, but I fear the quiet here belies the madness found through that hellish gate. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='英勇的托尔贝恩血统具有传奇性。我崇拜他。$B$B找到他时要是活着的，就在外域...$B$B<洛摩斯注视着你经过。>$B$B当我第一次看到他时，我几乎昏厥过去。难以阻挡的震惊力。当我跪在他面前，我必需勇敢面对。$B$B你能确信在我尽我能力完成某些事之后，洛萨之子能安全无虞。',Text0_1_loc4='无论萨尔是否存在，破碎之手氏族的秩序都将延续下去。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=8771; /* Text0_0: The heroics of the Trollbane bloodline are legendary. I idolize the man.$B$BAnd to find him alive, in the Outland...$B$B<Romus gazes past you.>$B$BWhen I first saw him, I nearly fainted. The shock was overwhelming. As I knelt before him, I had to fight back tears.$B$BYou can bet your sweet behind that I\'m going to do everything in my power to make sure the Sons of Lothar are kept safe. */ /* Text0_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text0: */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='<啜泣>我恨墓地。这麽多死亡。还有我的宝贝露荷娜……' WHERE entry=8780; /* Text0_0: <Sobbing> I hate graveyards.  So many dead.  And my sweet Luhanaa.... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='记得表现出你对世界元素的敬意。',Text0_1_loc4='记得表现出你对世界元素的敬意。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=8785; /* Text0_0: Remember to always show your respect for the elements of the world. */ /* Text0_1: Remember to always show your respect for the elements of the world. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我们一定要努力了解这世界元素之灵维护的平衡点。',Text0_1_loc4='我们一定要努力了解这世界元素之灵维护的平衡点。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=8786; /* Text0_0: We must strive to understand the balance maintained by this world\'s elemental spirits. */ /* Text0_1: We must strive to understand the balance maintained by this world\'s elemental spirits. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='靠近一点，朋友。不要让我的眼睛吓着你。$B$B我在好几年前就失去了我的视力，但是我从不需要眼睛去看待事物。' WHERE entry=8792; /* Text0_0: Come closer, friend.  Do not let my eyes startle you.$B$BI might have lost my sight many years ago but I never needed it to see the things that really matter. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='嗨。你今天过的还好吗?' WHERE entry=8794; /* Text0_0: Hello.  I trust that this day finds you well? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='很高兴看到其他的辛多雷$g兄弟:姐妹;！如你所见，这附近没有什么其他人可以说话。' WHERE entry=8795; /* Text0_0: It\'s so good to see another sin\'dorei $g brother : sister;!  As you can imagine, there\'s not much in the way of conversation around here. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='做为你所熟识的人让我备受尊重。' WHERE entry=8796; /* Text0_0: I am honored to make your acquaintance. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你能和我说这些真是太好了。请用你的任何方法帮助联盟。' WHERE entry=8797; /* Text0_0: So good of you to speak with me.  Please, help the Alliance in any way that you can. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你好。我是学者德尔兰，一个德莱尼人。你是谁？' WHERE entry=8798; /* Text0_0: Greetings.  I am Anchorite Delan - one of the draenei.  I am a teacher of sorts.  And who might you be? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='当我们教导联盟其他种族的人，我们有很多要和他们多学习的地方。保持你的眼睛、耳朵和你的心处於学习状态，$c。' WHERE entry=8799; /* Text0_0: While we have much to teach the other races of the Alliance, we have as much to learn from them.  Keep your eyes, ears and mind open, $c. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我太忙了没空闲聊。如果你在寻找猎人的工作，就和河边的狄克泰纳谈谈 - 在东边。她的工作一定还没做完...' WHERE entry=8804; /* Text0_0: I am far too busy to be wasting time on idle chatter. If you are looking for work as a huntsman, speak with Diktynna at the river\'s edge -- to the east. No doubt she\'s behind on her duties... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='看看埃索达，年轻的$c。很难想象我们在这场大灾难中生存了下来。$B$B<梅内莱厄斯叹了口气。>$B$B先知预言我们会在这里最终了解到自己的命运。我们用了毕生的时间来逃避疯狂的燃烧军团……现在我们终于可以在这里停下来了。$B$B不再逃跑……我已经准备好光荣地战死了。' WHERE entry=8806; /* Text0_0: Gaze upon the Exodar, young $r. It is hard to imagine that we survived such a catastrophe.$B$B<Menelaous sighs.>$B$BThe Prophet states that it is here that our fate will finally be known. Ten lifetimes spent fleeing from the madness of the Burning Legion... here we finally make a stand.$B$BNo more running... I am ready to die. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你好。我是德莱尼学者阿弗恩。我在这里研究农田避难所的失落者们，希望可以找到一个治愈他们的办法。' WHERE entry=8812; /* Text0_0: Greetings.  I am Anchorite Avuun of the draenei.  I am here studying the Lost Ones of the Fallow Sanctuary in the hope of being able to find a cure for their condition. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='在我们之间你是受欢迎的，$c。至少现在是。' WHERE entry=8813; /* Text0_0: You are welcome among us, $c.  At least for the time being. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='再次感谢你对被诅咒的失落者所提供的帮助。没有你的帮助，我想我是无法继续研究的。' WHERE entry=8814; /* Text0_0: Once more, thank you for your assistance with the cursed Lost Ones.  Without your help I would never have been able to continue my research. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我当然有工作给你!我们一直都在寻找$c。希望你比那些被我们送回艾克索达...参加葬礼的德莱尼好一点。$B$B<艾克缇昂笑着。>$B$B开玩笑的!你真该看看你刚才的表情。他们被送回艾克索达治疗小伤。没有什麽无法复原的大伤...' WHERE entry=8823; /* Text0_0: Of course I\'ve got a job for you! We\'re always looking for hunters. Hopefully you\'ll fare better than the draenei we had to send back to the Exodar -- for burial.$B$B<Acteon laughs.>$B$BI\'m joking! You should have seen the look on your face. They got sent back to the Exodar for treatment of minor wounds. Nothin\' that they won\'t recover from... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='回到你的人民那里并告诉他们派一个萨满来我这。' WHERE entry=8824; /* Text0_0: Return to your people and tell them to send one of your shaman to me. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='回到德莱尼那里并告诉他们派一个萨满来我这里。' WHERE entry=8825; /* Text0_0: Return to the draenei and tell them to send me one of their shaman. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='萨满祭司，你在这里的事情都完结了。回到你的族人那里去吧。' WHERE entry=8826; /* Text0_0: Your work here is complete, shaman.  Return to your people. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你有继续下去的体认了吗，萨满?你知道你为什麽会在这里吗?' WHERE entry=8827; /* Text0_0: Do you have the understanding to continue, shaman?  Do you know why you are here? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你好，$r。' WHERE entry=8828; /* Text0_0: Greetings, $r. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='能和元素一致活着真好。' WHERE entry=8829; /* Text0_0: It is a good day to be alive and one with the elements. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='而我为什麽要跟你说话，$r?' WHERE entry=8830; /* Text0_0: And why would I speak with you, $r? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='看看你的四周，萨满。你有看到大地，空气，水和火焰里的元素平衡吗?' WHERE entry=8832; /* Text0_0: Look around you, shaman.  Can you see the balance of the elements in the earth, the air, the water and the fire that has touched them all? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我会报复的!' WHERE entry=8836; /* Text0_0: I WILL have my revenge! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我现在很忙，年轻的$c。对不起。',Text0_1_loc4='我现在很忙，年轻的$c。对不起。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=8838; /* Text0_0: I\'m very busy right now, young $c. Please excuse me. */ /* Text0_1: I\'m very busy right now, young $c. Please excuse me. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你好，$c。我从艾克索达被派到这里监督蓝色守望的建造工程。' WHERE entry=8840; /* Text0_0: Greetings, $c. I have been sent here from the Exodar to oversee the construction of Azure Watch. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='链金师可以用普通的药草来创造奇蹟，让它们变成稳定的药水，从治疗到水下呼吸和其他各种效果都有。' WHERE entry=8844; /* Text0_0: An alchemist is able to work miracles with ordinary herbs, converting them into stable potions that range in effect from healing to breathing underwater and everything in between. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='且慢，朋友。小厨是我的名字，烹饪是我的拿手绝活。麦克威酱的血统是世代流传的厨师与商人，专门取悦感官细致的男男女女。' WHERE entry=8849; /* Text0_0: Avast ye, matey. Cookie is me name, cooking is me game. The McWeaksauce bloodline be a long line of cooks and tradesmen that work to please the more delicate senses o\' man and woman. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='圣光与你同在，$c。' WHERE entry=8851; /* Text0_0: Light be with you, $C. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='伊坎试了又试。我想这些残冠氏族的人更像是失落者，你知道……那些失落了的……' WHERE entry=8853; /* Text0_0: Ikan tries and tries.  I think these Dreghood are much like the Lost Ones, you know... lost. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='这会花点时间，但这些破碎者会了解圣光之道!' WHERE entry=8854; /* Text0_0: It will take a while, but these Broken Ones will learn the ways of the Light! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='欢迎，$N。我是蓝卓·长射-黑色烈焰的管理者。也许在此之前你并没有听过黑色烈焰这个名词。我一点都不惊讶，因为我们一向都保持低调。我们宁愿避开……派系与种族之间的斗争。$B$B黑色烈焰专门提供钱所能买的到最好的娱乐服务，不论是难以寻找的宝物、决斗场的战斗或者一掷千金的赌局。$B$B您想寻找哪一方面的刺激呢?' WHERE entry=8855; /* Text0_0: Welcome, $N. I am Landro Longshot - manager of the Black Flame. Perhaps you\'ve not heard of the Black Flame until now. That doesn\'t surprise me; we work to keep things that way. We prefer to avoid... factional entanglements.$B$BThe Black Flame specializes in providing the finest services and entertainment money can buy, whether they happen to be hard to find items, gladiatorial combat, or lucrative games of chance.$B$BAre you here seeking something specific?$B */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你想要什麽，孩子?' WHERE entry=8856; /* Text0_0: Ah - oddities and rarities. We specialize in Azeroth\'s more unique items for the discerning adventurer.$B$BSince you\'re speaking with me, you must already have an idea of what you\'re looking for. So, $N, which item are you interested in? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='幽暗之地仅靠军事力量是无法夺回的，$n。我们魔导师才是关键。$B$B我们的狡诈和魔法知识是无往而不利的。' WHERE entry=8860; /* Text0_0: The Ghostlands will not be won back by military force alone, $N.  That\'s where we magisters come in.$B$BOur guile and knowledge of the arcane are unmatched. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='在这里要小心你的脚步，陌生人。' WHERE entry=8864; /* Text0_0: Watch your step around here, stranger. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='到现在为止你帮了很大的忙，$N。你对营地的其他人也会很有助益。$B$B不要担心那些地精，我处理好所有的事了。' WHERE entry=8865; /* Text0_0: You\'ve been a great help thus far, $N. You would do well to help out the others at the encampment.$B$BAnd don\'t worry about those goblins, I\'m taking care of everything. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你在看什麽?' WHERE entry=8867; /* Text0_0: What are you looking at? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我是伟大之城铁炉堡的阿达曼·铁心。你们看我的制服应该猜到我曾是铁炉堡精英守卫之一。是的，我是麦格尼的副手!至少在我退休之前都是。现在我都在研究考古学。这是个嗜好;加上我认为这是个见识世界的好方法!' WHERE entry=8868; /* Text0_0: I am Adamant Ironheart of the great city of Ironforge. As you could probably guess by looking at my uniform, I was once part of the Ironforge elite guard. Yep, I was Magni\'s right hand man! At least until I retired. Now I dabble in archaeology. It\'s a hobby really; plus I figured it would be a great way to see the world! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='<科伦啜泣。>' WHERE entry=8869; /* Text0_0: <Cowlen sobs.> */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='如果不是神只，那会是谁?是什麽造成了这样的冲突?' WHERE entry=8871; /* Text0_0: If not the gods, who? How? What could cause such strife? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='军团?恶魔?他们追捕你?我的人民也被燃烧军团追捕:黑暗大师将他们视为毁灭的目标。$B$B<科伦擦去眼泪。>$B$B这是我和家人多年前搬迁至此的原因。' WHERE entry=8872; /* Text0_0: Legion? Demons? They hunt you? My people have also been hunted by Legion: Targeted by their dark masters for damnation.$B$B<Cowlen wipes the tears away.>$B$BIt is the reason that I moved my family here oh-so-many years ago. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你好，$c。在夜精灵邀请德莱尼加入他们之前，这片林地是被遗忘的。$B$B卡多雷和这片土地关系密切，而我们德莱尼很荣幸他们要我们一起接下重新振作林歌神殿的任务。' WHERE entry=8873; /* Text0_0: Greetings, $c. Before the night elves invited the draenei to join them here, this glade was all but forgotten.$B$BThe kaldorei are deeply tied to these lands, and we draenei are honored that they have asked us to share in the task of revitalizing Forest Song. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='再次在林歌神殿这里听到其他人的声音真好。我开始觉得好像我会是这片土地衰退腐败前最后一个注视它们的卡多雷人。' WHERE entry=8875; /* Text0_0: It\'s good to hear the voices of others here in Forest Song again. I\'d begun to feel as though I might be the last of the kaldorei ever to set eyes on these lands before their descent into corruption. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='虽然你已经给南方的恶魔势力造成了沉重的打击，但我还是觉得那个地方有些问题。' WHERE entry=8878; /* Text0_0: While you\'ve dealt the demonic evil from the south a serious blow, I still sense trouble from that region. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你是一个$r，对吗?在这里见到你让我很振奋!我们可以利用所有能获得的帮助。' WHERE entry=8881; /* Text0_0: You\'re a $r, right?  I am heartened to see you here!  We can use all of the help that we can get. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='为我们尊贵的英雄欢呼吧！',Text1_0_loc4='你的故事将被传颂！' WHERE entry=8892; /* Text0_0: All hail the exalted hero! */ /* Text1_0: The story of your journey will be told for years to come! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text2_0_loc4='我终于有个故事可以讲给孙儿们听了……一个叛徒曾与我们生活在一起！',Text3_0_loc4='说实话，我从来就没喜欢过那个侏儒……' WHERE entry=8892; /* Text2_0: I finally have a story to tell my grandchildren about... A traitor to the kingdom was living among us! */ /* Text3_0: Truth be told, I never liked that gnome... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text4_0_loc4='我们能够在这样的考验中生存下来，真是太幸运了。如果不是你，在岛上的每个人可能早已经被杀死了。',Text5_0_loc4='我怀疑还有多少这样的叛徒混在我们中间。我认识斯巴克很多年了，却从未想到过他会是个叛徒。' WHERE entry=8892; /* Text4_0: We are lucky to have survived this ordeal. If it wasn\'t for you, everyone on this island could have been killed! */ /* Text5_0: I wonder how many more of them live among us. I knew Spark for years - never could I have imagined that he was a traitor. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='真希望与你同行，$N。去暴风要塞吧，跟国王觐见室的塞尔曼・岩拳谈谈，他会帮助你转至奥特兰克山谷的。' WHERE entry=8934; /* Text0_0: Hi there, $N. How may I help you? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='西洋棋:人类步卒' WHERE entry=8952; /* Text0_0: <The footman stand resolute, muscles tense.> */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='当我们试着获得这世界对抗燃烧军团的人支援时，我们一定也要学着和他们和平共处。$B$B当你在整个艾泽拉斯旅行时请记住这点。愿圣光引导你。' WHERE entry=8953; /* Text0_0: As we attempt to gain the help of the peoples of this world against the Burning Legion, we must also learn to live peaceably amongst them.$B$BPlease keep this in mind as your journey takes you throughout Azeroth.  May the Light guide you. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='什麽事让你千里迢迢的来到这里，小$r?' WHERE entry=8954; /* Text0_0: What brings you all the way up here, little $r? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你勇敢地游到了我的领域，陆行者。' WHERE entry=8958; /* Text0_0: You are brave to swim down to my realm, land-walker. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='停止。我没有东西要给像你这样的人。',Text0_1_loc4='停止。我没有东西要给像你这样的人。',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=8960; /* Text0_0: Leave off. I don\'t have anything for the likes of you. */ /* Text0_1: Leave off. I don\'t have anything for the likes of you. */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='怎麽啦，$T小子:女孩;?你想找妈咪?嗯很抱歉。或许你该前往索尔玛官员的俱乐部去把她找回来?',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=8961; /* Text0_0: What\'s that $T scrub : girlie;? You want your mommy? Well too bad. Maybe you should pay a visit to the Thrallmar officer\'s club to get her back? */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text2_0_loc4='欢迎来到我们的酒店!',Text3_0_loc4='我的主人普拉格·史帕齐林是个不错的老板，而且他赚了很多钱。他的钱包都快要被撑破了!' WHERE entry=8961; /* Text2_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text2: */ /* Text3_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text3: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text4_0_loc4='嘘……你闻到什么东西?',Text5_0_loc4='我听说你已经死啦……嗯，以后你想要装死的话就不那么容易啦！' WHERE entry=8961; /* Text4_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text4: */ /* Text5_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text5: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text6_0_loc4='老国王死了吗？那不可能！',Text7_0_loc4='国王陛下，我可没有给你带来什么麻烦。' WHERE entry=8961; /* Text6_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text6: */ /* Text7_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text7: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='小声点，$c!',Text1_0_loc4='小声点，$c!' WHERE entry=8962; /* Text0_0: Keep your voice down, $c! */ /* Text1_0: If you have something to say, say it! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text2_0_loc4='小声点，$c!',Text3_0_loc4='小声点，$c!' WHERE entry=8962; /* Text2_0: You\'re a $T civilian : civilian;? */ /* Text3_0: I\'m busy, make it fast! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你和高阶女牧师谈过话了吗？她非常渴望听到你去朝圣的故事。' WHERE entry=8963; /* Text0_0: Have you spoken with the high priestess yet?  She\'s very eager to hear the tale of the pilgrimage from your point of view. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='今天真是美好的一天，$c!',Text0_1_loc4='无论萨尔是否存在，破碎之手氏族的秩序都将延续下去。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=8965; /* Text0_0: This is a great day, $c! */ /* Text0_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text0: */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='太感谢了，你让我的朝圣之梦成真了！' WHERE entry=8966; /* Text0_0: I cannot thank you enough for making my pilgrimage possible! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='是时间让公会派点新鲜血液给我们了！真不巧，你们辛辛苦苦来到这里，却什么都看不到。我们被禁止为客人们表演了，你能相信吗？莫罗斯禁止我们进行新的演出，我的支持者们都要发狂了！我们必须对莫罗斯做点什么了。' WHERE entry=8969; /* Text0_0: About time the guild sent some new blood our way! Too bad you came all this way for nothing. We\'re not allowed to put on a show for our guests, can you believe it? Moroes has forbidden us from starting a new show, and my backers are going nuts! Something needs to be done about Moroes. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='终於，一切就绪。你准备好初次登台了吗?',Text0_1_loc4='无论萨尔是否存在，破碎之手氏族的秩序都将延续下去。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=8970; /* Text0_0: Finally, everything is in place. Are you ready for your big stage debut? */ /* Text0_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text0: */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='别担心，你会没事的。吉人自有天相!',Text0_1_loc4='无论萨尔是否存在，破碎之手氏族的秩序都将延续下去。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=8971; /* Text0_0: Don\'t worry, you\'ll be fine. You look like a natural! */ /* Text0_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text0: */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你可以在碧蓝岗哨的南面和东面找到月痕雄鹿。' WHERE entry=8972; /* Text0_0: Moongraze stags can be found grazing south and east of Azure Watch. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='就在碧蓝岗哨的北面，你在那里很容易找到月痕巨鹿。$B$B狩猎愉快，$n！' WHERE entry=8973; /* Text0_0: Just north of Azure Watch is where you will have the best luck finding moongraze bucks.$B$BHappy hunting, $N! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='那些被感染的小型夜间潜伏者好像是从北边来的。如果我是你，我会从那里开始猎捕。' WHERE entry=8974; /* Text0_0: The infected nightstalker runts seem to be coming from the north. If I were you, that\'s where I would start my hunt. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你没看到我在忙吗?',Text0_1_loc4='无论萨尔是否存在，破碎之手氏族的秩序都将延续下去。' WHERE entry=8978; /* Text0_0: Can\'t you see that I\'m busy? */ /* Text0_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text0: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='粗俗的观众，但你会说服他们的。准备好再试一次吗?' WHERE entry=8981; /* Text0_0: Rough audience, but you\'ll win them over. Ready for another shot? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='[熊怪语]米欧\'欧克 克斯 伊尔芬 欧 欧姆托…',Text1_0_loc4='[熊怪语]米欧\'欧克 克斯 伊尔芬 欧 欧姆托…' WHERE entry=8983; /* Text0_0: [Furbolg] Mil\'ork kix ilfin o oomtor... */ /* Text1_0: [Furbolg] Poorov\'tarkh! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text2_0_loc4='[熊怪语]米欧\'欧克 克斯 伊尔芬 欧 欧姆托…',Text3_0_loc4='[熊怪语]米欧\'欧克 克斯 伊尔芬 欧 欧姆托…' WHERE entry=8983; /* Text2_0: [Furbolg] Yar vartslaf? */ /* Text3_0: [Furbolg] Boro gomsho! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='有什麽我能帮忙的吗，陌生人?' WHERE entry=8990; /* Text0_0: How can I help you, stranger? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='克夫是我的名字，陌生人。勇者克夫!' WHERE entry=8991; /* Text0_0: Gurf is my name, stranger. Gurf the Brave! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我是墨尔多，静松的长者猎人。' WHERE entry=8992; /* Text0_0: I am Moordo, elder hunter of Stillpine. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='欢迎来到我的店铺!' WHERE entry=8993; /* Text0_0: Welcome to my shop! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='啊，允诺者已来到。欢迎来到静松要塞。' WHERE entry=8994; /* Text0_0: Ah, the Promised One has arrived. Welcome to Stillpine Hold. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='好消息，$c。我是静松年少者，静松王座的继承人。' WHERE entry=8996; /* Text0_0: Good tidings, $c. I am Stillpine the Younger, heir to the throne of Stillpine. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你要保卫我的人民并为静松开创一个新的繁荣时代!' WHERE entry=8997; /* Text0_0: It is you who will defend my people and usher in a new era of prosperity for Stillpine! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我现在忙着处理马蹄铁的事。你可以改天再来吗?' WHERE entry=9002; /* Text0_0: I\'m afraid I\'m rather busy fixing horseshoes at the moment.  Would you mind coming back at another time? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我曾经为麦迪文效命...或是说假装为他效命。我希望紫罗兰之眼可以盯紧主人。$B$B但是现在我所想的只有...制作马蹄铁。不断地做。' WHERE entry=9003; /* Text0_0: I once served Medivh... or pretended to.  I helped the Violet Eye keep a close eye on the Master.$B$BBut now all I can think of is... making horseshoes.  Over and over. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='那你知道紫罗兰之眼吗?或许我等下才有空跟你说话。$B$B我要回去工作了。' WHERE entry=9004; /* Text0_0: You know about the Violet Eye then?  Maybe I\'ll have time for you later.$B$BI have to get back to my work. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我可以感觉到你对力量的渴望，$c。',Text0_1_loc4='我可以感觉到你对力量的渴望，$c。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=9006; /* Text0_0: I can sense your desire for power, $c. */ /* Text0_1: I can sense your desire for power, $c. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='圣光给我们力量和魔法来获得胜利!',Text0_1_loc4='圣光给我们力量和魔法来获得胜利!',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=9007; /* Text0_0: The Light gives us the strength and magic to triumph. */ /* Text0_1: The Light gives us the strength and magic to triumph. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你好，年轻的萨满。在我的沙洲内就把这里当自己的家吧。' WHERE entry=9014; /* Text0_0: Greetings, young shaman.  Make yourself at home within my reef. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我们会一起解决水质腐败的问题。' WHERE entry=9015; /* Text0_0: Together we will deal with this corruption of the water. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你做了一件伟大的事，$N。这里任何时候都欢迎你。' WHERE entry=9016; /* Text0_0: You have done a great thing, $N.  You are welcome here at any time. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我有新鲜的肉，鱼，和蘑菇。还有一大堆饮料!' WHERE entry=9020; /* Text0_0: I\'ve got fresh meat, fish and mushrooms.  And plenty to drink! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我是埃德门图斯，秘血岗哨的首领。' WHERE entry=9022; /* Text0_0: I am Admetius, leader of Blood Watch. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='欢迎来到萨尔玛，$n。随着你在萨尔玛的声望不断提升，我可以让你使用我们的更多物资。' WHERE entry=9023; /* Text0_0: Welcome to Thrallmar, $N!  As you continue to aid us in our cause, I will grant you access to more of our supplies. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='需要帮忙照顾你的动物夥伴吗?' WHERE entry=9024; /* Text0_0: Need me to take care of your animal companions? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='在阿古斯，麦克艾瑞是我们最神圣的城市。$B$B如果我告诉你走道两旁都排列着珍贵的矿物你会相信吗?河里即使是全黑的也闪着光芒?$B$B我渴望那些日子...已经过了多久了?一千年?一万年?' WHERE entry=9025; /* Text0_0: On Argus, Mac\'Aree was the most sacred of our cities.$B$BWould you believe me if I told you that the walkways were lined with precious minerals? That the rivers glittered even in complete darkness?$B$BI long for those days... How long has it been? A thousand years? Ten-thousand? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='搜索一下将小岛一分为二的河流，但是要多加小心，水里有很多臭角刺鱼。' WHERE entry=9028; /* Text0_0: Look in the waters that divide this island, but be warned: the stinkhorn striker makes its home in the waters of the river. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='欢迎来到秘血岗哨，$c。在我的旅途中，我收集到了各种文明的工具、文物和知识。$B$B如果你需要这些知识，只管来问我就是了。' WHERE entry=9029; /* Text0_0: Welcome to Blood Watch, $c. In my travels, I have amassed a wide variety of tools, artifacts, and knowledge from the various peoples we\'ve encountered.$B$BShould you find yourself in need of this knowledge, you have only to ask. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='顾名思义，你可以在洛雷萨兰废墟周围找到这东西。$B$B确切地说，这名字其实是我起的……很棒吧。' WHERE entry=9030; /* Text0_0: As the name suggests, it can be found near ruins. Loreth\'Aran holds the answer.$B$BActually, the name doesn\'t really suggest that -- I was just trying to be clever in naming the fungi. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='邪锥这个名字起源于堕落的邪恶魔法。去纳兹维安萨特营地寻找邪锥蘑菇吧，就在西边。' WHERE entry=9031; /* Text0_0: Fel cone derives its name from fel magic corruption. Seek the fel cone fungus at the Nazzivian satyr camp - to the west. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='血蘑菇和其它蘑菇比起来就普通多了，几乎可以在秘血岛周围森林中的任何地方找到。如果你不想丢了小命，就到秘血岛上的大道南边找找。' WHERE entry=9032; /* Text0_0: Blood mushrooms are more common than the other fungi varieties and can be found mostly anywhere in the woods around Bloodmyst. Keep your search south of the road dividing Bloodmyst if you value your life. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='如果你在血谜岛的时间里只学会一件事，$c，我希望那是警惕。这座岛会先夺去不警惕的生命，再开始削弱最谨慎的战士。$B$B你所到之处，都有一个敌人准备好要夺走你的性命。' WHERE entry=9033; /* Text0_0: If you only learn one thing during your time in Bloodmyst, $c, I hope that it is vigilance. This island claims the unwary first, then begins to wear down even the most guarded of warriors.$B$BEverywhere you turn, a foe stands ready to take your life. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='其他人看着这片风景而他们只看到了死亡，腐败，和厄运。没有任何东西短缺，的确，但眼前的景象让人忽略了我们环境所带来的机会。$B$B我不会坐视不管让这些机会被白白忽略，$c。有了你的帮助，我们可以让血色守望这里的其他人看看如何利用环境和其中的生物。' WHERE entry=9036; /* Text0_0: The others look at this landscape and see only death, corruption, and adversity. None of those things are in short supply, true, but that view ignores the opportunities presented by our environment.$B$BI will not stand by and watch these opportunities go ignored, $c. With your help, we can demonstrate to the others here at Blood Watch just how to make use of the environment and its creatures. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='哈罗，$c。$B$B长者凯索在那里，他是个聪明的人。如果我是你，我会非常小心的和他交易。$B$B他提供我照料伊莱克的工作叫我当一个蠢蛋，我以为是供我吃，训练，等等之类的。后来当他递给我铁锹时一切就很明显了...' WHERE entry=9037; /* Text0_0: Hello, $c.$B$BOld man Kessel over there, he\'s a clever one. I\'d be real careful in my dealings with him if I were you.$B$BHe offered me work \'caring for the elekk\' and being the fool I was, I took it to mean feeding, training, and the like. Things became real clear when he handed me the shovel... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='谢谢你的警告，$N!我们会做好准备!' WHERE entry=9038; /* Text0_0: Thanks for the warning, $N! We shall prepare! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='允诺者，我们感谢你的警告。静松部族会做好准备。' WHERE entry=9039; /* Text0_0: Promised One, we thank you for the warning. The Stillpine tribe will be prepared. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='谢谢你的警告，$N。我们会做好防御。' WHERE entry=9040; /* Text0_0: Thank you for the warning, $N. We will prepare our defenses. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我是凯索，伊莱克的统治者，阿古斯之手的追随者。你是新成员吗?' WHERE entry=9041; /* Text0_0: I am Kessel, lord of the elekk, disciple of the Hand of Argus. Are you the new recruit? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我是阿彻鲁斯，秘血岗哨远征军首席指挥官。' WHERE entry=9042; /* Text0_0: I am Achelus, chief expeditionary officer of Blood Watch. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我是往来于这里和秘蓝岛之间的邮差，$c。如果你有什么消息需要递送，很可能是要交给我来办的。' WHERE entry=9043; /* Text0_0: I deliver the mail to and from Azuremyst, $c. If you need a message delivered, it\'ll more than likely be routed through me first. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='成为阿古斯之手的意义...我们是圣光的密探。我们毫无疑问的效命。没有怀疑的死去。' WHERE entry=9044; /* Text0_0: What it means to be a Hand of Argus... We are agents of the Light. We serve without question. We die without question. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='是他们派你来找我的吗?我不会丢下我的人回去的。' WHERE entry=9045; /* Text0_0: Did they send you to find me? Well I\'m not going back without my men. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='是的，我是「破碎者」的一员。我相信这不会让你困扰吧?破碎者或德莱尼，我们一定要容忍社会对我们的奚落和嘲笑。和这世界的元素有更好的了解和沟通才是最重要的事。' WHERE entry=9050; /* Text0_0: Yes, I am one of the \'Broken\'.  I trust that this does not bother you?  Broken or draenei, we must endure the ridicule that some in our society may throw at us.  A better understanding and communication with the elements of this world is all that matters. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='请坐，请随意。',Text0_1_loc4='请坐，请随意。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=9051; /* Text0_0: Please, sit and make yourself comfortable. */ /* Text0_1: Please, sit and make yourself comfortable. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你好，$c。你需要一只可靠的角鹰兽吗?' WHERE entry=9052; /* Text0_0: Good day, $c. Are you in need of a reliable hippogryph? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='如果你需要去埃索达，就乘坐我的角鹰兽吧！' WHERE entry=9053; /* Text0_0: If you need to travel to the Exodar, I have just the hippogryph for you! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='嘘!安静;我正在观察鱼人。$B$B住在一个超大型的乌龟壳里是我愿意为科学所做的牺牲。毕竟，如果鱼人看到我在这里，他们的反应就会因为我的存在而改变，那样会降低我资料的真实度!$B$B身为探险者协会的第一名侏儒成员，我大胆地进入没有矮人敢去的地方!' WHERE entry=9054; /* Text0_0: Shh! Be very quiet; I\'m observing murlocs.$B$BLiving in an oversized turtle shell is a sacrifice I\'m willing to make for science. After all, if the murlocs see me here, they\'ll react to my presence and contaminate my data!$B$BAs the first gnomish member of the Explorers\' League, I\'m boldly going places no dwarf has gone before! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你疯了吗?看看你的四周，凡人。你没看到你站在分裂的大地上吗?离开这个地方，以免你遭受和我与人民一样的苦……' WHERE entry=9056; /* Text0_0: Are you mad? Look around you, mortal. Do you not see that you stand upon sundered earth? Leave this place lest you suffer as my people and I have... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你是个疯了还是瞎了?$B$B我是个鬼魂 - 一个残忍的提醒者，提醒着很久不存在的文明 - 系住一块我无法保护的土地。$B$B很久以前 - 一万年前 - 我是有血有肉的人，就像你一样。我是这块土地的王子也是个龙骑士，受翡翠梦境的伊瑟拉所庇护。' WHERE entry=9057; /* Text0_0: Are you blind as well as insane?$B$BI am a ghost - a cruel reminder of a civilization that has long since ceased to exist - anchored to a land that I failed to protect.$B$BLong ago - ten-thousand years past - I was flesh and bone, just like you. I was prince of this land and a dragon rider, blessed by Ysera of the Dream. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你没听过伊瑟拉?大自然的守护者?梦境之龙?她是所有绿龙军团的母亲!是的，是伊瑟拉亲自将她的后裔赠送给我的王国。我们和这些高贵的生物肩并肩作战，他们也允许我们骑着他们进入战场对抗我们的敌人。一切都相当地美好，持续了许多个世纪……直到……' WHERE entry=9058; /* Text0_0: Have you not heard of Ysera? Guardian of nature? Aspect of the Dream? She is the matron of all green dragons! Aye, it was Ysera herself that gifted my kingdom with her brood. We stood shoulder to shoulder with the noble creatures and they allowed us to ride them into battle against our enemies. All was well for many centuries... until... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='死亡之翼的后代……伊瑟拉的仁慈唤起了死亡之翼的愤怒 - 黑龙军团的庇护者。他们在我们沉睡中袭击我们!许多人在一开始的攻击中就死了，但绿龙军团便来保护我们。$B$B<托瑞斯王子指着这座岛。>$B$B那些曾经伟大的龙群只剩下这些白骨。没有一个幸免。' WHERE entry=9059; /* Text0_0: Deathwing\'s brood... Ysera\'s benevolence raised the ire of Deathwing - patron of the black dragonflight. They attacked us in our sleep! Many died on the initial surge but the greens rose to protect us.$B$B<Prince Toreth points around the island.>$B$BThe bones are all that remain of the once great dragons. None were spared. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我是最后一个死的人。当我感觉我的灵魂离开了我的凡人躯壳，我便发下血誓。$B$B<托瑞斯王子摇摇他的头。>$B$B我和这块土地签下一个契约:我的鲜血为这世界泼洒。我成了唯一守护我人民历史的人。$B$B在我确信罗萨伦龙骑士的故事尚未消失在时间的洪流之前我不会休息的。' WHERE entry=9060; /* Text0_0: I was the last to die. As I felt my spirit leaving my mortal shell, I swore a blood oath.$B$B<Prince Toreth shakes his head.>$B$BA pact was made between this land and I: My blood for this world. I became the sole keeper of the history of my people.$B$BI cannot rest until I am secure in knowing that the story of the dragon riders of Loreth\'Aran is not lost in the passages of time. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='学生就像绵羊。当你引导并密切注意他们，他们就会变的很有用甚至很可爱。$B$B你离开他们一下，他们就从悬崖上跌下或溺死在很浅的河里。' WHERE entry=9061; /* Text0_0: Students are a bit like sheep.  They\'re useful and even likeable when you guide and pay close attention to them.$B$BYou leave them alone for a minute and they end up falling down a cliff or drowning in a shallow river. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='这个公告牌上张贴着多种公告和执行危险任务的奖励。现在没什么可以吸引你的东西，也许你应该过段时间再回来看看。' WHERE entry=9062; /* Text0_0: This sign contains various announcements and notices of rewards for performing dangerous sounding tasks.  Nothing particularly catches your eye; perhaps you should check again at a later time. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你好，居民。如果你没什麽事要问我，那就请你走吧。' WHERE entry=9063; /* Text0_0: Greetings, citizen. I ask that you move along if you have nothing to ask of me. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你办到了!太杰出了!温德索尔元帅一直在等你。要不要我现在去通知他?' WHERE entry=9065; /* Text0_0: You made it! Outstanding! Marshal Windsor has been expecting you. Would you like me to signal him now? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='离我远一点，$r!当病痛再次对我缠身就不要再和我接近了。$B$B在它再发生之前不要再来找我。' WHERE entry=9067; /* Text0_0: Stay away from me, $r! There\'s no telling when the sickness will take me again.$B$BJust leave me alone before it happens again. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='检查屍体你推论这一定是血骑士晨星，死亡之域失败突击的领导者。' WHERE entry=9070; /* Text0_0: Examining the corpse, you conclude that this must be Blood Knight Dawnstar, the leader of the failed assault on Deatholme. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我可以帮你建立一个公会。' WHERE entry=9071; /* Text0_0: I can help you establish a guild. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='翻遍血骑士的尸体之后，你找到了那枚徽章。它并没有因为战争和周围的环境而受到任何损伤。' WHERE entry=9072; /* Text0_0: A search of the corpse\'s clothing and equipment reveals the insignia you need, undamaged by the battle and foul environment. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你以荣誉为三人之一效命，$N。我们的时间已到尽头。库罗斯准备好后会告诉你。' WHERE entry=9076; /* Text0_0: You have served one of three with honor, $N. Our time is at an end. Kuros will call for you when he is ready. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你好，$c。我是库罗斯，三头政治的第二人。' WHERE entry=9077; /* Text0_0: Greetings, $c. I am Kuros, second of the Triumvirate of the Hand. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我想尖叫可是只有一声低喘迸出我嘴边。我很快就被这次的反叛行动给打败。当我躺在地上，我可以看见马帝斯在萨鲁安的屍体前跺步。他看起来很担心。他声称如果萨鲁安被後打死去，赛罗娜斯或赛罗娜或类似这样的实体会把他的肉体从骨头上剥下。' WHERE entry=9081; /* Text0_0: I wanted to scream but only a low gasp escaped my lips. I was promptly beaten for this act of rebellion. As I lay on the ground, I could see Matis pacing in front of Saruan\'s body. He seemed visibly concerned. He stated that Sironas or Sirona or some such entity would have his flesh flayed from his bones if Saruan had perished in the beatings. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你好，$c。如果你想学习铁匠的艺术，那麽你来对地方了。' WHERE entry=9084; /* Text0_0: Good day, $c. If you wish to learn the smith\'s art, you\'ve come to the right place. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我们塞纳里奥的德鲁伊是自然平衡的保卫者。重点是平衡。当我们被徵召时一定要尽速采取果断的行动。不要让任何人左右你，尤其是我们之中那些只想静观其变的人。' WHERE entry=9086; /* Text0_0: We Cenarion druids are the protectors of the balance of nature.  The main point being the balance.  When called for, we shouldn\'t wait too long before taking decisive action.  Don\'t let anyone tell you otherwise, especially those of us who only want to observe! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你是谁?不要来烦我。' WHERE entry=9090; /* Text0_0: Who are you?  Just leave me be. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='到北方开始你的搜索吧，$N。我们的斥候已锁定海案线旁的星移活塞。' WHERE entry=9097; /* Text0_0: Begin your search to the north, $N. Our scouts have spotted the Warp Piston near the shoreline. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我的故事?你这样问真好。非常好。$B$B很久以前在德拉诺行星上 - 也就是现在残余的外域 - 所有的德莱尼都和平共处。但是后来燃烧军团来了，他们用邪恶魔法腐败了兽人。$B$B别无选择，我们为生存而作战，但暴露在这些邪恶能量下已对我们一些人产生了可怕的作用，长时间后将我们转变成像我一样的破碎者，或是更糟，看似无脑的失落者。$B$B我要继续吗?' WHERE entry=9098; /* Text0_0: My story? It is kind of you to ask. Very well.$B$BLong ago on the planet Draenor - the remains of which are now known as the Outland - all of the draenei lived in peace. But then the Burning Legion came, and they corrupted the orcs with their fel magics.$B$BWith no other option we fought to survive, but exposure to these fel energies had horrible effects upon some of us, over time transforming us into the Broken like me, or worse, the seemingly mindless Lost Ones.$B$BShall I go on? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我们身体的改变对破碎者和失落者造成副作用，切断我们和圣光的关系。当时我不知道为什麽，但身为一个牧师的我坚持要找出原因。我决定进行朝圣来找出答案。$B$B战争结束之后，我前往破碎行星的沙漠恳求圣光回到我们身边。但几十年过去，圣光从未回覆过我的祈求。$B$B你想再听下去吗?' WHERE entry=9099; /* Text0_0: The fel energies also had the side-effect on the Broken and the Lost Ones of cutting us off from the Light. At the time I did not know exactly why, but as a vindicator I insisted on finding out. I decided to make a pilgrimage to do just that.$B$BAnd so it was that after the war came to its fateful end, I journeyed into the desert of the fragmented planet, beseeching the Light to return to us. But decades passed, and the Light never answered my prayers.$B$BIs this something that you wish to hear more of? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我很幸运发现一个绿洲并决定留在那里直到我得到一个解答。然后我就坐在那里，只有必要的时候才会移动，以接近水边的生物维生。我引以为傲。$B$B如我所说，几十年过去了都没有一个答案。但我记得有一天傍晚的夕阳特别美丽。一阵微风轻拂大地，我确信我听到了一个声音，但附近并没有人。$B$B你可以想像，我以为我真的疯了。' WHERE entry=9100; /* Text0_0: I had been fortunate to find an oasis and made the decision to stay there until I received an answer. So there I sat, moving only when absolutely necessary, living off of the creatures that would come near the pool. Such was my pride.$B$BAs I said, decades passed without an answer. But I can remember a particularly beautiful sunset one evening. A warm zephyr blew across the land and I was sure that I heard a voice, but no one was around.$B$BAs you can imagine, I thought that I was finally losing my mind. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='这风有点不对劲;它停不下来。几周以来它一直吹着大地，不断变大又变小，但就是不停止。而且声音不断呼啸，不过我不太懂那是什麽意思，也不知道它究竟是从哪里来的。$B$B我隐居的日子让我学会如何平静下来并检视内心。这样做我才能保持清醒。而就是那时候我才开始了解那声音的意思。它是风发出的声音，有很多话想说!' WHERE entry=9101; /* Text0_0: There was something strange about that wind; it didn\'t stop. For weeks it blew across the land, waxing and waning, but never ceasing. And all the time the voice continued, though I could not understand it, nor did I know where it was coming from.$B$BMy time in solitude had taught me how to calm myself and look inward. This I did in order to keep my sanity. And that is when I began to understand the voice. It was coming from the wind itself and it had much to say! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='它告诉了我秘密和力量，同样也告诉我了真相。圣光并没有遗弃破碎者！很久以前，兽人用来对付德莱尼人的魔能已经侵入了我们的躯体，使我们聆听圣光的能力被封闭了，同时也导致了我们身体的退化。$B$B但是我们的灵魂并没有被封闭，空气给了我另一种选择，让我可以指引我的人民。' WHERE entry=9102; /* Text0_0: It spoke to me of secrets and power, and also of truths. The Light had not forsaken the Broken! The fel energies that the orcs had wielded long ago against the draenei had infused us, causing a break in our ability to be heard by, or perhaps to hear, the Light. The same that had been responsible for the degradation of our bodies.$B$BBut our spirits were not broken, and the air offered to me another path, through which I might deliver my people. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='它教了我萨满之道，在某种程度上它也是圣光的另一层面。加入风的是海洋的水，我的营地的火，和我坐着的土。所有元素都有话要说。$B$B过去几年他们教我如何召唤并与世界的元素同在。而且他们告诉我这世界天空中的所有星星，就连这一颗也一样，都是由这些元素形成的。$B$B但终於有一天我觉得我已学得够多足以离开了。' WHERE entry=9103; /* Text0_0: It taught me the path of shamanism, which in a way is just another facet of the Light. Joining the wind was the water of the oasis, the fire from my camp and the earth upon which I sat. All had something to say.$B$BOver the next few years they taught me what it was to call upon and be one with the elements of the world. And they told me that the worlds of all of the stars in the sky, even this one, are made up of these elements.$B$BBut the day came when I felt that I had learned enough to leave. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我回到我的人民那里，他们用微笑的脸庞和敞开的双臂迎接我，大部份都是破碎者。我不在的时候德莱尼对我们的偏见仍持续存在。但他们好像早就知道我要来了，而我很快就了解为什麽。$B$B费伦，德莱尼的领导者和预言家都在他们的幻象中看过我回来，他们也在那里欢迎我。他要求与我私下谈话而当我诉说我的故事给他听时，他点头并微笑，因为这些他都预见过了。' WHERE entry=9104; /* Text0_0: I returned to my people and was greeted with smiling faces and outstretched arms, mostly from the Broken. The prejudices against us from many draenei had continued in my absence. But it was as if they knew that I was coming, and I soon found out why.$B$BVelen, the prophet and leader of all of the draenei, had seen my return in one of his visions and was there to greet me as well. He asked to speak with me in private and as I related my story to him, he nodded and smiled, for this too he had foreseen. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='费伦鼓励我肩起破碎者领导者的职务。但更重要的是，他要我教所有人萨满之道;破碎者和德莱尼都一样。我接受了。$B$B我们后来便知道对某些人有偏见顶多也只是不随和的主张罢了。有些人鄙视破碎者，因为我们总是提醒着令人恐惧的过去。还有其他人认为萨满之道是对圣光的亵渎。$B$B无论如何，这是我的故事。' WHERE entry=9105; /* Text0_0: Velen urged me to take a leadership role amongst the Broken. But more importantly, he asked me to teach shamanism to all; Broken and draenei alike. I accepted.$B$BWe knew then that given the prejudices of some that this would be a difficult proposition at best. There are those that despise the Broken because we are a frightening reminder of the past. And there are others who believe the way of the shaman to be a blasphemy against the Light.$B$BIn any case, that is my tale. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='如果敌人能知道我们只想和他们和平共处，或许我们就不必冒生命危险攻打他们。' WHERE entry=9106; /* Text0_0: If our enemies would see that we only wish to live in harmony with them, maybe we wouldn\'t have to attack them for our own survival? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='随着新的敌人向我们逼近，我们绝对不能让旧时的敌人利用了我们现在的状况!' WHERE entry=9108; /* Text0_0: With new enemies on our doorsteps, we must not allow our ancient enemies to take advantage of our situation! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你说，你看到西面那个拱形的东西划过湖泊吗？我在想那东西去哪里了……也许我应该潜水到那里去看看。' WHERE entry=9110; /* Text0_0: Say, you happen to see that arch in the lake to the west?  I wonder where that goes?  I should go divin\' over there. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='恶心的真菌巨人！我们到底欠他们什么？' WHERE entry=9111; /* Text0_0: Filthy fungal giants!  What did we ever do to them? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='费斯伍尔喜欢小孢子人。他们拯救费斯伍尔。费斯伍尔不吃他们。$B$B费斯伍尔痛恨纳迦。费斯伍尔猛击!' WHERE entry=9113; /* Text0_0: Fhwoor like little sporelings.  They save Fhwoor.  Not eat them.$B$BFhwoor hate naga.  Fhwoor smash! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我是艾伊森，三头政治的第三人。' WHERE entry=9117; /* Text0_0: I am Aesom, third of the Triumvirate. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我就快要成功了!$B$B我来这里证明奎克米瑞的存在，最具神话色彩的真菌巨人。以某个角度来想，我已经达成我的愿望了。$B$B你一定要释放我!为了答谢你，我将会给你一点回报让你去对付奎克米瑞。' WHERE entry=9119; /* Text0_0: I almost made it!$B$BI came in here to prove the existence of Quagmirran, that most mythical of fungal giants.  I got my wish, sort of.$B$BYou must let me free!  In return I will grant you a boon to help you to deal with Quagmirran. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='谢天谢地还好有你!我和裂爪被沼泽之王莫斯莱克攻击的时候正在调查这个地方。他可以控制动物，就连德鲁伊也不例外!$B$B不幸的是，当时裂爪以熊形态被抓去，现在成了沼泽之王莫斯莱克的宠物。我不敢变成豹形态否则他也会把我抓去!$B$B不过你要救裂爪就要先和他打一场。只要往西走;你就会碰到他。' WHERE entry=9121; /* Text0_0: Thank goodness for you!  Claw and I were investigating this place when we were jumped by Swamplord Musel\'ek.  He can control animals, even druids!$B$BUnfortunately, Claw was caught in bear form at the time, and is now the swamplord\'s pet.  I don\'t dare change into cat form or he\'ll get me too!$B$BI\'m afraid you\'ll have to fight Claw in order to save him.  Just keep heading west; you can\'t miss him. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='身为唯一显而易见的幸存「破碎者」，传承先知诺柏多的萨满教学是我的责任也是荣耀。' WHERE entry=9122; /* Text0_0: As the only apparent surviving \'Broken\', it is both my duty and honor to carry on the shamanistic teachings of Farseer Nobundo. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='不要浪费我的时间。你想要什麽?',Text0_1_loc4='不要浪费我的时间。你想要什麽?',Text1_0_loc4='不要浪费我的时间。你想要什麽?',Text1_1_loc4='不要浪费我的时间。你想要什麽?' WHERE entry=9124; /* Text0_0: Do not waste my time.  What is it you want? */ /* Text0_1: Do not waste my time.  What is it you want? */ /* Text1_0: Can you not see that I am busy here? */ /* Text1_1: Can you not see that I am busy here? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text2_0_loc4='不要浪费我的时间。你想要什麽?',Text2_1_loc4='不要浪费我的时间。你想要什麽?',Text3_0_loc4='不要浪费我的时间。你想要什麽?',Text3_1_loc4='不要浪费我的时间。你想要什麽?' WHERE entry=9124; /* Text2_0: Yes?  What do you want? */ /* Text2_1: Yes?  What do you want? */ /* Text3_0: And you are? */ /* Text3_1: And you are? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='被猎人当做宠物来养是多麽难为情的一件事!$B$B你救了我一命，但拜托你，麻烦不要再干扰我的幸福了。既然你已从莫斯莱克那里释放了我，我就能自己找到生路。或许我还会顺道碰上瑞吉。' WHERE entry=9125; /* Text0_0: How embarrassing to be taken as a pet by a hunter!$B$BI owe you my life, but please, trouble yourself no longer with my welfare.  Now that you\'ve freed me from Musel\'ek, I\'ll be able to find my way out.  Maybe I\'ll pick up Rayge along the way. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='<复仇者艾伊森向你致敬。>$B$B你和阿德密特斯谈过了吗?我想他在打听你的下落。' WHERE entry=9130; /* Text0_0: <Vindicator Aesom salutes you.>$B$BHave you spoken with Admetius? I believe he was inquiring as to your whereabouts. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='德鲁伊们保护我不受邪恶的纳迦和失落者的伤害。作为交换，我向他们传授有关这片沼泽中的植物和动物的知识。' WHERE entry=9131; /* Text0_0: The druids protect me from the naga and evil Lost Ones.  In exchange, I teach them about the plants and animals of the marsh. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='感谢我被锁在这笼子里，$r。',Text0_1_loc4='感谢我被锁在这笼子里，$r。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=9134; /* Text0_0: Be thankful that I am locked inside this cage, $r. */ /* Text0_1: Be thankful that I am locked inside this cage, $r. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='<被俘虏的太阳之鹰密探怀疑地看着你。>$B$B我从没见过你。你是谁?',Text0_1_loc4='<被俘虏的太阳之鹰密探怀疑地看着你。>$B$B我从没见过你。你是谁?',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=9136; /* Text0_0: <The captured Sunhawk agent eyes you suspiciously.>$B$BI\'ve never seen you before. Who are you? */ /* Text0_1: <The captured Sunhawk agent eyes you suspiciously.>$B$BI\'ve never seen you before. Who are you? */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='<被俘虏的太阳之鹰密探奸笑。>$B$B别担心，新成员，还有更多传送门控制器和更多适合的传送地点。我相信赛罗娜斯很快就会有一个新的入口了。这些蓝皮肤的狗在这世界活不久了。赛罗娜斯和憎恨会把太阳之鹰军队留下的所有事物都清理的一乾二净。',Text0_1_loc4='<被俘虏的太阳之鹰密探奸笑。>$B$B别担心，新成员，还有更多传送门控制器和更多适合的传送地点。我相信赛罗娜斯很快就会有一个新的入口了。这些蓝皮肤的狗在这世界活不久了。赛罗娜斯和憎恨会把太阳之鹰军队留下的所有事物都清理的一乾二净。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=9137; /* Text0_0: <The captured Sunhawk agent smirks.>$B$BDon\'t worry, new blood, there are many more portal controllers and many more suitable locations for portals. I am certain that Sironas will have a new gate up very soon. These blue skinned dogs are not long for this world. Sironas and the abomination will clean up whatever the Sunhawk forces leave behind. */ /* Text0_1: <The captured Sunhawk agent smirks.>$B$BDon\'t worry, new blood, there are many more portal controllers and many more suitable locations for portals. I am certain that Sironas will have a new gate up very soon. These blue skinned dogs are not long for this world. Sironas and the abomination will clean up whatever the Sunhawk forces leave behind. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='那是希隆娜丝的主意……那个畸变者，确切地说，是一个德莱尼人。他是个德莱尼军事统帅部的高级成员，好像是叫三人执政团或者类似的东西。$B$B不管怎么说，他都是个魁梧、强大、充满愤怒的家伙。只要畸变者还在，任何针对矢量感应器的进攻都完全是浪费时间。',Text0_1_loc4='那是希隆娜丝的主意……那个畸变者，确切地说，是一个德莱尼人。他是个德莱尼军事统帅部的高级成员，好像是叫三人执政团或者类似的东西。$B$B不管怎么说，他都是个魁梧、强大、充满愤怒的家伙。只要畸变者还在，任何针对矢量感应器的进攻都完全是浪费时间。' WHERE entry=9138; /* Text0_0: It was Sironas\' idea... The abomination is actually one of their own. He is a high ranking member of the draenei military order: Triumvirate or some such nonsense.$B$BWhatever that thing is, it\'s massive, powerful, and full of rage. Any attacks against the Vector Coil will most certainly result in failure as long as that abomination is around. */ /* Text0_1: It was Sironas\' idea... The abomination is actually one of their own. He is a high ranking member of the draenei military order: Triumvirate or some such nonsense.$B$BWhatever that thing is, it\'s massive, powerful, and full of rage. Any attacks against the Vector Coil will most certainly result in failure as long as that abomination is around. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='很明显。不然她要怎麽渗入他们的阶级并以一个德莱尼的身份通过?她和他们住在一起很长的一段时间。',Text0_1_loc4='很明显。不然她要怎麽渗入他们的阶级并以一个德莱尼的身份通过?她和他们住在一起很长的一段时间。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=9140; /* Text0_0: Obviously. How else could she infiltrate their ranks and pass as a draenei? She had been living among them for a very long time. */ /* Text0_1: Obviously. How else could she infiltrate their ranks and pass as a draenei? She had been living among them for a very long time. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='很多?它有两个弱点:那栋建筑物西边和东边的底部。嘿，等等。你怎麽会知道旋绕导航器的事?你不是说你在成形之前都被俘虏了吗?',Text0_1_loc4='很多?它有两个弱点:那栋建筑物西边和东边的底部。嘿，等等。你怎麽会知道旋绕导航器的事?你不是说你在成形之前都被俘虏了吗?',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=9141; /* Text0_0: Numerous? It has two weak points: The base of the structure on the west side and the base of the structure on the east side. Hey, wait a minute. How would you know anything about the Vector Coil? Didn\'t you say that you were captured before you even materialized? */ /* Text0_1: Numerous? It has two weak points: The base of the structure on the west side and the base of the structure on the east side. Hey, wait a minute. How would you know anything about the Vector Coil? Didn\'t you say that you were captured before you even materialized? */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='是时候来摧毁旋绕导航器了!' WHERE entry=9142; /* Text0_0: The time has come to destroy the Vector Coil! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='粗野的干扰已结束，如我所说，奎克米瑞已经接近了!$B$B依先前允诺的，我可以用一个魔法恩赐增强你的力量，帮助你与他对抗。' WHERE entry=9144; /* Text0_0: Now that the rude interruption is over, as I was saying, Quagmirran is nearby!$B$BAs promised, I can fortify you with a magical boon that should aid you in your fight with him. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='[操着不流利的普通语]是时候庆祝我们做的事了。' WHERE entry=9145; /* Text0_0: [In broken Common] It is time celebrate we do. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='英雄，你还记得我们吗？你还记得库尔兹的预言吗？这是个命中注定的时刻。你完成了你与生俱来的使命。$B$B<止松老酋长在你面前鞠躬。>$B$B德莱尼人会永远受到我的人民的欢迎。' WHERE entry=9146; /* Text0_0: Promised One, do you remember us? Do you recall the prophecy of Kurz? This moment was pre-ordained. You have done what you were put on this world to do.$B$B<High Chief Stillpine bows before you.>$B$BDraenei will always be welcome among my people. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你走了很长一段路，$N。真的是很辛苦...但我知道你注定要成就伟大的事业。我们都知道。全体向$N敬礼!$B$B再次谢谢你解决了我们的侏儒问题...' WHERE entry=9149; /* Text0_0: You\'ve come a long way, $N. A long way indeed... But I knew you were destined for great things.  We all knew. All hail $N!$B$BAnd thanks again for taking care of our gnome problem... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我这辈子都不会忘记的，$n。$B$B<大主教梅内莱厄斯拥抱了你。>$B$B我们为你感到骄傲。' WHERE entry=9154; /* Text0_0: I wouldn\'t have missed this for the world, $N.$B$B<Exarch Menelaous hugs you.>$B$BWe are proud of you. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='很高兴再次见到你，$n。我带了个朋友过来，她非常想见到你。$B$B<凯希尔大笑起来。>' WHERE entry=9156; /* Text0_0: Good to see you again, $N. I brought a friend with me. She really wanted to see you.$B$B<Kessel laughs.> */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我特地穿越无尽之海来看你，朋友。我们永远都不会忘记你为我们所做的一切。' WHERE entry=9159; /* Text0_0: I would have traveled across the Great Sea to see you, friend. We will never forget what you did for us. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我想再次感谢你为我所做的一切。你给了我勇气从森林里的野兽手里夺回我的家园。同时，我还找到了麦格文!' WHERE entry=9160; /* Text0_0: I wanted to thank you once more for what you did for me. You gave me the courage to take back my home from the beasts of the forest. In doing so, I found Magwin! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='德莱尼的勇士就走在我们之中。这是个蓝谜岛和血谜岛救星的庆祝活动!' WHERE entry=9162; /* Text0_0: The draenei champion walks among us. This is a celebration for the savior of Azuremyst and Bloodmyst! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='这全都是给你的，$N。你做到了。你救了所有这些人们和几千几万的生命。$B$B你在这世界的冲突和悲剧之上兴起，将我们和你一起提升。$B$B你做了这麽多 - 比许多人十辈子可以做的还要多 - 但你的生命才刚开始。真希望我们有几千个像你一样的英雄。$B$B但听好了，$N。你的命运在外域。我在幻境中看过一个未透露的预言。$B$B找到我们的人民，$N。找到他们并把他们带回家...' WHERE entry=9163; /* Text0_0: This is all for you, $N. You did this. You saved all of these people and thousands more.$B$BYou have risen above the strife and tragedy of this world and in doing so, elevated all of us with you.$B$BYou have done so much - more than many could do in ten lifetimes - yet your life has just begun. If only we had a thousand heroes like you.$B$BBut listen well, $N. Your destiny lies in the Outland. I have seen it in visions, a prophecy yet untold.$B$BFind our people, $N. Find them and bring them home... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='伊斯欧认为一些敌方对手会对外域展开突击。这就是为什麽我们看守者也来到这里的原因。$B$B我们从未想过我们的对手会以纳迦呈现过的力量或数量出现。' WHERE entry=9167; /* Text0_0: Ysiel expected some enemy opposition to her foray into Outland.  That\'s why us wardens were brought along.$B$BWe never expected our opposition to come in the strength or numbers that the naga have shown. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='[操着不流利的普通语]静松做好准备!非常感激!' WHERE entry=9173; /* Text0_0: [In broken Common] Stillpine be ready! Many thanks! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='欢迎来到血骑士的总部，我们是奎尔萨拉斯的防御者，银月城的忠实仆从，圣光的真正主人。' WHERE entry=9174; /* Text0_0: Welcome to the headquarters of the Blood Knights, the defenders of Quel\'Thalas, the faithful servants of Silvermoon, and the true masters of the Light. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='大自然会帮助那些愿意了解它的奥妙的人，$N。' WHERE entry=9176; /* Text0_0: Nature favors those willing to learn its secrets, $N. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='自然是一种强大的力量，$r。那些想制服大自然的人从未永久成功过。' WHERE entry=9177; /* Text0_0: Nature is a powerful force, $r.  Those who seek to subdue never succeed in doing so permanently. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='灵魂很不安，$r。在纳葛兰要小心你的四周，免得被他们的愤怒给吞噬了。' WHERE entry=9180; /* Text0_0: The spirits are restless, $r. Be mindful of your surroundings while in Nagrand lest you be consumed by their fury. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='陶土议会想要保存元素的力量和庄严。' WHERE entry=9181; /* Text0_0: The Earthen Ring seeks to preserve the strength and majesty of the elements. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我是陶土议会的安崔哥。在元素王座的时候试着不要激怒元素。' WHERE entry=9183; /* Text0_0: I am Untrag of the Earthen Ring. Try not to upset the elements while you remain at the Throne of the Elements. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我可以感觉到你对力量的渴望，$c。',Text0_1_loc4='我可以感觉到你对力量的渴望，$c。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=9184; /* Text0_0: I can sense your desire for power, $c. */ /* Text0_1: I can sense your desire for power, $c. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='抱歉，$c。我把你错认成个有骨气的人。滚开，我们的秘密不是那些没经过训练的家伙有资格知道的。',Text0_1_loc4='抱歉，$c。我把你错认成个有骨气的人。滚开，我们的秘密不是那些没经过训练的家伙有资格知道的。' WHERE entry=9185; /* Text0_0: I apologize, $c. I mistook you for someone with a spine. Begone; our secrets are not for untrained ears. */ /* Text0_1: I apologize, $c. I mistook you for someone with a spine. Begone; our secrets are not for untrained ears. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我现在没空说教，$c。去别的地方寻找你的知识。',Text0_1_loc4='我现在没空说教，$c。去别的地方寻找你的知识。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=9186; /* Text0_0: I have no time for a sermon now, $c. Seek your knowledge elsewhere. */ /* Text0_1: I have no time for a sermon now, $c. Seek your knowledge elsewhere. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='看来你做了错误的选择，$c。',Text0_1_loc4='看来你做了错误的选择，$c。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=9187; /* Text0_0: It appears you took a wrong turn, $c. */ /* Text0_1: It appears you took a wrong turn, $c. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你好，$n。你没被人跟来吧，我能信任你吗?',Text0_1_loc4='你好，$n。你没被人跟来吧，我能信任你吗?',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=9188; /* Text0_0: Greetings, $n. You were not followed here, I trust? */ /* Text0_1: Greetings, $n. You were not followed here, I trust? */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我们没什麽好谈的，$c。或许你该去找别人，和你比较志趣相投的人。',Text0_1_loc4='我们没什麽好谈的，$c。或许你该去找别人，和你比较志趣相投的人。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=9189; /* Text0_0: We have little to discuss, $c. Perhaps you should seek other, more like-minded individuals. */ /* Text0_1: We have little to discuss, $c. Perhaps you should seek other, more like-minded individuals. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='看到这里有人神智清楚真好。有什麽我能帮忙的吗?',Text0_1_loc4='看到这里有人神智清楚真好。有什麽我能帮忙的吗?',Text1_0_loc4='看到这里有人神智清楚真好。有什麽我能帮忙的吗?',Text1_1_loc4='看到这里有人神智清楚真好。有什麽我能帮忙的吗?' WHERE entry=9190; /* Text0_0: It\'s a pleasure to see someone sane around here. How can I help you? */ /* Text0_1: It\'s a pleasure to see someone sane around here. How can I help you? */ /* Text1_0: Ah, a fellow ranger. What do you need? */ /* Text1_1: Ah, a fellow ranger. What do you need? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你明显地缺乏能力掌握秘法繁复难懂的细节，$c。你走吧。',Text0_1_loc4='你明显地缺乏能力掌握秘法繁复难懂的细节，$c。你走吧。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=9191; /* Text0_0: You clearly lack the capacity to grasp the intricacies of the arcane, $c. Off with you. */ /* Text0_1: You clearly lack the capacity to grasp the intricacies of the arcane, $c. Off with you. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我们的道路是给那些有钢铁意志和坚定决心的人走的。你看起来并不拥有这些特质，$c。',Text0_1_loc4='我们的道路是给那些有钢铁意志和坚定决心的人走的。你看起来并不拥有这些特质，$c。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=9193; /* Text0_0: Ours is a path for those with an iron will and unfaltering resolve. You seem to possess none of these traits, $c. */ /* Text0_1: Ours is a path for those with an iron will and unfaltering resolve. You seem to possess none of these traits, $c. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你好，我的$g兄弟:姐妹;。今天你需要怎样的指引呢？',Text0_1_loc4='你好，我的$g兄弟:姐妹;。今天你需要怎样的指引呢？' WHERE entry=9195; /* Text0_0: Greetings, my $g brother : sister;. How can I guide you today? */ /* Text0_1: Greetings, my $g brother : sister;. How can I guide you today? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='这本书包含了外域植物种类的资料。大部份详述的植物都是赞格沼泽土生土长的。$B$B书里的图表对你而言有点难以理解。或许作者可以给你一些指示。' WHERE entry=9197; /* Text0_0: This book contains information on the plant species of Outland.  Most of the plants detailed are native to Zangarmarsh.$B$BThe charts and diagrams are a bit beyond your understanding.  Perhaps the author could give you some pointers. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我还不知道该对你的种族作何感想，$r。你们有些人真的很暴力，一见到孢子人就杀。$B$B你看起来很友善...还长的挺有喜感的。' WHERE entry=9201; /* Text0_0: I don\'t know what to think of your kind yet, $r.  Some of you can be violent and kill sporelings on sight.$B$BYou seem friendly... though maybe a little bit funny looking, I suppose. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='欢迎你来斯博格尔，$r。我们这里通常见不到什麽你们的族人，但你已向我们证明了你的价值。请随意。' WHERE entry=9202; /* Text0_0: I welcome you to Sporeggar, $r.  We don\'t normally see many of your kind around here, but you\'ve proven your worth to us.  Make yourself at home. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='沼泽领主正在吞食孢子囊！必须阻止它们！' WHERE entry=9203; /* Text0_0: The bog lords are devouring the spore sacs!  They\'ve got to be stopped! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='多亏了你我们的青年们才能安全，$N。前往斯博格尔见见我的人民。他们都听过你伟大的事蹟了。' WHERE entry=9204; /* Text0_0: Thanks to you our young ones will be safe, $N.  Go to Sporeggar and meet my people.  They\'ve all heard great things about you. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='<大地的隆隆声因为戈达乌暂停移动而停了下来。>$B$B说。' WHERE entry=9208; /* Text0_0: <The earth rumbles as Gordawg\'s movements come to a halt.>$B$BSpeak. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我父亲去了更光怪陆离的地方寻找更大的猎物。不用担心，我们还会在这里继续打猎！' WHERE entry=9218; /* Text0_0: My father\'s off to more exotic locations in search of bigger prey.  Don\'t worry though, we\'re still on the hunt here! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我父亲在更奇特的地方寻找更大的猎物。不过别担心，我们仍在这里打猎!' WHERE entry=9219; /* Text0_0: Keep a sharp eye, $c.  You never know when some beastie is stalking you instead of the other way around. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='听着$g小子:小姑娘;。我将远征工作交给了我能干的儿子。当你追踪了艾泽拉斯上最棒的猎物，你就开始渴望更多东西。$B$B你有看到这里的野兽的大小吗?!$B$B我在这里猎捕你所见过最危险的猎物。我是说抓到长牙并将她的心脏带回去做为战利品!' WHERE entry=9220; /* Text0_0: Listen $g lad : lass;.  I left the expedition in the capable hands of me son, Junior.  When you\'ve stalked the finest game in all of Azeroth you start to itch for something more.$B$BAnd have you seen the size of the beasties here?!$B$BI\'m here hunting the most dangerous prey you\'ll ever lay your eyes on.  I mean to bag myself Tusker and take her heart as my trophy! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='$N!我对你的打猎本领印象深刻。你在荆棘谷的开始或许不太稳当，但你坚持到底，捕获老邦加拉西成为最出色的人之一。$B$B但听好了，$g小夥子:小姑娘;，外域的猎物是真的很难对付。我还有疤可以证明这点!' WHERE entry=9221; /* Text0_0: $N!  I remember your hunting prowess all too well.  You might have gotten off to a shaky start in Stranglethorn, but you stuck in there and became one o\' the finest when you bagged old Bangalash.$B$BBut listen, $g lad : lass;, the prey out here in the Outland is the real deal.  And I\'ve the scars to prove it! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='普罗德摩尔女士的部队为了拖延阿克蒙德和他的燃烧军团，已经经历了一场恶战。现在这个严酷的任务摆在了我们的面前。你准备好面对他们的冲击了吗？' WHERE entry=9225; /* Text0_0: Lady Proudmoore\'s forces have bled to delay Archimonde and his Burning Legion, and now this grim task falls to us. Are you ready to stand with me against the onslaught? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我谦逊地欢迎你来我们的神庙，灵魂。' WHERE entry=9226; /* Text0_0: I humbly welcome you to our temple, spirit. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='和那些在我们受苦的时候抛弃我们的德莱尼人协商？我不这么想。$B$B真正的灵魂是不会说出这种话的！露出你的真面目吧，骗子。是谁派你来的？' WHERE entry=9227; /* Text0_0: Treat with the draenei, the people who turned their backs on us while we suffered? I think not.$B$BA true spirit does not speak thus! Reveal yourself, impostor. Who sent you? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='那么让燃烧军团尽管使出他们的手段吧！' WHERE entry=9228; /* Text0_0: Then let the Legion do their worst! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='所以我们要信任那些用欺骗来侮辱我们的人吗?德莱尼那麽轻视我们所以他们必须使用奸计来引起我们的注意吗?$B$B我们知道他们想「救赎」我们，但我的人民根本不想要他们的救赎。我们可以自己站起来而且我们追求的是骄傲，独立的命运。把这个讯息带给你的盟友。' WHERE entry=9229; /* Text0_0: So we\'re to trust people who would insult us with this deception? Do the draenei think so little of us that they must resort to trickery to get our attention?$B$BWe\'re aware of their desire to \'redeem\' us, but my people want none of their redemption. We are capable of standing on our own and we will pursue our destiny as a proud and separate people. Carry this message to your allies. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='燃烧军团紧紧逼迫着我们，但是我们顶住他们潮水般的进攻。阿克蒙德接近世界之树的时间越晚，我们离胜利就越近一步。' WHERE entry=9230; /* Text0_0: The Burning Legion presses us hard, but our defenses hold. Every moment we keep Archimonde away from the World Tree brings us closer to victory. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='很好。确定他们了解。$B$B现在，如果你能安静的离开我的神庙我会非常感激。' WHERE entry=9231; /* Text0_0: Good. Be sure they understand.$B$BNow, I would appreciate it if you would leave my temple in peace. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='朋友，欢迎来到奥雷柏尔营地。在这里你没有什么可以感到恐惧的。我们是破碎者，但并不是你的敌人。$B$B我是库雷尼的伊库提，我们是一群期望和德莱尼兄弟以及他们新结识的同盟们重建联系的破碎者。' WHERE entry=9235; /* Text0_0: Welcome to the Orebor Harborage, friend. You have nothing to fear here. We are Broken, but we are not your enemies.$B$BI am Ikuti of the Kurenai, a group of Broken who desire to reestablish ties with our draenei brothers and their newfound allies. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='玛克吐没有认出你来，$r，但他很高兴见到你。如果你需要购买或修理护甲，别找别人，要找玛克吐。' WHERE entry=9236; /* Text0_0: Maktu doesn\'t recognize you, $r, but he is pleased to meet you. If ever you need to buy or repair armor, look no further than Maktu. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='这座神庙的回忆像一层厚厚的雾气覆盖了我的心灵，但我不能把它们拼凑成一个有条理的故事。这个地方曾对我而言有着某种意义。除非我可以重拾记忆，否则我会觉得一部分的自己不见了。$B$B或许德莱尼可以帮我想起我所遗忘的事情。' WHERE entry=9237; /* Text0_0: Memories of this temple shroud my mind like a thick haze, yet I cannot assemble them into a coherent story. This place meant something to me once. Until I can restore that memory, I will feel as though a part of me is missing.$B$BPerhaps the draenei can help me recover what I\'ve lost. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='有些人可以叫我「提姆」，但对我朋友而言，我是「专家」。' WHERE entry=9238; /* Text0_0: There are some who call me \'Tim,\' but to my friends, I am \'the specialist.\' */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='如果你要问，你根本不了解我，不足以使用那个称号。' WHERE entry=9239; /* Text0_0: If you have to ask, you don\'t know me anywhere near well enough to be using that appellation. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你好，$c。你想将你的猎人本领发展到极限吗?就是这里了。$B$B赫米特·奈辛瓦里召集了这世界上有史以来最厉害的远征队。如果你敢的话就加入我们的狩猎旅行队。' WHERE entry=9240; /* Text0_0: Greetings, $c.  You seek to push yourself to the limits of your hunting prowess?  Look no further.$B$BHemet Nesingwary has assembled the finest expedition the remnant of this world has ever known.  Join us on safari if you dare. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='卡拉赞不只是个建筑物，$N。如果你追溯横跨艾泽拉斯的能量界线，你会发现它们都会合在那里。$B$B<艾特罗斯指向哨塔下隐密的一点。>$B$B很棒，对吧?',Text1_0_loc4='卡拉赞不只是个建筑物，$N。如果你追溯横跨艾泽拉斯的能量界线，你会发现它们都会合在那里。$B$B<艾特罗斯指向哨塔下隐密的一点。>$B$B很棒，对吧?' WHERE entry=9242; /* Text0_0: Karazhan is more than a mere building, $N.  If you traced the ley-lines traversing Azeroth you would find that they all converge right about there.$B$B<Alturus points at an invisible spot below the tower.>$B$BFascinating, isn\'t it? */ /* Text1_0: Archmage Alvareux once wrote a treatise exploring a fascinating theory.  He proposed the existence of an exact copy of Karazhan in a world other than our own and that both somehow shared the same space.$B$BHe went mad soon after.  A real pity. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='纳鲁的智慧远远超出我们的理解。在过去的五个月里，我从阿达尔那里学到的东西，远比我这么多年在达拉然图书馆里学到的还多。' WHERE entry=9243; /* Text0_0: The naaru are wise beyond our understanding.  I\'ve learned more from A\'dal in the last five months than all the years I spent in the libraries of Dalaran. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='奖励捕获恶名昭彰的罪犯和邪恶的动物的悬赏就贴在这里。现在就去追求这份赏金对你而言还太危险了，等你获得了力量之后再来看这块布告。' WHERE entry=9244; /* Text0_0: Bounties for notorious criminals and vicious animals are posted here. It would be much too dangerous for you to pursue the bounty posted here right now, but check the board again as you gain strength. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='这块告示写着许多宣布事项和奖励办法。' WHERE entry=9246; /* Text0_0: This sign contains various announcements and notices of rewards. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='欢迎来到萨布拉金，$c。我是暗影猎人丹杰，这座前哨站的监督者，也是赞格沼泽的暗矛军队指挥官。' WHERE entry=9248; /* Text0_0: Welcome to Zabra\'jin, $c. I am Shadow Hunter Denjai, overseer of this outpost and commander of the Darkspear forces in Zangarmarsh. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='现在你别想试图逃跑小鱼人!我有着像老鹰一样的眼睛，像...像...像某种有强大能量动物的耳朵!' WHERE entry=9249; /* Text0_0: Now don\'t you be thinkin\' about tryin\' to make off with me baby murlocs! I got the eyes of a hawk and ears like... ears like... like somethin\' with mighty powerful ears! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你已证明自己是个非常称职的王牌猎人，$N。但仍有一只野兽还萦绕在你梦中...长牙!' WHERE entry=9256; /* Text0_0: You\'ve proven yourself a very capable game hunter, $N.  But there\'s still one beastie that haunts your dreams... Tusker! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你已捕获他们全部了:巴奇洛尔，班萨尔，卡特瑞普，还有强大的长牙!你真的是我所认识最厉害的王牌猎人!' WHERE entry=9257; /* Text0_0: You\'ve bagged them all: Bach\'lor, Banthar, Gutripper, and even the mighty Tusker!  You\'re truly the finest big game hunter that I know! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我就在一块多刺的矮树丛里打滚，和一只塔巴克雄鹿正面交锋，只有我锐利的小刀...<咳嗽>...和敏捷猎人的智力能救我。$B$B突然间一对凶猛的风翼猫头鹰猎人从天而降朝我弹过来!他们懦弱的攻击...<咳嗽>...完全帮不了他们自己。$B$B虽然我拿到他们的鸟喙做为战利品，但我也在战斗过程中被刮伤感染。有点令人不快，我也承受了很大的痛苦，但我相信一两天就会好了。' WHERE entry=9258; /* Text0_0: There I was tumbling in a patch of prickly undergrowth with a talbuk stag, hand-to-hand, only my sharp knife...<cough>... and keen hunter\'s intellect to save me.$B$BAll of a sudden I\'m jumped by a pair of fierce windroc hunters that came at me from the skies!  Their cowardly attack...<cough>... didn\'t help them any though.$B$BAnd while I have their beaks as trophies, I received an infected scratch out of the ordeal.  Kind of nasty, and I\'m in a lot of pain, but I\'m sure it\'ll heal up in a day or two. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我第一次看到蘑菇长的比树还要高，我不知道我是否可以称这个地方为家。过了一阵子之后你就不再注意了。' WHERE entry=9259; /* Text0_0: The first time I saw mushrooms taller than trees, I wasn\'t so sure I could call this place home. After a while you just stop noticing. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='泰伦多尔曾是德莱尼牧师和朝圣者的隐蔽休息处。牧师居民显少接见访客。$B$B当兽人开始攻击德莱尼居民们，难民开始大批到来。隐士阿浩恩和其他人将泰伦多尔从神殿转变为一个安全的避风港。许多德莱尼，包括我自己，都欠他一个人情。' WHERE entry=9261; /* Text0_0: Telredor was once a secluded retreat for draenei priests and pilgrims. The resident priests seldom received visitors.$B$BWhen the orcs started to attack draenei settlements, refugees began to arrive in larger numbers. Anchorite Ahuurn and the others transformed Telredor from a shrine into a safe haven. Many draenei, myself included, owe our survival to his efforts. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='欢迎来到泰伦多尔，$c。如果你需要任何东西，请随时来跟我要。' WHERE entry=9263; /* Text0_0: Welcome to Telredor, $c. If you need anything, don\'t hesitate to ask. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我从没见过一个地方有那麽多不同种类的蘑菇。如果有足够的时间，我相信我可以找出它们所有的用途。' WHERE entry=9264; /* Text0_0: I\'ve never seen so many different kinds of mushrooms in one place. Given enough time, I\'m sure I could find a use for all of them. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='泰伦多尔过去20年来经历的改变比先前几个世纪还要来的多。我不能抱怨，$N，因为世界那些时候改变更多。$B$B圣光为我带来了身为隐居牧师不会有的朋友和同伴。在这里学习过去带给你的经验。它会帮助你了解你的旅程将带你去哪里。' WHERE entry=9265; /* Text0_0: Telredor has seen more change in the last 20 years than it did in prior centuries. I cannot complain, $N, for the world has changed far more in that time.$B$BThe Light has brought me friends and companions I could not have met as a cloistered priest. Learn what you can of the past in your time here. It will help you to understand where your journey is leading you. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='暗影猎人丹杰派我和一支由建筑商和战士组成的小分遣队来这里建立这座前哨。我们才刚建好而他就已经开始向我们要报告了!$B$B如果你需要补给，我可以提供一些东西，但我们仍在等待第一批货物。' WHERE entry=9267; /* Text0_0: Shadow Hunter Denjai sent me here with a small contingent of builders and warriors to establish this outpost. We\'ve barely finished building it and he\'s already asking for reports!$B$BIf you need supplies, I can offer a few things, but we\'re still waiting for our first shipment. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='如果你看到巫医托卡斯就告诉他，他的混合物和符咒根本没用!我完全照着他的话做，但玛卡莎眼里还是只有祖瑞伊。$B$B不要相信那个假巫医告诉你的任何话!' WHERE entry=9268; /* Text0_0: If you ever meet Witch Doctor Tor\'gash, tell him his concoctions and charms don\'t work! I did exactly as he told me to and still Magasha has eyes only for Zurai.$B$BDon\'t believe a thing that sham witch doctor tells you! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你好，$c。我是被他们叫做破碎者的家伙。就像失落者那样，只不过还没像他们那么糟糕。邪能的摧残让我们从原来德莱尼人的形态转变到现在的这个样子。' WHERE entry=9270; /* Text0_0: Hello, $c.  I am what is referred to as one of the Broken.  Like the Lost Ones, though not as badly as they, we were afflicted with fel energies that transformed us from our original draenei forms. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='暗潮纳迦氏族和血鳞纳迦氏族首领的悬赏布告被列在这里。听说他们两个都非常危险，也许你应该以后再去看看。' WHERE entry=9273; /* Text0_0: Notices of reward for the naga leaders of the Darkcrest and Bloodscale tribes are listed here.  They both sound extremely dangerous, perhaps you should check again later. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='暗羽和血鳞部族的纳迦领导者悬赏公告公布在此。' WHERE entry=9274; /* Text0_0: Notices of reward for the naga leaders of the Darkcrest and Bloodscale tribes are listed here. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='他们死了。全部的人...$B$B当黑暗之血拿下我们，就有某种我无法理解的东西控制了我。告诉我，你曾感受过极大的愤怒，让你整个人像在燃烧一样吗?一种让生命都枯萎的高温?一种焚化你血管的热度?那就是我感受到的。$B$B<萨鲁法尔的双眼短暂地闪了一阵红光。>$B$B我是最后一个活下来的人。他们30个人围绕着我...黑暗之血...我只记得这个画面。后来我眼前一黑，过了不知道多久才醒来。' WHERE entry=9275; /* Text0_0: They died. All of them...$B$BAs the Murkbloods cut through us, something took hold of me that I cannot understand. Tell me, have you ever felt a rage so great that the whole of your being burns? A heat that wilts the living? A heat that incinerates the blood in your veins? That is what I felt.$B$B<Saurfang\'s eyes glow red for a brief moment.>$B$BI was the last one left alive. 30 of them surrounded me... Murkbloods... I remember nothing beyond that vision. I blacked out and awoke some time later. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='黑暗时期隐约出现在前方，陌生人...' WHERE entry=9276; /* Text0_0: Dark times loom ahead, stranger... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='灵魂都受到极大的煽动。我们一定要找出这次动乱的原因。' WHERE entry=9277; /* Text0_0: The spirits are greatly agitated. We must find the cause of this disturbance. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='赫米特是我所知道最出色的猎人。我们几个月前偶然在艾泽拉斯的冬泉谷大厅巧遇过。我们在追踪同一个猎物:一只叫拉克西里的巨豹。$B$B我们没为了猎物打起来，而是对牠做了个赌注;谁收集到霜刃豹的皮革就可以要求对方某事。让我永远羞愧的是，这就是我如何得到我的绰号，费兹。$B$B我看起来像费兹吗?' WHERE entry=9283; /* Text0_0: Hemet is the greatest hunter that I know.  We chanced upon each other in the hills of Winterspring back on Azeroth many moons ago.  He and I were stalking the same quarry: the great cat known as Rak\'shiri.$B$BRather than fight each other over our prey, we made a wager out of it; whoever collected the frostsaber\'s skin would get to demand something of the other.  To my eternal shame, this is how I earned the nickname, Fitz.$B$BDo I look like a Fitz? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='伟大的猎人，$N回来了。告诉我你最近追踪猎物的故事。' WHERE entry=9284; /* Text0_0: The mighty hunter, $N returns.  Tell me the tale of stalking your latest prey. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='对，对，我感觉好多了，但我还满喜欢这里的。',Text0_1_loc4='无论萨尔是否存在，破碎之手氏族的秩序都将延续下去。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=9286; /* Text0_0: Yeah, yeah, I\'m feeling better, but I kind of like it down here. */ /* Text0_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text0: */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='联合团已经筹备这个计画好几个月了!我们想挖掘欧夏刚，这是一种被誉为宇宙中最大的钻石。$B$B在我们要开始进行计画的数分钟前，奈萨斯王子哈拉玛德传话来命令我们在虚空风暴的一场政治冲突解决之前暂时按兵不动。我已经将我们的计画转变成目前暂时营运一个囤积走私宝石的货仓，但这样只会慢慢的吞噬我们的利润。' WHERE entry=9287; /* Text0_0: The Consortium has been planning this operation for months!  We were to dig Oshu\'gun, the largest known diamond in the universe.$B$BMinutes before we were to begin, Nexus-Prince Haramaad sends word that we\'re to hold off until a political matter is resolved in Netherstorm.  I\'ve transformed our operation into a clearing house for smuggled gems in the meantime, but this is slowly eating into our profits. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='吉札是来把工作做好的。我来确认这时候没有人打扰他。' WHERE entry=9288; /* Text0_0: Gezhe is here to get a job done.  I\'m here to make sure no one bothers him while he does it. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你知道我们是谁吗，陌生人?我们是玛格哈 - 咖啡色兽人，我听过你们族人这样称呼我们。玛格哈是生还者:一个堕落朝代的生还者;红色帕斯的生还者;一个粉碎世界的生还者...$B$B我是乔林，基尔罗格之子;亡眼的最后一个后裔:血之谷氏族的酋长。' WHERE entry=9289; /* Text0_0: Do you know who we are, stranger? We are Mag\'har - brown orcs, as I have heard your kind call us. The Mag\'har are survivors: Survivors of a fallen dynasty; Survivors of the Red Pox; Survivors of a shattered world...$B$BI am Jorin, son of Kilrogg; last of the lineage of Deadeye: Warchief of the Bleeding Hollow Clan. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你好 $N。' WHERE entry=9296; /* Text0_0: Greetings $N. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你看起来是个讲理的$r。或许我们可以互相帮助。' WHERE entry=9312; /* Text0_0: You look like a reasonable $r.  Perhaps we could be of mutual assistance. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='坚强一些。凯尔萨斯背叛了我们，我们的希冀变成了泡影，但是不要失去信心。我们会坚持到底，就像以前一样。阿尔萨斯的铁蹄没有摧毁我们的精神，凯尔萨斯也绝不可能让我们毁灭。就让这变故成为我们永远铭记的一课吧。' WHERE entry=9315; /* Text0_0: Be strong. Kael\'thas has betrayed us and what we know is in flux, but do not lose heart. We will endure, as we always have. Arthas did not crush our spirit when he swept through our land, and neither will Kael\'thas. Let it serve as a lesson to us all as we move forward to our prosperous future. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你想去我们城市的哪里呢?',Text0_1_loc4='你想去我们城市的哪里呢?',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=9316; /* Text0_0: Where in our fair city do you wish to go? */ /* Text0_1: Where in our fair city do you wish to go? */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我们的银月城有两座拍卖行，你喜欢哪个？',Text0_1_loc4='我们的银月城有两座拍卖行，你喜欢哪个？' WHERE entry=9317; /* Text0_0: We have two auction houses within Silvermoon. Which would you prefer? */ /* Text0_1: We have two auction houses within Silvermoon. Which would you prefer? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='西边拍卖场就在商店街中段，长者步道西边。',Text0_1_loc4='西边拍卖场就在商店街中段，长者步道西边。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=9318; /* Text0_0: The western auction house can be found in the middle of the Bazaar, just west of the Walk of Elders. */ /* Text0_1: The western auction house can be found in the middle of the Bazaar, just west of the Walk of Elders. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='皇家贸易区的拍卖行可以在城市的东部找到，就在血骑士和猎人的训练区域往南一点。',Text0_1_loc4='皇家贸易区的拍卖行可以在城市的东部找到，就在血骑士和猎人的训练区域往南一点。' WHERE entry=9319; /* Text0_0: The Royal Exchange auction house can be found in the eastern part of the city, just south of the training area for the blood knights and rangers. */ /* Text0_1: The Royal Exchange auction house can be found in the eastern part of the city, just south of the training area for the blood knights and rangers. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你想追寻什麽道路?',Text0_1_loc4='你想追寻什麽道路?',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=9320; /* Text0_0: What path do you wish to pursue? */ /* Text0_1: What path do you wish to pursue? */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='银月城银行就在花园街市。去东南角找找吧。',Text0_1_loc4='银月城银行就在花园街市。去东南角找找吧。' WHERE entry=9321; /* Text0_0: The Bank of Silvermoon can be found within the Bazaar. Seek it out in the southeast corner. */ /* Text0_1: The Bank of Silvermoon can be found within the Bazaar. Seek it out in the southeast corner. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='如果你在找城市东边的银行，就去皇家交易所拍卖场找吧。它就在北边的墙那里。',Text0_1_loc4='如果你在找城市东边的银行，就去皇家交易所拍卖场找吧。它就在北边的墙那里。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=9322; /* Text0_0: If you\'re seeking a bank in the eastern part of the city, look no further than the Royal Exchange. It lies along the north wall therein. */ /* Text0_1: If you\'re seeking a bank in the eastern part of the city, look no further than the Royal Exchange. It lies along the north wall therein. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='女飞行师·薄暮和她的龙鹰就在外头西边的牧羊人之门。',Text0_1_loc4='女飞行师·薄暮和她的龙鹰就在外头西边的牧羊人之门。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=9323; /* Text0_0: Skymistress Gloaming and her bats are just outside and to the west of the Shepherd\'s Gate. */ /* Text0_1: Skymistress Gloaming and her bats are just outside and to the west of the Shepherd\'s Gate. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='泰德林是银月城的公会注册员。她就住在长者步道上，离博学者之门很近。',Text0_1_loc4='泰德林是银月城的公会注册员。她就住在长者步道上，离博学者之门很近。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=9324; /* Text0_0: Tandrine is the guild master of Silvermoon. Her residence is along the Walk of Elders, close to the Magister\'s Gate. */ /* Text0_1: Tandrine is the guild master of Silvermoon. Her residence is along the Walk of Elders, close to the Magister\'s Gate. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='银月城旅店座落在皇家贸易区，由一个叫维兰德拉的女人经营着。我听说那个有名的调酒师有时也会出现在那里。',Text0_1_loc4='银月城旅店座落在皇家贸易区，由一个叫维兰德拉的女人经营着。我听说那个有名的调酒师有时也会出现在那里。' WHERE entry=9325; /* Text0_0: The Silvermoon City Inn, located in the Royal Exchange, is run by a talented woman named Velandra. I\'m told that the renowned vinemaster can sometimes be found there, as well. */ /* Text0_1: The Silvermoon City Inn, located in the Royal Exchange, is run by a talented woman named Velandra. I\'m told that the renowned vinemaster can sometimes be found there, as well. */
