UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='是谁这麽大胆站在『剑刃』兰崔索面前?你想找死吗，$g男孩:女孩;?',Text0_1_loc4='无论萨尔是否存在，破碎之手氏族的秩序都将延续下去。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=9361; /* Text0_0: Who so boldly stands before Lantresor of the Blade? Do you not know death by sight, $g boy:girl;? */ /* Text0_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text0: */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='那你就是个笨蛋。你不知道我是谁吗?',Text0_1_loc4='无论萨尔是否存在，破碎之手氏族的秩序都将延续下去。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=9362; /* Text0_0: Then you are a fool. Do you not know what I am? */ /* Text0_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text0: */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='一个兽人...$B$B<剑刃传授者嘲笑着。>$B$B我是个半兽人后代的剑类大师。',Text0_1_loc4='无论萨尔是否存在，破碎之手氏族的秩序都将延续下去。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=9363; /* Text0_0: An orc...$B$B<Lantresor scoffs.>$B$BI am a blademaster of half-orc descent. */ /* Text0_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text0: */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='德莱尼...因为如此，我两者都不是。不是兽人，也不是德莱尼。我的种族是罕见的一种。大部份的人都在几十年前被杀了...我会活下来全靠我的意志力。',Text0_1_loc4='无论萨尔是否存在，破碎之手氏族的秩序都将延续下去。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=9364; /* Text0_0: Draenei... And because of this, I am neither. Not orc, not draenei. My own kind are a rare breed. Most having been killed decades ago... I live because of my strength of will. */ /* Text0_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text0: */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='闭嘴，$R。我所经历过的一切，你只有在传说中才听说过。我无情地杀死过男人、女人，甚至是孩子。我为两任部落酋长效力过……而现在，我统治着石拳氏族。' WHERE entry=9365; /* Text0_0: Bite your tongue, $r. I have seen things in my lifetime that you have only heard about in legends. I have killed man, woman, and child without remorse. Under the banner of two Warchiefs of the Horde I have served... And now, I rule Boulderfist. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='那你的人民要剑刃传授者怎麽做，$r?',Text0_1_loc4='无论萨尔是否存在，破碎之手氏族的秩序都将延续下去。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=9366; /* Text0_0: And what do your people want of Lantresor, $r? */ /* Text0_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text0: */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='<剑刃传授者痛快地大笑。>$B$B你知道你现在在哪吗，笨蛋?这是巨魔的地盘。在兽人之前，在德莱尼之前，还有巨魔。而你却想发动一场必然会输的战争?石拳会粉碎你的。如果石拳没有毁灭你们，战槌也会...$B$B我想你的领导者早就知道这点了...',Text0_1_loc4='无论萨尔是否存在，破碎之手氏族的秩序都将延续下去。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=9367; /* Text0_0: <Lantresor laughs heartily.>$B$BDo you know where you are, fool? This is ogre land. Before orc, before draenei, there was ogre. Yet, you wish to start a war that you will inevitably lose? Boulderfist will crush you. And if Boulderfist does not destroy you, Warmaul will...$B$BBut I think your leaders already know this... */ /* Text0_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text0: */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你要发动一系列活动让吉尔索洛堡垒的吉尔索洛相信战槌巨魔攻击了他们的基地，再策划另一系列活动让战槌巨魔相信吉尔索洛正要攻击他们的基地。$B$B这样做你就解决了我们的两个麻烦。$B$B石拳将夺回他们的领土而你的人民将不再遭受石拳，战槌，和吉尔索洛的攻击。',Text0_1_loc4='无论萨尔是否存在，破碎之手氏族的秩序都将延续下去。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=9369; /* Text0_0: You will stage a series of events that will lead the Kil\'sorrow orcs of Kil\'sorrow Fortress to believe that the Warmaul ogres have attacked their base and then another series of events to make the Warmaul ogres believe the Kil\'sorrow orcs are attacking their base.$B$BDo this and you solve both of our problems.$B$BThe Boulderfist will have their territory back and your people will be free from attack from Boulderfist, Warmaul and Shadow Council. */ /* Text0_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text0: */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='没有什么畸形的虫子可以把我赶出赞加沼泽！我会让它们知道探险者协会不是好惹的……' WHERE entry=9370; /* Text0_0: No overgrown bug\'s gonna chase me out of Zangarmarsh! I\'ll show \'em what the Explorers\' League is made of... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='登记者在发布任何任务之前要先和守望者波洛克谈谈。$B$B我们会起诉未经同意的发布者。$B$B不要发布帐单。' WHERE entry=9373; /* Text0_0: Registrants are required to speak with Warden Bullrok before posting any task.$B$BThose found making unapproved postings will be prosecuted.$B$BPost no bills. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='想要张贴悬赏令的人必须事先与监护者莫布吉尔交谈。$B$B未经批准擅自张贴将被起诉。张贴悬赏令不需支付金币。' WHERE entry=9374; /* Text0_0: Registrants are required to speak with Warden Moi\'bff Jill before posting any task.$B$BThose found making unapproved postings will be prosecuted.$B$BPost no bills. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='如果你在找工作的话就看看布告栏，$r。' WHERE entry=9375; /* Text0_0: Check the bulletin board if you\'re looking for work, $r. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='他们对亡者没有尊敬，$r。一定要给巨魔一点教训。' WHERE entry=9376; /* Text0_0: They have no respect for the dead, $r. The ogres must be taught a lesson. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我们一定要寻找生还者。如果有任何人还活着，我们一定要至少试着把他们救回来...' WHERE entry=9377; /* Text0_0: We must search for survivors. If anyone is still alive, we must at least try and get them back... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你是谁?你想要什麽?',Text1_0_loc4='你是谁?你想要什麽?' WHERE entry=9383; /* Text0_0: Who are you?  What do you want here? */ /* Text1_0: Why did you do this to us? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text2_0_loc4='你是谁?你想要什麽?',Text3_0_loc4='你是谁?你想要什麽?' WHERE entry=9383; /* Text2_0: There are FOUR lights! */ /* Text3_0: My vicious teromoths will avenge me! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text4_0_loc4='大家都到哪里去了?',Text5_0_loc4='晚宴宾客应该表现更多尊重！' WHERE entry=9383; /* Text4_0: Where did everyone go? */ /* Text5_0: Dinner guests should show more respect! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text6_0_loc4='喔，这里真是个神圣的地方！',Text7_0_loc4='把治疗药膏涂在我头上。你喜欢我的刺棘皇冠吗?' WHERE entry=9383; /* Text6_0: Oh, what a sacred place is here overthrown! */ /* Text7_0: Anoint my head with a healing balm.  Do you like my crown of thorns? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我可以教你采矿。有兴趣吗?',Text0_1_loc4='我可以教你采矿。有兴趣吗?',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=9384; /* Text0_0: I can instruct you in mining.  Interested? */ /* Text0_1: I can instruct you in mining.  Interested? */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我可以教你草药学。有兴趣吗?',Text0_1_loc4='我可以教你草药学。有兴趣吗?',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=9385; /* Text0_0: I can instruct you in herbalism.  Interested? */ /* Text0_1: I can instruct you in herbalism.  Interested? */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='进入灌木丛要小心点，$c。有个具伤害力的光环徘徊在那个地方。那一定是以前摧毁曾在这里的德鲁伊的生物残渣。' WHERE entry=9391; /* Text0_0: Be careful going into the thicket, $c.  There is a harmful aura lingering about the place.  It must be the residue from whatever destroyed my fellow druids. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='这个森林是个令人毛骨悚然的地方。到处都是比联盟更多的邪恶护符，所以你要小心自身安全。' WHERE entry=9392; /* Text0_0: This forest be a spooky place.  It\'s full of more bad juju than just the Alliance, so you watch out for yourself. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='别挡我的路，$r。没看到我们正在打斗吗!' WHERE entry=9395; /* Text0_0: Get out of my way, $r. Can\'t you see that we\'re in the middle of a battle! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='太棒了！卡兹洛加死亡时发出的嚎叫应该会让燃烧军团感到畏惧。他们现在认识到了你们所拥有的力量，那么准备好接受燃烧军团的更强烈的打击吧。' WHERE entry=9396; /* Text0_0: Outstanding! Kaz\'rogal\'s death cry should strike fear into the core of the Burning Legion. They now know the power your forces possess, so expect the worst the Legion can offer. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='愿元素之灵与你同在。' WHERE entry=9397; /* Text0_0: May the spirits be with you. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='太精彩了！杀死一个像阿兹加洛这样的深渊领主并不是件小事，我的朋友。如果我们有更多的时间，我会很乐意倾听你和你同伴的故事。但是阿克蒙德不会给我们休息的机会，不管怎样，我的斥候报告说，燃烧军团正在我们营地外聚集更强大的力量，而且阿克蒙德离世界之树已经非常近了。我们正在普罗德摩尔女士的帮助下撤退。你应该立即向世界之树进发。我们世界的命运仍然未定。' WHERE entry=9398; /* Text0_0: Outstanding! Killing a Pit Lord such as Azgalor is no small feat, my friend. If we had more time, I would love to hear the story of you and your companions. Archimonde will not give us that pause, however. My scouts have already reported that the Legion is amassing an immense force outside our camp, and Archimonde is very close to the World Tree. We are evacuating with the help of Lady Proudmoore. You should head to the World Tree at once. The fate of our world is still undecided. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='一个破碎者的屍体躺在那里。很神秘的是，死亡的原因不像是因为那些突变的飞蛾。$B$B也许还有某种神秘的东西造成这件事情?' WHERE entry=9401; /* Text0_0: The corpse of one of the Broken lies here.  Mysteriously, the cause of its death does not appear to be from one of the mutated moths.$B$BPerhaps it has something to do with the strange object resting right next to its outstretched hand? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='嗨，勇士!你想过做个全职的神鬼战士吗?你和我可以大捞一笔。' WHERE entry=9403; /* Text0_0: Hail, champion! Have you ever thought about going into the gladiator business full time? You and I could make a mountain of gold. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='非常忙...非常忙!什麽?' WHERE entry=9405; /* Text0_0: Very busy... very busy!  What? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='既然我已被打的性命垂危，你想怎麽样呢?' WHERE entry=9406; /* Text0_0: Now that I\'ve been beaten to within an inch of my life what do you want? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='如果这场大屠杀是我们最不可能做的事，我们会追根究底!' WHERE entry=9407; /* Text0_0: We\'ll get to the bottom of this massacre if it\'s the last thing we do! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='欢迎来到时光之穴!',Text1_0_loc4='欢迎来到时光之穴!' WHERE entry=9414; /* Text0_0: Welcome to the Taverns of Time! */ /* Text1_0: Rest your weary feet, we have all the time in the world... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text2_0_loc4='欢迎来到时光之穴!' WHERE entry=9414; /* Text2_0: Can I offer you a drink? I promise you its aged like none other! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='天涯旅店没有什么我想要的。不过，这里却能吸引许多对我在售卖的商品十分感兴趣的客户。$B$B我专门研究稀奇的工程学物品，已经获得了很大的成就。有时候，我这里可能还会有一两件奇货出售。$B$B怎么样，有什么你感兴趣的吗？' WHERE entry=9417; /* Text0_0: The World\'s End Tavern has nothing to offer those of my kind.  However, I find that it attracts the type of clientele that are interested in what I have for sale.$B$BI specialize in exotic engineering goods acquired from far and wide.  From time to time I might even have a rare thing or two for purchase.$B$BWhat might I interest you in? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='当你望向西边，你看见了什麽，凡人?' WHERE entry=9419; /* Text0_0: What do you see when you look to the west, mortal? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你知道我看见什麽吗?一个入侵的前兆。$B$B是，大师将传送门密封起来是很聪明，但他也自此失去他的……我该怎麽说?大师失去了他的焦点。是的……焦点。$B$B因为如此，军团抓住了机会。他们开始渗透，逐日壮大他们的数量。',Text0_1_loc4='无论萨尔是否存在，破碎之手氏族的秩序都将延续下去。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=9420; /* Text0_0: Do you know what I see? A precursor to invasion.$B$BAye, the master was wise in sealing the portals but has since lost his... how shall I put this? The master has lost his focus. Yes... Focus.$B$BWith this loss, the Legion has seized opportunity. They seep out now, growing in number day by day. */ /* Text0_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text0: */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='喔不，怎麽又是你!走开!' WHERE entry=9425; /* Text0_0: Oh no, not you again!  Go away! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='这是我从你收集的调查资讯中获得的结果。$B$B有两个主要的炼冶场:西边的炼冶场:仇恨和西南方的炼冶场:恐惧。每个炼冶场有一个军团传送器，一个熔炉，和几个法术防护哨塔。此外，还有愤怒守卫操纵恶魔火炮来守卫炼冶场。最后，每个炼冶场都有一个深渊领主监督者。$B$B好吧，这样应该一点问题都没有了...$B$B<奥翠司笑着。>',Text0_1_loc4='无论萨尔是否存在，破碎之手氏族的秩序都将延续下去。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=9427; /* Text0_0: This is what I have gathered from the information that you collected from the survey.$B$BThere are two primary forge camps: Forge Camp: Hate, directly west of where we stand and Forge Camp: Fear, directly southwest. Each camp has a Legion transporter, one forge, and several spell warding towers. Additionally, the camps are guarded by wrathguards manning fel cannons. Lastly, each camp has a pit lord overseer.$B$BRight then, this should be no problem at all...$B$B<Altruis laughs.> */ /* Text0_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text0: */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我想我可以在其他人还在苦恼是否要进入欧夏刚时另外赚点收入。$B$B时间就是利润!' WHERE entry=9429; /* Text0_0: I think I\'ll make my own money on the side while the others try to decide whether it\'s okay to go into Oshu\'gun.$B$BTime is profit! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='灯塔点亮了，是时候发动进攻了！拿上一面部落军旗，把它插在墓地中吧！' WHERE entry=9430; /* Text0_0: The beacons are lit, now is the time to strike! Take one of these battle standards and plant it at the graveyard for the Horde! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='双塔废墟还没落入我方的控制之中!我的命令是点燃两座烽火台，并且在该区域处於我方控制之下时发送战旗。去将那两座烽火台夺下!' WHERE entry=9431; /* Text0_0: Twin Spire Ruins is not yet secure! My orders are to only give out battle standards when the two beacons are lit and the area is secure. Get out there and gain control of those beacons! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='烽火已点燃，现在是攻击的时刻了!拿起一面战旗，并且替联盟将它插在墓地上!' WHERE entry=9432; /* Text0_0: The beacons are lit, now is the time to strike! Take one of these battle standards and plant it at the graveyard for the Alliance! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='双塔废墟还没落入我方的控制之中!我的命令是点燃两座烽火台，并且在该区域处於我方控制之下时发送战旗。去将那两座烽火台夺下!',Text0_1_loc4='双塔废墟还没落入我方的控制之中!我的命令是点燃两座烽火台，并且在该区域处於我方控制之下时发送战旗。去将那两座烽火台夺下!',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=9433; /* Text0_0: Twin Spire Ruins is not yet secure! My orders are to only give out battle standards when the two beacons are lit and the area is secure. Get out there and gain control of those beacons! */ /* Text0_1: Twin Spire Ruins is not yet secure! My orders are to only give out battle standards when the two beacons are lit and the area is secure. Get out there and gain control of those beacons! */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='<沙萨拉毕恩对你咆哮，再回去喝他充满泡沫的饮料。>' WHERE entry=9435; /* Text0_0: <Sal\'salabim growls at you, then goes back to drinking his frothy beverage.> */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='<监护者忒洛斯滑稽地看着你，停了停，看起来似乎很难控制自己。>$B$B赞加沼泽……真相太近了。$B$B<他的脸再次变得疯狂起来。>$B$B他还在监视着吗！？' WHERE entry=9437; /* Text0_0: <Warden Treelos looks at you funny and then pauses a moment, clearly struggling.>$B$BZangarmarsh... too close to truth.$B$B<His face goes crazy again.>$B$BIs he still watching!? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='那是什么？赞加沼泽？为什么我要去那里？$B$B<忒洛斯似乎正在陷入沉思。>$b$B是的，赞加沼泽……我们……德鲁伊们快要发现为什么水平面正在下降。它正毁灭着一切！$B$B<癫狂又在监护者的眼中出现。>$B$B毁灭我们吧！明亮的圣光！轰！！' WHERE entry=9438; /* Text0_0: What\'s that?  Zangarmarsh?  Why would I want to go there?$B$B<Treelos looks thoughtful.>$B$BYes, Zangarmarsh... we... the druids there are getting close to figuring out why the water level is dropping.  It\'s destroying everything!$B$B<You can see the insanity creep back in behind the warden\'s eyes.>$B$BDestroyed us all!  Bright light!  BOOM!! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='火翼的血精灵们……不知道为什么，他们想阻止我们。$B$B<监护者忒洛斯努力地想镇静下来。>$B$B他们……他们派了一个破碎者作为……作为大使……但是他有炸弹！$B$B他们都死了，他们都死了！他们想逃跑！有些幸运的家伙甚至都不知道。$B$B我肯定是在爆炸的边缘。那实在太糟了……又开始监视我们了！$B$B<忒洛斯变得很沮丧，直钩钩地看着前方，好像把你当成了空气。>' WHERE entry=9439; /* Text0_0: The Firewing blood elves... for some reason they want to stop us.$B$B<Warden Treelos visibly struggles to keep his wits about him for a few more seconds.>$B$BThey... they sent one of the Broken as ... as an emissary....  But he had a bomb!$B$BThey died, they all died!  They tried to run away!  The lucky ones didn\'t even know.$B$BI must have been at the edge of the blast.  It was horr...IT\'S WATCHING US AGAIN!$B$B<Treelos becomes despondent and looks straight through you as if you\'re not there.> */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你想怎样?' WHERE entry=9440; /* Text0_0: WUT YOU WANT!? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='嘘～～?' WHERE entry=9441; /* Text0_0: Fshhhhhhsssfhhhhh? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='再次谢谢你，$N，帮助我揭发灌木丛这里发生的事。' WHERE entry=9444; /* Text0_0: Thank you again, $N, for helping me to uncover what happened here at the thicket. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='欢迎来到艾兰里堡垒，$c。' WHERE entry=9471; /* Text0_0: Welcome to the Allerian Stronghold, $c. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='小心点，$c。森林里充满了隐藏的危险和潜在的敌人。' WHERE entry=9472; /* Text0_0: Be wary, $c. The forest is full of hidden dangers and potential enemies. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='这真是太糟了。$B$B我不是为了我们的不安着想，但是我们必须做一些事情以减轻白骨荒野死者的伤痛!' WHERE entry=9477; /* Text0_0: This is just horrible.$B$BI care not for our own discomforts here, but we must do something to ease the pain of the dead in the Bone Wastes! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='如果你期待会有什麽正式欢迎款待之类的话，你恐怕要失望了，$c。在这里我们传统不算什麽，有什麽工作就好好做。' WHERE entry=9481; /* Text0_0: If you\'re expecting some kind of official welcome, you\'re going to be disappointed, $c. We don\'t stand on tradition, here. What works is what goes. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='悬赏告示上钉着几张羊皮纸，一张新的告示引人注目的钉在这个告示牌上。宣布一则在白骨荒野杀死鞭骨者的消息。' WHERE entry=9482; /* Text0_0: One note stands out from the other various pieces of parchment that are tacked onto this wanted poster.  It\'s a call to slay the bonelashers of the Bone Wastes. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='鞭骨者，我恨死他们了!$B$B要不是因为我没看到，而且还中了晕眩法术，我会在同一时间把他们全都射下!' WHERE entry=9485; /* Text0_0: Bonelashers, I hate them all!$B$BIf it weren\'t for the loss of my eye, and the fainting spells that I get sometimes, I\'d be out there shooting them down all the time! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我看到奥尔多正在修缮那些城墙。你知道，他们想要重建整座城市。$B$B他们比老工头奥斯洛在湖畔镇干得快多了，他不是把工具遗失在河里，就是被豺狼人拿走他的补给。$B$B我应该要求奥尔多去帮助他，这样他们就会很快修好那座断桥了。' WHERE entry=9486; /* Text0_0: I\'ve been watching the Aldor working on the walls. They\'re gonna rebuild the whole city, you know.$B$BThey work much faster than old Foreman Oslow did back home in Lakeshire. He kept losing his tools in the lake, or the gnolls would take his supplies.$B$BI should ask the Aldor to send him some help. They\'d have that bridge fixed faster\'n anything. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='玛鲁卡兹不断喋喋不休地讲着这个森林的历史有多重要，但我现在没有兴趣听这个历史，除非我们当前的问题解决了。$B$B我不是说他在这里的工作不重要，但要有个人去看管防御工事并掌管后勤流程。' WHERE entry=9488; /* Text0_0: Malukaz chatters incessantly about the historical importance of this forest, but I don\'t have the luxury of indulging in history until our present problems are settled.$B$BI\'m not saying his work here isn\'t important, but someone has to see to the defenses and logistics of running the hold. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='从纳葛兰旅行直到来到这个森林，我很害怕我们的原始文化会消逝，但我很高兴我错了。$B$B这里还是一如既往!' WHERE entry=9489; /* Text0_0: Until I traveled through Nagrand and came to the forest, I feared that too much of our original culture was lost. I\'m thankful to see that I was wrong.$B$BThere is so much to be done here! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='每当我穿了件衣服或帽子，你曾看过罗斯勒斯装做没看见我吗?这里所有的事情都安顿下来，我要带她去森林散步。$B$B就这麽一次，我错过暴风城所有精致的小酒馆。' WHERE entry=9493; /* Text0_0: Have you seen the way Ros\'eleth winks at me whenever I go to pick up a garment or hat? When things SETtle down around here, I\'m going to take her for a nice walk in the woods.$B$BFor once, I miss all those fancy taverns in Stormwind. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='<凯德对你发出嘘声>$B$B安静点，要不然你能击败兽人和联盟吗，你这个笨手笨脚的蠢蛋!$B$B这就对了，点头就好了，当我们谈话结束，你就离开这里然后忘记你在这里找到了我。' WHERE entry=9494; /* Text0_0: <Kaide hisses at you.>$B$BBe quiet, or you\'ll bring the orcs and the Alliance down on us, you clumsy oaf!$B$BThat\'s right, nod your head, and when we\'re done speaking, you\'ll walk away and forget you found me here. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我们可能会在一起工作，但是要小心谨慎，我再一次提醒你要注意你的言行举止。$B$B我可以保证在这里我们是最不亲近的。' WHERE entry=9495; /* Text0_0: We may be working together, but that only increases the need for discretion. Once again, be mindful of your words and actions.$B$BI can guarantee we\'re far from the only ones out here. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='是啊，你想要什麽?你看不出来我正在忙吗?暗影议会让我一刻不得闲!',Text0_1_loc4='是啊，你想要什麽?你看不出来我正在忙吗?暗影议会让我一刻不得闲!',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=9497; /* Text0_0: Yeah, what do you want?  Can\'t you see I\'m busy here?  The Shadow Council isn\'t paying me by the hour! */ /* Text0_1: Yeah, what do you want?  Can\'t you see I\'m busy here?  The Shadow Council isn\'t paying me by the hour! */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我看起来像是在做什麽?我在整修这个地方 - 而且还全靠我自己一个人 - 这样我们才能搬进来!$B$B有了运作基地在这里的森林，要知道撒塔斯、艾兰里、碎石和塞纳里奥的德鲁伊在干嘛就容易的多了。我们在奥齐顿的基地就很不方便。$B$B等一下，我认识你吗?',Text0_1_loc4='我看起来像是在做什麽?我在整修这个地方 - 而且还全靠我自己一个人 - 这样我们才能搬进来!$B$B有了运作基地在这里的森林，要知道撒塔斯、艾兰里、碎石和塞纳里奥的德鲁伊在干嘛就容易的多了。我们在奥齐顿的基地就很不方便。$B$B等一下，我认识你吗?',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=9498; /* Text0_0: What\'s it look like I\'m doing?  I\'m fixing the place up - all on my own I might add - so that we can move in!$B$BWith a base of operations out here in the forest, it\'ll be easier to keep track of what Shattrath, Allerian, Stonebreaker and the Cenarion druids are all up to.  Our base in Auchindoun is just too inconvenient for that.$B$BWait a minute, do I know you? */ /* Text0_1: What\'s it look like I\'m doing?  I\'m fixing the place up - all on my own I might add - so that we can move in!$B$BWith a base of operations out here in the forest, it\'ll be easier to keep track of what Shattrath, Allerian, Stonebreaker and the Cenarion druids are all up to.  Our base in Auchindoun is just too inconvenient for that.$B$BWait a minute, do I know you? */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='嗯?去你的，现在我得从头来过!',Text0_1_loc4='嗯?去你的，现在我得从头来过!',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=9502; /* Text0_0: Yes?  Darn it all, now I\'ll have to start over from scratch! */ /* Text0_1: Yes?  Darn it all, now I\'ll have to start over from scratch! */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='练习!不用多久我就可以加入其他召唤师并且轮到我去奥齐顿的暗影迷宫。$B$B我希望我有机会可以召唤更大的东西!或许像莫尔墨那麽大，虽然我不会对他失去掌控!',Text0_1_loc4='练习!不用多久我就可以加入其他召唤师并且轮到我去奥齐顿的暗影迷宫。$B$B我希望我有机会可以召唤更大的东西!或许像莫尔墨那麽大，虽然我不会对他失去掌控!',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=9503; /* Text0_0: Practicing!  Soon I\'ll be good enough to join the other summoners and take my turn inside the Shadow Labyrinth at Auchindoun.$B$BI hope that I\'ll get the chance to summon something big!  Maybe something as big as Murmur, though I wouldn\'t lose control of him! */ /* Text0_1: Practicing!  Soon I\'ll be good enough to join the other summoners and take my turn inside the Shadow Labyrinth at Auchindoun.$B$BI hope that I\'ll get the chance to summon something big!  Maybe something as big as Murmur, though I wouldn\'t lose control of him! */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你觉得我到底能为你做什麽?你难道不能看出我正忙着和我们伟大的领袖谈论重大的议题吗?$B$B兔崽仔，快说你有什麽事，要不我就扁你一顿!',Text0_1_loc4='你觉得我到底能为你做什麽?你难道不能看出我正忙着和我们伟大的领袖谈论重大的议题吗?$B$B兔崽仔，快说你有什麽事，要不我就扁你一顿!',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=9505; /* Text0_0: And what is it exactly that you think I can do for you?  Can\'t you see that I\'m very busy here discussing matters of import with our illustrious leader?$B$BBe quick about your business or I\'ll have you beaten, dog! */ /* Text0_1: And what is it exactly that you think I can do for you?  Can\'t you see that I\'m very busy here discussing matters of import with our illustrious leader?$B$BBe quick about your business or I\'ll have you beaten, dog! */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='好吧，我只是要给我们领袖进度报告，现在所有的事情都在进行中也包括了计画，不出几个礼拜，这个地方就能成型了。$B$B然而，我们希望暗影议会派一个人和兽人一起来到村庄。这样我们就可以完成祖先的要求并且暗中进行这件事。$B$B等等，我认识你吗?你叫什麽名字?',Text0_1_loc4='好吧，我只是要给我们领袖进度报告，现在所有的事情都在进行中也包括了计画，不出几个礼拜，这个地方就能成型了。$B$B然而，我们希望暗影议会派一个人和兽人一起来到村庄。这样我们就可以完成祖先的要求并且暗中进行这件事。$B$B等等，我认识你吗?你叫什麽名字?',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=9506; /* Text0_0: Well, I was just giving our leader here a progress report on how everything is proceeding according to plan.  It should only be a few more weeks and we\'ll have this place back in shape.$B$BWe may want the Shadow Council to only staff the village with orcs, however.  That way we can make an ancestral claim and work undercover.$B$BWait a minute.  Do I know you?  What\'s your name? */ /* Text0_1: Well, I was just giving our leader here a progress report on how everything is proceeding according to plan.  It should only be a few more weeks and we\'ll have this place back in shape.$B$BWe may want the Shadow Council to only staff the village with orcs, however.  That way we can make an ancestral claim and work undercover.$B$BWait a minute.  Do I know you?  What\'s your name? */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='这里有许多燃烧装置，$N。要小心一点，要是使用不当，它们会在一个时间内造成重大伤害。' WHERE entry=9515; /* Text0_0: Here are more of the incendiary devices, $N. Be careful with these, they can cause a great deal of disruption to time if used improperly. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='无论如何，我要弄清楚这个谜样的团体到底是怎麽回事!' WHERE entry=9517; /* Text0_0: I\'m going to figure out what this shadowy group is up to no matter what! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='对於这里我们有应尽的义务，$g男孩:女孩;好好留意，别让任何人对我们进行突袭。$B$B也就是说我们要主动行动!' WHERE entry=9521; /* Text0_0: We\'ve a duty out here, $g boy : girl;, to see to it that we don\'t let anyone surprise us.$B$BThat means proactive action! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你有没有听说他们在暗影迷宫里完全失去了对摩摩尔的控制？！',Text0_1_loc4='你有没有听说他们在暗影迷宫里完全失去了对摩摩尔的控制？！',Text1_0_loc4='他们没有付足够的工钱给我们。但是在这座荒废的村庄总比在奥金顿里躲躲藏藏好多了。',Text1_1_loc4='他们没有付足够的工钱给我们。但是在这座荒废的村庄总比在奥金顿里躲躲藏藏好多了。' WHERE entry=9523; /* Text0_0: Did you hear that they lost total control of Murmur in the Shadow Labyrinth?! */ /* Text0_1: Did you hear that they lost total control of Murmur in the Shadow Labyrinth?! */ /* Text1_0: They don\'t pay us enough for this.  But this ruined village sure beats skulking around inside of Auchindoun. */ /* Text1_1: They don\'t pay us enough for this.  But this ruined village sure beats skulking around inside of Auchindoun. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text2_0_loc4='我加入他们，因为他们说可以付给我足够的钱让我去学院。我叔叔说我下个学期就可以去了！',Text2_1_loc4='我加入他们，因为他们说可以付给我足够的钱让我去学院。我叔叔说我下个学期就可以去了！',Text3_0_loc4='你好，你肯定是新来的吧！很高兴认识你！$B$B有没有从奥金顿暗影迷宫传来有关我们是否重新控制了摩摩尔的消息？',Text3_1_loc4='你好，你肯定是新来的吧！很高兴认识你！$B$B有没有从奥金顿暗影迷宫传来有关我们是否重新控制了摩摩尔的消息？' WHERE entry=9523; /* Text2_0: I joined up because they said they\'d pay my way into the academy.  My uncle says that I can go next season! */ /* Text2_1: I joined up because they said they\'d pay my way into the academy.  My uncle says that I can go next season! */ /* Text3_0: Hey there, you must be the new recruit!  Good to meet you!$B$BAny word from the Shadow Labyrinth in Auchindoun on whether we\'ve regained control of Murmur yet? */ /* Text3_1: Hey there, you must be the new recruit!  Good to meet you!$B$BAny word from the Shadow Labyrinth in Auchindoun on whether we\'ve regained control of Murmur yet? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text4_0_loc4='我们一群人准备稍后去沙塔斯城喝酒，你有兴趣吗？',Text4_1_loc4='我们一群人准备稍后去沙塔斯城喝酒，你有兴趣吗？',Text5_0_loc4='有兴趣加入我们的皮球联赛吗？大部分情况下，我们在周一至周三比赛。$B$B我们很欢迎你在这次轮班以后加入我们。',Text5_1_loc4='有兴趣加入我们的皮球联赛吗？大部分情况下，我们在周一至周三比赛。$B$B我们很欢迎你在这次轮班以后加入我们。' WHERE entry=9523; /* Text4_0: If you\'re interested, a couple of us are going into Shattrath for drinks later. */ /* Text4_1: If you\'re interested, a couple of us are going into Shattrath for drinks later. */ /* Text5_0: Interested in joining up for the leather ball league?  We play Monday through Wednesday, mostly. $B$BYou\'re welcome to join us after this shift.  We\'re going to toss it around. */ /* Text5_1: Interested in joining up for the leather ball league?  We play Monday through Wednesday, mostly. $B$BYou\'re welcome to join us after this shift.  We\'re going to toss it around. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text6_0_loc4='我希望这个地方可以成为暗影议会的前哨基地。我知道这听上去很奇怪，但是我真的有点想念暗影迷宫了。',Text6_1_loc4='我希望这个地方可以成为暗影议会的前哨基地。我知道这听上去很奇怪，但是我真的有点想念暗影迷宫了。',Text7_0_loc4='<他斜靠了过来。>$B$B就我和你，我想也许哪天晚上我们可以一起出去，你知道我的意思。',Text7_1_loc4='<她斜靠了过来。>$B$B就我和你，我想也许哪天晚上我们可以一起出去，你知道我的意思。' WHERE entry=9523; /* Text6_0: I hope this place pans out as a forward base for Shadow Council operations.  I know it sounds weird, but I kind of miss the Shadow Labyrinth. */ /* Text6_1: I hope this place pans out as a forward base for Shadow Council operations.  I know it sounds weird, but I kind of miss the Shadow Labyrinth. */ /* Text7_0: <He leans in closer.>$B$BJust between you and me, I\'m thinking about \'mustering\' out one of these nights.  You know what I mean? */ /* Text7_1: <She leans in closer.>$B$BJust between you and me, I\'m thinking about \'mustering\' out one of these nights.  You know what I mean? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你以为你是谁可以跑进这里跟我大小声?我是这村子暗影议会的领导人。滚出我的视线!$B$B如果再让我看到你，我会让你看不到明天的太阳。懂了吗?$B$B或许你想被葬在奥齐顿的迷宫里，或是献祭给莫尔墨?' WHERE entry=9524; /* Text0_0: Who do you think you are that you can walk in here and address me?  I\'m the leader of the Shadow Council in this village.  Get out of my sight!$B$BIf I see you again, I\'ll be the last person that you ever see.  Understand?$B$BPerhaps you\'d like to be buried in the labyrinth of Auchindoun, or sacrificed to Murmur? */
