UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='伊斯比纳会很高兴帮助你照料动物同伴的。她在碧蓝岗哨的旅馆外面等着你。',Text0_1_loc4='伊斯比纳会很高兴帮助你照料动物同伴的。她在碧蓝岗哨的旅馆外面等着你。' WHERE entry=10075; /* Text0_0: Esbina will be happy to take care of your animal companion, my friend. She waits outside the inn within Azure Watch. */ /* Text0_1: Esbina will be happy to take care of your animal companion, my friend. She waits outside the inn within Azure Watch. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='啊，你是想要训练吗？有几个导师在碧蓝岗哨那里……你想学什么？',Text0_1_loc4='啊，你是想要训练吗？有几个导师在碧蓝岗哨那里……你想学什么？' WHERE entry=10076; /* Text0_0: Ah, seeking training, are you? There are several instructors who are camped in Azure Watch... what are you after? */ /* Text0_1: Ah, seeking training, are you? There are several instructors who are camped in Azure Watch... what are you after? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='德鲁伊？这里没人学习那种知识……但是我听说埃索达附近有些人很符合你的描述。好像是叫沙兰尤斯？',Text0_1_loc4='德鲁伊？这里没人学习那种知识……但是我听说埃索达附近有些人很符合你的描述。好像是叫沙兰尤斯？' WHERE entry=10077; /* Text0_0: Druid? No one here follows that path... but I believe I heard of someone matching that description near the Exodar. Shalannius, I think? */ /* Text0_1: Druid? No one here follows that path... but I believe I heard of someone matching that description near the Exodar. Shalannius, I think? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='艾克提恩是常驻这里的追踪者。而且他还干得很不错——他穿着的皮甲就是他技术的象征。他的营地就在碧蓝岗哨的东南方。',Text0_1_loc4='艾克提恩是常驻这里的追踪者。而且他还干得很不错——他穿着的皮甲就是他技术的象征。他的营地就在碧蓝岗哨的东南方。' WHERE entry=10078; /* Text0_0: Acteon is our resident tracker, and a good one he is, too - the skins he wears are testament to his skill. His camp is in the southeast of Azure Watch. */ /* Text0_1: Acteon is our resident tracker, and a good one he is, too - the skins he wears are testament to his skill. His camp is in the southeast of Azure Watch. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='什么？你想给银月城捐献布料吗？$B$B你只是想要只陆行鸟吧，不是吗？好吧，好吧……为这座城市捐献布料，我来负责让你声名远播。' WHERE entry=10079; /* Text0_0: What? You wish to donate cloth to Silvermoon?$B$BYou\'re merely after a Hawkstrider, aren\'t you? Very well, very well... do the city this service, and I will see to it that your reputation here rises. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='如果想要掌握奥术魔法，你只需要去找塞米德就可以了。他就在碧蓝岗哨的东边，和鲁安达在一起。',Text0_1_loc4='如果想要掌握奥术魔法，你只需要去找塞米德就可以了。他就在碧蓝岗哨的东边，和鲁安达在一起。' WHERE entry=10081; /* Text0_0: For mastery over the arcane, you need look no further than Semid. He teaches on the eastern side of Azure Watch along with Ruada. */ /* Text0_1: For mastery over the arcane, you need look no further than Semid. He teaches on the eastern side of Azure Watch along with Ruada. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='对人和善的朵拉斯是一名高尚的妇女，和一名英勇的圣光防卫者。她在旅馆里提供训练。',Text0_1_loc4='对人和善的朵拉斯是一名高尚的妇女，和一名英勇的圣光防卫者。她在旅馆里提供训练。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=10083; /* Text0_0: The good Tullas is a noble woman, and a stalwart defender of the Light. Her lessons are taught in the inn proper. */ /* Text0_1: The good Tullas is a noble woman, and a stalwart defender of the Light. Her lessons are taught in the inn proper. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
