UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='这里是卡拉赞之塔，我的主人麦迪文的住所。身为一个卑微的看门人，我没有其它的东西可以向你解释。' WHERE entry=10113; /* Text0_0: This is the tower of Karazhan and residence of my master, Medivh. As a humble doorman, there is little else I can explain to you. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='所有关于麦迪文的事都应该直接去问这里的管家莫罗斯，我几乎完全不知道主人在干些什么。如果你想知道更多的事情的话，我想现在正有一些贵族在宴会厅里和莫罗斯会面。' WHERE entry=10114; /* Text0_0: All inquiries regarding Medivh should be directed to Moroes, the Tower Steward. I myself know very little about the Master\'s business. I believe several nobles are currently having an audience with Moroes in the Banquet Hall, if you wish to inquire further. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='从门房这里，你可以向三个方向行进。我身后的楼梯通往会客间，客人们正在那里玩乐。我相信你已经闻到附近的马厩的味道，还有仆役宿舍的入口就在门房的大门旁边。' WHERE entry=10115; /* Text0_0: From here in the Gatehouse, you may travel in one of three directions. The stairs behind me lead to the Grand Ball Room, where guests are currently being entertained. I\'m sure you can smell the nearby Stables, and the entrance to Servant\'s Quarters lies next to the Gatehouse door. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='午夜是猎手阿图门的私人坐骑。我从未见过一匹比它更快、更强壮或者更英勇的马了。而且它的骑士更是喜怒无常！每个人都和它保持一定距离，以免被午夜踢到头，或被阿图门揍一顿。' WHERE entry=10117; /* Text0_0: Midnight is Attumen the Huntsman\'s personal mount. I\'ve never seen a faster, stronger, or more mean spirited horse. And her rider is even more temperamental! Everyone keeps their distance from her, lest they get a hoof upside the head from Midnight or a beating from Attumen. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='该死的蜘蛛、不断尖叫的蝙蝠、还有那些被诅咒的恶魔野兽，它们占据了仆役宿舍。那里已经很不安全了，尤其是当那些大家伙们从黑暗中跳出来的时候。' WHERE entry=10118; /* Text0_0: The damn spiders, the endlessly screeching bats, and those blasted demon beasts have all taken residence in the Servant\'s Quarters. It\'s not safe to walk around anymore, especially when the big ones come out of hiding. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='是的，我从未亲自见过它们，但有时候我可以从远处听到它们的声音。如果你想进去冒险的话，对它们要保持充分的警惕。' WHERE entry=10119; /* Text0_0: Oh yeah, I\'ve never seen them personally, but sometimes I hear them in the distance. Keep a watchful eye out for them if you venture inside. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我没有时间来闲聊了。我有很多人需要训练，还有一座塔需要看管。' WHERE entry=10120; /* Text0_0: I don\'t have time for idle chitchat. I have men and women to train, and a tower to watch. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你好！看这完美的乐器，真荣幸可以为主人和他的客人们演出。去观众那里找个座位，我听说表演很快就要开始了。' WHERE entry=10122; /* Text0_0: Greetings! Behold one of the finest musical instruments in all of Lordaeron. It\'s a true honor to perform for the Master and all his guests. Take a seat in the audience, I hear a show is starting soon. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='这个聚会毫无意义。那些愚蠢的贵族们永远都不可能看到麦迪文，他们不明白吗？我应该待在夜色镇，和我的家人在一起，而不是在这里浪费时间。' WHERE entry=10123; /* Text0_0: This party is pointless. Those foolish nobles will never get to see Medivh. Can\'t they see this? I should have just stayed in Darkshire with my family instead of wasting my time here. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='就在这里...的某个地方...我知道的。在这座图书馆的某处有我正在寻找的知识...' WHERE entry=10124; /* Text0_0: It\'s here... somewhere... I know it. Somewhere in this library is the knowledge I\'m looking for... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你在这里会影响我做一项重要的工作。请立刻离开。对了，我又做到哪了?' WHERE entry=10126; /* Text0_0: Your presence here is interfering with very important work. Please leave at once. Where was I, again? */
