UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='<即使拥有王者的气概，莱恩的智慧以及力量潜能仍然散发出不平凡的光辉。>' WHERE entry=10418; /* Text0_0: <Llane\'s true wisdom and strength burn bright, even in this likeness of the king.> */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='纳鲁庇难所的高级制皮大师希摩尔是该领域的绝对权威，可能就在贫民窟的集市上。' WHERE entry=10419; /* Text0_0: Seymour, the principal skinner in Shattrath and grand master of the trade, may be found in the lower city\'s open marketplace. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你准备好我们就战斗吧，$N。' WHERE entry=10421; /* Text0_0: We will fight when you are ready, $N. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我精通超过两种语言︰矮人语，侏儒语和非常普通的人类语言。但是我不了解你在说什麽!$B$B说大声点:引擎声这麽吵，我听不见你的声音!',Text0_1_loc4='我精通超过两种语言︰矮人语，侏儒语和非常普通的人类语言。但是我不了解你在说什麽!$B$B说大声点:引擎声这麽吵，我听不见你的声音!',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=10422; /* Text0_0: I AM FLUENT IN OVER TWO LANGUAGES: DWARVISH, GNOMISH AND THE VERY COMMON TONGUE OF HUMANS.  BUT I HAVE NO IDEA WHAT YOU ARE SAYING!$B$BSPEAK UP; I CANNOT HEAR YOU OVER THE GRINDING OF MY GEARS! */ /* Text0_1: I AM FLUENT IN OVER TWO LANGUAGES: DWARVISH, GNOMISH AND THE VERY COMMON TONGUE OF HUMANS.  BUT I HAVE NO IDEA WHAT YOU ARE SAYING!$B$BSPEAK UP; I CANNOT HEAR YOU OVER THE GRINDING OF MY GEARS! */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='是，是...欢迎到我的基地。$B$B那麽，你觉得如何呢?漂亮的俏皮话我们在这里都说过了，你不来点吗?$B$B无论如何，我很高兴能够摆脱那些希尔瓦纳的自大精灵。$B$B四处找点事做吧;到处都有许多的实验及匿名者等着需要帮忙。',Text0_1_loc4='无论萨尔是否存在，破碎之手氏族的秩序都将延续下去。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=10423; /* Text0_0: Yeah, yeah... welcome to my station.$B$BSo, what do you think?  Pretty nifty what we\'ve done here, wouldn\'t you say?$B$BMakes me glad to be rid of those stuffy elves at Sylvanaar anyway.$B$BMake yourself useful around here; there\'re plenty of experiments and whatnot to help out with. */ /* Text0_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text0: */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='<召唤恶魔正在对抗着麦迪文的游戏规则，他的身躯不停的颤抖着。他要你的灵魂!>' WHERE entry=10426; /* Text0_0: <The summoned daemon twitches, fighting against Medivh\'s rules of play.  He wants your soul!> */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='这个矮人看来像是在一项监视任务中途被发现并被杀害了。死亡熔炉的侍者将屍体留在外面，也许是想要警告那些其他想要闯入的人。' WHERE entry=10427; /* Text0_0: The dwarf appears to have been discovered and slain in the midst of a spy mission. The Deathforge\'s attendants have left the corpse in the open, perhaps as a warning to other would-be interlopers. */
