UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我们为你准备了盛宴，朋友。' WHERE entry=10975; /* Text0_0: We have quite the feast for you friend. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='哈罗，$g先生:小姐;!如果你要的话，我有一只虚空鳍刺等着带你到剑刃山脉上的御天者前哨。$B$B只要跟我说一声就行了。' WHERE entry=10979; /* Text0_0: Hello, $g sir : ma\'am;!  If you want, I have a nether ray waiting to take you to the Skyguard Outpost atop the Blade\'s Edge Mountains.$B$BJust let me know. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你好。当你在萨塔御天者的官阶晋升时，我就能够提供你直接飞行到我们位於剑刃山脉上的基地，御天者前哨。',Text0_1_loc4='无论萨尔是否存在，破碎之手氏族的秩序都将延续下去。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=10980; /* Text0_0: Good day to you.  When you\'ve risen a bit more in the ranks of the Sha\'tari Skyguard, I will be able offer you a direct flight to the Skyguard Outpost, our base atop the Blade\'s Edge Mountains. */ /* Text0_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text0: */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='遗忘魔焰裁缝专精并不是件轻松的事。如果你选择放弃，就会遗忘所有与魔焰裁缝专精相关的图样！$B$B你真的确定吗？' WHERE entry=10982; /* Text0_0: Forgetting your skill in Spellfire Tailoring is not something to do lightly.  If you choose to abandon it you will forget all recipes that require Spellfire Tailoring to create!$b$bAre you absolutely sure? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我们会为你奉上秘制饮品：鸡尾酒和梦想。至少我们能帮你实现其中一项。' WHERE entry=10983; /* Text0_0: We\'ll let you in on our secret diet: Cocktails and dreams. We can help you with one. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='所有人都要喝酒。我们能为你做些什么呢？' WHERE entry=10984; /* Text0_0: Everyone\'s gotta drink. What can we get for you? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你好，朋友。我们能为你做些什么吗？' WHERE entry=10985; /* Text0_0: Greetings $G brother:sister;, how can we help? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我们的美酒能滋润最干涸的喉咙。' WHERE entry=10986; /* Text0_0: Our drinks should quench even the mightiest of thirsts. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='要么饮酒，要么滚开！' WHERE entry=10987; /* Text0_0: Drink or be gone! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你除了跟我闲扯外没有别的事好做了吗，$g小夥子:小姑娘;?$B$B现在马上到外面去表现你的勇气!' WHERE entry=10988; /* Text0_0: Don\'t ya have something better ta do, $g lad : lass; than jaw with me?$B$BNow get out there and prove yer mettle! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='就是这股精神，$g小夥子:小姑娘;!你让我们大家对你的作为感到骄傲!$B$B你知道的，如果你想要快速的抵达我们在斯其索山脉的另一个基地的话，到下面去跟御天者管理者艾瑞娜谈谈。她会让你好好的起飞。' WHERE entry=10989; /* Text0_0: That\'s the spirit, $g laddy : lassie;!  Yer making all of us proud with all o\' the work ye be doing!$B$BAnd ya know, if ya want a quick trip ta our other base in the Skethyl Mountains, go down an talk ta Skyguard Handler Irena.  She\'ll set ya up nicely. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你受到了大家的尊敬，朋友！要不是我明白事理的话，肯定会以为你想抢我的饭碗！！！$B$B只要你像之前那样继续帮助我们，你就值得受到这样的尊重！' WHERE entry=10990; /* Text0_0: Yer gettin\' ta be something of a revered figure \'round here, $g boy : girl;!  If\'n I didn\'t know better, I\'d say ye were gunnin\' fer me job!!!$B$BAll the same, if ye keep up the way ye have been, ye\'ll deserve it! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我还能说什么，$n？你是最棒的沙塔尔天空卫士！$B$B别被溢美之词冲昏了头脑。我还有别的东西可以教给你！$B$B<天空指挥官凯勒对你咧嘴一笑，眨了眨眼睛。>' WHERE entry=10991; /* Text0_0: What can I say, $N?  Yer the finest o\' the Sha\'tari Skyguard!$B$BJust don\'t be lettin\' that go ta yer head.  I can still teach ya a thing or two, $G lad : lass;!$B$B<Sky Commander Keller grins at you and winks.> */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='尊敬的勇士，我们能帮你什么忙吗？' WHERE entry=10993; /* Text0_0: How can we be of service, exalted one? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我们很高兴为你提供补给。' WHERE entry=10996; /* Text0_0: We are happy to provide you with supplies. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='尊敬的勇士，我们能帮你什么忙吗？' WHERE entry=10998; /* Text0_0: Honored $G brother:sister;, how can we help? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='朋友！好久不见！我们能为你做些什么吗？' WHERE entry=10999; /* Text0_0: Friend! It\'s been too long.  What can we get for you? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你在找什麽?' WHERE entry=11000; /* Text0_0: What are you looking for? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='这些圣物真是一个伟大的谜团。或许藉由常态性的研究，你将会对他们的效用得到一个更好的评价。' WHERE entry=11007; /* Text0_0: The relics are truly a great mystery.  Perhaps by studying them regularly, you will gain a finer appreciation of their capabilities. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='钢铁并不强壮，高贵的人，肉身比较强壮。钢铁的力量来自於挥舞的人。不过那够了...我们要怎麽帮忙你呢，高贵的人?' WHERE entry=11008; /* Text0_0: Steel isn\'t strong, exalted one, flesh is stronger. Steel gains its strength from the one who wields it. But enough of that... How can we help you exalted one? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='<裘阿洛左边的头开口说，>$B$B我们发现你的热心帮助我们很动人...$B$B<他右边的头作结尾，>$B$B...而我们想要你知道我们真的很感谢你的帮忙!' WHERE entry=11009; /* Text0_0: <Chu\'a\'lor\'s left head says,>$B$BWe find your zeal to help us most appealing...$B$B<His right head concludes,>$B$B... and we want you to know that we greatly appreciate your efforts! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你的名字开始在这周遭受到敬重了。$B$B<裘阿洛的左眼以它冷酷的眼神盯着你。>$B$B保持良好的工作表现，$N!' WHERE entry=11010; /* Text0_0: Your name is beginning to be revered around here.$B$B<Chu\'a\'lor\'s left eye pierces you with its stony gaze.>$B$BKeep up the good work, $N! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='首先你变成了下面那些巨魔的$g国王:女王;，现在你已经受到身在欧格利拉当中我们的敬重。$B$B这是从未发生在一位$r的身上，现在，你就是一个活生生的证明。我谢谢你，$N，我们都欠你一份永远都无法回报的人情!' WHERE entry=11011; /* Text0_0: First you became $g king : queen; of the ogres below, and now you have exalted yourself amongst us of Ogri\'la.$B$BThis is unheard of for a $r, and yet, there you stand as living proof.  I thank you, $N, and we all owe you a debt that we will never truly be able to repay! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='一生当中能信任的东西可不多。钢铁就是其中之一。' WHERE entry=11012; /* Text0_0: There are few things you can trust in life. Steel, you can trust. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我们食人魔能得到你这样一位$r的帮助，我感到十分荣幸。你让我们重新拥有了一个光明的未来。$B$B现在，我们只需要处理掉这些剩下来的头疼事务就好了。不过，你确认不想要领养一个我们的孩子吗？' WHERE entry=11013; /* Text0_0: It\'s an honor to have a $r such as yourself aiding us ogres.  You\'re keeping our hope of a better future alive.$B$BNow if we could just get rid of these headaches.  Are you sure you don\'t want one of our sons? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='和钢铁比起来，铸钢者的双手是不是更厉害呢？' WHERE entry=11014; /* Text0_0: What is steel compared to the hand that shapes it? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你给予了我们这么多帮助，真是令我们感到惊讶。要是没有你，我们肯定早就被恶魔或是黑龙给撵出了家园！$B$B顺便说一句，我们提过想要将一个孩子便宜卖给你，对吧？不要？你不感兴趣吗？' WHERE entry=11015; /* Text0_0: It\'s amazing how much you\'ve helped us out.  We dare say that if it weren\'t for you, we\'d already have been overrun by the demons, or fried to a crisp by the Black Dragonflight!$B$BOn a side note, we did mention that we\'d sell you one of our sons, cheap, right?  No, not interested? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='在欧格利拉这我们有时间去思考有关钢铁的谜题。不过够了，我们可以帮你什麽吗?' WHERE entry=11016; /* Text0_0: Here in Ogri\'la we have time to contemplate the riddle of steel. But enough of that, how can we help? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你有需要制做的钢铁吗?' WHERE entry=11017; /* Text0_0: Do you have steel that needs shaping? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我们怎麽感谢都不足以表达对於你保护我的家庭所做的每一件事，$N。$B$B还有，你真的了解我们之前说要卖一个孩子给你是在开玩笑吗?不，真的…虽然我们真的感觉到有一对以上的头痛要来了。$B$B小夥子，冷静点，你会吗?!' WHERE entry=11018; /* Text0_0: We cannot thank you enough for everything you\'ve done to protect our family, $N.$B$BAnd, you do realize that we were joking before when we offered to sell you one of our sons?  No, really... although we do feel a couple more headaches coming on.$B$BJunior, be still, will you?! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我们有点开始喜欢小$n了！你好厉害！连恶魔也能打赢！' WHERE entry=11019; /* Text0_0: Us starting ta like little $N!  Yous bashem da demons real good! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='甘克喜欢小$r$n。你杀死了大恶魔，让所有小恶魔们感到害怕！$B$B<甘克的两个脑袋都在对着你笑。>' WHERE entry=11020; /* Text0_0: Gahk like little, $r $N.  Yous kill da big demon; make all da little demons scared!$B$B<Gahk\'s heads both grin at you.> */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我们确定常常在这看到你!$B$B裘阿洛说小$r是我们的$g英雄:英雌;!$B$B$N现在就是我们巨魔的一员了。不过，贾克觉得困惑，因为$N需要变更大点才行!' WHERE entry=11021; /* Text0_0: Us sure see yous here all da time!$B$BChu\'a\'lor say little $r our $g hero : heroine;!$B$B$N like one of us ogres now.  Only, Gahk confused because $N need to be bigger for dat! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我们能为你做些什么吗，尊贵的$G兄弟:姐妹;？' WHERE entry=11022; /* Text0_0: What can we get for you, our exalted $G brother:sister;? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我们能帮你什么忙吗？' WHERE entry=11023; /* Text0_0: How might we be of assistance? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='尊敬的$G兄弟:姐妹;，我们能帮你什么忙吗？' WHERE entry=11024; /* Text0_0: Honored $G brother:sister;, how may we help? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='哈罗朋友!我们能为你做点什麽吗?' WHERE entry=11025; /* Text0_0: Hello friend! What can we do for you? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你在这里的知名度已经相当高了，$r。这是件好事。$B$B我相信你不会被溢美之词冲昏了头脑，你会继续帮助我们放逐恶魔的，对吗？' WHERE entry=11027; /* Text0_0: You\'ve been making quite a name for yourself around here, $r.  Good for you.$B$BWe trust that you won\'t let that go to your single head, and that you\'ll still help out by banishing demons? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='在你的无私之下我们显得卑微，$N。要是过去我们好像有点自傲，请了解是因为你所以我们才能够改善我们的态度。$B$B我们很感谢你，并希望你会继续协助我们进行与炼冶场的抗争。' WHERE entry=11028; /* Text0_0: We are humbled by your selflessness, $N.  If in the past we\'ve seemed a bit conceited, realize that it is by your example that we were able to change our attitudes.$B$BWe thank you, and hope that you\'ll continue to assist us in our struggle against the forge camps. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你要得是什麽?' WHERE entry=11030; /* Text0_0: What is it that you want? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='<霸主莫格行礼。>' WHERE entry=11032; /* Text0_0: <Overlord Mor\'ghor salutes.> */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='嘿，记住，$N，当你完成许多好事，我们会让你可以买到这件东西的。这就像是因果循环，或是其他的。$B$B所以，尽量到处帮忙，包括我们位於北边的御天者盟友。$B$B太棒了...谢谢!' WHERE entry=11035; /* Text0_0: Hey, remember, $N, we\'ll make this stuff available for you to buy as you do good deeds.  It\'s like a karma thing, or something.$B$BSo, help out where you can, including with our Skyguard friends just to the north.$B$BAwesome... thanks! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='裘阿洛已经说过有过你的功绩了，$N。如果你要的话，我们有贩卖几种特别的巨魔酒。$B$B真的很好喝喔!' WHERE entry=11036; /* Text0_0: Chu\'a\'lor\'s been saying good things about you, $N.  If you want, we have a couple of special ogre brews for sale.$B$BThey\'re really tasty! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你在这里很受尊敬，朋友。好像每个人都在说起你。真酷。$B$B请随便看看吧，说不定有你感兴趣的东西呢。我们有很多上等货。' WHERE entry=11037; /* Text0_0: You\'re like something of a revered figure around here, $g man : kitten;.  Seems like everyone\'s talking about you.  That\'s cool.$B$BLet\'s see if there\'s something in stock that you\'re interested in.  We have a lot of nice stuff. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我们能说什麽呢，$N?$G帅哥:美女;，所有我们店里的东西你都可以购买喔!$B$B就是现在!' WHERE entry=11038; /* Text0_0: What can we say, $N?  $G Dude : Dudette;, anything that we have in the store is yours to purchase!$B$BRight on! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='停止。我没有东西要给像你这样的人。',Text0_1_loc4='停止。我没有东西要给像你这样的人。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=11042; /* Text0_0: Leave off. I don\'t have anything for the likes of you. */ /* Text0_1: Leave off. I don\'t have anything for the likes of you. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='过来，过来。要是你已经准备好了上好的皮革，我会让你看看怎么制作有用的物品。',Text0_1_loc4='过来，过来。要是你已经准备好了上好的皮革，我会让你看看怎么制作有用的物品。' WHERE entry=11049; /* Text0_0: Come, come. If you\'ve properly prepared your leather for once, I\'ll show you how to fashion serviceable items. */ /* Text0_1: Come, come. If you\'ve properly prepared your leather for once, I\'ll show you how to fashion serviceable items. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我听说海的那一边有一个技术高超的铁匠叫萨鲁·钢怒。如果你想要继续你的专业技巧，这个在奥格玛的铁匠铺就是你要前往的地方，$c。' WHERE entry=11051; /* Text0_0: I\'ve heard tell of a truly skilled smith across the sea named Saru Steelfury. The smithy in Orgrimmar is where you should head if you wish to ply your trade, $c. Best of luck. */
