UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='想要点什么吗？可想而知……能供你挑选的东西也不多。' WHERE entry=12553; /* Text0_0: Can I get you anything?  My selection is a little limited, but that\'s to be expected... all things considered. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='哈？' WHERE entry=12554; /* Text0_0: Huh? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='为国家牺牲是军人的职责。如果将这场战争称为闹剧就算是叛国的话，那我就是一名十足的叛徒了。' WHERE entry=12555; /* Text0_0: Dying for one\'s country is a soldier\'s duty.  But if calling this war folly is treason, then I\'m a traitor. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='别走神啊。这场战争非比寻常，前线的气氛尤其紧张。$b$b想帮忙的话就打起精神来，让我看看你有多大的本事。' WHERE entry=12566; /* Text0_0: Focus your mind, mortal. This is the front line of a war unlike any you\'ve witnessed.$b$bYou\'ll need full command of your faculties if you are to be of any use. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你一定要在我们引导火焰的这段时间内挡住埃霍恩的手下。在我们削弱埃霍恩之前，不要靠近它。',Text0_1_loc4='你一定要在我们引导火焰的这段时间内挡住埃霍恩的手下。在我们削弱埃霍恩之前，不要靠近它。' WHERE entry=12571; /* Text0_0: You must survive Ahune\'s minions while we channel our flames.  Do not approach the Frost Lord until we can wither him. */ /* Text0_1: You must survive Ahune\'s minions while we channel our flames.  Do not approach the Frost Lord until we can wither him. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='当艾胡恩出现时，我们会准备好了吗?',Text0_1_loc4='当艾胡恩出现时，我们会准备好了吗?',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=12572; /* Text0_0: When Ahune surfaces, will we be ready? */ /* Text0_1: When Ahune surfaces, will we be ready? */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='局势动荡！$B$B巫妖王率领萨莱因卷土重来，巨龙们纷纷投身魔枢之战，而维库人也在此时再度觉醒。$B$B你们乘坐木船来到严寒的极北之地与他们作战。各方势力互相牵制，形势大乱，使得海象人处于进退维谷的尴尬境地。$B$B眼下，新的邪恶势力又企图利用魔法力量彻底炸毁这片土地。我们必须寻找一处安全的避风港才能继续生存下去。$B$B这两位大使让我挺为难的……$r，你愿意帮助我的族人吗？' WHERE entry=12575; /* Text0_0: The land is in great upheaval!$B$BThe Dark One rides forth again with his San\'layn, the dragons fight in their great Nexus War, and the vrykul are reawakened.$B$BYour people sail north on your wooden ships to fight them and one another, and we Kalu\'ak are caught in the middle.$B$BAnd now some great evil has been done so that the land explodes with the magical power of the world. We must find a safe haven where we will have a chance to survive.$B$BThese two ambassadors make my head hurt... perhaps you can help my people, $r? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='$n，克瓦迪尔生性残忍，可是我不能放弃神圣的卡斯卡拉。只要我们不抛弃灵魂，灵魂就不会抛弃我们。' WHERE entry=12578; /* Text0_0: The Kvaldir are without mercy, $N.  But I cannot abandon sacred Kaskala.  If we don\'t abandon the spirits, the spirits will not abandon us either. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='卡斯卡拉遭到攻击！我们必须拖住敌军，直到所有人安全撤离。' WHERE entry=12579; /* Text0_0: Kaskala\'s under attack!  We must hold them off until we can escape. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='该死的巨人！如果他们想打仗，那就打吧！' WHERE entry=12580; /* Text0_0: Cursed giant-men!  If they want a fight, a fight they\'ll get! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='欢迎，$c。你是来荣耀这座火焰的吗?$B$B记住:我们的节庆火焰在每个拥有部落营区的土地上燃烧着。如果可以的话，花点时间前去荣耀每一座火焰吧。$B$B联盟也是一样，燃烧着属於他们的火焰。当你遇到联盟的火焰时，你还是亵渎一下像这样没有意义的努力比较好。',Text0_1_loc4='欢迎，$c。你是来荣耀这座火焰的吗?$B$B记住:我们的节庆火焰在每个拥有部落营区的土地上燃烧着。如果可以的话，花点时间前去荣耀每一座火焰吧。$B$B联盟也是一样，燃烧着属於他们的火焰。当你遇到联盟的火焰时，你还是亵渎一下像这样没有意义的努力比较好。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=12582; /* Text0_0: Welcome, $c. Have you come to honor this flame?$b$bRemember: Our festival fires burn in every land with a Horde settlement. Make time to honor each of them, if you can.$b$bThe Alliance, too, burns fires of their own. You would do well to desecrate such unworthy efforts when you see them. */ /* Text0_1: Welcome, $c. Have you come to honor this flame?$b$bRemember: Our festival fires burn in every land with a Horde settlement. Make time to honor each of them, if you can.$b$bThe Alliance, too, burns fires of their own. You would do well to desecrate such unworthy efforts when you see them. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='这名年轻的海象人似乎经历过一场激烈的打斗，不像是淹死的。' WHERE entry=12585; /* Text0_0: This young tuskarr appears to have been slain in combat rather than drowned. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我很高兴你来了。现在你了解了我们的火焰，还有荣耀火焰的事…还有敌人的火焰，以及熄灭它们的事…你可以回去找他并接受奖励了。',Text0_1_loc4='我很高兴你来了。现在你了解了我们的火焰，还有荣耀火焰的事…还有敌人的火焰，以及熄灭它们的事…你可以回去找他并接受奖励了。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=12587; /* Text0_0: Then I am glad you came. Now that you know of our fires, and of honoring them... and of the fires of our enemies, and of extinguishing them... you may return to him and be rewarded. */ /* Text0_1: Then I am glad you came. Now that you know of our fires, and of honoring them... and of the fires of our enemies, and of extinguishing them... you may return to him and be rewarded. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='简言之，就是魔法。$b$b凡人的生命如此短暂，他们从不考虑自己的行为可能会造成怎样的长远影响。$b$b过于活跃的奥术能量严重影响了世界的稳定。如果听之任之的话，艾泽拉斯世界迟早会被毁灭。$b$b对于这一点，我们已经达成了共识。可还没等我们组织起专门的议会，玛里苟斯就擅自采取了行动。$b$b我们别无选择，只能与他作战。' WHERE entry=12590; /* Text0_0: In a word, magic.$b$bIrresponsible mortals with their brief lifespans think nothing of the lasting effects of their actions.$b$bArcane energies have been tapped too liberally, disrupting the world\'s balance. If this is allowed to continue, Azeroth will soon be annihilated.$b$bOn this, both sides agree. But before a council could even be appointed, Malygos put his own plan into action.$b$bWe had no choice but to confront him. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='$r，我们取得了一些进展，但还是太慢了。' WHERE entry=12591; /* Text0_0: We\'re making progress, $r, but far too slowly. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我们不能失败！艾泽拉斯世界的命运就维系在这脆弱的平衡上……' WHERE entry=12592; /* Text0_0: We must succceed! Azeroth\'s fate lies in the balance.... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='魔法之王玛里苟斯是蓝龙军团的统帅。作为蓝龙守护者，他是艾泽拉斯世界最古老的生物之一。$b$b据说他已经从数千年来的疯狂中觉醒，可是他最近的行为表明他远没有恢复理智。$b$b对于我们的困境，他竟然决定以摧毁艾泽拉斯世界所有施法者的方式来解决。$b$b生命守护者红龙不得不采取行动。$b$b蓝龙军团和红龙军团展开了一场激战，世界的命运，就取决于那脆弱的平衡。' WHERE entry=12593; /* Text0_0: Malygos the Spellweaver, the Lord of Magic, Master of the Blue Dragonflight. He is the blue dragon aspect, one of the most ancient creatures on Azeroth.$b$bHe is said to be recovering from a madness which has lasted for millennia, but his recent actions lead me to believe that he is still far from sane.$b$bHis solution to our dilemma is to search out and destroy every magic-wielding mortal on Azeroth.$b$bAs the guardians of life, this has forced the red dragonflight to take action.$b$bDragon now fights against dragon, and the fate of our frail world lies in the balance. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='赛拉娜上尉吩咐我前来协助你进行在太阳之井高地的工作。' WHERE entry=12597; /* Text0_0: Captain Selana has instructed me to assist you with your efforts here on the Sunwell Plateau. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='所有挡在你前往太阳之井路上的魔法屏障都已经被摧毁了。前往太阳之井吧！立刻阻止基尔加丹进入这个世界！' WHERE entry=12604; /* Text0_0: All of the barriers blocking you from reaching the Sunwell have been destroyed. Enter the Sunwell and stop Kil\'jaeden from entering this world! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我和一位朋友前来解救一位年轻的人类女性逃离军团领主基尔加丹与其邪恶手下的掌控。$B$B我们发现凯尔萨斯正试图将基尔加丹从太阳之井的深处召唤出来。$B$B为了整个世界的安危 - 这件事绝不能发生!我保证会亲自阻止这件事。' WHERE entry=12606; /* Text0_0: A friend and I have come to rescue a young human woman from the clutches of the Legionlord, Kil\'jaeden and his vile minions.$b$bWe\'ve discovered that Kael\'thas is trying to summon Kil\'jaeden from the depths of the Sunwell itself.$b$bFor the sake of this world - this cannot come to pass! I am committed to seeing that it does not.$B */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='玛卓苟莎在此趟旅行中和我同行，不过我们在太阳之井中分散了。$B$B希望命运眷顾，她平安无恙。' WHERE entry=12607; /* Text0_0: Madrigosa accompanied me on this journey, but we have become separated in the Sunwell.$b$bMay fate keep her safe.$B */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='安薇娜不只是凡人，$r。那些了解她真实本质的人都想要拥有她。$B$B她曾经救过我，现在我想要报答她的恩惠。' WHERE entry=12608; /* Text0_0: Anveena is no mere mortal, $r. Those who recognize her true nature stop at nothing to possess her.$b$bShe once rescued me, and now I intend to return the favor. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='喜欢这个节庆吗，$c?$B$B虽说火焰持护者偏向当前的火焰，但我也不只是个只熟悉节庆过去的历史学家而已。当然，我也记录今年的节庆活动。目前一切进展的很顺利，你不觉得吗?$B$B你知道的，$n，在节日中持续燃烧的节庆火焰中潜藏着力量。我们看顾着我们的火焰，但我确信在我们敌人的城市深处有着神圣的火焰在燃烧着...',Text0_1_loc4='喜欢这个节庆吗，$c?$B$B虽说火焰持护者偏向当前的火焰，但我也不只是个只熟悉节庆过去的历史学家而已。当然，我也记录今年的节庆活动。目前一切进展的很顺利，你不觉得吗?$B$B你知道的，$n，在节日中持续燃烧的节庆火焰中潜藏着力量。我们看顾着我们的火焰，但我确信在我们敌人的城市深处有着神圣的火焰在燃烧着...',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=12609; /* Text0_0: Enjoying the festival, $c?$b$bWhile the Flame Keepers tend to the fires of the present, I am more of a historian, keeping close the festivals past. I\'m also, of course, documenting this year\'s festivities. Things are going well thus far, don\'t you think?$b$bYou know, $n, there is power inherent in all festival fires burning throughout the holiday. We\'re taking care of ours, but I\'m certain there are sacred flames burning deep within our enemy\'s cities... */ /* Text0_1: Enjoying the festival, $c?$b$bWhile the Flame Keepers tend to the fires of the present, I am more of a historian, keeping close the festivals past. I\'m also, of course, documenting this year\'s festivities. Things are going well thus far, don\'t you think?$b$bYou know, $n, there is power inherent in all festival fires burning throughout the holiday. We\'re taking care of ours, but I\'m certain there are sacred flames burning deep within our enemy\'s cities... */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='$c，欢迎来到我们的营地。你可以在这里休息。',Text0_1_loc4='$c，欢迎来到我们的营地。你可以在这里休息。' WHERE entry=12610; /* Text0_0: Welcome to our camp, $c. You\'re free to rest here if you\'d like. */ /* Text0_1: Welcome to our camp, $c. You\'re free to rest here if you\'d like. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='这鬼地方什么都没有。',Text0_1_loc4='这鬼地方什么都没有。',Text1_0_loc4='我的家人都被残忍地杀害了。连孩子都不能幸免。',Text1_1_loc4='我的家人都被残忍地杀害了。连孩子都不能幸免。' WHERE entry=12611; /* Text0_0: There is nothing left for us here. */ /* Text0_1: There is nothing left for us here. */ /* Text1_0: My family was slaughtered without mercy. Even the young. */ /* Text1_1: My family was slaughtered without mercy. Even the young. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text2_0_loc4='巫妖王对这片土地所做的一切，足以让他永远在地狱之火中倍受煎熬。',Text2_1_loc4='巫妖王对这片土地所做的一切，足以让他永远在地狱之火中倍受煎熬。',Text3_0_loc4='我们已经是无家可归的人了。',Text3_1_loc4='我们已经是无家可归的人了。' WHERE entry=12611; /* Text2_0: May the Lich King burn in hellfire for what he has called down upon this land. */ /* Text2_1: May the Lich King burn in hellfire for what he has called down upon this land. */ /* Text3_0: We are a people without a home to call our own now. */ /* Text3_1: We are a people without a home to call our own now. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text4_0_loc4='天灾军团是不懂得恐惧的机器，他们只知道摧毁这个世界上所有的生命。',Text4_1_loc4='天灾军团是不懂得恐惧的机器，他们只知道摧毁这个世界上所有的生命。',Text5_0_loc4='被他们称为“地狱咆哮”的那个人恐怕是我们最后的希望了。' WHERE entry=12611; /* Text4_0: The Scourge are a fearless machine set to bring about the end of all life on this world. */ /* Text4_1: The Scourge are a fearless machine set to bring about the end of all life on this world. */ /* Text5_0: The one that they call Hellscream might be our only hope. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text6_0_loc4='现在只有部落能救我们了。',Text6_1_loc4='现在只有部落能救我们了。' WHERE entry=12611; /* Text6_0: Only the Horde can save us now. */ /* Text6_1: Only the Horde can save us now. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='<霸德一动也不动，假装没听到你说的话。靠近一看，你看见他的面具底下滴下几滴口水。>',Text1_0_loc4='<霸德一动也不动，假装没听到你说的话。靠近一看，你看见他的面具底下滴下几滴口水。>' WHERE entry=12617; /* Text0_0: <Budd holds very still, pretending not to hear you. Looking closely you see a bit of drool drip from under his mask.> */ /* Text1_0: <Budd rocks back and forth on his haunches, muttering something that sounds like troll speech.> */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text2_0_loc4='<霸德一动也不动，假装没听到你说的话。靠近一看，你看见他的面具底下滴下几滴口水。>',Text3_0_loc4='<霸德一动也不动，假装没听到你说的话。靠近一看，你看见他的面具底下滴下几滴口水。>' WHERE entry=12617; /* Text2_0: Go away, mon. */ /* Text3_0: No time to be talkin\', mon. I be needin\' to rest now.... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text4_0_loc4='巨魔最强，老兄！',Text5_0_loc4='你有什么毛病啊，老兄?你没见过巨魔?' WHERE entry=12617; /* Text4_0: Troll powah, mon! */ /* Text5_0: What be wrong wit you, mon? Ain\'t ya never seen a troll before? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='部落能让我参与对抗天灾军团的战争吗？',Text0_1_loc4='部落能让我参与对抗天灾军团的战争吗？' WHERE entry=12618; /* Text0_0: Will the Horde grant me the chance to battle the Scourge? */ /* Text0_1: Will the Horde grant me the chance to battle the Scourge? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我愿意与你们结盟，为我死去的族人，为驱逐贪得无厌的天灾军团。我愿意用我的生命向部落起誓。',Text0_1_loc4='我愿意与你们结盟，为我死去的族人，为驱逐贪得无厌的天灾军团。我愿意用我的生命向部落起誓。' WHERE entry=12619; /* Text0_0: To avenge my people, to drive out the blight that has engulfed our land - I will take your oath. I will pledge all that I have and all that I am to the Horde. */ /* Text0_1: To avenge my people, to drive out the blight that has engulfed our land - I will take your oath. I will pledge all that I have and all that I am to the Horde. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='Lok\'tar ogar！非胜即死——为了这一信念我宣誓效忠部落。这是所有部落战士最神圣最基本的信条。

我自愿将全部身心奉献给伟大的酋长。我愿意无条件服从酋长的意志和命令。

从这一刻起直到永远——为了部落！',Text0_1_loc4='Lok\'tar ogar！非胜即死——为了这一信念我宣誓效忠部落。这是所有部落战士最神圣最基本的信条。

我自愿将全部身心奉献给伟大的酋长。我愿意无条件服从酋长的意志和命令。

从这一刻起直到永远——为了部落！' WHERE entry=12620; /* Text0_0: Lok\'tar ogar! Victory or death - it is these words that bind me to the Horde. For they are the most sacred and fundamental of truths to any warrior of the Horde.$B$BI give my flesh and blood freely to the Warchief. I am the instrument of my Warchief\'s desire. I am a weapon of my Warchief\'s command.$B$BFrom this moment until the end of days I live and die - FOR THE HORDE! */ /* Text0_1: Lok\'tar ogar! Victory or death - it is these words that bind me to the Horde. For they are the most sacred and fundamental of truths to any warrior of the Horde.$B$BI give my flesh and blood freely to the Warchief. I am the instrument of my Warchief\'s desire. I am a weapon of my Warchief\'s command.$B$BFrom this moment until the end of days I live and die - FOR THE HORDE! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我，妈妈。还有这些巨魔兄弟们!',Text1_0_loc4='是时候弄一些巨魔标签了，妈妈！' WHERE entry=12622; /* Text0_0: Ey, mon! Take me to mah troll bruddas! */ /* Text1_0: Time to play some troll tag, mon! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text2_0_loc4='巨魔兄弟们今天玩得很开心！',Text3_0_loc4='哈哈哈！去找些乐子吧！' WHERE entry=12622; /* Text2_0: My troll bruddas be in for some real fun today, mon! */ /* Text3_0: Hee hee hee! Dis gunna be some fun, mon! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text4_0_loc4='你确定我们走的路没错？',Text5_0_loc4='<嗅，嗅> 我能闻到他们。' WHERE entry=12622; /* Text4_0: You sure we be goin\' da right way, mon? */ /* Text5_0: <sniff, sniff> I can smell \'em, mon. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text6_0_loc4='Nuttin 说 luvin" 像是在一个小杯子敲打着 。"',Text7_0_loc4='Nuttin 说 luvin" 像是在一个小杯子敲打着 。"' WHERE entry=12622; /* Text6_0: Nuttin\' says luvin\' like a little tap on da noggin. */ /* Text7_0: Nuttin\' says luvin\' like a little tap on da noggin. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='太阳之井的三道门全都被终结了，$N。$B$B你必须得率领你的队伍在一切都太迟以前阻止基尔加丹进入艾泽拉斯!' WHERE entry=12623; /* Text0_0: All three of the gates at the Sunwell Plateau have been brought down, $N.$B$BYou must marshal your forces and stop Kil\'jaeden from entering Azeroth before all is lost! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='朋友，你在看什么呢？' WHERE entry=12634; /* Text0_0: What ye be lookin\' at, matey? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='真搞不懂为什么有些海盗喜欢把财宝埋起来，你看……我就喜欢将它们放在随手可及的地方。' WHERE entry=12636; /* Text0_0: I never understood why some pirates bury their treasure.  Me... I like to keep it within arm\'s reach. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='大海龟“踏浪者”将从这个港口游往龙骨荒野的莫亚基港口。' WHERE entry=12637; /* Text0_0: The great sea turtle Walker of Waves travels from this dock to Moa\'ki Harbor in Dragonblight. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='联盟的蒸汽动力破冰船“北海之矛”将穿越东部王国的海域，开往湿地的米奈希尔港。' WHERE entry=12638; /* Text0_0: The steam-powered Alliance icebreaker Northspear sails from here to Menethil Harbor in the Wetlands, across the sea in the Eastern Kingdoms. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='莫亚基港口因两只大海龟“踏浪者”和“绿背岛”而闻名。它们往返于乌努比和卡玛古。' WHERE entry=12640; /* Text0_0: Moa\'ki Harbor is blessed with two great sea turtles: Walker of Waves and Green Island. They swim between Unu\'pe and Kamagua. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='想去诺森德的话，就乘坐破冰船“北海之矛”吧。它会载你前往嚎风峡湾的瓦加德。' WHERE entry=12642; /* Text0_0: If you\'re looking to travel to Northrend, the icebreaker Northspear sails from here to Valgarde in the Howling Fjord. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='嗨！你想念东部王国了吧？如果你想回去的话，“海怪号”正要返回暴风城。那里的气候肯定比这里温暖得多！' WHERE entry=12644; /* Text0_0: Hey there! Miss the Eastern Kingdoms, huh? Well, the Kraken sails back to Stormwind if you\'re really itching to return. I know I\'d enjoy the warmer weather! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='大海龟“绿背岛”将从这个港口游往龙骨荒野的莫亚基港口。' WHERE entry=12645; /* Text0_0: Our blessed great sea turtle, Green Island, travels from here to Moa\'ki Harbor in Dragonblight. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='嗨。你想回到艾泽拉斯世界吗？搭乘“吻云号”返回提瑞斯法林地吧。' WHERE entry=12646; /* Text0_0: Yo. Lookin\' to get back to the Old World? Fly to Tirisfal Glades in style on the Cloudkisser. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='嗨。你可以乘坐“强风号”前往诺森德。她会载你飞往北风苔原的战歌要塞。' WHERE entry=12647; /* Text0_0: Hey there. If you wanna get to Northrend, then The Mighty Wind is the way to go. She\'ll fly you straight to Warsong Hold in the Borean Tundra. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='$c，想回家吗？如果你住在卡利姆多的话，“强风号”可以送你一程。她将直接飞往杜隆塔尔。' WHERE entry=12650; /* Text0_0: Heading home, $c? The Mighty Wind will get you there, if home\'s in Kalimdor. She flies straight from here to Durotar. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='悬赏猎杀部落叛徒！$B$B赏金由高尔特上尉提供。' WHERE entry=12657; /* Text0_0: Wanted DEAD for treason and other treacherous acts against the Horde!$B$BAll bounties paid by Captain Gort. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='嗨！菲兹兰克的飞行员都是王牌中的王牌呀。坚持训练是我们保持领先的秘诀。这其中就包括了跳伞训练。你永远也不知道什么时候会用到降落伞，但是迟早你会用上的。$b$b因此，我们设置了通往塔顶的传送装置。如果你是真正的士兵，就勇敢地拉开降落伞跳下来吧。塔顶有一位军官，负责提供降落伞包。$b$b$c，想要接受训练的话，我就教你如何使用传送装置。喏，你只需要踩在上面就是了。',Text0_1_loc4='嗨！菲兹兰克的飞行员都是王牌中的王牌呀。坚持训练是我们保持领先的秘诀。这其中就包括了跳伞训练。你永远也不知道什么时候会用到降落伞，但是迟早你会用上的。$b$b因此，我们设置了通往塔顶的传送装置。如果你是真正的士兵，就勇敢地拉开降落伞跳下来吧。塔顶有一位军官，负责提供降落伞包。$b$b$c，想要接受训练的话，我就教你如何使用传送装置。喏，你只需要踩在上面就是了。' WHERE entry=12658; /* Text0_0: Hello there!  Fizzcrank\'s pilots are the best of the best.  We stay that way through constant training.  That includes parachute training.  You never know when you will need to use your chute, but you do know that one day you\'ll have to use it.$b$bSo what we have here is a teleporter to the top of this spire.  Once you get up there, the only way for a real soldier to get back down is with a parachute.  We\'ve got another trooper stationed up top ready with the parachutes.$b$bIf you feel like trying it out, $c, I\'ll clear you for teleporter use.  Then just step onto the teleporter. */ /* Text0_1: Hello there!  Fizzcrank\'s pilots are the best of the best.  We stay that way through constant training.  That includes parachute training.  You never know when you will need to use your chute, but you do know that one day you\'ll have to use it.$b$bSo what we have here is a teleporter to the top of this spire.  Once you get up there, the only way for a real soldier to get back down is with a parachute.  We\'ve got another trooper stationed up top ready with the parachutes.$b$bIf you feel like trying it out, $c, I\'ll clear you for teleporter use.  Then just step onto the teleporter. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='早安，朋友!找个位置坐下喝点什麽，好吧?' WHERE entry=12659; /* Text0_0: G\'day mate! Sit an\' have yerself a sip, won\'t yeh? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我一直希望能再次为国王效劳。出于人道精神，一起对抗共同的敌人。$B$B但是我发现有教徒混进了我们中间……而所有证据都表明，纳克萨纳尔就是这场灾难的源头。' WHERE entry=12663; /* Text0_0: All I ever wished for was to serve my king once again.  For humanity, against a common enemy.$B$BInstead, I find that our numbers have been infiltrated by cultist scum.... and all signs point to Naxxanar as the origin of this rot. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='教徒接到的指令都来自于他们的首领。这家伙也许很快就会出现。$B$B这是个好机会。' WHERE entry=12664; /* Text0_0: This is where the cultists\' orders are coming from.  Their leader is bound to show up soon.$B$BLet\'s not miss this opportunity. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='安薇娜的牺牲为我们带来了新的希望。' WHERE entry=12665; /* Text0_0: Anveena\'s sacrifice has given us all a new hope for the future. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='嗯？干什么？！走开。' WHERE entry=12666; /* Text0_0: Huh?  What?!  Go away. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='趁这时候赶紧捞钱啊！我老爸经常说：战争是发横财的绝好机会。' WHERE entry=12668; /* Text0_0: There\'s money to be made!  Just like pops always said - no better time for raking in the cash than a time of war. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='当你站在这尊古老的人偶面前，你感觉到好像有什麽东西现身了。' WHERE entry=12669; /* Text0_0: You feel a strange presence as you stand before this ancient idol. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='数千年来存放预言者之眼的位置如今已是空空如也。' WHERE entry=12670; /* Text0_0: Where the Eye of the Prophets rested for millenia, only an empty niche remains. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='欢迎！想找地方休息的话，我能为你提供食宿服务哦。',Text0_1_loc4='欢迎！想找地方休息的话，我能为你提供食宿服务哦。' WHERE entry=12673; /* Text0_0: Welcome!  If you need a place to rest, I can solve that problem. */ /* Text0_1: Welcome!  If you need a place to rest, I can solve that problem. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我们要杀死阿尔萨斯！即便是天灾军团，也不能与部落抗衡！' WHERE entry=12678; /* Text0_0: We will crush Arthas! The Scourge cannot stand up to the might of the Horde! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='在找竞技场战场军官吗?你可以在城镇间的道路上找到他们，或是主城里。$B$B你可以绑定在这里，我也能把你传送至其中一个主城。',Text0_1_loc4='在找竞技场战场军官吗?你可以在城镇间的道路上找到他们，或是主城里。$B$B你可以绑定在这里，我也能把你传送至其中一个主城。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=12684; /* Text0_0: Looking for an Arena Battlemaster? You can find them on the road between towns, or in the capitals.$B$BYou can bind here, at me. I can also teleport you to one of the capitals. */ /* Text0_1: Looking for an Arena Battlemaster? You can find them on the road between towns, or in the capitals.$B$BYou can bind here, at me. I can also teleport you to one of the capitals. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='欢迎你，$c！希望你没有恐高症！$b$b我为你准备了练习用的降落伞。它们是在紧急着陆时使用的。如果你想要缓缓落地，还不如骑着坐骑随便蹦两下呢。如果你想体验极速快感，就要从高处跳下来，在快到落地时打开降落伞！动作要快！你的反应够快吗？$b$b降落伞的效果只能持续几秒，因此你必须在适当的时机使用它。不知道你能不能掌握其中的诀窍。希望你成功。',Text0_1_loc4='欢迎你，$c！希望你没有恐高症！$b$b我为你准备了练习用的降落伞。它们是在紧急着陆时使用的。如果你想要缓缓落地，还不如骑着坐骑随便蹦两下呢。如果你想体验极速快感，就要从高处跳下来，在快到落地时打开降落伞！动作要快！你的反应够快吗？$b$b降落伞的效果只能持续几秒，因此你必须在适当的时机使用它。不知道你能不能掌握其中的诀窍。希望你成功。' WHERE entry=12687; /* Text0_0: Welcome, $c!  I hope you aren\'t afraid of heights!$b$bI\'ve got a practice parachute for you.  These chutes are for quick landings.  If you want to gently soar to the ground, use a mount.  If you want action and an adrenaline rush, you fall.  At the last possible moment you use your chute.  That\'s how these were made.  Quick action!  Are you ready for some quick action?$b$bThe chute only lasts a few seconds.  So you\'ll need to time it just right.  I\'m not sure you can handle it, $c.  I\'d like to see you prove me wrong. */ /* Text0_1: Welcome, $c!  I hope you aren\'t afraid of heights!$b$bI\'ve got a practice parachute for you.  These chutes are for quick landings.  If you want to gently soar to the ground, use a mount.  If you want action and an adrenaline rush, you fall.  At the last possible moment you use your chute.  That\'s how these were made.  Quick action!  Are you ready for some quick action?$b$bThe chute only lasts a few seconds.  So you\'ll need to time it just right.  I\'m not sure you can handle it, $c.  I\'d like to see you prove me wrong. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你最好滚远点，除非你也想尝尝被关进牢笼的滋味……' WHERE entry=12694; /* Text0_0: You\'d better get outta here unless you want to find yourself in one of these cages.... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='$c，谢谢你，自从收到兄弟的来信后，我就一直在关注这件事。$B$B他的牺牲总算不是徒劳的，愿他的灵魂安息。蓝龙军团会付出惨痛的代价的。$B$B我等着这一天！',Text0_1_loc4='$c，谢谢你，自从收到兄弟的来信后，我就一直在关注这件事。$B$B他的牺牲总算不是徒劳的，愿他的灵魂安息。蓝龙军团会付出惨痛的代价的。$B$B我等着这一天！' WHERE entry=12696; /* Text0_0: Thank you, $c, for seeing to it that I received the letter from my brother.$B$BRest assured, his death will not have been in vain. The blue dragonflight will pay for this.$B$BI\'ll see to it personally! */ /* Text0_1: Thank you, $c, for seeing to it that I received the letter from my brother.$B$BRest assured, his death will not have been in vain. The blue dragonflight will pay for this.$B$BI\'ll see to it personally! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='士兵，阻止天灾军团的行动！随时向我汇报情况。一旦你发现可疑的人物，不管是谁，先杀了再说！' WHERE entry=12698; /* Text0_0: Do your part in keeping the Scourge at bay, soldier! Report all suspicious activity and kill first, ask questions later! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='记住我说过的话，这帮愚蠢的被遗忘者迟早会毁了我们！',Text1_0_loc4='你问我的意见？我觉得我们应该趁早杀掉所有的药剂师！' WHERE entry=12699; /* Text0_0: Mark my words, these forsaken fools will be the death of us all! */ /* Text1_0: If you ask me, and you DID, I think we should kill all of the apothecaries before it\'s too late! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text2_0_loc4='部落是为荣耀与战斗而生的。这帮药剂师肯定在干什么不光彩的勾当。',Text3_0_loc4='我始终留意着这群白痴的一举一动。真是怎么提防都不为过！' WHERE entry=12699; /* Text2_0: The Horde is about honor and war. I am certain that there is nothing honorable about what these apothecaries are doing. */ /* Text3_0: I\'m keeping an eye on the forsaken idiots down there. You can never be too cautious around them! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text4_0_loc4='如果你要和那些医师打交道的话，千万当心。他们一定在干什么不正常的勾当。' WHERE entry=12699; /* Text4_0: If you have dealings with the doctor over there, be cautious. Whatever they\'re up to, it\'s unnatural. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='朋友，西边那片荒野上都是尸体。如果你还想活命的话，就离开这里！' WHERE entry=12701; /* Text0_0: Mon, da west wastes of dis place be full o\' baddies. Stay away from dis here area if ya want to live! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我在阿格玛之锤的工作远不止照料兽栏里的动物这么简单。' WHERE entry=12703; /* Text0_0: My charge at Agmar\'s Hammer extends far beyond the care of the animals at the stables. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='死？我吗？嘿嘿，还早着呢。那次不过是点小擦伤。' WHERE entry=12705; /* Text0_0: Expire? Me? Heh, not hardly, kid. That was just a scratch. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='很震撼吧？这些巨人简直是完美的炮灰……呃，是盟友啦。这位就是他们的首领，但他一直拒绝和我谈话。' WHERE entry=12706; /* Text0_0: Impressive, aren\'t they? These giants would be the perfect fodd... er, allies.  This one is their leader, but he continues to refuse to speak with me. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你好，$r。你也是为了躲避巨龙才来到这条峡谷的吧，我们欢迎你啊。但是你要当心那个矮小的家伙……地精就没一个可靠的。' WHERE entry=12707; /* Text0_0: Hello, $r.  You are welcome to share this canyon with us as refuge from the dragons.  Beware the goblin runt though... his kind cannot be trusted. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='只要有足够的钱，我就能征服全世界……' WHERE entry=12708; /* Text0_0: With enough money, I could take over the world... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='控制台位在冒烟的碎石堆前面，你可以听见底下传来引擎的声响。',Text0_1_loc4='控制台位在冒烟的碎石堆前面，你可以听见底下传来引擎的声响。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=12709; /* Text0_0: This console stands before steaming rubble.  The sounds of an engine can be heard below. */ /* Text0_1: This console stands before steaming rubble.  The sounds of an engine can be heard below. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='旅行者，欢迎来到龙眠神殿。$B$B这里供奉着巨龙先祖的遗骸，是巨龙们商谈要事的圣地。$B$B但是最近，蓝龙军团突然对神殿发动攻击，打破了持续数千年的宁静。$B$B带着我们的祝福进入神殿吧，但是请谨记，我们绝不允许任何挑衅行为。' WHERE entry=12713; /* Text0_0: Welcome to Wyrmrest Temple, traveler.$B$BHere the dragonflights confer in peace with one another amidst the bones of their honored ancestors.$B$BAt least, we were peaceful until the Blue Dragonflight launched a surprise attack upon the temple itself.$B$BEnter with our blessing, but know that we will brook no aggression within our walls. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='别来烦我，蠢货！' WHERE entry=12715; /* Text0_0: Leave me be, fool! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='嗯？$c，你想接受我的训练？那你最好做好准备。' WHERE entry=12718; /* Text0_0: What? You want to train under me, $c? You better be ready to work. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='如果你愿意的话，就去兵营休息吧。但不要吵醒我的士兵，不然我会亲手将你扔到雪地里。' WHERE entry=12720; /* Text0_0: You can sleep in the barracks, if you\'d like. Just don\'t wake my men, or I\'ll throw you out in the snow myself. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='谢谢你救了我，$n。我永远不会忘记你的勇气和决心。' WHERE entry=12721; /* Text0_0: Thank you for rescuing me, $N. I will never forget your courage and determination. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='$n，能以部落的兄弟的身份与你并肩作战是我的荣幸。我接受你的提议。' WHERE entry=12722; /* Text0_0: It would be an honor to battle alongside of you as a brother of the Horde, $N. I accept your offer. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='除非你亲手杀死一条龙，否则我可不认你这个朋友……' WHERE entry=12725; /* Text0_0: You not a real mon til you killed a dragon... mon. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='还有什么比猎杀巨龙更惊心动魄的呢。' WHERE entry=12726; /* Text0_0: There\'s no thrill like the thrill of a dragon hunt. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='为什么打搅我？' WHERE entry=12730; /* Text0_0: Why do you disturb me? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='嘿！需要什么东西，直接告诉我就行啦。' WHERE entry=12732; /* Text0_0: Hey dere. You need anythin\', you let me know. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='可恨的天灾军团……他们很快就会得到报应的。' WHERE entry=12733; /* Text0_0: Scourge aberrations... They\'ll get what\'s coming to them soon enough. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='如果你饿了，我这里有食物；如果你需要休息，可以钻进我的帐篷。',Text0_1_loc4='如果你饿了，我这里有食物；如果你需要休息，可以钻进我的帐篷。' WHERE entry=12734; /* Text0_0: I have food, if you are hungry, and you may make use of my tent, should you require rest. */ /* Text0_1: I have food, if you are hungry, and you may make use of my tent, should you require rest. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='外头或许没有下雪，但这里的夜晚够把你的鼻子给冻得掉下来。卧舖就在后头 - 只要别让自己惹人嫌就行了。' WHERE entry=12735; /* Text0_0: Might not be snowy out there, but the nights here can freeze your nose right off. The bunks are in the back - just don\'t make a nuisance of yourself. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='嗨。没有谁要故意为难你啦，不过你最好另找地方过夜。瞧你这身细皮嫩肉的，我不忍心让你吃苦。' WHERE entry=12736; /* Text0_0: Heh. Nothing against you, pup, but you might want to find somewhere else to bed down for the night. Wouldn\'t want that tender skin of yours to get bruised. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='进来坐在火堆旁休息一下吧，$r。希望你不要介意鱼腥味儿。',Text0_1_loc4='进来坐在火堆旁休息一下吧，$r。希望你不要介意鱼腥味儿。' WHERE entry=12738; /* Text0_0: Come in by the fire and rest, $r. I hope you don\'t mind the smell of fish. */ /* Text0_1: Come in by the fire and rest, $r. I hope you don\'t mind the smell of fish. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你好！需要什么吗？' WHERE entry=12740; /* Text0_0: Greetings!  Do you need something? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我的S.T.O.U.T.不只是丢掷啤酒杯的目标，它还是个贵重的训练资产。如果你能击中S.T.O.U.T.，你就能击中所有的东西!$B$B只要别击到我就好。' WHERE entry=12744; /* Text0_0: My S.T.O.U.T. is more than just a target for throwing steins, it\'s a valuable training asset.  If you can hit S.T.O.U.T. you can probably hit anything!$b$bJust try not to hit me. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='高级执行官乌洛斯负责发送悬赏令的奖励。$B$B有诚意者请入内咨询。$B$B谢绝中介！' WHERE entry=12750; /* Text0_0: All rewards to be paid by High Executor Wroth upon verification.$B$BSerious-minded individuals inquire within.$B$BNO SOLICITORS! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='乔伊，是你。真的是你！' WHERE entry=12752; /* Text0_0: Limpy Joe, it\'s you. It\'s really you! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你来这里干什么，小家伙？' WHERE entry=12753; /* Text0_0: What brings you out here, little one? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='<海象人怀疑地打量着你。>$b$b别在此地久留。你并不了解我们，我可希望招惹什么麻烦。',Text0_1_loc4='<海象人怀疑地打量着你。>$b$b别在此地久留。你并不了解我们，我可希望招惹什么麻烦。' WHERE entry=12755; /* Text0_0: <The Tuskarr eyes you suspiciously.>$b$bDo not stay long. You do not understand our people, and I don\'t want trouble. */ /* Text0_1: <The Tuskarr eyes you suspiciously.>$b$bDo not stay long. You do not understand our people, and I don\'t want trouble. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='天空并不安全，朋友。要小心！' WHERE entry=12756; /* Text0_0: The sky is not safe, friend. Be alert! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你需要什么？要不要修理一下护甲或是武器？嗯？' WHERE entry=12759; /* Text0_0: You need something? Maybe your armor or weapon repaired? Hmm? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='小心，周围可能有那些传播着巫妖王诅咒的爪牙。',Text0_1_loc4='小心，周围可能有那些传播着巫妖王诅咒的爪牙。' WHERE entry=12774; /* Text0_0: Be wary, for the plagued tendrils of the Lich King lurk close. */ /* Text0_1: Be wary, for the plagued tendrils of the Lich King lurk close. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='厕所好像被占用了。' WHERE entry=12775; /* Text0_0: The outhouse appears to be occupied at the moment. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='愿圣光净化你，勇敢的$n。',Text0_1_loc4='愿圣光净化你，勇敢的$n。' WHERE entry=12776; /* Text0_0: May the Light purge your infection, brave $N. */ /* Text0_1: May the Light purge your infection, brave $N. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我的父亲将他的作战盔甲和斧头都送给我啦。很快我就能好好利用它们了。' WHERE entry=12777; /* Text0_0: My father has gifted me with his battle armor and axe. Soon I put it to good use. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='真幸运，厕所现在没人。' WHERE entry=12779; /* Text0_0: Fortunately, the outhouse is currently vacant. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='当我得知北方还有宗亲时，就满心欢喜地赶来寻访。可我见到的全是侵略性极强的部族，他们身上完全没有和平的天性。$B$B$c，我很绝望。就连伟大的乌索克都没能逃过堕落的命运。$B$B我已经丧失了所有希望。' WHERE entry=12785; /* Text0_0: When I learned about my relatives here in the north, I came to learn more.  What I found was warring tribes acting against our very nature.$B$BI have no hope left, $r.  Even great Ursoc has been tainted by this cursed place.$B$BI\'ve lost all hope. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='是的……我能感觉到沃达希尔的魔法能量……没有丝毫被污染的迹象。$B$B让我帮助你吧！命运让我来到这里，或许我能帮上忙的！' WHERE entry=12787; /* Text0_0: Yes... I sense Vordrassil\'s magic... free of any perceivable taint.$B$BPlease!  You must allow me to help you.  Fate brought me here, perhaps I can serve a purpose yet! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='塞巴鲁斯打心眼儿里感激你。若不是你，我早就没命啦，说不定还会变成亡灵的一员……' WHERE entry=12790; /* Text0_0: Zybarus thanks you from the bottom of his heart, hero. Without you, Zybarus would have died, or worse, Zybarus would have become one of them... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我曾在灰白之丘游荡过，伟大的厄索克之子，统治了那个地方。$B$B但是如今…如今我却注定在这个洞穴里面度过余生了。' WHERE entry=12793; /* Text0_0: I once roamed the Grizzly Hills, son to the great Ursoc, who ruled over this land.$B$BBut now... now I\'m doomed to spend the rest of my life in this cave. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你不明白。如果我想的话我可以杀出这个洞窟。$B$B是我的父亲，厄索克。他从死亡中回来了…但是不再是以前的他。$B$B他在几千年前的先祖之战中牺牲了性命。几百年来，信仰他的熊怪们试图找出复活他的方法。$B$B最后他们决定试图重植世界树，沃达希尔，并且使用世界树的魔法将我的父亲带回这世界。' WHERE entry=12794; /* Text0_0: You don\'t understand.  If I wanted to I could fight my way out of this cave.$B$BIt\'s my father, Ursoc.  He has returned from the dead... but he\'s not the same.$B$BHe gave his life during the War of the Ancients thousands of years ago.  For centuries, the furbolg who worshipped him tried to devise a way to resurrect him.$B$BFinally they decided they were to attempt to regrow the failed world tree, Vordrassil, and use its magic to bring back my father. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='他们种下的树苗结出了果实。起初似乎很顺利，厄索克回来了，有一阵子我心中充满了喜悦。$B$B但当他复活之后，很显然跟以前不同了。熊怪也是。$B$B不论是什麽样的邪恶导致上古德鲁伊摧毁了沃达希尔，它显然寄居在新的树中，并且把他们全部变成了嗜血的怪兽。$B$B现在在灰白之丘走动的怪物并不是我的父亲，我们得让他安息。' WHERE entry=12796; /* Text0_0: The sapling they grew bore a fruit.  At first it seemed to work.  Ursoc did come back and I was filled with joy for a brief moment.$B$BAs he recovered, it was clear that he wasn\'t the same.  Neither were the furbolg.$B$BWhatever evil caused the ancient druids to tear down Vordrassil manifested itself in the new tree and turned them all into monsters filled with bloodlust.$B$BThe thing that now walks the Grizzly Hills is not my father and it must be put to rest. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我是寇荻安，厄索克之女。我守护这个一度神圣的祭坛。$B$B我已经很久没有看过陌生人来此了。' WHERE entry=12797; /* Text0_0: I am Kodian, daughter of Ursoc.  I watch over this once sacred shrine.$B$BI\'ve not seen a stranger come here in a long time. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='一个名叫图尔·怒掌的熊怪，不是我们之一。$B$B他来自南边，属於木喉部族。$B$B他想要见厄索克。他似乎觉得沃达希尔的腐化可以被净化，并且用来拯救我父亲。$B$B用这样的希望来戏弄我是很愚蠢的，当你见到他，如同我一样，被黑暗所折磨，你会同意我说的话的。' WHERE entry=12798; /* Text0_0: A furbolg named Tur Ragepaw.  Not one of ours.$B$BThis one came from the southern lands.  He was of the Timbermaw tribe.$B$BHe wanted to see Ursoc.  He seemed to think that Vordrassil\'s taint could be purified and used to save my father.$B$BIt is foolish to entertain such hopes.  You will agree when you see the darkness that has afflicted him like I have. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='啊，你是来救我的吧。快带我离开这个鬼地方！' WHERE entry=12805; /* Text0_0: Oh good, you\'re here to rescue me. Now let me out of here! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='嘿！我觉得我好像在哪儿见过你。$B$B不如救我出去，怎么样？' WHERE entry=12806; /* Text0_0: Hey, $g buddy : ma\'am;. I\'ve seen you around.$B$BMind getting me out of here? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我根本不知道出了什么状况。我刚到怨毒镇没多久，就突然在睡梦中被关进了牢笼！$B$B你是来救我的吗？' WHERE entry=12808; /* Text0_0: I don\'t know what happened. I had just arrived at Venomspite and then all of a sudden I woke up in this cage!$B$BAre you here to rescue me? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='族长特沃德·艾利克森易怒的元龙被拴在这里。' WHERE entry=12811; /* Text0_0: Thane Torvald Eriksson\'s temperamental proto-drake is chained up here. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='嗯?你想说什麽?' WHERE entry=12812; /* Text0_0: Yes? What is it? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='每隔两年竞赛之灵都会变得特别激动热情…而现在正是这个时候!我们穿着这身外袍前往战场荣耀它们，打败我们的敌人然后赢得它们的眷顾。',Text0_1_loc4='每隔两年竞赛之灵都会变得特别激动热情…而现在正是这个时候!我们穿着这身外袍前往战场荣耀它们，打败我们的敌人然后赢得它们的眷顾。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=12819; /* Text0_0: Every two years the Spirits of Competition grow especially fervent... and now is that time! We wear this tabard into the Battlegrounds to honor them, seeking to defeat our enemies and earn their favor. */ /* Text0_1: Every two years the Spirits of Competition grow especially fervent... and now is that time! We wear this tabard into the Battlegrounds to honor them, seeking to defeat our enemies and earn their favor. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
