UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我受不了啦……$b$b他们会杀了你，然后吃掉你的尸体！据说这样还算幸运的！你能想象比这更倒霉的遭遇吗！',Text0_1_loc4='我受不了啦……$b$b他们会杀了你，然后吃掉你的尸体！据说这样还算幸运的！你能想象比这更倒霉的遭遇吗！',Text1_0_loc4='你一定要救我出去，$r！$b$b我可不想落得他们那样悲惨的下场！',Text1_1_loc4='你一定要救我出去，$r！$b$b我可不想落得他们那样悲惨的下场！' WHERE entry=13069; /* Text0_0: I can\'t take it anymore....$b$bThey kill you, then eat you! And that\'s if you\'re lucky! */ /* Text0_1: I can\'t take it anymore....$b$bThey kill you, then eat you! And that\'s if you\'re lucky! */ /* Text1_0: You gotta help me get outta here, $r!$b$bI don\'t wanna become like them! */ /* Text1_1: You gotta help me get outta here, $r!$b$bI don\'t wanna become like them! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text2_0_loc4='自打我来到这里，就一直吃不下睡不着。$b$b我根本不该加入银色北伐军……',Text2_1_loc4='自打我来到这里，就一直吃不下睡不着。$b$b我根本不该加入银色北伐军……',Text3_0_loc4='<呜咽>我叔叔是银色黎明的成员。$b$b他怎么有勇气面对这些肮脏的怪物啊？',Text3_1_loc4='<呜咽>我叔叔是银色黎明的成员。$b$b他怎么有勇气面对这些肮脏的怪物啊？' WHERE entry=13069; /* Text2_0: I haven\'t been able to eat or sleep since I got here.$b$bI\'m just not cut out for the Crusade.... */ /* Text2_1: I haven\'t been able to eat or sleep since I got here.$b$bI\'m just not cut out for the Crusade.... */ /* Text3_0: <sob> My uncle served in the Argent Dawn.$b$bHow was he able to face these foul things? */ /* Text3_1: <sob> My uncle served in the Argent Dawn.$b$bHow was he able to face these foul things? */
