UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='达卡莱帝国走上了自我毁灭的道路，我们为此感到悲哀。$B$B他们通过弑神夺来的力量只能维持一段很短的时间。$B$B这短暂的收益将葬送达卡莱帝国的未来。' WHERE entry=13176; /* Text0_0: It saddens all of us to see the Drakkari destroying themselves this way.$B$BThe power that they gain from killing the natural gods of the land is transitory.$B$BWhat is gained in the short run will be lost to them for all eternity. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='集中精神，我们必须继续前进。' WHERE entry=13177; /* Text0_0: Gather your senses quickly, we must press on. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='局势严峻。斯坦索姆正在燃烧。我们必须穿越着火带，击杀沿途的天灾军团，设法抵达玛尔加尼斯所在的十字军广场。做好准备吧。' WHERE entry=13179; /* Text0_0: This isn\'t getting any easier. Stratholme is burning. We must brave the Scourge and the flames to reach Mal\'Ganis. Prepare yourselves. */
