UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='全盛状态的琥珀幼龙可以使用时间裂隙，制造出压缩时间结界包围敌对目标。穿过结界的法术将对该目标造成双倍的伤害，还能在目标身上叠加震击能量。' WHERE entry=13257; /* Text0_0: An Amber Drake at full power can perform Temporal Rift, which creates a bubble of compressed time around an enemy.  Spells that pass through the bubble deal double damage and can generate Shock Charges on the target. */
