UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='科弗斯能为你提供什么服务？' WHERE entry=13262; /* Text0_0: What is it that you need from Corvus? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='仔细回想今天你目睹的一切，$n。$B$B未来已经注定，你唯一需要考虑的只是你想在其中扮演怎样的角色。' WHERE entry=13265; /* Text0_0: Ponder on da thing you have witnessed this day, $n.$b$bDa future already be written. Only thing to decide be your part in it, mon. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='玛里苟斯最强大的仆从守卫着上层的环。单凭你的力量，根本不可能战胜他们。我们将赋予你召唤幼龙的能力。你可以骑着幼龙在魔环飞翔并使用强大的龙族魔法。' WHERE entry=13267; /* Text0_0: Malygos\' most powerful agents protect the rings above.  Alone, you cannot hope to defeat them.  We can grant you power to call upon drakes from our dragon flights.  Mounted on the back of a drake, you will be able to fly here in the Oculus and command powerful dragon magic. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='没有谁比死亡骑士更了解天灾军团。$B$B相信我，$r。全力火拼，以牙还牙才是最奏效的战争策略。' WHERE entry=13270; /* Text0_0: None know the Scourge better than we death knights.$b$bBelieve me, $r, there\'s nothing more effective than fighting fire with fire.... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='对老纳斯宽容点。他年纪大了，体力早已不如从前。' WHERE entry=13271; /* Text0_0: Take it easy on old Nass. He\'s not as young and resilient as he once was. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我的同胞或许会让你探索祖达克的秘密，但是赞达拉氏族始终肩负着见证历史的使命，并将如实地记载巨魔帝国毁灭的篇章。' WHERE entry=13282; /* Text0_0: Though my compatriots would have you take an active role in what is transpiring in Zul\'Drak, we Zandalari are primarily here to witness what is occurring and to chronicle the end of an empire. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你准备好和我一起挑战玛尔加尼斯了吗？' WHERE entry=13287; /* Text0_0: Are you ready to face Mal\'Ganis with me? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='一切都准备就绪啦。' WHERE entry=13288; /* Text0_0: Everything is set up and ready to go. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='达卡莱巨魔将我囚禁在祭坛，令我的肉身处于濒死状况。但是他们无法看见我的灵魂。$B$B我们必须协同作战，阻止他们夺取我的力量。' WHERE entry=13291; /* Text0_0: The Drakkari are keeping my body close to death up in the altar building. They cannot see my spirit though.$B$BWe must work together to prevent them from getting my power. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='请你快一点，$n。我承受着莫大的痛苦，时间已经不多了。' WHERE entry=13293; /* Text0_0: Please hurry, $N. I am in a great deal of pain and time is running out. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='嗷嗷……瞧那只食尸鬼。$b$b跳一下呀！跳一下！$b$b哈哈哈……真是一只可爱的食尸鬼。' WHERE entry=13300; /* Text0_0: Awww... look at da purty lil\' gool.$b$bJump, lil\' gool! Jump!$b$bHa, ha, ha.... Attsa guud lil\' gool. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='只要这堵墙拆掉，我们就要舖另外一条通往暴风港的路…但是那个疯矮人用了足以移平整座广场的火药啦!$B$B我不晓得当初艾力克斯顿大人雇用她的时候脑袋在想什麽…她是个满口脏话、刻薄成性、刚愎自用的人!' WHERE entry=13302; /* Text0_0: We\'re building another road down into Stormwind Harbor as soon as this wall has been removed... but this mad dwarf brought enough powder to level the entire quarter!$B$BI don\'t know what Master Alexston was thinking when he hired her... she\'s foul-mouthed, mean, and stubborn as an ox! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='哨站属于无齿轮区域。如果有谁在制造机械装置时使用齿轮，就会遭到无情的嘲笑。' WHERE entry=13306; /* Text0_0: This outpost is a cog-free zone. Persons employing cogs in the construction of mechanical devices will be subject to unrelenting mockery. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='看来你和我的想法一样啊。你想找些水果，对吧？',Text0_1_loc4='看来你和我的想法一样啊。你想找些水果，对吧？' WHERE entry=13307; /* Text0_0: Looks like you had the same idea I did. Hunting for fruit, are you? */ /* Text0_1: Looks like you had the same idea I did. Hunting for fruit, are you? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='洛肯？！这下我们碰到大麻烦了……虽然铁矮人已经被全部摆平了，但我敢打赌不知道什么鬼地方还有台机器，正不停向外吐着铁维库人！' WHERE entry=13308; /* Text0_0: Loken?! That\'s downright bothersome... We might\'ve neutralized the iron dwarves, but I\'d lay odds there\'s another machine somewhere else churnin\' out a whole mess o\' these iron vrykul! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='去城外东南方找东部飞艇塔。',Text0_1_loc4='去城外东南方找东部飞艇塔。' WHERE entry=13311; /* Text0_0: Look for the eastern Zeppelin Landing Tower outside of the city to the southeast. */ /* Text0_1: Look for the eastern Zeppelin Landing Tower outside of the city to the southeast. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='苔行鳄鱼人似乎受了重伤。' WHERE entry=13318; /* Text0_0: The mosswalker looks severely injured. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我可怜的飞行器。她在坠机事故中遭到严重损坏，我偏偏没有备用零件。看样子她是没法恢复原貌了！' WHERE entry=13322; /* Text0_0: My poor flying machine. She didn\'t survive the crash and without spare parts, I\'ll never get \'er up and running again! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='来吧，凡人……$B$B忍耐！你将拥有真正的力量！' WHERE entry=13325; /* Text0_0: Ya be on da path, mortal....$b$bEndure, and ya be gettin\' great power! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='Mphmm rmphhimm rrhumghph？',Text1_0_loc4='Rmmurphum mmph hmrphum！' WHERE entry=13326; /* Text0_0: Mphmm rmphhimm rrhumghph? */ /* Text1_0: Rmmurphum mmph hmrphum! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text2_0_loc4='Umphrum mmphur, murruphru……',Text3_0_loc4='Mhrrumph rummrhum phurr！' WHERE entry=13326; /* Text2_0: Umphrum mmphur, murruphru... */ /* Text3_0: Mhrrumph rummrhum phurr! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='欢迎光临。请问你想休息还是进餐？',Text0_1_loc4='欢迎光临。请问你想休息还是进餐？' WHERE entry=13328; /* Text0_0: Welcome. May I offer you rest or sustenance? */ /* Text0_1: Welcome. May I offer you rest or sustenance? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你是来找哈古斯买东西的吗？' WHERE entry=13342; /* Text0_0: Come to buy from Hargus, you have? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='想要赢得巫妖王的宠爱？$B$B有充分价值的人才能获得黑暗的礼物……' WHERE entry=13348; /* Text0_0: Another supplicant seeking the favors of da Lich King?$b$bOnly da worthy be obtainin\' da dark gifts.... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='欢迎来到达拉然公会注册办事处。请问你需要什么帮助？',Text0_1_loc4='欢迎来到达拉然公会注册办事处。请问你需要什么帮助？' WHERE entry=13349; /* Text0_0: Welcome to Dalaran\'s Guild Registry offices. How may I help you? */ /* Text0_1: Welcome to Dalaran\'s Guild Registry offices. How may I help you? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我费了很多功夫，才迫使赫米特遵守协议。只希望大法师能赏识我的才能。' WHERE entry=13352; /* Text0_0: I hope the archmage appreciates what I\'ve gone through to uphold Hemet\'s end of the bargain. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我们将夺走他们的一切，死亡骑士。' WHERE entry=13355; /* Text0_0: We will take everything from them, death knight. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='狂心氏族将夺得这块土地的控制权。大舌头怪最好滚得远远的，不然我们就将他们统统杀掉。' WHERE entry=13359; /* Text0_0: Frenzyheart will take land for own. Big-tongues will leave or we kill them good. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='狂心狼獾人很看起来凶猛，但其实我们是好人呀。时间长了，你就会发现，我们和聪明强壮的朋友相处得很好。$B$B我们只是不善于和笨蛋打交道而已。' WHERE entry=13360; /* Text0_0: Frenzyheart can be vicious, but we good people. You see if you stay long, we friends with smart and strong just fine.$B$BWe just don\'t like dumb. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='这就是雨水巨石。我们保护它，向它供奉闪闪发亮的宝贝；它就会庇护我们。$B$B你有亮闪闪的宝贝吗？' WHERE entry=13361; /* Text0_0: This the Great Rain Stone. We keep it safe and bring it shinies and it take care of us.$B$BHave more shinies for stone maybe? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我的个子不高，但是我会很厉害的魔法。我负责保护迷雾巨石……嗯，大多数时候我还是相当称职的。$B$B愚蠢的狗狗人。' WHERE entry=13362; /* Text0_0: What I not have in height I make up for in magics. I take care of Great Mist Stone good... most of time anyway.$B$BDumb puppy-men. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='狗狗人的攻击已经持续好几天了。但是闪电巨石还很安全。$B$B跟往常一样，索乌霍鲁向我们伸出了援手……狗狗人不会有获胜的机会。' WHERE entry=13363; /* Text0_0: Puppy-men been attacking us for days now. Great Lightning Stone is still safe though.$B$BSoo-holu come to help us like many times before... puppy-men not stand a chance. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='卡塔克是来吃大舌头怪的。我们要为他准备一顿大餐。' WHERE entry=13364; /* Text0_0: Kartak comes for big-tongue meat. Frenzyheart make sure plenty is ready. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='干皮人，你好。',Text1_0_loc4='你在看什麽?' WHERE entry=13365; /* Text0_0: Hello, dryskin. */ /* Text1_0: What are you looking at? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text2_0_loc4='为什么我们还待在这里？',Text3_0_loc4='你想要什么东西吗？' WHERE entry=13365; /* Text2_0: Is there a reason we\'re still standing here? */ /* Text3_0: I assume you want something. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='一切顺利吗？',Text1_0_loc4='啥?' WHERE entry=13366; /* Text0_0: Everything okay? */ /* Text1_0: Yeah? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text2_0_loc4='有你这样优秀的猎手陪同，感觉真好。',Text3_0_loc4='怎么啦？' WHERE entry=13366; /* Text2_0: It nice having a good hunting partner. */ /* Text3_0: Something wrong? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='嗨！你还好吧？我们很好……嗯，很好很好。嗨！',Text1_0_loc4='你被自己绊倒过吗？我们有过这样的经历诶。有点痛。不好玩，我们不要再绊倒了。' WHERE entry=13367; /* Text0_0: Hi! How you? We\'re good... yup, good good. Hi! */ /* Text1_0: Ever trip over own feet? We have. Kind of hurt. No do it, not fun. Nope. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text2_0_loc4='你好！你看上去又强壮又和善。我喜欢你。我们做朋友好不好啊？',Text3_0_loc4='要帮忙吗？要帮忙吗？我们是很乐于助人的。' WHERE entry=13367; /* Text2_0: Hello! You\'re pretty strong and nice and stuff. I like you. Lets stay friends, okay? */ /* Text3_0: Want us to help with something? What we help with? We good at helping. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='天气不错啊，很适合飞行，不是吗？' WHERE entry=13375; /* Text0_0: Nice day for flying, isn\'t it? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我一眼就能认出谁是王牌飞行员。谢谢你救了我！' WHERE entry=13376; /* Text0_0: I know an ace when I see one.  Thanks again for saving my life! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='看看你所取得的成就，死亡骑士！你真是天灾军团的荣耀！' WHERE entry=13382; /* Text0_0: Look at what you have done, death knight! You have brought glory to the Scourge! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='放我出去，朋友！',Text1_0_loc4='你不是天灾军团的成员。朋友，你来这儿做什么？' WHERE entry=13390; /* Text0_0: Lemme outta here, mon! */ /* Text1_0: You\'re no Scourge. What you doin\' here, mon? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text2_0_loc4='天灾军团怎么会允许你四处闲逛？',Text3_0_loc4='你迷路了吧……' WHERE entry=13390; /* Text2_0: Why da Scourge let you walk around in here, mon? */ /* Text3_0: I think you be lost, mon.... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='祖达克不欢迎天灾军团！',Text1_0_loc4='朋友，祖达克属于达卡莱氏族。永远都是！' WHERE entry=13391; /* Text0_0: You Scourge not welcome in Zul\'Drak! */ /* Text1_0: Zul\'Drak belongs to da Drakkari, mon. Always will! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text2_0_loc4='天灾军团注定会失败。',Text3_0_loc4='我们会杀光天灾兵！' WHERE entry=13391; /* Text2_0: You Scourge gunna fail here, mon. */ /* Text3_0: Our people gunna kill every last one o\' you Scourge! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text4_0_loc4='滚开，恶心的天灾兵！' WHERE entry=13391; /* Text4_0: Get away from me, nasty Scourge! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='一旦放置天灾锅，这块看似普通的南瓜田就会成为诅咒的源头！' WHERE entry=13395; /* Text0_0: It might look like an ordinary pumpkin patch now, but once the plague cauldron is placed it will become a source of disease, rot and plague! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你竟敢提起他！滚出我的视线！',Text1_0_loc4='那个马屁精大概正在房间里练习芭蕾舞吧。' WHERE entry=13396; /* Text0_0: How dare you! Get out of my sight! */ /* Text1_0: That no good kiss-up is probably practicing ballet in his chambers. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text2_0_loc4='别在我面前提他的名字！我只警告你这一次！',Text3_0_loc4='我可以告诉你他不在哪儿……' WHERE entry=13396; /* Text2_0: NEVER say that name around me! Consider this your one and only warning! */ /* Text3_0: I can tell you where he\'s not... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text4_0_loc4='希尔盖可能在清理他那间肮脏的舞蹈室。' WHERE entry=13396; /* Text4_0: Heigan is probably performing maintenance on his slime and crap filled dance studio. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='新阿瓦隆被攻陷只是时间问题。' WHERE entry=13397; /* Text0_0: It\'s only a matter of time before the plague overtakes New Avalon. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='芬努斯这里有你需要的东西，朋友。' WHERE entry=13402; /* Text0_0: Fineous has what you need, friend. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='十字军……$B$B<瑞文戴尔男爵摇了摇头。>$B$B他们是一群特殊的人类。在我看来，十字军似乎不具备高等智慧，他们无法理智地评估局势并计算得失。只要提到圣光，就能让他们群情激昂——接着，这帮家伙会完全无视自己的利益，盲目地投身战斗。' WHERE entry=13419; /* Text0_0: Crusaders...$B$B<Rivendare shakes his head.>$B$BI am convinced that they are a unique lot amongst the humans. My theory is that they lack higher brain function, unable to logically assess a situation and calculate an outcome. One has only to make mention of the Light to get them frothing and battle ready - at which point they will rush headlong into any engagement with complete disregard for their own well being. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='$n！我一直在等你。你怎么去了那么久？$b$b我们可以对荒芜之血进行转换了。$b$b让我们共同见证军队的诞生吧！' WHERE entry=13422; /* Text0_0: $n! I\'ve been awaiting your return. What be takin\' ya so long, mon?$b$bIt be time to complete da conversion of da Blightbloods.$b$bJoin me and witness the creation of our army! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我伤得很重，但是我会尽量帮忙的。你最好待在我撑起的反魔法屏障中，否则侍僧的魔法会将你撕成碎片。' WHERE entry=13425; /* Text0_0: I\'m badly injured, but I\'ll do what I can to help. Try and stay inside of my anti-magic barrier or the acolytes\' magic will tear you apart. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='$C，有什麽我可以帮你的吗?',Text0_1_loc4='$C，有什麽我可以帮你的吗?' WHERE entry=13426; /* Text0_0: What can I do for you, $R? */ /* Text0_1: What can I do for you, $R? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='<库尔迪拉呻吟着。>' WHERE entry=13430; /* Text0_0: <Koltira groans.> */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='血色十字军将迎来一名新主子——我是说，在他们死后……' WHERE entry=13432; /* Text0_0: The Scarlet Crusade will serve a new master - in death... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你这是挑衅吗？',Text0_1_loc4='你这是挑衅吗？' WHERE entry=13433; /* Text0_0: Are you challenging me, $g brother:sister;? */ /* Text0_1: Are you challenging me, $g brother:sister;? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='总有一天，雷耶克会成为强大的战士。' WHERE entry=13438; /* Text0_0: One day, Rejek be mighty warrior. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='要去奥伯丁或者无畏要塞吗？只要穿过运河，就能抵达位于教堂广场和花园之间的暴风城港口。',Text0_1_loc4='要去奥伯丁或者无畏要塞吗？只要穿过运河，就能抵达位于教堂广场和花园之间的暴风城港口。',Text1_0_loc4='暴风城港口是前往奥伯丁和无畏要塞的捷径。它就在教堂广场和花园之间。',Text1_1_loc4='暴风城港口是前往奥伯丁和无畏要塞的捷径。它就在教堂广场和花园之间。' WHERE entry=13439; /* Text0_0: Trying to reach Auberdine or Valiance Keep?  You can find Stormwind Harbor if you head through the Canals, between the Cathedral District and the Park. */ /* Text0_1: Trying to reach Auberdine or Valiance Keep?  You can find Stormwind Harbor if you head through the Canals, between the Cathedral District and the Park. */ /* Text1_0: Stormwind Harbor is the fastest way to get to Auberdine or Valiance Keep.  You can find it between the Cathedral District and the Park. */ /* Text1_1: Stormwind Harbor is the fastest way to get to Auberdine or Valiance Keep.  You can find it between the Cathedral District and the Park. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你好，$c。我想你是来告诉我有关全球受邀典礼的好消息吧?如果没错，那你来这里就是要告诉我验证码的。而为了感谢你提供的验证码，我会给你一份礼物，泰瑞尔之柄。$B$B等你准备好后，就在我耳边小小声地告诉我吧。',Text0_1_loc4='你好，$c。我想你是来告诉我有关全球受邀典礼的好消息吧?如果没错，那你来这里就是要告诉我验证码的。而为了感谢你提供的验证码，我会给你一份礼物，泰瑞尔之柄。$B$B等你准备好后，就在我耳边小小声地告诉我吧。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你 $N' WHERE entry=13441; /* Text0_0: Greetings, $c. I trust that you bring me good news concerning the Worldwide Invitational event? If you are, then surely that means you were given a secret code to tell me. In return for your code I will give you a gift, Tyrael\'s Hilt.$B$BJust whisper it in my ear when you are ready. */ /* Text0_1: Greetings, $c. I trust that you bring me good news concerning the Worldwide Invitational event? If you are, then surely that means you were given a secret code to tell me. In return for your code I will give you a gift, Tyrael\'s Hilt.$B$BJust whisper it in my ear when you are ready. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我们是被巫妖王选中的死亡骑士，$n。身为天灾军团的一员，我们要坚定执行巫妖王的意志。' WHERE entry=13444; /* Text0_0: We are the chosen ones, $N. Death knights of the Scourge, sent to sow the seeds of the master\'s destruction. */
