UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你好，$c。我可以帮你找回失散的伙伴。',Text0_1_loc4='你好，$c。我可以帮你找回失散的伙伴。' WHERE entry=13584; /* Text0_0: Greetings, $c. I can assist you in recovering lost companions. */ /* Text0_1: Greetings, $c. I can assist you in recovering lost companions. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我踏遍了艾泽拉斯的每一寸土地，想要寻找失落的荣耀并收复属于我的王国。在我离开暴风城的这段日子里，联盟经历了种种考验。有你这样的英雄保卫我们脆弱的盟国，我真是倍感欣慰。' WHERE entry=13593; /* Text0_0: Too long have I been gone, fighting my way across Azeroth to rediscover my past and reclaim my throne. With all the challenges that have tested the Alliance in my absence, it warms my heart to see heroes such as yourself defending our coalition. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='别再浪费时间了。$c，消灭巫妖王的爪牙！' WHERE entry=13607; /* Text0_0: You\'re wasting time. Go kill the minions of the Lich King, $c! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='对抗巫妖王的战事有何进展，$c？' WHERE entry=13608; /* Text0_0: How fare your efforts against the Lich King, $c? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='先锋军将彻底消灭巫妖王的部队！' WHERE entry=13609; /* Text0_0: It is good to see you again, $N. How could I ever forget the $g man : woman; who saved my sister\'s life? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='很高兴再次见到你，$N。' WHERE entry=13610; /* Text0_0: It is good to see you again, $N. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='<当你靠近时，霜脉斥候试图站起来；但是他很快就跌倒在地，紧紧地捂住身体上那条明显的伤口。>' WHERE entry=13611; /* Text0_0: <The Frostborn Scout attempts to rise to his feet as you approach, but stumbles back to the ground, clenching an obviously painful wound in his side.> */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='来不及了。我失血过多……坚持不了多久了。' WHERE entry=13612; /* Text0_0: I don\'t think that\'s going to happen, $G lad:lass;. I\'ve lost a lot of blood... there\'s no way I\'m making it back. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='一群鹰身人突然冲出山谷。带领她们的是一只名叫希尔拉娜的鹰身人……我无路可逃。我不明白……她们为何变得如此具有攻击性……我放松了警惕……是我的失误。' WHERE entry=13613; /* Text0_0: A pack of harpies came up from the valley. A big one named Sirana led them... I didn\'t have anywhere to escape. They haven\'t been this aggressive for a long time... I didn\'t expect it... I let my guard down.... it\'s my own fault. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='没……没有用……太晚了。$B$B<霜脉斥候往雪地上咳出几口鲜血。>$B$B替我……报仇……$B$B<霜脉斥候咽下最后一口气，摊倒在地。>' WHERE entry=13614; /* Text0_0: It\'s a little late... for that... $G lad:lass;.$B$B<The Frostborn Scout coughs up some blood on the snow.>$B$BGet... that wench in charge for me...$B$B<The Frostborn Scout slumps over as he breathes his last breath.> */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你千万不能败露自己的行踪。我要继续装出臣服于巫妖王的模样！' WHERE entry=13616; /* Text0_0: Do keep out of sight, will you? I\'m trying to pretend that I\'m still under the Lich King\'s control! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='戈尔克、布尔和达加斯都死了……只有我和马克拉尔活了下来。希望你为我们带来了好消息。' WHERE entry=13619; /* Text0_0: Gerk, Burr, Dargath: all gone... It\'s just MacKellar and I left out here. I hope you\'ve brought some good news. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='安静！孩子们在睡觉！',Text0_1_loc4='安静！孩子们在睡觉！' WHERE entry=13628; /* Text0_0: Please to be quiet! Pups asleeping! */ /* Text0_1: Please to be quiet! Pups asleeping! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我自由了，暴风的复仇将随之而来！' WHERE entry=13639; /* Text0_0: With my freedom comes the vengeance of storm! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='开战之前，我会向你介绍敌人的情况。听仔细了，要对付天灾军团，必须做好充分的准备。',Text0_1_loc4='开战之前，我会向你介绍敌人的情况。听仔细了，要对付天灾军团，必须做好充分的准备。' WHERE entry=13640; /* Text0_0: Listen to what I have to tell you about our enemy before we start. You don\'t want to be unprepared while we\'re out smashing Scourge in the field. */ /* Text0_1: Listen to what I have to tell you about our enemy before we start. You don\'t want to be unprepared while we\'re out smashing Scourge in the field. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='<布莱恩满怀期待地看着你。>' WHERE entry=13641; /* Text0_0: <Brann looks at you expectantly.> */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你能想象吗？奥杜尔中埋藏着所有的智慧与知识，甚至还有生命本身的秘密！' WHERE entry=13642; /* Text0_0: Imagine all the wisdom and knowledge locked away within Ulduar. The very secrets of life could be held there! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='伯克塔认为坠机事故只是一次倒霉的经历，但是我相信我们可以从中学到点什么。' WHERE entry=13646; /* Text0_0: Boktar thinks this crash an unfortunate event, but I believe we\'re intended to learn something from it. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='伊米亚的战争领主，天选者奥贾尔就在东北方的痛苦之匣，准备唤醒他的瓦古大军。$B$B跨越东边的死亡旷野，你可以在通往祖达克第二层的阶梯附近找到纳瓦留斯王子。$B$B塞穆不知所踪，从体型来看，他是很难藏匿的。$B$B必须将他们统统解决！' WHERE entry=13647; /* Text0_0: The Ymirjar battle lord, Algar the Chosen, rouses his Vargul armies at the Reliquary of Pain, northeast of this cage.$B$BPrince Navarius is across the Dead Fields, east of here, near the great steps leading up to the second level of Zul\'Drak.$B$BThrym\'s location is currently unknown, which is curious considering his size.$B$BAll must be dealt with! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='毒药……胃部在剧烈翻腾……',Text0_1_loc4='毒药……胃部在剧烈翻腾……' WHERE entry=13650; /* Text0_0: Poison... my insides are churning... */ /* Text0_1: Poison... my insides are churning... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你准备好了就告诉我一声。我希望越快越好……因为毒药正在慢慢发作。',Text0_1_loc4='你准备好了就告诉我一声。我希望越快越好……因为毒药正在慢慢发作。' WHERE entry=13651; /* Text0_0: Let me know when you\'re ready. I\'d prefer sooner than later... what with the slowly dying from poison and all. */ /* Text0_1: Let me know when you\'re ready. I\'d prefer sooner than later... what with the slowly dying from poison and all. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我们必须继续攻打尤顿海姆。不能给他们丝毫喘息的机会！让他们不眠不休地疲劳作战！拒绝纳降！$B$B即便是灰烬使者的持有者提里奥·弗丁和他麾下的银色北伐军，都不可能取得你如今的成就！$B$B$n，开战吧！就在我们闲聊的时候，说不定局势已经发生了巨大的逆转。' WHERE entry=13654; /* Text0_0: We must strike at Jotunheim continuously. Never give them a chance to catch their breath, never a chance to sleep, and never accept surrender!$B$BTirion Fordring with all the might of Ashbringer and the Argent Crusade behind him cannot hope to accomplish what you are doing!$B$BNow, be quick about your business, $N. There is too much occurring for idle chit-chat. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='等你准备好，我就将你放在我的头顶，然后我们一起消灭祖达克的天灾军团。你要指挥我对付敌人！' WHERE entry=13656; /* Text0_0: When you are ready I will place you atop my head and we will march into the heart of the Scourge in Zul\'Drak. You must direct me to smash and destroy our enemies! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我们遇到麻烦了，$r！当心身后！' WHERE entry=13658; /* Text0_0: We\'re in over our heads, $r! Watch your back! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='感谢你帮助黑锋骑士团夺取了暗影拱顶。能得到你的支持真是我们的荣幸。$B$B联盟和部落仍在互相厮杀，殊不知这只会让巫妖王获益。我们必须集中精力，处理好眼前的要事。$B$B对银色北伐军来说，他们总是在制定作战计划时犹豫不决，一心想着如何完美地击败敌人，我们就没有这些乱七八糟的担忧。$B$B$n，你就是我们执行复仇大业的工具。' WHERE entry=13659; /* Text0_0: The Ebon Blade is indebted to you for your help in taking The Shadow Vault. We are lucky to have you.$B$BWhile the Alliance and the Horde fight each other, doing the Lich King\'s job for him, we will stay focused on the task at hand.$B$BWhere the Argent Crusade might falter and think twice about how best to crush the enemy, we will have no such moral difficulties.$B$BYou shall be our instrument of vengeance, $N. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='如果你没别的事可做，就去杀掉这些家伙吧！' WHERE entry=13671; /* Text0_0: If there\'s nothing else that you can do, kill these things! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我能照顾自己的，$n。' WHERE entry=13673; /* Text0_0: I can take care of myself, $N. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你在这儿干什么？$B$B别挡我的路。我不会让你这种人干扰血色先锋军的！' WHERE entry=13674; /* Text0_0: What are YOU doing here?$B$BJust make sure that you stay out of my way. I didn\'t leave the Scarlet Onslaught to be distracted by the likes of you! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你似乎能帮我赚点钱。来痛苦斗兽场转转怎么样，伙计？' WHERE entry=13679; /* Text0_0: You look like you could make us some money. How about a spin inside the Amphitheater of Anguish, pal? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='现在你是斗兽场的勇士啦！你觉得自己能保住这个头衔吗？' WHERE entry=13680; /* Text0_0: You\'re the champion now, buddy! Do you think you have what it takes to defend your title? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='本单元正在忙碌。请稍后查询。' WHERE entry=13681; /* Text0_0: This unit is busy. Please inquire later. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='在监工看见我们之前，快回去工作吧。' WHERE entry=13682; /* Text0_0: Go back to work before the overseer sees us. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='这件霍迪尔号角的仿制品是为了纪念安格里姆国王以及所有在落雷谷之战中牺牲的巨人而造的。' WHERE entry=13685; /* Text0_0: This likeness of the Horn of Hodir stands in memorial of King Arngrim and all others lost in the battle of Thunderfall. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我能帮你做什么吗？' WHERE entry=13690; /* Text0_0: What can I do for you? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='弗约恩的铁砧被摆放在丹尼芬雷最显然的位置，象征着他们击败弗约恩以及冰霜巨人大军的战绩。$b$b你忍不住笑了起来，你的举动竟然对世界产生了如此深远的影响。' WHERE entry=13697; /* Text0_0: Fjorn\'s Anvil now stands prominently in Dun Niffelem as a symbol of their victory over Fjorn and his armies.$b$bYou can\'t help but smile, knowing that your actions have had such a lasting impact on the world. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='奥努森来这里挑战维库人，以此提升自己的地位。$B$B然后，奥努森要在瓦哈拉斯战斗并赢得胜利，奥努森要为巫妖王效力！' WHERE entry=13701; /* Text0_0: Onu\'zun here to challenge the vrykul and work himself up in the ranks.$B$BThen when Onu\'zun fight in Valhalas and win, Onu\'zun gonna be workin\' for the Lich King! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我能帮你做什么吗？',Text0_1_loc4='我能帮你做什么吗？' WHERE entry=13702; /* Text0_0: How may I help you? */ /* Text0_1: How may I help you? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你好，$n。这里是守护者米米尔的工作室。' WHERE entry=13703; /* Text0_0: Greetings, $N. This is the workshop of Keeper Mimir. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我曾经拥有一切。名望、财富、一整套最棒的角斗士套装……我却亲手毁了这一切。$B$B他们发现我有舞弊行为……进行胜负交易……一切全完蛋了。$B$B如今我一无所有，只剩下这身破烂的衣衫，还有一只坏掉的肝脏。' WHERE entry=13707; /* Text0_0: I had it all, once. Fame, fortune, a full set of the very best gladiator\'s gear... and then I threw it all away.$B$BOnce the Cartel caught me rigging fights... trading wins... it was all over.$B$BNow I\'ve got nothing but these rags and a bad liver. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你是谁？$B$B走开……港口的建设工作非常繁重，我已经累得筋疲力尽了。现在我要喝上两口矮人啤酒，痛痛快快地哭一场再美美地打个盹儿。' WHERE entry=13709; /* Text0_0: Who are you?$B$BGo away... I\'m exhausted from working so hard on the Harbor Road. It\'s time to drink some dwarven ale, have a good cry, and take a nap. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='这简直是里程碑式的胜利！皇家炼金师协会花费了数年时间来破解巫妖王诅咒的秘密，现在总算取得了突破！$B$B虽然实验的成功堪称历史的转折点，但是还有很多东西有待研究。我要做更多的实验……挑选更多的样本……$B$B至少我不用担心浮空城。联盟会解决那个玩意儿的。这样我就有足够的时间来研究，揭示其中的奥妙。' WHERE entry=13731; /* Text0_0: What a landmark discovery! The Royal Apothecary Society has spent years working to break the secrets of the Lich King\'s plague, and I\'ve finally done it!$B$BDespite this turning point in history, there is still so much to discover. I have more experiments to conduct... test subjects to acquire...$B$BAt least I don\'t have to worry about Scourge necropoli. The Alliance is dealing with that problem. This leaves me plenty of time to delve into the secrets of the plague and uncover what I can. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='有霜脉矮人的地方就有雄鹰。在我降生之前，它们就是氏族的盟友了……如今我已不再年轻了。' WHERE entry=13733; /* Text0_0: Where there are frostborn, there are eagles. They\'ve been our allies for longer than I\'ve walked the land... and I\'m not exactly young anymore, $G laddy:lass;. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我能帮你做什么吗？' WHERE entry=13734; /* Text0_0: What can I do for you? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='朋友，你最近还好吗？' WHERE entry=13735; /* Text0_0: How you be doin\' mon? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='有什麽能帮你的吗?' WHERE entry=13737; /* Text0_0: How may I serve you? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你想要什麽?' WHERE entry=13738; /* Text0_0: What do you want? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='欢迎你，土灵的朋友和盟友。' WHERE entry=13740; /* Text0_0: You are welcome here, as a friend and ally of the earthen. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='$r，我允许你进入我们的城堡。$b$b但是，别让我们蒙羞！' WHERE entry=13747; /* Text0_0: You are permitted to visit our stronghold, little $r.$b$bDo not bring us dishonor! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我对你的信任还不够，抱歉不能将如此重要的信息透露给你。$b$b你必须尊重我们接受的考验以及我们背负的重担……$b$b如果你能为丹尼芬雷带来荣耀的话，我或许会考虑与你分享我们的知识。' WHERE entry=13748; /* Text0_0: I do not trust you enough to speak of such things.$b$bYou must respect the trials our people have endured, the burdens we have borne...$b$bPerhaps, if you were to bring great honor to Dun Niffelem, I would be inclined to share with you the knowledge of our people. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='很好，$c。$b$b虽然你还需要付出更多努力，才能缓解我们与托里姆的关系，但是我决定将这个秘密告诉你。$b$b等你做好了解真相的准备后，再来与我谈话吧。' WHERE entry=13749; /* Text0_0: Very well, little $c.$b$bWhile there is much left for you to do to mend our relations with Thorim, I am compelled to share with you this one secret.$b$bSpeak to me again when you are ready to be shown that which you seek. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你好，$r。我能帮你什么忙吗？',Text0_1_loc4='你好，$r。我能帮你什么忙吗？' WHERE entry=13759; /* Text0_0: Hello, $r. How can I help you today? */ /* Text0_1: Hello, $r. How can I help you today? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='对不起，朋友。只有部落的正式军官才有权购买载具。',Text0_1_loc4='对不起，朋友。只有部落的正式军官才有权购买载具。' WHERE entry=13761; /* Text0_0: Sorry, friend. Only certified officers of the Horde can authorize the purchase of a vehicle. */ /* Text0_1: Sorry, friend. Only certified officers of the Horde can authorize the purchase of a vehicle. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='很高兴再次见到你！$B$B雷心国王告诉我，说他会离开一段日子……他回忆起一些可怕的往事，决定算清这笔旧账。他坚持不让我们随行，按照惯例，我们也尊重他的决定。$B$B同时，我负责接管整个氏族。当然，你仍然是我们的贵客。' WHERE entry=13764; /* Text0_0: Good to see ya again!$B$BKing Stormheart has informed me that he will be taking his leave for a time... a grim memory brought back to him has left him with a score to settle it seems. He was very insistent that we not join him, so we have respected his wishes as we always do.$B$BI have taken responsibility for our clan in the meantime. You are still welcome with us, of course. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你不是牦牛人。你为什么闯入我族战士的埋骨圣地？' WHERE entry=13776; /* Text0_0: You are no taunka. Why have you come to the sacred burial grounds of our warriors? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='让我独自反省吧，$r。' WHERE entry=13782; /* Text0_0: Leave me to my shame, $r. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='对不起，朋友。我们手头的零件好象都用完了。',Text0_1_loc4='对不起，朋友。我们手头的零件好象都用完了。' WHERE entry=13786; /* Text0_0: Sorry, friend. I\'m afraid we\'ve used all of the parts we can spare at the moment. */ /* Text0_1: Sorry, friend. I\'m afraid we\'ve used all of the parts we can spare at the moment. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='喂，喂！' WHERE entry=13790; /* Text0_0: Hello, hello! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='很高兴见到你，$c。' WHERE entry=13793; /* Text0_0: Pleased to meet you, $c. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='这片山脉的历史非常悠久……你要随时停下脚步来倾听，$c。' WHERE entry=13794; /* Text0_0: The mountains are rich with history... don\'t forget to stop and take it all in, $c. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你好，$n！今天你想要点什么？',Text0_1_loc4='你好，$n！今天你想要点什么？' WHERE entry=13798; /* Text0_0: Hello, $n! How can I help you today? */ /* Text0_1: Hello, $n! How can I help you today? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='说吧，$c。' WHERE entry=13799; /* Text0_0: Speak, $c. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='长久以来，我一直不明白自己的命运。我的使命从未像现在这样清晰过。$B$B我必须亲手解决洛肯。' WHERE entry=13800; /* Text0_0: I\'ve hidden from my destiny long enough.  What I must do has never been clearer.$B$BLoken must be destroyed by my hand. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='刚才那一瞬间，我把你当成了我亲爱的西芙……那一缕头发……不！那不可能……西芙已经死了……$B$B我……我的兄弟……杀了她！' WHERE entry=13801; /* Text0_0: For a moment I thought you were my beloved Sif... that strand of hair... but no!  It can\'t be... Sif is dead....$B$BMy... my brother.... killed her! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='奥杜尔……我曾经发誓要守护奥杜尔。$B$B发誓要守护造物者圣台。$B$B发誓要守护与冰霜巨人之间的盟誓。$B$B可是我都没有做到！我被我的兄弟欺骗了。他诱使我将矛头指向我的朋友。他骗我说是我亲密的朋友，冰霜巨人之王安格里姆害死了西芙。$B$B当我意识到自己做了什么时……我……陷入了绝望。' WHERE entry=13802; /* Text0_0: Ulduar... I was sworn to protect Ulduar.$B$BSworn to protect the Terrace of the Makers.$B$BSworn to protect the pacts between the races of frost.$B$BBut I failed!  I let my brother trick me.  I let him turn me against my allies.  He tricked me into blaming Sif\'s death on a dear friend, Arngrim, the king of the frost giants.$B$BAfter I realized what I\'d done... I... gave in to despair. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你是谁，小家伙！竟然对强大的托里姆说这些话……$B$B我应该……撕碎你！$B$B但是你将我从昏迷中唤醒了。你的来到是一个预兆！$B$B我把你错当成西芙，这并不是巧合。她会怎么看我呢？我必须准备战斗了。$B$B我一定要为她报仇，把泰坦的圣地从我那个疯狂的兄弟手中解放出来！' WHERE entry=13803; /* Text0_0: Who are you, little one?  To come speak these words to the mighty Thorim...$B$BI should... crush you!$B$BYet, you\'ve delivered me from my stupor.  Your presence here is a sign!$B$BIt was no accident that I mistook you for Sif.  What would she think of me?  I must prepare for battle.$B$BI must avenge her death and liberate the titans\' sacred grounds from my brother\'s madness! */
