UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='克拉苏斯平台位于达拉然的最东端。$B$B本城的飞行管理员和寒冷天气飞行训练师都在那里。',Text0_1_loc4='克拉苏斯平台位于达拉然的最东端。$B$B本城的飞行管理员和寒冷天气飞行训练师都在那里。' WHERE entry=14009; /* Text0_0: Krasus\' Landing is in easternmost Dalaran.$B$BThe city\'s flight master is there, as well as the cold weather flying trainer. */ /* Text0_1: Krasus\' Landing is in easternmost Dalaran.$B$BThe city\'s flight master is there, as well as the cold weather flying trainer. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='达拉然没有拍卖行。你必须通过传送门返回各大主城才能使用拍卖行。$B$B传送门位于达拉然的联盟和部落区：银色领地和夺日者圣殿。',Text0_1_loc4='达拉然没有拍卖行。你必须通过传送门返回各大主城才能使用拍卖行。$B$B传送门位于达拉然的联盟和部落区：银色领地和夺日者圣殿。' WHERE entry=14010; /* Text0_0: Dalaran has no auction house of its own. You must take a portal back to one of your capitals.$B$BThey can be found in Dalaran\'s Alliance and Horde quarters: the Silver Enclave and the Sunreaver\'s Sancturary. */ /* Text0_1: Dalaran has no auction house of its own. You must take a portal back to one of your capitals.$B$BThey can be found in Dalaran\'s Alliance and Horde quarters: the Silver Enclave and the Sunreaver\'s Sancturary. */
