UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='阿尔萨斯的弱点就是骄傲。随着他的力量日益强大，这个弱点也越来越明显。我相信，黑锋骑士团一定能找到机会击败这位前王子。' WHERE entry=14038; /* Text0_0: Arthas\'s weakness is his pride. That weakness only grows as his power does. The Ebon Blade will have its chance to strike at the once-prince - of that I have no doubt. */
