UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text2_0_loc4='有点忙。',Text2_1_loc4='有点忙。' WHERE entry=14047; /* Text2_0: On duty. GO. AWAY. */ /* Text2_1: On duty. GO. AWAY. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你准备好参与夺回幽暗城一战了吗，$n？' WHERE entry=14050; /* Text0_0: Are you ready to begin the assault and win back the Undercity for the Horde, $N? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='元素之灵与我们同在，$n。在它们的帮助下，我们可以竭尽全力阻止瓦里玛萨斯和普特雷斯的阴谋得逞！LOK\'TAR OGAR！' WHERE entry=14051; /* Text0_0: The elements are with us in force, $N. With their help, we will do all that is in our power to stop Varimathras and Putress! LOK\'TAR OGAR! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='形势严峻，没有捷径可走。如果你的战斗力够强，请掩护我的小队，直到他们做好爬上伊米海姆的准备。他们需要一切可利用的帮助。' WHERE entry=14055; /* Text0_0: We don\'t have any easy path before us. If you\'ve got a strong arm on you, stick around until one of my squads is ready to ascend to Ymirheim. They could use all the help they can get. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='自信号上虫灾泛滥，我们没法开往诺森德了。',Text1_0_loc4='我们已经做好了扬帆诺森德的准备，突然发现船上出现了大批害虫。' WHERE entry=14056; /* Text0_0: The Assurance has somehow become inundated with bugs and we are unable to set sail to Northrend. */ /* Text1_0: We were all set to sail into Northrend, but we\'ve noticed a severe number of pests aboard our ship. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text2_0_loc4='在开往诺森德之前，我们必须解决自信号上的虫害问题。' WHERE entry=14056; /* Text2_0: Before we can set sail to Northrend, we\'ve got to eliminate our pest problem aboard the Assurance. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='哎呀，你长得真难看！不过这并不表示你不会战斗。$B$B我麾下的一支小队很快就要出发啦——加入他们的行列，一起爬上伊米海姆吧！' WHERE entry=14061; /* Text0_0: Well you\'re an ugly one! Don\'t mean you don\'t know how to fight though.$B$BOne of my squads should be geared and ready to march soon - get your sorry butt in line and make the climb with them! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='竞技场排名赛将在$6318d后再次拉开帷幕。$B$B未来的竞技场冠军正在忙于练习作战技巧以及搜寻最好的装备。你准备好了吗？',Text0_1_loc4='竞技场排名赛将在$6318d后再次拉开帷幕。$B$B未来的竞技场冠军正在忙于练习作战技巧以及搜寻最好的装备。你准备好了吗？' WHERE entry=14062; /* Text0_0: Ranked arena matches start again in $6318d.$B$BWould-be champions are already busy honing their skills and acquiring the best gear they can. Are you going to be ready? */ /* Text0_1: Ranked arena matches start again in $6318d.$B$BWould-be champions are already busy honing their skills and acquiring the best gear they can. Are you going to be ready? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='要我为你指引道路吗，年轻人？',Text0_1_loc4='要我为你指引道路吗，年轻人？' WHERE entry=14063; /* Text0_0: How I can guide your path, young one? */ /* Text0_1: How I can guide your path, young one? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我们在这里的行动关系到许多人的性命。你想说什么就快说吧，$c。',Text1_0_loc4='你带来了最新的战况情报吗，$r？' WHERE entry=14064; /* Text0_0: Lives depend on the actions we take here.  Be quick with what you have to say, $c. */ /* Text1_0: Do you bring news of battle, $r? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text2_0_loc4='最好的战术是速战速决。谈话也是一样。你想说什么，$r？' WHERE entry=14064; /* Text2_0: The best war is a swift war.  The same can be said of conversation.  What say you $r? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='有很多声音在对我讲话。',Text1_0_loc4='我必须服从。' WHERE entry=14068; /* Text0_0: The voices are talking to me. */ /* Text1_0: I must obey. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text2_0_loc4='你最好赶紧离开，不然你也会被它影响！',Text3_0_loc4='它就在我们身边。就在我的脑海里！' WHERE entry=14068; /* Text2_0: You have to get out of here before it gets to you, too! */ /* Text3_0: It\'s all around us. It\'s in my head! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text4_0_loc4='萨隆邪铁……里面藏有什么东西！',Text5_0_loc4='邪铁里藏有东西！就在岩石和泥土里！' WHERE entry=14068; /* Text4_0: The saronite... there\'s something in it! */ /* Text5_0: There\'s something here.  It\'s in the rocks and the earth! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text6_0_loc4='我要离开这里！你能放我出去吗？',Text7_0_loc4='你听见了吗？它正在你的脑海中低语。' WHERE entry=14068; /* Text6_0: I have to get out of here! Can you get me free? */ /* Text7_0: Can you hear it speaking in your mind? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='准备工作尚未完成。我们暂时还不会离开。' WHERE entry=14069; /* Text0_0: We\'re still making preparations. We won\'t be ready to go for a while. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我们就快准备好啦。再给我们一点时间，很快就能出发了。' WHERE entry=14070; /* Text0_0: We\'re almost ready to depart. Just give us a little bit longer to finish our preparations. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='士兵们都准备好了。我们要让那些维库人流血！' WHERE entry=14071; /* Text0_0: My men are ready. Let\'s draw some Vrykul blood! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我在旅途中学会了精魂披风的图样。$B$B图样可交易，是史诗级的施法者披风，装备后可获得耐力、法术强度、智力以及法力回复速度的加成。我一直在寻找有资格学习这张图样的人。$B$B打通诺森德所有的普通难度地下城，并获得“诺森德地下城大师”成就的人才有资格学习精魂披风的图纸。' WHERE entry=14072; /* Text0_0: In my travels I have learned the recipe for the Wispcloak.$B$BThis cloak is a tradeable Epic spellcasting cloak that grants Stamina, Spellpower, Intellect and Mana Recovery.   I am looking for someone worthy to teach this recipe to.$B$BSomeone who had completed all the normal dungeons of Northrend and had the "Northrend Dungeonmaster" achievement would be worthy of learning the recipe for the Wispcloak. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我曾去过许多黑暗的地方，学会了死寒披风的图样。$B$B图样可交易，是史诗级的施法者披风，装备后可获得法术强度、急速以及爆击的加成。我一直在寻找有资格学习这张图样的人。$B$B完成诺森德的大部分任务，并获得“诺森德的博学者”成就的人才有资格学习死寒披风的图纸。' WHERE entry=14074; /* Text0_0: I have ventured to dark places and learned the tailoring recipe for the Deathchill Cloak.$B$BThis cloak is a tradeable Epic cloak for spellcasters that grants Spellpower, Haste and Critical Strike.   I am looking for someone worthy to teach this recipe to.$B$BSomeone who had completed most of the quests across Northrend and had the "Loremaster of Northrend" achievement would be worthy of learning the recipe for the Deathchill Cloak. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你是一位颇为出色的裁缝，因此我可以教你一些特别的图样，比如精魂披风和死寒披风。' WHERE entry=14076; /* Text0_0: Since you are a tailor of some skill, I can tell you that I know some special recipes.   I know recipes for both the Wispcloak and the Deathchill Cloak. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你！快过来！尽情吃喝一顿吧，为下一次的战斗做好准备。$B$B不许在这里打架！不然我就送你去喂狼。',Text0_1_loc4='你！快过来！尽情吃喝一顿吧，为下一次的战斗做好准备。$B$B不许在这里打架！不然我就送你去喂狼。' WHERE entry=14077; /* Text0_0: You! COME! Drink, feast, rest for the next battle.$B$BBut do not fight! Or I will feed you to my wolves. */ /* Text0_1: You! COME! Drink, feast, rest for the next battle.$B$BBut do not fight! Or I will feed you to my wolves. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='欢迎来到奇妙玩具店！$B$B请随意看看。我们出售许多奇妙的玩具，老少咸宜！' WHERE entry=14082; /* Text0_0: Welcome to the Wonderworks!$B$BPlease take your time and browse the shop. We have wonderful toys for people young and old! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你好，朋友。我能为你做什么吗？' WHERE entry=14087; /* Text0_0: Greetings, friend.  Something I can do for ya? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='嘿，等一等。你没有属于自己的飞行坐骑诶。$B$B如果出行不便的话，恐怕你没有办法帮助其他的地精了。他们付钱给我，让我将旧坐骑借给你这样的人使用——免费使用哦。$B$B怎么样？' WHERE entry=14088; /* Text0_0: Hey there, hold on just one second.  I see you\'re not riding a flying mount of your own.$B$BYou probably won\'t be of much use to the other goblins here if you can\'t get around.  They\'ve paid me to loan my used mounts to people such as yourself -- at no cost to you.$B$BInterested? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我已经找到了诺甘农钥石的线索，有了它就能进入奥杜尔的档案室；但是泰坦将钥石分成了两块并分别藏了起来。$B$B钥石的外壳藏在北部海滩的创世者图书馆里，就在奥杜尔以南。首先，你要从图书馆守护者那里获得访问磁盘的碎片。' WHERE entry=14089; /* Text0_0: I\'ve got a lead on Norgannon\'s keystone, which guards access to Ulduar\'s archives, but the Titans divided it into two pieces and secreted them away.$B$BOne of the pieces, the keystone\'s shell, is held within the Inventor\'s Library on the northern coast, south of Ulduar itself. The first thing you\'ll need to do is retrieve the fragments of an access disk from the library\'s guardians. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='那些嘲笑我的战袍的人都是蠢货。$B$B这件衣服所用的旧钢都来自一个远古的学习之地！' WHERE entry=14091; /* Text0_0: Only a fool would mock the appearance of my battle-garb.$B$BThis raiment of well-worn steel is from an ancient place of learning! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='达拉然北部的再来一杯应该能满足你的需求。',Text0_1_loc4='达拉然北部的再来一杯应该能满足你的需求。' WHERE entry=14095; /* Text0_0: You\'ll find what you are looking for at One More Glass in northern Dalaran. */ /* Text0_1: You\'ll find what you are looking for at One More Glass in northern Dalaran. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='达拉然南部的好战的秘法师应该能满足你的需求。',Text0_1_loc4='达拉然南部的好战的秘法师应该能满足你的需求。' WHERE entry=14096; /* Text0_0: The Militant Mystic in southern Dalaran should have what you desire. */ /* Text0_1: The Militant Mystic in southern Dalaran should have what you desire. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='达拉然东部的猎人用品店出售枪支、弓弩、弹药等商品。',Text0_1_loc4='达拉然东部的猎人用品店出售枪支、弓弩、弹药等商品。' WHERE entry=14097; /* Text0_0: The Hunter\'s Reach in eastern Dalaran sells guns, bows, ammunition and the like. */ /* Text0_1: The Hunter\'s Reach in eastern Dalaran sells guns, bows, ammunition and the like. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='达拉然东南部的神兵利器出售各类近战武器。',Text0_1_loc4='达拉然东南部的神兵利器出售各类近战武器。' WHERE entry=14098; /* Text0_0: The Arsenal Absolute in southeast Dalaran carries all manner of melee weapons. */ /* Text0_1: The Arsenal Absolute in southeast Dalaran carries all manner of melee weapons. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='达拉然西部的耶比托·乔巴斯的奇妙玩具店会出售这类物品。',Text0_1_loc4='达拉然西部的耶比托·乔巴斯的奇妙玩具店会出售这类物品。' WHERE entry=14100; /* Text0_0: Jepetto Joybuzz\'s Wonderworks in western Dalaran carries such items. */ /* Text0_1: Jepetto Joybuzz\'s Wonderworks in western Dalaran carries such items. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='达拉然东南部的荣耀杂货店中，“红发”杰克·芬德出售各种杂货。$B$B如果你想购买特殊物品，就去魔法商业区吧。那里的店铺都设有供给商贩。',Text0_1_loc4='达拉然东南部的荣耀杂货店中，“红发”杰克·芬德出售各种杂货。$B$B如果你想购买特殊物品，就去魔法商业区吧。那里的店铺都设有供给商贩。' WHERE entry=14101; /* Text0_0: Red at Glorious Goods in southeast Dalaran can provide most general trade supplies.$B$BIf you need something more specialized, try the Magus Commerce Exchange. Each trade shop there has its own supply vendor. */ /* Text0_1: Red at Glorious Goods in southeast Dalaran can provide most general trade supplies.$B$BIf you need something more specialized, try the Magus Commerce Exchange. Each trade shop there has its own supply vendor. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='艾美的货车通常停在达拉然北部，就在达拉然银行附近。',Text0_1_loc4='艾美的货车通常停在达拉然北部，就在达拉然银行附近。' WHERE entry=14102; /* Text0_0: Aimee\'s cart can usually be found in northern Dalaran, near the Bank of Dalaran. */ /* Text0_1: Aimee\'s cart can usually be found in northern Dalaran, near the Bank of Dalaran. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='魔法动物店位于达拉然东北部。那里出售宠物用品和珍稀坐骑，并提供兽栏服务。',Text0_1_loc4='魔法动物店位于达拉然东北部。那里出售宠物用品和珍稀坐骑，并提供兽栏服务。' WHERE entry=14103; /* Text0_0: The Magical Menagerie is located in northeast Dalaran. Pet supplies, exotic mounts, and stables are all available there. */ /* Text0_1: The Magical Menagerie is located in northeast Dalaran. Pet supplies, exotic mounts, and stables are all available there. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='达拉然西部的巫术姐妹出售各种魔法材料。$B$B不过你要小心莫尔海德的那只黑猫……',Text0_1_loc4='达拉然西部的巫术姐妹出售各种魔法材料。$B$B不过你要小心莫尔海德的那只黑猫……' WHERE entry=14104; /* Text0_0: You\'ll find reagants and more at the Sisters Sorcerous in western Dalaran.$B$BJust mind the Mooreheads\' black cat... */ /* Text0_1: You\'ll find reagants and more at the Sisters Sorcerous in western Dalaran.$B$BJust mind the Mooreheads\' black cat... */
