UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='达拉然南部的摩尔珍品店有好几位商贩，他们出售各类饰品、圣物、家传宝物和副手武器。',Text0_1_loc4='达拉然南部的摩尔珍品店有好几位商贩，他们出售各类饰品、圣物、家传宝物和副手武器。' WHERE entry=14110; /* Text0_0: The various merchants of Curiosities & Moore in southern Dalaran sell trinkets, relics, heirlooms, and off-hand items of all sorts. */ /* Text0_1: The various merchants of Curiosities & Moore in southern Dalaran sell trinkets, relics, heirlooms, and off-hand items of all sorts. */
