UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='天哪，我从来没有想过能亲眼目睹泰坦之城奥杜尔。当布莱恩恳求我资助这支探险队时，我怎么能忍心拒绝呢？！' WHERE entry=14362; /* Text0_0: My, my, I never thought I would have the chance to see Ulduar myself. Why, when Brann asked me to help fund this expedition, how could I refuse?! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我还以为我们没法逃出那片雾蒙蒙的丛林呢！现在，我是这支探险队的首席工程师啦。' WHERE entry=14363; /* Text0_0: I never thought we\'d escape from that steamy jungle! Now I\'m the lead engineer of this expedition. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='这些宝贝儿看上去跟废铁似的，但是它们可以高速前进，猛烈地撞击敌人。器械前端的撞锤加载了可以施放电能震击的高压电容器。$B$B就连炮塔也升级成了防空火箭，使它比那些破烂攻城车更具优势。',Text0_1_loc4='这些宝贝儿看上去跟废铁似的，但是它们可以高速前进，猛烈地撞击敌人。器械前端的撞锤加载了可以施放电能震击的高压电容器。$B$B就连炮塔也升级成了防空火箭，使它比那些破烂攻城车更具优势。' WHERE entry=14364; /* Text0_0: These babies may look like scrap, but they can rush ahead, knocking enemies aside. The front ram has been overloaded with a electroscopic hyper capacitor, letting it discharge electrical blasts. $B$BEven the turret has been upgraded with anti-air rockets, providing it with a definitive edge over those blasted demolishers. */ /* Text0_1: These babies may look like scrap, but they can rush ahead, knocking enemies aside. The front ram has been overloaded with a electroscopic hyper capacitor, letting it discharge electrical blasts. $B$BEven the turret has been upgraded with anti-air rockets, providing it with a definitive edge over those blasted demolishers. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='这里汇集了外域最丰富的藏书。即便是银月城的大图书馆也要相形见绌了。$B$B请……尽情享受阅读的乐趣吧。所有的书籍都已分门别类，整理得井井有条。' WHERE entry=14365; /* Text0_0: Here I have amassed what may well be the greatest depository of lore in all of Outland. Even the grand libraries of Silvermoon City pale in comparison.$B$BPlease... look, read, browse to your heart\'s content. You\'ll find everything organized and clearly labeled. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='能找到足够的零件让这些宝贝儿重新运转起来，还真是幸运！$B我能帮你什么忙吗？' WHERE entry=14367; /* Text0_0: We were in luck to find enough parts to get these babies working again!$BHow can I help you? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='老大，我能为你做什么吗？' WHERE entry=14372; /* Text0_0: Something I can do for you, Boss? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你好。' WHERE entry=14375; /* Text0_0: Greetings. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='银色盟约欢迎你参加锦标赛。银色北伐军委托我们登记并训练那些对比赛感兴趣的选手。' WHERE entry=14379; /* Text0_0: The Silver Covenant welcomes you to the tournament. The Argent Crusade has asked us to register and train those interested in competing. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='控制台显得非常陈旧，却没有一丝破损或是荒废的迹象。上面刻有一道插槽，似乎可以放入大型的圆盘。' WHERE entry=14383; /* Text0_0: The console appears ancient though there is no sign of dilapidation or decay.  A single slot appears to fit large circular discs. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你做好和勇士战斗的准备了吗？',Text0_1_loc4='你做好和勇士战斗的准备了吗？',Text1_0_loc4='别以为你可以轻而易举地战胜一位勇士。你确定自己已经准备好了吗？',Text1_1_loc4='别以为你可以轻而易举地战胜一位勇士。你确定自己已经准备好了吗？' WHERE entry=14384; /* Text0_0: Are you sure you are ready to fight a valiant? */ /* Text0_1: Are you sure you are ready to fight a valiant? */ /* Text1_0: It would be unwise to assume that fighting a valiant would be a simple task.  Are you sure you are ready? */ /* Text1_1: It would be unwise to assume that fighting a valiant would be a simple task.  Are you sure you are ready? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text2_0_loc4='你做好与我交战的准备了吗？',Text2_1_loc4='你做好与我交战的准备了吗？' WHERE entry=14384; /* Text2_0: Are you sure you are ready to fight me? */ /* Text2_1: Are you sure you are ready to fight me? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我们来到这里，为荣耀而战，为名誉而战，为获得与银色北伐军的兄弟们并肩作战的资格而战。' WHERE entry=14395; /* Text0_0: We have come to compete for honor, renown, and the right to fight the Scourge alongside the brothers of the Argent Crusade. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='诺莫瑞根的精英来参加锦标赛啦。祝我们好运！' WHERE entry=14398; /* Text0_0: Gnomeregan\'s finest have come to compete in the tournament. Wish us luck! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='达纳苏斯的精灵们希望在锦标赛中一展身手。' WHERE entry=14399; /* Text0_0: We of Darnassus look forward to competing in the tournament. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='锦标赛开始后，所有人都将见证被遗忘者的胜利。' WHERE entry=14402; /* Text0_0: When the tournament starts, all will see the Forsaken emerge triumphant. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='竞争会非常激烈，但是奥格瑞玛的勇士是所向披靡的。' WHERE entry=14403; /* Text0_0: The competition will be fierce, but Orgrimmar\'s champions will decimate all who stand in our way. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我们不仅为荣耀而战，还要为我们的先祖和人民赢得光荣。' WHERE entry=14404; /* Text0_0: We compete not only for glory, but to bring honor to our ancestors and to our people. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='暗矛氏族已经做好了竞争的准备。' WHERE entry=14405; /* Text0_0: The Darkspears stand ready to face the competition and the enemy. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我代表夺日者欢迎你参加锦标赛。银色北伐军委托我们登记并训练那些对比赛感兴趣的选手。' WHERE entry=14406; /* Text0_0: On behalf of the Sunreavers, I welcome you to the tournament. The Argent Crusade has asked us to register and train those interested in competing. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你做好和银色北伐军勇士作战的准备了吗？',Text0_1_loc4='你做好和银色北伐军勇士作战的准备了吗？' WHERE entry=14407; /* Text0_0: Are you prepared to fight a valiant of the Argent Crusade? */ /* Text0_1: Are you prepared to fight a valiant of the Argent Crusade? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='当你准备好参加勇士的晋级测试后，我会召来一位银色北伐军的成员。',Text0_1_loc4='当你准备好参加勇士的晋级测试后，我会召来一位银色北伐军的成员。' WHERE entry=14408; /* Text0_0: When you are ready to test for the rank of valiant, I will call forth a member of the Argent Crusade. */ /* Text0_1: When you are ready to test for the rank of valiant, I will call forth a member of the Argent Crusade. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='这座竞技场专供冠军们互相切磋之用。我负责召唤骑兵来参加战斗练习。',Text0_1_loc4='这座竞技场专供冠军们互相切磋之用。我负责召唤骑兵来参加战斗练习。' WHERE entry=14409; /* Text0_0: This is the ring where the champions practice fighting each other. It\'s my job to summon the knights to their practice battles. */ /* Text0_1: This is the ring where the champions practice fighting each other. It\'s my job to summon the knights to their practice battles. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='祝你好运。等广场清理干净后，我就到里面去跟你会合。' WHERE entry=14415; /* Text0_0: Good luck to you in there. I\'ll try to find you farther inside once the concourse is clear. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='高墙内的秘密远远超越了我们的想象。' WHERE entry=14420; /* Text0_0: There are secrets contained within these halls that are beyond our wildest dreams. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你做好与冠军作战的准备了吗？',Text0_1_loc4='你做好与冠军作战的准备了吗？',Text1_0_loc4='别以为你可以轻而易举地战胜一位冠军。你确定自己已经准备好了吗？',Text1_1_loc4='别以为你可以轻而易举地战胜一位冠军。你确定自己已经准备好了吗？' WHERE entry=14421; /* Text0_0: Are you sure you are ready to fight a champion? */ /* Text0_1: Are you sure you are ready to fight a champion? */ /* Text1_0: It would be unwise to assume that fighting a champion would be a simple task.  Are you sure you are ready? */ /* Text1_1: It would be unwise to assume that fighting a champion would be a simple task.  Are you sure you are ready? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text2_0_loc4='你做好与我交战的准备了吗？',Text2_1_loc4='你做好与我交战的准备了吗？' WHERE entry=14421; /* Text2_0: Are you sure you are ready to fight me? */ /* Text2_1: Are you sure you are ready to fight me? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='布拉斯波兄弟的建筑工程是速度最快，造价最低、质量最上乘的！' WHERE entry=14426; /* Text0_0: No one builds it faster, cheaper, and better than the Blastbolt brothers! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='能协助布莱恩探索泰坦古城奥杜尔的秘密真是莫大的荣幸。' WHERE entry=14428; /* Text0_0: It\'s a real honor to be able to aid Brann in exploring ancient Ulduar. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我所知道的关于探险的知识，都是布莱恩教给我的。',Text0_1_loc4='我所知道的关于探险的知识，都是布莱恩教给我的。' WHERE entry=14429; /* Text0_0: Brann taught me everything I know about exploring. */ /* Text0_1: Brann taught me everything I know about exploring. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='$c，很高兴见到你。$B$B我负责向候选者传授骑乘近身战的诀窍。' WHERE entry=14431; /* Text0_0: Well met, $c.$B$BI train Aspirants in the art of mounted close combat. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='这是什么，小凡人……$b$b嗯……是$r？我能为你做些什么？',Text1_0_loc4='怎麽，$C?这是什麽?' WHERE entry=14432; /* Text0_0: What is it, puny mort-$b$bErr... yes, $r? What can I do for you? */ /* Text1_0: Yes, $C? What is it? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='嗨，你好！$B$B你是来学习冲锋技巧的吗，$c？' WHERE entry=14436; /* Text0_0: Hey there, how are ye?$B$BCome ta learn the art o\' the Charge, $c? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='好吧！骑乘冲锋可不仅仅是让你的坐骑高速冲刺，体验那种心飙到嗓子眼的快感……当然这的确是最有趣的部分，嘿嘿！但是冲锋目标可以帮助你掌握更多诀窍。$B$B冲锋的关键在于距离与时机。不能靠得太近，否则无法全力提速。也不能离得太远，否则坐骑就会进入疲惫状态！至于冲锋的时机……$B$B在冲锋之前，你最好确认一下冲锋目标身上是否有防御效果。如果有，你应该先使用碎盾然后再冲锋！$B$B实战中遵循着同样的原则：在冲锋前要尽可能地削弱对手的防御效果！' WHERE entry=14437; /* Text0_0: Well then! A mounted Charge is about more than just kickin\' yer mount ta full speed an\' hollerin\' yer lungs out... though that IS the fun part, heh! But the Charge Target will teach ye the finer points.$B$BA good Charge is all about distance and timing. Ye can\'t be TOO close, or ye won\'t get enough speed. But ye can\'t be too far away either or yer mount will tire! As for timin\'...$B$BYe\'ll want ta make sure the Charge Target doesn\'t have a layer o\' Defend up before ye rush in. If it does, use yer Shield Breaker ta make it vulnerable, and THEN Charge in!$B$BSame goes for the real thing: Try ta drop yer opponent defenses before ye Charge! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='哎呀。又一位$c，你是来学习碎盾的技巧的吗……？' WHERE entry=14438; /* Text0_0: Well. Another $c, come to learn the ways of the Shield-Breaker...? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='远程碎盾攻击上手容易精通难。碎盾攻击所能造成的伤害不高，但是配合刺击和冲锋使用就能发挥出完美的效果，令你在骑乘作战中所向披靡。$B$B选定一个远程目标，估算一下碎盾攻击的射程……你需要多远的距离以及你能将长枪掷多远。$B$B接下来，就开始投掷长枪吧，直到你破坏目标身上的所有防御效果。$B$B骑乘实战中遵循着同样的原则：彻底粉碎对手的防御……然后狠狠地揍他们！' WHERE entry=14439; /* Text0_0: The ranged Shield-Breaker attack is simple to learn, but difficult to master. Alone it may seem weak, but in conjunction with Thrusts and Charges the Shield-Breaker makes a successful jouster.$B$BFind a Ranged Target. Take a moment to understand the Shield-Breaker\'s range... how much space you need, and how far you can hurl the lance.$B$BAfter that? Well. Start throwing, and do not stop until you\'ve broken every last layer of Defend and pierced the vulnerable target.$B$BThis tactic will serve you well in actual mounted combat: Break down your opponents\' defenses... and then crush them! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='朋友，你来得正是时候。很快我就会给你安排更多的任务了……' WHERE entry=14441; /* Text0_0: All in good time, mon. I be havin\' more work for you to do soon.... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我看出来了。荒芜水晶的储量大增，很快就能满足需求了。' WHERE entry=14442; /* Text0_0: Indeed you have, mon. Our stores of blight crystals be nearly sufficient! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='达穆克这个饭桶再也不能惹麻烦了！耐心点，朋友。很快就会有更多的工作交给你做了……' WHERE entry=14443; /* Text0_0: Darmuk\'s incompetence be hinderin\' us no more! Patience, mon. Dere soon be more for you to do.... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='除掉那些酋长之后，我们就准备发动攻击了！用不了多久的，$n……' WHERE entry=14444; /* Text0_0: With da chieftains out of da way, we be poised to make our assault! Soon, $n.... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='朋友，眼下的形势你已经了如指掌了！做好准备吧……我们很快就要发动攻击了！' WHERE entry=14445; /* Text0_0: Now ya be knowin\' everything, mon! Prepare yourself... we attack soon! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='洛丹伦沦陷时，我正在这里拜访亲戚……唉。我大概再也不能回到西部荒野了。$B$B有时我会思念家人，也不知他们是否依然健在。但是更多的时候，我的内心平静地如同一滩死水，好像没有什么能让我牵挂的了。' WHERE entry=14446; /* Text0_0: I was here visiting relatives when Lordaeron fell, and then... well. I suppose I won\'t ever be returning to Westfall, now.$B$BSometimes I wonder if my family is still alive. More often, though, I wonder why I no longer care. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='这只碗里散发出强烈的气味，闻起来好象是各种草药和燃烧的毛发混合在一起。' WHERE entry=14447; /* Text0_0: The strong odor coming from the bowl smells like a mixture of various herbs with burning hair. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你必须骑上锦标赛坐骑，我才能教你如何骑乘作战。$B$B拿上一支长枪，然后从你所在阵营的兽栏中挑选一匹坐骑吧。' WHERE entry=14453; /* Text0_0: You must be riding a tournament mount before I can instruct you.$B$BEquip a lance and find a tournament mount outside your faction\'s pavilion. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你必须骑上锦标赛坐骑，我才能教你如何骑乘作战。$B$B拿上一支长枪，然后从你所在阵营的兽栏中挑选一匹坐骑吧。' WHERE entry=14455; /* Text0_0: My advice is no good to ye unless ye\'re ridin\' a tournament mount.$B$BEquip a lance and grab a tournament mount outside yer faction\'s pavilion. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='只有暴风城的勇士才有资格从我这里购买物品。' WHERE entry=14456; /* Text0_0: Only champions of Stormwind may purchase what I have to offer. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='急什么呢，$r！$B$B只有铁炉堡的勇士才有资格从我这里购买物品。' WHERE entry=14457; /* Text0_0: Not so fast, $r!$B$BOnly champions of Ironforge can purchase what I got ta offer. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='很抱歉，$r。只有雷霆崖的勇士才有资格从我这里购买物品。' WHERE entry=14458; /* Text0_0: Apologies, $r, but only champions of Thunder Bluff may purchase what I have to offer. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='哎呀，只有达纳苏斯的勇士才有资格从我这里购买物品。' WHERE entry=14463; /* Text0_0: Alas, only champions of Darnassus may purchase what I have to offer. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='哎呀，只有银月城的勇士才有资格从我这里购买物品。' WHERE entry=14465; /* Text0_0: Alas, only the esteemed champions of Silvermoon City may purchase what I have to offer. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你成功地击败了那只金属怪物。看来面前的障碍已经不多啦。$B$B一旦除掉前厅尽头的机器人，我们就能进入奥杜尔了。$B$B我们还发现了一头巨型喷火始祖龙和一个熔化的巨人。不过他们并没有挡住我们的去路，如果你想避开它们也没有问题。' WHERE entry=14471; /* Text0_0: Great job with that metal monstrosity. There appears to be only a few more obstacles in our way.$B$BOnce you clear out that clanking robot at the end of the hall, we\'ll be inside Ulduar.$B$BWe also noticed an enormous, fire-breathing protodrake and a molten giant. They aren\'t in our way, though, if you\'d like to just avoid them. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='欢迎你参加锦标赛，$n。' WHERE entry=14472; /* Text0_0: Welcome to the tournament, $N. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='训练并骑乘毒皮暴掠龙需要耗费大量精力。' WHERE entry=14474; /* Text0_0: It takes a lot of dedication to train and ride a Venomhide. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='银色北伐军的骑兵将攻击和防御巧妙地结合起来，在作战中实现平衡与精准。$B$B但是，由于他们需要时刻与你保持距离，因此你可以伺机冲锋。$B$B你必须抢在他们之前发起冲锋，拉近彼此的距离，接下来在围绕他们跑动的过程中使用碎盾并看准机会使用刺击。',Text0_1_loc4='银色北伐军的骑兵将攻击和防御巧妙地结合起来，在作战中实现平衡与精准。$B$B但是，由于他们需要时刻与你保持距离，因此你可以伺机冲锋。$B$B你必须抢在他们之前发起冲锋，拉近彼此的距离，接下来在围绕他们跑动的过程中使用碎盾并看准机会使用刺击。' WHERE entry=14476; /* Text0_0: The Argent Crusade riders believe in balance and precision, deftly mixing attack and defense.$B$BHowever, they will often open themselves to Charges by trying to gain range on you.$B$BClose that range with a Charge before they can do the same, and then Shield-Break them as you wheel around for more Thrusts. */ /* Text0_1: The Argent Crusade riders believe in balance and precision, deftly mixing attack and defense.$B$BHowever, they will often open themselves to Charges by trying to gain range on you.$B$BClose that range with a Charge before they can do the same, and then Shield-Break them as you wheel around for more Thrusts. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='欢迎来到这座圣光礼拜堂。请坐。愿你暂时远离痛苦的尘世，享受片刻的宁静。',Text0_1_loc4='欢迎来到这座圣光礼拜堂。请坐。愿你暂时远离痛苦的尘世，享受片刻的宁静。' WHERE entry=14487; /* Text0_0: Welcome to our little chapel of the Light. Please, take a seat. Enjoy a respite from the world\'s ills. */ /* Text0_1: Welcome to our little chapel of the Light. Please, take a seat. Enjoy a respite from the world\'s ills. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='让我们开始吧，$r。$b$b我们的时间不多了，但还有很多事要做。' WHERE entry=14488; /* Text0_0: Let\'s get to it, $r.$b$bThere\'s little time and much to do. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='今天你已经战胜了一位骑兵，我不能再接受你的挑战了。',Text0_1_loc4='今天你已经战胜了一位骑兵，我不能再接受你的挑战了。' WHERE entry=14489; /* Text0_0: You\'ve already bested one of our riders today, so I cannot accept your challenge. */ /* Text0_1: You\'ve already bested one of our riders today, so I cannot accept your challenge. */
