UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我的女士。$b$b我没有能保护她。我又怎么能回到银月城……' WHERE entry=14494; /* Text0_0: My lady.$b$bI was unable to protect her. How can I return to Silvermoon... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='能在锦标赛中代表银色北伐军出场真是无上的荣耀。',Text0_1_loc4='能在锦标赛中代表银色北伐军出场真是无上的荣耀。' WHERE entry=14495; /* Text0_0: It is an honor to represent the Argent Crusade in this tournament. */ /* Text0_1: It is an honor to represent the Argent Crusade in this tournament. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='激活辅助防御系统后，轨道炮台将消灭所有未经认证的生命体。$B$B你属于未经认证的生命体。请确认。' WHERE entry=14496; /* Text0_0: Activating secondary defensive systems will result in the extermination of unauthorized life forms via orbital emplacements.$B$BYou are an unauthorized life form. Please confirm. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='允许安全控制。辅助防御系统已激活。$B$B可以通过广场上的独立能源塔关闭这些辅助系统。' WHERE entry=14497; /* Text0_0: Security override permitted. Secondary defensive systems activated.$B$BBackup deactivation for secondary systems can be accessed via individual generators located on the concourse. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='银色锦标赛在冰冠冰川的北部边界拉开了帷幕，$c。如果你不知道怎么去哪儿，我可以免费送你一程。$B$B我们积累的作战经验越多，在面对巫妖王时胜算也就更大。' WHERE entry=14500; /* Text0_0: The Argent Tournament has begun in the northern reaches of Icecrown, $c. If you\'ve yet to find your way there, I can pay your way.$B$BThe more we have participating in the melee, the stronger we\'ll be when we strike against the Lich King. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='欢迎，孩子。' WHERE entry=14505; /* Text0_0: Welcome, child. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='鲜血与雷鸣,$n!' WHERE entry=14507; /* Text0_0: Blood and Thunder, $n! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我们要面对许多危险，但我们不能因此而忽视自然。这样的话，自然将会在我们有所需要时舍我们而去。我们曾经有过这样的教训。' WHERE entry=14508; /* Text0_0: There are many dangers facing us, but we cannot find ourselves neglecting nature, lest it neglect us in our time of need. We\'ve learned this lesson before. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='阻挡自然者即是异端，即便在自然发挥它破坏之力时亦然如此。$B$B但如今要摧毁黑海岸的并非自然的力量。我不会让这片土地分崩离析。' WHERE entry=14509; /* Text0_0: Standing in the way of nature is heresy.  Even when nature\'s force is a destructive one.$B$BThe forces that would destroy Darkshore are not natural, however.  I will not let this land be torn asunder. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='不要这样傻站着，$r……$b$b还有很多工作要做呢！' WHERE entry=14514; /* Text0_0: Don\'t just stand around, $r...$b$bThere\'s work to be done! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='安静，小东西，这样你就能听到这片古老的土地在说话。它正在痛苦地呼号。' WHERE entry=14517; /* Text0_0: Be still, little one, and you can hear this ancient land speak. It cries out in pain. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='嗯，这么年轻就拥有了如此强大的力量，这可真是惊人。你一定能以联盟的名义杀死无数敌人。但必须记住，在伟大的循环之中，生具有和死一样强大的力量。$B$B<安努缓缓地伸手到自己的头顶，摘下一颗不显眼的橡实，然后以从容不迫的姿态将手放在你面前>$B$B它有着特别的力量。$B$B……很抱歉，希望你不会认为我这是在自吹自擂。' WHERE entry=14518; /* Text0_0: Hum, hrm. A powerful reagent for one so young. You will kill many foes in the name of your Alliance, but it is important to remember that in the great cycle, birth is as powerful as death.$B$B<Onu slowly reaches up to his head and withdraws an inconspicuous acorn. He lowers his arm to you with unhurried calm.>$B$BThis is extremely potent.$B$B...I apologize, I did not wish that to sound like a boast. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='小$r，来看看我们是不是能把敌人冻住。' WHERE entry=14520; /* Text0_0: Let us see if we can freeze the enemy where they stand, little $r. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我们的兄弟迷失了。他烧焦了大地，蒸发了水体，吞噬了太多空气。$B$B帮助我们让他回复平衡与和谐吧。' WHERE entry=14521; /* Text0_0: Our brother has lost his way. He scorches the ground, he vaporizes the water, and devours too much air.$B$BHelp us to bring him back into balance and harmony. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='<*轰隆*轰隆*轰隆*>' WHERE entry=14523; /* Text0_0: <*Rumble*Rumble*Rumble*> */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='<这只幼崽死盯着你，仿佛想分辨出你是不是它的妈妈。>' WHERE entry=14527; /* Text0_0: <The hatchling looks at you as if trying to determine whether or not you\'re its mother.> */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='放弃挖掘？这太荒谬了！在我漫长而勤勉的一生中，我还从没有放弃过一个发掘点。也许我有勘探错误的时候，但从不曾有意放弃过任何值得挖掘的地方。你又是谁？我们在这里做什么？' WHERE entry=14529; /* Text0_0: Abandon the dig? Ridiculous! In my long industrious career, I\'ve never abandoned a site. Not intentionally. Misplaced a few, maybe. Who are you again? What are we doing here? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='鱼人，呸！' WHERE entry=14532; /* Text0_0: Murlocs. Bah! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='能给我们点陈年蛋黄吃吗？',Text1_0_loc4='难道连造物主的包包也满了吗？' WHERE entry=14535; /* Text0_0: We can has aged yolk? */ /* Text1_0: Do Great Ones ever run out of bag space for shinies? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text2_0_loc4='你觉得小狗狗人为什么总追问我们是否同情拉弗乌呢？拉弗乌的确很多话，但他是我们的好朋友。',Text3_0_loc4='那么$n，你能给我们个哨子吗？这样我们想你的时候吹吹哨子就能见到你了，好吗？' WHERE entry=14535; /* Text2_0: Why you think puppy-man hatchlings keep asking if we pity Lafoo? Lafoo talks a lot, but he\'s our friend. */ /* Text3_0: Soo-$n, maybe you give us whistle for when we need to call you. Oki? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text4_0_loc4='也许我们长大了会成为$r呢。是不是呀？',Text5_0_loc4='你也是因为狗狗人才变成孤儿了吗？' WHERE entry=14535; /* Text4_0: Maybe we be a $r when we grow up. Think so? */ /* Text5_0: Are you alone because puppy-men killed your parents too? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你得离海象人远点。他们会弄痛你。' WHERE entry=14536; /* Text0_0: You should stay away from walrus-men. They could pup-nap you. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='当大地被撕裂之后，我一直在帮助飞行管理员寻找逃散的角鹰兽。直到现在，我们的鸟还是无法真正安定下来。' WHERE entry=14541; /* Text0_0: I have been assisting the flight masters to round up the Hippogryphs that fled their post when the land tore itself apart. Even now our birds remain squeamish. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='在悼念日，人们会聚集在墓地，追忆、告慰那些逝者的亡魂。$B$B届时任何主城的墓地都会举行这个仪式，在那里有悼念日食品、舞蹈、化装聚会和其他活动。',Text0_1_loc4='在悼念日，人们会聚集在墓地，追忆、告慰那些逝者的亡魂。$B$B届时任何主城的墓地都会举行这个仪式，在那里有悼念日食品、舞蹈、化装聚会和其他活动。' WHERE entry=14544; /* Text0_0: During the Day of the Dead, people gather in graveyards to celebrate with and cherish the spirits of those they have lost.$B$BYou can find the festivities in the cemeteries of any major city, where you\'ll be able to cook, dance, don costumes, and more. */ /* Text0_1: During the Day of the Dead, people gather in graveyards to celebrate with and cherish the spirits of those they have lost.$B$BYou can find the festivities in the cemeteries of any major city, where you\'ll be able to cook, dance, don costumes, and more. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='艾露恩指引我们，$c。' WHERE entry=14547; /* Text0_0: Elune guide us, $c. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我们绝不能向敌人让出一寸土地。如果他们进攻黑海岸，我们就把他们打回去。我们要像保卫达纳苏斯一样保卫这里。' WHERE entry=14548; /* Text0_0: We must not allow an inch to our enemy.  If they strike in Darkshore we will fight them back just as if they had attacked Darnassus itself. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='能够再度和亲友一起欢庆，彼此分享旧日的故事，这种感觉实在太好了。',Text0_1_loc4='能够再度和亲友一起欢庆，彼此分享旧日的故事，这种感觉实在太好了。' WHERE entry=14552; /* Text0_0: It\'s good to visit with friends and family again, celebrating and sharing stories of old. */ /* Text0_1: It\'s good to visit with friends and family again, celebrating and sharing stories of old. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='<喷鼻息>懦夫就是这么战斗的吗，$r！' WHERE entry=14553; /* Text0_0: <Snort> Is this how cowards fight, $r? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='<这头野猪人用他黑珠子一样的眼睛紧盯着你。>',Text1_0_loc4='<这头野猪人抽着鼻子，一边哼哼，一边嗅着你。>' WHERE entry=14555; /* Text0_0: <The quilboar fixes his beady black eyes on you.> */ /* Text1_0: <The quilboar wrinkles his nose at you and snorts.> */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text2_0_loc4='怎么样，$r？想干什么就干吧。',Text3_0_loc4='我们是骄傲的战士，$n。<哼哼>数量还很多。' WHERE entry=14555; /* Text2_0: What now, $r? Do your worst. */ /* Text3_0: We\'re warriors, $n. <Snort> Many and proud. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='<熊怪闻闻你，哼了两声。>' WHERE entry=14557; /* Text0_0: <The furbolg sniffs at you and grunts.> */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='$c，在你的一生中，你肯定有过一段做学生的时光。从导师那里学习知识，并想要为导师争光，对不对？我不是指具体的某个人，但导师肯定是比你知道更多，而且愿意教导你的人。不过，要不是这样呢？想象一下……$b$b如果你发现，你的导师所知道的也许并不如你想象的那样多，你也许能找到更好的办法提升自己，你又会怎样做？' WHERE entry=14560; /* Text0_0: Surely you\'ve been a student once in your life, $c. You learned from an instructor, and you gained respect for them in some way, yes? Maybe not as a person, but at the least, as one who knew more than you and was willing to teach you. If not, use your imagination...$b$bWhat would you do if you came to realize your instructor may not know as much as you thought, and that you may have found a better path? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我曾经不断地将各种辎重和食物从奥格瑞玛拖送到十字路口，那可是件繁重的工作。现在我的脖子总会因为那时的劳累而隐隐作痛。' WHERE entry=14564; /* Text0_0: Used to be hauling gear and food from Orgrimmar to Crossroads was peon-work. Nowadays my neck\'s always on the line. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='哦，$n！我的兄弟巴尔格告诉我，你在科多兽背上的表现可谓是百发百中。这支运输队能从前沿哨所安全地来到这里，你可是立了一大功。$B$B听着，我知道你在格罗多姆还有很多工作要做……不过我更希望你能够继续护送运输队前往十字路口。$B$B做好准备以后再来找我吧！' WHERE entry=14565; /* Text0_0: Ho, $N! My brother Balgor tells me you\'re quite the shot from the back of a kodo. Great work getting that caravan here from Far Watch in one piece.$B$BListen, there\'s plenty of work for you here in Grol\'dom... but I could use your trigger fingers for the rest of the ride to Crossroads.$B$BCome see me when you\'re ready! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你准备好了吗，$n？' WHERE entry=14566; /* Text0_0: Are you ready to do this, $N? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='$n，小心！' WHERE entry=14568; /* Text0_0: Beware, $N! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你好啊，$r。' WHERE entry=14571; /* Text0_0: Good day to you, $r. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='森林的拯救者！如果不是你的英勇行为，阿斯特兰纳和灰谷一定会落进燃烧军团的手中。$B$B希望你诸事顺利，$n！' WHERE entry=14572; /* Text0_0: The savior of the forest! Were it not for your actions, Astranaar and then the rest of Ashenvale surely would have fallen to the Burning Legion.$B$BI hope that this day finds you well, $N! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='嘿，你是怎么找到我的？看来我要找一个更好的藏身地了。' WHERE entry=14574; /* Text0_0: Hey mon, how\'d you find me? I gotta find a better hiding spot. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你的名字叫做$n？这对于熊怪来说可真是个奇怪的名字。$B$B看来你不是从灰谷来的。' WHERE entry=14575; /* Text0_0: You call yourself, $N? That is a strange name for a furbolg.$B$BYou\'re not from Ashenvale. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='<奥塔·旺的眼睛本已经因为饱受奴役而变得灰暗。听到你的方案，它们重新闪烁出光芒。你感觉到达图尔魔棒的力量通过你传到了这只熊怪的身上。>$B$B你要反抗吗？' WHERE entry=14576; /* Text0_0: <Ota Wen\'s eyes, already dull from his enslavement, glaze over even more at your suggestion. You feel the power of Dartol\'s Rod begin to course through you and reach out to touch the furbolg.>$B$BRise up? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='<一道奇怪的光芒在奥塔·旺的眼中闪过。他挺起身子，向天空发出咆哮。>$B$B我们会奋起抗争！摧毁我们的枷锁！' WHERE entry=14577; /* Text0_0: <A strange light ignites in Ota Wen\'s eyes as he stands up straight, roaring at the heavens.>$B$BYES, WE WILL RISE UP! RISE UP AND DESTROY OUR JAILORS! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='$c，深吸一口气。雷鸣峰顶的空气非常稀薄，不过这里毕竟没有下面那种呛鼻子的尘土。' WHERE entry=14579; /* Text0_0: Take a deep breath, $c. The air atop Thunderhead Summit is thin, but free of the choking dust that strangles the land below. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='小朋友，能帮个忙吗？' WHERE entry=14580; /* Text0_0: Some help, my little friend? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='偷偷摸摸，鬼鬼祟祟。让我告诉你关于格高的事：格高从来不会躲躲藏藏。' WHERE entry=14585; /* Text0_0: Sneak, sneak, sneak. Let me tell you something about Gorgal: Gorgal doesn\'t sneak. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='嗨，$r。最近有什么赚钱的买卖吗？' WHERE entry=14591; /* Text0_0: Hey $r. Seeing any profit lately? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='这些猴子真让人头痛！' WHERE entry=14593; /* Text0_0: These monkeys are a real pain! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='什么？$n，你不是个术士。$B$B我不可能教导你这样的$c，$g先生:女士;。' WHERE entry=14595; /* Text0_0: What? $N, you\'re not a warlock.$B$BThere\'s nothing that I can teach a $c like you, $g sir : ma\'am;. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='$n，很高兴你在这里。或许我能教你一两招。$B$B你觉得怎么样，$g先生:小姐;？' WHERE entry=14596; /* Text0_0: $N, I\'m glad that you\'re here. Maybe I can teach you a thing or two.$B$BWhat do you think, $g sir : ma\'am;? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='不管怎样，我怀疑你不会想接受我的训练，$n。我不确定你的手指能不能控制好火焰箭。' WHERE entry=14597; /* Text0_0: Somehow I doubt that you want training from me, $N. I\'m not sure those fingers can handle a firebolt. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你能相信这些猴子吗，$n？' WHERE entry=14599; /* Text0_0: Can you believe these monkeys, $N? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='哦，你来得正好……未来的元素大师！今天你想接受怎样的训练？' WHERE entry=14600; /* Text0_0: Ah good, there $g he : she; is... my future $g master : mistress; of the elements! What kind of training would you like today? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='全能战士NX-01型当前处于离线状态。' WHERE entry=14605; /* Text0_0: Warrior-Matic NX-01 is currently offline. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='<那个喝醉的工程师眨着惺忪醉眼，向你挥手。>' WHERE entry=14612; /* Text0_0: <The drunken engineer blinks blearily and waves at you.> */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='如果这只绿色的大怪物在五秒钟之内不安静下来，我就要聋掉了。我知道该如何操纵这家伙。我可不是白痴！' WHERE entry=14613; /* Text0_0: I\'m going deaf. That big green harpy won\'t shut up for five seconds. I know how to drive this thing, all right? I\'m not an idiot! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='如果你不介意这些沙尘，那这就是一次很不错的旅行。',Text0_1_loc4='如果你不介意这些沙尘，那这就是一次很不错的旅行。',Text1_0_loc4='离这道悬崖远一点，我可不想看到你摔下去。',Text1_1_loc4='离这道悬崖远一点，我可不想看到你摔下去。' WHERE entry=14615; /* Text0_0: It\'s a pretty smooth ride if you don\'t mind the dust. */ /* Text0_1: It\'s a pretty smooth ride if you don\'t mind the dust. */ /* Text1_0: Keep away from the edge there, champ. Don\'t want you falling. */ /* Text1_1: Keep away from the edge there, champ. Don\'t want you falling. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text2_0_loc4='我干活呢。',Text2_1_loc4='我干活呢。' WHERE entry=14615; /* Text2_0: I\'m workin\', here. */ /* Text2_1: I\'m workin\', here. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='<工程师一头栽倒在地。>' WHERE entry=14616; /* Text0_0: <The Engineer slumbers fitfully on the floor.> */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='嘿，我正在休息。' WHERE entry=14617; /* Text0_0: Hey. I\'m on break. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='欢迎登上西风号飞艇。搭乘它，你能以最快的速度穿越贫瘠之地。请坐下来，尽情享受飞行的乐趣吧。没有什么能比干燥的空气混合上汽油味更好闻的了。' WHERE entry=14618; /* Text0_0: Welcome aboard the Zephyr, the smoothest ride you\'re likely to get across the Barrens. Sit back and enjoy the flight, eh, kid? Ain\'t nothing like that sweet, dry air mixed with the scent of oil. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我是图维。我的工作就是维护这里的和平，警惕敌人的入侵。所以我一直保持着最高度的警觉。' WHERE entry=14619; /* Text0_0: I be Tolwe. Job be to keep da peace an\' watch. So I be watchin\'. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你相信吗？他们终于解除了这个地方的禁制，让我们的飞艇能够穿越这里的天空了！这里不再是飞行禁区了。毕竟，我们在测试飞行中只不过让一艘飞艇撞上了崖壁。我完全不明白他们到底在担心什么。' WHERE entry=14622; /* Text0_0: Can you believe it? They finally opened this place up for us to fly a zeppelin through here! No fly zone no more, am I right? We only crashed one zeppelin into a cliff on the test run. I don\'t see why they were so worried. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你在看什么，$r？想要折磨囚犯吗？' WHERE entry=14623; /* Text0_0: What\'re ye starin\' at, $r? Come ta torment the condemned? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='<巴隆举起他的镣铐。>$B$B好吧，$c。你信任我吗？' WHERE entry=14624; /* Text0_0: <The Baron lifts his manacles.>$B$BCome on then, $c. Do ye trust me? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='怎么样？你没有脑袋可以踢，没有宝藏可以挖吗？' WHERE entry=14625; /* Text0_0: Well? Don\'t ye have heads ta roll an\' treasure ta dig up? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你好，$n。如果你想要接受烹饪训练，那你就找对地方了。当感恩节进行的时候，我经常会有很多新学生。',Text0_1_loc4='你好，$n。如果你想要接受烹饪训练，那你就找对地方了。当感恩节进行的时候，我经常会有很多新学生。' WHERE entry=14627; /* Text0_0: Hello, $N. If you\'re looking for cooking training, you\'ve come to the right place. I usually get lots of new students when Pilgrim\'s Bounty rolls around. */ /* Text0_1: Hello, $N. If you\'re looking for cooking training, you\'ve come to the right place. I usually get lots of new students when Pilgrim\'s Bounty rolls around. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='如果你想对感恩节的节日传统有更多了解，就和那些女侍应们聊聊天吧。' WHERE entry=14628; /* Text0_0: If you\'re interested in learning more about the traditional Pilgrim\'s Bounty feast, speak to any of the hostesses. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你来到这里是为了和我们一起庆祝感恩节吗？' WHERE entry=14630; /* Text0_0: Are you here to celebrate Pilgrim\'s Bounty with us? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='感恩节。嗯，我明白这些牛头人都渴望着向部落酋长表达他们的感激和情谊。但亡灵呢？$B$B我还以为他们早就丢弃了这种多愁善感的传统。',Text0_1_loc4='感恩节。嗯，我明白这些牛头人都渴望着向部落酋长表达他们的感激和情谊。但亡灵呢？$B$B我还以为他们早就丢弃了这种多愁善感的传统。' WHERE entry=14635; /* Text0_0: "Pilgrim\'s Bounty." Hrm. I can understand the tauren\'s eagerness to express their sense of gratitude and comraderie to the Horde\'s warchief, but the Forsaken?$B$BI imagined they would have dropped such sentimental traditions long ago. */ /* Text0_1: "Pilgrim\'s Bounty." Hrm. I can understand the tauren\'s eagerness to express their sense of gratitude and comraderie to the Horde\'s warchief, but the Forsaken?$B$BI imagined they would have dropped such sentimental traditions long ago. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='有人告诉我，在感恩节之中，我们要做的就是纵情狂欢，并和周围的人们分享我们的快乐。$B$B我们幸运地找到了这个世界和这里勇敢的居民。我们应该全无保留地将我们的知识和力量与我们新的盟友分享。',Text0_1_loc4='有人告诉我，在感恩节之中，我们要做的就是纵情狂欢，并和周围的人们分享我们的快乐。$B$B我们幸运地找到了这个世界和这里勇敢的居民。我们应该全无保留地将我们的知识和力量与我们新的盟友分享。' WHERE entry=14636; /* Text0_0: I am told Pilgrim\'s Bounty is a time to reflect upon one\'s good fortune and share with all around you.$B$BWe are lucky to have found this world and its bold inhabitants; it is only fitting that we lend our knowledge and strength to these new-found allies. */ /* Text0_1: I am told Pilgrim\'s Bounty is a time to reflect upon one\'s good fortune and share with all around you.$B$BWe are lucky to have found this world and its bold inhabitants; it is only fitting that we lend our knowledge and strength to these new-found allies. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='人类总是把身子裹在那种破烂的亚麻口袋里。不过他们的确知道该如何烹调美食。感恩节？那可是我的最爱！',Text0_1_loc4='人类总是把身子裹在那种破烂的亚麻口袋里。不过他们的确知道该如何烹调美食。感恩节？那可是我的最爱！' WHERE entry=14637; /* Text0_0: Humans can\'t brew their way out of a tattered linen pouch, but there sure know how to cook. Pilgrim\'s Bounty? I\'m all for it! */ /* Text0_1: Humans can\'t brew their way out of a tattered linen pouch, but there sure know how to cook. Pilgrim\'s Bounty? I\'m all for it! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='为了庆祝感恩节而进行的大规模后勤工作实在是令人吃惊……无数物资与人力都被投入其中。成千上万箱各种物料成品被运送到世界各地，摆放在数不清的盛宴餐桌上。$B$B说实话，这次的后勤活动给我留下了很深的印象。而且现在我已经饿坏了……我能闻到南瓜馅饼的香味。你能闻到吗？',Text0_1_loc4='为了庆祝感恩节而进行的大规模后勤工作实在是令人吃惊……无数物资与人力都被投入其中。成千上万箱各种物料成品被运送到世界各地，摆放在数不清的盛宴餐桌上。$B$B说实话，这次的后勤活动给我留下了很深的印象。而且现在我已经饿坏了……我能闻到南瓜馅饼的香味。你能闻到吗？' WHERE entry=14638; /* Text0_0: The logistics involved in the optimal celebration of Pilgrim\'s Bounty are quite staggering... so many raw materials, so much labor, thousands upon thousands of crates of finished product shipped here and there and everywhere for countless Bountiful Tables.$B$BHonestly, I\'m quite impressed! And hungry... I can smell pumpkin pie. Can you smell that pie? */ /* Text0_1: The logistics involved in the optimal celebration of Pilgrim\'s Bounty are quite staggering... so many raw materials, so much labor, thousands upon thousands of crates of finished product shipped here and there and everywhere for countless Bountiful Tables.$B$BHonestly, I\'m quite impressed! And hungry... I can smell pumpkin pie. Can you smell that pie? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='感恩节？倒不如说是“蠢猪节！”$B$B成千上百箱食物就这样被白白送出去了……居然一个子儿也不收！肯定是脑子进水了！$B$B不过呢，我想我应该将我的一部分家禽投资转移到火鸡上去……我无法相信那笔鸡肉投资竟然有这么大规模。那么多复活节蛋到底是从哪里来的？！',Text0_1_loc4='感恩节？倒不如说是“蠢猪节！”$B$B成千上百箱食物就这样被白白送出去了……居然一个子儿也不收！肯定是脑子进水了！$B$B不过呢，我想我应该将我的一部分家禽投资转移到火鸡上去……我无法相信那笔鸡肉投资竟然有这么大规模。那么多复活节蛋到底是从哪里来的？！' WHERE entry=14639; /* Text0_0: "Pilgrim\'s Bounty?" More like "Fool\'s Folly!"$B$BHundreds of cargo holds full of food given away for free... FREE! It boggles the mind!$B$BStill, I suppose I should shift some of my Poultry Portfolio funds to turkey... I can\'t believe how big of a bust that chicken investment was. Where did all those Noblegarden eggs COME from?! */ /* Text0_1: "Pilgrim\'s Bounty?" More like "Fool\'s Folly!"$B$BHundreds of cargo holds full of food given away for free... FREE! It boggles the mind!$B$BStill, I suppose I should shift some of my Poultry Portfolio funds to turkey... I can\'t believe how big of a bust that chicken investment was. Where did all those Noblegarden eggs COME from?! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='感恩节是人们纵情狂欢，并与你周围的朋友分享快乐的节日。$B$B我们希望，在这个节日里，我们所有高贵的朋友们都能加入到庆祝的行列中来。',Text0_1_loc4='感恩节是人们纵情狂欢，并与你周围的朋友分享快乐的节日。$B$B我们希望，在这个节日里，我们所有高贵的朋友们都能加入到庆祝的行列中来。' WHERE entry=14640; /* Text0_0: Pilgrim\'s Bounty is a time to reflect upon one\'s good fortune and share with all around you.$B$BWe hope that all of our noble allies will join us in feasting and celebration. */ /* Text0_1: Pilgrim\'s Bounty is a time to reflect upon one\'s good fortune and share with all around you.$B$BWe hope that all of our noble allies will join us in feasting and celebration. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='这样的节日和人类的风格实在是有着巨大的反差。有谁会想到，贪婪无情的人类竟然会举办一个表达赠与和分享的节日？$B$B我很高兴看到这样欢乐的景象。达纳苏斯会不遗余力地支持这一活动。',Text0_1_loc4='这样的节日和人类的风格实在是有着巨大的反差。有谁会想到，贪婪无情的人类竟然会举办一个表达赠与和分享的节日？$B$B我很高兴看到这样欢乐的景象。达纳苏斯会不遗余力地支持这一活动。' WHERE entry=14641; /* Text0_0: Such a stark contrast, this holiday, to typical human behavior. Who\'d have thought such a relentlessly voracious people would make a celebration of giving and sharing?$B$BIt\'s pleasant to see. Darnassus should do its utmost to support and encourage it. */ /* Text0_1: Such a stark contrast, this holiday, to typical human behavior. Who\'d have thought such a relentlessly voracious people would make a celebration of giving and sharing?$B$BIt\'s pleasant to see. Darnassus should do its utmost to support and encourage it. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='兽人和牛头人能够在这个世界上彼此找到，成为伙伴，这对他们来说实在是一件幸运的事。这两个种族有着不相上下的强猛力量。我们很高兴能和他们一起庆祝这个节日。$B$B就连被遗忘者一族也参加了这次节日庆典。虽然我并不确定他们要怎样庆祝这个节日……',Text0_1_loc4='兽人和牛头人能够在这个世界上彼此找到，成为伙伴，这对他们来说实在是一件幸运的事。这两个种族有着不相上下的强猛力量。我们很高兴能和他们一起庆祝这个节日。$B$B就连被遗忘者一族也参加了这次节日庆典。虽然我并不确定他们要怎样庆祝这个节日……' WHERE entry=14642; /* Text0_0: The orcs and tauren are fortunate to have found one another, for each people\'s strengths compliment the other\'s.  We are glad to join them in this celebration.$B$BEven the Forsaken partake, though to what end I am not certain... */ /* Text0_1: The orcs and tauren are fortunate to have found one another, for each people\'s strengths compliment the other\'s.  We are glad to join them in this celebration.$B$BEven the Forsaken partake, though to what end I am not certain... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='感恩节是人们纵情狂欢，并与你周围的朋友分享快乐的节日。$B$B在莫高雷和部落中间，我们都找到了家的感觉和亲密的朋友，来共同享用各种美好的果实。$B$B我们希望，在这个节日里，我们所有的朋友都能加入到庆祝的行列中来。',Text0_1_loc4='感恩节是人们纵情狂欢，并与你周围的朋友分享快乐的节日。$B$B在莫高雷和部落中间，我们都找到了家的感觉和亲密的朋友，来共同享用各种美好的果实。$B$B我们希望，在这个节日里，我们所有的朋友都能加入到庆祝的行列中来。' WHERE entry=14643; /* Text0_0: Pilgrim\'s Bounty is a time to reflect upon one\'s good fortune and share with all around you.$B$BIn Mulgore and the Horde, we have found both a home and friends to enjoy its many fruits with.$B$BIt is our hope that every one of our allies will be able to join us in feasting and celebration. */ /* Text0_1: Pilgrim\'s Bounty is a time to reflect upon one\'s good fortune and share with all around you.$B$BIn Mulgore and the Horde, we have found both a home and friends to enjoy its many fruits with.$B$BIt is our hope that every one of our allies will be able to join us in feasting and celebration. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='那些牛头人真的很懂得什么叫美食！你有没有看见过他们做的那些菜？$B$B我要一直吃到把自己撑死……然后再从坟墓里爬出来，重新开始吃！',Text0_1_loc4='那些牛头人真的很懂得什么叫美食！你有没有看见过他们做的那些菜？$B$B我要一直吃到把自己撑死……然后再从坟墓里爬出来，重新开始吃！' WHERE entry=14644; /* Text0_0: Dem tauren, dey be KNOWIN\' how ta cook. Have ya SEEN all de food dey be servin\'?$B$BI\'m gonna eat \'til I die... an\' den come back from de grave ta be eatin\' some more! */ /* Text0_1: Dem tauren, dey be KNOWIN\' how ta cook. Have ya SEEN all de food dey be servin\'?$B$BI\'m gonna eat \'til I die... an\' den come back from de grave ta be eatin\' some more! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='<你面前的这个巨魔从头到脚都是伤疤。一道新伤口横亘在他的脸上，豁开了他的嘴唇。>$B$B你好！$B$B巨魔把恐龙当坐骑。但与野生恐龙进行交流，并进一步训练它们是个难题！所以我会到这里来。我是一名恐龙训练师。' WHERE entry=14649; /* Text0_0: <The troll before you is covered head-to-toe with gashes and scars, including a fresh slice across his face that has fattened his lip.>$B$BHewwo!$B$BAs you know, twolls wide waptors. The pwobwem is cowwecting the wild waptors for twaining! That\'s where I come in. I\'m a waptor twapper. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='小心那些恐龙，它们可能非常非常聪明。$B$B上个星期，两头恐龙吸引了我的注意力，而第三头恐龙却用一根棒子偷袭我。' WHERE entry=14652; /* Text0_0: Be caweful with the waptors, they can be wewy wewy smawt.$B$BLast week two hewd me down while a thiwd beat me with a stick. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你会在灵魂高地的西部边缘，飞艇停泊处附近找到克伦德尔。我可不喜欢看到那种地精机器从这里飞过去……但它的确能把你送到奥格瑞玛去，只要你在那上面没吐到晕过去。',Text0_1_loc4='你会在灵魂高地的西部边缘，飞艇停泊处附近找到克伦德尔。我可不喜欢看到那种地精机器从这里飞过去……但它的确能把你送到奥格瑞玛去，只要你在那上面没吐到晕过去。' WHERE entry=14658; /* Text0_0: You\'ll find Krendle Bigpockets near the zeppelin\'s perch on the western edge of Spirit Rise. I\'m not fond of the goblin contraption flying through here... but it will take you to Orgrimmar if you can stand it. */ /* Text0_1: You\'ll find Krendle Bigpockets near the zeppelin\'s perch on the western edge of Spirit Rise. I\'m not fond of the goblin contraption flying through here... but it will take you to Orgrimmar if you can stand it. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='真正的十字军绝不仅仅是在战场上对抗邪恶……十字军是一个榜样，一面正义的旗帜，是大众心中一名坚不可摧的守护者。$B$B作为高阶十字军，我的责任就是向这样的战士们分派各种值得他们去完成的任务。',Text0_1_loc4='真正的十字军绝不仅仅是在战场上对抗邪恶……十字军是一个榜样，一面正义的旗帜，是大众心中一名坚不可摧的守护者。$B$B作为高阶十字军，我的责任就是向这样的战士们分派各种值得他们去完成的任务。' WHERE entry=14659; /* Text0_0: The true crusader is more than just a hero in the battle against evil... he is an exemplar, a rallier to the cause, a champion in the eyes of all his people.$B$BAs High Crusader, it is my duty to task such men and women with worthy quests. */ /* Text0_1: The true crusader is more than just a hero in the battle against evil... he is an exemplar, a rallier to the cause, a champion in the eyes of all his people.$B$BAs High Crusader, it is my duty to task such men and women with worthy quests. */
