UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='干得好！你竟然打败了所有这些猛兽，这简直太神奇了！不过，我听说下一个挑战将更加艰难！' WHERE entry=14678; /* Text0_0: Well done! Your fighting against all those beasts was splendid! I hear the next challenge should be even tougher! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='现在我们暂时压制住了加拉克苏斯大王，但我们不可能压制住他太长时间。' WHERE entry=14679; /* Text0_0: We\'re holding Lord Jaraxxus back for now, but we can\'t keep him bound for much longer. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='敌人将有多么强大，你很快就会知道了。现在，你是否已经准备好了迎接下一场挑战？' WHERE entry=14680; /* Text0_0: You\'ll find out soon enough. Are you ready for the next challenge? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='这太好了，一定及时给我信号，让我知道该在什么时候放下那些法术。' WHERE entry=14682; /* Text0_0: That\'s great, just give me the signal for when to drop the binding spells. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我可真喜欢你！你相信我？是吗？',Text1_0_loc4='甜心，你去哪里了？你是否知道，当我无法联系到你的时候，是多么担心吗！' WHERE entry=14683; /* Text0_0: I adore you! You believe me? Right, baby? */ /* Text1_0: Sweetie, where have you been? You know how worried I get when you don\'t check in with me! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text2_0_loc4='你觉得我的腹肌如何，亲爱的？我刚刚从健身馆回来。$B$B现在我够健美了吧！',Text3_0_loc4='其她那些女人只是普通朋友，亲爱的。' WHERE entry=14683; /* Text2_0: What do you think of my abs, baby? I just got back from the gym.$B$BI am one fine piece of meat! */ /* Text3_0: Those other women are just friends, baby. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text4_0_loc4='我喜欢你的衣服！',Text5_0_loc4='我知道，昨晚和前天晚上我都答应过你。等到明天晚上，我一定会带你去个好地方！' WHERE entry=14683; /* Text4_0: I like what you\'re wearing! */ /* Text5_0: I know that I promised you last night, and the night before that, but I\'m taking you out someplace really nice tomorrow night! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text6_0_loc4='听说早些时候南海海盗进入了港口。如果你要进城的话，一定要小心！$B$B那些海盗之中甚至还有女人！嗯，也许我应该亲自去查看一下？这只是为了保护你的安全，亲爱的。',Text7_0_loc4='我热辣的公司总监女朋友今天过得如何？既然你已经在管理这么多事情。我想，我们随时都有可能会改称你为贸易女王$n了！我真期待那一天的到来！那样我就能随心所欲地在健身馆健身，在池塘边把皮肤晒成健美的褐色了。' WHERE entry=14683; /* Text6_0: I heard that some Southsea pirates pulled into dock earlier. Be careful if you go into town!$B$BThey even have women pirates! Hmm, maybe I should go check it out myself? Just to make sure it\'s safe for you out there, baby. */ /* Text7_0: How\'s my hot, company executive girlfriend today? With the way you run things around here, I think that any day now we\'ll be calling you Trade Princess $N!$B$BI cannot wait! I\'m gonna spend my days at the gym and working on my tan by the pool. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='嗨，头儿。这批巨魔奴隶可是我见过的最糟糕的一批！$B$B幸运的是，卡亚矿石似乎并没有让他们的豆腐渣脑子变得更聪明一些，对不对？' WHERE entry=14684; /* Text0_0: Hey there, boss-$g man : lady;. This batch of troll slaves has got to be the worst yet!$B$BLucky for us that the Kaja\'mite doesn\'t seem to be making their soft brains any smarter, eh? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='$c，是否已经准备好了迎接第一个挑战？' WHERE entry=14688; /* Text0_0: Are you ready for your first challenge, $c? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你要学习如何驾驭坐骑？' WHERE entry=14689; /* Text0_0: You come to learn how to ride? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='多年以来，我一直在这个被世界遗忘的角落里工作着，查看这里的地形，在无聊中打发时间。但我的时代终会到来的。奥格瑞玛正将全部力量转向艾萨拉，我们打开了通往灰谷的通道，并终将统治这片大陆。欢迎来到前线，$c。' WHERE entry=14690; /* Text0_0: For years I served in this backwater corner of the world, learning the terrain and biding my time. At last our time has come. The full might of Orgrimmar is now turned to Azshara, our gateway to Ashenvale and dominance over this continent. Welcome to the front lines, $c. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='<这头角鹰兽看上去已经急切地准备要走了！>' WHERE entry=14692; /* Text0_0: <The Hippogryph looks anxious and ready to go!> */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='快滚开，否则奇普·英代尔的老拳可就要砸在你脸上了！' WHERE entry=14694; /* Text0_0: Beat it, pal, before I give you the ol\' Chip Endale fist to the face! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你好，$n$g先生:女士;。欢迎来到南海第一科赞贸易与商业银行。$B$B我能为你做些什么？' WHERE entry=14695; /* Text0_0: Welcome to First Bank of Kezan, a wholly-owned subsidiary of the Bilgewater Traders & Merchants Bank Of The South Seas.$B$BWhat can I do for you today? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='呦！你看上去像是个有些品味的$g男人:女人; 。$B$B我能为你做些什么？' WHERE entry=14697; /* Text0_0: Yo! You look like a $g man : woman; of discerning tastes.$B$BWhat can I do you for? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='这件首饰就像你的妈妈一样好！' WHERE entry=14698; /* Text0_0: That bling is phat like your momma! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='看看和我共事的都是什么人。苏扎博能弄出奇迹来吗？$B$B<苏扎博叹了口气>$B$B是的，是的，苏扎博认为他能为你做些事。' WHERE entry=14700; /* Text0_0: Look what I have to work with. Szabo can perform miracles?$B$B<Szabo sighs>$B$BYes, yes. Szabo thinks he can do something with you. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='哦，看看苏扎博做了什么。真是杰作啊！$B$B说实话，你配不上这身行头，但苏扎博需要钱。<叹气>' WHERE entry=14702; /* Text0_0: Oh, just look at what Szabo has done. A masterpiece!$B$BYou are not worthy of such an outfit, but Szabo needs the money. <sigh> */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='元素之灵是睿智的。在我们出现之前，他们早已经存在于此，在我们尽数消失之后，他们仍然会在这里长存不息。当他们对我们说话的时候，我们必须仔细倾听。' WHERE entry=14723; /* Text0_0: The spirits of the elements are wise. They\'ve been here long before us and will persist long after we\'re gone. When they speak to us, we must listen. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='元素之灵就在我们身边。我们必须时刻注意倾听他们的声音。我亲眼见到过当我们忽视他们的警告时，发生了怎样的灾难……' WHERE entry=14724; /* Text0_0: The spirits of the elements surround us. We must always listen. I have seen firsthand the consequences when we ignore their warnings... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='滚开，虫子。你不属于这个地方。不要激怒我。' WHERE entry=14729; /* Text0_0: Begone, insect. You do not belong in these lands. Do not provoke my ire. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='再次感谢你能“帮助”那些懒家伙，老板。$B$B要我说，我们既然已经不再是那些巨魔的奴隶，就不应该对那些巨魔太仁慈。' WHERE entry=14731; /* Text0_0: Thanks again for the help with these lazy cretins, boss-$g man : lady;.$B$BIf you ask me, we shouldn\'t have been so lenient with the trolls when we freed ourselves from being their slaves. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='找我有事吗，$c?' WHERE entry=14735; /* Text0_0: Yes, $C? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='的确会有人不再想获得经验。他们想永远停留在现有的水平，不再变得更强。$B$B我可以实现这一点……当然，我需要收取一些费用。$B$B但你要明白：一旦你把酬金支付给我，你就无法再获得经验了。是一直，而不是一段时间。$B$B如果你以后又改变主意，想要重新开始获取经验，也可以向我支付同样多的酬金，让我解除这一禁制。',Text0_1_loc4='的确会有人不再想获得经验。他们想永远停留在现有的水平，不再变得更强。$B$B我可以实现这一点……当然，我需要收取一些费用。$B$B但你要明白：一旦你把酬金支付给我，你就无法再获得经验了。是一直，而不是一段时间。$B$B如果你以后又改变主意，想要重新开始获取经验，也可以向我支付同样多的酬金，让我解除这一禁制。' WHERE entry=14736; /* Text0_0: There are some who desire to stop gaining experience from their actions; to forever remain at the level of strength they are now, and never grow stronger.$B$BI can make this possible... for a fee, of course.$B$BBut understand this: Once you pay me, you will NO LONGER GAIN EXPERIENCE. None. Not one whit.$B$BShould you change your mind afterwards and want to start gaining experience again, I can undo the process for the same fee. */ /* Text0_1: There are some who desire to stop gaining experience from their actions; to forever remain at the level of strength they are now, and never grow stronger.$B$BI can make this possible... for a fee, of course.$B$BBut understand this: Once you pay me, you will NO LONGER GAIN EXPERIENCE. None. Not one whit.$B$BShould you change your mind afterwards and want to start gaining experience again, I can undo the process for the same fee. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='今天，你在竞技场上的表现给所有人都留下了深刻的印象。现在，你将在万众瞩目下成为这次比武的冠军。' WHERE entry=14738; /* Text0_0: You\'ve impressed everyone here today with your skills in the arena.  It is now time to be recognized before all as a champion of the tournament. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='这座纪念碑以永不消失的古老能量发出各种嗡嗡和噼啪的声音。' WHERE entry=14739; /* Text0_0: This monument hums and crackles with perpetual ancient energies. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='在你眼前的是这个世界上最具艺术品位的采矿系统。只有土包子才会在山下挖隧道以获得矿石。我们则会将整座山移开！现在，我们就可以直接从地面上挖掘珍贵的金属了。' WHERE entry=14740; /* Text0_0: You\'re looking at the most state-of-the-art mining operation in the world. Only rubes would bother to tunnel under a mountain to get at the minerals below. We moved the whole mountain! Now we can just scoop the precious metals right off of the ground. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='寒风猛烈地吹过这里的峭壁，在冰冠冰川的这个角落，绝大多数生命都不会做片刻停留。不过，只需要一点耐心，生命又都会回来。所以我现在走在这片大地上。总有一天，这些树木会高过我们所有人。' WHERE entry=14751; /* Text0_0: The wind fiercely cuts across this bluff, and most life has long since fled this corner of Icecrown. However, all it takes is a bit of coaxing for it to return, and that is why I walk these grounds. One day these trees will tower over us all. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='第一场挑战需要你骑上一匹银色战马。' WHERE entry=14757; /* Text0_0: The first challenge requires you to be mounted on an Argent Warhorses.  You will find these mounts along the walls of this coliseum.$b$bPlease, mount the warhorse, speak to me, and then we can proceed. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='猛犸人并不像看上去那样愚蠢。看管戈莫克就是一个非常困难的任务。但现在他已经被紧紧地捆住，应该不会有任何危险了。' WHERE entry=14759; /* Text0_0: The magnataur are not as stupid as they appear. Keeping Gormok until his time is a difficult task, but he is bound tightly enough that there is no danger. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我帮助戈莫克照顾这些怪物。我并不完全赞同这种屠杀。但至少，他有机会进行战斗了。' WHERE entry=14760; /* Text0_0: I tend these creatures of Gormok as he cannot. I do not fully agree with this slaughter, but at the least he will have his chance to fight. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='雪人是一种凶猛而狡诈的怪物，而这头雪人又是雪人之中最强壮的一头。我们在他的食物里掺了药，让他睡着了。$b$b但你可千万别以为他在斗兽场里还会这样昏昏沉沉地酣睡。' WHERE entry=14761; /* Text0_0: The yeti is a fierce, cunning creature, and this one is one of the strongest of his kind. We keep him asleep through herbs in his food.$b$bDo not think he will be lethargic in the ring, however. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我……我失去了对这些矿藏的控制！$B$B求求你，$g先生:女士;，不要解雇我！' WHERE entry=14762; /* Text0_0: I... I lost control of the mines!$B$BPlease, $g sir : ma\'am;, don\'t fire me! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你好，如果你需要我的拍卖服务，那么我只能遗憾地告诉你：不行。只有宗师级工程师才有足够的能力操纵我的超级功能。$b$b更重要的是，为什么你还在和我说话？' WHERE entry=14764; /* Text0_0: Good day, $N.  If you require my services as an auctioneer, I regret to inform you: no.  Only grand master engineers possess the minimum intellectual capacity to interface with my superior functions.$b$bMore importantly, why are you still talking to me? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='卡莱莎，你还活着！赶快找掩蔽所，这些怪物简直……无穷无尽！',Text1_0_loc4='我还在流血？我不能……不能坚持下去了。你有没有见到任何一位大法师？' WHERE entry=14766; /* Text0_0: Kalytha - you\'re still alive! Find some cover, there\'s no end to these ... things! */ /* Text1_0: Am I still bleeding? I can\'t ... I can\'t keep this up much longer. Have you seen any of the archmages? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text2_0_loc4='嗯，我想这是魔法作用的结果。你收获了你所见到的一切……愿艾露恩保佑我们。',Text3_0_loc4='卡莱莎，大法师瑟维恩正在找你。她应该就在附近……' WHERE entry=14766; /* Text2_0: Hmph. I suppose these are the consequences of magic. You reap what you sew ... Elune help us all. */ /* Text3_0: Kalytha! Archmage Selwyn was looking for you. She should be nearby... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text4_0_loc4='这些怪物……它们实在太多了。这么多人都死了！艾萨拉陷入了火海。那些上层精灵到底做了些什么？',Text5_0_loc4='为什么我没有和其他人一起逃走？他们已经将学院包围了。我们被困在了这里。' WHERE entry=14766; /* Text4_0: These creatures ... so many of them. So many dead! Look at Azshara burn. What have the highborne done? */ /* Text5_0: Why didn\'t I flee with the others? They\'ve got the academy surrounded. We\'re trapped here. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='当进攻冰冠堡垒的战斗开始时，我一定会加入。' WHERE entry=14771; /* Text0_0: I will join in the assault upon Icecrown Citadel when the time to strike is upon us. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你好，$c。$B$B现在部落控制着冬拥堡垒。但争夺这座堡垒的战斗已经开始了。快些赶往冬拥湖，帮助我们进行这场战斗吧！',Text0_1_loc4='你好，$c。$B$B现在部落控制着冬拥堡垒。但争夺这座堡垒的战斗已经开始了。快些赶往冬拥湖，帮助我们进行这场战斗吧！' WHERE entry=14777; /* Text0_0: Greetings, $c.$B$BThe Horde currently control Wintergrasp Fortress, but the battle has begun.  Hurry to Wintergrasp and support our forces! */ /* Text0_1: Greetings, $c.$B$BThe Horde currently control Wintergrasp Fortress, but the battle has begun.  Hurry to Wintergrasp and support our forces! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我们照顾这些虫子已经有一段时间了。我希望它们能在斗兽活动中充分发挥作用。要知道，你要打败的不是一条冰虫，而是两条。' WHERE entry=14779; /* Text0_0: We have been tending these worms for some time. I hope they will be fit in time for the ring event of this organization. You must face not one, but two jormungar, after all. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你好，$c。$B$B现在联盟控制着冬拥堡垒。但争夺这座堡垒的战斗已经开始了。快些赶往冬拥湖，帮助我们进行这场战斗吧！',Text0_1_loc4='你好，$c。$B$B现在联盟控制着冬拥堡垒。但争夺这座堡垒的战斗已经开始了。快些赶往冬拥湖，帮助我们进行这场战斗吧！' WHERE entry=14781; /* Text0_0: Greetings, $c.$B$BThe Alliance currently control Wintergrasp Fortress, but the battle has begun!  Hurry to Wintergrasp and support our forces! */ /* Text0_1: Greetings, $c.$B$BThe Alliance currently control Wintergrasp Fortress, but the battle has begun!  Hurry to Wintergrasp and support our forces! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你好，$g先生:女士;！我能为你做些什么？' WHERE entry=14783; /* Text0_0: Good day, $gsir:madam;!  How may I be of assistance? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='在时间和空间构造上出现的这道裂痕看起来非常凶险。许多截然不同的景象从这道裂痕中以可怕的速度闪过。此时此刻，大概只有极为勇敢的人才会跳入其中……' WHERE entry=14785; /* Text0_0: This tear in the fabric of time and space looks ominous.  Different scenes flash by at terrifying speed.  A very brave person might try to jump through at the right time... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='这里并不安全，$n。赶快去找避难所。' WHERE entry=14786; /* Text0_0: It is not safe out here, $N.  Seek shelter before it\'s too late. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你！好啊，就是你！$b$b好好看着我。对你来说，遇到我是你不可多得的幸运。过不了多久，全世界的人都会知道并畏惧威尔弗雷德·菲兹班的名字和我威严的面容！一旦我宏大的召唤最终完成，将没有任何人敢怀疑我的能力！' WHERE entry=14787; /* Text0_0: You! Yes, you!$b$bGaze upon me and treasure this moment of meeting, for soon the world will come to know and fear the name and stern visage of Wilfred Fizzlebang! Once my magnificent summoning is complete, no one will doubt my ability! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你好，$c。$b$b看看你的周围。你有没有认真考虑过所有这些东西的意义？' WHERE entry=14792; /* Text0_0: Greetings, $c.$b$bLook around you. Have you stopped to ponder what all of this means? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='这是破坏行为！我已经被毁了……$b$b这一切的幕后操纵者一定要付出代价！我说话算话……' WHERE entry=14795; /* Text0_0: Sabotage! I\'m ruined....$b$bWhoever\'s behind this will pay! I promise you that.... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='$n? $G先生:女士;，你不是猎人，你是$c。' WHERE entry=14796; /* Text0_0: $N? $G Sir : Ma\'am;, you\'re not a hunter, you\'re a $c. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='哦，我们将一起渡过一段重要的时光。关于猎人之路，我有很多东西要教你。' WHERE entry=14797; /* Text0_0: Oh, you and I are going to have a great time. I have so much to teach you about the ways of the hunter. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我们需要你，$n！这里到处都是狼人！' WHERE entry=14798; /* Text0_0: We need you, $N!  There are worgen everywhere! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='这太恐怖了。我怀疑他们全都死了。$B$B现在我该怎样把卡亚矿石从这里运出去？' WHERE entry=14799; /* Text0_0: It\'s just horrible. I think they\'re all dead.$B$BHow will I get the Kaja\'mite out of there now? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我无法对你进行任何训练，$n。但我需要你帮我对付这些该死的猴子！' WHERE entry=14802; /* Text0_0: I can\'t offer you any training, $N, but I sure could use your help against these damn monkeys! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我喜欢术士！今天我能在你的耳边说一些怎样的黑暗秘密？' WHERE entry=14803; /* Text0_0: There\'s my favorite warlock! What dark secret can I whisper in your ear today? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我们也许只能在上流社会的阴影中做着默默无闻的事情。只有离开这里，在战争的最前线，我们的力量才能得到应有的尊重。',Text0_1_loc4='我们也许只能在上流社会的阴影中做着默默无闻的事情。只有离开这里，在战争的最前线，我们的力量才能得到应有的尊重。' WHERE entry=14804; /* Text0_0: We may operate in the shadows of polite society, but out here on the battlefront our powers are properly respected at last. */ /* Text0_1: We may operate in the shadows of polite society, but out here on the battlefront our powers are properly respected at last. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='嗨，$n$g先生:女士; ，我无法传授你魔法技艺，只能教你如何用手指按摩僵硬的脖子。' WHERE entry=14805; /* Text0_0: Hey there, $g Mr. : Ms.; $N. I can\'t train you in the ways of magic, but all of this finger-waggling means that I can give a mean neck massage. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='这正是个传授神秘技艺的好日子。你是不是也这样想，$n$g先生:女士;？' WHERE entry=14806; /* Text0_0: What a wonderful day for some training in the mystical arts. Wouldn\'t you agree, $g Mr. : Ms.; $N? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='干得漂亮，$n$g先生:女士;。保持这种高水平的发挥吧。' WHERE entry=14807; /* Text0_0: You\'re doing a great job, $g Mr. : Ms.; $N. Keep up the good work. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我预见到了你光辉的未来，我的孩子！今天我要教你些什么？' WHERE entry=14808; /* Text0_0: I see such a bright future for you, my $g boy : girl;! What shall I teach you today? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='那名术士肯定没有召唤末日守卫。你在下一场挑战中将和银色十字军作战。做好接受挑战的准备了吗？' WHERE entry=14813; /* Text0_0: That warlock certainly didn\'t summon a Doomguard! Your next challenge will find you fighting knights of the Argent Crusade. Think you\'re up for the challenge? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='好吧，你做好准备之后，我就会向提里奥发出信号。' WHERE entry=14814; /* Text0_0: Well then, I\'ll give the signal to Tirion when you are ready to go. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='这场战斗真是野蛮残忍至极。我已经有许多年没见到过如此大规模的战斗了！实在是令人震惊！' WHERE entry=14815; /* Text0_0: That fight was savage and brutal. I haven\'t seen a grand melee like that in many years! Amazing! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我已经等不及要看到下一场战斗了！他们似乎已经做好了准备。所以，你们也赶快进行准备吧！' WHERE entry=14816; /* Text0_0: I can\'t wait to see it! They seem ready for another round now, so prepare yourselves! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='为了抓住你就要见到的这个挑战者，我们可是蒙受了很大的伤亡！' WHERE entry=14819; /* Text0_0: We suffered a lot of casualties when capturing your next challenge! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='瓦格里的团队协作能力真是令人震惊。现在我终于明白，为什么只是抓住两只瓦格里就会如此困难。' WHERE entry=14820; /* Text0_0: The Val\'kyrs\'  teamwork is rather astounding. I now see why we had such problems capturing the two of them. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你最好记住！你要面对的是阿尔萨斯最强大的两个瓦格里侍从！' WHERE entry=14821; /* Text0_0: You better believe it! You\'re going to face two of Arthas\' most powerful Val\'kyr lieutenants! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我希望你能够迅速提高！' WHERE entry=14822; /* Text0_0: Well I hope you improve quickly! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='当我作为一名奥格瑞玛卫兵接受训练的时候，萨尔叮嘱我们在对敌作战的时候需要保持耐心和谨慎。$B$B但纳迦时刻都有可能完全占领这座半岛。萨尔也不再是我的酋长了。现在应该是对敌人予以痛击的时候了，$c。' WHERE entry=14826; /* Text0_0: When I trained as a guard in Orgrimmar, Thrall urged us to be patient and cautious when dealing with enemies.$B$BBut Naga threaten to overrun this peninsula, and Thrall is no longer my Warchief. The time has come to shed some blood, $c. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='太好了，今天你们证明了自己是强大的勇士。只要你们和银色十字军并肩作战，我们必将战胜天灾军团！' WHERE entry=14828; /* Text0_0: Splendid, you\'ve proven yourselves as great champions here today. With you fighting alongside the Argent Crusade, victory against the Scourge is inevitable! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='无论给予你怎样的赞扬都不会过份。提里奥肯定想亲自表彰你的功绩。嗨，你有没有突然觉得有些冷？' WHERE entry=14829; /* Text0_0: The praise is well deserved. Tirion will want to praise you himself, shortly. Hey, have you noticed it getting a bit cold all of a sudden? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='持剑的手臂要挺直，$n。' WHERE entry=14831; /* Text0_0: Keep that sword arm straight, $N. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你不是战士！你最好回到安全的地方去……当然，我这样说不是要冒犯你。' WHERE entry=14832; /* Text0_0: You\'re not a warrior!  You\'d better go back inside the perimeter to where it\'s safe... no offense. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='向你致以我最谦恭的道歉，勇士，但你现在已经没有机会完成这次大十字军的试炼了。不过请记住，你和你的同伴每一周都有一次机会再次开始大十字军的试炼。希望你们在这周得到的教训能够让你们向这里的最终的胜利更迈进一步，并帮助你们彻底战胜天灾军团！' WHERE entry=14833; /* Text0_0: My humblest apologies, Champion, but you have run out of opportunities to complete the Trial of the Grand Crusader. As a reminder, you and your fellow adventurers are able to begin the Trial of the Grand Crusader once every week. May the lessons learned this week bring you one step closer to final victory here and against the Scourge! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我们会消灭他们的，$n。那些怪兽敌不过我们。' WHERE entry=14838; /* Text0_0: We\'ll get through this, $N.  We\'ll be wearing these beasts\' pelts when we\'re done. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='一定要非常、非常安静。这里到处都是狼人。' WHERE entry=14839; /* Text0_0: Be very, very quiet.  There\'s worgen everywhere. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我想，我们也许已经激怒他们了。' WHERE entry=14846; /* Text0_0: I think that we might have angered them. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='对于我所保藏的秘密，即使是最肤浅的一瞥，也能够让你发疯，$c。' WHERE entry=14848; /* Text0_0: Even the most superficial glimpse into the secrets I hold would drive you mad, $c. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='什么事，凡人？' WHERE entry=14849; /* Text0_0: Yes, fleshling? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='欢迎，勇士！你是否已经聚集起力量，做好准备，打算迎接大十字军的试炼的挑战了？只有最强大，最聪明的冒险者才能进行这样的试炼。为了参与这次试炼，你们必须首先完成普通的十字军的试炼。' WHERE entry=14850; /* Text0_0: Welcome, champion! Have you gathered your forces in preparation for the challenges of the Trial of the Grand Crusader? Only the most powerful and accomplished of combatants are able to participate in these trials. To participate in these trials, you must have completed the normal Trial of the Crusader. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='大十字军的试炼比十字军的试炼更加困难。这里的每一个敌人都会变得更强大。而且你无法为自己挑选敌人，除非你们曾经战胜过他们。如果在这周之内，你们进行了50次不成功的尝试，就只能等到下周再继续大十字军的试炼了。在成功地完成大十字军的试炼之后，你们将获得另一个宝物匣。现在，是否已经为这一试炼做好了准备？' WHERE entry=14853; /* Text0_0: The Trial of the Grand Crusader is a more difficult version of the Trial of the Crusader. Each encounter is more difficult, and you will not be able to freely attempt the encounters until you win. After 50 unsuccessful attempts, the Trial of the Grand Crusader will end for the week. After successfully completing the Trial of the Grand Crusader, you will receive an additional tribute chest of rewards as compensation. Are you prepared for this trial? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='<基拉格示意你压低声音。>' WHERE entry=14860; /* Text0_0: <Kilag motions you to keep your voice down.> */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我立马就会出发去下一个集结点。' WHERE entry=14863; /* Text0_0: I\'m leaving for the next rendezvous point in a few seconds. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='现在，你已经完成了十字军的试炼，你应该考虑去参加大十字军的试炼了。只有最强大的冒险者才有希望完成这一试炼。但你的努力一定能换回丰厚的报偿。' WHERE entry=14865; /* Text0_0: Now that you have completed the Trial of the Crusader, you should consider returning to take part in the Trial of the Grand Crusader. Only the strongest adventurers can hope to complete the Trial, but you will be rewarded well for your efforts. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='祝贺，请在准备好之后进入这个通向达拉然的传送门！' WHERE entry=14866; /* Text0_0: Congratulations, please take the portal to Dalaran when you\'re ready! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='这只嘉奖箱中的奖励品数量和质量取决于你在大十字军的试炼中进行过多少次不成功的尝试。不成功的尝试越少，得到的奖励就越丰厚。' WHERE entry=14867; /* Text0_0: The quantity and quality of rewards inside the tribute chest is based upon how many unsuccessful attempts you had during the Trial of the Grand Crusader. The fewer unsuccessful attempts, the better the rewards. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你们两个要更加小心！我们的人只有这么点了！' WHERE entry=14868; /* Text0_0: You two be more careful! There are only so many of us! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='什么？！你认为我是矿工出身？$B$B你还能有更糟糕的想法吗？' WHERE entry=14869; /* Text0_0: What?! You think I\'m made out of miners?$B$BHow bad can it be in there? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='拿上钥匙，然后到旋翼机那里去！' WHERE entry=14871; /* Text0_0: Get the keys and then get to that gyrochoppa! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我已经见到了未来，$r。$b$b如果我们不能迅速采取行动，半人马的土地将永远地堕落。' WHERE entry=14873; /* Text0_0: I have been shown the future, $r.$b$bCentaur lands will be forever corrupted if we fail to act quickly. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='啧！这肯定是侏儒建造的。' WHERE entry=14874; /* Text0_0: Bleh! Clearly built by gnomes. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='一位地精？我肯定是眼花了。感谢你，并很高兴见到你，小家伙！' WHERE entry=14875; /* Text0_0: A goblin? I must be seeing things. Throm-Ka and thank you, little one! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='$n，坐下。火已经热了。这可不是给猴子准备的。',Text1_0_loc4='谁能想到，在我们渡过那么多难关之后，却会在这里结束？' WHERE entry=14879; /* Text0_0: $N, sit on down. The fire\'s warm and the monkeys don\'t seem to like it. */ /* Text1_0: Who would\'ve thought we\'d wind up here after everything we\'ve been through? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text2_0_loc4='嗨，看啊，是$n！',Text3_0_loc4='看样子我们被困在这儿了。你能让我们从这里出去吗？' WHERE entry=14879; /* Text2_0: Hey, look guys, it\'s $N! */ /* Text3_0: Looks like we\'re in a pretty tight jam. Think you can get us out of here? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='<大胖哼哼着。>$B$B俺现在是银行家了！' WHERE entry=14881; /* Text0_0: <Gobber grunts.>$B$BMe banker now! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='为了部落的荣耀，$n！' WHERE entry=14886; /* Text0_0: Lok\'tar ogar, $N! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你好！终于见到一个身上没有臭鱼味的人了。我喜欢。' WHERE entry=14888; /* Text0_0: Hello! Someone who doesn\'t smell like fish. I like. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你好，朋友。$b$b相信你很喜欢这个地方吧？' WHERE entry=14897; /* Text0_0: Greetings, friend.$b$bEnjoying the glade, I trust? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你可以在炼金区找到他们。你可以叫他们赫伯特·哈尔希医生和马尔什医生。要小心。',Text0_1_loc4='你可以在炼金区找到他们。你可以叫他们赫伯特·哈尔希医生和马尔什医生。要小心。',Text1_0_loc4='赫伯特·哈尔希医生就是你要找的人。别干傻事。再搞那种无聊的瘟疫，你的脑袋就得搬家。',Text1_1_loc4='赫伯特·哈尔希医生就是你要找的人。别干傻事。再搞那种无聊的瘟疫，你的脑袋就得搬家。' WHERE entry=14899; /* Text0_0: You\'ll find them in the Apothecarium. Names are Doctor Herbert Halsey and Doctor Marsh. Just watch your back. */ /* Text0_1: You\'ll find them in the Apothecarium. Names are Doctor Herbert Halsey and Doctor Marsh. Just watch your back. */ /* Text1_0: Doctor Herbert Halsey is who you want. Just don\'t try anything funny. Any more of that plague nonsense and you\'ll find an axe in uncomfortable places. */ /* Text1_1: Doctor Herbert Halsey is who you want. Just don\'t try anything funny. Any more of that plague nonsense and you\'ll find an axe in uncomfortable places. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='所有的拍卖师都在中央区域。',Text0_1_loc4='所有的拍卖师都在中央区域。',Text1_0_loc4='如果你想看看这里的市场，那么就到中央区域去吧。',Text1_1_loc4='如果你想看看这里的市场，那么就到中央区域去吧。' WHERE entry=14900; /* Text0_0: Head to the central ring; you\'ll find auctioneers stationed there. */ /* Text0_1: Head to the central ring; you\'ll find auctioneers stationed there. */ /* Text1_0: If you want to access the market here, get to the central ring of the city. */ /* Text1_1: If you want to access the market here, get to the central ring of the city. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='银行？就在贸易区中间的塔里。',Text0_1_loc4='银行？就在贸易区中间的塔里。',Text1_0_loc4='就在城的正中央。中心区的小房间。',Text1_1_loc4='就在城的正中央。中心区的小房间。' WHERE entry=14901; /* Text0_0: The bank? It\'s that tower in the middle of the Trade Quarter. */ /* Text0_1: The bank? It\'s that tower in the middle of the Trade Quarter. */ /* Text1_0: It\'s right in the center of the city. The hub of the wheel. */ /* Text1_1: It\'s right in the center of the city. The hub of the wheel. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='纳兹尼克是这里的理发师。他的理发店就开在贸易区的上层区域。',Text0_1_loc4='纳兹尼克是这里的理发师。他的理发店就开在贸易区的上层区域。' WHERE entry=14902; /* Text0_0: Naznik\'s the local barber. He set up shop on the top ring of the Trade Quarter. */ /* Text0_1: Naznik\'s the local barber. He set up shop on the top ring of the Trade Quarter. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='迈克尔·加勒特是幽暗城的蝙蝠管理员。他就在贸易区的上层区域。',Text0_1_loc4='迈克尔·加勒特是幽暗城的蝙蝠管理员。他就在贸易区的上层区域。',Text1_0_loc4='蝙蝠管理员的架子就搭在贸易区的上层区域。远远的就会闻到那股味儿的。',Text1_1_loc4='蝙蝠管理员的架子就搭在贸易区的上层区域。远远的就会闻到那股味儿的。' WHERE entry=14903; /* Text0_0: Michael Garrett tends the Undercity\'s bats. He\'s in the upper ring of the Trade Quarter. */ /* Text0_1: Michael Garrett tends the Undercity\'s bats. He\'s in the upper ring of the Trade Quarter. */ /* Text1_0: The bat handler has his roost on the upper ring of the Trade Quarter. You can\'t miss the smell. */ /* Text1_1: The bat handler has his roost on the upper ring of the Trade Quarter. You can\'t miss the smell. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='战场军官都在皇家区内；你可以在王座厅四周找到他们。',Text0_1_loc4='战场军官都在皇家区内；你可以在王座厅四周找到他们。' WHERE entry=14904; /* Text0_0: The battlemasters are stationed in the Royal Quarter; you\'ll find them around the throne room. */ /* Text0_1: The battlemasters are stationed in the Royal Quarter; you\'ll find them around the throne room. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='詹姆斯·范·布朗特的锻造生意一直不错，就在军事区的内环区域。',Text0_1_loc4='詹姆斯·范·布朗特的锻造生意一直不错，就在军事区的内环区域。',Text1_0_loc4='铁匠在军事区干活，买了他们武器的人马上就可以在旁边试上一试。铁匠就在那里的内环区域。',Text1_1_loc4='铁匠在军事区干活，买了他们武器的人马上就可以在旁边试上一试。铁匠就在那里的内环区域。' WHERE entry=14905; /* Text0_0: James Van Brunt runs a decent forge in the War Quarter. He\'s on the inner ring. */ /* Text0_1: James Van Brunt runs a decent forge in the War Quarter. He\'s on the inner ring. */ /* Text1_0: The blacksmith here works in the War Quarter, close to where his weapons will be put to use. He\'s there on the inner ring. */ /* Text1_1: The blacksmith here works in the War Quarter, close to where his weapons will be put to use. He\'s there on the inner ring. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='贸易区的尤奈斯·伯奇是这里的厨师。是你的肚子在叫，不是我的。',Text0_1_loc4='贸易区的尤奈斯·伯奇是这里的厨师。是你的肚子在叫，不是我的。',Text1_0_loc4='这里的厨师是尤奈斯·伯奇，你可以在贸易区找到她。',Text1_1_loc4='这里的厨师是尤奈斯·伯奇，你可以在贸易区找到她。' WHERE entry=14906; /* Text0_0: Eunice Burch cooks what passes for food here over in the Trade Quarter. It\'s your stomach, not mine. */ /* Text0_1: Eunice Burch cooks what passes for food here over in the Trade Quarter. It\'s your stomach, not mine. */ /* Text1_0: The cook around here is in the Trade Quarter. Her name\'s Eunice Burch. */ /* Text1_1: The cook around here is in the Trade Quarter. Her name\'s Eunice Burch. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='拉文尼亚·克洛文是这里的附魔师。他的店就开在炼金区的内环区域。',Text0_1_loc4='拉文尼亚·克洛文是这里的附魔师。他的店就开在炼金区的内环区域。',Text1_0_loc4='炼金区内环区域的拉文尼亚·克洛文可以教你有关附魔的知识。',Text1_1_loc4='炼金区内环区域的拉文尼亚·克洛文可以教你有关附魔的知识。' WHERE entry=14907; /* Text0_0: Lavinia Crowe\'s the local enchanter. She\'s set up shop on the inner ring of the Apothecarium. */ /* Text0_1: Lavinia Crowe\'s the local enchanter. She\'s set up shop on the inner ring of the Apothecarium. */ /* Text1_0: If you want to learn enchanting, go find Lavinia Crowe on the inner ring of the Apothecarium. */ /* Text1_1: If you want to learn enchanting, go find Lavinia Crowe on the inner ring of the Apothecarium. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='弗兰克林·洛伊德是这里的工程师。他平时都在盗贼区外环区域修修补补。',Text0_1_loc4='弗兰克林·洛伊德是这里的工程师。他平时都在盗贼区外环区域修修补补。',Text1_0_loc4='听着，如果你要去见盗贼区外环区域的那些工程师，那就看好标记。',Text1_1_loc4='听着，如果你要去见盗贼区外环区域的那些工程师，那就看好标记。' WHERE entry=14908; /* Text0_0: The engineer here is called Franklin Lloyd. He tinkers in the Rogues\' Quarter, on the outer ring. */ /* Text0_1: The engineer here is called Franklin Lloyd. He tinkers in the Rogues\' Quarter, on the outer ring. */ /* Text1_0: Look, if you want to go talk to those engineers on the outer ring of the Rogues\' Quarter, it\'s your hide. */ /* Text1_1: Look, if you want to go talk to those engineers on the outer ring of the Rogues\' Quarter, it\'s your hide. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你可以找玛丽·艾塔斯谈一谈。她就呆在盗贼区的内环区域。',Text0_1_loc4='你可以找玛丽·艾塔斯谈一谈。她就呆在盗贼区的内环区域。',Text1_0_loc4='即使是行尸走肉也需要维护自己的身体。玛丽·艾塔斯精通此道。她就在盗贼区的内环区域。',Text1_1_loc4='即使是行尸走肉也需要维护自己的身体。玛丽·艾塔斯精通此道。她就在盗贼区的内环区域。' WHERE entry=14909; /* Text0_0: Mary Edras is the one you want. She\'s set up at the inner ring of the Rogues\' Quarter. */ /* Text0_1: Mary Edras is the one you want. She\'s set up at the inner ring of the Rogues\' Quarter. */ /* Text1_0: Even the walking dead need to mend themselves. Mary Edras handles it here. She\'s in the Rogues\' Quarter, on the inner ring. */ /* Text1_1: Even the walking dead need to mend themselves. Mary Edras handles it here. She\'s in the Rogues\' Quarter, on the inner ring. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='疯狂的渔夫就在魔法区的港口那。',Text0_1_loc4='疯狂的渔夫就在魔法区的港口那。',Text1_0_loc4='我不知道阿曼德·克伦威尔在试图追赶什么，不过他已经到了魔法区的码头。',Text1_1_loc4='我不知道阿曼德·克伦威尔在试图追赶什么，不过他已经到了魔法区的码头。' WHERE entry=14910; /* Text0_0: The crazy fisherman is on the dock in the Magic Quarter. */ /* Text0_1: The crazy fisherman is on the dock in the Magic Quarter. */ /* Text1_0: I don\'t know what he\'s trying to catch there, but Armand Cromwell is on the dock in the Magic Quarter. */ /* Text1_1: I don\'t know what he\'s trying to catch there, but Armand Cromwell is on the dock in the Magic Quarter. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='克里斯托弗·德库尔是这里的公会注册员。他的办公区设在贸易区东侧平台。',Text0_1_loc4='克里斯托弗·德库尔是这里的公会注册员。他的办公区设在贸易区东侧平台。',Text1_0_loc4='公会注册员在贸易区办公。你可以在东侧平台找到他。',Text1_1_loc4='公会注册员在贸易区办公。你可以在东侧平台找到他。' WHERE entry=14911; /* Text0_0: The guild master is Christopher Drakul. He\'s on the eastern platform in the Trade Quarter. */ /* Text0_1: The guild master is Christopher Drakul. He\'s on the eastern platform in the Trade Quarter. */ /* Text1_0: The guild master handles his business in the Trade Quarter. He\'s up on the eastern platform. */ /* Text1_1: The guild master handles his business in the Trade Quarter. He\'s up on the eastern platform. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='马尔萨·奥列斯塔是这里的草药学家。你可以在炼金区的内环区域找到她。',Text0_1_loc4='马尔萨·奥列斯塔是这里的草药学家。你可以在炼金区的内环区域找到她。',Text1_0_loc4='去炼金区的内环区域，那里的马尔萨·奥列斯塔可以教你有关草药学的知识。',Text1_1_loc4='去炼金区的内环区域，那里的马尔萨·奥列斯塔可以教你有关草药学的知识。' WHERE entry=14912; /* Text0_0: The herbalist around here is Martha Alliestar. She\'s over on the inner ring of the Apothecarium. */ /* Text0_1: The herbalist around here is Martha Alliestar. She\'s over on the inner ring of the Apothecarium. */ /* Text1_0: Head to the Apothecarium\'s inner ring. Martha Alliestar is there, and she\'ll instruct you in herbalism. */ /* Text1_1: Head to the Apothecarium\'s inner ring. Martha Alliestar is there, and she\'ll instruct you in herbalism. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='旅馆——如果算得上的话——在贸易区的上层区域。那里连床铺都没有。',Text0_1_loc4='旅馆——如果算得上的话——在贸易区的上层区域。那里连床铺都没有。',Text1_0_loc4='贸易区上层区域的诺曼是这里的旅店老板，他的店只不过是几面满是灰尘和裂缝的墙壁。',Text1_1_loc4='贸易区上层区域的诺曼是这里的旅店老板，他的店只不过是几面满是灰尘和裂缝的墙壁。' WHERE entry=14913; /* Text0_0: The inn - if you can call it that - is on the upper ring of the Trade Quarter. They don\'t even have beds. */ /* Text0_1: The inn - if you can call it that - is on the upper ring of the Trade Quarter. They don\'t even have beds. */ /* Text1_0: Innkeeper Norman keeps a dusty crack in the wall he calls an inn on the upper ring of the Trade Quarter. */ /* Text1_1: Innkeeper Norman keeps a dusty crack in the wall he calls an inn on the upper ring of the Trade Quarter. */
