UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='如果要钥匙，你可以找盗贼区的沃特尔·索雷夫谈一谈，不过要小心。',Text0_1_loc4='如果要钥匙，你可以找盗贼区的沃特尔·索雷夫谈一谈，不过要小心。' WHERE entry=14916; /* Text0_0: If you need keys, talk to Walter Soref in the Rogues\' Quarter, but watch yourself. */ /* Text0_1: If you need keys, talk to Walter Soref in the Rogues\' Quarter, but watch yourself. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='法师？他们都在魔法区的中央建筑中。你得机灵点儿才能找得到。',Text0_1_loc4='法师？他们都在魔法区的中央建筑中。你得机灵点儿才能找得到。',Text1_0_loc4='在魔法区的外环区域你能找到一座大型、阶梯式的建筑。法师们都在那里。',Text1_1_loc4='在魔法区的外环区域你能找到一座大型、阶梯式的建筑。法师们都在那里。' WHERE entry=14917; /* Text0_0: Mages? They\'re in the Magic Quarter, in the central building. Thought you\'d be smart enough to figure that out. */ /* Text0_1: Mages? They\'re in the Magic Quarter, in the central building. Thought you\'d be smart enough to figure that out. */ /* Text1_0: On the outer ring of the Magic Quarter you\'ll find a large, stepped building. That\'s where the mages hide. */ /* Text1_1: On the outer ring of the Magic Quarter you\'ll find a large, stepped building. That\'s where the mages hide. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='邮箱在贸易区的棺材铺前面，也有人管那里叫旅馆。',Text0_1_loc4='邮箱在贸易区的棺材铺前面，也有人管那里叫旅馆。',Text1_0_loc4='邮箱吗？你可以到城中央上层区域的旅店看看，那里有邮箱。',Text1_1_loc4='邮箱吗？你可以到城中央上层区域的旅店看看，那里有邮箱。' WHERE entry=14918; /* Text0_0: The mailbox is in the Trade Quarter by that coffin storage closet they call an inn. */ /* Text0_1: The mailbox is in the Trade Quarter by that coffin storage closet they call an inn. */ /* Text1_0: Mailbox? You want to head to the inn in the center of the city\'s upper ring. It\'s right there. */ /* Text1_1: Mailbox? You want to head to the inn in the center of the city\'s upper ring. It\'s right there. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='和军事区内环区域的布罗姆·基里安谈一谈，他可以教你如何采矿。',Text0_1_loc4='和军事区内环区域的布罗姆·基里安谈一谈，他可以教你如何采矿。',Text1_0_loc4='这里的采矿训练师在军事区的内环区域工作。他的名字叫布罗姆·基里安。',Text1_1_loc4='这里的采矿训练师在军事区的内环区域工作。他的名字叫布罗姆·基里安。' WHERE entry=14919; /* Text0_0: If you want to learn to mine, talk to Brom Killian at the inner ring of the War Quarter. */ /* Text0_1: If you want to learn to mine, talk to Brom Killian at the inner ring of the War Quarter. */ /* Text1_0: The miner here works in the War Quarter on the inner ring. His name\'s Brom Killian. */ /* Text1_1: The miner here works in the War Quarter on the inner ring. His name\'s Brom Killian. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='找圣骑士你得去皇家区。那些有几个精灵可以教你。',Text0_1_loc4='找圣骑士你得去皇家区。那些有几个精灵可以教你。' WHERE entry=14920; /* Text0_0: If you want to find a paladin, you\'ll have to go to the Royal Quarter. There\'s some elf there who can teach you. */ /* Text0_1: If you want to find a paladin, you\'ll have to go to the Royal Quarter. There\'s some elf there who can teach you. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='牧师们都在军事区的外环区域。',Text0_1_loc4='牧师们都在军事区的外环区域。',Text1_0_loc4='去军事区外环区域看看吧。那里的牧师努力确保没有哪个断掉的肋骨长时间得不到修复。',Text1_1_loc4='去军事区外环区域看看吧。那里的牧师努力确保没有哪个断掉的肋骨长时间得不到修复。' WHERE entry=14921; /* Text0_0: The priests are located on the outer ring of the War Quarter. */ /* Text0_1: The priests are located on the outer ring of the War Quarter. */ /* Text1_0: Head to the War Quarter. The priests are there on the outer ring making sure no limb remains unattached for long. */ /* Text1_1: Head to the War Quarter. The priests are there on the outer ring making sure no limb remains unattached for long. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='盗贼们都呆在盗贼区。就这么简单。你可以在外环区域找到他们。',Text0_1_loc4='盗贼们都呆在盗贼区。就这么简单。你可以在外环区域找到他们。',Text1_0_loc4='你可以在盗贼区外环区域找到那些潜行者。',Text1_1_loc4='你可以在盗贼区外环区域找到那些潜行者。' WHERE entry=14922; /* Text0_0: The rogues are in the Rogues\' Quarter. Simple as that. Look for them on the outer ring. */ /* Text0_1: The rogues are in the Rogues\' Quarter. Simple as that. Look for them on the outer ring. */ /* Text1_0: Go to the outer ring of the Rogues\' Quarter if you want to find rogues. */ /* Text1_1: Go to the outer ring of the Rogues\' Quarter if you want to find rogues. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='基里安·哈根是这里的剥皮训练师。他就在盗贼区的内环区域。',Text0_1_loc4='基里安·哈根是这里的剥皮训练师。他就在盗贼区的内环区域。',Text1_0_loc4='如果你想学习剥皮，就要前往盗贼区。剥皮训练师的铺位就在内环区域。',Text1_1_loc4='基里安·哈根在盗贼区传授剥皮的技能。' WHERE entry=14923; /* Text0_0: The skinner here is named Killian Hagey. He works in the Rogues\' Quarter on the inner ring. */ /* Text0_1: The skinner here is named Killian Hagey. He works in the Rogues\' Quarter on the inner ring. */ /* Text1_0: If you want to learn how to skin things, head to the Rogues\' Quarter. The skinner has his place on the inner ring. */ /* Text1_1: Us have skinning hook.  We get it from Killian Hagey who teach us how to skin kills.  You have nice skin.  You find him on inner ring of Rogues\' Quarter. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='如果你真的想把宠物委托给某个亡灵，那你可以和安雅·玛尔雷谈谈，他就呆在贸易区上层的旅馆里。',Text0_1_loc4='如果你真的想把宠物委托给某个亡灵，那你可以和安雅·玛尔雷谈谈，他就呆在贸易区上层的旅馆里。',Text1_0_loc4='你可以同安雅·玛尔雷谈一谈，他就在贸易区上层的旅店旁边。我并不建议你这样做，不过它们毕竟是你的宠物。',Text1_1_loc4='你可以同安雅·玛尔雷谈一谈，他就在贸易区上层的旅店旁边。我并不建议你这样做，不过它们毕竟是你的宠物。' WHERE entry=14924; /* Text0_0: If you really trust some undead with your pets, you can talk to Anya Maulray at the inn on the upper ring of the Trade Quarter. */ /* Text0_1: If you really trust some undead with your pets, you can talk to Anya Maulray at the inn on the upper ring of the Trade Quarter. */ /* Text1_0: You can talk to Anya Maulray up by the inn on the upper ring of the Trade Quarter. I wouldn\'t recommend it, but they\'re your pets. */ /* Text1_1: You can talk to Anya Maulray up by the inn on the upper ring of the Trade Quarter. I wouldn\'t recommend it, but they\'re your pets. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='这里的裁缝叫乔瑟夫·格里高利。他就在魔法区的内环区域。',Text0_1_loc4='这里的裁缝叫乔瑟夫·格里高利。他就在魔法区的内环区域。',Text1_0_loc4='先到魔法区，然后朝内环区域走，裁缝店就在那里。',Text1_1_loc4='先到魔法区，然后朝内环区域走，裁缝店就在那里。' WHERE entry=14925; /* Text0_0: The tailor here\'s Josef Gregorian. He\'s in the Magic Quarter on the inner ring. */ /* Text0_1: The tailor here\'s Josef Gregorian. He\'s in the Magic Quarter on the inner ring. */ /* Text1_0: Go to the Magic Quarter and head to the inner ring. The tailor\'s there. */ /* Text1_1: Go to the Magic Quarter and head to the inner ring. The tailor\'s there. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你竟然有胆量问我有关术士的事。到魔法区的外环区域看看吧，现在给我消失。',Text0_1_loc4='你竟然有胆量问我有关术士的事。到魔法区的外环区域看看吧，现在给我消失。',Text1_0_loc4='你可以在魔法区的主建筑区域找到那些术士，我希望告诉你这些不会引起什么麻烦。',Text1_1_loc4='你可以在魔法区的主建筑区域找到那些术士，我希望告诉你这些不会引起什么麻烦。' WHERE entry=14926; /* Text0_0: You have guts asking me about warlocks. Go to the Magic Quarter\'s outer ring and get out of my sight. */ /* Text0_1: You have guts asking me about warlocks. Go to the Magic Quarter\'s outer ring and get out of my sight. */ /* Text1_0: You\'ll find the warlocks in the Magic Quarter\'s main building, but I better not hear of any trouble that comes of this. */ /* Text1_1: You\'ll find the warlocks in the Magic Quarter\'s main building, but I better not hear of any trouble that comes of this. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='战士都在军事区外环区域进行操练。',Text0_1_loc4='战士都在军事区外环区域进行操练。',Text1_0_loc4='你可以在军事区的外环区域找到那些战士。',Text1_1_loc4='你可以在军事区的外环区域找到那些战士。' WHERE entry=14927; /* Text0_0: The warriors are in the War Quarter, practicing on the outer ring. */ /* Text0_1: The warriors are in the War Quarter, practicing on the outer ring. */ /* Text1_0: In the War Quarter is where you\'ll find the warriors. Head to the outer ring there. */ /* Text1_1: In the War Quarter is where you\'ll find the warriors. Head to the outer ring there. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='到军事区内环区域找到阿基巴德，他可以教你如何某些使用武器。',Text0_1_loc4='到军事区内环区域找到阿基巴德，他可以教你如何某些使用武器。',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴有人愿意学点儿真正有用的东西。到军事区的内环区域去找阿基巴德吧。',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴有人愿意学点儿真正有用的东西。到军事区的内环区域去找阿基巴德吧。' WHERE entry=14928; /* Text0_0: If you want to learn how to wield weapons, go to Archibald on the inner ring of the War Quarter. */ /* Text0_1: If you want to learn how to wield weapons, go to Archibald on the inner ring of the War Quarter. */ /* Text1_0: Good to see someone wanting to learn something useful. Head to Archibald on the inner ring of the War Quarter. */ /* Text1_1: Good to see someone wanting to learn something useful. Head to Archibald on the inner ring of the War Quarter. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你想离开这，这我不怪你。先到最顶层，然后朝废墟的北面走。坐上两座塔那的地精飞艇就可以离开了。',Text0_1_loc4='你想离开这，这我不怪你。先到最顶层，然后朝废墟的北面走。坐上两座塔那的地精飞艇就可以离开了。',Text1_0_loc4='飞艇塔就在幽暗城的北面。',Text1_1_loc4='飞艇塔就在幽暗城的北面。' WHERE entry=14929; /* Text0_0: I don\'t blame you for wanting to get out of here. Go up topside and head north of the ruins. The zeppelins leave from the two towers there. */ /* Text0_1: I don\'t blame you for wanting to get out of here. Go up topside and head north of the ruins. The zeppelins leave from the two towers there. */ /* Text1_0: The zeppelin towers are just north of the Undercity. */ /* Text1_1: The zeppelin towers are just north of the Undercity. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='在这看到兽人感到意外吧？用不着这样。$b$b需要有人看着那些被遗忘者。如果从一开始我们就好好盯着，或许天谴之门的事根本就不会发生。',Text0_1_loc4='在这看到兽人感到意外吧？用不着这样。$b$b需要有人看着那些被遗忘者。如果从一开始我们就好好盯着，或许天谴之门的事根本就不会发生。',Text1_0_loc4='希望你要找的不是那些憎恶。炼金师没有一个靠得住，他们造出来的那些在大厅里巡逻的东西也一样。真正保卫这里安全的是我们。',Text1_1_loc4='希望你要找的不是那些憎恶。炼金师没有一个靠得住，他们造出来的那些在大厅里巡逻的东西也一样。真正保卫这里安全的是我们。' WHERE entry=14931; /* Text0_0: Surprised to see an orc here? Don\'t be.$b$bThe forsaken need watching. If we\'d been paying closer attention from the start, maybe the Wrath Gate wouldn\'t have happened. */ /* Text0_1: Surprised to see an orc here? Don\'t be.$b$bThe forsaken need watching. If we\'d been paying closer attention from the start, maybe the Wrath Gate wouldn\'t have happened. */ /* Text1_0: Hope you\'re not looking for those abominations. The apothecaries can\'t be trusted, and that means none of their little constructs patrolling the halls. We\'re here to keep things safe. */ /* Text1_1: Hope you\'re not looking for those abominations. The apothecaries can\'t be trusted, and that means none of their little constructs patrolling the halls. We\'re here to keep things safe. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text2_0_loc4='Lok\'tar。不要在这里做出任何可疑的行为。如果那些亡灵打算加入部落，他们就得接受我们的监视。',Text2_1_loc4='Lok\'tar。不要在这里做出任何可疑的行为。如果那些亡灵打算加入部落，他们就得接受我们的监视。' WHERE entry=14931; /* Text2_0: Lok\'tar. Don\'t try anything suspicious around here. If these undead are going to be part of the Horde, they\'re going to mind themselves under our watch. */ /* Text2_1: Lok\'tar. Don\'t try anything suspicious around here. If these undead are going to be part of the Horde, they\'re going to mind themselves under our watch. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='速度要快，$r。' WHERE entry=14932; /* Text0_0: Make it quick, $r. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='怎么了？骨头堆。在找人吗？这里只有我，要买东西就快点儿。',Text0_1_loc4='怎么了？骨头堆。在找人吗？这里只有我，要买东西就快点儿。',Text1_0_loc4='我敢说你们这些无赖一定觉得自己在天谴之门干得很漂亮，对吧？游戏结束了。我们来就是要阻止你们的一切行为。',Text1_1_loc4='我敢说你们这些无赖一定觉得自己在天谴之门干得很漂亮，对吧？游戏结束了。我们来就是要阻止你们的一切行为。' WHERE entry=14933; /* Text0_0: What\'s wrong, bonebag? Looking for someone else? I\'m all you\'ve got now, so if you want something, make it quick. */ /* Text0_1: What\'s wrong, bonebag? Looking for someone else? I\'m all you\'ve got now, so if you want something, make it quick. */ /* Text1_0: I bet you rotters thought you were pretty clever at the Wrath Gate, didn\'t you? Playtime\'s over. We\'re here to make sure you don\'t try anything. */ /* Text1_1: I bet you rotters thought you were pretty clever at the Wrath Gate, didn\'t you? Playtime\'s over. We\'re here to make sure you don\'t try anything. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text2_0_loc4='我会告诉你都该知道些什么，但这并不表示我有多么愿意。我们一直在监视着你和你的同类。',Text2_1_loc4='我会告诉你都该知道些什么，但这并不表示我有多么愿意。我们一直在监视着你和你的同类。' WHERE entry=14933; /* Text2_0: I\'ll tell you what you need to know, but I don\'t have to like it. We\'re watching you and your kind. */ /* Text2_1: I\'ll tell you what you need to know, but I don\'t have to like it. We\'re watching you and your kind. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='坑里臭气熏天，还有一群蛇围着我。不过我来这是有事要做的。$b$b自从普特雷斯在天谴之门上演了一出好戏，酋长便不再信任那些人，而是离他们远远的。这就是为什么我们会在这里。那些药剂师离了我什么都做不了。' WHERE entry=14934; /* Text0_0: This pit stinks and I\'m surrounded by snakes, but I\'m here to do a job.$b$bEver since Putress pulled his stunt at the Wrath Gate, the Warchief doesn\'t trust these people as far as he can throw them. That\'s why we\'re here. The apothecaries can\'t do a thing without me. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我没有能在吉尔尼斯城保护我的人民。但命运似乎是要给我第二次机会，$n。我不会再失败了！' WHERE entry=14938; /* Text0_0: I failed to defend my people in Gilneas City.  It seems the fates have given me a second chance, $N.  I will not fail again! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我们的新…客人对我们的工作的确有些拖累，不过在从事种族灭绝工作中保持机警是没错的。也许，在适当的时候他们会认识到普特雷斯就是个倒霉的异类，并且允许我们安安稳稳地继续我们的工作。' WHERE entry=14940; /* Text0_0: It\'s true our new... guests are limiting our work somewhat, but it is only natural to be wary when a genocidal attempt is made. Perhaps in time they will be convinced that Putress was an unfortunate anomaly and allow us to continue our work in peace. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='这是什么，$c？恶魔不在了，这里有很多东西我要看。总得有人来整理这些文书，确保普特雷斯的事不再发生。$b$b我真是走运。' WHERE entry=14941; /* Text0_0: What is it, $c? I\'ve got a lot to see to around here now that the demon\'s gone. Someone has to shuffle the paperwork and make sure we don\'t see another lapse like the one with Putress.$b$bLucky me. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='<格蒙刚的声音发出隆隆的回音，让你感到耳鼓震痛，脚下的地面也在一阵阵颤抖。>$B$B你好，小软人。$B$B你们总是喜欢四处乱窜。来，和我休息一会儿吧。' WHERE entry=14945; /* Text0_0: <Gormungan\'s voice booms deep from within, hurting your ears and reverberating in the very ground beneath your feet.>$B$BHallo, softling.$B$BYour kind dashes about, always running, never stopping. Rest with me a while. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='哈——啊哈！食物？我们可不吃这种有汁水的东西，朋友，除非他们来伤害我们。我们吃的是岩石、石块和沙砾。不过有时候我也觉得嚼嚼小骨头是一种不错的调剂。$B$B<格蒙刚用一只巨大的手举起一块巨石。将你带来的尸体摁在上面，就好象在蛋糕上放一块水果。然后在一阵宏亮的“嘎吱”声中，他把那块石头嚼碎，咽下了肚。>' WHERE entry=14946; /* Text0_0: Ha - harrrum! Food? We don\'t eat squishlings, friend, not unless they aggravate us. We eat rocks and stones and earth. Though I sometimes find the crunch of bones makes a delightful seasoning.$B$B<Gormungan lifts up a boulder and, with one enormous hand, smashes the corpses you\'ve given him onto the boulder as one would put icing on a cupcake. He crunches his treat, rumbling happily.> */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='艾萨莱特水晶？你们这些软弱的家伙倒是喜欢乱起新名字。这个“艾萨莱特水晶”又是什么？' WHERE entry=14947; /* Text0_0: Azsharite? You soft ones come up with new names for everything. What is this "azsharite?" */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='<格蒙刚的笑声浑厚而悠长。大地也随着他的声音在颤抖，远处细碎的砾石在不住地滑动。>$B$B哦……哈！哈！哈！小朋友，我很抱歉。我想，我们一族的行为方式和你总会有些区别。' WHERE entry=14948; /* Text0_0: <Gormungan\'s laugh, deep and long, rumbles the ground and causes distant rockslides.>$B$BOh - hah! Harroooo - Ha harum! Little friend, I am sorry. I suppose my kind does not pick up after ourselves as you do. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='它来自——嗯——你们的语言是怎样说的？嗯。我要说，我们一族可是没有厕所的。你明白吗？' WHERE entry=14949; /* Text0_0: It comes from - harum - what is your word for it? Harrrm. Let us say that my kind does not have bathrooms. Do you understand? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='看起来是这样。你和你的朋友们可以随意收集这些东西。我想，它可能是有些用处。我们可不是经常会有这些东西的。' WHERE entry=14950; /* Text0_0: It would seem so. You and your friends are welcome to as much as you can find. I suppose it\'s very potent. We don\'t need to go that often. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我们的生命进程不像你们那样快，我柔软的朋友！一个健康的巨人每十年会吃三顿饭。不过我每两年会吃一次小点心。我们每15到25年会上一次厕所……拉肚子除外。' WHERE entry=14951; /* Text0_0: We don\'t live our lives as quickly as you do, my mushy friend. A healthy giant eats three square meals a decade, although I am known to indulge in a snack every couple of years. We\'ll go to the bathroom every 15 to 25 years... barring any tummy trouble. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='<格蒙刚和善地喷了一下鼻息。>$B$B 哈！我还没有这样细致地考虑过自己的个人习惯呢。你们总是让我感到吃惊。再见，朋友，祝你好运……无论你要找的是什么。' WHERE entry=14952; /* Text0_0: <Gormungan emits a good-natured snort.>$B$BHaaarrum! I have never had my personal habits scrutinized so. Your kind never ceases to surprise me. Farewell, friend, and good luck with ... whatever it is you are on about. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='听着，$n，我不能让别人看见我在和你说话。你不再是贸易大王眼中的红人了，而我则需要为我的未来考虑。$B$B你明白我的意思，对吧，宝贝儿？另外，我现在和小甜甜在一起了。' WHERE entry=14956; /* Text0_0: Listen, $N, I can\'t be seen talking with you. You\'re not exactly at the top of the Trade Prince\'s list these days and I need to think about my future.$B$BYou understand, right, babe? Besides, I\'m with Candy now. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='<贸易大王用低微的耳语说道。>$B$B不管你是否能逃掉，绝不要以为我会忘记你这个卑微的家伙，$n。$B$B不必再为你那颗$g简单:漂亮;的脑袋而担心了。记住，我很快就会进行复仇！$B$B到时候，你将羡慕那些能成为我的奴隶的人。你逃不出我的手心。' WHERE entry=14959; /* Text0_0: <The trade prince lowers his voice to barely a whisper.>$B$BDon\'t think for a moment that I\'ve forgotten how much I despise you, $N, rescue or not.$B$BDon\'t worry your $g simple : pretty; head. I\'ll get my revenge soon enough, mark my words!$B$BYou\'ll fare far worse than being my slave. There\'ll be no escape for you this time. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我们欠你的永远都还不清，$n。' WHERE entry=14961; /* Text0_0: We owe you a debt that will be hard to repay, $N. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='又见到你了，柔软的小朋友。这次你要做什么？' WHERE entry=14964; /* Text0_0: Hallo again, soft little friend. What\'s that you have there? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='嗨，$g兄弟:小姐;。乘坐火箭吧！耶！' WHERE entry=14965; /* Text0_0: Hey, $g bro : lady;. Rocket ride! Yeah! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='<格蒙刚带着怀疑的神情看着这团软软的东西，然后又嗅了嗅它，便气恼地将它捏塑成一只地精的样子。>$B$B我怀疑你那些小绿人朋友没想让你做好事儿。去告诉他们，我们巨人可不是任人玩弄的。$B$B<为了表达他的意思，格蒙刚在把他刚做成的地精雕像交给你的时候，又用力拧断了它的脑袋。>' WHERE entry=14967; /* Text0_0: <Gormungan eyes the laxative with suspicion, then sniffs it. With visible irritation, he begins smooshing and molding the laxative into the shape of a goblin.>$B$BI suspect your little green friends are putting you up to no good. Please explain to them that we giants are not to be toyed with.$B$B<To demonstrate his point, Gormungan twists the head off of his chocolaty goblin statue before handing it back to you.> */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='嗯，什么？' WHERE entry=14971; /* Text0_0: Hum - Wha? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='这套衣服真漂亮。专程为了聚会穿的吧！' WHERE entry=14976; /* Text0_0: Lovely outfit. Dressed for the part! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='<这是一段手写的文字：>$B$B          秘密实验室档案馆$B     X.尼泽柏克，实验室主管$B$B$B请按蜂鸣器呼叫服务。' WHERE entry=14977; /* Text0_0: <A hand-lettered sign reads:>$B$B          Secret Lab Archives$B     X. Nizzlebex, Lab Director$B$B$BPlease ring buzzer for service. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='嗨，$n。我知道这挺糟的，但贸易大王的船骸暂时就是我们的家了。' WHERE entry=14981; /* Text0_0: Hey there, $N. I know, it\'s not much, but the trade prince\'s wreck is home for now. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我早知道我会受到这种冷遇。长久以来我们一直在隐居，因为我们必须要与族人分离。$b$b那段时间已经过去。不管这颗幼树之荫下的居民是否会接受我们，上层精灵们都要摒弃过去的身份，从黑暗中返回光明。' WHERE entry=14984; /* Text0_0: I suppose I should not be surprised at this cold reception. We have long been in hiding, and the separation from our brethren was necessary.$b$bThat time, however, is done. Whether the residents of this young tree come to accept us or not, the Highborne are returning to light, and we will not turn our backs on what we are. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='这真的是个好主意吗？' WHERE entry=14985; /* Text0_0: Is this really a good idea? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我的兄弟和我乘船几天时间就能到达北吉尔尼斯。当然，我们得先完成修理工作。' WHERE entry=14986; /* Text0_0: My brothers and I can reach northern Gilneas by boat in a matter of days.  As soon as we finish the repairs, that is. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='哦，别盯着我不放。我只是个传话儿的。死亡猎手的领袖当然不会蠢到亲自到这来送死。历史不会重演的。' WHERE entry=14987; /* Text0_0: Oh, pay no attention to me. I\'m just a messenger. The leader of the Deathstalkers certainly wouldn\'t be stupid enough to stand here on the dais waiting to be gutted. No need for history to repeat itself. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='刚出油锅，又入烈火，是吗，$n？' WHERE entry=14988; /* Text0_0: Out of the frying pan and into the fire, eh $N? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我现在还有点耐心。但如果他们不尽快让火箭弹射器正常工作，有人可就要吃我的暗影箭了！' WHERE entry=14990; /* Text0_0: I\'ve been patient up to this point, but if they don\'t get that rocket sling working soon, I\'m going to shadow bolt someone! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我现在还有点耐心。但如果他们不尽快让火箭弹射器正常工作，有人可就要吃我的暗影箭了！$B$B需要训练吗，$n？' WHERE entry=14991; /* Text0_0: I\'ve been patient up to this point, but if they don\'t get that rocket sling working soon, I\'m going to shadow bolt someone!$B$BNeed some training, $N? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我看见戴姆维克骑过这东西。所以我宁可使用缓落术。不过我还不知道这法术该怎么用。' WHERE entry=14992; /* Text0_0: I saw Dampwick ride across on that thing. I\'d rather use a Slow Fall spell, but I don\'t know that one yet. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='干得好，$n！这是不是很令人兴奋？我很想知道，下一座岛会是什么样？' WHERE entry=14994; /* Text0_0: Good job, $N! Isn\'t this all very exciting? I wonder what the next island will be like? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='干得好，$n！这是不是很令人兴奋？我很想知道，下一座岛会是什么样？$B$B我能教你些新东西吗？' WHERE entry=14995; /* Text0_0: Good job, $N! Isn\'t this all very exciting? I wonder what the next island will be like?$B$BCan I teach you anything new? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='全能战士NX-01型当前处于离线状态。' WHERE entry=15000; /* Text0_0: Warrior-Matic NX-01 is currently offline. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='全能战士NX-01型在线。$B$B请塞入硬币，接受训练。' WHERE entry=15001; /* Text0_0: Warrior-Matic NX-01 online.$B$BPlease insert coins for training. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你会想看看幽暗城的模样。它就坐落在南边的旧洛丹伦废墟，你会找到一个下行的升降梯。等你到了，幽暗城的卫兵会给你更详细的指引。',Text0_1_loc4='你会想看看幽暗城的模样。它就坐落在南边的旧洛丹伦废墟，你会找到一个下行的升降梯。等你到了，幽暗城的卫兵会给你更详细的指引。' WHERE entry=15005; /* Text0_0: You\'ll want to look in the Undercity.  In the old Ruins of Lordaeron, south of here, you\'ll find an elevator down. Once you\'re there, ask an Undercity Guardian for further directions. */ /* Text0_1: You\'ll want to look in the Undercity.  In the old Ruins of Lordaeron, south of here, you\'ll find an elevator down. Once you\'re there, ask an Undercity Guardian for further directions. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='卡亚矿……你是否知道，就是这种传说中的玩意儿，帮助地精全族成为了炼金术和工程学的究极大师？！$B$B正是这种材料帮助我们推翻了压迫我们的丛林巨魔，控制了科赞——愿她得到安息——它是最珍贵的矿石！$B$B嗨，你不会是认为卡亚矿石对那些猴子也起了作用吧？' WHERE entry=15007; /* Text0_0: Kaja\'mite... you know, the stuff that legend holds helped the entire goblin race to evolve into the ultimate masters of alchemy and engineering?!$B$BIt\'s the stuff that helped us to overthrow our jungle troll oppressors, to take control of Kezan -- may she rest in peace -- and is the most valuable ore in all of existence!$B$BHey, you don\'t think that it\'s having any effect on those monkeys do you? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='散布在这一地区的废墟是暗夜精灵文明发展到顶峰时期留下的遗迹。对于研究奥术的人来说，它们是蕴含着无数珍贵信息的宝藏。$B$B看样子，一队最不同寻常的暗夜精灵法师已经注意到了它们。是的，听我说，$r——暗夜精灵要取回他们的魔法遗产！如果他们在这里发现了有价值的东西，很可能会导致可怕的后果。除此之外，我倒是觉得他们的举动很有些意思。' WHERE entry=15008; /* Text0_0: The ruins scattered throughout this area are remnants of the night elven civilization at its former peak. They are a treasure trove of information for those who study the arcane.$B$BAnd it would seem they have attracted the attention of a most unusual group of night elven mages. Yes, you heard me $r - night elves are trying to reclaim their magical heritage! I would find it amusing but for the terrible potential should they discover anything of value here. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='$n，我的孩子！$B$B你想要学习我的手掌热疗技术吗？$B$B不？绷带技术？你想要学习绷带技术？' WHERE entry=15012; /* Text0_0: $N, my $g boy : girl;!$B$BWant me to teach you any of my thermal palms healing techniques?$B$BNo? How about bandages? Do you want to learn about bandages? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='请不要见怪，$n。也许你的确是一台狂野的杀戮机器，不过你现在至少还是我们这一边的。' WHERE entry=15013; /* Text0_0: No hard feelings, $N.  You might be a feral killing machine, but it looks like you\'re with us for now. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我还记得和我的兄弟一起在艾萨拉荒野上露营的时候。看看它现在的样子。' WHERE entry=15021; /* Text0_0: I remember when my brother and I would camp alone in the Azshara wilderness. Look at it now. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='时刻保持警惕，$n。' WHERE entry=15028; /* Text0_0: Keep your sights straight, $N. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你需要什么，$c？' WHERE entry=15029; /* Text0_0: You need something, $c? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='对新武器有兴趣吗，$c？' WHERE entry=15035; /* Text0_0: Can I interest you in a new weapon, $c? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='当我在失落群岛上束手无策的时候，我见识了我们新地精盟友的能力。但现在，我们要测试他们的才华了：我们要在敌人的要塞中与他们作战。' WHERE entry=15036; /* Text0_0: I witnessed the handiwork of our new goblin allies when I was stranded in the Lost Isles. But now we put their ingenuity to the test: here we face down our foes in their own stronghold. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='有人不相信传说中的暗夜精灵莫霍克。$B$B真为他们悲哀。' WHERE entry=15037; /* Text0_0: There are some who do not believe in the legendary Night Elf Mohawks.$B$BI pity the fools. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='幸会，莫霍克的好$G兄弟:姐妹;。' WHERE entry=15038; /* Text0_0: Well met, fellow Mohawk $GBrother:Sister;. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='第一场挑战要求你骑上一头银色战狼。你会在演武场的墙边找到这些坐骑，骑着它们来找我，然后我们继续。' WHERE entry=15043; /* Text0_0: The first challenge requires you to be mounted on an Argent Battleworg.  You will find these mounts along the walls of this coliseum.$b$bPlease, mount the battleworg, speak to me, and then we can proceed. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='要让我说的话，暗夜精灵在一万年以前就已经丢掉了这个地方。今天他们被我们驱逐只不过是一个形式上的事情。' WHERE entry=15063; /* Text0_0: If you ask me, the night elves lost this area ten thousand years ago. Their expulsion today at our hands is merely a formality. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='在这见到我吃惊吗？每个人都需要干净衣服，除了找你的水元素帮忙，还有更好的办法吗？$B$B只需把你的衣服拿来，象征性的付点钱，不知不觉中你的衣服又变得清爽、干净！' WHERE entry=15066; /* Text0_0: Are you surprised to see me here? Everyone needs clean laundry, and what better way to do it than with your own water elemental?$B$BSimply bring your laundry, pay a nominal fee, and before you know it, everything will be fresh and clean! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你来这要干什么，$c？' WHERE entry=15074; /* Text0_0: What is your business here, $c? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='永远不要相信那些夺日者。他们不遗余力的破坏我们和银色北伐军盟友的关系。' WHERE entry=15076; /* Text0_0: Never trust the Sunreavers. They are hard at work undermining us in the eyes of our Argent Crusade allies. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='找到你了！我几乎以为你已经被逐日者劫走了。你准备好把宝典递送给冰冠冰川的使者了吗？' WHERE entry=15077; /* Text0_0: There you are! I was beginning to think that the Sunreavers had intercepted you. Are you ready to deliver the tome to our representatives in Icecrown? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='只有几次漂亮的坠毁才能真正“磨砺”一台飞行器。$B$B任何头脑正常的地精都不会只安心于安全的飞行。' WHERE entry=15083; /* Text0_0: It takes a few good crashes to really "season" a flying machine.$B$BNo goblin in their right mind flies one pristine. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='旧伤尚未复原，$g小伙子:姑娘;。我尚能深深地感觉到。没错，我还有仇要向阿尔萨斯报，当他还未成气候时我就应该好好教训他，我会给他补上这个的。总是感觉他有些不对劲。$B$B你的船员准备好以后告诉我一声，我们准备起飞直达堡垒的顶部。$B$B阿尔萨斯决不会料到这一招！' WHERE entry=15101; /* Text0_0: The old wounds still linger, $g lad:lass;. I can feel \'em in me bones, even now. Aye, I got a score to settle with Arthas and ye can believe I\'m gonna give that boy the beatin\' I shoulda given \'im when he was a wee lad. Always knew there was something wrong with \'im.$B$BTell me when yer crew is ready and we\'ll lift off for the top o\' the citadel.$B$BArthas won\'t be expectin\' this! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='这是我们最后的阵地。今天的一切都将千古流传。无论是生是死，我们都是为了荣誉而战。我们都是为了自由和人民而战！记住，英雄们，在这邪恶之地，恐惧是你们最大的敌人。勇气将让你们的灵魂比千颗太阳还要明亮。敌人会在你们面前溃不成军。正义的光芒将彻底摧毁他们！' WHERE entry=15103; /* Text0_0: This is our final stand. What happens here will echo through the ages. Regardless of outcome, they will know that we fought with honor. That we fought for the freedom and safety of our people.$B$BRemember, hero, fear is your greatest enemy in these befouled halls. Steel your heart and your soul will shine brighter than a thousand suns. The enemy will falter at the sight of you. They will fall as the light of righteousness envelops them! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='$G先生:女士;' WHERE entry=15104; /* Text0_0: $G Sir.:Ma\'am.; */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='元素在眷顾你。你要向它们要求什么？',Text0_1_loc4='元素在眷顾你。你要向它们要求什么？' WHERE entry=15110; /* Text0_0: The elements favor you.  What will you ask of them? */ /* Text0_1: The elements favor you.  What will you ask of them? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='元素变幻莫测，没有受过训练的双手很难控制它们。很抱歉，我并不需要你。',Text0_1_loc4='元素变幻莫测，没有受过训练的双手很难控制它们。很抱歉，我并不需要你。' WHERE entry=15111; /* Text0_0: The elements are fickle and best left out of untrained hands.  My apologies, but I have no need for yours. */ /* Text0_1: The elements are fickle and best left out of untrained hands.  My apologies, but I have no need for yours. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='能拥有如此众多忠诚而具有献身精神的学徒，这是我的幸运。如果没有这些测试样品，我的工作也不可能进行。' WHERE entry=15112; /* Text0_0: I am truly blessed to have so many loyal and dedicated apprentices. My work would be impossible without this influx of test subjects. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我的指挥官就在我的眼前被杀害了，兄弟们不断地在我身边倒下。我无法继续战斗下去。我没有能为他们报仇，$c，我让他们蒙受了羞耻。',Text1_0_loc4='我们得到命令，要再次进行冲锋。而迎击我们的是一片长矛组成的壁垒。我做不到，$c。我的武器滑出了双手，两条腿也无法动弹。$B$B我玷污了自己的荣誉。' WHERE entry=15117; /* Text0_0: My commander was butchered before my eyes - my brothers dead all around me - I could not fight on. I am so ashamed, $c. I did not avenge them. */ /* Text1_0: We grunts were ordered to charge once more - into a wall of pikes - I could not do it, $c. My weapon slid from my hands and my legs did not move.$B$BI am dishonored. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text2_0_loc4='不要看我，$r，我让部落蒙羞，我彻底完蛋了。',Text3_0_loc4='任何兽人都不应该像我一样逃离战场。别理我，让我单独咀嚼自己的耻辱吧。我不害怕死在这座塔里，却害怕知道我的祖先会如何看待我的懦弱。' WHERE entry=15117; /* Text2_0: Do not look at me, $r. I have disgraced the Horde. I am done. */ /* Text3_0: No orc should ever flee from battle as I did. Leave me to my disgrace. Would that I would die in this tower, but I dread learning what my ancestors think of my cowardice. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='只有当你潜入雪层时，你的冰虫才能够移动，但潜入后你的冰虫无法攻击。浮出雪层的冰虫可以使用它强大的酸性攻击穿透钢铁巨像的护甲。要做好随时下潜的准备以躲避钢铁巨像最具毁灭性的攻击。' WHERE entry=15119; /* Text0_0: Your jormungar can only move if you\'ve submerged beneath the snow, but it cannot attack while submerged. Once your jormungar emerges, it can use its powerful acid attack to wear through the armor of the Iron Colossus. Be ready to submerge to escape from the Iron Colossus\'s most devastating attacks. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='还没有哪支队伍能够把这么不利的局势扳回来！' WHERE entry=15121; /* Text0_0: No team\'s ever come back from this far behind! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='火箭背包不见了？看看在不在背包里。' WHERE entry=15123; /* Text0_0: Lost your Rocket Pack? Have you checked your bags? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='几年以前，恐怖图腾袭击了我的村庄。直至今日，痛苦、愤怒和失落仍然沉重地压在我的心上。$B$B现在，我自己却在安慰和帮助其他失去了自己村庄的人。' WHERE entry=15127; /* Text0_0: Years ago, the Grimtotem raided my village. The pain, the anger, the loss - still they weigh on my heart.$B$BAnd now I find myself giving comfort and aid to others who have lost their village to a savage attack. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='借助这些隐秘的路径，我们能够对下面的敌人发动猛烈的进攻。$B$B游击战算不上是荣誉的行动，但一名优秀的战士明白该如何让他的敌人措手不及。' WHERE entry=15128; /* Text0_0: From these hidden paths we can rain terror down on our enemies below.$B$BThere is not much honor in hit-and-run strikes, but a good warrior knows to keep his foe off-balance. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='$n，那些巨魔可真奇怪。我不喜欢这样，一点也不喜欢。' WHERE entry=15132; /* Text0_0: The trolls are acting strangely, $n.  I don\'t like it.  I don\'t like it one bit. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='敌人的数量远远超过我们，我们与十字路口和杜隆塔尔的联系已经被切断。但一个兽人能打败十个联盟懦夫。$B$B我们要对他们迎头痛击，把他们像赶猪群一样轰走。' WHERE entry=15135; /* Text0_0: We are outnumbered here, our ties to Crossroads and Durotar severed. But one orc is worth 10 Alliance cowards.$B$BWe will bottle them up in this pass and gut them like swine. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='联盟耍了一个极端狡诈的诡计，$n。联盟的军队从北方城堡出发，沿着黄金之路前进，在日暮时分向十字路口发动了进攻。到了深夜，他们又掉头南进，只留下空无一人的营地和依旧在燃烧的篝火。$B$B当黎明的第一缕曙光出现时，我们在荣耀岗哨的大军突然遭到了联盟的猛烈袭击。大批联盟士兵冲过隘口。我们许多最勇敢的战士都死在了他们的刀锋之下。' WHERE entry=15136; /* Text0_0: It was a clever ruse, $N. Alliance forces streamed out of Northwatch and marched up the gold road, besieging Crossroads as dusk fell. Then, in the heart of the night, they force-marched southward, leaving their campfires burning behind.$B$BOur meager forces at Honor\'s Stand were caught unawares as the Alliance poured through the pass at dawn\'s first light. Many of our bravest warriors fell before their blades. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='是的，我们在隘口东边重新集结，准备发动反击。但在第二天，天空变成了赤红色，大地分裂成两块，就好象一块被小孩掰开的饼干。在地平线与地平线之间，一切都惨遭凌夷。$B$B刚刚建起防御碉堡的联盟军队也像我们一样惊恐异常，茫然不知所措。这本来是最佳的进攻时机！但督军加杜尔坚持要撤往南方，重组队伍。$B$B<基洛克向地面上啐了一口。>$B$B我们之中有许多人没有跟着他走。在上一场战争中，我曾经和恶魔正面交战，半步未退，$n。现在我也不打算掉头逃跑，让联盟占据我们的土地。' WHERE entry=15137; /* Text0_0: Yes. We regrouped east of the pass and prepared a counter-attack, but the next day, the skies reddened and the land was cleaved in two, as easily as a child might split open a cactus apple. See how the devastation stretches from horizon to horizon?$B$BOur Alliance foes in their makeshift bunkers were as surprised and disorganized as we were by the disaster. It would\'ve been the perfect time to strike! But Warlord Gar\'dul insisted we pull back to the south to refortify.$B$B<Kilrok spits on the ground.>$B$BNot all of us followed. I stood toe-to-toe with demons in the last war, $N. I\'m not about to turn tail and let the Alliance plant roots on my soil. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='是的，我们继续作战。也许我们难免一死，但我们不会给他们半寸土地，$c。$B$B敌人的数量远远超过我们。我们的盔甲破碎，武器损坏。$B$B但这是我们的土地！我们的牛头人盟友熟悉这片山丘中的每一条小道、裂谷和每一个山口。我们埋伏在高地上，向联盟发动了出其不意的突袭，然后又像影子一样消失。恐惧就是我们的武器，我们要向敌人发动毫无止歇的攻击。' WHERE entry=15138; /* Text0_0: To fight, yes. To die? Likely. But we will give them no ground, $c.$B$BWe are outnumbered. Our armor is patchwork, our weapons scavenged.$B$BBut this is our land! Our tauren allies know every hidden trail, crevice, and pass through these hills. We descend from the high ground where they least expect us, then disappear into the terrain like phantoms. Fear is our weapon, and we will strike at them unceasingly. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='哦，天哪。菲利克斯的情况并不乐观。' WHERE entry=15139; /* Text0_0: Oh dear.  Things aren\'t looking good for Felix. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你认为我什么时候能离开？我还要回去工作呢。',Text0_1_loc4='你认为我什么时候能离开？我还要回去工作呢。',Text1_0_loc4='那些穴居人到底是从哪里来的？他们一直都住在地下吗？',Text1_1_loc4='那些穴居人到底是从哪里来的？他们一直都住在地下吗？' WHERE entry=15140; /* Text0_0: When d\'ye think we can leave?  I need ta get back to work. */ /* Text0_1: When d\'ye think we can leave?  I need ta get back to work. */ /* Text1_0: Where are all these troggs coming from?  Were they livin\' underground the whole time? */ /* Text1_1: Where are all these troggs coming from?  Were they livin\' underground the whole time? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text2_0_loc4='你最好能安下心来。在穴居人被消灭干净之前，铁枷不会让任何人出去。',Text2_1_loc4='你最好能安下心来。在穴居人被消灭干净之前，铁枷不会让任何人出去。',Text3_0_loc4='外面有什么新闻吗？我听说那些巨魔也在蠢蠢欲动。',Text3_1_loc4='外面有什么新闻吗？我听说那些巨魔也在蠢蠢欲动。' WHERE entry=15140; /* Text2_0: Might as well make yerself comfortable.  Ironstock\'s not lettin\' anybody out until the troggs die down. */ /* Text2_1: Might as well make yerself comfortable.  Ironstock\'s not lettin\' anybody out until the troggs die down. */ /* Text3_0: Have ye any news from outside?  I hear the trolls have been actin\' up too. */ /* Text3_1: Have ye any news from outside?  I hear the trolls have been actin\' up too. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text4_0_loc4='这里真是拥挤得令人窒闷。我在密闭空间里总是感到不自在。',Text4_1_loc4='这里真是拥挤得令人窒闷。我在密闭空间里总是感到不自在。',Text5_0_loc4='试想一下，在经历了灾变程度的大地震后，你最不想待的地方应该就是屋里了，不是吗？',Text5_1_loc4='试想一下，在经历了灾变程度的大地震后，你最不想待的地方应该就是屋里了，不是吗？' WHERE entry=15140; /* Text4_0: It\'s gettin\' awful crowded in here.  I don\'t do well in confined spaces. */ /* Text4_1: It\'s gettin\' awful crowded in here.  I don\'t do well in confined spaces. */ /* Text5_0: Ye\'d think that, after an earthquake of cataclysmic proportions, the LAST place ye\'d want ta be is indoors, wouldn\'t ye? */ /* Text5_1: Ye\'d think that, after an earthquake of cataclysmic proportions, the LAST place ye\'d want ta be is indoors, wouldn\'t ye? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text6_0_loc4='$n! 我听说你是铁枷的新$r奴隶。她要你做些什么？',Text6_1_loc4='$n! 我听说你是铁枷的新$r奴隶。她要你做些什么？',Text7_0_loc4='我觉得自己永远都要被关在这里了。已经到美酒节了吗？',Text7_1_loc4='我觉得自己永远都要被关在这里了。已经到美酒节了吗？' WHERE entry=15140; /* Text6_0: $N!  I hear you\'re Ironstock\'s new little whipping $r.  What\'s she got ya doin\' now? */ /* Text6_1: $N!  I hear you\'re Ironstock\'s new little whipping $r.  What\'s she got ya doin\' now? */ /* Text7_0: I feel like I\'ve been cooped up in here forever.  Is it Brewfest yet? */ /* Text7_1: I feel like I\'ve been cooped up in here forever.  Is it Brewfest yet? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='天哪，这里全都是石头！' WHERE entry=15141; /* Text0_0: My gosh, it\'s full of rocks! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你好吗，$c？' WHERE entry=15145; /* Text0_0: How do you do, $c? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='到黄昏时分，火舌已经照亮了天空。我失去了一切。一切。$B$B为什么他们要烧掉一家旅店？' WHERE entry=15146; /* Text0_0: By dusk, the flames towered into the sky. I lost everything. Everything.$B$BWhy would they burn an inn? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='<克尔苏瓦避开你的眼睛。>$B$B我在战斗中逃了出来，但没有能及时放开所有被拴住的牲口。$B$B我没办法聚拢它们，结果它们全都逃进烟雾里去了……' WHERE entry=15147; /* Text0_0: <Kelsuwa doesn\'t make eye contact with you.>$B$BI escaped amidst the fighting, but not before freeing all the stabled animals.$B$BI couldn\'t keep them with me. They scattered into the smoke... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='火山岩！来看看这里的火山岩吧！',Text1_0_loc4='出售火山岩！刚离开火山，还热气腾腾哪！你想要的，就在我这里！' WHERE entry=15148; /* Text0_0: Volcano rocks! Get your volcano rocks here! */ /* Text1_0: Volcano rocks for sale! Hot off the mountain! You want \'em, I got \'em! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text2_0_loc4='火山岩，最新低价！你一定会爱上我的岩石。',Text3_0_loc4='来看看这里的火山岩吧！……对猫正合适！' WHERE entry=15148; /* Text2_0: Volcano rocks - new low price! You\'re gonna love my rocks. */ /* Text3_0: Get your volcano rocks here! ...Great for cats! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text4_0_loc4='把大灾变的纪念带回家吧！出售火山岩——火热，火热，火热的火山岩！',Text5_0_loc4='能做镇纸，能挡门，还能砸窗户！来看看，来看看！火山岩。' WHERE entry=15148; /* Text4_0: Take home a piece of the Cataclysm! Volcano rocks for sale - hot, Hot, HOT! */ /* Text5_0: Papers to weigh? Doors to stop? Windows to break? bam, Bam, BAM! Volcano rocks. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text6_0_loc4='火山岩。用法多多。',Text7_0_loc4='火山岩！限时供应！配有品质证书和一切相关手续！' WHERE entry=15148; /* Text6_0: Volcano rocks. Million and one uses. Lava, java, sauna, banana.... */ /* Text7_0: Volcano rocks! Limited time offer! Papers of authenticity and everything! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='这看上去像是萨洛瑞安·寻晨者的遗体，奎尔德拉最后的使用者。' WHERE entry=15155; /* Text0_0: These appear to be the remains of Thalorien Dawnseeker, the last wielder of Quel\'Delar. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='接受现实吧，$c。$b$b巫妖王的统治已经到了尽头。' WHERE entry=15158; /* Text0_0: Ready yourself, $c.$b$bThe time has come for the Lich King\'s reign to come to an end. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='巫妖王已经离我们很近了，$n。我感觉到了他声音中的嘲弄…$b$b去让他安静下来吧！' WHERE entry=15166; /* Text0_0: The Lich King is near, $n. His voice taunts me...$b$bLet us silence him at last! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='嗨！我来自皇冠药剂公司。$B$B你在寻找礼物吗？还是要找份工作？想不想送自己点东西？好吧，你来对地方了，朋友。$B$B如果我没有你想要的东西，那么在我旁边的福星基维或是可爱的商贩一定会有。' WHERE entry=15170; /* Text0_0: Yo! I\'m here representing the Crown Chemical Company.$B$BYou looking for a gift? A job? Maybe a little something for yourself? Well, you\'ve come to the right place, friend.$B$BIf I don\'t have what you need, our mascot Kwee or the Lovely Merchant beside me will. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我们要利用那些补给为所有人做好战斗的准备。$B$B继续吧。我们会再见面的。' WHERE entry=15171; /* Text0_0: We\'ll make use of these supplies to get everyone ready for a fight.$B$BContinue on. We\'ll meet you ahead. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我会集结其它的奴隶，被让他们做好战斗的准备。在你同天灾领主泰兰努斯开始交战前我们会赶上你的。' WHERE entry=15172; /* Text0_0: I\'ll gather up the rest of slaves and get them ready to fight. We\'ll catch up with you before you engage Scourgelord Tyrannus. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我曾经在陶拉祖营地安全的环境中训练年轻的猎人熟悉荒野之道。$B$B现在我们不能奢望再有那种条件了。敌人已经踏过了我们的门槛，我们的年轻人必须在与敌人的激烈搏杀中学会战斗的技巧。' WHERE entry=15173; /* Text0_0: From the safety of Camp Taurajo I once trained young hunters in the ways of the wild.$B$BWe have no such luxury now - skills must be learned in the heat of battle against a foe camped on our very doorstep. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='英雄们，我们会追随你们的领导。今夕就是天灾领主的死期。' WHERE entry=15174; /* Text0_0: We will follow your lead, heroes. The Scourgelord will die this eve. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='这是一道紧急撤离传送门。' WHERE entry=15185; /* Text0_0: This is an Emergency Evacuation Portal. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='嘿，伙计，我不认识你，也不知道你为什么要一直跟着我，但我马上就要上船了，并且我想自己一个人呆着，明白吗？' WHERE entry=15188; /* Text0_0: Hey, pal, I don\'t know who you are or why you\'ve been following me around, but I\'m about to board a ship and I want to be left alone, got it? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='那是一场激烈的战斗，$n！集结部队、重整旗鼓。谁知道在那道门后面等待我们的是什么？$B$B准备好以后告诉我，我们准备向上游攻打敌人的堡垒。' WHERE entry=15194; /* Text0_0: \'Twas a fierce battle, $N! Take a moment to rest and gather yer forces. Who knows what lies beyond that door?$B$BLet me know when yer ready and we\'ll begin our ascent into the upper reaches of the citadel. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你能肯定吗，$g 伙计:小姑娘;？再给你一两分钟？' WHERE entry=15195; /* Text0_0: Are ye sure, $g lad:lass;? Ye don\'t need another minute or two? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='欢迎来到凄凉要塞，$c。我们在此等待时机，向联盟还以颜色。' WHERE entry=15196; /* Text0_0: This is Desolation Hold, $c. Here we bide our time until we are ready to strike back against the Alliance. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='快一点， $c。酋长亲自派我来评估我们在贫瘠之地的工作进展，然而我却在这里看到我们的城镇燃起大火，联盟败狗肆无忌惮地发狂。' WHERE entry=15197; /* Text0_0: Make this quick, $c. The Warchief personally sent me to evaluate our progress in the Barrens, and when I get here I find our towns aflame and Alliance dogs running amok. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你很有潜力，$n。要想重获对贫瘠之地的控制权，就绝对少不了像你这样的精兵。' WHERE entry=15198; /* Text0_0: You have a lot of potential, $N. I\'m going to need soldiers like you if we\'re going to regain the initiative here in the Barrens. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='血柄督军？加尔鲁什的狗腿子？$B$B正如你看到的，这儿不需要他——啊，告诉他这里的一切状况都在我的掌握之中。' WHERE entry=15200; /* Text0_0: Warlord Bloodhilt? Garrosh\'s pet?$B$BThere\'s no need for him to be here, as you can see, ah, tell him I have the situation well in hand. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='但是，啊，目前的供给非常紧张。而且，呃，我这里的人力也很短缺。告诉血柄，啊-' WHERE entry=15201; /* Text0_0: But, ah, supplies have been tight. I\'ve got, ah, a manpower shortage. Tell Bloodhilt that, ah - */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='不要再耽搁了，他——啊——他就快到了！$B$B到最北边塔的塔顶找我' WHERE entry=15203; /* Text0_0: Don\'t delay, he\'s - ah - he\'s almost here!$B$BMeet me at the top of the northernmost tower. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='就是这里。我能感觉到这就是发生那场大悲剧的地方。痛苦的嚎叫仿佛仍然在这里回荡。毫无疑问，这就是那些异界的恐怖曾经肆虐横行的地方。$B$B为了能彻底将那些异界怪物入侵这个世界的道路封死，我必须先将它完全打开。那时，我需要你的力量来挡住可能从其中出来的一切东西。$B$B你准备好了吗？' WHERE entry=15205; /* Text0_0: This is it. I can sense that this was once the site of great tragedy; mortal suffering still echoes through it. No doubt this is what the horrors beyond have seized onto.$B$BTo fully seal this intrusion into our world, I must first fully open it. I will need your strength to hold back whatever may attempt to come through.$B$BAre you prepared? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我派出了我们最强干的侏儒来对付这些大门，$n！根据他们的计算，打开那道大门还需要$4939W天！' WHERE entry=15208; /* Text0_0: I\'ve brought in the best gnomes we\'ve got to get those doors open, $N! They\'re estimatin\' that it\'s gonna take another $4939W days before that door comes down! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='<他看了看火箭，咧开嘴紧张地笑了笑。>$b$b好吧，我是给别人做了些火箭。那又怎么样？价格不错，我也得到了酬劳。这不是出不出人命的问题。工作就要实事求是。这跟你有关系吗？' WHERE entry=15209; /* Text0_0: <He looks at the rocket and flashes a nervous grin.>$b$bOkay, yeah, so maybe I made a couple rockets for some guys. So what? The gold was good and I was paid for my work. It\'s not like anyone died. That\'s about as honest as work gets. What\'s it to you? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='听着，我不知道，可以吗？我不知道！$b$b我只是拿钱做了一些火箭，用来空运那些化学品，这就是我是任务。我的任务结束了，朋友。火箭都做好了，而且装备完成发射了出去。我拿了钱，正准备去消费消费，你就在这个时候满世界的追我。我这没有那种化学品了，我也不知道那究竟是什么东西。' WHERE entry=15210; /* Text0_0: Look, I don\'t know, okay? I don\'t know!$b$bI just got paid to make rockets that deliver an airborne chemical payload, and that\'s what I did. Job\'s done, pal. They\'re all made, packaged, and sent off. I got the money and I was TRYING to enjoy myself a little when you started chasing me all over town.  I don\'t have any more of that chemical and I don\'t know what it was. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你要我想起所有那些让我精神失常的事？听着。他们并没有付钱让我跟进这件事，我们之间的协议也不允许我透露这些。我可以把我的账本扔在地上，你自己捡起来然后别来烦我了。$b$b听明白了？' WHERE entry=15211; /* Text0_0: You expect me to remember all that off the top of my head? Look. They didn\'t pay me enough to put up with this, and the contract only asked for my silence. So I\'m just gonna drop my ledger on the floor here, and you\'re going to take it and leave me alone.$b$bGot it? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你听说过我们的“慈善情人符”计划吗？$B$B官方的加冕活动，像我这样的福星会得到授权，分发可爱的情人符工具箱。$B$B你可以用得来的可爱的情人符为自己的朋友和心爱的人制作可爱的情人符手镯，或是把它们拿到可爱的商贩那里来兑换爱情信物！$B$B这期间的另一个流行做法是将自己制作的手镯送给自己喜爱的领袖，让他们感受到众人对他们的欣赏和爱戴…' WHERE entry=15212; /* Text0_0: Did you know about our "Charitable Charms" program?$B$BOfficial Crown event mascots like myself are authorized to distribute Lovely Charm Collector\'s Kits.$B$BYou can then use the Lovely Charms you gather to create Lovely Charm Bracelets for friends and loved ones, or turn them in to Lovely Merchants for Love Tokens!$B$BOne popular activity is making bracelets for your favorite leaders to let them know they\'re appreciated and adored... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我已经把我知道的都告诉你了，现在走吧！' WHERE entry=15213; /* Text0_0: I told you what I know, now shove off! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='无论你要什么，布雷泽·盖茨！明白吗？$B$B而且我指的不光是那些“合法”的东西。我是说——无论——你要什么，朋友！任何东西……' WHERE entry=15214; /* Text0_0: Whatever you need, Brazie Getz! Get it?$B$BAnd I\'m not just talkin\' about the "legal" stuff, either. WHATEVER YOU NEED, PAL! Anything... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='部落勇敢的战士，我向你致敬！如果没有你和你盟友的帮助，我们一定会死在联盟炮艇的火力下。$B$B请稍事休息，随后我们会展开针对敌人堡垒上游的袭击。' WHERE entry=15217; /* Text0_0: Brave soldier of the Horde, I salute you! We would have surely been destroyed by the Alliance gunship had it not been for you and your allies.$B$BTake a moment to rest before we begin our assault upon the upper reaches of the citadel. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你能肯定吗，$n？要想战胜天灾军团，我们必须全力以赴。如果你休息得差不多了，我们就开始吧。' WHERE entry=15218; /* Text0_0: Are you sure, $N? We must face the Scourge at full strength if we are to succeed. If you do not require more rest, we will begin. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我曾听过我的孩子在那里发生的故事。现在，他已经成了巫妖王手下一名强大的死亡骑士。如果这是真的，我必须大义灭亲。$B$B我现在的责任就是指挥奥格瑞姆之锤号抵达冰冠堡垒之顶，并消灭所有阻拦我们的天灾军团。你和你的盟友准备好以后我们就出发。' WHERE entry=15219; /* Text0_0: I have heard tale of my boy being here. That he\'s now a powerful death knight in service of the Lich King. If this is true, then it must be me that ends the bloodline.$B$BMy charge now is to command Orgrim\'s Hammer to the top of Icecrown Citadel and destroy all Scourge that get in our way. We leave when you and your allies are ready. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='他的灵魂已经摆脱了巫妖王的束缚。我们现在必须集中力量击破那几面阻挡我们前往上方的高墙。这只是个时间问题，$n。攻城工程师只需$4939W天就可以攻破大门了。' WHERE entry=15220; /* Text0_0: His spirit is free from the grasp of the Lich King. We must now focus our attention on breaking down the walls that block our passage into the upper reaches. It is only a matter of time now, $N. The siege engineers should have the door down in $4939W days. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='传送器闪出水晶般的光芒。',Text0_1_loc4='传送器闪出水晶般的光芒。' WHERE entry=15221; /* Text0_0: The transporter glimmers with a crystalline light. */ /* Text0_1: The transporter glimmers with a crystalline light. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='现在，我们要赢得这场战争！$B$B越过这片满目疮痍的地区向东，联盟希望在他们的海岸要塞之间建立起陆上连接。他们想要在这里，在贫瘠之地的正中心建立一座堡垒。但这是我的贫瘠之地。$B$B我绝不会允许那座堡垒出现。' WHERE entry=15222; /* Text0_0: Now - to the business of winning this war!$B$BAcross the scarred terrain to the east, the Alliance hopes to build an overland link between their coastal strongholds. They think to build a fortress here, in the center of the Barrens. In the center of MY Barrens.$B$BIt will not stand. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='这太可怕了，$c。我被蛮横地赶出奥格瑞玛。当我被拖出奥格瑞玛的大门时，我的实验材料全都被扔在地上，被彻底毁了。$B$B他们对待我就好象对待某种可怕的怪物！$B$B幸运的是，我在这里还能继续我的研究。这里从不会缺乏新鲜的实验材料。' WHERE entry=15223; /* Text0_0: It was dreadful, $c. Unceremoniously booted from Orgrimmar, jars of fresh squirming body parts smashed to the ground as I was hauled through the gates.$B$BLike I was some kind of monster!$B$BFortunately I\'ve been able to continue my research here, where there\'s no shortage of fresh corpses. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='<一只蟑螂从卡尔德的嘴里爬出来，又爬进了他的一只空眼窝。>' WHERE entry=15224; /* Text0_0: <A cockroach slithers from Calder\'s mouth and scurries back into his skull through an empty eye socket.> */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='<一看到你，卡尔德装上他的下巴，准备和你说话。>' WHERE entry=15225; /* Text0_0: <On seeing you approach, Calder re-hinges his jaw to speak with you.> */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='<你发现卡尔德正用一把匕首无聊地拨弄着他的耳朵。>' WHERE entry=15226; /* Text0_0: <You find Calder idly picking at his ear with a dagger.> */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='知道我喜欢什么吗，$n？' WHERE entry=15227; /* Text0_0: Do you know what I like, $N? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='杀戮。' WHERE entry=15228; /* Text0_0: Murder. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='慢一些，朋友。你说将军就要来了？$B$B我的墙上又要增添一件战利品了！我会吸引那些近卫的注意，你的任务就是去干掉霍索恩将军。准备好了吗？' WHERE entry=15233; /* Text0_0: Slow down, friend. You say the General is coming?$B$BNow THERE\'S a trophy for my wall! I\'ll distract the bodyguards, but it will be up to you to kill General Hawthorne himself. Are you ready to strike? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='陶拉祖的屠夫将会付出代价。' WHERE entry=15235; /* Text0_0: The Butcher of Taurajo will pay. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='在把他们赶回到大海之前，我不会休息，$n。' WHERE entry=15236; /* Text0_0: I will not rest, $N. Not until they are driven back to the sea. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='明白！Grok\'thar More\'gar。Bok choy，朋友。呃。达姆达姆！' WHERE entry=15237; /* Text0_0: Yes! Grok\'thar More\'gar. Bok choy, friend. Um. Zub zub! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='遵……遵命。呃。准备工作！' WHERE entry=15238; /* Text0_0: Okidoki. Uh. R-ready to work! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='只有取得游侠将军的许可才能进入太阳井高地。',Text0_1_loc4='只有取得游侠将军的许可才能进入太阳井高地。' WHERE entry=15239; /* Text0_0: Only those who have the ranger general\'s approval may enter the Sunwell Plateau. */ /* Text0_1: Only those who have the ranger general\'s approval may enter the Sunwell Plateau. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='等你准备好了，我就护送你去太阳井。',Text0_1_loc4='等你准备好了，我就护送你去太阳井。' WHERE entry=15240; /* Text0_0: I will escort you into the Sunwell when you\'re ready. */ /* Text0_1: I will escort you into the Sunwell when you\'re ready. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我告诉过加杜尔，不要在异种生物的巢穴上建造城堡。$B$B他会听克劳格的话吗？不！' WHERE entry=15241; /* Text0_0: I told Gar\'dul not to build a fortress on top of a Silithid colony.$B$BDid he listen to Crawgol? No! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我的天才不可能被束缚在一个胶囊里！$B$B等等，这里不是艾萨拉？！这是什么地方？这是一座休眠火山！$B$B我本来有些想去找贸易大王的！但我也在考虑将肉鸡蛋实现武器化的可能！' WHERE entry=15243; /* Text0_0: My genius cannot be contained within a box!$B$BWait, this isn\'t Azshara?! What is this place? That\'s a dormant volcano!$B$BI have half a mind to go join the Trade Prince! The other half of my mind is considering the possible weaponization of the clucker eggs! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='靠我近点，朋友。我在上一次袭击中被一颗子弹射中了。$B$B<甘恩努力想挪动一下身体，却只是痛苦地呻吟了一声。他的左手按在一处伤口上。血不断地从他的指缝间涌出。>$B$B当矮人们最初入侵贫瘠之地的时候，我只是满足于骚扰他们的挖掘工，破坏他们的设备。我真应该趁有机会的时候对他们发动致命的打击。' WHERE entry=15246; /* Text0_0: Kneel beside me, friend. I caught a bullet during that last raid.$B$B<Gann grunts in pain as he tries to shift position. His left hand clutches a wound, blood welling between his quivering fingers.>$B$BWhen the dwarves first invaded the Barrens, I contented myself with harassing their diggers and sabotaging their equipment. I should\'ve struck a killing blow when I had the chance. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='维兹尔·滑影，伪装大师！' WHERE entry=15248; /* Text0_0: Weezil Slipshadow - master of disguise! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='这不算什么大挑战，朋友，但在接纳你之前，我们要确认你有能力对付这个地穴里的东西。',Text0_1_loc4='这不算什么大挑战，朋友，但在接纳你之前，我们要确认你有能力对付这个地穴里的东西。' WHERE entry=15251; /* Text0_0: This ain\'t much of a big challenge, mon, but we gotta know ya can handle the pit before we can take ya in. */ /* Text0_1: This ain\'t much of a big challenge, mon, but we gotta know ya can handle the pit before we can take ya in. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='他们正在进行挑战，朋友。耐心一些。',Text0_1_loc4='他们正在进行挑战，朋友。耐心一些。' WHERE entry=15252; /* Text0_0: They\'re in mid challenge, mon. Be patient. */ /* Text0_1: They\'re in mid challenge, mon. Be patient. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我一点也不喜欢这个皇冠药剂公司的样子。' WHERE entry=15256; /* Text0_0: I don\'t like the look of this \'Crown Chemical Co.\' one bit. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='照顾好你的武器，它们就能照顾好你。' WHERE entry=15257; /* Text0_0: Take care of ya weapons an\' they\'ll take care of ya back. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我不能帮助你，如果你想接受德鲁伊训练，就去和岑塔布拉谈谈。',Text0_1_loc4='我不能帮助你，如果你想接受德鲁伊训练，就去和岑塔布拉谈谈。' WHERE entry=15260; /* Text0_0: I can\'t help ya. Go talk ta Zen\'Tabra if ya want druid trainin\'. */ /* Text0_1: I can\'t help ya. Go talk ta Zen\'Tabra if ya want druid trainin\'. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我不能帮助你，如果你想接受法师训练，就去和索拉萨谈谈。',Text0_1_loc4='我不能帮助你，如果你想接受法师训练，就去和索拉萨谈谈。' WHERE entry=15263; /* Text0_0: I can\'t help ya. Go talk ta Soratha if ya want mage trainin\'. */ /* Text0_1: I can\'t help ya. Go talk ta Soratha if ya want mage trainin\'. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我不能帮助你，如果你想接受牧师训练，就去和图娜尼谈谈。',Text0_1_loc4='我不能帮助你，如果你想接受牧师训练，就去和图娜尼谈谈。' WHERE entry=15264; /* Text0_0: I can\'t help ya. Go talk ta Tunari if ya want priest trainin\'. */ /* Text0_1: I can\'t help ya. Go talk ta Tunari if ya want priest trainin\'. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='侍从是骑士的左右手。要知道，手应该特别擅长于搬运东西，所以你的第一个任务就是负责搬运我的杂物、小东西和其它各种随身用具。这样我才能放心地在世界各处维护正义。毕竟搬运杂物可不是骑士应该做的事情。' WHERE entry=15266; /* Text0_0: A squire is the right hand of the knight.  As you are already fully aware, hands are especially good at carrying things, and thus your first duty will be to carry my sundries, knickknacks, and other miscellaneous paraphernalia while I dispense justice across the land.  To lug around such etcetera is a job unbefitting of a knight. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='很好。第二，你必须知道，对于骑士来说，最重要的莫过于骑士精神。骑士永远要秉承慷慨仁慈的骑士情怀，就如同绝对不能放开手中的长枪。他的勇猛果敢必须比他身上的铠甲更加耀眼夺目。无论他的佩剑多么锋利刚硬，他对待朋友却必须和善谦恭。$b$b现在，告诉我，$n，你会立下誓言，坚守骑士的精神和勇气吗？' WHERE entry=15267; /* Text0_0: Very good.  Secondly, you must know that a knight embraces no tenet more tightly than that of chivalry.  He clings to his generosity as tightly as he clings to his lance.  His valor shines as brightly as his armor.  And while his smallsword may be sharp, his manner among allies is soft and courteous.$b$bNow tell me $n, do you give your oath to hold to the teachings of chivalry and gallantry? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='哈！我没有说过吗，好$n，骑士精神和勇气是骑士必须坚持的原则？你要做的只是一名侍从。严格的骑士精神对于侍从来说是难以承受的重担。就像我曾经提到过的一样，你要扛起的担子只有我的随身物品。' WHERE entry=15268; /* Text0_0: Ha!  Did I not just say, good $n, chivalry and gallantry are the charge of the KNIGHT?  You seek only to be a SQUIRE.  The colossal burden of chivalry is unfit for the squire, for as I mentioned before, the only colossal burden that you are to bear is that of my belongings. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='开始吧！骑士精神是骑士之道，我正是一名骑士。你必须明白，我天生就是一名勇者。这是真的，我为多罗莉亚女士而战，要将她的美丽与高贵在全世界传颂。任何对她的美好有所质疑的人都是我最大的敌人，一定会得到我正义的惩罚。$b$b当我说话的时候，我才意识到我的一个失误。我们已经正式开始了接纳侍从的仪式，但我还没有确认你是应该接受我的赞许，还是我的正义怒火。$b$b现在我必须知道，你是否认为多罗莉亚女士是艾泽拉斯无可置疑的最美丽的人？' WHERE entry=15269; /* Text0_0: Moving on!  As chivalry is the way of the knight, and I am a knight, you must know then that my own intentions are indeed valorous.  It is true, I fight for my Lady Doloria, to proclaim her beauty and majesty across all the lands.  Any who question her beauty are without a doubt the most vile of enemies, and must be brought to justice.$b$bAs I speak, it occurs to me that I am a failure.  We have come quite far in the squiring ceremony, yet I have not yet ascertained whether or not you deserve my charity or my righteous fury.$b$bI must know, now, do you agree that my Lady Doloria is unquestionably the fairest Lady across all of Azeroth? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='很高兴听到你这样说。祝贺你，$n，你已经完成了训练。现在你可以跟随我一同上战场了。' WHERE entry=15270; /* Text0_0: I\'m rather glad to hear that.  Congratulations, $N, for you have completed your training.  You may now ride beside me into the fray. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='骤隐骤现。当人们看到你所做的一切，却看不到你的时候，你就掌握了你的职业技巧。' WHERE entry=15273; /* Text0_0: Strike swiftly an\' fade away. You\'ll know ya beginin\' ta master ya skills when people know ya deeds, but never heard of you. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='聪明，你会发现，魔法比任何武器都要强大得多。' WHERE entry=15275; /* Text0_0: Wit\' practice, ya\'ll find that magic can be much stronga than any weapon. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='<麦斯米兰沉浸在祈祷中，忘却了你的存在。>' WHERE entry=15277; /* Text0_0: <Maximillian is deep in prayer, oblivious to your presence.> */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='收起你的剑，取下你的头盔。在我们用刀剑作战之前，我有好些话得先灌输到你的耳朵里去。$b$b准备好了吗？' WHERE entry=15278; /* Text0_0: Stay your sword and loosen your cap.  Before we do battle with our blades, I first have prepared an assault to unleash upon your ears.$b$bAre you prepared? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='朋友，无需四处寻觅。$B$B要买Crown holiday goods，你就一定要去城里的Lovely Merchant。',Text0_1_loc4='朋友，无需四处寻觅。$B$B要买Crown holiday goods，你就一定要去城里的Lovely Merchant。' WHERE entry=15280; /* Text0_0: No snooping around, friend.$B$BIf you\'re looking to buy Crown holiday goods, you\'ll have to do it at the Lovely Merchant in the city. */ /* Text0_1: No snooping around, friend.$B$BIf you\'re looking to buy Crown holiday goods, you\'ll have to do it at the Lovely Merchant in the city. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你没什么东西要搬吗？',Text0_1_loc4='你没什么东西要搬吗？' WHERE entry=15282; /* Text0_0: Don\'t you have some packages to move? */ /* Text0_1: Don\'t you have some packages to move? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='有东西在发出臭味，这次可不是我的袜子。',Text0_1_loc4='有东西在发出臭味，这次可不是我的袜子。' WHERE entry=15284; /* Text0_0: Something stinks, and for once it\'s not my socks. */ /* Text0_1: Something stinks, and for once it\'s not my socks. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='真是一把神器的剑，你觉得呢？这绝不会是出自矮人之手，不，还要古老的多。$B$B这些夺日者和银色盟约的使者似乎打算对这一秘密一探究竟。我已经开始准备给布莱恩的报告了。' WHERE entry=15287; /* Text0_0: Truly an amazing sword, don\'t you think? That\'s no weapon of dwarven make, no, it\'s far more ancient than that.$B$BThese Sunreaver and Silver Covenant representatives seem intent on getting to the bottom of the mystery. I\'m already working on a report for Brann. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='作为德鲁伊，我们的任务就是维护自然的平衡。但我的努力却与此背道而驰。我的愚蠢造成极为巨大的混乱。必须在这种异常的作物进一步扩散之前将它收割。' WHERE entry=15288; /* Text0_0: As Druids, we are tasked with protecting the balance of nature. My life\'s work has gone against this. In my folly, I have sewn chaos, and this deviant crop must be reaped before it spreads further. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我会留在这里，照看这片正在痊愈的大地。请一定注意来自于这里的游荡者……' WHERE entry=15289; /* Text0_0: I will stay here and watch over the land as it heals.  Do keep an eye out for any stragglers from here... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我等待这一天的到来已经太久了，英雄。你和你的同袍们是否已经准备好对巫妖王进行正义的审判？我们将在你的命令下向敌人发起冲锋！' WHERE entry=15290; /* Text0_0: Long have I waited for this day, hero. Are you and your allies prepared to bring the Lich King to justice? We charge on your command! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='来吧，侍从$n，冒险正等待着我们！' WHERE entry=15291; /* Text0_0: Come, Squire $N, for adventure awaits us! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='巴尔莫丹……那些矮人……' WHERE entry=15292; /* Text0_0: Bael Modan... the dwarves... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='这道伤痕被封印了！感谢塞纳留斯……' WHERE entry=15293; /* Text0_0: The scar is sealed! Thank Cenarius... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='救救我！我的东西都掉在这个热泉里了。$b$b我的长袍就在那里！' WHERE entry=15294; /* Text0_0: Save me!  I\'ve dropped my belongings into the hot springs.$b$bMy gowns are in there! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='又是你……真希望你不曾如此尽心竭力地想要安抚我的灵魂。我早就明白，没有了她，就不会有和平，再也不会有了。$B$B我要将他们的家全部夷为平地。你准备好消灭这些可憎的杀人犯了么？' WHERE entry=15295; /* Text0_0: You again...I hope you didn\'t put too much faith in your actions settling my spirit. I\'ve realized there will be no peace without her, not anymore.$B$BI will see their very homes razed. Are you ready to slay more of these disgusting murderers? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我不确定这一切代表了什麽，我只觉得我被严重羞辱了。噢，谢谢你把我的皮包拿了回来...我是说箱子!',Text0_1_loc4='我不确定这一切代表了什麽，我只觉得我被严重羞辱了。噢，谢谢你把我的皮包拿了回来...我是说箱子!',Text1_0_loc4='我不确定这一切代表了什麽，我只觉得我被严重羞辱了。噢，谢谢你把我的皮包拿了回来...我是说箱子!',Text1_1_loc4='我不确定这一切代表了什麽，我只觉得我被严重羞辱了。噢，谢谢你把我的皮包拿了回来...我是说箱子!' WHERE entry=15296; /* Text0_0: You\'ve caught me at a critical time in my research! No worries, you\'re welcome to join me in quiet contemplation... emphasis on "quiet", if you don\'t mind though. */ /* Text0_1: You\'ve caught me at a critical time in my research! No worries, you\'re welcome to join me in quiet contemplation... emphasis on "quiet", if you don\'t mind though. */ /* Text1_0: You\'ve caught me at a critical time in my research! No worries, you\'re welcome to join me in quiet contemplation... emphasis on "quiet", if you don\'t mind though. */ /* Text1_1: You\'ve caught me at a critical time in my research! No worries, you\'re welcome to join me in quiet contemplation... emphasis on "quiet", if you don\'t mind though. */
