UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='朋友，这是自己造成的创伤。我实在无法面对这样一个在巫妖王的蹂躏下充满恐慌的世界。$B$B这是我救赎之旅的第一站，如果我的罪孽无法得到原谅，我会设法用我的余生加以偿还。' WHERE entry=15297; /* Text0_0: A self-inflicted wound, friend.  I could not bear to look upon a world where I\'d committed so many horrors under the Lich King\'s grasp.$B$BIt was my first step towards redemption, and if my sins are unforgivable, then I will attempt to atone for them for the rest of my life. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我曾经是一名圣骑士，$n。由于我罪孽深重，现在圣光已离我远去。$B$B我会尽我所能帮助我的盟友，我绝不会再触碰黑暗的力量。' WHERE entry=15298; /* Text0_0: I was once a paladin, $N.  Now the Light shuns me, for my sins are too great.$B$BI will aid my allies as best I can, but never again will I wield the powers of darkness. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='从这里，你能看到大灾变所造成的全部破坏。看到我们的世界竟然如此脆弱，这真是令人胆寒。' WHERE entry=15301; /* Text0_0: From up here you can see the full scope of the cataclysm\'s destruction. It is chilling to see just how fragile our world really is. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='$c，东方吹来了一阵污秽的风。' WHERE entry=15302; /* Text0_0: A foul wind blows from the East, $c. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='对于治疗这种蔓生，我有一点主意，$c。$B$B不幸的是，纳拉雷克斯已经完全陷入了混乱，拒绝进行任何尝试。' WHERE entry=15303; /* Text0_0: I have a few ideas on how to help heal the overgrowth, $c.$B$BUnfortunately, Naralex is so upset, he refuses to take any more chances. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='绝不能让悲痛的心情削弱我们的力量。我们将并肩作战，以强大的力量击退入侵者。' WHERE entry=15309; /* Text0_0: We must not let our grief weaken us. Our people will stand strong against the invaders. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='终于盼到我要的援助了！我准备了滑栓需要的各项文书。现在只剩下找人执行了。' WHERE entry=15310; /* Text0_0: Finally, the backup I\'ve been waiting for! I prepared the paperwork that Snagglebolt requested. All that remains is for someone to serve it. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='很高兴你能和我们在一起，$n。对付纳迦可不是一件容易的事！' WHERE entry=15313; /* Text0_0: I\'m glad you\'re out here with us, $N. It\'s not easy getting stuff from naga! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你好，$c！荣耀岗哨就在前面。那是联盟在石爪山脉和海岸之间的唯一通道。$B$B根据我的亲身经验，那也是一条充满危险的道路。' WHERE entry=15315; /* Text0_0: Hail, $c! Just up ahead you\'ll find Honor\'s Stand, the Alliance\'s only link between Stonetalon and the coast.$B$BThe road\'s a treacherous one, though. I speak from experience. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='她回来了。暗矛部族的仇恨终于要在今天有个了结。$B$B准备好以后就告诉我们，$n。我们绝不会再让她逃走。' WHERE entry=15318; /* Text0_0: She has returned. Tha revenge of the Darkspear finally comes to pass dis day.$B$BLet me know when ya ready, $n. We\'ll not let her slip away again. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='瓦里玛萨斯？不，他已经有一阵子没来报到了。他无疑是外出完成他的女王交给他的任务去了。' WHERE entry=15319; /* Text0_0: Varimathras? No, he hasn\'t reported in for some time. No doubt he\'s off on an errand of importance for his queen. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='瓦里玛萨斯，嗯…不在的时候，我被派来协助布拉贡大人完成任务。' WHERE entry=15320; /* Text0_0: While Varimathras is, uh... away, I\'ve been assigned to assist Captain Bragor in his duties. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='由于幽暗城的大部分兵力都已部署在了诺森德的复仇港，酋长派我们来支援幽暗城的防守。',Text0_1_loc4='由于幽暗城的大部分兵力都已部署在了诺森德的复仇港，酋长派我们来支援幽暗城的防守。' WHERE entry=15321; /* Text0_0: With the bulk of Undercity\'s forces deployed to Vengeance Landing in Northrend, the Warchief has sent us to reinforce the city\'s defenses. */ /* Text0_1: With the bulk of Undercity\'s forces deployed to Vengeance Landing in Northrend, the Warchief has sent us to reinforce the city\'s defenses. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我们来到安戈洛只为了一件事：利润。我的同伴我和一直在寻找生意上的合作对象。你有兴趣吗？' WHERE entry=15325; /* Text0_0: We came here to Un\'Goro with one objective in mind: profit.  My associates and I are always looking for business partners, if you\'re interested. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你好， $n。很高兴见到你在这里。这里简直是一团乱了。' WHERE entry=15326; /* Text0_0: Heya, $N. I\'m sure glad that you\'re here. This is turning into a mess. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你知道吗？贫瘠之地曾经是一片青葱茂密的森林。几千年以前，那时第一次大崩裂还没有发生。卡多雷照料着这片繁荣富饶之地。但随着大陆分崩离析，这一片被撕裂的陆地成为了现在被我们称为卡利姆多的地方，昔日的绿地成为了一片被阳光炙烤的荒芜平原。$B$B当我第一次听说这场恐怖的悲剧时，我就决定要找到办法，让森林重新生长在这片土地上。' WHERE entry=15327; /* Text0_0: Did you know that the Barrens was once a lush forest? Thousands of years ago, before the first Sundering, it was verdant and thriving, watched over by the Kaldorei. But when the continents were torn apart, and this land became separated as what we call Kalimdor, this valley of nature became a harsh, sun-scorched plain.$B$BWhen I first learned this, I saw it as a great tragedy. I decided I would find a way to regrow the forests once more. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='在研究这片土地的时候，我发现有一座洞穴一直延伸到地下很深的地方。在这片炎热的荒原下面，地下暗河形成的水网覆盖了很大一片地方。我称这座因暗河冲刷而形成的洞穴为哀嚎洞穴。因为风和水流在这座洞中总是会发出一阵阵凄厉的嚎叫。$B$B我相信，这座洞穴是让大地回复生机的契机。暗河中的水已经在贫瘠之地的一些角落里渗透到地面，形成了一些葱翠茂盛的绿洲……如果这种渗水作用得到加强，那么这片土地就会被绿色所覆盖。' WHERE entry=15328; /* Text0_0: While studying the land, I discovered a cave that stretched deep beneath the earth. These waterways carried underground rivers for miles beneath the parched savannah above. I named them the Wailing Caverns, for the howls made by the wind and steam as they coursed through its depths.$B$BThis would be the instrument of revival, I thought. The water had already bubbled to the surface as small, lush oases throughout the Barrens...if it were imbued, enhanced, this growth could spread across the entire land. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我的计划是将这些地下水与翡翠梦境直接连通。我带领我忠实的信徒们，进入到哀嚎洞穴深处，在冥想中进入翡翠梦境。通过我的躯体，这个世界和翡翠梦境连接在一起。$B$B然而就在那时，发生了可怕的灾祸。' WHERE entry=15329; /* Text0_0: My plan was to connect these underground waters directly to the Emerald Dream itself. With my faithful disciples, I journeyed deep within the Wailing Caverns, settled into meditation, and entered the Dream. Through my own body, this world was connected to it.$B$BIt was there that everything went wrong. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我在翡翠梦境中遭遇了可怖的腐蚀力量，言语难尽其详。无尽的噩梦抓住了我，折磨我的心智。我无法摆脱它的囚禁。我的信徒们无法唤醒我。$B$B无论这种腐蚀来自于何处，它已经通过我的躯体来到了我们的世界。它的能量藉由我进入哀嚎洞穴。那种恐怖的力量扭曲了这里的野生动物，让它们变成了怪物。就连我的信徒们也受到了影响。他们的意识变得疯狂野蛮。他们的身体变得如同巨大的毒蛇。现在他们称自己为尖牙德鲁伊。' WHERE entry=15330; /* Text0_0: I came upon what I can only describe as an overwhelming corruption within the Emerald Dream. An unending nightmare that seized me in its claws and tore at my very mind. I could not break free of its grasp; my disciples were unable to wake me.$B$BWhatever this corruption was, it found its way into our world through my body. I did indeed channel its energies into the Wailing Caverns, and its horrible influence twisted the wildlife there into chaotic, deviate forms. Even my disciples were affected; their minds overcome by madness and savagery, they took on the forms of serpents, and called themselves the Druids of the Fang. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我被我的最后一名信徒穆约和一队冒险者救了出来。我以为我的计划已经彻底失败了。当大灾变到来时，我才意识到，我的计划可以说是过度地成功了！$B$B当贫瘠之地裂开时，巨大的地下水流涌上地表，其中充满了那股在哀嚎洞穴中肆虐的诡异能量。各种生命随之迅速繁衍壮大，无论植物还是动物……都在不受控制地过度生长。$B$B我以为自己能控制自然本身的形态和变化。而现在，我必须为自己的傲慢做出补救。这种生命的蔓生必须被阻止，否则它就会吞没整个自然生态。' WHERE entry=15331; /* Text0_0: I was saved by my last disciple, Muyoh, and a band of adventurers. I considered the entire incident a failure. It wasn\'t until the Cataclysm occured that I realized I\'d been far too successful!$B$BWhen the Barrens was cracked apart, a great font of underground water was breached and flowed up to the surface, full of the energies it was imbued with in the Wailing Caverns. Life immediately sprung from the earth around it, and the animals thrived...and then it continued to grow, uncontrollably, unchecked.$B$BNow I have to answer for my arrogance in thinking I could dictate the flow and shape of nature myself. This overgrowth must be stopped, before it chokes out the natural wildlife entirely. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='胡说。难道我雇佣了一个瞎眼的侍从？这里到处都是龙。$b$b我的邻居斯巴克说它们是“恐龙”。但我知道龙是什么样子。所以它们必须被消灭。' WHERE entry=15332; /* Text0_0: Nonsense.  Have I hired a blind squire?  There are dragons everywhere.$b$bMy neighbor Spark refers to them as "dinosaurs", but I know a dragon when I see one.  They must be slayed. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='这是个好问题。$b$b温泉的周围，西边悬崖上的烽火，以及北面通往希利苏斯的小路。$b$b这些都是我要去查看的地方。' WHERE entry=15333; /* Text0_0: A fair question.$b$bOne might check the perimeter of the hot springs.  Or one might look for signal fires up in the cliffs to the west.  Finally, the path to Silithus, far to the north, is often wrought with danger.$b$bThose would be the places I\'d check. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我的主人需要你。' WHERE entry=15346; /* Text0_0: My patron requests your presence. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='嗯，$N?' WHERE entry=15347; /* Text0_0: Yes, $N? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你是谁？你想从我们的部族得到什么？',Text1_0_loc4='娜博亚，是你吗？' WHERE entry=15348; /* Text0_0: Who are you?  What do you want with our tribe? */ /* Text1_0: Nablya, is that you? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text2_0_loc4='外乡人，欢迎来到我们的家园。',Text3_0_loc4='你是来进行观察的吗？想要一个椰子吗？' WHERE entry=15348; /* Text2_0: Welcome, outsider, to our home. */ /* Text3_0: Have you come to observe?  Would you like a coconut? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我们部落中的一些人能够驾驭雷电的力量。我们就是用这种力量来抵抗入侵者，不管是人类、兽人还是恐龙。$b$b要知道，我们的雷电能够震晕任何恐龙。' WHERE entry=15349; /* Text0_0: A few of our tribe have harnessed the power of thunder.  We use it to defend ourselves against invaders, whether human, orc, or dinosaur.$b$bOur thunder stuns all dinosaurs, you know. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='个体的力量很重要，但全族的力量更加重要。只有当我们部族中最弱小的个体也强大起来，我们的部族才会真正变得强大。' WHERE entry=15350; /* Text0_0: Individual strength is important, but tribal strength is more so.  Our tribe is only as strong as its weakest member. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='南边的鳄鱼人喜欢吃小动物，比如青蛙和鹦鹉。我们猩猩则喜欢吃鳄鱼人。恐龙喜欢吃猩猩。所有这些都是严肃的自然规律。$b$b人类和兽人也会猎杀猩猩。但他们只剥去我们的毛皮，我们的尸体则被随意丢弃，任由它们腐烂。所以我们才会攻击人类和兽人。' WHERE entry=15351; /* Text0_0: The lashers to the south will eat small creatures, like frogs and parrots.  We, the gorillas, will eat the lashers.  And dinosaurs will eat gorillas.  All this is honorable and natural.$b$bThe humans and orcs also hunt the gorilla, but they take the skin and leave the body to rot.  This is why we attack the humans and orcs. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='安戈洛环形山中的这种花是非常特别的。你说对不对，$n？' WHERE entry=15353; /* Text0_0: The flora of Un\'Goro Crater are quite remarkable, to be sure.  Wouldn\'t you agree, $N? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='就像过去一样，对不对， $n？' WHERE entry=15354; /* Text0_0: Just like old times, eh, $N? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='有人愿意帮忙吗？还是你需要更多训练，$n？$B$B不知你是否注意到，我现在很忙。' WHERE entry=15357; /* Text0_0: A little help here? Or do you need more training, $N?$B$BI\'m kinda busy at the moment if you hadn\'t noticed. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='这个地方看上去很不错。只是需要进行一下清洁。$B$B你在找工作吗，$n？' WHERE entry=15360; /* Text0_0: This place seems nice enough, I suppose. Needs a little elbow grease.$B$BYou looking for a job, $N? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='全能战士NX-01型毁坏！' WHERE entry=15367; /* Text0_0: Warrior-Matic NX-01 destroy! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='嗨，你听过那个关于$r$c的故事么？事情是这样的：$b$b一个$r$c走进一座洞穴，开始和猩猩战斗。那群猩猩的头领说：“嘿，你为什么要这么干？！”那个$r$c就说：“是一个地精让我这么干的。”$b$b猩猩头领说：“地精让你干什么，你就干什么？”$r$c回答：“是的，因为我很笨，浑身臭气，而且还用两条腿走路。”$b$b很有趣，对不对？嗯……也许还需要再做些加工……' WHERE entry=15369; /* Text0_0: Hey, did you hear the one about the $r $c?  OK, here goes:$b$bA $r $c walks into a cave and starts fighting gorillas.  The leader of the gorillas says, "Hey, why are you doing that?!"  So then the $r $c says, "A goblin told me to."$b$bThe gorilla leader says, "Do you do everything that goblins tell you to do?"  And the $r $c says, "Yes, because I\'m stupid and smelly and I walk on two legs."$b$bPretty funny, huh?  Hmm... maybe it needs some work... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='夺回吉尔尼斯城的时刻已经到了。' WHERE entry=15377; /* Text0_0: The time to take back Gilneas City is at hand. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你好，$r。我察觉到你对我出现在这里感到困惑。其他人也心存怀疑，不过鉴于我的同胞给他们带来的遭遇，我并不怪他们。$B$B太阳之井事件后发生了很多事，几乎没有一样是好事。我着手开始收拾残局，希望能挽救我此行带来的影响。要说的很多，要做的更多，不过记住这一点：不是蓝龙军团的每个成员都责怪艾泽拉斯的凡人给这个世界带来的祸患。$B$B我们中的某些成员对此有着更深的理解。' WHERE entry=15381; /* Text0_0: Greetings, $r. I sense some confusion at my presence here. The others harbor suspicion as well, and I cannot blame them, after what my brethren have put them through.$B$BMuch has happened since the events at the Sunwell, little of it good. And so it falls to me to pick up the pieces, and attempt to salvage the pride of my flight. There is much to say, and more to do, but know this: Not all in the Blue Dragonflight blame the mortal races of Azeroth for the troubles that have befallen the world.$B$BSome of us have more sense than that. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我们必须坚守阵地。如果北方城堡失守，我们就只能背水一战了！' WHERE entry=15393; /* Text0_0: We must hold fast. If Northwatch falls, there is nothing to our backs but the sea! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我到这里来可不是为了渡假，朋友。诺格弗格派我来这里完成一个任务：确认该如何从这些异种怪物身上获取利润。如果不行，就将它们消灭干净。$B$B如果像你这样的$r想要为热砂集团做些事情，那么我倒是可以给你个机会。' WHERE entry=15394; /* Text0_0: I\'m not here on vacation, pal. Noggenfogger sent me down here with a mission: Find out how to turn a profit on these silithid, or wipe \'em clean.$B$BIf a $r like you wants to do some favors for the Steamwheedle Cartel, I could use a hand. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='全体上甲板！把他们赶走！' WHERE entry=15397; /* Text0_0: All hands topside! Run \'em through! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='即使我们能取得胜利，我也要用一个月的时间才能把甲板上的脏东西清理干净。' WHERE entry=15398; /* Text0_0: Assuming we make it through this, it\'ll take a month to clean the brains off my brasswork. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你的提问相当机敏，年轻的$c。铭文师能够制作蕴藏强大力量的塔罗牌，当然即使是铭文师自己也无法完全驾驭他们所创造出来的东西。决定一切的还是命运。$b$b如果你有办法集齐完整的套牌，请把它带给我，你会得到不错的回报。' WHERE entry=15400; /* Text0_0: You are astute to ask, young $c.  Scribes are capable of inscribing tarot cards of great power, although even they do not have full control of what they make.  The fates decide for them.$b$bIf you manage to obtain a completed deck, please bring it to me for a magnificent reward. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='专注于比赛，$n！' WHERE entry=15401; /* Text0_0: Get your head in the game, $N! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你好，小子。你干得很不错！$B$B我会在另一边等你。' WHERE entry=15403; /* Text0_0: Heya, kid. Great job out there!$B$BSee you on the other side. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='这些关于食物的话题让我更饿了！' WHERE entry=15404; /* Text0_0: All this talk about food is making me hungry! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='现在不是自相残杀的时候，$n。' WHERE entry=15408; /* Text0_0: It is not the time to turn against one another, $N. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='他们把科林伍德沉入了海底，但我们还是把她的舰炮拖到了岸上。$B$B只要我有火药，那些野兽肮脏的绿脚就别想踏上这片海滩！' WHERE entry=15409; /* Text0_0: They sunk the Collingwood off the coast, but we managed to drag her carronades to the shore.$B$BThose animals won\'t set one filthy green foot on this beach! Not while I\'ve got powder! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='说话很容易，但行动才有力量，$n$g先生:女士; 。' WHERE entry=15411; /* Text0_0: Quick is the word and sharp is the action, $gMister:Miss; $N. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='霜翼大厅前的最后一道屏障已经被我们击破了，$g小伙子:姑娘;。只有辛达苟萨还挡在正义之师和巫妖王之间！还等什么？！' WHERE entry=15412; /* Text0_0: We got the final barrier blockin\' entry to Frostwing Halls down, $g lad:lass;. Only Sindragosa stands between the Lich King and divine retribution! What are ye waitin\' for?! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='所有的屏障都被击破了，$n！只有辛达苟萨还挡在我们和巫妖王之间。审判即将开始…' WHERE entry=15415; /* Text0_0: All barriers are now down, $N! Only Sindragosa stands between the Lich King and us. Justice comes soon... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我们在这里的情况相当糟糕，$n。' WHERE entry=15418; /* Text0_0: We\'re in a pretty tight pickle here, $N. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我们待在这里干什么？难道我们不应该想办法离开这座岛吗？！！！' WHERE entry=15421; /* Text0_0: What are we doing up here? Shouldn\'t we be trying to find a way off of this island?!!! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='胶囊镇实在是工程学上的一项伟大成就！' WHERE entry=15422; /* Text0_0: This Town-In-A-Box is a remarkable feat of engineering! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='是的，是的，这非常有趣。但你要知道，我们正在为生存而战。和藏在那座洞里的东西相比，这些俾格米人根本算不上什么问题！$B$B我那个没用的助手在哪里？我现在可是非常需要她呢！也许她又去偷懒了。我猜她肯定还在抱怨没有人关心她，没有人看重她……' WHERE entry=15431; /* Text0_0: Yes, yes, that\'s all very interesting, but as you can see here, we\'re in a fight for our lives, and these pygmies are the least of our problems compared to what\'s inside that cave!$B$BWhere\'s my worthless assistant when I need her the most? Probably off being lazy somewhere and complaining that no one asks her how her day is going.... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='去哪里都行，只要离开这里……' WHERE entry=15432; /* Text0_0: Anywhere but here... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='想要什么？',Text1_0_loc4='食人魔看起来很有趣。' WHERE entry=15435; /* Text0_0: What want? */ /* Text1_0: Ogre look funny. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text2_0_loc4='我饿了。',Text3_0_loc4='我不喜欢沙子。' WHERE entry=15435; /* Text2_0: Me hungry. */ /* Text3_0: Me not like sand. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='吉尔尼斯城之战正在进行！你可以直接到前线去，或者等待我们的队伍重新集结，展开下一波进攻。' WHERE entry=15442; /* Text0_0: The Battle for Gilneas City is underway!  You can head to the frontlines or wait until our men regroup for the next attack. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我们的战士正在重新集结。再过几分钟，他们就能做好战斗准备。' WHERE entry=15443; /* Text0_0: Our men are regrouping.  They will be ready for battle in mere minutes. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我帮助地精女士和食人魔交朋友。' WHERE entry=15444; /* Text0_0: Me help goblin lady make friend with ogres. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你好，英雄。我制造和出售德鲁伊需要的树纹套装。',Text0_1_loc4='你好，英雄。我制造和出售德鲁伊需要的树纹套装。' WHERE entry=15445; /* Text0_0: Greetings, hero. I craft and sell Freya\'s Lasherweave armor for druids. */ /* Text0_1: Greetings, hero. I craft and sell Freya\'s Lasherweave armor for druids. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你好，英雄。我制造和出售猎人需要的安卡哈猎血套装。',Text0_1_loc4='你好，英雄。我制造和出售猎人需要的安卡哈猎血套装。' WHERE entry=15449; /* Text0_0: Greetings, hero. I craft and sell Ahn\'kahar Blood Hunter armor for hunters. */ /* Text0_1: Greetings, hero. I craft and sell Ahn\'kahar Blood Hunter armor for hunters. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你好，英雄。我制造和出售战士需要的伊米亚之王套装。' WHERE entry=15450; /* Text0_0: Greetings, hero. I craft and sell Ymirjar Lord\'s armor for warriors. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='<你在路旁发现了这名不幸的士兵，他的身上有许多仿佛是用长匕首划开的伤口。你将他的身体翻转过来，注意到一些齿印。>$B$B<这会是野兽干的吗？>' WHERE entry=15455; /* Text0_0: <The unfortunate soldier you find at the side of the road has been gutted with what appears to have been long knives. Rolling the body over, you notice teeth marks.>$B$B<Could wild animals have done this?> */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='太奇怪了。我听说贫瘠之地非常……贫瘠。$B$B而这片森林在昨天晚上才冒出来，现在却已经吞掉了我的营地，还把道路堵住了！' WHERE entry=15459; /* Text0_0: Look at this mess. I was told the Barrens would be... barren.$B$BThis jungle appeared overnight and has already swallowed up my camp and choked off the roads! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你是来参加狩猎的吗，$n？',Text0_1_loc4='你是来参加狩猎的吗，$n？' WHERE entry=15460; /* Text0_0: Have you come to join the hunt, $N? */ /* Text0_1: Have you come to join the hunt, $N? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='滚吧，$c。我的狩猎不需要你。',Text0_1_loc4='滚吧，$c。我的狩猎不需要你。' WHERE entry=15461; /* Text0_0: Be gone, $c.  I have no need of you in my hunt. */ /* Text0_1: Be gone, $c.  I have no need of you in my hunt. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='那么，你想要找到传说中的沙怒之剑？$B$B为了寻求财富与权力，你已经准备好为苏萨斯而杀戮？将热血泼洒在黄沙之上？$B$B既然如此……欢迎来到这片沙漠，朋友。' WHERE entry=15466; /* Text0_0: So, you wanna find de fabled swords of de Sandfury, eh?$B$BYa be ready ta kill for Sul\'thraze? Spill de blood across de sands? In search of treasure, of power?$B$BIf ya are...welcome to de desert, mon. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我会确保暗矛巨魔顽强屹立，发挥出它所应有的力量。' WHERE entry=15468; /* Text0_0: I will see ta it personally dat the Darkspear rise as a power in their own right. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='这已经不是我第一次在古怪危险的丛林中拼尽全力挣扎求生了。我去过这个世界的许多地方，$g孩子:姑娘;，如果我会在这里完蛋，那我也只不过是个没用的家伙。' WHERE entry=15471; /* Text0_0: This ain\'t the first time I been stuck up to me teef in a jungle that up an\' done ambushed me. I been all over the world, $gson:missy;, an\' I\'ll be hog-smacked if this one\'s gonna be the end of me. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='在很久以前，我和我的同伴根本没有几个钱喝酒。几番豪饮之后，我们就花光了所有的铜板，搞得连每天的日常酒钱都没了着落。$B$B于是我们决定上老巴克的啤酒馆去，从他堆在酒馆顶楼上那些硕大的啤酒桶里“征收”一桶来。$B$B说干就干，我们用短柄斧砍断了支撑酒桶的架子，好家伙，那满满装着啤酒的酒桶就这么从茅草屋顶上滚了下去，就好象一只从巢里掉出来的鸟崽，呃，应该是只大胖鸟，能轧死人的那种。' WHERE entry=15473; /* Text0_0: Back in the day \'afore the day, me and me mates didn\'t have much in the way of drinkin\' money, as is we spent our pay on booze an\' that didn\'t leave none left over for more casual drinkin\'.$B$BSo we decide we\'re gonna comm-an-deer one of them epic-sized kegs of ol\' Barkerstout from the loft of Barky\'s Brewpub.$B$BWe chopped the supports out with hatchets and that ol\' boy just up an\' ROLLED on out through the side of the thatch roof like a baby bird leavin\' the nest, but some sort of big round beer bird, that could crush a man. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='知道为什么他们管它叫刚强烈酒吗？因为它曾经一直从山上滚下来。那时你可没办法和它商量，和它讲道理。它根本不懂得同情，不知道后悔，也绝不会害怕。$B$B那简直就像是一场啤酒雪崩，要是在那里死掉绝对算得上是轰轰烈烈。$B$B酒桶在撞到山下的孤儿院时炸开了。我立刻大张着嘴扑到了满是酒液的泥地里，然后……我记不清那个故事是怎样结尾的了。想要看看我的刺青吗？$B$B<老脏鬼佩蒂脱下了裤子。>' WHERE entry=15474; /* Text0_0: You know why they call it stout? \'Cuz once it were rolling down the hill it couldnae be bargained wit\', couldnae be reasoned wit\'. It felt no pity, no remorse, no fear.$B$BIt were like a beervalanche, which is a damn fine way to die.$B$BSo that keg explodered soon as it hit the orphanage at the bottom of the hill, and I dove inta the mud puddle wit\' me mouth open, an\'... Come to think of it, I don\'t \'member how this story ends. Wanna see the tattoo?$B$B<Ol\' Durty Pete drops his pants.> */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='看到这杆枪了吗，$g小子:小妞;？$B$B<老脏鬼佩蒂满不在乎地在你面前挥舞着他的武器。>$B$B这杆枪去过诺森德以外的每一块大陆。我已经数不清它救过我几次命了，大概七次吧。有一次，“大麦克”麦当高——我说的可不是那个小麦当高，而是他的老爹。那家伙想要用他最年轻的女儿和我换这杆枪。$B$B要知道，爱蒂可是个有趣的女孩。她和我的枪有很多相同的地方——嘴很大，还是大龅牙，很容易走火，一走火就能把你烤个半熟。$B$B你有没有听说过那个小爱蒂和查克·白酒须用25枚银币打赌的故事？他们赌的就是爱蒂能一脚踢在查克的脑袋上，让查克疼得大哭鼻子！' WHERE entry=15475; /* Text0_0: You see this here gun, $gboy:missy;?$B$B<Ol\' Durty Pete casually waves his weapon directly at your face.>$B$BThis here gun\'s seen action on every continent but for Northrend. It\'s saved me life more times than I can count: Seven. One time, "Big Mackie" MacDungal - not the wee MacDungal now, but his pappy - offered me his youngest daughter in barter for me gun.$B$BLet me tell you somethin\' about Edie: she and me gun had a lot in common. Wide-mouthed. Buck-toofed. Dangerous from the biz-ness end. Likin\' to go oft half-cocked.$B$BYou heard about the time wee Edie bet Chuck Brandybeard 25 silver she could kick \'im in the head so hard he would weep snot? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='唔，这消息以惊人的速度传播。没过多久，米奈希尔港的所有人都聚集了起来，有些人开始打赌，水果小贩则干脆就地做起了生意。他们就具体的规则进行了冗长的争论，直到镇长亲自出面他们才达成了共识：擦血不算输。$B$B就这样，查克跪倒下去，她则在一只凳子上挺起身，扬起她的那条大粗腿——我好像扯远了。重点是，我当时真应该接受那提议，因为这把枪现在有点儿不灵光了。' WHERE entry=15476; /* Text0_0: Ayup, word got around fast and soon the whole of Menethil gathered around to see it through, with bettin\' and fruit vendors and the like, an\' there were some consternation over the rules that had to be ironed out with a big rigamarole, \'til the mayor hisself agreed that weepin\' blood tain\'t count fer nothin\'.$B$BSo Chuck kneels down an\' she gets up on a stool and REARS back with that big \'ol thick leg of hers and - but I\'m digressin\'. Point is, I shoulda taken the deal, \'cuz this gun\'s a bit dodgy. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='他们一直都叫我老脏鬼佩蒂。$B$B不过我也有过又年轻又脏的时候。那时我曾经打算用自己的雕刻工艺吸引一个名叫贝丽的姑娘。她可真是个肉感的甜心。$B$B老贝丽！她就完全是另一回事了。我的那个贝丽可不一样。她的身上除了中间的一段细腰之外，都是那么丰满，真是该多么漂亮就有多么漂亮。$B$B所以我找了一块像她的皮肤一样雪白的石灰石，打算雕出了一件惊世杰作。但我把比例全搞错了。最后，我只弄出一个奇怪的大块头。应该叫它什么呢？枪靶子吧！' WHERE entry=15477; /* Text0_0: They didn\'t always call me Ol\' Durty Pete.$B$BOnce, when I were young an\' durty, I thought I\'d impress a sweet buxom lass named Bellie with me chiselin\' styles.$B$BOl\' Bellie! She were somthin\' else. Firm, that one. All big but for the middle, like they was meant to be.$B$BSo I found me a chunk of limestone white like her skin and I set about to chiselin\' and carvin\' and creatin\' what you\'d call a masterpiece, but I got me scale all wrong, see? I ended up with an enormous, what would you call it? Butt. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='听我说，$g小子:小妞;，一个枪靶子可不能当作送给女士的礼物。但我还是很喜欢它。所以我把它送给了当地的酒馆做装饰品。$B$B他们管它叫脏鬼佩蒂的屁股。最后就连那家酒馆也被叫成这个名字了。可恨的是，那家酒馆后来被兽人烧成了一块黑炭。现在那里只剩下了我那个变黑的大屁股嵌在一堆残垣断壁上。$B$B<老脏鬼佩蒂的眼眶里落下一滴泪水。>' WHERE entry=15478; /* Text0_0: You heard me, $glad:lass; - a butt! Not a fitting gift for a lady. But I liked it. So I offered to donate it to me local drinkin\' hole.$B$BThey called it Durty Pete\'s Bottom, and eventually named the pub after it, afore them orcs burned it to toast, and all that\'s left today is me big blackened bottom amidst a heap of rubble.$B$B<Ol\' Durty Pete sheds a single tear.> */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='在那场战争中——我说的是很早以前的那场战争。那时兽人好似都还骑着龙打仗？总之，我和威斯利从南海镇出发，前往米奈希尔港。我们只乘着一艘用多节的松木做成的独木舟，肚子里灌满了樱桃酒。$B$B因为周围只有海水，所以我们很难判断走了多远的路。不过，应该是在走完三分之一路程的时候，我感到我的脚被打湿了。' WHERE entry=15479; /* Text0_0: Back in the war - not that one, the udder one - when them orcs rode dragons? Me and Whistler set out to cross from Southshore to Menethil Harbor inna rowboat we\'d built outta knotty pine while soused to our eyeballs on Cherry Grog.$B$BAn\' we got about a third the way by my reckoning, which were mostly far judgin\' by the fact that there were nothing all around us but the sea, when my feet got to start feelin\' wet. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='现在，$g小子:姑娘;，让我和你说说那根长满瘤子的老松木吧。它的确是有很多瘤子和疖子。$B$B那些节瘤让松木上多了许多窟窿，用这种木材可做不出好的独木舟来。我要给它上面涂一层柏油，威斯利却不同意。所以我们决定用拼酒来达成一致。$B$B酒喝光了以后，我们开始抽出匕首来对打。当然，我们只是要比试一下。$B$B不管怎样，那艘松木船最后也没能到达米奈希尔港。我相信我们之中至少有一个人，或者两个人都溺水了。' WHERE entry=15480; /* Text0_0: Now let me tell you somethin\' about knotty pine, it\'s got knots, $gson:missy;.$B$BAnd knots is just big holes in trees, which makes for a stupid rowboat and I blamed Whistler but he had his own ideas about my choice of tar (I chose to forget it) so we decided to settle it by drinking.$B$BWhen the grog ran out, that\'s when we had the knife fight. For sport.$B$BAnyways, we never made it to Menethil, and I\'m pretty sure one or both of us drowned. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='要是你有胃口，贫瘠之地可是个打猎的好地方。' WHERE entry=15481; /* Text0_0: There\'s some good huntin\' to be found here in the Barrens, if you\'ve the stomach for it. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我们和前线指挥站还没取得联系。但多亏了你和那些野猪人的“沟通”。只要再做些努力，就能重新打通道路了。' WHERE entry=15482; /* Text0_0: We\'re still cut off from Forward Command, but thanks to your \'negotiations\' with the quilboar, we should be able to re-open the roads with a little elbow grease. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='人们对迅猛龙的了解只限于野蛮凶残，除此之外知之甚少。实际上，他们的忠诚和机智超乎你的想象。' WHERE entry=15484; /* Text0_0: People tink raptors wild and vicious, but little else. In truth, they be loyal and cunnin\' in ways ya hardly know. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你想要加入对抗纳迦的战斗吗？' WHERE entry=15485; /* Text0_0: Ya want to join the attack on the naga? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='作为暗矛部族的一员，是我最大的光荣。沃金将领导我们赢取巨大的荣耀。' WHERE entry=15490; /* Text0_0: I\'ve never been more proud ta be a Darkspear. Vol\'jin leads us ta glory. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='$c，你叫什么名字？$n？欢迎来到贫瘠之地。你正站在我们在这片大陆上最重要的前锋阵地之一。如果你能帮助我们，我会感到非常荣幸。' WHERE entry=15495; /* Text0_0: What is your name, $c? $N?$B$BWelcome to the Barrens. You are standing at the vanguard of one of our most important operations on this continent. I would be honored if you were to lend us your strength. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='要知道，我衷心感谢你的帮助，$c。我们在这里的敌人并不是普通的野兽，而是兼具狡诈与疯狂的怪物。我们必须团结一致，否则就会被它们逐一击破。' WHERE entry=15496; /* Text0_0: I want you to know that I sincerely appreciate your aid, $c. We are not fighting beasts out here, but a foe both cunning and fanatical. We must stick together or hang separately. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='这太疯狂了！沃金是认真的。他要找到那个女海巫，向她复仇。' WHERE entry=15500; /* Text0_0: Dis is wild! Vol\'jin\'s not messin\' around. He\'s going afta tha Sea Witch wit a vengeance. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='嗨，$g小伙子:姑娘;我正在想应该怎样拿到我的那一份。',Text0_1_loc4='嗨，$g小伙子:姑娘;我正在想应该怎样拿到我的那一份。',Text1_0_loc4='你也想分一份？那你可要努力了，宝贝儿！',Text1_1_loc4='你也想分一份？那你可要努力了，宝贝儿！' WHERE entry=15501; /* Text0_0: Hey $gman:woman;, I\'m just tryin\' to get my slice of the pie. */ /* Text0_1: Hey $gman:woman;, I\'m just tryin\' to get my slice of the pie. */ /* Text1_0: You want in on this? Smash and grab, baby! */ /* Text1_1: You want in on this? Smash and grab, baby! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text2_0_loc4='赶快，$c！能拿的全拿走！',Text2_1_loc4='赶快，$c！能拿的全拿走！',Text3_0_loc4='所有这些牛头人的身上都只有一些念珠和垃圾。你有没有找到什么有用的东西？',Text3_1_loc4='所有这些牛头人的身上都只有一些念珠和垃圾。你有没有找到什么有用的东西？' WHERE entry=15501; /* Text2_0: Hurry up, $c! Take everything you can! */ /* Text2_1: Hurry up, $c! Take everything you can! */ /* Text3_0: All these dead Tauren got on \'em is beads and junk. Did you score anything good? */ /* Text3_1: All these dead Tauren got on \'em is beads and junk. Did you score anything good? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text4_0_loc4='嗨，$c！这个地方已经被搜检得差不多了。不过你也许还可以花些时间来搜索一下。',Text4_1_loc4='嗨，$c！这个地方已经被搜检得差不多了。不过你也许还可以花些时间来搜索一下。',Text5_0_loc4='喔，你来这里不是要对我们进行突击搜查吧？',Text5_1_loc4='喔，你来这里不是要对我们进行突击搜查吧？' WHERE entry=15501; /* Text4_0: Hey, $c! This place is pretty picked over but you might still be able to find somethin\' worth your time. */ /* Text4_1: Hey, $c! This place is pretty picked over but you might still be able to find somethin\' worth your time. */ /* Text5_0: Whoa, you aren\'t here to bust us, are you? */ /* Text5_1: Whoa, you aren\'t here to bust us, are you? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='火山爆发的时候，你的朋友全都被贸易大王加里维克斯抓住了。$B$B我们必须尽快解决联盟的人，这样才能救出他们，离开这座岛。' WHERE entry=15508; /* Text0_0: Your friends were all taken prisoner by Trade Prince Gallywix while the volcano was exploding.$B$BWe are going to have to deal with the Alliance quickly if we\'re to rescue them and get off of this island. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='为杰罗德工作并不是那么糟糕。他也许偶尔会发发脾气，但他付的薪水很高。当我不能按进度完成工作的时候，他甚至还会帮我的忙。' WHERE entry=15510; /* Text0_0: Working for Jerrod isn\'t all that bad.  He might lose his temper now and again, but he pays well, and he even gives me a boost when I can\'t reach something in the cart. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我能为你做些什么？' WHERE entry=15511; /* Text0_0: What is it I can do for you? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='<亡灵卫兵希米尔专注地看着你。>' WHERE entry=15512; /* Text0_0: <Deathguard Simmer looks at you expectantly.> */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='任何野蛮人都可能赢得一场战斗。但真正的英雄所关注的并不是战场上的胜利，而是在最后一支羽箭落下之后去维系长久的和平。' WHERE entry=15514; /* Text0_0: Any savage can win a war. The true hero aims not merely for victory on the battlefield, but to attain a lasting peace after the final arrow falls. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你在贫瘠之地立下了令人难以置信的功绩，$n。$B$B有了像你这样的英雄，我们就能守住卡利姆多确保我们的家园能够实现长久的和平。' WHERE entry=15515; /* Text0_0: You\'re doing incredible work here in the Barrens, $N.$B$BWith the help of heroes like you, we can secure Kalimdor, and in doing so ensure a lasting peace in our homelands. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='$n!我该怎样帮助你，老朋友？' WHERE entry=15517; /* Text0_0: $N! How can I help you, old friend? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='这话可别对别人说。我很担心这里的将军并不想做他该做的事情。$B$B我们要对付的是部落。历史表明，他们从不会给予我们真正的和平。$B$B我们的目标是……把敌人消灭干净。' WHERE entry=15518; /* Text0_0: Just between you and me, I worry that the good General here doesn\'t have the stomach to do what needs to be done.$B$BThis is the Horde we\'re dealing with. History shows there can never be peace.$B$BOur goal should be ... annihilation. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你也许不会相信，像我这样的狼人竟然能做出美味的肉排。$B$B就因为我喜欢吃生肉……我还没有从飞行的疲惫中恢复过来……我脑袋上的血管还在一蹦一蹦的……$B$B我们在说什么？哦，是了！我在吉尔尼斯可是一位著名的美食家。' WHERE entry=15519; /* Text0_0: You might not think that a Worgen like myself would know how to cook a fine steak.$B$BJust \'cuz I like my meat raw... Still panting from flight... Arterial spray in my face...$B$BWhat were we talking about? Oh yes! I was quite the gourmet back in Gilneas. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='要到哪里去？' WHERE entry=15524; /* Text0_0: Going somewhere? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我们在这里竭尽全力医治残破的大地。就在这种极为艰难的情况下，我们还在夜晚遭到了袭击。' WHERE entry=15528; /* Text0_0: We do our best here to heal the broken earth. It was difficult enough before we started getting raided at night. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='希米尔说葛尔多有肚子，却没有脑子。这是什么意思？',Text1_0_loc4='葛尔多喜欢摘花。摘花就像是打仗。' WHERE entry=15531; /* Text0_0: Simmer say Gordo got guts, but got no brains.  Why he mean? */ /* Text1_0: Gordo like picking flowers.  Pick flowers kind of like killing. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text2_0_loc4='这里通风很不错。',Text3_0_loc4='乔汉说，葛尔多需要个裁缝来修整一下葛尔多的肚子。' WHERE entry=15531; /* Text2_0: It drafty out here. */ /* Text3_0: Johaan say Gordo need a tailor to fix Gordo tummy. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我代表杰出的，并依旧保持中立的热砂集团向你表示问候，并衷心希望你能在这里渡过一段愉快的时光。$B$B请记住，加基森欢迎所有人！只有海盗除外。' WHERE entry=15532; /* Text0_0: On behalf of the illustrious and still neutral Steamwheedle Cartel, I hope you enjoy your stay.$B$BRemember, everyone is welcome in Gadgetzan! Everyone except pirates. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='绝不能再耽搁了。必须完成凯旋壁垒的建造和布防，否则我们将没有可能在这片大陆上建立永久定居点。' WHERE entry=15535; /* Text0_0: We can afford no delay. Fort Triumph must be completed and reinforced, or any hope we have for permanent settlement on this continent will be erased. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='当我和我的蛮锤佣兵受雇守卫凯旋壁垒的时候，我以为我们的敌人将是部落。$B$B但现在我们却陷入了无数敌人的围困之中！爆炸的地精，挖洞的虫子，放电的蜥蜴……' WHERE entry=15536; /* Text0_0: When me and my Wildhammer Mercenaries were hired on to secure Fort Triumph, I imagined we\'d be fighting the Horde.$B$BBut we\'re set on from all sides! \'Sploding goblins, burrowing bugs, electro-fied lizards... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='萨尔万岁，$n！你是要帮我们消灭那些可恶的矮人和侏儒吗？' WHERE entry=15542; /* Text0_0: Thrall Hall, $N! Here to help kill some misguided dwarves and gnomes? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='嗨，$n。你要进去吗？' WHERE entry=15544; /* Text0_0: Hey there, $N. You heading in? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='$n！能帮帮我摆脱菲兹吗？他又要发脾气了！' WHERE entry=15545; /* Text0_0: $N! You wanna help me out here with Fizz? He\'s up to no good again! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='走吧，$c。$B$B在大灾变到来之前，我们发现了一些东西。$B$B我们挖出了一些本应该永远被深埋在地下的东西。$B$B无论你信仰什么神，你最好现在就向他祈祷崩裂的大地能再把它埋住……',Text0_1_loc4='走吧，$c。$B$B在大灾变到来之前，我们发现了一些东西。$B$B我们挖出了一些本应该永远被深埋在地下的东西。$B$B无论你信仰什么神，你最好现在就向他祈祷崩裂的大地能再把它埋住……' WHERE entry=15547; /* Text0_0: Turn away, $c.$B$BBefore the cataclysm hit, we found something.$B$BWe dug something up that should\'ve stayed buried.$B$BPray to whatever you believe in that the landslide was enough to keep it down... */ /* Text0_1: Turn away, $c.$B$BBefore the cataclysm hit, we found something.$B$BWe dug something up that should\'ve stayed buried.$B$BPray to whatever you believe in that the landslide was enough to keep it down... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我不敢相信菲兹和艾沃竟然会自相残杀。这一定是因为他们的压力太大了。现在我们更加需要你了，$n。' WHERE entry=15549; /* Text0_0: I can\'t believe that Fizz and Evol are at each other\'s throats again. It\'s the pressure. We need you now more than ever, $N. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='请投入硬币。' WHERE entry=15551; /* Text0_0: Please insert coins. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='这是我的工作，$c。将军在巡逻的时候，我扛起他的旗帜，并将旗帜牢牢插在土中。$B$B一位将军怎么可能没有旗帜？他还不如不穿裤子。' WHERE entry=15552; /* Text0_0: That\'s me job, $c. The General goes out on patrol, and I carry his banner and plant it in the dirt.$B$BImagine a General out and about without his banner. He might as well not wear pants. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='嗨！别碰那面旗，$g小子:姑娘;。' WHERE entry=15554; /* Text0_0: Hey! Hands off the banner, $gson:missy;. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='别闲逛了，我们在这里还有工作。' WHERE entry=15558; /* Text0_0: Do not loiter; we\'ve work to do here. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='这就是真相！战斗导致杀戮，杀戮导致战争。而这几乎就是我们全部客户的结局！$B$B现在，当人们要进行战斗的时候，它就发生在这里，也在这里结束！并发挥出最大的观赏潜力！' WHERE entry=15559; /* Text0_0: This is the truth of it! Fighting leads to killing, and killing leads to warring. And that was nearly the end of all our customers!$B$BNow, when men get to fighting, it happens here. And it finishes here! For maximum viewing potential! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我听说过这个叫奈辛瓦里的家伙。他来自于荆棘谷，以猎捕各种野兽为乐。$B$B他认为这是一种运动。真是个彻头彻尾的白痴，对不对？真不知道他到底把多少值钱的东西扔在田野里，任由它们烂掉！' WHERE entry=15561; /* Text0_0: I\'ve heard about this Nesingwary guy, out of Stranglethorn Vale, hunting all sorts of beasts for sport.$B$BFor SPORT. What a complete idiot, right? Think of all the profit he\'s letting rot in the field! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='呸！吵闹的牛头人吓不住我。' WHERE entry=15563; /* Text0_0: Bah! Rowdy tauren don\'t scare me none. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='这是一架单座飞机。但你可以骑在机身上。这非常安全。$B$B准备好了吗？' WHERE entry=15564; /* Text0_0: It\'s a one-seater plane, but you can always sit up on the fuselage. It\'s perfectly safe.$B$BYou ready? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='他是我的助手。$B$B虽然他也受到了瘟疫的感染，但显然感染的方式和我们有些区别。就像你和我一样，他也臣服于希尔瓦娜斯。$b$b这话不要告诉别人……说实话，我相信当他进入黑暗女王的房间时，黑暗女王并没有怀疑他的忠诚。' WHERE entry=15565; /* Text0_0: He\'s my assistant.$B$BSure, he\'s not been plagued in the same manner as we have, but he is clearly plagued nonetheless.  He\'s bent the knee to Sylvanas, so he\'s as much one of us as you or I.$b$bAnd just between you and me... to be perfectly honest, I think the Dark Lady thought he was already bending his knee when he entered her chamber! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='坚持住，$r。$b$b纳迦随时有可能再次发动攻击。',Text1_0_loc4='这里正是这场可能毁灭世界的大灾变爆发的核心区域之一。$b$b如果我们要生存下去，就必须发掘出它的原因。' WHERE entry=15569; /* Text0_0: Brace yourself, $r.$b$bThe naga could attack again any moment. */ /* Text1_0: This region is one of the epicenters of the cataclysm that threatens to rend our world.$b$bIf we manage to survive, we must try to discover its cause. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text2_0_loc4='对于这些船只的攻击显然不是偶然的。$b$b我们必须查清楚那些纳迦的动机。' WHERE entry=15569; /* Text2_0: The attacks on these ships, they are clearly not random.$b$bWe must discover the motives of the naga here. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='需要什麽吗?' WHERE entry=15572; /* Text0_0: Need something? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你必须帮助我，$c！暮光之锤袭击了我的飞艇，妄图夺走正在被运往奥格瑞玛的石板和水晶。' WHERE entry=15575; /* Text0_0: You have to help me, $c! Twilight\'s Hammer attacked my zeppelin and their men tried to take the tablets and the crystal I was transporting to Orgrimmar. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='侏儒夺回家园的时候终于到了。$B$B诺莫瑞根将再次回到我们的手中！' WHERE entry=15578; /* Text0_0: At last it is time for the exiled gnomes to return.$B$BOnce again Gnomeregan will be our home! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我们在矮人王国中得到了庇护。因此，我们对矮人感激不尽。但瑟玛普拉格对诺莫瑞根的统治应该到头了。$B$B我们犯下的大错让诺莫瑞根承受了太长时间的毒害。辐射炸弹曾经让我们彻底失去家园。现在，我们终于掌握了恢复家园的技术！$B$B我们必须夺回诺莫瑞根，让瑟玛普拉格得到正义的审判！' WHERE entry=15580; /* Text0_0: The dwarves have kept us safe in their home for some time now, and for that we thank them.  However, the traitorous Thermaplugg\'s occupation of our home must at last come to an end.$B$BGnomeregan has festered beneath the atomic weight of our ill-conceived plan for too long. The detonation of the radiation bombs drove us from our city, but we now possess the technology to take it back!$B$BWe will regain what is ours... and bring Thermaplugg to justice! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='诺莫瑞根行动将分成数个步骤完成：$B$B首先，我们必须夺回航空塔。这样我们的飞机才能支援进攻诺莫瑞根主入口的部队。$B$B而且，我们还在诺莫瑞根入口附近的一座建筑中发现了防辐射服。装备上防辐射服的侏儒部队能够直接进入诺莫瑞根。$B$B这样，我们就能在诺莫瑞根的核心对瑟玛普拉格发动直接攻击！' WHERE entry=15581; /* Text0_0: Operation: Gnomeregan is divided into a number of phases:$B$BFirst, we must retake the air tower.  This will allow our planes give us air support as we move towards Gnomeregan\'s main entrance.$B$BIn addition, a cache of mechanized Battle Suits was discovered in one of the nearby buildings.  Once we have those suits, our assault on the entrance should be unstoppable.$B$BThen, we go straight for Thermaplugg in the heart of Gnomeregan! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='矿车已经做好了出发的准备。' WHERE entry=15585; /* Text0_0: The mine cart is prepped and ready to go. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='欢迎来到前线，$c！如果只是躲在城堡里面，你将无法对现在的战争态势有真正的感受。这就是我总不愿意离开战场的原因。' WHERE entry=15586; /* Text0_0: Welcome to the field, $c! You can\'t get a feel for the tactical situation if you\'re hiding in a fortress all day. I always like to get my boots dirty. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你去过巴尔莫丹吗？那里发生了什么事？' WHERE entry=15588; /* Text0_0: Have you been to Bael Modan? What\'s going on over there? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='他们一定要付出代价，$n。他们全都要付出代价。' WHERE entry=15589; /* Text0_0: They\'re going to pay, $N. They\'re all going to pay. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='那些疯狂的牛头人。已经有好几年了，他们总是要炸掉我的飞行器！' WHERE entry=15590; /* Text0_0: These crazy tauren - always trying to blow up my flying machine. This has been going on for years! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我有一个有趣的计划，孩子！' WHERE entry=15597; /* Text0_0: I\'ve got a game plan, kid! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='不知道我们能将他们拖延多久，$g小子:姑娘;，希望你知道该怎样做！' WHERE entry=15598; /* Text0_0: Don\'t know how long we\'re gonna be able to hold them off, $g bud : lady;. Hope you have a plan! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='<哼哼>' WHERE entry=15599; /* Text0_0: <Grunt> */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='灰烬审判军和像你一样的英雄们以惨重的牺牲为代价，终于接近了最终的胜利。现在，我来到冰冠堡垒，帮助所有对抗天灾军团的勇士们。我们将并肩作战，结束巫妖王的暴行！' WHERE entry=15602; /* Text0_0: The continued sacrifice of the Ashen Verdict and heroes such as yourself bring us all closer to final victory. Now I have come to Icecrown Citadel to lend aid to those who fight against the Scourge. Together we will end the tyranny of the Lich King! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你一个人就行？你是傻了？还是自信过度？

当然，我能在你的眼睛里看到取胜的决心。不过你需要用实力来证明自己。好吧，如果你想要这样，我会从战场上撤退。' WHERE entry=15603; /* Text0_0: You can do this alone, you say? Is this simple foolishness or misplaced confidence I see before me?

No, I can see it in your eyes. You have to know. You have to prove to yourself that you can do this alone. Very well. I will retreat from the battlefield if you so wish it. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='要击败巫妖王，你需要的将不止是勇气。祝你好运。' WHERE entry=15604; /* Text0_0: You will need more than bravery to defeat the Lich King. Good luck. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你已经做出了选择。至于是生是死，就只能靠你自己了。' WHERE entry=15605; /* Text0_0: Your choice has been made. Whether you live or die by that choice is now up to you. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='战歌远征军已经到达冰冠堡垒。胜利就在眼前！巫妖王的惨败将成为部落新的荣耀！' WHERE entry=15606; /* Text0_0: With the Warsong Offensive here in Icecrown Citadel, victory is within our grasp! The death of the Lich King will bring glory to the Horde! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你的选择很勇敢！而你对荣耀和功业的欲望也值得尊敬！光荣地去死吧，$n！' WHERE entry=15607; /* Text0_0: Your choice was bold! I respect your desire for glory and honor! Die well, $N! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='以前的情形要比现在好得多……我们到底出了什么事？' WHERE entry=15612; /* Text0_0: Things used to be so much better... what happened to us? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='看上去，它足以承载一名侏儒，也许还能承载两个。' WHERE entry=15615; /* Text0_0: Looks just powerful enough to carry one gnome.  Maybe two. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='要是菲兹能稍微机灵点儿，我们绝对不会被捉住！' WHERE entry=15620; /* Text0_0: If Fizz hadn\'t been so clumsy, we never would have been caught! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='全靠你了，$n。你必须击败贸易大王，否则我们将一败涂地。' WHERE entry=15623; /* Text0_0: You\'re the one, $N. You must defeat the Trade Prince or all is lost. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='嗨。' WHERE entry=15626; /* Text0_0: Hey. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='请插入硬币，然后继续同贸易大王做交易。' WHERE entry=15627; /* Text0_0: Please insert coins and then proceed to deal with the Trade Prince. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='运气如何？' WHERE entry=15628; /* Text0_0: Any luck out there? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='不管是地震还是洪水，魂灵使出的任何把戏都别想阻止我履行自己的职责。' WHERE entry=15629; /* Text0_0: No earthquake, flood, or any other act of the spirits will stop me from doing my duty. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='天意如此，$n。你必须获胜，否则我们将落得一败涂地，与这座岛屿一同消亡。' WHERE entry=15630; /* Text0_0: Everything has been leading to this, $N. You must not fail, or all is lost and we will die with this island. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='老实说，这些家伙怎么老是会被捉住？真是彻彻底底的无能！$B$B这简直让我为地精的身份而感到羞耻。$B$B说到羞耻，我那个好吃懒做的助手跑哪儿去了？不用猜，她肯定正坐在什么地方发呆呢！$B$B喔，这可真叫做能者多劳。我想只能靠我来想办法帮大家脱困了。' WHERE entry=15631; /* Text0_0: Honestly, how do these people keep getting captured? It\'s massive incompetence, I tell you!$B$BIt almost makes me ashamed to be a goblin.$B$BSpeaking of shame, where\'s that lazy assistant of mine? No doubt she\'s just sitting around somewhere doing nothing.$B$BOh the burdens that come with genius. I suppose I\'ll just have to think us all out of this mess by myself. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我们来此表达对伟大森林的敬意，亲眼见证大地之母馈赠的奇迹。' WHERE entry=15632; /* Text0_0: We are here to pay respect to the great forest, and take part in the wonder of the Earth Mother\'s gifts. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='<这只机器人大猩猩似乎已经损坏了。>' WHERE entry=15639; /* Text0_0: <This robotic gorilla appears to be damaged.> */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我吓到你了吗，$r？' WHERE entry=15642; /* Text0_0: Do I frighten you, $r? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='怎么了，老兄……没见过狼人吗？' WHERE entry=15643; /* Text0_0: What\'s the matter, chum... never seen a worgen before? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='炸毁那些杜隆塔尔的岩石大道！我已经确定了几个需要炸毁的地方。但这里并不是其中之一。' WHERE entry=15648; /* Text0_0: Blast these rocky Durotar roads!  I\'ve got places to be, and this isn\'t one of them. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='坡道上面，$n！帮助萨尔击败贸易大王！' WHERE entry=15649; /* Text0_0: Up the ramp, $N! Help Thrall defeat the Trade Prince! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='$n，帮助我。贸易大王已经强大了许多！$B$B我不知道自己还能坚持多久。' WHERE entry=15651; /* Text0_0: Assist me, $N. The Trade Prince has become far more powerful!$B$BI do not know how much longer I can hold out. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='<菲兹尔的躯体晃动着，毫无生命气息，右手却依然紧攥着那颗宝珠。>' WHERE entry=15661; /* Text0_0: <Fizzle\'s body bobs lifelessly.  His orb is clutched tightly in his right hand.> */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='<你抓住那颗宝珠，但菲兹尔的手将它抓得更紧了。这颗球微微闪烁着光亮。>' WHERE entry=15662; /* Text0_0: <You grab at the orb, but Fizzle\'s hand clutches around it even tighter.  The orb glows slightly.> */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='别被鹰身人那长满羽毛的翘臀迷惑……她们的杀伤力可是致命的！' WHERE entry=15664; /* Text0_0: Try to ignore the firm, feathery behinds of the harpies... the creatures are really quite deadly! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='Lok\'tar ogar，士兵。' WHERE entry=15665; /* Text0_0: Lok\'tar ogar, soldier. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我们暂时还无法返回卡利姆多。只有卡乌格会跟你一起回去。另一艘船会把我们剩下这些人带去目的地。$B$B最伟大的冒险还在前方等着你呢，$n。我们的道路还会再次交汇，到那时，世界的命运将掌握在我们手中！' WHERE entry=15667; /* Text0_0: For now we cannot return to Kalimdor. Only Chawg is going back with you.  Another ship is coming to take the rest of us on to our destination.$B$BThe greatest adventure is yet ahead of you, $N. Our paths will cross again, and when they do, the fate of the world will be in your hands! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='Lok\'tar，$c。' WHERE entry=15669; /* Text0_0: Lok\'tar, $c. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我们要先去奥格瑞玛，$g 小伙子 : 姑娘;，然后前往我们在艾萨拉的新家。在那儿见吧！' WHERE entry=15670; /* Text0_0: We\'re Orgrimmar bound, $g bud : girlie;, and then on to our new home in Azshara. See you there! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='谢谢……你……' WHERE entry=15672; /* Text0_0: Thank... you... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='这里就是被你称为很糟糕的地方！' WHERE entry=15677; /* Text0_0: This right here is what you\'d call bad for business! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你成功了，孩子！你带球冲进了得分区，引爆并一举取得了胜利！$B$B现在让我们离开这儿吧。我想新的队伍可以命名为$n爆破队！' WHERE entry=15679; /* Text0_0: You got the stuff, kid! You got the ball into the endzone and you detonated it for the win!$B$BNow let\'s get out of here. I\'m thinking that the new team might need to be called the $N Explosion! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你做到了，我的$g 小伙子 : 姑娘;，你做到了！$B$B现在让我们前往艾萨拉，是时候开始我的新事业了。这个假期可真漫长，我还有账单要付！' WHERE entry=15680; /* Text0_0: You did it, my $g boy : girl;, you did it!$B$BNow, let\'s get to Azshara so that I can set up my new practice. This has been a long vacation and I have bills to pay! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我不认为你还能想到什么办法把我们从这里弄出去？有吗？$B$B啊，好吧，希望当岩浆缓缓流进来时，我们不会死得太痛苦。' WHERE entry=15681; /* Text0_0: I don\'t suppose that there\'s any way that you can get us out of here? No?$B$BAh well, I suppose it won\'t be too painful as the lava slowly pours into this pit. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我知道你一直都有这潜质，$n。$B$B现在说说——你觉得在艾萨拉会有我的位置吗？那儿有巨魔吗？' WHERE entry=15683; /* Text0_0: I knew you had it in you all along, $N.$B$BNow, do you think there\'ll be a position for me in Azshara? Do they have trolls there? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我只想说声谢谢，$n。$B$B这儿的医生能把你救醒真是太好了，不然我们现在都已经死了，甚至更糟！' WHERE entry=15684; /* Text0_0: I just wanted to say thanks, $N.$B$BI\'m sure glad that the doc here was able to shock you back to life or we\'d all be dead by now, or worse! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我才不会为你收拾残局呢，你听好了！$B$B你得去解决贸易大王那只老鼠，我就是这么想的！' WHERE entry=15685; /* Text0_0: I am NOT going to sweep the ground of a mud pit, I can tell you that!$B$BYou need to deal with that rat, the Trade Prince, that\'s what I think! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='为$n三呼万岁！$B$B我真恨不得现在就去艾萨拉搭起我的小床，吃顿可口的早餐。你觉得那里会是什么样的？' WHERE entry=15686; /* Text0_0: Three cheers for $N!!!$B$BI really cannot wait to setup my own little bed and breakfast in Azshara. What do you think it\'s like there? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你干得棒极了，$n。你可真是一流！$B$B不过，当然，要是没有我的聪明才智，你也做不到——我相信你肯定会在工作报告中写上这一条的。不管怎样，虽然我那笨手笨脚的助手老是添乱，你还是圆满完成了。' WHERE entry=15687; /* Text0_0: You did a superb job, $N. Top notch!$B$BNow, of course, you couldn\'t have done it without my tinkering genius, which I\'m sure you\'ll put in your company report, but you really pulled it off, despite the bumbling of my assistant here. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我们的目的地是奥格瑞玛和艾萨拉。舰船宝贝儿，起航！' WHERE entry=15688; /* Text0_0: We\'re Orgrimmar and Azshara bound. Let\'s get this baby out to sea! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='请把硬币插入船里，以驶离爆炸的岛屿。' WHERE entry=15689; /* Text0_0: Please insert coins into ship in order to move away from exploding island. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='让我们起航前先把菲兹扔出去。我抬头，你搬脚！' WHERE entry=15690; /* Text0_0: Let\'s jump Fizz right before we set sail. I\'ll hit him high and you go low! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='让我们彻底解决那个废物吧，艾沃。艾萨拉没法同时容下我们两个人！' WHERE entry=15691; /* Text0_0: Let\'s deal with that punk, Evol, once and for all. Azshara\'s not big enough for the two of us! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我就知道你能做到，$n！你救了我们。$B$B现在趁我还没杀死菲兹和艾沃，让我们赶快离开这儿。' WHERE entry=15692; /* Text0_0: I knew you had it in you, $N! You saved our skins.$B$BNow let\'s get out of here before I have to kill Fizz and Evol. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我现在没和你说话。如果我是你，我决不会指望今年的加薪了，$n。' WHERE entry=15695; /* Text0_0: I\'m not talking to you right now. If I were you, I wouldn\'t count on getting a raise this year, $N. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你成功了！我们得救了！',Text0_1_loc4='你成功了！我们得救了！',Text1_0_loc4='我们真的要去艾萨拉吗？那里是不是也有一座火山？',Text1_1_loc4='我们真的要去艾萨拉吗？那里是不是也有一座火山？' WHERE entry=15696; /* Text0_0: You did it! We\'re saved! */ /* Text0_1: You did it! We\'re saved! */ /* Text1_0: Are we really finally going to Azshara? Is there a volcano there, too? */ /* Text1_1: Are we really finally going to Azshara? Is there a volcano there, too? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text2_0_loc4='我该怎么感谢你呢，$n？',Text2_1_loc4='我该怎么感谢你呢，$n？',Text3_0_loc4='如果我是你，我就会放亮眼睛、竖起耳朵。有传闻说，卡亚罗和失落群岛的火山喷发都与你有关。$B$B我知道这听起来很疯狂。但人们八卦的素材总是千奇百怪，而且总以毁掉英雄为乐——尤其是在有利润和晋升驱使的情况下。',Text3_1_loc4='如果我是你，我就会放亮眼睛、竖起耳朵。有传闻说，卡亚罗和失落群岛的火山喷发都与你有关。$B$B我知道这听起来很疯狂。但人们八卦的素材总是千奇百怪，而且总以毁掉英雄为乐——尤其是在有利润和晋升驱使的情况下。' WHERE entry=15696; /* Text2_0: How can I ever thank you, $N? */ /* Text2_1: How can I ever thank you, $N? */ /* Text3_0: I\'d keep my eyes and ears open if I were you. There\'s a rumor going around that you caused both Mount Kajaro and the Lost Isles volcanoes to explode.$B$BCrazy, I know. But people will gossip about anything and love to tear down their heroes, especially if there\'s a chance for profit and promotion. */ /* Text3_1: I\'d keep my eyes and ears open if I were you. There\'s a rumor going around that you caused both Mount Kajaro and the Lost Isles volcanoes to explode.$B$BCrazy, I know. But people will gossip about anything and love to tear down their heroes, especially if there\'s a chance for profit and promotion. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text4_0_loc4='我们得在被火山杀死之前离开码头！',Text4_1_loc4='我们得在被火山杀死之前离开码头！',Text5_0_loc4='等您准备好就能出发了，$g 阁下 : 女士;！',Text5_1_loc4='等您准备好就能出发了，$g 阁下 : 女士;！' WHERE entry=15696; /* Text4_0: Let\'s leave dock before the volcano destroys us all! */ /* Text4_1: Let\'s leave dock before the volcano destroys us all! */ /* Text5_0: Ready to go when you are, $g sir : ma\'am;! */ /* Text5_1: Ready to go when you are, $g sir : ma\'am;! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text6_0_loc4='我不知道。我想我会想念这里的。我们在这儿共度了不少美好时光。',Text6_1_loc4='我不知道。我想我会想念这里的。我们在这儿共度了不少美好时光。',Text7_0_loc4='我有个主意……这次我们别在联盟和部落的海战中徘徊了。$B$B我只是说说。',Text7_1_loc4='我有个主意……这次我们别在联盟和部落的海战中徘徊了。$B$B我只是说说。' WHERE entry=15696; /* Text6_0: I don\'t know. I think I\'m going to miss this place. We had some pretty good times here. */ /* Text6_1: I don\'t know. I think I\'m going to miss this place. We had some pretty good times here. */ /* Text7_0: I have an idea... this time let\'s not wander through a naval battle between the Alliance and the Horde.$B$BI\'m just saying. */ /* Text7_1: I have an idea... this time let\'s not wander through a naval battle between the Alliance and the Horde.$B$BI\'m just saying. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你的生命之歌将永远激昂，$n。下次再见。' WHERE entry=15698; /* Text0_0: The song of your life will be sung by the mighty, $N. Until we meet again. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我在艾萨拉还有其它事情要解决，所以我会和你一起上路，$n。' WHERE entry=15699; /* Text0_0: I have other business that must be done in Azshara, so I will join you on your journey, $N. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你有一颗巨人的心，$n。我无比荣幸！' WHERE entry=15700; /* Text0_0: You have the heart of a giant, $N. It has been an honor! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='Thoth\'al amun Ree\'thael vormos！Vormos！Vormos！',Text1_0_loc4='Al\'tha， Al\'tha bormaz， Ni bormaz ta\'thall？它来了，它行走在火焰中，$r！' WHERE entry=15711; /* Text0_0: Thoth\'al amun Ree\'thael vormos! Vormos! Vormos! */ /* Text1_0: Al\'tha, Al\'tha bormaz. Ni bormaz ta\'thall? It comes, it walks in flames, $r! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text2_0_loc4='阴影看得见。Bo\'al lal arwi C\'toth。末日即将来临，掩藏在无声的烈焰之中。',Text3_0_loc4='Mar\'kowa tallol ye\'tarin，它知道，它明白。' WHERE entry=15711; /* Text2_0: The shadow sees. Bo\'al lal arwi C\'toth. The end comes, cloaked in silent fire. */ /* Text3_0: Mar\'kowa tallol ye\'tarin, it knows, it knows. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text4_0_loc4='恐惧从永恒之心内蒸腾而出。别逼我看！我所看到的一切已经超出了我的承受极限！',Text5_0_loc4='我们什么都不是。Tulall par\'okoth。Far\'al, ka\'kar。虚空吞噬一切。' WHERE entry=15711; /* Text4_0: Fear broils forth from the heart of the infinite. Don\'t make me look! I\'ve seen more than I can stand! */ /* Text5_0: We are nothing. Tulall par\'okoth. Far\'al, ka\'kar. The void devours. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text6_0_loc4='<暮光仆从向你“嘎嘎”地叫着，白色的泡沫从嘴角边淌了下来。>',Text7_0_loc4='H\'thon，黑暗的幕帘延伸到视野之外。H\'thon marwol qualar：面对黑暗的永恒之握。' WHERE entry=15711; /* Text6_0: <The Twilight Servitor gurgles at you, white spittle foaming and bubbling from his mouth.> */ /* Text7_0: H\'thon, the column of darkness stretching beyond sight. H\'thon marwol qualar: the infinite grasp of night. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='不知恢复神智是不是件好事。$B$B我所知道的一切……也许即将发生在这世界上的一切……$B$B<他战栗着陷入了沉默。>' WHERE entry=15717; /* Text0_0: I don\'t know if it\'s good to have my mind back.$B$BKnowing what I know... Knowing what may happen to our world...$B$B<He shudders and falls silent.> */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你好啊，$c。我想你一定有很多问题要问。$B$B简单说吧，罗伊斯·暮语把我派到这个食人魔洞穴里干什么与暮光之眼相关的活计，可进展得并不顺利。$B$B要是我能抓住那个皮包骨头、没心没肺、油嘴滑舌的暗夜小精灵……$B$B<倒吊在空中的克里斯托弗无助的扭动着，脸涨得通红。>' WHERE entry=15725; /* Text0_0: Hello, $c. I imagine you have a lot of questions.$B$BSuffice it to say that Royce Duskwhisper sent me into the middle of an ogre cave for some "Eye of Twilight" jib-job, and it hasn\'t gone well.$B$BIf I ever get my hands on that lanky, heartless, mealy-mouthed little night elf...$B$B<Kristoff wriggles helplessly as he dangles in the air, his face reddening.> */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='努力工作吧，$c。我们完成任务的时间已经不多了。预言即将实现。' WHERE entry=15730; /* Text0_0: Work hard, $c. We have little time to complete our tasks before the prophecies are fulfilled. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我们的世界很快就要完结。但我们将共同得到升华，得到元素的力量。' WHERE entry=15732; /* Text0_0: Our world will end soon, but together we will ascend and inherit the power of the elements. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你闻到什么了吗？',Text1_0_loc4='我很愿意帮你，可我被……链子缠住了。我只能往回晃一点儿。' WHERE entry=15733; /* Text0_0: You smell somethin\'? */ /* Text1_0: I\'d lend a hand, but I\'ve got... chain rash. I\'ll just hang back a little. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text2_0_loc4='你可真是个与众不同的$c，$n。我不是在说你坏话。我只是说，你还挺有趣儿。',Text3_0_loc4='我吊在那儿多久了？感觉应该有好多天了。' WHERE entry=15733; /* Text2_0: You\'re one unusual $c, $N. I don\'t mean that it a negative way. I\'m just sayin\', you\'re kinda funny. */ /* Text3_0: How long was I hanging back there? It felt like days. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text4_0_loc4='像那样吊在链子上的滋味可不怎么好。不过，老实说，那对我头发有好处。',Text5_0_loc4='食人魔。$B$B我恨食人魔。' WHERE entry=15733; /* Text4_0: I don\'t recommend hanging from a chain like that. But, to be honest, it did great things for my hair. */ /* Text5_0: Ogres.$B$BI hate ogres. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text6_0_loc4='当有东西给你杀时，你总是话那么多吗？',Text7_0_loc4='少说废话，多杀点儿食人魔。好吗？' WHERE entry=15733; /* Text6_0: Do you always talk so much when there\'s stuff to kill? */ /* Text7_0: Less yap flappin\'. More ogre thwappin\'. Deal? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='他们本来有机会和我在一起。但他们却只是嘲笑我的信仰。他们对我已经毫无意义了。' WHERE entry=15734; /* Text0_0: They had their chance to come with me, and instead they mocked my beliefs. They are nothing to me. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='难道她不明白？我希望她能到我身边来。我很年轻，我还不想死。我们还要共渡许多美好的岁月。而这是唯一能让我们活下去的办法。把这些告诉她，请一定让她明白。' WHERE entry=15735; /* Text0_0: Doesn\'t she realize I wanted her to come with me? I\'m young; I don\'t want to die. We should have many good years ahead of us and this is the only way. Tell her these things. Make her understand. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='嗨。对，我知道。我又被抓住了。$B$B我不想谈这些。$B$B你准备好了吗？' WHERE entry=15737; /* Text0_0: Hi. Yeah, I know. I got captured again.$B$BI don\'t want to talk about it.$B$BYou ready? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='嗯？你打算帮我下去吗？' WHERE entry=15738; /* Text0_0: Well? Are you going to help me down? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='$n，$n，我能叫你$n吗？$B$B我马上就要被挂到食人魔洞穴里的肉钩子上了。$B$B你觉得我的研究进度如何？你这个中看不中用的笨$c！到这里来！你这个坏家伙！$B$B<克里斯托弗在锁住他的链子上晃来晃去，拼命想要踢到你的脸。>' WHERE entry=15740; /* Text0_0: $N, $N. Can I call you $N?$B$BI am hanging from a meathook in the back of an ogre cave.$B$BHow do you THINK my research is progressing, you pompous dirt-sucking ass-$c? C\'mere! C\'mere you son of a swineherd!$B$B<Kristoff flutters back and forth on his chain, trying desperately to kick you in the face.> */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='<克里斯托弗哼哼着。>' WHERE entry=15741; /* Text0_0: <Kristoff grunts.> */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='在所有远古半神中，戈德林是最杰出的一位。他的狂怒，他的决心……你一定能赶上他。' WHERE entry=15742; /* Text0_0: Of all the ancients, Goldrinn is the most magnificent. His fury, his resolve... you would do well to emulate. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='奥格瑞玛正在发生一些可怕的事情。这里的女人们都在传说有人失踪了。还有人说，世界将要完结。这到底是什么意思？' WHERE entry=15749; /* Text0_0: There\'s something going on in Orgrimmar, and I don\'t like the look of it. These women complain that people have disappered. Others say the world will end. What does it mean? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='$c，世界末日就要到了。但不需要绝望。听听我所说的，看看我的兄弟所给予你的一切吧。',Text0_1_loc4='$c，世界末日就要到了。但不需要绝望。听听我所说的，看看我的兄弟所给予你的一切吧。' WHERE entry=15750; /* Text0_0: The end of the world nears, $c. There is no need to despair. Hear what I say and what my brethren have to offer. */ /* Text0_1: The end of the world nears, $c. There is no need to despair. Hear what I say and what my brethren have to offer. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你好，$c。$B$B山脉崩塌，大灾变造成海水灌入，淹没了千针石林。$B$B我们需要你的帮助，就是现在！' WHERE entry=15755; /* Text0_0: Greetings, $c.$B$BThe mountains have crumbled and the Cataclysm has caused the seas to rush in and drown Thousand Needles.$B$BWe need your help, now! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='这是个好人，$r。我们曾在多次战争中并肩作战……$b$b这些野兽有债要偿！' WHERE entry=15756; /* Text0_0: This was a good man, $r. We\'d served together through many battles...$b$bThese beasts have a debt to pay! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='啊……$b$b我的感觉……不太好……' WHERE entry=15769; /* Text0_0: Ugh...$b$bI don\'t... feel so good... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我们来此为我们的人民守护这些土地。' WHERE entry=15771; /* Text0_0: We are here to preserve these lands for our people. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='$R，你要找我？自从主人去世之后，我已经被遗弃多久了？' WHERE entry=15772; /* Text0_0: $R. Have you been sent to speak with me? How long has it been since the master\'s demise on these very slopes? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我的帮助？事态已经恶化到如此地步了吗？$B$B<黑角残忍的黑色瞳仁里闪着许久未见的光焰。>$B$B告诉我，我为什么不该让你的世界自生自灭？' WHERE entry=15778; /* Text0_0: My help? Have things really grown so dire?$B$B<The distant flames flicker in Blackhorn\'s cruel, dark eyes.>$B$BTell me why I shouldn\'t let your world burn. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='凡人？不错，我曾是个凡人。弱小的凡人。$B$B你看到我现在所受的束缚了吗？但与身为凡人的桎梏相比，这些根本算不了什么。$B$B甚至现在，我主人的馈赠都在我体内激涌，随时准备释放。$B$B不，$c，凡人的身份已经离我远去，假如我体内还有丝毫过往生命的残焰在燃烧，我也希望它尽快熄灭。你最好去想其它办法，$r。' WHERE entry=15780; /* Text0_0: Mortal? Yes I was once mortal. Weak.$B$BYou see my bonds now? These restraints are nothing compared to being shackled within a mortal coil.$B$BEven now the master\'s gifts stir within me, ready to be unleashed.$B$BNo, $c, my mortal days have passed, and if any flame of my former life still flickers within I would wish it extinguished. You\'ll have to do better than that, $r. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='<黑角挣扎了一下。他第一次显露出烦乱的神情。>$B$B算了吧！难道你真能逃出燃烧军团的魔爪吗？不要自鸣得意了！难道你们十年前的所为和在外域的所作所为曾经减慢过燃烧军团的步伐吗？他们一定会回来的，$r。他们会回来。我则会在这里迎接他们。' WHERE entry=15782; /* Text0_0: <Blackhorn strains against his bonds, for the first time visibly upset.>$B$BRedemption! You act as if there\'s an escape from the Burning Legion. So smug! As though your efforts a decade ago or in Outland have slowed the Legion a single iota! They will come, $r. They will return. And I will be here to welcome them. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='<咳嗽。>$b$b我……死了吗？' WHERE entry=15783; /* Text0_0: <Cough.>$b$bHave I... died? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你很有天赋，$n。但仁慈使你懦弱。' WHERE entry=15784; /* Text0_0: You have talent, $N. But mercy makes you weak. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='……主人？' WHERE entry=15785; /* Text0_0: ...master? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='真好，你终于来了！$b$b时间不多，你准备好了吗？' WHERE entry=15794; /* Text0_0: Great, ye found yer way here!$b$bNo time to waste. Ye ready? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='如果你想要蝙蝠，那么你可是来对地方了。我掌管着全部哨兵的蝙蝠。' WHERE entry=15806; /* Text0_0: If ya need a bat, ya come to da right place. I be handlin\' all de bats for de scouts. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你！$B$B你以为你能像这样轻而易举的走进来夺走我的位置？再好好想想吧，$g小男孩:小姑娘;！$B$B我听见了会议室里的窃窃私语。在指挥部里围绕在你身边的那些人都是些溜须拍马的狗腿子，为上位不择手段。我应该知道的……当初是我把他们找来的。$B$B你的飞黄腾达只不过是侥幸，而且我已经做好充分的准备把你打回原形！你给我小心点儿，$n。没准儿哪天你还需要我帮你的忙！' WHERE entry=15807; /* Text0_0: YOU!$B$BYou think you can just waltz in here and take my spot? Think again, $g boy : girl;!$B$BI\'ve heard the whispering in the boardroom. The people you\'ve surrounded yourself with at headquarters are all boot-licking sycophants who will do anything to get ahead. I should know... I hired all of them.$B$BYour meteoric rise to power is a fluke, and I\'m fully prepared to knock you down a gear or two! Watch your step, $N. Who knows when you\'re going to need me on your side? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你为战争做好准备了吗，$r？' WHERE entry=15808; /* Text0_0: Are you prepared for war, $r? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='是的，只要毁了四种元素，门就会打开。我确定。不过要小心那些穴居人。那些脾气乖戾、又臭又脏的生物——尽管他们还没屈服于血肉诅咒。' WHERE entry=15815; /* Text0_0: Yep, destroy the four elementals, then the door will open. I\'m sure of it. Just watch out for the Troggs. Nasty tempered, filthy creatures, even if they have not succumbed to the Curse of Flesh. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我就是尖端技术的代表，宝贝儿！灌注元素能量的高科技。到艾泽拉斯海洋的最深处去探求失落的学识与新的资源吧。$B$B请牢记我的名字。' WHERE entry=15818; /* Text0_0: I\'m the bleeding edge, baby! Elemental infused technologies. Exploring the depths of Azeroth for lost knowledge and new resources.$B$BRemember the name. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我不知道你怎么样，老兄，可我不能在水下呼吸。' WHERE entry=15819; /* Text0_0: I don\'t know about you, pal, but I can\'t breathe water. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='然后放弃我帅气的特制潜水头盔？没门。' WHERE entry=15820; /* Text0_0: And miss out on wearing my awesome custom-made helmet? Not a chance. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你在这儿真是太好了，朋友！$B$B那些野生动物不得不逃到这片树林里来躲避烈火。它们已经无处可去了。我们必须保护幸存者！' WHERE entry=15827; /* Text0_0: I\'m glad you are here, friend!$B$BThe fires have driven the wildlife to seek shelter in this grove. They can run no farther. We must protect the survivors! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='嘿，$g老兄:小姐;！听说你对贸易大王的职位有兴趣。$B$B是真的吗？',Text1_0_loc4='我可真想一拳打在奇普的脸上！我还想一口亲在小甜甜的脸上！' WHERE entry=15829; /* Text0_0: Heya, $g dude : toots;! The word is that you\'re gunning for the Trade Prince\'s job.$B$BThat true? */ /* Text1_0: I\'d like to punch that Chip right in the kisser! I\'d also like to kiss that Candy right in the kisser, too! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text2_0_loc4='哈，有人在说“聚会”?',Text3_0_loc4='这瓶叫做卡亚可乐的玩意儿让我想法不断。我们真需要竞赛来获取灵感吗？' WHERE entry=15829; /* Text2_0: Did someone say, party? */ /* Text3_0: This Kaja\'Cola thing\'s got me thinking. Do we really want the competition to have ideas? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='嘿，嘿！别再怀有敌意了！我就是你们常遇到的那些人畜无害的中立地精，跟部落没关系！' WHERE entry=15834; /* Text0_0: Hey, hey! Cease your hostilities! I\'m one of those frequently encountered and completely harmless neutral goblins, not the Horde kind! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='$C，这场大灾变震碎了山脉。南海淹没了千针石林。$B$B我们需要你的帮助！' WHERE entry=15845; /* Text0_0: $C, the cataclysm has crumbled the mountains and the South Sea has rushed in to drown Thousand Needles.$B$BWe need your help, now! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='愿英灵指引你，$c。' WHERE entry=15846; /* Text0_0: May de spirits guide ya, $c. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='在我们最为危难的时刻，恐怖图腾怎么能对我们作出这种事？' WHERE entry=15848; /* Text0_0: How could the Grimtotem do this to us in our greatest time of need? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='看看这惨状，$c！放眼望去，视线所及到处都是鲜血与灰烬。$B$B但自然不会如此轻易被打败。只要我们做些努力，这片焦灼的土地将会重焕生机。' WHERE entry=15849; /* Text0_0: Look at this devastation, $c! Blood and ash, as far as the eye can see.$B$BBut nature is not so easily put down. With some effort, we may yet coax life from this scorched soil. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我的迅猛龙能战胜任何事任何人！' WHERE entry=15852; /* Text0_0: My raptor can take on ANYTHING and ANYONE! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='欢迎来到侏儒区！' WHERE entry=15863; /* Text0_0: Welcome to Tinker Town! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='这块碎冰中回荡着冰川切割地壳时深沉的碎裂声。它能够将你的思维变成没有生命，没有尽头的寒冬。' WHERE entry=15864; /* Text0_0: This shard of ice echoes the deep, cracking rumble of invading glaciers.  Its cold turns your thoughts to a lifeless, endless winter. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='扎拉赞恩就要完蛋了。回音群岛将再次属于暗矛部族！' WHERE entry=15865; /* Text0_0: Zalazane\'s time be runnin\' out. De Echo Isles will belong to de Darkspear Tribe again! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='暗矛部族回到了家园！$n，如果没有你的帮助，我们无法实现这个梦想。现在，让我们庆祝吧！' WHERE entry=15866; /* Text0_0: De Darkspears have a home again! An\' we couldn\'t have done it wit\'out ya helpin\', $N. Now, we celebrate! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='沃金要我在他回来之前一直敲这面鼓。如果你在等他，那么我可以告诉你，他很快就会回来夺回这些岛屿了。$B$B暂时先在这里等一等他，欣赏一下这音乐吧！' WHERE entry=15873; /* Text0_0: Vol\'jin told me ta keep hittin\' da drum till he gets back.  If ya be waitin\' for him, he\'d be back soon to take back da Isles.$B$BJust wait here and enjoy da music! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='菲兹尔、普兹克、金吉……他们都把自己当成我们的救星。但其实是我！船是我造的！$B$B它应该叫拉泽瑞克的赛艇平台！' WHERE entry=15874; /* Text0_0: Fizzle, Pozzik, Jinky... they all think that they saved us. But it was me! I built the ship!$B$BIt should be called, Razzeric\'s Speedbarge! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我们正在为夺回回音群岛做准备。扎拉赞恩一直在施展他的黑暗魔法，操纵傀儡，进行古老的黑暗仪式。$B$B他知道我们的行动，所以我们必须做好万全的准备。' WHERE entry=15876; /* Text0_0: We\'d be gettin\' ready to take back da Echo Isles. Zalazane has been workin\' his voodoo magic for some time, convincing folks dat he be dead and performing ancient dark rituals.$B$BHe knows we\'d be coming, so we have ta make sure we be prepared. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='如果要成功地夺回这些岛屿，我们就需要有援军的帮助。$B$B岑塔布拉一直在照看这片群岛上的动物们。我们需要她和那些动物的帮助。$B$B邦桑迪是一位强大的神灵。他控制着这片群岛上死者们的灵魂。他的祝福对我们是至关重要的。$B$B当我们取得他们的援助之后，扎拉赞恩和被他控制的巨魔将必败无疑！那时，回音群岛就会回到暗矛部族的怀抱！' WHERE entry=15877; /* Text0_0: We require da help of allies on da islands.$B$BZen\'tabra has been watching over da animals of de Islands for some time now.  We\'d need her help and da help of da animal creatures.$B$BBwonsamdi is a powerful loa dat controls de spirits of de dead on da islands.  His blessing is crucial for our attack.$B$BOnce our allies have joined us, Zalazane and his army of mind-controlled trolls will have no chance!  Then, da Echo Isles will be de Darkspears! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='显然是这些人对我们的船只发动了突袭，可我没看见任何失踪者。他们被带到哪儿去了？' WHERE entry=15878; /* Text0_0: These are definitely the ones that raided our boats, but I don\'t see any of our missing people. Where did they take them? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='要是有谁能严肃对待我的工作，我会感激不尽。虽然我干的不是像和鲨鱼摔跤或是把鳗鱼打结那样的活儿，可不代表这就不重要。' WHERE entry=15880; /* Text0_0: I\'d appreciate if someone started to take my work seriously. Just because I\'m not wrestling sharks or tying eels in knots doesn\'t mean this isn\'t important. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='<上古半神的眼睛巨大而深邃。>$B$B<它说话的速度很慢。你也听不懂它所说的语言。寒意爬上了你的脊骨，恐惧和困惑占据了你的心灵。>' WHERE entry=15881; /* Text0_0: <The ancient\'s eyes are vast and deep.>$B$B<The creature speaks slowly, in a language you do not understand. Chills run up your spine. You\'re overwhelmed with feelings of terror and confusion.> */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='<上古半神缓缓地张开眼睛，那双眼睛如同充满痛苦与畏惧的深潭。>' WHERE entry=15882; /* Text0_0: <The ancient\'s eyes open slowly, revealing deep pools of pain and fear.> */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='<上古半神巨大的黑眼睛盯着你，眼睛里流露出不信任的神情。>' WHERE entry=15886; /* Text0_0: <The ancient\'s enormous dark eyes peer at you distrustfully.> */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='要是你问我的话，我认为我的兄弟应该解决这些地精！据说他们当中有人用足球炸弹引发了大灾变！$B$B我们得尽快除掉他们，再晚就来不及了！' WHERE entry=15887; /* Text0_0: If you ask me, I think my brother should do something about all of these goblins! It\'s said that one of them set off the Cataclysm with a footbomb!$B$BWe need to get rid of all of them before it\'s really too late! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='要不是因为那些侏儒，我们怎么会陷入这种混乱！$B$B众所周知，他们才是大灾变的罪魁祸首！引起灾难的就是他们那些能放大世界的装置和诸如此类的破烂！' WHERE entry=15890; /* Text0_0: We wouldn\'t be in this mess if it weren\'t for the gnomes!$B$BIt\'s a well-known fact that they were the ones that caused the Cataclysm with all of their world-enlarging devices, and other such nonsense! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我已经尽力让这艘船不至于散架，我能做的就这么多，而且我还得腾出精力去对付像菲兹尔那样自吹自擂的小丑！' WHERE entry=15892; /* Text0_0: It\'s all I can do to keep this ship from tearing itself apart and I still have to deal with puffed up baffoons like Fizzle here! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我告诉你，这家伙快要把我逼疯了！难道真有人相信，地精能帮忙完成像这座赛艇驳船平台一样的宏伟之作？$B$B他们唯一的本事就是炸东西，而且多半炸飞的是自己！' WHERE entry=15893; /* Text0_0: I tell ya this guy\'s driving me nuts! Does anyone truly believe that a goblin could help run anything so magnificent as this speedbarge?$B$BAll they know how to do is blow stuff up and half of the time, they take themselves out doing even that! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='啊，$n！一只小鸟告诉我，你会来这里。$B$B这是艾维娜传递信息的方式。' WHERE entry=15896; /* Text0_0: Ah, $N! A little bird told me you would be coming.$B$BThat\'s how Aviana sends messages around. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='到处都是烟尘。就算热不死我，我也会窒息而死。' WHERE entry=15897; /* Text0_0: Smoke and ash. If the heat doesn\'t kill me, I may suffocate. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我欠你的永远还不清，$n。也许，能还清？$B$B嗯？' WHERE entry=15898; /* Text0_0: I owe you a debt that I can never repay, $N. Or, can\'t I?$B$BHmm? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='听着，$n，我不喜欢亏欠任何人。所以你能不能低调处理这件事，保守我们俩之间的秘密？$B$B我可不想让我的债主知道。' WHERE entry=15899; /* Text0_0: Listen, $N, I hate being indebted to anyone. So can you make sure to keep this on the down-low, just between the two of us?$B$BI\'d hate for my creditors to find out. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='嗯？怎么了？' WHERE entry=15901; /* Text0_0: Yeah?  What\'s the matter? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='干得好，$c。$b$b现在我和我的人已经准备好面对敌人了。' WHERE entry=15908; /* Text0_0: You\'ve done well, $c.$b$bMy men and I are now prepared to face the enemy. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我们很快就会再见……' WHERE entry=15909; /* Text0_0: We be meetin\' again so soon... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你得帮帮我！我可怜的，可怜的切尔希……' WHERE entry=15911; /* Text0_0: You gotta help me! My poor, poor Chelsea... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你会灭火并阻止那些海盗上船的，对吧？' WHERE entry=15914; /* Text0_0: You\'re going to put out the fires and stop those pirates from boarding us, right? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='喔天哪！喔神哪！你会扑灭火焰，并阻止那些海盗登上赛艇平台，是吧？！！' WHERE entry=15915; /* Text0_0: Oh gosh! Oh golly! You\'re gonna put out the fires and stop those pirates from getting on the Speedbarge, right?!! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='海盗、半人马、恐怖图腾，我的天！$B$B而且我想我昨晚还看到一个庞然大物从头顶上飞了过去。它可真是太大了，大得把月亮都遮住了！' WHERE entry=15918; /* Text0_0: Pirates and centaurs and Grimtotem, oh my!$B$BAnd I think I saw something big fly overhead last night. It was so big it blocked out the moon! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我们在这儿可能会遇到各种各样的麻烦，但至少我们已经进入开放水域了。$B$B虽然我们不一定能逃过昨晚从我头顶飞过的那大家伙。那玩意儿可真大……我是说，真的很大！' WHERE entry=15920; /* Text0_0: We may be surrounded by all sorts of nasties here, but at least we\'re out over the open water.$B$BThat won\'t protect us from whatever it was that I saw fly over last night, though. It was big... I mean, really big! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='献给那些在冰封荒原上为了对抗天灾军团而英勇牺牲的战士们。' WHERE entry=15921; /* Text0_0: Dedicated to those that fell to the Scourge during the war in the frozen wastes. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='小心，朋友。炎魔之王有结界保护，让我们无法对他发动攻击。' WHERE entry=15931; /* Text0_0: Be wary, allies. There are bound to be traps to protect the Firelord from our incursion. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我们在此对抗的势力远远不止暮光之锤、拉格纳罗斯甚至是死亡之翼。我们惟有取胜才能确保我们的世界不至于消亡。' WHERE entry=15935; /* Text0_0: The forces we are up against here go beyond the Twilight\'s Hammer, Ragnaros or even Deathwing.  We must succeed here if our world is going to survive at all. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我得尽快找个安全的地方。$b$b老马克的情况不太好。' WHERE entry=15943; /* Text0_0: I need to find a safe place soon.$b$bOl\' Mack\'s not doin\' so well. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='从传送门那边又有人过来了！希望你已经做好了战斗的准备，$c。' WHERE entry=15952; /* Text0_0: Someone else from beyond the portal! I hope you\'re ready for a fight, $c. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我们现在已经深入敌后了，$n。我们要尽可能地对敌人制造伤害！' WHERE entry=15953; /* Text0_0: We\'re behind enemy lines, $N. We\'ve got to do as much damage as we can! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='要是我们任由暮光之锤在艾泽拉斯各地打开像这样的传送门，那这世上就没有任何军团能挽救这个星球。我们必须一举解决这个坑道网！' WHERE entry=15954; /* Text0_0: If we allow Twilight\'s Hammer to open up portals like these all over Azeroth, no army in the world can save the planet. We\'ve got to shut this tunnel network down! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我们必须坚持，$n。我从我们敬爱的狼神先祖身上学到了一样东西。$B$B那就是永远、永远、永远都不要放弃。' WHERE entry=15955; /* Text0_0: We must perservere, $N. That is something I learned from our beloved wolf ancient.$B$BNever, never, never give up. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='派伦迪乌斯倒下了！我们在这儿的工作完成了。$B$B现在只要穿过火焰之门就能返回海加尔山了，$c。我会确保看好大门的。' WHERE entry=15956; /* Text0_0: Pyrendius is slain! Our work here is done.$B$BJust step through the flamegate to return to Mount Hyjal, $c. I\'ll make sure the gate is taken care of. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='嘘！轻点儿！你要害我们被发现了。' WHERE entry=15962; /* Text0_0: Shhhh! Keep it down! You\'ll blow our cover. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='莱恩为名，买卖随性！你想来点儿什么？' WHERE entry=15970; /* Text0_0: Ryan\'s the name, trading\'s the game! What\'ll ya have? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='在这下面小心点儿，$c。这些雪怪都是残暴的战士。' WHERE entry=15972; /* Text0_0: Watch yerself down here, $c. These wendigos are savage fighters. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我这辈子看够这个洞穴了。我恨不得立即返回卡拉诺斯。' WHERE entry=15973; /* Text0_0: I\'ve seen enough of this cave for a lifetime. I can\'t wait to get back to Kharanos. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='这些雪怪当然是个麻烦，可真正的战斗却是对付那些霜鬃难民。' WHERE entry=15974; /* Text0_0: These wendigos are an annoyance, sure, but the real fight is with those Frostmane refugees. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='石爪山这里总是困难重重，$n，但这片土地和生活在这里的人民从没像现在这么痛苦过。如果不加以制止的话，部落会把我们全都毁掉。' WHERE entry=15979; /* Text0_0: Stonetalon has always had its fill of problems, $N, but never has the land and its people suffered so badly. The Horde will destroy us all if left unchecked. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你一定要救救我，$c！他已经疯了……疯了知道吗！由于他不能改变千针石林被洪水吞没的事实，他已经彻底精神失常了！$B$B他把一切都怪罪到我头上，包括大灾变。他可能认为我是死亡之翼或什么东西假扮的！$B$B救命！' WHERE entry=15981; /* Text0_0: You\'ve got to save me here, $c! He\'s gone mad... mad I telll you! His inability to stop the flooding of Thousand Needles has caused him to go completely bonkers!$B$BHe blames me for everything, including the Cataclysm. He probably thinks that I\'m Deathwing in disguise, or something!$B$BHelp! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='需要什么吗？' WHERE entry=15991; /* Text0_0: Need some smithin\'? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='欢迎你，$c！欢迎来到艾维娜圣殿——天空中所有生灵的避风港。$B$B艾维娜或许已经不再与我们同在，但她的心魂与她的凶猛战力却将永远留存在所有藉双翼翱翔的生灵身上。$B$B要是你想了解艾维娜的故事，可以与位于下方的楚伦娜交谈。' WHERE entry=15998; /* Text0_0: Welcome, $c! Welcome to the Shrine of Aviana, a haven for all creatures of the sky.$B$BAviana may no longer be with us, but her heart and her ferocity live on in all winged creatures.$B$BSpeak with Choluna down below if you are curious about Aviana\'s story. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我不知道我在这儿干什么。我没有做合约谈判员的经验。$B$B我以前曾经干过酒保，可因为黛西的原因做不下去了。也许是时候转行了。' WHERE entry=16001; /* Text0_0: I don\'t know what I\'m doing here. I have no experience as a contract negotiatior.$B$BI used to serve drinks for a living, but Daisy put me out of business. Time for a new career, I guess. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='楚伦娜和希萨莉都已经把他们的报告给了我。现在我已经非常清楚了……$B$B$n，我相信艾维娜应该很快就会回来了，但我们必须阻止黑龙塞西莉亚！' WHERE entry=16002; /* Text0_0: Choluna and Thisalee have both given me their reports. It\'s all very clear to me now...$B$B$N, I believe Aviana may soon return to us, but only if we can stop the black dragon Sethria! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我以前就是个在赛道边上谋生的奖券商。可现在没比赛，也就没钱赚了。$B$B我现在正在努力学习谈判。你能帮我让这里的一切顺利进行吗？他们有油！' WHERE entry=16004; /* Text0_0: I used to be a simple ticket redeemer at the racetrack. Well, no more racetrack, so no more job.$B$BI\'m trying my hand at negotiations now. Could you help me get things going here? They have oil! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你能教一名士兵学会杀戮的技巧，可你不能教他杀戮的欲望。还好我们在这下面不用担心这一点。我的每一位弟兄都已经迫不及待地想要把那些纳迦撕成碎片，让他们为犯下的恶行付出代价，而我也一样。$B$B我们要想办法与上面建立联系，可在那之前，我想先跟那些纳迦“联系”一下。那些倒下的兄弟不能白死。' WHERE entry=16008; /* Text0_0: You can teach a soldier how to kill, but you can\'t teach him to want to kill.  That is one thing we don\'t have to worry about down here.  Every single one of my boys can\'t wait to take a piece out of those naga for what they did to us, and I can\'t say I feel  much different.$B$BWe need to find a way to make contact with the surface, but before that, I want to make a bit of "contact" with these naga.  We have some brothers to avenge. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='这里有令人惊叹的材料。任何工程材料和替换件都能找到代用品。一切皆有可能！' WHERE entry=16014; /* Text0_0: Amazing materials down here. Amazing! Substitutes for everything. Substitutes for substitutes. Everything\'s possible! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='这地方让我们比先前更加暴露了，$r。$b$b我们必须尽快找到安全的藏身处！',Text1_0_loc4='我们必须集结你的同伴，探明纳迦在这里的真正目的。$b$b不过首先，我们得先找个更为安全的地方。' WHERE entry=16015; /* Text0_0: Here, we are even more exposed than before, $r.$b$bWe must find safe shelter soon! */ /* Text1_0: We must find your allies and discover the naga motives in this region.$b$bBut first, we must find a more secure location. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text2_0_loc4='我觉得我们对纳迦在此地出现的原因了解得远远不够。$b$b我以前从没见过他们像现在这么富于组织性和纪律性。' WHERE entry=16015; /* Text2_0: I feel that we are just scratching the surface of the naga presence here.$b$bI have never seen them so organized and disciplined before. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='村庄……消失。家庭消失。纳迦……带走……一切。' WHERE entry=16016; /* Text0_0: Village... gone.  Family gone.  Naga take... everything. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='这对我们所有人来说都很困难，可我们正在勉强支撑。$B$B你要做的就是挽起袖子，做你该做的事。' WHERE entry=16018; /* Text0_0: It\'s been hard on all of us, but we\'re getting by.$B$BYou\'ve just gotta roll up your sleeves and do what needs to be done. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='<这名士兵痛苦的呻吟声在水中变得有些扭曲。>',Text0_1_loc4='<这名士兵痛苦的呻吟声在水中变得有些扭曲。>',Text1_0_loc4='<这名受伤的士兵似乎还有呼吸。谢天谢地，他的魔法气泡还没掉。>',Text1_1_loc4='<这名受伤的士兵似乎还有呼吸。谢天谢地，他的魔法气泡还没掉。>' WHERE entry=16019; /* Text0_0: <The injured soldier\'s pained groans are somewhat distorted by the water.> */ /* Text0_1: <The injured soldier\'s pained groans are somewhat distorted by the water.> */ /* Text1_0: <The injured soldier appears to still be breathing. Thankfully, his bubble remains intact.> */ /* Text1_1: <The injured soldier appears to still be breathing. Thankfully, his bubble remains intact.> */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text2_0_loc4='<这名士兵的体侧有一道深得可怕的伤口。>',Text2_1_loc4='<这名士兵的体侧有一道深得可怕的伤口。>',Text3_0_loc4='<看样子，这名士兵靠装死摆脱了纳迦的怀疑。这个举动大概救了他的命。>',Text3_1_loc4='<看样子，这名士兵靠装死摆脱了纳迦的怀疑。这个举动大概救了他的命。>' WHERE entry=16019; /* Text2_0: <There is a a painful looking gash along the soldier\'s side.> */ /* Text2_1: <There is a a painful looking gash along the soldier\'s side.> */ /* Text3_0: <It looks as if this solider might be feigning to throw off naga suspicion. It likely saved his life.> */ /* Text3_1: <It looks as if this solider might be feigning to throw off naga suspicion. It likely saved his life.> */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='第三舰队被诅咒的魂灵将永世游荡在这片海岸上，$r。帕雷斯之眼掌控着我们的生命，并永远将我们囚禁在泥沼之中。' WHERE entry=16022; /* Text0_0: The souls of the Third Fleet are cursed to roam this shore, for eternity, $r. The Eye of Paleth lay claim to our lives, and trapped us in the mire forevermore. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='嘘，小声点儿！我们正躲着呢。' WHERE entry=16024; /* Text0_0: Shh, mon!  We be hidin\' here. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='奥莉里拉不喜欢让我们这些非兽人进入镇子，但那并不妨碍她安排我们去工作。不管怎样……我倒宁可待在这外面。' WHERE entry=16025; /* Text0_0: Okrilla doesn\'t like to let us non-orcs into town, but that doesn\'t stop her from putting us to work.  No matter... I prefer it out here anyway. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我需要你按我说的去做，$r。如果我们退却，我们就很可能落入拉瑟莱克的股掌之中。' WHERE entry=16031; /* Text0_0: I need you to do what I say, $r.  If we falter, then we may be playing right into Razelikh\'s hands. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我们正在对付的，看来要比大地之环预料到的任何东西都要大得多。',Text1_0_loc4='在这个洞穴之外集结了大批纳迦。$b$b我们能神不知鬼不觉地到达这个地方，可真是幸运。' WHERE entry=16032; /* Text0_0: We appear to be dealing with something far bigger than any in the Earthen Ring had suspected. */ /* Text1_0: There is a great concentration of naga just outside of this cavern.$b$bWe were fortunate to reach this place unnoticed. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我们的士兵……他们都已沦为俘虏。',Text1_0_loc4='我们当中有许多人试图摆脱纳迦。$b$b可只有我成功了……' WHERE entry=16033; /* Text0_0: Our soldiers... they\'re all captives now. */ /* Text1_0: Many of us tried to escape the naga.$b$bI am the only one who succeeded... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text2_0_loc4='我不知道原因，但那些怪物在想方设法让我们的人活下来……' WHERE entry=16033; /* Text2_0: I don\'t know why, but those monsters are going out of their way to keep our men alive... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='好！拿去护符，可$r要帮助岩池鱼人。' WHERE entry=16034; /* Text0_0: Fine!  Amulet take, but $r help Rockpool. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我们生活在同一片海浪中，吞吐着同一片海水，膜拜着同一位神灵。那究竟是为什么——纳迦要与我们反目为敌？' WHERE entry=16035; /* Text0_0: We lived under the same waves, breathed the same water, and worshipped the same god.  Why, then, would the naga turn against us? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='也许这里并不怎么舒适宜人，可这里仍旧是卡兹莫丹，所以它还是我们的家。' WHERE entry=16046; /* Text0_0: It may not be quite comfy out here, but it\'s still Khaz Modan, so it\'s still our home. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我们的城镇沉没在被诅咒的洋底，我们的要塞已被黑铁叛徒侵占，而我也身受重伤，对这种局面束手无策。$B$B所以欢迎来到米奈希尔港！' WHERE entry=16047; /* Text0_0: Our town\'s under the blasted ocean, our keep\'s full of Dark Iron traitors, and I\'m laid up with such a wound I can\'t do a single thing about any of it.$B$BSo welcome to Menethil Harbor! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='伊瑟拉派我来这里与艾森娜的荒野灵魂取得联系。$B$B可这古老的灵魂仍在保持沉默。' WHERE entry=16050; /* Text0_0: Ysera has sent me here to make contact with the wilderness spirit of Aessina.$B$BYet the ancient remains silent. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='不是我们将战火引向部落，而是部落将战火引向我们。' WHERE entry=16051; /* Text0_0: We didn\'t bring the war to the Horde, the Horde brought the war to us. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='正当我以为我们终于能摆脱那些迅猛龙，喘口气时，这里的情况却变得更糟。$B$B可是抱怨是没用的。我们得像个真正的矮人一样去面对！' WHERE entry=16053; /* Text0_0: Just when I thought we\'d gotten a break by getting away from those raptors, things get even worse around here.$B$BNo use bellyaching though. We\'re gonna face this like proper dwarves! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='别提那些迅猛龙。提也别提。' WHERE entry=16054; /* Text0_0: Don\'t even ask about the raptors. Just don\'t. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='东西都弄坏了，嗯？' WHERE entry=16058; /* Text0_0: Gear all banged up, eh? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='<这些小岩池鱼人似乎是被遗弃在这里了。现在他们的境遇肯定很糟糕。耐普托一定想让你将他们带回到大海去。他们在那里才有可能躲避开纳迦的捕猎。>' WHERE entry=16060; /* Text0_0: <These baby Rockpool murlocs seem to have been abandoned here.  You suspect that they are in trouble, and that Neptool would want you to bring them back to the ocean, where they stand a chance of escaping the naga.> */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='列兵霍金纳多·伯纳德，暴风城步兵团第十三编队……$g阁下:女士;。' WHERE entry=16061; /* Text0_0: Private Reginald Pollard, 13th brigade, Stormwind infantry... $gsir:ma\'am;. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我们发现了他们……部落的船队……然后突然就不见了，有触手伸出来一把抓住了我们的船……把它折成了两截！$b$b幸存者们……我们一落水就立刻被纳迦抓住。$b$b那是差不多一星期以前的事了。' WHERE entry=16062; /* Text0_0: We had them in our sights... the Horde ships... then out of nowhere, tentacles reached up and seized our ship... broke it right in two!$b$bThe survivors... we were captured by naga as soon as we hit the water.$b$bThat was nearly a week ago. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='真是奇怪……从没想过纳迦竟然会设法让我们活下来。$b$b他们弄出这些像珍珠一样的泡泡……一人一个……让我们能够呼吸。$b$b他们每天都会送走一些囚犯……不知道去往哪里。$b$b再也没见过他们……' WHERE entry=16063; /* Text0_0: Strange... never thought the naga would go out of their way to keep us alive.$b$bThey create these pearly bubbles... one per man... made it so we could breathe.$b$bEvery day they send a bunch of the prisoners off... somewhere.$b$bNever see them again.... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='另一名士兵设法获得了自由，打碎了我们的珍珠……释放了我们。$b$b有人游向了水面……有人看到这座洞穴，并向它游来。$b$b我是唯一一个活下来的……' WHERE entry=16064; /* Text0_0: Another soldier somehow got free and broke a bunch of our pearls... freed us.$b$bSome swam up towards the surface... some saw this cave and swam for it.$b$bI\'m the only one that made it.... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='啊！$r！后退！' WHERE entry=16065; /* Text0_0: Ack!  Stay back, $r! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='说不好……$b$b他们每天都会带来新的士兵。部落和联盟的都有。$b$b有些在来的当天就会被拖走……其它像我一样的，会在那儿待上一个星期……也许更久。' WHERE entry=16066; /* Text0_0: No telling...$b$bThey brought new soldiers in every day. Horde and Alliance, both.$b$bSome would get hauled away the same day... others, like me, kept there for a week... maybe more. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='试都别试，$r。$b$b趁还来得及，赶快离开这儿……$b$b有太多人都将……必死无疑……' WHERE entry=16067; /* Text0_0: Don\'t even try, $r.$b$bGet out of here while you can...$b$bThere are too many... certain death... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='城市已被攻陷。艾萨尔向你发出了胜利的恭贺。你今天为自己赢得了足够的尊重。' WHERE entry=16069; /* Text0_0: The city has been routed. The Azsh\'ir cry your name as a victory call. You\'ve earned much respect this day. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我没想到能这么快地夺取这座城市。看来我们将有大把时间来准备入侵。' WHERE entry=16070; /* Text0_0: I\'d not expected the city to be taken so quickly. It seems we\'ll have much time to prepare for the invasion. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='大灾变在丹莫罗引起了混乱。穴居人以我们前所未见的规模成群结队地迁移到地表，把我们的宿敌霜鬃巨魔赶到了离我们居住地更近的地方。$B$B铁炉堡已经派出我的巡山小队来协助解决这一问题。' WHERE entry=16074; /* Text0_0: The Catacylsm has created chaos in Dun Morogh. The troggs have come to the surface in numbers we haven\'t seen before, driving our traditional enemies, the Frostmane trolls, ever closer to our settlements.$B$BIronforge has dispatched my mountaineer company to help deal with the problems. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='从过往的灰烬中生出新的生命……这是艾森娜的馈赠。$B$B如果没有你，这奇迹决不会出现。' WHERE entry=16075; /* Text0_0: New life from the ashes of old... this is Aessina\'s gift.$B$BWithout you, this miracle never would\'ve happened. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='<这个上古生物盯着你。那双眼睛比你的头还要大。望着它们就好象坠入了一片深蓝的海洋。>' WHERE entry=16076; /* Text0_0: <The ancient turns to gaze at you with eyes larger than your entire head. Peering into them is like falling into a deep blue ocean.> */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='等我们完成之后，那些霜鬃巨魔会把我们看作是比穴居人更可怕的对手。他们只能离开，别无选择。' WHERE entry=16077; /* Text0_0: When we\'re done here, those Frostmanes will fear us more than the troggs. They\'ll have no choice but to leave. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='哇——我这是在哪儿？你是和他们一伙的吗？',Text0_1_loc4='哇——我这是在哪儿？你是和他们一伙的吗？',Text1_0_loc4='都结束了没有？',Text1_1_loc4='都结束了没有？' WHERE entry=16078; /* Text0_0: Wha - Where  am I? Are you one of them? */ /* Text0_1: Wha - Where  am I? Are you one of them? */ /* Text1_0: Is it all over yet? */ /* Text1_1: Is it all over yet? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text2_0_loc4='必须……回到……铁木那里！',Text2_1_loc4='必须……回到……铁木那里！',Text3_0_loc4='你不是暮光之锤的人。外面发生什么事了？',Text3_1_loc4='你不是暮光之锤的人。外面发生什么事了？' WHERE entry=16078; /* Text2_0: Must ... return to ... Irontree! */ /* Text2_1: Must ... return to ... Irontree! */ /* Text3_0: You\'re not from Twilight\'s Hammer. What is happening out there? */ /* Text3_1: You\'re not from Twilight\'s Hammer. What is happening out there? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text4_0_loc4='我烧伤了。非常严重。',Text4_1_loc4='我烧伤了。非常严重。',Text5_0_loc4='暮光之锤……我听见他们尖叫窜逃……我们是在发动反攻吗？',Text5_1_loc4='暮光之锤……我听见他们尖叫窜逃……我们是在发动反攻吗？' WHERE entry=16078; /* Text4_0: I\'m burned. Badly. */ /* Text4_1: I\'m burned. Badly. */ /* Text5_0: Twilight\'s Hammer... I heard them screaming and running... are we making a counter-attack? */ /* Text5_1: Twilight\'s Hammer... I heard them screaming and running... are we making a counter-attack? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text6_0_loc4='城镇……被毁了！我们无法阻止他们。',Text6_1_loc4='城镇……被毁了！我们无法阻止他们。',Text7_0_loc4='他们打开了通往火焰之地的传送门……告诉我希望还在！',Text7_1_loc4='他们打开了通往火焰之地的传送门……告诉我希望还在！' WHERE entry=16078; /* Text6_0: The town... demolished! We couldn\'t stop them. */ /* Text6_1: The town... demolished! We couldn\'t stop them. */ /* Text7_0: They\'ve opened gateways to the Firelands... tell me there\'s still hope! */ /* Text7_1: They\'ve opened gateways to the Firelands... tell me there\'s still hope! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='这个生灵……她相当年迈且非常睿智。要是我们能与奈瑟匹拉交谈的话，我们就能了解很多与瓦丝琪尔和纳迦有关的事。' WHERE entry=16084; /* Text0_0: This creature... she is quite old, and very wise.  We stand to learn a great deal about Vashj\'ir and the naga, if we can only speak with Nespirah. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='这间破旧的旅馆从外面看已经惨不忍睹，不过倒是个理想的据点。' WHERE entry=16085; /* Text0_0: This old inn isn\'t much to look at anymore, but it makes for a great stronghold. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我不明白这地方的起源与用途。$B$B这些通道是行军用的，这没错，可这里同样遍布烧焦与饱受折磨的尸体，有些尸体已经部分被吞食，而大部分则只是被打得面目全非。$B$B尽管我们是在火焰之地，我却感觉像是已经跨进了地狱。' WHERE entry=16090; /* Text0_0: I cannot fathom the origin or purpose of this place.$B$BThese corridors are used for troop movements, yes, but they\'re also littered with charred and tortured corpses, some partially devoured, most simply crushed and beaten.$B$BWe are in the Firelands, but I feel as though we\'ve crossed the threshold into hell. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我已经试着向沙尔斯巴里解释过很多次了——我没办法把他变成一只狼人。可他总是充耳不闻，反而让自己坚信，只要能获得我的信任，我就会和他分享秘密。$B$B侏儒可真是奇怪的家伙。' WHERE entry=16094; /* Text0_0: I\'ve tried explaining to Salsbury time and time again that there is no possible way that I could transform him into a worgen. He refuses to listen and has instead convinced himself that if he gains my trust I will let him in on the secret.$B$BGnomes are very strange. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='戈德林的坚韧战力充满着传奇色彩。$B$B各地的战士都纷纷到访这座圣殿，祈求能像戈德林那样勇猛卓绝。' WHERE entry=16095; /* Text0_0: Goldrinn\'s tenacity is the stuff of legend.$B$BWarriors from all walks visit this shrine in hopes of tapping into that kind of battle prowess. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='士气变得高涨了，多谢你的努力，$c。',Text1_0_loc4='要是我们能从这儿杀出去，地狱咆哮一定会获知你的功绩，$r。' WHERE entry=16099; /* Text0_0: Morale is growing higher, thanks to your efforts, $c. */ /* Text1_0: If we find a way to fight our way out of here, Hellscream will know of your deeds, $r. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text2_0_loc4='这些兽人和我已经在多次战斗中出生入死。$b$b我不羡慕任何进到这里的纳迦。' WHERE entry=16099; /* Text2_0: These orcs and I have served together through many battles.$b$bI do not envy any naga that enters this place. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='他从不放弃——铁木队长——他说要让他们为其所玷污的每一寸土地付出代价。他很可能就在那下面，也许还活着！' WHERE entry=16100; /* Text0_0: He never gave up - Captain Irontree - said he\'d make them pay for every inch of ground they defile. He may still be alive down there! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='这些水下的资源真是让人无话可说。任何工程材料和替换件都能找到代用品。给我几天时间，我就能用水藻和贝壳做出一辆水下改装跑车！' WHERE entry=16101; /* Text0_0: Can\'t complain about the materials down here. Substitutes for everything. Substitutes for substitutes. Gimme a few days and I\'ll build a aquatic hotrod out of kelp and shells! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='这地方跟废墟相比没那么凉爽，如果要我说的话，这儿的空气也有些太过潮湿，不过确实给我一种舒服的、回到家里的感觉。$B$B你不这么认为吗？' WHERE entry=16105; /* Text0_0: This place isn\'t quite as cool as the ruins, and the air in here is a bit humid if I do say so myself, but it does have a comfy, home feel to it.$B$BDon\'t you think? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我不知道你怎么想，可我真的很想念下面废墟里那些取之不尽的原料！$B$B就凭我们在这洞里找到的少得可怜的材料，我甚至都不知道能不能造出一颗哑弹！' WHERE entry=16106; /* Text0_0: I don\'t know about you, but I really miss the unlimited raw materials that were down in the ruins!$B$BI\'m not even sure if I could make a dud grenade out of the little that can be scrounged in this cave! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='纳迦。$B$B<维索恩充满厌恶地朝地上吐了口唾沫。>$B$B他们可真蠢，居然妄想能用鞭子把兽人训得任其差遣。我们要让他们后悔，没把握住机会杀了我们，让他们一个个全都后悔。' WHERE entry=16107; /* Text0_0: Naga.$B$B<Vilethorn spits on the ground in disgust.>$B$BIt was foolish of them to think they could make an orc labor at their whip. We will make every last one of them regret not killing us when they had the chance. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='如何是好？' WHERE entry=16111; /* Text0_0: Coming or going? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='狼魂先祖的坚忍战力充满传奇色彩。$B$B以他为榜样吧，$c，胜利一定就在前方等着你。' WHERE entry=16112; /* Text0_0: The tenacity of the wolf ancient is the stuff of legend.$B$BLearn from his example, $c, and victory is all but certain. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='从野性生灵在艾泽拉斯出现的那一刻起，这个世界上就有了戈德林的身影。他就像是猎手之魂，是野兽嗅到食物或感受到幼子身处险境时迸发的动物本能。他出现时是一头身形巨大的白狼，凶猛而诡诈。$B$B他闻名于各种文化。兽人甚至给他起了个特有的名字——“洛戈什”。$B$B一万年前，当恶魔首次入侵艾泽拉斯时，戈德林与其它远古半神们比肩拼死抵抗。' WHERE entry=16113; /* Text0_0: From the moment the wild creatures first stirred on Azeroth, Goldrinn was there. His is the spirit of the hunter, the animal instinct that kicks in when wild things smell food or feel their children are in jeopardy. He appears as a great white wolf, ferocious and cunning.$B$BHe\'s known across all cultures. The orcs even have their own name for him: "Lo\'Gosh."$B$BTen thousand years ago, when demons first breached Azeroth, Goldrinn stood with the other ancients to mount a desperate defense. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='就是那段最黑暗的日子，为戈德林坚忍的作战风格笼上了一层传奇色彩。正当别人在那些恶魔军团面前战栗时，他们的数量却只会激发出狼神先祖更强大的战技。他会冲进敌阵，尖牙沾满敌人肮脏的血液，他的利爪会一下刺穿数十个敌人……$B$B据说，他在暗夜精灵撤离埃雷萨拉斯——现在被我们叫做厄运之槌的古城时，在后方担负着掩护的重任。$B$B他死了吗？我不知道这凶猛的野兽之魂是否会真的死去，$n。' WHERE entry=16114; /* Text0_0: It was during those darkest of days that Goldrinn\'s tenacity in war became legendary. While others quaked at the visage of those demon hordes, their multitudes only spurred the great wolf ancient to ever greater feats of strength. He would wade into their ranks, fangs bared and spattered with their vile ichor, his great claws thrashing them by the dozen...$B$BIt was said he stayed behind to cover the Night Elf retreat from Eldre\'Thalas, the ancient city we know now as Dire Maul.$B$BDid he die? I\'m not certain the spirit of animal ferocity can ever truly die, $N. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='洛戈什是猎手之魂，是野兽嗅到食物或感受到幼子身处险境时迸发的动物本能。他始终与我们同在，与部落血脉相连，永存于我们的天性与血液之中。$B$B他以多种形态出现在我们的世界与此地。在艾泽拉斯，人们说他是一只巨大的白狼，凶猛又诡诈。暗夜精灵叫他“戈德林”。$B$B他们讲述着一场发生在一万年前的传奇之战——洛戈什击败了恶魔军团。你想要了解一下吗？' WHERE entry=16115; /* Text0_0: Lo\'Gosh is the spirit of the hunter, the animal instinct that kicks in when one smells food or sees one\'s children in jeopardy. He has always been with us, a part of our Horde, in our instincts and in our blood.$B$BHe has appeared in many forms, both on our world and here. On Azeroth, he is seen as a great white wolf, ferocious and cunning. The night elves call him "Goldrinn."$B$BThey tell of a legendary battle ten thousand years ago, where Lo\'Gosh fought off the demon hordes. Do you want to hear about it? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='一万年前，恶魔首次侵入了我们的世界，就像他们夺取兽人的家园德拉诺一样。他们鱼贯而入，将战火蔓延到了各个角落。艾泽拉斯伟大的远古半神们帮助凡间种族拼死抵抗。$B$B洛戈什的坚忍战力便是在这段最黑暗的日子里成为了传奇。他对恶魔毫无畏惧。他会冲进敌阵，尖牙沾满敌人肮脏的血液，他的利爪会一下刺穿数十个敌人……$B$B他不屈于恶魔的勇武精神激励着我们每一个人。我们都能从他身上汲取能量。' WHERE entry=16116; /* Text0_0: Ten thousand years ago demons first breached this world, just as they had the orc homeworld of Draenor. They flooded across the terrain in legion. The great ancients of Azeroth helped the mortal races to mount a desperate defense.$B$BThe tenacity of Lo\'Gosh in these dark days became the stuff of legend. He feared no demon. He would wade into their ranks, fangs bared and spattered with their vile ichor, his great claws thrashing them by the dozen...$B$BHis stand against the demons inspires us all. We can all learn from his example. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='啊，托尔托拉！它总是被误解，总是被低估。那些在陆地和海洋之间轻松穿行的生物都会将托尔托拉当作神祗和祖先来崇拜。$B$B一万年以前，燃烧军团入侵艾泽拉斯。托尔托拉与塞纳留斯和其他凡间种族共赴战场。$B$B当恶魔大军对守卫者们的阵线发动冲击的时候，他们拿托尔托拉毫无办法。一开始，他们对它并不在意。但托尔托拉可怕的重量和致命的双颚在转瞬间就杀死了成百上千的恶魔……' WHERE entry=16123; /* Text0_0: Ah, Tortolla! Often misunderstood and always, always underestimated. Creatures who move effortlessly between land and sea look to Tortolla as their patron ancient.$B$BTen thousand years ago the Burning Legion invaded Azeroth, and Tortolla was among the ancients who took to the field of battle alongside Cenarius and the mortal races.$B$BAs the demon hordes crashed against the front lines of the beleaguered defenders, they didn\'t know what to make of Tortolla. At first they tried to ignore him, but his terrible weight and crushing jaws laid waste to hundreds... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='托尔托拉从未倒下。尽管最后被那些强大的军团末日守卫团团围住，可他们却对他那坚硬的皮肤和刀枪不入的龟壳束手无策。喔，他们当时别提有多暴怒了！在凡间种族得以重整兵力来关闭传送门、终结入侵之前，托尔托拉守住了阵地，并掩护他们完成了决定性的撤退。$B$B据说在战斗结束后，有人发现托尔托拉被压在堆成山的恶魔尸体下面。他抖抖身上的尸体，从斑驳血污里伸出了头。然后安静地、慢慢地……问我们打赢了没。$B$B<哈缪尔把一只手按在了肚子上，发出了发自肺腑、无法抑制的狂笑。>' WHERE entry=16124; /* Text0_0: Tortolla never fell. Eventually the greatest Doomguards of the legion surrounded him, but couldn\'t pierce his stony skin and invulnerable shell. Oh, how they raged! Tortolla held his ground and covered a final retreat, before the mortal races regrouped and managed to seal the portal and end the invasion.$B$BIt was said that after the battle, Tortolla was found underneath a mountain of demon corpses. He shook the bodies free and his head emerged from the gore. Then, quietly, slowly... he asked if we had won.$B$B<Hamuul rests a hand on his stomach and bellows a deep, unselfconscious laugh.> */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我们的战士……他们现在都已沦为俘虏。',Text1_0_loc4='我们当中有许多人试图摆脱纳迦。$b$b可只有我成功了……' WHERE entry=16126; /* Text0_0: Our warriors... they\'re all captives now. */ /* Text1_0: Many of us tried to escape the naga.$b$bI am the only one who succeeded... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text2_0_loc4='这说不通，可那些恶棍却不遗余力地想要延长我们的生命……' WHERE entry=16126; /* Text2_0: It makes no sense, but those vermin are going to great lengths to keep our troops alive... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我们是地狱咆哮的先锋战士！' WHERE entry=16127; /* Text0_0: I am Gurrok, of Hellscream\'s Vanguard. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我们抓到他们了！$b$b该死的联盟船只……我们本可以第一时间抄近路直取暴风城，彻底解决了他们！$b$b可不知打哪儿冒出来巨大的触手，一把抓住了我们的船……把它断成了两截！$b$b幸存者们……我们一落水就立刻被纳迦抓住了。' WHERE entry=16128; /* Text0_0: We had them!$b$bWretched Alliance ships... we could\'ve cut a path to Stormwind and put an end to them!$b$b...But out of nowhere, gigantic tentacles reached up and seized our ship... broke it right in two!$b$bThe survivors... we were captured by naga as soon as we hit the water. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='真是奇怪，从没想过纳迦竟然会设法让我们活下来。$b$b他们用神秘的珍珠造出牢房——让我们能够呼吸的小单间，然后就不管我们了……。$b$b他们每天都会送走一些囚犯……不知道去往哪里。$b$b再也没见过他们……' WHERE entry=16129; /* Text0_0: Strange that the naga would go out of their way to keep us alive.$b$bThey create prisons from mystical pearls - cells that allowed us to breathe, but little else..$b$bThey ship the prisoners off... somewhere.$b$bNever see them again.... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我们当中有位战士得以逃脱，并打碎了许多牢笼……我们自由了——至少是片刻的自由。$b$b有些人朝水面蜂拥游去……有些则看到并朝这个洞穴游来。$b$b我是唯一活下来的人……' WHERE entry=16130; /* Text0_0: One of our warriors broke free and smashed many of the prisons... we were free - at least for a moment.$b$bSome swam up towards the surface... some saw this cave and swam for it.$b$bI\'m the only one that lived.... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我不知道他们发生了什么事。$b$b不断有俘虏出现。部落和联盟的都有——几乎都只剩下一口气。$b$b他们一定是被强行拖到海沟那边去了，不然就只有死路一条。' WHERE entry=16131; /* Text0_0: I do not know what became of them.$b$bThere was a constant flow of captives. Horde and Alliance, both - all barely alive.$b$bThey must\'ve been hauled away beyond the trench, or they have perished. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='他们的人数多得难以计算。他们的防御仿佛无懈可击。$b$b我找不出任何可以利用的薄弱环节，$r。' WHERE entry=16132; /* Text0_0: Their numbers are too many to count. Their defenses look impenetrable.$b$bI saw no weaknesses to exploit, $r. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='地狱咆哮之眼注视着我们！' WHERE entry=16138; /* Text0_0: Hellscream\'s eyes are upon us all! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='黑暗女王在注视着你……' WHERE entry=16142; /* Text0_0: The Dark Lady watch over you... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='在这种情况下要我怎么保持旅店的清洁？你会负责处理这俾格米的麻烦吗？' WHERE entry=16143; /* Text0_0: How can I keep a clean inn with all of this going on? Are you going to take care of this pygmy problem? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='地精僵尸？！接下来是什么……火山喷发？' WHERE entry=16144; /* Text0_0: Goblin zombies?! What\'s next... the volcano exploding? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='女武士，你的出现使我倍感荣幸。现在可以开始仪式了吗？' WHERE entry=16149; /* Text0_0: Battlemaiden, you honor me with your presence. Is it time for the ritual to commence? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='啊！嗯……你好啊。我在这儿只是在检查这个壳。继续！这儿没什么好看的！' WHERE entry=16164; /* Text0_0: Ah!  Umm... hello there.  I was just inspecting this shell, here.  Carry on!  Nothing to see here! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我看来遇到了……漂浮的麻烦。' WHERE entry=16165; /* Text0_0: I seem to be having a... floating problem. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我也不确定。可能是因为我骨头太轻，或是肺活量异于常人。也许只是因为我中午吃的那块奶酪。$b$b不管怎样，要不是有这壳在，我早就像火箭一样窜出水面了。' WHERE entry=16166; /* Text0_0: I couldn\'t tell ya.  Maybe I\'ve got a low bone density, or a larger-than average lung capacity.  Maybe it\'s all that cheese I had for lunch.$b$bEither way, this shell is the only thing that\'s keeping me from rocketing to the surface. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='哎，家族遗传问题。恐怕掘歌家的人总是被浮力问题困扰。' WHERE entry=16167; /* Text0_0: Aye, and it runs in the family.  The Digsongs have always had buoyancy issues, I\'m afraid. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我用手划啊划啊，$g小伙子:小姑娘;……精疲力竭地划。我都不知道究竟有多少海水直接灌进了我的鼻子。$b$b不过你应该看见我用脚和牙齿力战大螃蟹的精彩场面了！那可真是荣耀啊，真的。' WHERE entry=16168; /* Text0_0: Hand over hand, $g lad: lass;... hand over aching hand.  I can\'t tell ya how many gallons of seawater went right up my nose.$b$bYou shoulda seen me fight off that pyreshell crab using my feet and my teeth, though!  \'Twas a thing of glory, \'twas. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我记得当我还是个小不点儿的时候……别的男孩子都能一猛子扎到洛克莫丹湖底，拾上来各种各样的海胆和贝壳。奥斯卡和我却只能趴在湖面上，两腿乱蹬，分享不到半点儿乐趣。' WHERE entry=16169; /* Text0_0: I remember when I was just a wee little lad... the other boys would swim down to the bottom of Loch Modan to pick up sand dollars and seashells.  Oskar and I were stuck on the lake\'s surface, kicking our legs uselessly into the air, but we couldn\'t join them. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我都数不清究竟有多少次，远远看见水底有金光闪闪的矿脉，透过水面折射出诱人的光芒。我却只能拿着矿锄两手空空地游走，眼睁睁地看着该死的兽人和血精灵轻而易举的潜入水底，大摇大摆的携矿而去。' WHERE entry=16170; /* Text0_0: I can\'t even remember how many times I\'ve spotted a beautiful mining vein at the bottom of a lake or river, glimmering mockingly at me.  I\'m forced to float orelessly by, mining pick in hand, only to watch some blasted orc or blood elf swim down to the bottom and take it away from me. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你根本无法想象像这样被困在瓦丝琪尔是什么感觉！你知道有多少鱼把我当成海草，咬我的脚趾头，在我的护甲里钻来钻去吗？$b$b光是挠痒痒就能把一个矮人逼疯！' WHERE entry=16171; /* Text0_0: Ya have no idea what it\'s like to be stuck here in Vashj\'ir like this!  Do ya know how many fish have confused me for a piece of seaweed, nibbling on my toes and hiding between pieces of my armor?$b$bThe tickling alone is enough to drive a dwarf mad! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我知道你没兴趣听我抱怨这些。不要紧。$b$b但别忘了你有多幸运——“深谙水性”还能“向着一个方向游泳而不是只能往上浮”。' WHERE entry=16172; /* Text0_0: I can tell ya don\'t want to hear my grumbling.  That\'s fine.$b$bJust don\'t forget how lucky you are, with your "sea legs" and your "ability to swim in a direction other than up". */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='痛肠可真了不起。痛肠是在这新地方头一个打碎弱小人类的英雄。$B$B痛肠可真高兴。' WHERE entry=16173; /* Text0_0: Goutgut very special. Goutgut am first to get to crush puny humans in new place.$B$BGoutgut so happy. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='不找到她，我就哪儿都不去！' WHERE entry=16178; /* Text0_0: I\'m not going anywhere until I find her! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='谢谢你为我带回了狼。' WHERE entry=16179; /* Text0_0: Thank you for returning Wolf. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='有人正在用这些烧杯和炼金工具进行各种潜水艇燃料的实验。',Text0_1_loc4='有人正在用这些烧杯和炼金工具进行各种潜水艇燃料的实验。' WHERE entry=16180; /* Text0_0: Someone is using these beakers and alchemy tools to perform experiments with various types of submarine fuel. */ /* Text0_1: Someone is using these beakers and alchemy tools to perform experiments with various types of submarine fuel. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我们的人民被人类当作囚犯、当作奴隶，就关在这座营地里。我被锁在这些笼子里面；我看到我的兄弟们被关在这儿，吊在这些绞架上。$B$B我看见我们所有人的领袖——奥格瑞姆·毁灭之锤，被利刃刺穿背部。他的血把我们脚下的土地都染成了深色。$B$B现在再看看我们。落锤镇——我们世代的家园，我们在这里失去了一切，然后再用我们自己的双手夺回来。' WHERE entry=16181; /* Text0_0: Our people were held as prisoners, as slaves, in this very camp by the humans. I was locked in these cages; I saw my brothers held in these stocks, hung in these gallows.$B$BI saw Orgrim Doomhammer, leader of us all, stabbed in the back. His blood stained black the earth we stand on.$B$BAnd look at us now. This is our legacy: Hammerfall, where we lost everything, and then took it back with our own hands. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你面前放着几种油料样本，旁边还有一个空烧杯。烧杯看起来能装下大约五种样本。$b$b你想先选哪种油料？',Text0_1_loc4='你面前放着几种油料样本，旁边还有一个空烧杯。烧杯看起来能装下大约五种样本。$b$b你想先选哪种油料？' WHERE entry=16182; /* Text0_0: Several small samples of oil sit in front of you, along with an empty beaker.  The beaker looks like it can probably fit about five samples inside of it.$b$bWhat kind of oil will you take first? */ /* Text0_1: Several small samples of oil sit in front of you, along with an empty beaker.  The beaker looks like it can probably fit about five samples inside of it.$b$bWhat kind of oil will you take first? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你接下来想要选哪种油料？',Text0_1_loc4='你接下来想要选哪种油料？' WHERE entry=16183; /* Text0_0: What type of oil will you select next? */ /* Text0_1: What type of oil will you select next? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你现在有两份油料样本了。接下来想要选哪种？',Text0_1_loc4='你现在有两份油料样本了。接下来想要选哪种？' WHERE entry=16184; /* Text0_0: You now have two samples of oil.  Which sample will you select next? */ /* Text0_1: You now have two samples of oil.  Which sample will you select next? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你现在有三份样本了。接下来想要选哪种？',Text0_1_loc4='你现在有三份样本了。接下来想要选哪种？' WHERE entry=16185; /* Text0_0: You now have three samples.  Which sample will you select next? */ /* Text0_1: You now have three samples.  Which sample will you select next? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你现在选好四份样本了，只能再选一份。选哪种呢？',Text0_1_loc4='你现在选好四份样本了，只能再选一份。选哪种呢？' WHERE entry=16186; /* Text0_0: You have four samples, and only have room to test one more.  Which one will it be? */ /* Text0_1: You have four samples, and only have room to test one more.  Which one will it be? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你已经把五份样本都选好了。',Text0_1_loc4='你已经把五份样本都选好了。' WHERE entry=16187; /* Text0_0: You have selected all five of your samples. */ /* Text0_1: You have selected all five of your samples. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你可以用这些烧杯和炼金工具进行各种潜水艇燃料的实验。',Text0_1_loc4='你可以用这些烧杯和炼金工具进行各种潜水艇燃料的实验。' WHERE entry=16188; /* Text0_0: You can use these beakers and alchemy tools to perform experiments with various types of submarine fuel. */ /* Text0_1: You can use these beakers and alchemy tools to perform experiments with various types of submarine fuel. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你发现了一种新型生物燃料！快把它拿给工程师“洗衣桶”测试一下。',Text0_1_loc4='你发现了一种新型生物燃料！快把它拿给工程师“洗衣桶”测试一下。' WHERE entry=16189; /* Text0_0: You have discovered a new type of bio-fuel!  Bring it to Engineer Hexascrub for testing. */ /* Text0_1: You have discovered a new type of bio-fuel!  Bring it to Engineer Hexascrub for testing. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你发现了一种新型生物燃料！快把它拿给菲亚斯科·尖笑测试一下。',Text0_1_loc4='你发现了一种新型生物燃料！快把它拿给菲亚斯科·尖笑测试一下。' WHERE entry=16190; /* Text0_0: You have discovered a new type of bio-fuel!  Bring it to Fiasco Sizzlegrin for testing. */ /* Text0_1: You have discovered a new type of bio-fuel!  Bring it to Fiasco Sizzlegrin for testing. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='<弗瑞恩呻吟着。>' WHERE entry=16192; /* Text0_0: <Furien groans.> */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我们坚持到现在已经消灭了许多纳迦，可他们还在前仆后继地冲过来。到底要怎么做才能逃出这该死的洞穴？' WHERE entry=16193; /* Text0_0: We\'ve killed dozens of naga to get this far, but they still keep coming.  What will it take to escape this wretched cavern? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我不在乎自己是否会死在这儿，$n。我要让这些纳迦为我们每一个被杀死或奴役的同胞付出代价！$b$b就让其它人去烦恼该如何逃生吧。我要考虑的是该怎么让这些魔鬼受到惩罚。' WHERE entry=16194; /* Text0_0: I don\'t care if I die inside this husk, $n.  I\'ll pay these naga back for every one of my fellow soldiers they\'ve killed or enslaved!$b$bThe others can worry about escape.  I\'ll worry about doling out punishment to these snakes. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我们需要你的帮助，$c。我们已经拼尽了全力，但纳迦的攻势丝毫没有减弱。' WHERE entry=16197; /* Text0_0: We need your help, $c.  We\'ve fought tooth and nail to get here, but the naga keep coming. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='要是你的双手沾上了纳迦的鲜血，那你就是我的盟友。$b$b很久以前，我发誓决不再做任何人的奴隶，在那以后我一直信守对自己的承诺，直到落在埃卓凯丝的手里。现在我已经抑制不住胸中的怒火。鲜血是我唯一的渴望……我可以不吃不睡，甚至可以不要胜利……只要鲜血。' WHERE entry=16199; /* Text0_0: If you have naga blood on your hands, then you\'re an ally of mine.$b$bA long time ago, I swore I\'d never be anyone\'s slave again, and I kept that bargain until Idra\'kess captured us.  Now I can barely contain my fury.  All I want is blood... not food, not sleep, not even victory... only blood. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我的伤口还没愈合，$r。要是我们不尽快行动，恐怕我就要死在这家伙的肚子里。' WHERE entry=16200; /* Text0_0: My wounds are not healing, $r.  I fear I may die inside this creature\'s gut if we do not act soon. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='<拉葛雷克的声音在你脑中回荡。>$B$B我已经要……死了。你必须帮忙……阻止……暮光之锤。$B$B他们汲取……我的能量……来创造……他们的升腾者。他们在……对抗耐普图隆的……战争中……将是重大的……威胁。' WHERE entry=16202; /* Text0_0: <L\'ghorek\'s voice booms inside your mind.>$B$BI AM ALMOST... DEAD. YOU MUST HELP... STOP... THE TWILIGHT\'S HAMMER.$B$BTHEY DRAIN... MY ENERGY TO... CREATE... THEIR ASCENDANTS. THEY ARE A... GRAVE THREAT IN... THE IMMINENT WAR... VERSUS... NEPTULON. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='元素在愤怒的咆哮着。这与纳迦的到来一定不会是巧合。他们一定在等待着什么。' WHERE entry=16203; /* Text0_0: Tha elements be crying out in rage. It ain\'t no coincidence dat da naga are here. Dey be wantin\' someting. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='啊，就算没有这些新麻烦不断的冒出来，维持这儿的秩序就已经够让人头痛的了！希望你有好消息，$n……',Text0_1_loc4='啊，就算没有这些新麻烦不断的冒出来，维持这儿的秩序就已经够让人头痛的了！希望你有好消息，$n……' WHERE entry=16211; /* Text0_0: Ach, it\'s hard enough keeping order around here without all these new troubles popping up!  I hope you have good news, $n... */ /* Text0_1: Ach, it\'s hard enough keeping order around here without all these new troubles popping up!  I hope you have good news, $n... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='见过我所见过的那些，做过我所做过的那些，而现在还能呼吸……我真是个幸运的侏儒。' WHERE entry=16214; /* Text0_0: To have seen the things I\'ve seen, to have done the things I\'ve done, and to still breathe... I am a lucky gnome. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='为国王料理膳食是份荣耀，可不是工作。你有时间帮我跑跑腿儿吗？',Text0_1_loc4='为国王料理膳食是份荣耀，可不是工作。你有时间帮我跑跑腿儿吗？' WHERE entry=16216; /* Text0_0: Cooking for the King is an honor, not a job.  Do you have time to help me on some errands? */ /* Text0_1: Cooking for the King is an honor, not a job.  Do you have time to help me on some errands? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我只是稍事休息。永恒地坚守并不像听上去那么容易，$r。' WHERE entry=16220; /* Text0_0: I was just taking a rest.  Eternal watch is not as easy as it sounds, $r. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='<这群岩池鱼人宝宝朝海洋的方向看去。>' WHERE entry=16231; /* Text0_0: <These baby Rockpool murlocs look toward the ocean.> */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='就算我们要死，也要带着消灭夙敌的荣耀！' WHERE entry=16234; /* Text0_0: If we are to die, let it be with honor against our hated enemies! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='在我们加入最终战斗之前，我们必须对发生在对面那个上古生灵体内的事情做个了断。否则，我们将毫无胜算。$B$B尽全力去帮埃鲁纳克吧，$n。' WHERE entry=16236; /* Text0_0: Before we can join the final battle, we must ensure that whatever\'s happening inside of that Ancient across from us is put to an end. Otherwise, we will not stand a chance.$B$BLend Erunak your full assistance, $N. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='拉葛雷克是位远古之神，就在沟壑的另一侧。他正在受到某种力量的侵扰。$B$B我们必须终结这一切，否则我们谁都活不了！' WHERE entry=16237; /* Text0_0: L\'ghorek is the name of the Ancient god that sits across the chasm from us. It is being infested by something.$B$BWe must put an end to this or we will certainly all meet our doom! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='尽管我们拼尽了全力，纳迦还是对裂口发动了攻击！$B$B必须守住水元素位面！' WHERE entry=16238; /* Text0_0: In spite of our best efforts, the naga have attacked the breach!$B$BThe Plane of Water must be defended! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='在深渊裂口，一场战争正在酝酿。希望与扳钳X2号一起赶来的援军足够抵挡。' WHERE entry=16239; /* Text0_0: There is a battle brewing at the Abyssal Breach. I hope that the reinforcements that arrived with the Pincer X2 will be enough. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='在我们加入深渊裂口的最终战斗之前，我们必须终结在对面那上古生灵体内所发生的一切。否则，我们都将失败。$B$B尽全力去帮埃鲁纳克吧，$n。' WHERE entry=16241; /* Text0_0: Before we join the final battle at the Abyssal Breach, we must stop whatever\'s happening inside of that Ancient across from us. Otherwise, we will fail.$B$BLend Erunak all of your might, $N. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你想要什么？',Text0_1_loc4='你想要什么？',Text1_0_loc4='我什么都不会告诉你！',Text1_1_loc4='我什么都不会告诉你！' WHERE entry=16250; /* Text0_0: Whaddya want? */ /* Text0_1: Whaddya want? */ /* Text1_0: I ain\'t tellin\' you nothin\'! */ /* Text1_1: I ain\'t tellin\' you nothin\'! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text2_0_loc4='滚开。',Text2_1_loc4='滚开。',Text3_0_loc4='喔，是大英雄来了。我得救了！对，是的……',Text3_1_loc4='喔，是大英雄来了。我得救了！对，是的……' WHERE entry=16250; /* Text2_0: Get lost. */ /* Text2_1: Get lost. */ /* Text3_0: Oh the big hero has arrived. I\'m saved! Yea, right... */ /* Text3_1: Oh the big hero has arrived. I\'m saved! Yea, right... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text4_0_loc4='你想聊聊？给钱。',Text4_1_loc4='你想聊聊？给钱。' WHERE entry=16250; /* Text4_0: You wanna talk? Pay up. */ /* Text4_1: You wanna talk? Pay up. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='这片土地在饱受煎熬……它在乞求怜悯，$r，它在乞求怜悯。' WHERE entry=16256; /* Text0_0: The land suffers... it cries for mercy, $r, it cries for mercy. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='喂饱 一支部落大军可不是件容易的事。我有许多活儿要干，你有时间帮帮我吗？',Text0_1_loc4='喂饱 一支部落大军可不是件容易的事。我有许多活儿要干，你有时间帮帮我吗？' WHERE entry=16258; /* Text0_0: Feeding a Horde army is no easy task.  I have lots to do, do you have time to help? */ /* Text0_1: Feeding a Horde army is no easy task.  I have lots to do, do you have time to help? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我这辈子都没离开过西部荒野，$g兄弟:姐妹;。我还记得西部荒野曾是荆棘谷这一侧最富生机的地方。那些日子已经一去不复返了。$B$B尽管我们摆脱了迪菲亚制造的麻烦，但他们恐怖统治的影响至今犹存。更糟糕的是，我们现在正面临有史以来最严重的经济危机。由于我们将所有的积蓄都拿去对付天灾军团，所以那些不在军中任职的普通百姓全都陷入失业与最终无家可归的境地。$B$B你猜这些人最后怎么办了？' WHERE entry=16260; /* Text0_0: Been in Westfall all my life, $g brother:sister;. I can remember a day when Westfall was the lushest land this side of Stranglethorn Vale. Those days are long gone.$B$BWhile we no longer have Defias causing problems, the fallout from their reign of terror can still be felt. To make matters worse we\'re in the worst economic downturn in history. All that gold we spent on fighting the Scourge left anyone not in a military related occupation jobless and eventually homeless.$B$BGuess where all those people ended up? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='没错，她是这么说的：“只是一次前往废土的简单旅程，毫无压力。”' WHERE entry=16262; /* Text0_0: Oh sure, she said, it\'ll be a simple trip out into the wastes. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='就算是在这儿——在这海浪与暖日的环抱下，我都能感觉到在这些土地上涌动的黑暗力量。$B$B这可真有趣儿，你不觉得吗？' WHERE entry=16264; /* Text0_0: Even here, among the surf and sun, I can feel the darkness that lurks in these lands.$B$BIt\'s fascinating, don\'t you think? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我们自豪地宣称，我们是效忠于部落的森林巨魔最后的部族。$B$B总有一天，我们将战胜其它部族，还有那些矮人，辛特兰将属于我们。' WHERE entry=16265; /* Text0_0: We are proud to call ourselves the last tribe of Forest Trolls to serve the Horde.$B$BIn time, we will overcome the other tribes, and the dwarves, and the Hinterlands will be ours. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='辛萨罗一定属于我们，朋友。邪枝部族只不过是软弱而令人生厌的背叛者，他们不配得到神灵的眷顾。' WHERE entry=16272; /* Text0_0: Jintha\'alor gonna be ours, mon. The vilebranch be weak, nasty traitors, undeservin\' of the favor of the loa. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='去做准备吧，$n，但动作要快！' WHERE entry=16280; /* Text0_0: Make your preparations, $n, but do it quickly! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='别去打扰这年老的龙喉兽人喝酒了，$c。$B$B我曾经对抗过足以把你脊椎扭弯的怪物，在湿地的沼泽和外域的废墟间看着自己的人民惨遭屠戮。$B$B茫然。无措。' WHERE entry=16283; /* Text0_0: Leave this old Dragonmaw to his drink, $c.$B$BI\'ve fought creatures that would curl your spine and I\'ve seen my people all but slaughtered in the swamps of the wetlands and amidst the ruins of Outland.$B$BGet. Lost. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='这是什么，$c？你知道我叫什么？$B$B那你可知道我的名气？$B$B我是龙喉部族的火牙。我曾统领军团，驭龙驰骋，见证过格瑞姆巴托的分崩离析……$B$B该死的暮光之锤，还有他们屁股后面那群食人魔哈巴狗。看看我现在的落魄样。只能絮叨着与廉价的烈酒为伴。' WHERE entry=16284; /* Text0_0: What\'s this, $c? You know my name?$B$BDo you know, then, of my reputation?$B$BI am Flametusk of the Dragonmaw clan. I commanded legions, flew on dragonback, witnessed the sundering of Grim Batol...$B$BCurse the Twilight\'s Hammer, and curse their ogre lapdogs. Look at me now. All talk and cheap liquor. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='这么说来，暮光之锤想要除掉我？恬不知耻的垃圾！$B$B我一定会帮助你的，$c。你说你需要一张地图？' WHERE entry=16285; /* Text0_0: So, Twilight\'s Hammer is trying to finish me off? Honorless filth!$B$BI will definitely help you, $c. You say you need a map? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你怎么还待在这儿，$c？$B$B你不是应该已经抵达暮光高地，让那该死的教派彻底毁灭吗？' WHERE entry=16288; /* Text0_0: What are you still doing here, $c?$B$BShouldn\'t you be in Twilight Highlands laying waste to that wretched cult? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='麦氏移山人有限公司杰萨普·麦格雷，为您效劳。',Text1_0_loc4='要是您想要搬山，找我就对了。我还能为您造座山出来。' WHERE entry=16293; /* Text0_0: Jessup McCree, of McCree\'s Mountain Movers, at your service. */ /* Text1_0: If you need a mountain moved, I can do that. I can make \'em for you, too. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text2_0_loc4='这不是我所干过最重要的工作，连边儿都沾不上。大灾变一定是我们所经历过最棒的事了！' WHERE entry=16293; /* Text2_0: This isn\'t the biggest job I\'ve done, not even close. This cataclysm may just be the best thing that ever happened to us! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='嘿，$c！$B$B有兴趣签几份赚钱的合约吗？我会分给你十分之一！百分之一的十分之一！' WHERE entry=16297; /* Text0_0: Hey, $c!$B$BGot any leads on some lucrative contracts? I\'ll cut you in on one tenth! Of a percent! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='到底是怎么回事，$c？$B$B码头附近有传言说，你最近一直在我的建筑工地附近游荡……' WHERE entry=16298; /* Text0_0: What\'s the deal, $c?$B$BWord on the docks is that you\'ve been poking around my construction sites... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='关于此次攻击没什么混乱的。元素和巨人们有组织地前来对付我们。看来我们在不经意间引起了石母本人——塞拉赞恩的愤怒。' WHERE entry=16303; /* Text0_0: Dere be nothin\' chaotic about dis attack. Da elementals and giants be organizin\' against us. It be seemin\' dat somehow we\'ve earned da ire of Therazane, da Stonemother herself. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='碎轮的失败将向他的主人瑟玛普拉格发出强大的信息。诺莫瑞根的侏儒是不可被阻止的！' WHERE entry=16305; /* Text0_0: Crushcog\'s defeat will send a powerful message to his master, Thermaplugg. The gnomes of Gnomeregan will not be stopped! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你可真勇敢，居然想要逃走，年轻的奥根阿卡。$b$b在你继续之前，让我教你如何用牙齿咬破那些巨魔的网。' WHERE entry=16311; /* Text0_0: You are brave to try to escape, young Ohgan\'aka.$b$bBefore you continue, let me teach you how to use your teeth to bite through the trolls\' nets. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你要离开迅猛龙巢穴了吗？我奉命守卫这岗哨并阻止逃逸，不过……我想我明白你为什么会想要离开。$b$b好吧。你可以通过这里，但首先，我有个要求。$b$b巨魔们经常会携带好多包迅猛龙爱吃的食物，而我已经许多天没进过食了。也许你打架毫无胜算，可你身形小巧，应该能趁那些巨魔熟睡时从帐篷里偷点儿吃的出来……' WHERE entry=16312; /* Text0_0: You are leaving the raptor dens?  I was commanded to guard this post and prevent escapes, but... I think I understand why you want to leave.$b$bFine.  You may pass, but first, I have a request.$b$bThe trolls often carry packs of raptor food, and I haven\'t been fed in days.  You don\'t stand a chance in combat, but you\'re small enough that you might be able to steal it from one of the sleeping trolls inside the tents... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='能走到这一步可真令人印象深刻啊，奥根阿卡。你可真是只天赋异禀的年轻迅猛龙……可最难通过的考验还在后面呢。$b$b巨魔们就在前方的桥附近巡视，他们的注意力很难被分散。可要是你能在他们的必经之路上放块头骨，也许能把他们绊个跟头……' WHERE entry=16313; /* Text0_0: Quite impressive to have made it this far, Ohgan\'aka.  You are truly a talented young raptor... but the toughest test is yet to come.$b$bThe trolls patrol the bridges up ahead, and they will be difficult to distract.  If you drop a skull in their path, however, you may be able to cause them to trip and fall... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你好，朋友！$B$B酋长命我集结他麾下最精锐的部队攻击暮光高地。$B$B你看起来底子不错，$c，可我们需要的士兵得更加……久经沙场一些。也许有一天你和我能并肩作战。在那以前，继续加紧训练吧！' WHERE entry=16319; /* Text0_0: Throm\'ka, friend!$B$BThe Warchief has ordered me to assemble his greatest veterans for an assault on the Twilight Highlands.$B$BYou look like one tough $c, but we need soldiers who are a bit more... battle-hardened. Perhaps someday you and I will fight side-by-side. Until then, continue your training! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你好，朋友！很高兴见到诺森德战役的老战友。$B$B酋长命我集结他麾下最精锐的部队攻击暮光高地。$B$B<酋长把你上下打量了一番。>$B$B我们也许需要你的帮助。去奥格瑞玛的酋长那里，看看他有没有任务交给你。' WHERE entry=16320; /* Text0_0: Throm\'ka, friend! It is good to see a fellow veteran of the Northrend campaign.$B$BThe Warchief has ordered me to assemble his greatest warriors for an assault on the Twilight Highlands.$B$B<Warlord Krogg looks you up and down.>$B$BWe may need your help. Check in with the Warchief in Orgrimmar and see if he has a use for you yet. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='一位士兵在这样的城镇里能惹上许多麻烦。$B$B许多麻烦。' WHERE entry=16321; /* Text0_0: A soldier could get into a lot of trouble in a town like this.$B$BA lot of trouble. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='谢谢你。$b$b作为回报，我会教你如何分散前面那群巨魔的注意力。' WHERE entry=16322; /* Text0_0: Thank you.$b$bIn return, I will teach you how to distract the trolls up ahead. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你想逃走？没问题，可你必须得先了解一些事情。$b$b离那些巨魔远点儿。他们不会杀你，可他们会困住你然后把你带回来。$b$b和你所见到的每只迅猛龙都打个招呼。它们不仅能教你新的技能，还会帮你记住你的进度，让你能更加容易地逃离祖尔格拉布。$b$b你已经学会了急奔技能——用它来脱离险境吧。$b$b喔……还要注意别下水。$b$b祝你好运！' WHERE entry=16324; /* Text0_0: You wish to escape?  That is fine, but you must know some things first.$b$bStay away from the trolls.  They will not kill you, but they will trap you and bring you back here.$b$bSpeak with every raptor you see.  Not only can they teach you new abilities, but they will help you remember your progress and make your path out of Zul\'Gurub much easier.$b$bYou already have a Dash ability - use it to get out of tight spots.$b$bOh... and stay out of the water.$b$bGood luck! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你需要协助吗?' WHERE entry=16330; /* Text0_0: Is there something you need? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='$c，欢迎来到格罗姆高。为了避免今后发生问题，我现在要提醒你，我的营地里可容不下懒人。希望像你这样的健康$r能在这里发挥出应有的作用。' WHERE entry=16334; /* Text0_0: Welcome to Grom\'gol, $c.  Before we get off on the wrong foot, I\'ll have you know that I won\'t have slackers in my Base Camp.  I expect a healthy $r like you to pull your own weight around here. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='即使是在这个世界如此偏远的角落里，都不要忘记地狱咆哮的双目在注视着你。' WHERE entry=16335; /* Text0_0: Even in this remote corner of the world, know that Hellscream\'s eyes are upon you. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='荆棘谷的巨魔对我们暗矛部族并不怎么友好。我不怕那些血顶或劈颅，可是……格罗姆高的高墙令我感到安全。' WHERE entry=16336; /* Text0_0: The trolls of Stranglethorn don\'t take too kindly to us Darkspear.  I\'m not afraid of no Bloodscalp or Skullsplitter, but still... Grom\'gol\'s high walls make me feel safe. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='也许格罗姆高并非像我想的那么安全。$b$b身为巨魔，不论走到哪里，都要随时小心自己的脖颈被偷袭。' WHERE entry=16337; /* Text0_0: Maybe I wasn\'t as safe as I thought I was here in Grom\'gol.$b$bA troll\'s gotta watch his neck wherever he goes. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='<大锅在冒着气泡。>' WHERE entry=16338; /* Text0_0: <The cauldron bubbles.> */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='<巨魔自己唱着歌，眼睛看着锅里。他像是受了伤。>' WHERE entry=16339; /* Text0_0: <The troll sings to himself and stares into the cauldron.  He appears to be injured.> */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='在那片丛林里可藏着许多钱，$r。你看见了吗？$b$b不，这钱的样子跟你平时见到的金币或铜币不同。它的外观是迅猛龙的龙皮，还有矿脉，以及古老的巨魔圣物。$b$b好吧，也许矿脉和金币铜币的样子有点儿像。$b$b不过反正你明白我的意思了，对吧？' WHERE entry=16340; /* Text0_0: There\'s a lot of money out there in that jungle, $r.  Can you see it?$b$bNo, it doesn\'t look like gold or copper.  It looks like raptor hides, and mineral veins, and ancient troll artifacts.$b$bOK, maybe the mineral veins might look like gold or copper.$b$bBut still, you get my point, right? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='伟大的拉斯塔哈为你送来了问候，部落的成员。' WHERE entry=16341; /* Text0_0: The great Rastakhan sends his greetings to you, member of the Horde. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你必须飞往巨石之炉，帮我的人民击败石头穴居人，救出我的父亲。$B$B等我与唤地者谈过之后就会去那里找你。$B$B别让他死了，$n，否则我会亲手把你埋进地里！' WHERE entry=16343; /* Text0_0: You must fly up to Stonehearth, aid my people against the stone troggs, and free my father.$B$BI will meet you there shortly after speaking with the Earthcaller.$B$BDon\'t let him die, $N, or I will put you in the ground myself! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你去过丛林吗，$r？$b$b那可真是个好地方。',Text1_0_loc4='荆棘谷，$g伙计:宝贝儿;。就在那儿！' WHERE entry=16344; /* Text0_0: You ever been to the jungle, $r?$b$bIt\'s real nice. */ /* Text1_0: Stranglethorn, $g man: babe;.  That\'s where it\'s AT! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text2_0_loc4='你好。',Text3_0_loc4='啊，要是再回到荆棘谷。那些发出尖啸的迅猛龙，巨魔间的战争，目力所及处各式各样的丛林生物，就等着人们的捕杀……$b$b<博特叹了口气。>' WHERE entry=16344; /* Text2_0: Hi. */ /* Text3_0: Ah, to be back in Stranglethorn.  The screeching raptors, the troll wars, jungle creatures as far as the eye see, just ASKING to be killed...$b$b<Bort sighs.> */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='难道你又带了一队人来，会吗？我们这儿已经没有人手了。' WHERE entry=16345; /* Text0_0: I don\'t suppose you brought another squad with you, did you? We\'ve got our hands full out here. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='暮光教派中存在着对我们具有严重威胁的法术。$B$B我们恨不得马上让他们滚出我们的家园。$B$B我们被分开了，所以我们不能这么做。$B$B于是我在观望着……$B$B等待着……' WHERE entry=16348; /* Text0_0: Among the Twilight cult are magics that threaten us greatly.$B$BWe have every desire to wipe their existence from our home.$B$BWe are divided, and so we cannot.$B$BAnd so I watch...$B$BAnd wait... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我们必须终结渗入灰谷的堕落之息。' WHERE entry=16363; /* Text0_0: We must put an end to the corruption permeating Ashenvale. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='深岩之洲是个平静而节奏缓慢的地方。永远都充满生机，平稳改变，有条不紊。我一度努力与大地融为一体。在很大的程度上，我成功了。$B$B后来，大地的守卫者回来了，身上带着累累伤痕。起初他并没有扰乱平衡。他曾经在这里生活过，我们了解他。直到暮光教派开始和他打交道以后，他才真正开始发生了变化。' WHERE entry=16365; /* Text0_0: Deepholm was a slow, quiet place. Always alive. Steadily moving. Never rushed. In this time, I strived to become one with the earth, and to a large degree, I succeeded.$B$BLater, the Earthwarder returned, injured. He did not upset the balance at first. He\'d stayed here before, and we knew of him. The shift did not truly begin until the Twilight cult joined him. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='当大地守护者逐渐恢复的时候，他开始不满足于这里的安静与和平。没过多久，他就驱使岩石巨龙攻击我们。$B$B死亡之翼离开之后，它们一直没有明确的目标。我们能够让它们明白我们的力量，再次将它们送回到大地母神的怀抱中。' WHERE entry=16366; /* Text0_0: When the Earthwarder began to recover, he became ill content with the quiet. With the peace. It was not long before he turned the stone dragons upon us.$B$BWith Deathwing gone, they are without purpose again. We can remind them of our strength. Bring them back to the Earthmother. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='$n，要去岸边？$B$B只要你说一声，我就会为你放下一艘小船。' WHERE entry=16372; /* Text0_0: Going ashore, $N?$B$BSay the word and I\'ll lower a boat for you. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='他们怎么敢囚禁我们的国王！$B$B我们要夺回巨石之炉，然后将战线推进到石头穴居人的老窝，在那里彻底粉碎他们！' WHERE entry=16373; /* Text0_0: How dare they take our king prisoner!$B$BWe will take back Stonehearth and then move through the front to crush the stone troggs in their home! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='让我们从这里出去，把那些石头穴居人赶回到地底去，$r！' WHERE entry=16374; /* Text0_0: Let\'s get out there and put those stone troggs back into the ground, $r! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我需要你上阵支援我，$n。$B$B你将使战局产生逆转。我们将一举击溃石头穴居人。$B$B我们必须救出岩幔国王！' WHERE entry=16375; /* Text0_0: I need you out on the front, $N.$B$BYou\'re going to make the difference. We\'ll crush the stone troggs once and for all.$B$BWe must rescue King Oremantle! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='<克莱嘟囔着，冷笑着。>$B$B这个该死的时代。' WHERE entry=16376; /* Text0_0: <Clay grumbles and sneers.>$B$BDamn kids these days. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='等到仪式完成的时候，玛尔纳就会到来。我的人会帮忙塑造出这个奇异的怪物。' WHERE entry=16378; /* Text0_0: By the time the ritual is complete, Marnal will arrive, and my men will help carve up this grotesque creature. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='死亡之翼的侵入在我们的世界和深岩之洲之间打开了一道裂隙。$B$B重建世界之柱是唯一控制住裂隙的方法。' WHERE entry=16383; /* Text0_0: Deathwing\'s entry into our world opened a rift between it and Deepholm.$B$BRebuilding the World Pillar is the only way to stabilize the rift. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='谈判进展得并不顺利，$n。龙喉氏族还不是意志自由的兽人。$B$B不管怎样，我们必须争取他们加入部落！$B$B如果你要返回舰队，就告诉我。' WHERE entry=16384; /* Text0_0: Negotiations aren\'t going well, $N. The Dragonmaw are not yet free orcs.$B$BSomehow, we MUST get them to join the Horde!$B$BLet me know if you need transport back to the fleet. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='去哪里，朋友？',Text0_1_loc4='去哪里，朋友？' WHERE entry=16386; /* Text0_0: Where to, buddy? */ /* Text0_1: Where to, buddy? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我们龙喉氏族经历过太多的磨难……在格瑞姆巴托的失败……那么多强大的战士死在外域……现在，暮光之锤又向我们发动了进攻。$B$B有时我会怀疑，我们是否还能再次强大起来。但像扎伊拉这样的年轻人让我们这些老骨头又有了希望。' WHERE entry=16387; /* Text0_0: We Dragonmaw have seen so much suffering... our defeat at Grim Batol... the loss of so many great warriors in Outland... and now incursions from Twilight\'s Hammer.$B$BI sometimes wonder if we will ever be great again. But younglings like Zaela, they give this old heap of bones some hope. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你需要什么，外乡人？我不应该和你说话的……' WHERE entry=16388; /* Text0_0: What is it you need, outsider? I shouldn\'t be speaking with you... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我可不喜欢坐在这个洞里。真希望我们在等待达纳斯将军回来的时候能好好喝上一杯潘趣酒。' WHERE entry=16390; /* Text0_0: I\'m sick of sittin\' in this hole. I hope whatever sorry pencil-pusher is holdin\' up Danath\'s return gets a punch in the jimmies. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='嗨，这身红褂子就让我看上去是一件可消耗品吗？' WHERE entry=16391; /* Text0_0: Hey, does this red shirt make me look expendable? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='欢迎来到鹰巢山，蛮锤部族的家园。$B$B大领主弗斯塔德·蛮锤已经前往铁炉堡，有事情的话可以和我说。' WHERE entry=16393; /* Text0_0: Welcome to Aerie Peak, home of the Wildhammer Clan.$B$BWith High Thane Falstad off in Ironforge, you\'ll be dealin\' with me. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='这片土地的英灵不会再容忍这种黑暗魔法和邪恶的献祭。$B$B邪枝巨魔必须被赶走！' WHERE entry=16394; /* Text0_0: The spirits o\' this land won\'t tolerate this dark magic and vicious sacrifice any longer.$B$BThe Vilebranch have got to go! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='不要浪费时间了！这里还有许多亡灵呢。' WHERE entry=16399; /* Text0_0: Let\'s not waste time! There\'s undead afoot. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你是否愿意不惜一切代价来挽救你的王国？' WHERE entry=16402; /* Text0_0: Will you do whatever it takes to save your kingdom? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='这么多无谓的损失。' WHERE entry=16412; /* Text0_0: So much senseless loss. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='钓鱼是我家族世代相传的天性。不过你看上去倒像是能帮点儿小忙。替钓鱼者跑跑腿儿怎么样？' WHERE entry=16413; /* Text0_0: Fishing has always come naturally to my family.  You look like you could use a little help though.  How about running a few errands for a Master Angler? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你一杯！我一杯！愿我们默契永相随。$b$b可要是没了默契……那你就去死吧！我再来一杯。' WHERE entry=16418; /* Text0_0: Here\'s to you!  Here\'s to me!  May we never disagree.$b$bBut if we do... BLAST YOU!  Here\'s to me. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='这一定就是海克拜瑞·斯莫特船长提到的那艘救生船。' WHERE entry=16420; /* Text0_0: This must be the lifeboat that Captain Hecklebury Smotts spoke about. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我们来这儿是想要帮忙的，可看来他们对你的好感还没有延及我们。' WHERE entry=16422; /* Text0_0: We\'ve come to try to help, but it seems that their favor for you does not yet extend to us. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我不能和你做交易，$c。这是酋长的命令。',Text0_1_loc4='我不能和你做交易，$c。这是酋长的命令。',Text1_0_loc4='我这儿没什么东西可以卖给你。',Text1_1_loc4='我这儿没什么东西可以卖给你。' WHERE entry=16425; /* Text0_0: I can\'t do business with you, $c. Warchief\'s Orders. */ /* Text0_1: I can\'t do business with you, $c. Warchief\'s Orders. */ /* Text1_0: I have nothing I\'m allowed to sell to you. */ /* Text1_1: I have nothing I\'m allowed to sell to you. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text2_0_loc4='走开，$c！我可不想让执行者看见我在和你做交易……',Text2_1_loc4='走开，$c！我可不想让执行者看见我在和你做交易……',Text3_0_loc4='滚开，我不想让酋长发现我在跟部落的人说话。',Text3_1_loc4='滚开，我不想让酋长发现我在跟部落的人说话。' WHERE entry=16425; /* Text2_0: Get lost, $c! I don\'t want the enforcers to see me doing business with you... */ /* Text2_1: Get lost, $c! I don\'t want the enforcers to see me doing business with you... */ /* Text3_0: Go away, I don\'t want the Warchief to find out I\'ve been talking to the Horde. */ /* Text3_1: Go away, I don\'t want the Warchief to find out I\'ve been talking to the Horde. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text4_0_loc4='我不会把商品卖给部落。你不满意？那去找酋长吧！',Text4_1_loc4='我不会把商品卖给部落。你不满意？那去找酋长吧！',Text5_0_loc4='莫格霍尔酋长不许我们和部落做生意。$B$B<商人暴怒地朝地上吐了口口水，拒绝再对这话题有任何回应。>',Text5_1_loc4='莫格霍尔酋长不许我们和部落做生意。$B$B<商人暴怒地朝地上吐了口口水，拒绝再对这话题有任何回应。>' WHERE entry=16425; /* Text4_0: My goods aren\'t for sale to the Horde. Don\'t like it? Take it up with the Warchief! */ /* Text4_1: My goods aren\'t for sale to the Horde. Don\'t like it? Take it up with the Warchief! */ /* Text5_0: Warchief Mor\'ghor ordered us not to do business with the Horde.$B$B<The merchant spits on the ground, infuriated, but refuses to speak any more on the subject.> */ /* Text5_1: Warchief Mor\'ghor ordered us not to do business with the Horde.$B$B<The merchant spits on the ground, infuriated, but refuses to speak any more on the subject.> */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我帮不了你的忙，$c。要是我敢把我们的双足飞龙借给部落使用，莫格霍尔酋长会把我处死的。$B$B总有一天他会得到他应得的……' WHERE entry=16426; /* Text0_0: I can\'t help you, $c. Warchief Mor\'ghor would have me executed if I allowed the Horde to use one of our wind riders.$B$BSome day he\'ll get what\'s coming to him... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='这地方还不赖，前提是你不过分专注于那“阳光”。' WHERE entry=16427; /* Text0_0: Not a bad place here, if you aren\'t into the whole "sunshine" thing. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='猩猩可真是令人着迷的生物。比暗夜精灵要好多了，那些家伙就只会干蠢事……比如在赌场上输个精光，还害自己登上“海狼”马克基雷的黑名单。' WHERE entry=16429; /* Text0_0: The gorillas are fascinating creatures.  Better than night elves, who do foolish things, like... gambling away all their money and getting put on Sea Wolf MacKinley\'s hit list. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='继续，$r。给我个理由。',Text1_0_loc4='这儿可是莫格霍尔酋长说了算。别忘了这一点。' WHERE entry=16430; /* Text0_0: Go ahead, $r. Give me an excuse. */ /* Text1_0: Warchief Mor\'ghor runs the show here. Don\'t forget it. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text2_0_loc4='<执行者的眼中闪着红光。>$B$B我倒希望你们这些可怜的兽人来攻击我们。我很久没畅快地挥洒热血了，$c！',Text3_0_loc4='那愤怒！那力量！我一生中从未感到如此强壮。$B$B很快，整个龙喉部族都将有同样的感觉。' WHERE entry=16430; /* Text2_0: <The enforcer\'s eyes flash red.>$B$BI hope your pathetic Horde tries to attack us. I am itching to shed some blood, $c! */ /* Text3_0: The fury! The power! I have never felt so strong in all my life.$B$BSoon, ALL the Dragonmaw will feel as I do. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text4_0_loc4='不要自取其辱，$c。$B$B<执行者握住剑柄的手指又紧了紧，就等你先动手了。>',Text5_0_loc4='莫格霍尔酋长将率领龙喉部族再次崛起！$B$B我们用不着你们这群没用的部落。' WHERE entry=16430; /* Text4_0: Don\'t try anything funny, $c.$B$B<The enforcer tenses his fingers near the hilt of his blade, eager for you to make a scene.> */ /* Text5_0: Warchief Mor\'ghor will make the Dragonmaw great again!$B$BWe have no need for your pathetic Horde. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='呀。' WHERE entry=16435; /* Text0_0: Yarr. */
