UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text2_0_loc4='我能帮什么忙吗？' WHERE entry=16558; /* Text2_0: Can I help? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你好啊，$c！奥格瑞玛是世界航运的枢纽。北飞艇塔能把你送往荆棘谷和幽暗城。南飞艇塔会带你去雷霆崖或直达诺森德。$B$B飞行管理员多拉斯会送你畅游卡利姆多各地——至少能把你送到你已经去过的地方。' WHERE entry=16559; /* Text0_0: Hello, $c!$B$BOrgrimmar\'s skyway is the center of the world. The north zeppelin tower will take you to Stranglethorn or Undercity. The south tower wll take you to Thunderbluff or all the way to Northrend.$B$BFlight Master Doras can send you all over Kalimdor - at least, anyplace you\'ve already explored. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='教派？我不知道。不过似乎有些可疑分子在南飞艇塔附近晃来晃去。',Text1_0_loc4='我什么都不知道！去问别人吧。' WHERE entry=16560; /* Text0_0: Cult? I don\'t know. Seen some suspicious types lingering around the south zeppelin tower, though. */ /* Text1_0: I don\'t know nothing! Ask the others. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text2_0_loc4='秘密教派？是不是在南飞艇塔底下集会的那些人？',Text3_0_loc4='秘密教派？有些鬼祟的兽人在南飞艇塔附近游荡，这事儿跟你没关系吧？' WHERE entry=16560; /* Text2_0: Secret cult? Is that who I see having meetings at the base of the south zeppelin tower? */ /* Text3_0: Secret cult? You\'re not with those creepy orcs who lurk around the south zeppelin tower, are you? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text4_0_loc4='我这么蠢，根本加入不了教派。自从我从飞艇的后部摔下来就成这样了。我被螺旋桨打到。然后掉到了一块石头上。他们用一只金属大碗把我的头固定住，以让它变得又圆又硬。$B$B<他用拳头敲了敲自己的头。>$B$B然后闪电就来了。',Text5_0_loc4='南飞艇塔里一直能听到兽人在诡异地窃窃私语。每当我走近，他们就立即不说话了。' WHERE entry=16560; /* Text4_0: I\'m too dumb to be in a cult. Been that way since I felled off the back of the zeppelin. And hit them propellors. Landed on a rock. They fixed my head up with a metal bowl to make it round and hard.$B$B<He thunks his fist against his skull.>$B$BThen the lightning done come. */ /* Text5_0: I hear strange orcs whispering all the time inside the south zeppelin tower. They always shut up whenever I get near. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text6_0_loc4='我不知道。$B$B别打我！' WHERE entry=16560; /* Text6_0: I don\'t know.$B$BDon\'t hit me! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='真是活见麻疯侏儒了！见到你真是太好了。我原本还在担心前面那只熔岩巨虫会把来访者都吓跑了。既然你来了，就来帮我一把。' WHERE entry=16565; /* Text0_0: Leaping Leper Gnomes! You\'re a sight for sore eyes. I was worried the giant magma worm out front would deter visitors. Now that you\'re here you can give me a hand. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我们必须尽快找到世界之柱的中部碎片，返回大地神殿。' WHERE entry=16566; /* Text0_0: You have my undying gratitude and that of my people, $N. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我这里没有你要学的东西。去找$c训练师吧。',Text0_1_loc4='我这里没有你要学的东西。去找$c训练师吧。' WHERE entry=16569; /* Text0_0: I cannot help you with your training. Seek out a $c trainer. */ /* Text0_1: I cannot help you with your training. Seek out a $c trainer. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你是来接受训练的吗，猎人？',Text0_1_loc4='你是来接受训练的吗，猎人？' WHERE entry=16570; /* Text0_0: Are you here to train, hunter? */ /* Text0_1: Are you here to train, hunter? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='Lok\'tar！我们需要你的帮助！' WHERE entry=16571; /* Text0_0: Lok\'tar! We need your help! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='尽量……别丢了……那个。' WHERE entry=16572; /* Text0_0: TRY NOT TO... LOSE... THAT ONE. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你是来这儿学习考古的吗？',Text0_1_loc4='你是来这儿学习考古的吗？' WHERE entry=16573; /* Text0_0: Are you here to train in Archaeology? */ /* Text0_1: Are you here to train in Archaeology? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你得去找别的训练师，$c。我帮不了你。' WHERE entry=16578; /* Text0_0: Ya\'ll need to find a different trainer, $c. I cannot help ya. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='需要接受训练可随时回来找我。' WHERE entry=16579; /* Text0_0: Return any time ya need trainin\'. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='在我的坚守下，佐拉姆加一定会成为御敌入侵的新壁垒。$B$B为了部落的荣耀！' WHERE entry=16580; /* Text0_0: Zoram\'gar will be a new bastion of power against our enemies under my watch.$B$BGlory to the Horde! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我想我真是太好命了，$n。以被遗忘者和皇家药剂师协会成员的身份重回这个世界……我的命可真是好得无可挑剔。' WHERE entry=16583; /* Text0_0: I must have lived a charmed life, $N.  To return to the world as a member of the Forsaken and the Apothecary Society... I couldn\'t have asked for a more suitable fate. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='与外部冲突相比，激怒这里的野猪人太危险了，$r。我的图腾不能永远把他们挡在外面。$B$B我们必须终止他们侵害自然的行为。' WHERE entry=16587; /* Text0_0: The Quilboar here are too dangerous to get riled up over outside conflicts, $r. My totem will not ward them off forever.$B$BWe must put a stop to their transgressions against nature. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='看来你带来了整支舰队啊，$n！还找来一群愤怒的急浪成员！$b$b但愿你已经做好了战斗的准备，因为这些家伙可不是吃素的。' WHERE entry=16588; /* Text0_0: Looks like you brought the whole fleet with you, $N!  And a pack of angry Brashtide to boot!$b$bI hope you\'re battle-ready, because these guys sure came packin\'. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我已经老了！他们人数太多了！$b$b<舰队指挥官卡拉·海角停下来喘了口气。>$b$b我在说什么？他们人数太少了！去死吧，你们这群下贱的杂种！' WHERE entry=16589; /* Text0_0: I\'m getting too old for this!  There\'s too many of them!$b$b<Fleet Master Seahorn pauses to catch his breath.>$b$bWhat am I saying?  There\'s not enough of them!  HAVE AT YOU, YOU MANGY CURS! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='他们在不断地冲过来！把他们击退！我们必须尽力救出更多的吉尔尼斯人！' WHERE entry=16592; /* Text0_0: They keep coming!  Push them back!  We must make sure we save as many Gilneans as possible! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='什么？当然不是！这么简单的装置根本困不住我，可我没时间。看见没，就在不久前我还在一只猛兽的肚子里住了好几个月……' WHERE entry=16593; /* Text0_0: What? Of course not! I could easily escape this simple contraption, but I\'m much too busy. See, a while back I spent a few months inside the belly of a beast... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='这并非出于完全自愿，可我有个令人难以置信的大发现。这野兽看来能消化一切，而且从不会产生不良反应。' WHERE entry=16594; /* Text0_0: It wasn\'t strictly voluntary, but I discovered something truly incredible. The beast seemed to be able to consume almost anything with no ill effects. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='哎呀！那控制杆激活了胆汁喷洒机。喔，要是你刚好能找到一把钥匙的话……' WHERE entry=16597; /* Text0_0: Oops! That lever activates the Bile-O-Tron. Oh, and if you happen to come across a key... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='总共有两个：一个是贸易区的交易者大厅，另一个是矮人区的暴风城拍卖行。',Text0_1_loc4='总共有两个：一个是贸易区的交易者大厅，另一个是矮人区的暴风城拍卖行。' WHERE entry=16601; /* Text0_0: There are two: The Trader\'s Hall in the Trade District, and the Stormwind Auction House in the Dwarven District. */ /* Text0_1: There are two: The Trader\'s Hall in the Trade District, and the Stormwind Auction House in the Dwarven District. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你能在矮人区的最北边，城北降落点的附近找到那间拍卖行。',Text0_1_loc4='你能在矮人区的最北边，城北降落点的附近找到那间拍卖行。' WHERE entry=16602; /* Text0_0: You\'ll find it in the northernmost part of the Dwarven District, near the Northern Landing. */ /* Text0_1: You\'ll find it in the northernmost part of the Dwarven District, near the Northern Landing. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='暴风城共有两个银行——分别是位于贸易区的暴风城会计室和位于矮人区的暴风城皇家银行。',Text0_1_loc4='暴风城共有两个银行——分别是位于贸易区的暴风城会计室和位于矮人区的暴风城皇家银行。' WHERE entry=16603; /* Text0_0: There are two banks in the city: The Stormwind Counting House in the Trade District, and the Royal Bank of Stormwind in the Dwarven District. */ /* Text0_1: There are two banks in the city: The Stormwind Counting House in the Trade District, and the Royal Bank of Stormwind in the Dwarven District. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='暴风城皇家银行位于矮人区最北边的角落里，城北降落点区域内。',Text0_1_loc4='暴风城皇家银行位于矮人区最北边的角落里，城北降落点区域内。' WHERE entry=16604; /* Text0_0: Stormwind\'s Royal Bank is in the northernmost corner of the Dwarven District, just inside the Northern Landing. */ /* Text0_1: Stormwind\'s Royal Bank is in the northernmost corner of the Dwarven District, just inside the Northern Landing. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='暴风城最热门的两个旅馆分别坐落于贸易区与矮人区——镶金玫瑰旅店与黄金酒桶旅店。',Text0_1_loc4='暴风城最热门的两个旅馆分别坐落于贸易区与矮人区——镶金玫瑰旅店与黄金酒桶旅店。' WHERE entry=16605; /* Text0_0: Stormwind\'s two most popular inns are located in the Trade and Dwarven Districts: The Gilded Rose and The Golden Keg. */ /* Text0_1: Stormwind\'s two most popular inns are located in the Trade and Dwarven Districts: The Gilded Rose and The Golden Keg. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='黄金酒桶旅店位于矮人区的北部，就在喷泉旁边。',Text0_1_loc4='黄金酒桶旅店位于矮人区的北部，就在喷泉旁边。' WHERE entry=16606; /* Text0_0: The Golden Keg is in the northen part of the Dwarven District, right by the fountain. */ /* Text0_1: The Golden Keg is in the northen part of the Dwarven District, right by the fountain. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='暴风城有许多特色景点，从矿道地铁到暴风要塞。$B$B你想去哪里呢？',Text0_1_loc4='暴风城有许多特色景点，从矿道地铁到暴风要塞。$B$B你想去哪里呢？' WHERE entry=16607; /* Text0_0: Stormwind has many points of interest, from the Deeprun Tram to Stormwind Keep.$B$BWhat were you looking for? */ /* Text0_1: Stormwind has many points of interest, from the Deeprun Tram to Stormwind Keep.$B$BWhat were you looking for? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='在旧城区与矮人区都能找到兽栏管理员。',Text0_1_loc4='在旧城区与矮人区都能找到兽栏管理员。' WHERE entry=16608; /* Text0_0: There are stable masters in both Old Town and the Dwarven District. */ /* Text0_1: There are stable masters in both Old Town and the Dwarven District. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我们遭到攻击了！' WHERE entry=16612; /* Text0_0: We\'re unda attack! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='纳迦不会就此罢休。我们得集结盟友的力量，把他们彻底击退！' WHERE entry=16613; /* Text0_0: Da naga won\'t be givin\' up. We need to be findin\' our friends and takin\' the fight to dem. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我去找埃鲁纳克……必要的话我只能自己去！' WHERE entry=16614; /* Text0_0: I\'m going in after Erunak... alone if I have to! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='雷塔维在过去的近四十年里一直都是考古界的英雄。要是他还记得它们，哦，他要讲的那些故事……' WHERE entry=16615; /* Text0_0: Remtravel has been a hero to the archaeology world for nearly 40 years. If he could only remember them, oh, the stories he would tell... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='嗯，我想我应该跟他进去。$b$b再没有比在这时候去面对地狱咆哮更坏的事情了……' WHERE entry=16616; /* Text0_0: Well, I suppose I should go in there after him.$b$bCan\'t be any worse than facing Hellscream after this... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='在旧城区指挥部与矮人区里都能找到猎人训练师。',Text0_1_loc4='在旧城区指挥部与矮人区里都能找到猎人训练师。' WHERE entry=16617; /* Text0_0: There are hunters training in Old Town\'s Command Center as well as in the Dwarven District. */ /* Text0_1: There are hunters training in Old Town\'s Command Center as well as in the Dwarven District. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你在旧城区的东门外总能看到几位猎人。',Text0_1_loc4='你在旧城区的东门外总能看到几位猎人。' WHERE entry=16618; /* Text0_0: You can always find a handful of hunters just outside Old Town\'s east gate. */ /* Text0_1: You can always find a handful of hunters just outside Old Town\'s east gate. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='花园……？$B$B已经变成废墟了。你没听说吗？巨龙死亡之翼从暴风城上空掠过，顺便把它给毁了。$B$B老实说，我不懂他为什么没夷平整座城市，但感谢圣光，幸好他没这么干。',Text0_1_loc4='花园……？$B$B已经变成废墟了。你没听说吗？巨龙死亡之翼从暴风城上空掠过，顺便把它给毁了。$B$B老实说，我不懂他为什么没夷平整座城市，但感谢圣光，幸好他没这么干。' WHERE entry=16619; /* Text0_0: The Park...?$B$BIt\'s in ruins. Haven\'t you heard? The great dragon Deathwing soared over Stormwind and destroyed it in passing.$B$BNot sure why he didn\'t level everything, honestly, but we all thank the Light he didn\'t. */ /* Text0_1: The Park...?$B$BIt\'s in ruins. Haven\'t you heard? The great dragon Deathwing soared over Stormwind and destroyed it in passing.$B$BNot sure why he didn\'t level everything, honestly, but we all thank the Light he didn\'t. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='要塞位于暴风城北部。$B$B沿着运河向北前行，你就会看到一座吊桥……通往要塞庭院。',Text0_1_loc4='要塞位于暴风城北部。$B$B沿着运河向北前行，你就会看到一座吊桥……通往要塞庭院。' WHERE entry=16620; /* Text0_0: The keep is in northren Stormwind.$B$BJust follow the canals north and you\'ll eventually come across a drawbridge... that leads into the keep\'s courtyard. */ /* Text0_1: The keep is in northren Stormwind.$B$BJust follow the canals north and you\'ll eventually come across a drawbridge... that leads into the keep\'s courtyard. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='监狱？你干吗要去那儿？就在城中央，法师区的东北部。$B$B你要是真去可一定要小心。听说最近发生了不少暴动事件。',Text0_1_loc4='监狱？你干吗要去那儿？就在城中央，法师区的东北部。$B$B你要是真去可一定要小心。听说最近发生了不少暴动事件。' WHERE entry=16621; /* Text0_0: The prison? Why would you want to go there? It\'s in the center of the city, just northeast of the Mage Quarter.$B$BIf you\'re truly going there, be careful. I\'ve heard news of riots. */ /* Text0_1: The prison? Why would you want to go there? It\'s in the center of the city, just northeast of the Mage Quarter.$B$BIf you\'re truly going there, be careful. I\'ve heard news of riots. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='随着时间的推移，艾泽拉斯的元素变得越发躁动。平息这躁动的关键就在此地——纳格兰。当德拉诺分崩离析之时，所有元素位面都陷入了极大的混乱之中，再也没有恢复平静。这里的裂隙是自然形成的，也彰显着大地所遭受的重创。$B$B在艾泽拉斯看到像这样的崩裂之景并不仅会让人心神不宁，还可能预示着一场前所未见的大毁灭将降临在这个世界上。$B$B$n，把你在外域找到的任何有用信息都带回来给我。$B$B我必须花些时间来解决这里的元素问题，想办法让艾泽拉斯的元素再次平静下来……再晚就来不及了。' WHERE entry=16625; /* Text0_0: The elements in Azeroth are becoming more disturbed each passing day.  The key to this disturbance lies here, in Nagrand.  When Draenor was torn apart, all of the elemental planes were thrown into great turmoil and have never recovered.  The rifts here form naturally and are a sign of a severely damaged world.$B$BTo see this same kind of disruption on Azeroth is not just unnerving, it could be a precursor to a type of destruction the world has never seen before.$B$B$n, bring me any information you may find when walking around Outland.$B$BI must spend time with the elements here, researching a way to calm the elements again in Azeroth...before it\'s too late. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='位于贸易区与运河间的登曼家族珠宝，你在那里应该可以找到所有想要找的东西。',Text0_1_loc4='位于贸易区与运河间的登曼家族珠宝，你在那里应该可以找到所有想要找的东西。' WHERE entry=16627; /* Text0_0: Denman Family Jewelers, between the northern Trade District and The Canals, should have everything you\'re looking for. */ /* Text0_1: Denman Family Jewelers, between the northern Trade District and The Canals, should have everything you\'re looking for. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='除了外出实地考察外，哈里森·琼斯平时都在暴风要塞的皇家图书馆里教授考古学。',Text0_1_loc4='除了外出实地考察外，哈里森·琼斯平时都在暴风要塞的皇家图书馆里教授考古学。' WHERE entry=16628; /* Text0_0: Harrison Jones teaches Archaeology in Stormwind Keep\'s Royal Library when not out in the field. */ /* Text0_1: Harrison Jones teaches Archaeology in Stormwind Keep\'s Royal Library when not out in the field. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='专业技能供应商总是待在对应的专业技能训练师附近。其它商贩则遍布暴风城的各个角落。$B$B你要买什么？',Text0_1_loc4='专业技能供应商总是待在对应的专业技能训练师附近。其它商贩则遍布暴风城的各个角落。$B$B你要买什么？' WHERE entry=16629; /* Text0_0: Profession vendors can always be found near their respective trainers. Other sorts of vendors are scattered throughout Stormwind.$B$BWhat were you looking for? */ /* Text0_1: Profession vendors can always be found near their respective trainers. Other sorts of vendors are scattered throughout Stormwind.$B$BWhat were you looking for? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='勇士大厅位于旧城区的东南端。$B$B荣誉与战利品军需官就在那里。',Text0_1_loc4='勇士大厅位于旧城区的东南端。$B$B荣誉与战利品军需官就在那里。' WHERE entry=16630; /* Text0_0: The Champions\' Hall is located in the southeastern end of Old Town.$B$BThe Honor and Conquest quartermasters can be found there. */ /* Text0_1: The Champions\' Hall is located in the southeastern end of Old Town.$B$BThe Honor and Conquest quartermasters can be found there. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='军需官就在位于旧城区东南门外的指挥部里。',Text0_1_loc4='军需官就在位于旧城区东南门外的指挥部里。' WHERE entry=16631; /* Text0_0: In the Command Center, just outside of Old Town\'s southeast gates, you\'ll find the quartermasters. */ /* Text0_1: In the Command Center, just outside of Old Town\'s southeast gates, you\'ll find the quartermasters. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='马厩就在旧城区东南门边上。你在那里能找到骑术训练师与养马人。',Text0_1_loc4='马厩就在旧城区东南门边上。你在那里能找到骑术训练师与养马人。' WHERE entry=16632; /* Text0_0: There are stables just beyond Old Town\'s southeast gates. You can find a riding trainer and a horse breeder there. */ /* Text0_1: There are stables just beyond Old Town\'s southeast gates. You can find a riding trainer and a horse breeder there. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你知道贸易区那边的狮鹫栖息地吗，就是飞行管理员所在的地方？$B$B有几个蛮锤矮人正在那儿饲养和贩售狮鹫，他们还能教你学会骑乘这种坐骑。',Text0_1_loc4='你知道贸易区那边的狮鹫栖息地吗，就是飞行管理员所在的地方？$B$B有几个蛮锤矮人正在那儿饲养和贩售狮鹫，他们还能教你学会骑乘这种坐骑。' WHERE entry=16634; /* Text0_0: Do you know of the Gryphon Roost off the Trade District, where the Flight Master may be found?$B$BA pair of Wildhammer dwarves raises and sells gryphons there, and can even train you to ride the beasts. */ /* Text0_1: Do you know of the Gryphon Roost off the Trade District, where the Flight Master may be found?$B$BA pair of Wildhammer dwarves raises and sells gryphons there, and can even train you to ride the beasts. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你看上去累极了。出了什么事？',Text0_1_loc4='你看上去累极了。出了什么事？',Text1_0_loc4='很高兴见到你。',Text1_1_loc4='很高兴见到你。' WHERE entry=16635; /* Text0_0: You look exhausted. Is something wrong? */ /* Text0_1: You look exhausted. Is something wrong? */ /* Text1_0: Good to see you. */ /* Text1_1: Good to see you. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text2_0_loc4='有事吗?',Text2_1_loc4='有事吗?',Text3_0_loc4='你取回最后一块了吗？',Text3_1_loc4='你取回最后一块了吗？' WHERE entry=16635; /* Text2_0: Yes? */ /* Text2_1: Yes? */ /* Text3_0: Have you recovered the final piece? */ /* Text3_1: Have you recovered the final piece? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text4_0_loc4='找到塞拉赞恩了吗？',Text4_1_loc4='找到塞拉赞恩了吗？',Text5_0_loc4='你看上去很不安。有什么需要我帮忙的吗？',Text5_1_loc4='你看上去很不安。有什么需要我帮忙的吗？' WHERE entry=16635; /* Text4_0: Any luck with Therazane? */ /* Text4_1: Any luck with Therazane? */ /* Text5_0: You look intent. Is there something I can help with? */ /* Text5_1: You look intent. Is there something I can help with? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text6_0_loc4='需要我帮忙吗？',Text6_1_loc4='需要我帮忙吗？',Text7_0_loc4='我想我恐怕得稍微休息一会儿。我可真没用。',Text7_1_loc4='我想我恐怕得稍微休息一会儿。我可真没用。' WHERE entry=16635; /* Text6_0: Am I needed? */ /* Text6_1: Am I needed? */ /* Text7_0: And I thought I might get a bit of rest. Silly me. */ /* Text7_1: And I thought I might get a bit of rest. Silly me. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='暮光之锤已经渗入了我的城市。如果没人去制止他们，城市就将彻底覆灭。在围剿他们位于高地的据点前，我必须确认暴风城不会成为他们阴谋的牺牲品。$B$B我需要在城里安插更多脚踏实地、忠心不二的耳目。像你这样经验丰富的$c，作用是无可估量的。你准备好帮助暴风城了吗？' WHERE entry=16638; /* Text0_0: Twilight\'s Hammer has infiltrated my city. Left unchecked, they\'ll rot it to the core. Before we besiege their stronghold in the Highlands, I must be certain that Stormwind is safe from their machinations.$B$BI need more feet on the ground, reliable eyes and ears throughout the city. An experienced $c like yourself would be invaluable.$B$BAre you prepared to help Stormwind\'s cause? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='欢迎来到暴风城，$c。' WHERE entry=16641; /* Text0_0: Welcome to Stormwind, $c. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='<安度因上下打量了你>$B$B$n，对吧？你的一些英勇事迹已经被广为传诵。$B$B在诺森德奋战的感觉还好吗？你见到世界之树了吗？那些关于瓦丝琪尔的传闻是真的吗？我有太多问题要问了！' WHERE entry=16642; /* Text0_0: <Anduin sizes you up.>$B$B$N, is it? A few of your triumphs have been the talk of the court.$B$BWhat was it like to serve in Northrend? Have you seen the World Tree? Are the stories about Vashj\'ir true? I have so many questions! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我相信你和我儿子相处得不错？安度因唯一不具备的特质就是内向。' WHERE entry=16651; /* Text0_0: I trust you and my son are getting along? Anduin is anything but shy. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='等守住了暴风城，就该轮到我们把战火烧到暮光高地了！' WHERE entry=16653; /* Text0_0: When Stormwind is secure, we will take this fight to the Highlands. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='血色十字军将荣返故里！' WHERE entry=16663; /* Text0_0: The Scarlet Crusade will return to its noble roots! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='也许我可爱的同伴已经告诉你了，我们正在追寻某样神秘而强大的物品。现在所有的线索都指向真主之门。$B$B不幸的是，那些叫做暮光之锤的狂热邪教徒却阻止我们搜寻那片区域。我相信像你这样声名远播的$c一定能帮神圣遗物学会解决这个小问题吧？' WHERE entry=16673; /* Text0_0: As my lovely companion may have already enlightened you, we are in pursuit of something mysterious and powerful. All of our clues point to the Masters\' Gate.$B$BUnfortunately, the nihilistic cultists known as the Twilight\'s Hammer have prevented our attempts to research the area. Surely a $c with your reputation can assist the Reliquary in its time of need? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你来了，$n！我还以为你已经忘了我了。' WHERE entry=16682; /* Text0_0: There you are, $N! I thought you\'d forgotten about me. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你想要什么？你没看到我还有蝙蝠粪便要清理吗？' WHERE entry=16683; /* Text0_0: What do you want? Can\'t you see I have bat droppings to clean up? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='巫妖王既死，我所拥有的就只剩下责任。没有家人，没有朋友……只有这个。$b$b战争。' WHERE entry=16687; /* Text0_0: With the death of the Lich King, all I have left is my duty.  There is no family, there are no friends... there is only this.$b$bWar. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='更多加兹瑞迪安？你为什么觉得我还愿意要更多这玩意？我已经积压了九千个了，一个都卖不出去！我竟然以为有人会对这种超大块头的毒蛇雕像感兴趣！啊呸！',Text1_0_loc4='我看见废土强盗和他们的领袖——卡利夫·斯科比斯汀往南边去了。多加小心，他们看起来更强大了！' WHERE entry=16688; /* Text0_0: MORE Ghaz\'ridian?  Why would you think I would want any MORE of those infernal things?  I\'m stuck with about nine thousand, and they\'re not selling!  Why did I ever think anyone would want a statue of an overgrown snake?  Pah! */ /* Text1_0: I saw the Wastewander and their leader, Caliph Scorpidsting, heading south of here.  Watch out, they look like they\'ve toughened up some! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text2_0_loc4='我见到一只你前所未见的大虫子，就在那其中一个——要不就是两个异种蝎虫巢附近徘徊。我想我快要中暑了……你看见那边那只沙猫没？',Text3_0_loc4='我对龙没什么研究，可有一天，突然有一只又大又可怕的龙出现在那边——就在时光之穴入口附近。他不停的叫嚷着……说什么来着……我们所知的时间尽头？我还真没怎么注意听。' WHERE entry=16688; /* Text2_0: I saw the biggest bug you\'ve ever seen wandering around one of those Silithid hives.  Or maybe it was both of them.  I think the heat\'s getting to me...do you see that sand kitten over there? */ /* Text3_0: I don\'t know much about dragons, but a big, scary one showed up one day just over yonder, near the entrance to the Caverns of Time.  He kept yelling something about...what was it...the end of time as we know it?  I wasn\'t really paying much attention. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text4_0_loc4='我一位名叫Frokle的老友原本是要前往加基森，可他和船上的所有锈水船员却从来都没有抵达。我听说在遥远的南边，有一伙疯狂的地精潜伏在一架被击落的飞行器附近，会不会是……？',Text5_0_loc4='我在沙丘那边分析森提帕尔异种蝎小吃（专利申请中）的潜在利润时，发现了一辆破旧的货车。于是我想，“嘿，免费货车哎！”后来就出现了那只你前所未见的大蜥蜴，害得我只能空手而逃！' WHERE entry=16688; /* Text4_0: An old friend of mine named Frokle was supposed to be heading in to Gadgetzan, but him and the rest of the Bilgewater crew manning the ship never arrived.  I\'ve heard rumors of a crazy goblin that hangs out near a downed flying machine in the far south, could it be...? */ /* Text5_0: I found a broken-down cart amongst the dunes when I was checking out the potential profitibility of Centipaar Silithid Snacks (patent pending).  I thought to myself, "hey, free cart!"  That is, until the biggest basilisk you\'ve ever seen showed up, and I had to leave the whole thing behind! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text6_0_loc4='你见过那些会在沙丘地下窜来窜去的大土堆吗？它们是隧道虫的一种，艾泽拉斯大陆上可从来没出现过这玩意儿！要是能和它们斗上一场，对向你这样经验丰富的冒险家来说，一定是次难得的学习机会。',Text7_0_loc4='大灾变发生时，艾泽拉斯元素间的连结大大弱化了。其中一个元素——亚奎门塔斯，获得了自由。我听说他正在给南海海盗制造不小的麻烦！' WHERE entry=16688; /* Text6_0: Have you seen those huge dirt mounds moving around beneath the dunes?  They belong to a species of tunneling worm the likes of which Azeroth has never seen!  I\'m sure that battling one would be a great learning experience for a seasoned adventurer such as yourself. */ /* Text7_0: When the Cataclysm happened, the links bounding elementals across Azeroth weakened significantly.  One such elemental, Aquementas, is no longer imprisoned.  I hear he\'s causing some major problems for the Southsea gang! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='<厕所里一片死寂。>' WHERE entry=16689; /* Text0_0: <The outhouse is silent.> */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='嘿老兄！你是来帮赞吉吉出去的吗？' WHERE entry=16694; /* Text0_0: \'Ey, mon!  You come to help Zen\'Kiki out? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我能指导你锻造的技巧，并向你提供必要的工具。$B$B需要我帮忙吗？',Text0_1_loc4='我能指导你锻造的技巧，并向你提供必要的工具。$B$B需要我帮忙吗？' WHERE entry=16705; /* Text0_0: I can instruct you in blacksmithing as well as supply the necessary tools.$B$BHow may I help you? */ /* Text0_1: I can instruct you in blacksmithing as well as supply the necessary tools.$B$BHow may I help you? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我能指导你草药学的技巧，并向你提供各种有用的物资。$B$B需要我的帮助吗？',Text0_1_loc4='我能指导你草药学的技巧，并向你提供各种有用的物资。$B$B需要我的帮助吗？' WHERE entry=16706; /* Text0_0: I can instruct you in herbalism as well as offer helpful supplies.$B$BHow may I help you? */ /* Text0_1: I can instruct you in herbalism as well as offer helpful supplies.$B$BHow may I help you? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='感谢你帮助我，朋友！我已经不想再变形了……现在我要努力提高我的治疗术水平！' WHERE entry=16711; /* Text0_0: Thanks for helpin\' me out, mon!  No more shapeshifts for me... I\'m gonna work on my healing! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你好，年轻人，真高兴能再见到一个高贵的灵魂。$B$B埃德萨拉已经彻底堕落，成为了今日的厄运之槌。我亲眼看着我的同胞们败倒在黑暗和混乱力量的脚下。可能许多人都认为，只有把这里彻底夷为平地，才能永远结束盘踞在这里的恐怖。$B$B但厄运之槌还是值得拯救的，凡人。帮帮我，也许我们的共同努力能够重新唤醒这里巨大的善良力量，让久远以前的美好时代重新回来。' WHERE entry=16712; /* Text0_0: Greetings, young one, it is good to see a noble soul again.$B$BDire Maul, formerly Eldre\'thalas, is corrupt to its very core. I have watched my brethren fall to the forces of darkness and chaos. Many would have this place razed to the ground to end its horrors forever.$B$BBut Dire Maul is worth saving, mortal. Help me, and perhaps together we can unleash the vast power lost here for the forces of good, as they once were so long ago. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='大地之子，需要我的帮助吗？',Text0_1_loc4='大地之子，需要我的帮助吗？' WHERE entry=16714; /* Text0_0: How may I be helpin\' ya, Child of de Earth? */ /* Text0_1: How may I be helpin\' ya, Child of de Earth? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='丛林中暗影重重，但它的土地肥沃丰茂。$B$B愿大地之灵眷顾你，$c。',Text0_1_loc4='丛林中暗影重重，但它的土地肥沃丰茂。$B$B愿大地之灵眷顾你，$c。' WHERE entry=16715; /* Text0_0: Dark is de jungle, but fertile is its soil.$B$BMay de spirits of de earth watch over ya, $c. */ /* Text0_1: Dark is de jungle, but fertile is its soil.$B$BMay de spirits of de earth watch over ya, $c. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='戈多克们不喜欢达戈索尔，所以他杀了他们。那些愚蠢的树和山羊人也不喜欢达戈索尔，所以他也想杀光他们。$B$B小$r喜欢达戈索尔吗？是不是愿意帮助他征服这个地方？还是达戈索尔也要杀掉你？$B$B愚蠢的树一直在盯着大使达戈索尔……' WHERE entry=16716; /* Text0_0: Da Gordok no like Dagg\'thol, so he kill them. Da stupid trees and goat men no like Dagg\'thol, so he want kill them too.$B$BPuny $r like Dagg\'thol and help him take dis place for Master? Or does Dagg\'thol need kill you too?$B$BStupid tree keep staring at Ambassador Dagg\'thol... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我已经彻底弹尽粮绝了，而道路又遭到了兽人的封锁，我的运气可真好啊！' WHERE entry=16717; /* Text0_0: I\'m completely out of supplies and the road is blocked by orcs, just my luck! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='<少校略点了一下头。>' WHERE entry=16719; /* Text0_0: <The Major nods curtly.> */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='$n，这么快就回来了？有没有从码头工人那里得到什么消息？' WHERE entry=16720; /* Text0_0: Back so soon, $N? Did you learn anything from the dockworkers? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='现在我唯一关心的就是修复埃德萨拉。在这座城市平安无事之前，其它所有事情，战争、冲突、忠诚，对我都没有意义。' WHERE entry=16726; /* Text0_0: I care far too deeply about redeeming Eldre\'thalas to deal with any other matter. War, strife, allegiances, none of it matters until this city is safe. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='愿光明拥抱你。' WHERE entry=16727; /* Text0_0: May the light embrace you. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='接管铁炉堡的时候，我也在场——那时真是一片混乱。$B$B所以当我离开城堡的时候，父亲会采取这样的保护措施也就不奇怪了。' WHERE entry=16729; /* Text0_0: I was in Ironforge during the takeover - it was chaos.$B$BNo wonder father gets so protective when I leave the keep. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我们要离开这里！' WHERE entry=16730; /* Text0_0: We\'ve got to get out of here! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='那是什么东西？' WHERE entry=16731; /* Text0_0: What WAS that thing? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='嗯？' WHERE entry=16732; /* Text0_0: Hm? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你怎么能活着走到这里？你一定就是那个来对抗厄运之槌的英雄。' WHERE entry=16733; /* Text0_0: How did you manage to get here on foot alive? You must be quite the hero to brave Dire Maul. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='进来，朋友……暂时把你的担忧放到一边去吧！$B$B让自己的灵魂和躯体都好好休息一下。',Text0_1_loc4='进来，朋友……暂时把你的担忧放到一边去吧！$B$B让自己的灵魂和躯体都好好休息一下。' WHERE entry=16734; /* Text0_0: Come in, mon... forget yer cares for a while!$B$BRest de body, rest de soul. */ /* Text0_1: Come in, mon... forget yer cares for a while!$B$BRest de body, rest de soul. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你已经证明了自己的实力和才智。我相信你将成为打败旋岩虫的英雄。那是我们无法完成的任务。你要深入碎岩之渊，那里是我们唯一无法通过的地方。' WHERE entry=16737; /* Text0_0: You have proven capable. Resourceful. I think you will be the one to take the fight to the gyreworms where we cannot. You will be the one to make your way deep into the Crumbling Depths, the only place where we cannot pass. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='维尔顿只不过是个该死的懦夫。他刚刚逃得一条活命，现在却装成一副英雄的样子跑到这里来了？$B$B呸！' WHERE entry=16742; /* Text0_0: Weldon is nothing more than a damned coward. He fled from the scourge and now dares to come here as if he were some sort of hero?$B$BBah! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='不要听阿莱克斯瞎说。瘟疫袭来的时候他却不知道逃走，那只能说明他的愚蠢。看看他现在的样子——和这里的其他憎恶没有两样。$B$B别担心，我们会夺回通灵学院和它周围的土地。把它们交给巴罗夫最后一个活着的儿子。他才是这里的合法继承人。' WHERE entry=16743; /* Text0_0: Don\'t listen to anything Alexi says. He was a fool to stay during the plague and now look at him - he\'s no better than the other abominations in this place.$B$BDon\'t fret, we will reclaim Scholomance and the surrounding lands for the last living son of Barov - the rightful heir. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你不会是又想偷我的炸药吧，是吗？',Text1_0_loc4='看看这地方！$b$b这是考古学家的梦想……' WHERE entry=16744; /* Text0_0: You\'re not thinkin\' about stealing my explosives again, are ya? */ /* Text1_0: Just look at this place!$b$bIt\'s an archaeologist\'s dream... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text2_0_loc4='这次可不要偷走我的炸药了，好吗？' WHERE entry=16744; /* Text2_0: How about you don\'t go runnin\' off with my explosives this time, okay? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='看看这地方！$b$b这是考古学家的梦想……' WHERE entry=16745; /* Text0_0: Just look at this place!$b$bIt\'s an archaeologist\'s dream... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='他们会吸干洛克湖，直到那里只剩下一点泥巴，但我们还是要英勇奋战以保卫它。' WHERE entry=16748; /* Text0_0: They can drain the Loch until it\'s little more than a drip of mud, and we\'ll still fight to keep it ours. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我能告诉你的秘密会让你的灵魂四分五裂，$c。$B$B相信我：你应该去别人那里接受训练。',Text0_1_loc4='我能告诉你的秘密会让你的灵魂四分五裂，$c。$B$B相信我：你应该去别人那里接受训练。' WHERE entry=16749; /* Text0_0: De secrets I have ta share would blast your soul apart, $c.$B$BTrust me: You be wantin\' ta talk ta someone else about trainin\'. */ /* Text0_1: De secrets I have ta share would blast your soul apart, $c.$B$BTrust me: You be wantin\' ta talk ta someone else about trainin\'. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='有多少人知道，外界的黑暗中到底隐藏着怎样的恐怖……那是能够让灵魂发疯的诡谲之物！$B$B我们一直都很清楚这一点。而你也想来此一探究竟，对么？',Text0_1_loc4='有多少人知道，外界的黑暗中到底隐藏着怎样的恐怖……那是能够让灵魂发疯的诡谲之物！$B$B我们一直都很清楚这一点。而你也想来此一探究竟，对么？' WHERE entry=16750; /* Text0_0: Who knows what dark an\' horrid tings be gibberin\' in de outer darkness... tings dat\'d drive a soul mad ta see?$B$B-We- be knowin\'. An\' you\'ve come lookin\' ta know -more,- haven\'t ya? */ /* Text0_1: Who knows what dark an\' horrid tings be gibberin\' in de outer darkness... tings dat\'d drive a soul mad ta see?$B$B-We- be knowin\'. An\' you\'ve come lookin\' ta know -more,- haven\'t ya? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你好，$n。你想要学习隐秘的艺术吗？',Text0_1_loc4='你好，$n。你想要学习隐秘的艺术吗？' WHERE entry=16751; /* Text0_0: Greetin\'s, $N.  Are ya here ta be learnin\' of de Hidden Arts? */ /* Text0_1: Greetin\'s, $N.  Are ya here ta be learnin\' of de Hidden Arts? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你好，$g勇敢的:美丽的;$c。我能为你做些什么？' WHERE entry=16754; /* Text0_0: Good day, $g brave: fair; $c.  How can I be of service? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='嗯，让我想想……我看见几个苦工从那边的矿井里跑出去了。嘴里念叨着蜘蛛还是什么的。新客户？嗯，有位年轻可爱的侏儒小姐，名叫杰拉莉，她上星期买了把比她大一倍的斧子。喔，魔导师毕斯普来咨询过护甲。不知道他要板甲做什么……' WHERE entry=16755; /* Text0_0: Well, let\'s see... I saw some drudges running away from that mine over there.  Said something about a spider.  New customers?  Well, there\'s Jeralee, the lovely young gnome, who bought an axe twice her size last week.  Oh, and Magus Bisp came by asking for armor.  Not sure why he\'d need plate armor... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我能帮你吗?' WHERE entry=16756; /* Text0_0: Can I help you? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='这算什么，审问吗？你不是弗丁的内部事务处理人员吧？$b$b嗯，反正我也没什么可隐瞒的。让我翻翻我的记录。上星期米纳尔中尉从我这儿买了件舞会礼服，这让我感到有些奇怪。还有……魔导师毕斯普买了几件皮上衣，也没说出什么原因。喔，弗拉尔·伯林汉姆来为他的硬钳避世乐园之旅订购泳衣。就这些。$b$b要是你不介意的话，我得招呼客人了！' WHERE entry=16757; /* Text0_0: What is this, an interrogation?  You\'re not one of Fordring\'s internal affairs guys, are you?$b$bWell, I\'ve got nothing to hide.  Let me look over my records.  Last week I sold a ball gown to Lieutenant Myner, which struck me as odd.  What else... Magus Bisp bought several dozen leather jerkins, which he couldn\'t give a reason for.  Oh, and Friar Burlingham came by to stock up on swimwear for his trip to Hardwrench Hideaway.  That\'s about it.$b$bNow if you don\'t mind, I have customers! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='愿光明眷顾你，孩子。在这样美好的日子里，我能为你做些什么？' WHERE entry=16760; /* Text0_0: May the Light watch over you, child.  And how may I help you this fine day? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='被盗的补给品？嗯，让我想想……$b$b我知道有个叫达莉亚的祭司，在上星期活动结束后把剩下的酒都拿走了，并没有照我说的放回来。不过我相信她很快就会前来为此道歉的。$b$b<阿尔法斯朝你眨了眨眼。>$b$b我还听到那个法师……叫什么来着……克里斯普？还是利斯普？差不多就是这名字吧。他这礼拜一反常态地做了不少次忏悔。$b$b好了，快走开吧。' WHERE entry=16761; /* Text0_0: Stolen supplies?  Well, let me think about it...$b$bI know a certain priest named Daria who took all the extra wine after last week\'s service, but didn\'t throw it out as I asked.  I believe she\'ll be apologizing soon, though.$b$b<Alphus winks at you.>$b$bI\'ve also heard an abnormal number of confessions this week from one of the mages... what was his name?  Crisp?  Lisp?  Something along those lines.$b$bNow, be on your way. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你……你在这里做什么，$r？难道你看不出，你已经干扰了银色北伐军的官方行动？！' WHERE entry=16762; /* Text0_0: W-what are you doing up here, $r?  Can\'t you see you\'re interfering with OFFICIAL ARGENT CRUSADE BUSINESS!? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='<哼哼>$b$b你需要些什么，$r？',Text0_1_loc4='<哼哼>$b$b你需要些什么，$r？',Text1_0_loc4='怎么了？我现在有些忙。',Text1_1_loc4='怎么了？我现在有些忙。' WHERE entry=16763; /* Text0_0: <Grunt>$b$bYou need something, $r? */ /* Text0_1: <Grunt>$b$bYou need something, $r? */ /* Text1_0: What is it?  I\'m a little busy here. */ /* Text1_1: What is it?  I\'m a little busy here. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text2_0_loc4='我正在接受训练。可以等一会儿吗？',Text2_1_loc4='我正在接受训练。可以等一会儿吗？',Text3_0_loc4='有事吗?',Text3_1_loc4='有事吗?' WHERE entry=16763; /* Text2_0: I\'m training right now.  Can this wait? */ /* Text2_1: I\'m training right now.  Can this wait? */ /* Text3_0: Yes? */ /* Text3_1: Yes? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='在我们与部落交战之后，我们的舰队在进入港口的时候还保持了大致完整的规模。我们在滩头堡的阴影中起锚，重新集结。$B$B就在此时，纳迦出现了。$B$B无数只覆盖着闪光鳞片的手攀住锚链……将人们拖入水中，让他们尖叫着沉入深渊……$B$B这是被诅咒的海岸，$n。被诅咒了。' WHERE entry=16766; /* Text0_0: The fleet was mostly intact as it limped into harbor after our engagement with the Horde. We weighed anchor in the shadow of Highbank here to regroup.$B$BThen the naga came.$B$BScaly, glistening hands clambering up the anchor chains... dragging men, screaming, into the depths...$B$BThese are cursed shores, $N. Cursed. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='消灭他们，$c！摧毁尽可能多的纳迦，为逝去者报仇。' WHERE entry=16767; /* Text0_0: Slaughter them, $c! Destroy as many naga as you can to honor those that fell. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我们不能失败，$n。许多个世界的未来都将由这场战斗而决定。' WHERE entry=16768; /* Text0_0: We cannot fail, $N.  The future of multiple worlds is at stake here. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='在死亡之后，我还能帮你些什么？',Text0_1_loc4='在死亡之后，我还能帮你些什么？' WHERE entry=16771; /* Text0_0: How may I assist you in the afterlife? */ /* Text0_1: How may I assist you in the afterlife? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='在死亡之后，我还能帮你些什么？',Text0_1_loc4='在死亡之后，我还能帮你些什么？' WHERE entry=16772; /* Text0_0: How may I assist you in the afterlife? */ /* Text0_1: How may I assist you in the afterlife? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='看起来，这只箱子的功用应该是储存武器和盔甲。' WHERE entry=16774; /* Text0_0: This crate looks like it was used to store weapons and armor. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你以为我对付不了他们？不要因为我矮就瞧不起我。不管怎样，还是要感谢你的帮忙。' WHERE entry=16776; /* Text0_0: Thought I couldn\'t handle them? Don\'t let my size be follin\' ya. Anyway, thanks for the hand. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='戴上这副面具，我什么都看不见。但我可不会告诉她这个。' WHERE entry=16778; /* Text0_0: I can\'t see a thing with this mask on, but I\'m not about to tell HER that. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='武器……盔甲……这些都是取得胜利的关键。任何一名战士，无论他是多么强壮，都很难周全地保护自己。$B$B$r，我曾经打造过许多传奇的武器和护甲，你在全艾泽拉斯也无法找到能和它们比拟的杰出作品。它们正是我的同胞赢取胜利的关键。' WHERE entry=16779; /* Text0_0: Weapons...armor...these are the keys to victory. Any warrior, no matter how strong, is essentially defenseless without them.$B$BI have crafted many a legend in my day, $r. You will find nothing like them in all of Azeroth. They are the key to my brethren\'s success. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='血肚一直想当个农夫。',Text1_0_loc4='血肚站在太阳底下真高兴。' WHERE entry=16780; /* Text0_0: Gory always wanted to be a farmer. */ /* Text1_0: Gory just happy to be in the sun. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text2_0_loc4='血肚想帮忙干农活。血肚已经准备好镰刀了！',Text3_0_loc4='血肚不太擅长耕种，可血肚超级擅长收割。' WHERE entry=16780; /* Text2_0: Gory wants to help out on farm.  Gory already has his own scythe! */ /* Text3_0: Gory not very good at planting, but Gory VERY good at reaping. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我一直都在打算调查这个地方。$b$b而现在这种情形还从没有发生过！' WHERE entry=16786; /* Text0_0: I\'ve been meaning to investigate this site.$b$bNo time like the present! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我听说过许多关于你的事情，$n。这个世界比以往更加需要像你这样的人。' WHERE entry=16787; /* Text0_0: I\'ve heard much about you, $N.  The world needs people like you now more than ever. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='嗨，朋友。$B$B你需要找回一个丢失的同伴吗？',Text0_1_loc4='嗨，朋友。$B$B你需要找回一个丢失的同伴吗？' WHERE entry=16789; /* Text0_0: Hey der, mon.$B$BDid ya need help recoverin\' a lost companion? */ /* Text0_1: Hey der, mon.$B$BDid ya need help recoverin\' a lost companion? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='抱歉，$c。$B$B我不认为你有能力掌握传送门魔法的真髓。',Text0_1_loc4='抱歉，$c。$B$B我不认为你有能力掌握传送门魔法的真髓。' WHERE entry=16790; /* Text0_0: Sorry, $c.$B$BI ain\'t believin\' ya got de right mind for graspin\' de nature of portal magic. */ /* Text0_1: Sorry, $c.$B$BI ain\'t believin\' ya got de right mind for graspin\' de nature of portal magic. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='拍卖行和银行就位于山谷中部那高耸入云的建筑顶部，伙计。$B$B去找泽基和Makavu吧。',Text0_1_loc4='拍卖行和银行就位于山谷中部那高耸入云的建筑顶部，伙计。$B$B去找泽基和Makavu吧。' WHERE entry=16792; /* Text0_0: De auction house and bank be at de top of de tall building in de middle of de valley, mon.$B$BLook for Ziji and Makavu. */ /* Text0_1: De auction house and bank be at de top of de tall building in de middle of de valley, mon.$B$BLook for Ziji and Makavu. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你得去找斯加姆比，伙计。$B$B她就在山谷中部那座高高的建筑里。',Text0_1_loc4='你得去找斯加姆比，伙计。$B$B她就在山谷中部那座高高的建筑里。' WHERE entry=16793; /* Text0_0: You be wantin\' Sijambi, mon.$B$BShe be in de tall building in de middle of de valley. */ /* Text0_1: You be wantin\' Sijambi, mon.$B$BShe be in de tall building in de middle of de valley. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='就在这座山谷的旅店外面，朋友。$B$B就是山谷中部的那座高大的建筑物。',Text0_1_loc4='就在这座山谷的旅店外面，朋友。$B$B就是山谷中部的那座高大的建筑物。' WHERE entry=16794; /* Text0_0: Right outside de valley\'s inn, mon.$B$BIt be de tall building in de middle. */ /* Text0_1: Right outside de valley\'s inn, mon.$B$BIt be de tall building in de middle. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你在找什么？',Text0_1_loc4='你在找什么？' WHERE entry=16795; /* Text0_0: Which ya be lookin\' for? */ /* Text0_1: Which ya be lookin\' for? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='比起其它任何组织，圣光兄弟会更有能力铲除敢于冒犯圣光的人。我们会采取一切必要手段，将亡灵那样的邪恶怪物从这个世界上彻底清除掉。没有任何人能阻挡我们。$B$B你要加入我们？还是和我们作对？' WHERE entry=16796; /* Text0_0: The Brotherhood of the Light transcends the ability of any other group to eradicate affronts to the Light. We will take any actions necessary to rid the world of foul beasts like these undead. Nothing will stand in our way.$B$BAre you with us, or against us? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你要找的人是塞瑟比，伙计。$B$B她通常在老渔夫——恩姆贝托旁边的树下打盹儿，看上去就像只大老虎。',Text0_1_loc4='你要找的人是塞瑟比，伙计。$B$B她通常在老渔夫——恩姆贝托旁边的树下打盹儿，看上去就像只大老虎。' WHERE entry=16798; /* Text0_0: You be lookin\' for Sesebi, mon.$B$BShe most often be sleepin\' under de tree by old Umbehto, de fisherman, lookin\' like a big ol\' tiger. */ /* Text0_1: You be lookin\' for Sesebi, mon.$B$BShe most often be sleepin\' under de tree by old Umbehto, de fisherman, lookin\' like a big ol\' tiger. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='库扎莉和曾迦是一流的训练大师，他们就在山谷东南端的一座小岛上，伙计。',Text0_1_loc4='库扎莉和曾迦是一流的训练大师，他们就在山谷东南端的一座小岛上，伙计。' WHERE entry=16799; /* Text0_0: Kuzari and Zanga are trainin\' headhunters on one of de small islets towards de southeast end of de valley, mon. */ /* Text0_1: Kuzari and Zanga are trainin\' headhunters on one of de small islets towards de southeast end of de valley, mon. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='他们就在这座山谷东南尽头那座高大的建筑物顶上。',Text0_1_loc4='他们就在这座山谷东南尽头那座高大的建筑物顶上。' WHERE entry=16800; /* Text0_0: Dey be on top of de tall building in de southeast end of de valley. */ /* Text0_1: Dey be on top of de tall building in de southeast end of de valley. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='这里没有激动，这里没有道统，这里没有狂热。$B$B凝聚在这里的只有兄弟间生死与共的誓言。$B$B乌瑟尔·光明使者就是在这座礼拜堂中加入了白银之手骑士团。而我，科尔法克斯，圣光之勇士，将在此地让无畏者感到恐惧。$B$B没有任何力量能抑制我的愤怒——血色十字不行，银色黎明不行，我的兄弟们不行，你同样不行。' WHERE entry=16801; /* Text0_0: There are no emotions. There are no morals. There are no zealots.$B$BThere is only the Brotherhood.$B$BHere, in the very chapel where Uther the Lightbringer joined the Order of the Silver Hand, I, Korfax, Champion of the Light, will inspire fear into the fearless.$B$BNothing will curb my fury - not the Scarlet Crusade, not the Argent Dawn, not my brothers, not even you. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='暗影行者祖鲁能够帮助你。$B$B你可以在东南方那座更高的建筑物最下面的一层中找到他。',Text0_1_loc4='暗影行者祖鲁能够帮助你。$B$B你可以在东南方那座更高的建筑物最下面的一层中找到他。' WHERE entry=16803; /* Text0_0: Shadow-Walker Zuru can help ya.$B$BYou\'ll find him on de lowest floor of de taller building in de southeast. */ /* Text0_1: Shadow-Walker Zuru can help ya.$B$BYou\'ll find him on de lowest floor of de taller building in de southeast. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='夜行者库纳基应该是你要找的人。$B$B他就在山谷中部建筑的北边。',Text0_1_loc4='夜行者库纳基应该是你要找的人。$B$B他就在山谷中部建筑的北边。' WHERE entry=16804; /* Text0_0: Ku\'nanji, de Night-Stalker, is who yer lookin\' for.$B$BHe be just north of de valley\'s central building. */ /* Text0_1: Ku\'nanji, de Night-Stalker, is who yer lookin\' for.$B$BHe be just north of de valley\'s central building. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='巫医尤姆布一直在山谷四处活动，照料受伤的病人与元素之灵。$B$B去中部建筑附近找他吧。',Text0_1_loc4='巫医尤姆布一直在山谷四处活动，照料受伤的病人与元素之灵。$B$B去中部建筑附近找他吧。' WHERE entry=16805; /* Text0_0: Witch Doctor Umbu spends his time walkin\' about de valley, tendin\' to de people and elemental spirits alike.$B$BLook for him around de central building. */ /* Text0_1: Witch Doctor Umbu spends his time walkin\' about de valley, tendin\' to de people and elemental spirits alike.$B$BLook for him around de central building. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你一定是疯了，伙计，居然对那样的巫术感兴趣。可我没资格阻止你。$B$B乌恩加里·邪语就在东南方那座较高的建筑里，穿过暗影祭司的神殿就是了。',Text0_1_loc4='你一定是疯了，伙计，居然对那样的巫术感兴趣。可我没资格阻止你。$B$B乌恩加里·邪语就在东南方那座较高的建筑里，穿过暗影祭司的神殿就是了。' WHERE entry=16806; /* Text0_0: You be crazy, mon, meddlin\' with dat bad mojo. But I ain\'t one ta stop ya.$B$BUnjari Feltongue is in de taller building in de southeast, past de shadow priest\'s shrine. */ /* Text0_1: You be crazy, mon, meddlin\' with dat bad mojo. But I ain\'t one ta stop ya.$B$BUnjari Feltongue is in de taller building in de southeast, past de shadow priest\'s shrine. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='扎姆沙是奥格瑞玛最好的厨师，朋友。$B$B你可以在这座山谷的中心建筑南边找到她。如果你真的很饿，也可以在巴塔姆西那里买到扎姆沙烹制的食物。',Text0_1_loc4='扎姆沙是奥格瑞玛最好的厨师，朋友。$B$B你可以在这座山谷的中心建筑南边找到她。如果你真的很饿，也可以在巴塔姆西那里买到扎姆沙烹制的食物。' WHERE entry=16807; /* Text0_0: Zamja be de best cook in Orgrimmar, mon.$B$BYou can find her just south of de valley\'s central building. Batamsi sells de food Zamja makes, too, if ya just be hungry. */ /* Text0_1: Zamja be de best cook in Orgrimmar, mon.$B$BYou can find her just south of de valley\'s central building. Batamsi sells de food Zamja makes, too, if ya just be hungry. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='加迪和希尔拉亚就在这座山谷中心建筑北边的一座小屋里工作。$B$B他们能提供你所需要的帮助，朋友。',Text0_1_loc4='加迪和希尔拉亚就在这座山谷中心建筑北边的一座小屋里工作。$B$B他们能提供你所需要的帮助，朋友。' WHERE entry=16808; /* Text0_0: Jandi and Zeal\'aya work from a hut just north of de valley\'s central building.$B$BDey can help ya wit\' whatever ya need, mon. */ /* Text0_1: Jandi and Zeal\'aya work from a hut just north of de valley\'s central building.$B$BDey can help ya wit\' whatever ya need, mon. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='老恩姆贝托就在位于山谷中部建筑东面的一座小岛上。',Text0_1_loc4='老恩姆贝托就在位于山谷中部建筑东面的一座小岛上。' WHERE entry=16810; /* Text0_0: Old Umbehto be on a lil\' islet east of de valley\'s central buildin\'. */ /* Text0_1: Old Umbehto be on a lil\' islet east of de valley\'s central buildin\'. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='Huju和克森图能帮上你的忙。$B$B去山谷的中央建筑里找他们吧，伙计。',Text0_1_loc4='Huju和克森图能帮上你的忙。$B$B去山谷的中央建筑里找他们吧，伙计。' WHERE entry=16811; /* Text0_0: Huju and Xen\'to can take care of ya.$B$BFind dem in de valley\'s central building, mon. */ /* Text0_1: Huju and Xen\'to can take care of ya.$B$BFind dem in de valley\'s central building, mon. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我们的一些德鲁伊和斥候组成了一支小队伍，前来援助乱风岗的牛头人，对抗我们共同的敌人：恐怖图腾部族。' WHERE entry=16812; /* Text0_0: A small group of us, druids and sentinels, have come to aid the tauren of Freewind Post with our common enemy: the Grimtotem Clan. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='克萨迪斯和他的蛇群就在这座山谷的中心建筑周围游荡，朋友。',Text0_1_loc4='克萨迪斯和他的蛇群就在这座山谷的中心建筑周围游荡，朋友。' WHERE entry=16813; /* Text0_0: Xan\'tish and his snakes are slitherin\' around de valley\'s central building, mon. */ /* Text0_1: Xan\'tish and his snakes are slitherin\' around de valley\'s central building, mon. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='如果你需要材料，尽可以在我这里挑选。' WHERE entry=16815; /* Text0_0: If you should need reagents, I have a full selection available. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='<在爆炸前，质量均可保证！>$B$B<塞入钱款，即可得到专业训练和售卖服务。>' WHERE entry=16824; /* Text0_0: <Quality you can depend upon until the explosive end!>$B$B<Insert moolah for profession training and vending services.> */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='如果你愿意，可以在这里休息。现在大地神殿由我们管理。' WHERE entry=16825; /* Text0_0: You may rest here, if you like. The Temple of Earth is under our care, now. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='这是恐怖图腾最后一次向我们发动进攻了。既然他们不可能明白自己的错误，我们就要像消灭野兽一样摧毁他们。$B$B愿大地母亲原谅我们。' WHERE entry=16828; /* Text0_0: The Grimtotem have struck us for the last time. Since they cannot be taught the error of their ways, we will destroy them like beasts.$B$BEarth Mother forgive us. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='这是艾泽拉斯的困难时期，$n。',Text0_1_loc4='这是艾泽拉斯的困难时期，$n。' WHERE entry=16829; /* Text0_0: These are grave times for Azeroth, $n. */ /* Text0_1: These are grave times for Azeroth, $n. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='抱歉，朋友。你只能去别的地方寻找训练机会了。' WHERE entry=16831; /* Text0_0: Sorry, friend. You\'ll have to seek training elsewhere. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='只要一点捐赠，我就能教导你牧师的技艺。' WHERE entry=16832; /* Text0_0: For a small donation, I can train you in the priestly arts. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='他们的营地几乎被彻底摧毁了。不过我们还是从那片废墟中找到了一些可用的东西。$B$B你需要些什么，$r？' WHERE entry=16835; /* Text0_0: Little of their camp has been left intact. Still, there might be something we can make use of.$B$BDid you require something of me, $r? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我这里没有你要找的东西。$B$B不过赫格莉德正在收集暮光补给品，供我们自己使用。你也许应该找她谈一谈。' WHERE entry=16836; /* Text0_0: I have nothing for you.$B$BHegrid, though, has been gathering Twilight supplies to replenish our own. You might speak with her. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='别人丢下的东西，我都会收集起来。$B$B最近可是有不少东西需要收集。' WHERE entry=16839; /* Text0_0: That which falls, I collect.$B$BOf late, there have been many things to gather. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我不能。我只负责收集。$B$B伊布迪尔应该能帮到你。他擅长修理。' WHERE entry=16840; /* Text0_0: I cannot. I merely collect.$B$BIbdil may help you. His way is to mend. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='别人弄坏的东西，我都会修理好。$B$B最近可是有不少东西需要修理。实在是太多了。' WHERE entry=16841; /* Text0_0: That which has broken, I mend.$B$BSo much has been broken in recent time. So very much. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我这里没有什么能帮到你的东西。$B$B也许德罗姆的收集品中会有一些能让你感兴趣的东西。' WHERE entry=16844; /* Text0_0: There is nothing I call my own that would be of use to you.$B$BPerhaps D\'lom will have something of interest to you in his collection. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='一旦你决定成为一名萨满祭司，就再无法回头了。$B$B我曾经严重低估了火元素的效用。而且它也很容易管束：只需要加水就可以了。' WHERE entry=16846; /* Text0_0: Once you go shaman, you don\'t go back.$B$BI completely underestimated the usefulness of fire elementals. Easy to discipline too: just add water. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='暮光之锤一直在这片高地的各处向我们发动进攻。现在他们已经占领了不少地方。这是我们最后的阵地了，我们可不打算把它丢给敌人，无论他们会从地底下召唤出多么恐怖的怪物来攻击我们。' WHERE entry=16847; /* Text0_0: Da Twilight\'s Hammer have been assaultin\' our rings all over da highlands, and dey\'ve taken many for demselves in da process. Dis be our last and we have no intention of givin\' it up, no matter what kind of horrors dey be summonin\' from the earth to assault us. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='嗯，有的……克罗米需要这个？应该是吧。$b$b我可以把它给你，随你翻看。它会告诉你达隆郡的历史，以及导致那么多人死亡的许多事件细节。' WHERE entry=16849; /* Text0_0: Why, yes... does Chromie need this?  I suppose she would.$b$bYes, you may have it.  Feel free to leaf through the pages.  Inside you will find the history of Darrowshire, and the details of the events that led to the deaths of so very many men. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='绝不要低估后勤供给的作用。战士们也许会赢得几次战斗，但只有足够的物资供应才能确保一场战争的胜利。' WHERE entry=16850; /* Text0_0: Never underestimate the power of proper supply management. The warriors may win the battles, but it\'s the supplies that win the war. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我没办法保证你们能在这里得到平静的休息环境，$c。这些兽人根本不知道什么是平静。',Text0_1_loc4='我没办法保证你们能在这里得到平静的休息环境，$c。这些兽人根本不知道什么是平静。',Text1_0_loc4='一个喝醉的兽人很值得看一看。而一支喝醉的兽人军队则是我绝对不想看到的。',Text1_1_loc4='一个喝醉的兽人很值得看一看。而一支喝醉的兽人军队则是我绝对不想看到的。' WHERE entry=16851; /* Text0_0: I cannot promise that your rest will be peaceful, $c.  These orcs do not know when to quit. */ /* Text0_1: I cannot promise that your rest will be peaceful, $c.  These orcs do not know when to quit. */ /* Text1_0: A drunk orc is  a sight to see.  An army of drunk orcs is a sight I wish to never see again. */ /* Text1_1: A drunk orc is  a sight to see.  An army of drunk orcs is a sight I wish to never see again. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text2_0_loc4='如果我妈妈告诉我会有这样的时代，我绝对不会相信她的话。',Text2_1_loc4='如果我妈妈告诉我会有这样的时代，我绝对不会相信她的话。' WHERE entry=16851; /* Text2_0: If my mother had told me there would be days like this I would not have believed her. */ /* Text2_1: If my mother had told me there would be days like this I would not have believed her. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我已经在那个镇子里浪费了太长时间。那是一个不错的地方，我很享受在那里的生活。但我想，我更喜欢留在这里。' WHERE entry=16858; /* Text0_0: I\'ve spent far too long in that town.  It\'s a wonderful place, and I enjoyed my service there, but I think I\'d prefer to stay here. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='嗯，我们正好顺路。是那些在道路上出没的怪兽让我无法成行，只能在皇冠哨卫这里耽误时日。$b$b我想和你做笔交易：帮我清除道路上的怪物，我就会加入你们的队伍。' WHERE entry=16862; /* Text0_0: Well, I am headed in that direction.  I\'ve only been dallying here at Crown\'s Guard because of all the wildlife activity on the roads.$b$bI\'ll make you a deal: help me clear the roads, and yes, I\'ll join your group. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你好，旅行者？' WHERE entry=16864; /* Text0_0: Yes, traveler? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='马车里放的都是装货物的箱子。还有菲奥拉和她的同伴们的一些私人物品。' WHERE entry=16865; /* Text0_0: Inside the caravan are boxes of vendor supplies, along with the personal belongings of Fiona and her companions. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='这个地方真是考古学家的梦想之地！$b$b真希望我能有时间进行一场彻底的考古发掘。' WHERE entry=16866; /* Text0_0: This place is an archaeologist\'s dream!$b$bI wish there were time to conduct a proper excavation. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='这里的地形真可怕！吸饱了地下水的泥土中混杂着许多树根和石块，就像一锅煮糊的麦片粥。黏软的泥浆甚至能把一辆蒸汽坦克吸进去。$B$B我们的设备全都陷在了泥里，还有部落的混蛋不停地给我们捣乱！' WHERE entry=16867; /* Text0_0: This here terrain is terrible! Spongy ground, all lumpy-like with stumps and stones. Like angry oatmeal. The mud\'ll practically swallow a steam tank whole.$B$BOur gear\'s all mired in the muck, getting thumped by the Horde! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='别害怕。我其实并不像外表显示的这样可怕。$B$B我的名字是阿克莱多斯塔兹，你可以称呼我阿克莱德。我的女王派我到这里来阻止奈法利安。在任务完成之前，我绝不会休息。但这里还有一些敌人守卫着他的巢穴。仅凭我的力量是无法战胜他们的。$B$B请帮我消灭掉他们。阿莱克丝塔萨一定会因此而感激你。也许你还不知道这个名字，但我相信，你总有一天会因为今天帮助了我而感到庆幸。' WHERE entry=16869; /* Text0_0: Do not be alarmed. I am not as I appear.$B$BMy name is Acridostrasz, though you may call me Acride. My Queen sent me here to stop Nefarian, and I will not rest until my task is complete. However, there are other foes here guarding his lair that I cannot take on alone.$B$BHelp me dispose of them, and you will be in the favor of Alexstrasza. You may not know that name, but you will one day be thankful you do, of this I am certain. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='这里的大门永远都向你和你的钱敞开着。',Text0_1_loc4='这里的大门永远都向你和你的钱敞开着。' WHERE entry=16870; /* Text0_0: You and your coin are -always- welcome here. */ /* Text0_1: You and your coin are -always- welcome here. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你不需要和我作战，$r。我对你没有恶意。' WHERE entry=16871; /* Text0_0: You do not need to fight me, $r.  I mean you no ill will. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='她被困在了这堆垃圾里，而我已经失去了蒸汽动力。这里的地面太泥泞了！$B$B你能帮我们离开这里么？',Text0_1_loc4='她被困在了这堆垃圾里，而我已经失去了蒸汽动力。这里的地面太泥泞了！$B$B你能帮我们离开这里么？' WHERE entry=16872; /* Text0_0: She\'s hung up in the debris and I\'ve lost steam pressure. This terrain is murder!$B$BCan you get us out of this? */ /* Text0_1: She\'s hung up in the debris and I\'ve lost steam pressure. This terrain is murder!$B$BCan you get us out of this? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='锅炉开始猛烈地冒起了气泡。' WHERE entry=16873; /* Text0_0: The cauldron bubbles violently. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='似乎什么事都没有发生。天灾之锅也许已经被毁掉了，但它看上去的确和以前没什么两样。你要怎样做？' WHERE entry=16874; /* Text0_0: Nothing seems to happen.  The plague cauldron may be ruined, but it certainly doesn\'t look any different.  What will you do? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='<你可以学习最多两种主要专业技能。请从下列专业技能中选择：>' WHERE entry=16875; /* Text0_0: <You may train in up to two primary professions. Please choose from the following selections:> */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='<你可以学习所有种类的辅助专业技能。请从下列专业技能中选择：>' WHERE entry=16876; /* Text0_0: <You may train any of the secondary professions. Please choose from the following selections:> */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='<数据错误……请前往扎普诺兹医生处获取进一步指示。>' WHERE entry=16877; /* Text0_0: <Error retrieving data.... Please see Doc Zapnozzle for further instruction.> */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我没有恶意，但我觉得你连一头科多兽的肚子都射不中。$B$B我们不应该再浪费彼此的时间了，去找一位合适的训练师吧。',Text0_1_loc4='我没有恶意，但我觉得你连一头科多兽的肚子都射不中。$B$B我们不应该再浪费彼此的时间了，去找一位合适的训练师吧。' WHERE entry=16878; /* Text0_0: No offense, but you don\'t look like you could shoot the broad side of a pack kodo.$B$BHow about we stop wastin\' each other\'s time and you go find the right trainer. */ /* Text0_1: No offense, but you don\'t look like you could shoot the broad side of a pack kodo.$B$BHow about we stop wastin\' each other\'s time and you go find the right trainer. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='嗨，想进行瞄准练习么？',Text0_1_loc4='嗨，想进行瞄准练习么？' WHERE entry=16879; /* Text0_0: Yo. Up for a little target practice? */ /* Text0_1: Yo. Up for a little target practice? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='嗨，$n。想要学习知识吗？我可没有一整天的时间跟你耗……',Text0_1_loc4='嗨，$n。想要学习知识吗？我可没有一整天的时间跟你耗……' WHERE entry=16880; /* Text0_0: Hey there, $N. Here for a lesson? I ain\'t got all day... */ /* Text0_1: Hey there, $N. Here for a lesson? I ain\'t got all day... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='这里没什么可看的，朋友。为什么不到别处去逛逛？',Text0_1_loc4='这里没什么可看的，朋友。为什么不到别处去逛逛？' WHERE entry=16882; /* Text0_0: Nothin\' ta see here, mon.  Be on yer way, why don\'cha? */ /* Text0_1: Nothin\' ta see here, mon.  Be on yer way, why don\'cha? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我听说你走了很远的路才来到这里，朋友。也许你需要更多一些训练？',Text0_1_loc4='我听说你走了很远的路才来到这里，朋友。也许你需要更多一些训练？' WHERE entry=16883; /* Text0_0: I heard ya comin\' a league away, mon. Maybe ya need some more trainin\'? */ /* Text0_1: I heard ya comin\' a league away, mon. Maybe ya need some more trainin\'? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='什么？我看上去像个$c吗？$B$B请让开一点，好吗？',Text0_1_loc4='什么？我看上去像个$c吗？$B$B请让开一点，好吗？' WHERE entry=16884; /* Text0_0: What?  I look like a $c to you?$B$BGet outta here, will ya? */ /* Text0_1: What?  I look like a $c to you?$B$BGet outta here, will ya? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你需要什么？$B$B太糟糕了。我可帮不了你，$c。',Text0_1_loc4='你需要什么？$B$B太糟糕了。我可帮不了你，$c。' WHERE entry=16886; /* Text0_0: You need somethin\'?$B$BToo bad. I got nothin\' for ya, $c. */ /* Text0_1: You need somethin\'?$B$BToo bad. I got nothin\' for ya, $c. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='“为了乐趣和利润控制元素。”$B$B这就是重点所在，同意我的话吗？让我们开始吧。',Text0_1_loc4='“为了乐趣和利润控制元素。”$B$B这就是重点所在，同意我的话吗？让我们开始吧。' WHERE entry=16887; /* Text0_0: "Controlling the Elements for Fun and Profit."$B$BThat\'s what it\'s all about, am I right?  Let\'s get ta work. */ /* Text0_1: "Controlling the Elements for Fun and Profit."$B$BThat\'s what it\'s all about, am I right?  Let\'s get ta work. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='听着，你不会想知道我到底掌握着什么。$B$B别以为我在开玩笑。那种力量能融化你的大脑。去别的地方，找些好玩的事情吧。',Text0_1_loc4='听着，你不会想知道我到底掌握着什么。$B$B别以为我在开玩笑。那种力量能融化你的大脑。去别的地方，找些好玩的事情吧。' WHERE entry=16888; /* Text0_0: Look. You don\'t even WANNA know the sorta stuff I could teach ya.$B$BSeriously. It\'d melt yer brain. Go play nice somewhere else. */ /* Text0_1: Look. You don\'t even WANNA know the sorta stuff I could teach ya.$B$BSeriously. It\'d melt yer brain. Go play nice somewhere else. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你会喜欢恶魔能量的：廉价，能够恢复，而且肯定能把你痛恨的东西炸碎。$B$B当然，你也会因此而必须面对一些东西——那种超越时间和空间的，难以想象的恐怖。你可能会因此而永远丢失你的心智。不过只有冒险才能得到巨大的回报！$B$B那么，你想让我教你些什么，嗯？',Text0_1_loc4='你会喜欢恶魔能量的：廉价，能够恢复，而且肯定能把你痛恨的东西炸碎。$B$B当然，你也会因此而必须面对一些东西——那种超越时间和空间的，难以想象的恐怖。你可能会因此而永远丢失你的心智。不过只有冒险才能得到巨大的回报！$B$B那么，你想让我教你些什么，嗯？' WHERE entry=16889; /* Text0_0: You gotta love fel energy: Cheap, renewable, and guaranteed to blow things up.$B$BSure, you risk losin\' your eternal will to Unimaginable Horrors from Beyond Time and Space, but hey, risk versus reward!$B$BNow, what did you wanna see me about, hmmm? */ /* Text0_1: You gotta love fel energy: Cheap, renewable, and guaranteed to blow things up.$B$BSure, you risk losin\' your eternal will to Unimaginable Horrors from Beyond Time and Space, but hey, risk versus reward!$B$BNow, what did you wanna see me about, hmmm? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='<次元之门发出“嗡嗡”的响声。>' WHERE entry=16893; /* Text0_0: <The dimensional portal hums.> */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我的鸟！闪电——他们射中了她！那些肮脏的野兽从天空中射中了她！' WHERE entry=16897; /* Text0_0: My bird! Lightning - they shot her! Those filthy beasts shot her from the sky! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='可怜的闪电。她需要一段时间才能复原。' WHERE entry=16898; /* Text0_0: Poor Lightning. She\'s gonna need some time to recouperate. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='好吧。准备好飞翔了吗？' WHERE entry=16899; /* Text0_0: Well then. Ready to fly? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='没有什么比在高空中翱翔更令人兴奋了。$B$B嗯，也许在飞翔时战斗会更好，最好在战斗之后还能喝上一杯上好的啤酒！' WHERE entry=16907; /* Text0_0: There\'s nothing more exciting than to soar through the air.$B$BWell, maybe to fight while soaring through the air, and a good tankard of ale afterward! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='为什么你不早说？替我给那些暮光异教徒狠狠来一下子，好不好？' WHERE entry=16908; /* Text0_0: Well, why didn\'t you say so? Give those Twilight cultists a good one from me, will ya? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='如果有人告诉你天灾军团被打败了，不要信他的话。看看吧……难道他们不是仍然在病木林横行肆虐吗？他们死守着他们的腐蚀之地，如同儿童拼命抓住自己的小床。$b$b我别无选择，只能战斗。在我呼出最后一口气之前，我绝不会停止和他们的战斗。' WHERE entry=16909; /* Text0_0: Don\'t let anybody tell you that the Scourge is defeated.  Look... do they not still roam the Plaguewood?  They cling to their corrupted land like a child\'s blanket.$b$bI have no choice but to fight.  Until my last breath, I will fight them. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='$c，你将拥有这座半岛。$B$B你将成为一件武器。$B$B你将成为带来胜利的战争之神。' WHERE entry=16914; /* Text0_0: You will own this peninsula, $c.$B$BYou will be a weapon.$B$BYou will be a minister of death, praying for war. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='报告！' WHERE entry=16918; /* Text0_0: Report! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='经过一番快速的查看，你确定这个人刚刚死了几个小时。' WHERE entry=16920; /* Text0_0: After a quick assessment, you determine that this fellow has expired within the last several hours. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我们要不惜一切代价，阻止古加尔制造出他的终极武器，就算这意味着我们要牺牲自己的生命。' WHERE entry=16923; /* Text0_0: We must stop Cho\'gall from creating his ultimate weapon at all costs, even if that means sacrificing ourselves. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='没有任何事情能比飞到敌人头顶上，向他们“轰隆轰隆”地扔炸弹更痛快的了！$B$B把两百五十磅的兽人扔到敌人头顶上也不错。对不对，朋友？' WHERE entry=16928; /* Text0_0: Dere\'s nothin\' bettah dan flyin\' ovah ya enemies an\' droppin\' dey boom-boom bombs on dem!$B$BDat, or droppin\' two-hundred, fifty pound orcs on dere heads. Right, mon? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='嘿，你干嘛不早说？教训教训那群暮光之锤，回来之后我们好好庆祝一下！$B$B我跟我的夫人在海滩上筑了个温馨的小窝。记得来串门！' WHERE entry=16929; /* Text0_0: Hey, why not you say so? Give dem Twilight\'s the ol\' one-two, den ya comin\' back here an\' we party!$B$BI gots me a sweet lil\' place down on dey beach with me lady. You comin\' by! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='很难向龙喉兽人解释“火力覆盖”和“压制炮火”这样的概念。$B$B幸运的是，他们很清楚什么是“杀”和……嗯……“杀光”。' WHERE entry=16941; /* Text0_0: It\'s hard to explain to the Dragonmaw concepts like, "Fields of Fire" or "Suppressive Barrage."$B$BFortunately, they have a firm grasp of "Kill Zones" and ... uh, "Murder." */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我请求援军来帮我们守住海滩。结果部落就派来了这群小不点儿和他们的小金属管。$B$B<格拉洛克不屑地看了看身边的地精。>' WHERE entry=16942; /* Text0_0: I asked for reinforcements to help us hold the beach. And the Horde sent these tiny little men and their small metal tubes.$B$B<Gralok eyes the nearby goblins with disdain.> */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我们将永远纪念卡加斯·刃拳，为了他曾经为部落所做的一切。他是有史以来最优秀的战士之一。即使是联盟也不能否认这一点。$B$B卡加斯远征军以他为名，也以他为荣。我们将在他的名义下，驱逐黑铁矮人，夺回黑石山以及其周围区域。这些都是应该属于部落的国土。$B$B你将成为酋长对抗索瑞森的有力武器。这也是属于你的巨大光荣。' WHERE entry=16944; /* Text0_0: We will always remember Kargath Bladefist for what he once was to the Horde. He was one of the finest warriors to ever live, even the Alliance recognizes this.$B$BThe Kargath Expeditionary force was named in his honor, and I plan to ensure we live up to his name. We will drive out the Dark Iron Dwarves and claim Blackrock Mountain, and all of the surrounding areas, for the Horde as they so rightfully belong.$B$BYou will be the Warchief\'s blade against Thaurissan. Wear that honor proudly. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='吉德文就在附近……我知道。这是圣骑士的直觉。' WHERE entry=16951; /* Text0_0: Gidwin is nearby... I know it.  Paladin\'s intuition. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你提供了一个有趣的选择，$r。我会好好考虑一下。$b$b好吧，我考虑好了。我会与你同行。也许我在圣光之愿礼拜堂已经待了太长时间。我已经准备好要行动了！呵呵！' WHERE entry=16957; /* Text0_0: You present an interesting option, $r.  I\'ll take that into consideration.$b$bAlright, I\'ve considered it.  Sure, I\'ll join you.  I\'ve probably stayed in Light\'s Hope Chapel for too long anyhow.  Like a gnome at a urinal, I\'m gonna have to stay on my toes!  Heh heh! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='嗨，老板，如果你需要有人帮你赶马车，就和老比吉尔说一声。' WHERE entry=16958; /* Text0_0: Hey boss.  You need someone to help drive the caravan, you just let ol\' Beezil know. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='真高兴又看见你了，$n。当你准备对大门发动进攻的时候，我们中的一些人也潜入到这里。$B$B我们计划在这里与肖尔大师碰面。$B$B<那名小队长拿出一张暮光堡垒的地图，指出那个地点。>$B$B等你准备好之后就告诉我，我们将并肩作战。' WHERE entry=16959; /* Text0_0: Good to see you again, $N. We snuck some more of us in here while you were prepping the Gates for the attack.$B$BI\'ll show you where we\'re to rendezvous with Master Shaw.$B$B<The squad leader produces a map of the Twilight Citadel and points to the spot.>$B$BLet me know when you\'re ready, and we\'ll all head up together. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='旅途中有人作伴的感觉真好。否则一路上孤孤单单的。' WHERE entry=16963; /* Text0_0: It\'s good to have traveling companions.  The road gets lonely out here. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你好，$N。' WHERE entry=16964; /* Text0_0: Greetings, $N. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='现在还不行，$g小伙子:姑娘;。$B$B我还要调试老板的伐木机。$B$B她可不喜欢像那些老木头一样徒步在城周围走来走去，特别是在她要去对付那个酋长的时候。' WHERE entry=16965; /* Text0_0: Not now, $gpal:lady;.$B$BI gotta re-tune the boss\' shredder.$B$BShe don\'t like movin\' around the city on foot like any old chump, ESPECIALLY if she\'s gotta go deal with the warchief. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='在病木林深处很少会有访客。通常都是憎恶。$b$b我能帮你什么忙吗？' WHERE entry=16966; /* Text0_0: I don\'t get many visitors this deep in the Plaguewood.  Abominations, mostly.$b$bCan I help you with something? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='将军在上一次海战中不幸遇难。我把他的舰船改造成了堡垒。$B$B这只是个应急方案，$c。' WHERE entry=16967; /* Text0_0: The Admiral was killed during our last naval engagement. I\'ve turned this ship into a fortress.$B$BWe\'re improvising here, $c. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='从石板上的秘密符文看来，有办法让这装置重新焕发活力。$b$b我们只需要想出该如何做……' WHERE entry=16968; /* Text0_0: The hieroglyphs on your tablets indicate that there\'s a way to get this mechanism working again.$b$bWe just need to figure out how... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='看来你的前人已经把信号弹搭好了，但还没来得及发射。$b$b现在看你的了，$n。' WHERE entry=16969; /* Text0_0: It looks like your predecessor had time to set the flares up, but they have not yet been launched.$b$bThis is your time to shine, $N. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='信号弹发射器已清空。' WHERE entry=16970; /* Text0_0: The flare launcher has been emptied. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='这片高地上的树木质都很坚硬。它们之中有一些……甚至是石头。我也不明白这究竟是为什么。$B$B为了砍伐这些木材，我们在伐木机上装备了钻石刀刃。但联盟却总是在破坏那些伐木机。' WHERE entry=16973; /* Text0_0: The trees here in the Highlands are made of stout wood. And some of them... stone. I don\'t pretend to understand.$B$BWe\'ve got diamond-bladed shredders to harvest the stuff, but the Alliance keeps whacking them. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我的人民长久以来都和蛮锤部族保持着良好的关系。$B$B我们当中有少数人在此定居。那些人把这片土地看作是值得守护的家园。' WHERE entry=16975; /* Text0_0: My people have enjoyed a good relationship with the Wildhammer for quite some time now.$B$BA few of us have settled here... those who have found this land to be a home worth defending. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='哈卡有许多尽为人知的名字。有人叫他血神，另一些人则直白地把他称作夺灵者。抛开名衔不说，他是这个世界上强大力量与邪恶意图的化身。$B$B我早先发现了这座神庙，并将它沉到了悲伤沼泽的下方。不幸的是，我们似乎只是在帮助阿塔莱——确保他们召唤哈卡的计划能在不受干扰的环境下实施。许多负责守卫神庙的巨龙都已被腐化，夺灵者的气息却一天天变得更为强烈。$B$B我无法凭自己的力量阻止他们。但如果我们合作，也许能有足够的时间终止他们的疯狂举动。' WHERE entry=16980; /* Text0_0: Hakkar is known by many names. Some call him the Blood God, others simply refer to him as The Soulflayer. Titles aside, he is an entity of enormous power with malicious intentions for our world.$B$BMy flight discovered this temple early on and sank it beneath the Swamp of Sorrows. Unfortunately, we only seemed to aid the Atal\'ai by ensuring their efforts to summon Hakkar went on undisturbed. Many of the dragons tasked with guarding the temple have been corrupted, and the Soulflayer\'s presence grows with each passing day.$B$BI cannot stop them alone. Together, though, we might have enough time to stop this madness. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='死亡之翼途径暴风城，为花园区留下了满目疮痍。我们只得暂时返回达纳苏斯。' WHERE entry=16981; /* Text0_0: With Stormwind\'s park district destroyed by Deathwing\'s pass over the city, we\'re returning to Darnassus for a time. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='上层精灵回来了，还带回了失落已久的神秘法术。$B$B你有什么需要我检视的东西吗？',Text0_1_loc4='上层精灵回来了，还带回了失落已久的神秘法术。$B$B你有什么需要我检视的东西吗？' WHERE entry=16982; /* Text0_0: The Highborne have returned, and with them spellcraft lost to the world for centuries.$B$BDo you have something for me to examine? */ /* Text0_1: The Highborne have returned, and with them spellcraft lost to the world for centuries.$B$BDo you have something for me to examine? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='如果你想要找奥术重铸师重铸物品，可以去法师区外的附魔商店，那里有一位上层精灵法师可以帮上你的忙。',Text0_1_loc4='如果你想要找奥术重铸师重铸物品，可以去法师区外的附魔商店，那里有一位上层精灵法师可以帮上你的忙。' WHERE entry=16984; /* Text0_0: If you\'re looking for an Arcane Reforger, there is a highborne mage inside the enchanting shop just outside the Mage District. */ /* Text0_1: If you\'re looking for an Arcane Reforger, there is a highborne mage inside the enchanting shop just outside the Mage District. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='有个神器——那是种武器，正在被注入上古之神的力量。我们不知道它究竟在哪儿，可我们必须赶在古加尔完成之前找到它。$B$B其它任何事都是次要的。任何人的生命都是可以牺牲的，包括你和我。' WHERE entry=16986; /* Text0_0: There\'s an artifact, a weapon, being forged with the power of an Old God. We don\'t know exactly what it is, but we need to get to it before it\'s completed by Cho\'gall.$B$BEverything else is secondary. Everyone is expendable, including you and I. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你认识我父亲吗？' WHERE entry=16987; /* Text0_0: Do you know my dad? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我可怜的宝贝儿，你一定累坏了。$B$B这儿有食物和饮料，要是你愿意的话，可以放心地在这儿休息。',Text0_1_loc4='我可怜的宝贝儿，你一定累坏了。$B$B这儿有食物和饮料，要是你愿意的话，可以放心地在这儿休息。' WHERE entry=16988; /* Text0_0: Poor dear, you must be exhausted.$B$BThere\'s food and drink, if you like, and it\'s safe to rest here. */ /* Text0_1: Poor dear, you must be exhausted.$B$BThere\'s food and drink, if you like, and it\'s safe to rest here. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='想吃点儿什么吗，$c？$B$B还是你只想找个地方放松一会儿？',Text0_1_loc4='想吃点儿什么吗，$c？$B$B还是你只想找个地方放松一会儿？' WHERE entry=16989; /* Text0_0: Looking for something to eat, $c?$B$BOr just a place to rest your weary bones for a while? */ /* Text0_1: Looking for something to eat, $c?$B$BOr just a place to rest your weary bones for a while? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='喔伙计，终于有人来了！这下面简直疯狂透顶！比疯狂还要疯狂！' WHERE entry=16990; /* Text0_0: Oh man, I\'m glad someone is here! Things are CRAZY down here! Crazier than usual! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我仅代表卓绝而永保中立的热砂集团——欢迎来到沼桨镇！我们是东部王国独一无二的滨海度假胜地与军用武器补给港。$B$B也许你们这些家伙刚刚在南面不远处经历了战火的洗礼，可在这围墙之内，只有欢声笑语。忘了肩头的重担吧，来歇会儿，喝上两杯，但切记别找麻烦……否则我这儿的彪悍卫兵会让你们明白什么叫做“中立地域”。' WHERE entry=16991; /* Text0_0: On behalf of the illustrious and always-neutral Steamwheedle Cartel, welcome to Bogpaddle! We\'re proud to be the only beachfront resort and military-grade weapons yard in the Eastern Kingdoms.$B$BYou guys may have that little war ragin\' just south of here, but inside these walls, it\'s all fun and games. So take a load off, have some R&R and a drink or two, and keep out of trouble... or my bruisers will remind your skull what "neutral territory" means. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='托尔本·光爆，传送应对方案工程师为您效劳！' WHERE entry=16995; /* Text0_0: Torben Zapblast, teleportation solutions engineer at your service! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你好啊。$B$B你是来存放宠物，还是在寻找失踪的同伴？',Text0_1_loc4='你好啊。$B$B你是来存放宠物，还是在寻找失踪的同伴？' WHERE entry=16996; /* Text0_0: Yo.$B$BYou here to stable your pets, or lookin\' for a lost companion? */ /* Text0_1: Yo.$B$BYou here to stable your pets, or lookin\' for a lost companion? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你好啊。$B$B你是在寻找失踪的同伴？',Text0_1_loc4='你好啊。$B$B你是在寻找失踪的同伴？' WHERE entry=16997; /* Text0_0: Yo.$B$BYou lookin\' for a lost companion? */ /* Text0_1: Yo.$B$BYou lookin\' for a lost companion? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='等我们安全回到地表之后，会有大把的时间供我们交谈。' WHERE entry=16998; /* Text0_0: There will be more time to talk once we get back to the surface safely. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你好，我名叫泰瑟兰·血望者。我将一生中最好的时光都用来进行巫术的训练，并召集与我志同道合的血精灵，组成了神圣遗物学会。$B$B要知道，在这个世界的各个角落里埋藏着许多古老、强大的宝物。我打算利用这些宝物将我的族人从他们堕落的嗜好中解救出来，让他们重新团结为一体，成为往日那个光荣而坚强的种族。$B$B我可以向你保证，魔法是可以接触的。只要得到适当的教导，任何人都能使用这种力量并且免于因它而堕落。$B$B现在，联盟的各个种族，甚至是部落的人都在嘲笑我们遭受重创的首都，仍然矗立的逐日者雕像，和我们在世界各处一次又一次遭受的挫折。$B$B但这种情况不会再继续下去了。' WHERE entry=17000; /* Text0_0: Greetings, my name is Tae\'thelan Bloodwatcher. I have spent the better part of a lifetime training in the art of sorcery and gathering like-minded blood elves to form The Reliquary.$B$BYou see, there are ancient, powerful relics spread throughout this world that I plan to use to free my people from their addiction and unify them again  as the proud, indomitable race we once were.$B$BMagic is something to be embraced and, I assure you, a force that can be utilized free of corruption with proper teaching.$B$BAs it stands, the other races of the Alliance and even the Horde mock our kind for our half-destroyed capital, still-standing statues of Sunstrider and blunder after blunder across the world.$B$BNo more. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你们一族注定要承受这一切，$r。',Text1_0_loc4='你和这些魔鬼结盟了？你也将会有被焚毁的一天！' WHERE entry=17004; /* Text0_0: Your kind will be made to suffer for this, $r. */ /* Text1_0: You ally yourself with these fiends? You, too, shall someday burn! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text2_0_loc4='<黑色的巨龙身上布满了伤口。他一直盯着你，眼睛里闪烁着凶恶的光芒。>',Text3_0_loc4='<凶恶的黑色巨龙拼命扯拽着捆缚他的锁链。你最好还是离他远一些。>' WHERE entry=17004; /* Text2_0: <The enormous black drake, covered with open wounds, stares you down with malice in his eyes. It does not blink.> */ /* Text3_0: <The ferocious black drake strains at the chains that bind it. It\'s best to keep your distance.> */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text4_0_loc4='我不可能永远困在这里，$c。你最好现在就祈祷，祈祷当我复仇的时候，你不会在我面前。' WHERE entry=17004; /* Text4_0: The bonds that hold me are not so permanent, $c. Pray you are not near when I have my vengeance. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='龙并不是猪和牛那样简单的野兽。他们是一种自然的力量。强大……原始的力量。$B$B让他们服从你，就是要驾驭这个世界。$B$B能够支配他们，你也就支配了命运的力量。' WHERE entry=17005; /* Text0_0: Dragons are no mere beasts, like hogs or cattle. They are a force of nature. Powerful... Primal.$B$BTo bend them to your will is to harness the world.$B$BTo take up their reigns is to take destiny into your hands. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='他们的火力相当强劲。也许我们不应该小看那些地精矬子。' WHERE entry=17007; /* Text0_0: That was some real firepower. Maybe there\'s more to these runty little goblins than meets the eye. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='如果是凯莉派你来抓我回去，那她可要失望了。这里还有许多暮光暴徒没消灭干净呢。' WHERE entry=17009; /* Text0_0: If Keely sent ya to be ropin\' me back in, ya can just forget it. There\'s Twilight that need bashin\'. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='看到前面的通道了吗，$g小子:姑娘;？' WHERE entry=17010; /* Text0_0: Ya see that pass ahead dere, $glad:lass;? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='有埋伏。' WHERE entry=17011; /* Text0_0: That\'s an ambush. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='哦，$g小伙子:姑娘;！已经4次了。' WHERE entry=17012; /* Text0_0: Oh yeah, $glad:lass;! Been through 4 times already. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='该死的，没错！' WHERE entry=17013; /* Text0_0: Damn right! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我很快就会回来的，$g小伙子:小姑娘;。为了能过上好日子，还得再走一趟。' WHERE entry=17014; /* Text0_0: I\'ll be headin\' back shortly, $glad:lass;. Just one more go, for good time\'s sake. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你好，$r。我是绿龙军团的伊萨里奥斯勋爵。$B$B我带着善良的意愿来到这里，要从这座神殿的邪恶中解救我的同族。你愿意帮助我吗？' WHERE entry=17019; /* Text0_0: Greetings, $r. I am Lord Itharius of the Green Dragonflight.$B$BI am here to free my kin from the evil within this temple, hopefully for good. Will you assist me? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='只有当最高议会全体表决通过的时候，拉穆卡恒才会对尼斐塞特发动战争。$B$B我们的机会不大，但我的兄弟必须明白，死亡之翼的盟军绝对不会讲任何道理。' WHERE entry=17024; /* Text0_0: Ramkahen will only wage war against Neferset if the High Council\'s vote is unanimous.$B$BThe odds are against us, but my brother needs to understand there is no reasoning with Deathwing\'s allies. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你和那些尼斐塞特 杂碎是一伙的？是不是他们派你来干什么肮脏的勾当？快说！' WHERE entry=17026; /* Text0_0: Are you with the Neferset scum?  Did they send you to do their dirty work?  Speak! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='喂！' WHERE entry=17029; /* Text0_0: Ahoy! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='部落的战争机器需要你！' WHERE entry=17030; /* Text0_0: The Horde war machine needs you! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你是来这里助战的吗？海加尔山必将燃起熊熊大火！' WHERE entry=17031; /* Text0_0: Are you here to help the cause? Mount Hyjal burns! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='那只巨型鱿鱼就要完蛋了。凡尔纳已经重整装备，准备再次上阵……现在，我们只需要耐心等待。$B$B它会回来的。$B$B你就看着吧。' WHERE entry=17032; /* Text0_0: That giant squid didn\'t stand a chance. The Verne\'s already rearmed and ready for another go... now we just wait.$B$BIt\'ll be back.$B$BYou\'ll see. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='联盟需要你。响应英雄的号召吧！' WHERE entry=17034; /* Text0_0: The Alliance needs you. Answer the hero\'s call! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='远处的那片碎石堆曾经是我们家族传承了五代的产业。$B$B我们正在把它夺回来。$B$B敌人的数量远远超过我们……但我们是蛮锤氏族！你愿意帮助我们吗？' WHERE entry=17036; /* Text0_0: That heap o\' rubble yonder was me family\'s homestead fer five generations.$B$BWe\'re takin\' it back.$B$BWe\'re outnumbered... But we\'re Wildhammer! Are yeh with me? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你在找我？' WHERE entry=17038; /* Text0_0: You lookin\' for me? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='真是一团乱！我们刚刚从拯救深岩之洲的战斗中回来，却看到了这种场面？$B$B可憎的暮光之锤！$B$B幸好你在这里，把他们解决掉了！' WHERE entry=17042; /* Text0_0: What a mess! We come back from saving Deepholm and what do we find?$B$BThe Twilight\'s Stinkin\' Hammer!$B$BGood thing you\'re here to straighten this all out! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你必须保护我，$n。没有了武器和图腾，我完全没有自卫的能力！' WHERE entry=17045; /* Text0_0: You\'re gonna have to protect me, $N. Without my weapons and totems, I\'m defenseless! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='真……渴啊……' WHERE entry=17046; /* Text0_0: So... thirsty... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='这具矮人的尸体被严重地损毁了。暮光之锤一定都是些以屠杀为乐的疯子。',Text0_1_loc4='这具矮人的尸体被严重地损毁了。暮光之锤一定都是些以屠杀为乐的疯子。' WHERE entry=17051; /* Text0_0: This dwarf\'s body is severely battered. The Twilight\'s Hammer must take pleasure in their killing. */ /* Text0_1: This dwarf\'s body is severely battered. The Twilight\'s Hammer must take pleasure in their killing. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我必须承认那些暮光暴徒并非无能之辈……也许他们缺乏战斗技巧，但他们的数量和坚韧完全可以弥补这个缺陷。在我们的上一次战斗中，他们的确取得了一些战果。' WHERE entry=17052; /* Text0_0: I have to give these Twilight a wee bit of credit... what they lack in skill, they make up for in numbers and tenacity. They got a few good licks in during our last bout. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='哈！我的兄弟们正渴望着一战。我已经无法再阻止他们了。$B$B你要参加这一战吗？' WHERE entry=17055; /* Text0_0: Hah! My brothers be itchin\' for a fight. It was all I could do ta hold them back this long.$B$BYou in? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你的时间就要结束了。',Text0_1_loc4='你的时间就要结束了。',Text1_0_loc4='随你怎么想吧，但你会看到，我才是对的。',Text1_1_loc4='随你怎么想吧，但你会看到，我才是对的。' WHERE entry=17057; /* Text0_0: Your time is coming to an end. */ /* Text0_1: Your time is coming to an end. */ /* Text1_0: Gloat all you want, but you\'ll see we were right. */ /* Text1_1: Gloat all you want, but you\'ll see we were right. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text2_0_loc4='也许我现在是陷入了困境，但是当主人的复仇之雨在这座城市上洒落的时候，我必将重获自由。',Text2_1_loc4='也许我现在是陷入了困境，但是当主人的复仇之雨在这座城市上洒落的时候，我必将重获自由。',Text3_0_loc4='我已经踏上成神的道路，那种狂妄而卑微的英雄不可能阻挡我。',Text3_1_loc4='我已经踏上成神的道路，那种狂妄而卑微的英雄不可能阻挡我。' WHERE entry=17057; /* Text2_0: I may be restrained now, but my master will set me free when his vengeance rains down upon this city. */ /* Text2_1: I may be restrained now, but my master will set me free when his vengeance rains down upon this city. */ /* Text3_0: I am on the path to ascension and no petty, aspiring hero is going to stop me. */ /* Text3_1: I am on the path to ascension and no petty, aspiring hero is going to stop me. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text4_0_loc4='你的生命即将终结，而我的则刚刚开始。',Text4_1_loc4='你的生命即将终结，而我的则刚刚开始。',Text5_0_loc4='当你察觉到真实情况的时候，一切都已经太晚了。',Text5_1_loc4='当你察觉到真实情况的时候，一切都已经太晚了。' WHERE entry=17057; /* Text4_0: It is your life that will end soon; mine is just beginning. */ /* Text4_1: It is your life that will end soon; mine is just beginning. */ /* Text5_0: By the time you realize the truth, it will be too late. */ /* Text5_1: By the time you realize the truth, it will be too late. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你就像顿沃德家族的一员。我喜欢你。' WHERE entry=17061; /* Text0_0: Like a Dunwald. I like you. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='这座笨重的雕像立在这里，已经有许多个世纪没有被碰触过了。' WHERE entry=17072; /* Text0_0: The hulking statue stands inert, untouched for centuries. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='虽然这座雕像已经非常古老了，却没有任何被风蚀损坏的痕迹。' WHERE entry=17073; /* Text0_0: While it is clearly quite old, this statue does not appear to have crumbled at all over the centuries. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='根据颜色判断，这一定就是戒卫。$b$b你在它上面找到一个小缺口，与你的棋卒轮廓正好吻合。' WHERE entry=17074; /* Text0_0: Judging by its color, this must be The Warden.$b$bYou see a small indentation where your pawn might fit. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='这座红色雕像很像是你带在身上的哨卫的棋卒。$b$b这座雕像上有一个小缺口，正好与你的棋卒形状相吻合。' WHERE entry=17075; /* Text0_0: This red statue looks a lot like the Sentinel\'s pawn that you hold.$b$bThe statue has a small indentation that matches the size of your pawn. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='希望你带来了矿工锄，朝圣者。没有任何地方能比这里更适合挖掘古代宝藏了。' WHERE entry=17080; /* Text0_0: Hope you brought your mining pick, pilgrim.  No place better than here for digging up ancient treasure. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='在火刃部族灭亡之后，我们剑圣就发誓，要从恶魔的统治之下解放我们自己和我们的族人。$B$B这个任务终于完成了，但我的荣誉并没有得到恢复。$B$B我要为部落而战，直到我在战场上光荣牺牲。这是我唯一的道路。',Text0_1_loc4='在火刃部族灭亡之后，我们剑圣就发誓，要从恶魔的统治之下解放我们自己和我们的族人。$B$B这个任务终于完成了，但我的荣誉并没有得到恢复。$B$B我要为部落而战，直到我在战场上光荣牺牲。这是我唯一的道路。' WHERE entry=17085; /* Text0_0: After the fall of the Burning Blade Clan, we blademasters swore to free ourselves and our people from demonic control.$B$BThis may be done, but my honor remains unsatisfied.$B$BI shall fight for the Horde - and train other warriors to do so - until I die gloriously in battle. This is the only path I may tread. */ /* Text0_1: After the fall of the Burning Blade Clan, we blademasters swore to free ourselves and our people from demonic control.$B$BThis may be done, but my honor remains unsatisfied.$B$BI shall fight for the Horde - and train other warriors to do so - until I die gloriously in battle. This is the only path I may tread. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='在火刃部族灭亡之后，我们剑圣就发誓，要从恶魔的统治之下解放我们自己和我们的族人。$B$B这个任务终于完成了，但我的荣誉并没有得到恢复。$B$B我要为部落而战，直到我在战场上光荣牺牲。这是我唯一的道路。$B$B好吧，你准备好进行训练了吗？',Text0_1_loc4='在火刃部族灭亡之后，我们剑圣就发誓，要从恶魔的统治之下解放我们自己和我们的族人。$B$B这个任务终于完成了，但我的荣誉并没有得到恢复。$B$B我要为部落而战，直到我在战场上光荣牺牲。这是我唯一的道路。$B$B好吧，你准备好进行训练了吗？' WHERE entry=17086; /* Text0_0: After the fall of the Burning Blade Clan, we blademasters swore to free ourselves and our people from demonic control.$B$BThis may be done, but my honor remains unsatisfied.$B$BI shall fight for the Horde - and train other warriors to do so - until I die gloriously in battle. This is the only path I may tread.$B$BSo. Are you ready to train? */ /* Text0_1: After the fall of the Burning Blade Clan, we blademasters swore to free ourselves and our people from demonic control.$B$BThis may be done, but my honor remains unsatisfied.$B$BI shall fight for the Horde - and train other warriors to do so - until I die gloriously in battle. This is the only path I may tread.$B$BSo. Are you ready to train? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='守卫部落的银行和财宝要比呆在一个铁笼子里分发钱币，收发物品有意思多了。$B$B我可不会和那些只知道耍笔杆子的地精交换工作。',Text0_1_loc4='守卫部落的银行和财宝要比呆在一个铁笼子里分发钱币，收发物品有意思多了。$B$B我可不会和那些只知道耍笔杆子的地精交换工作。' WHERE entry=17087; /* Text0_0: Guarding the bank and treasures of the Horde is far more satisfying than dispensing coins and trade goods from inside a cage of iron.$B$BI would not exchange places with one of those quill-pushing goblins for a moment. */ /* Text0_1: Guarding the bank and treasures of the Horde is far more satisfying than dispensing coins and trade goods from inside a cage of iron.$B$BI would not exchange places with one of those quill-pushing goblins for a moment. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='很高兴见到你，年轻的$g先生:女士;。' WHERE entry=17097; /* Text0_0: Pleasure to meet ya, young $gman:lady;. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='他们在我们没有察觉的时候偷袭了我们……同时对高地各处发动了攻击。他们破地而出，又从空中俯冲而下。大部分狮鹫都受惊逃走了。许多优秀的矮人白白牺牲。$B$B如果不是科甘及时将我们召集起来，重整了队伍，我们可能早已经被围歼了。是他救了我的命。至少现在，我们还有反击的机会。' WHERE entry=17098; /* Text0_0: They took us unaware... attacked all of the highlands all at once, burstin\' forth from the ground, swoopin\' from the air. Most of the gryphon wings were scattered, and far too many good dwarves lost their lives.$B$BThere\'d be little hope at all if Keegan hadn\'t rallied us together. I owe that man my life. At least now we have a chance. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你肯定不是本地人。不过这对我来说没什么关系。无论是谁，只要真心愿意帮助我们，我都会和他生死与共。' WHERE entry=17099; /* Text0_0: You\'re certainly not local. Matters to me little though. I\'ll put my life on the line for anyone here as long as they pull their weight. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我很久以前就来到这里，研究我们受到诅咒的兄弟，寻找治疗他们的办法。$B$B玛格图尔热情地欢迎我。我住在这里的时候，他成为了我最亲密的朋友。$B$B而现在，他躺在我面前，奄奄一息……' WHERE entry=17100; /* Text0_0: I came here long ago to study our cursed brothers, in search of a way to cure their affliction.$B$BMagtoor welcomed me with open arms. Living here, he became my closest friend.$B$BAnd now, before my eyes, he is dying... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='看上去，你能为我们挣不少钱。去杀戮熔炉里转一圈如何，朋友？' WHERE entry=17102; /* Text0_0: You look like you could make us some money. How about a spin inside the Crucible of Carnage, pal? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='看上去，这头狮鹫受了伤。也许治疗或急救技能可以让它重新站起来。' WHERE entry=17103; /* Text0_0: The gryphon appears to be injured. Perhaps healing or first aid could get it back on its feet. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='狮鹫专注地看着你。它显然是从你的衣服上闻到了熟悉的气味。' WHERE entry=17104; /* Text0_0: The gryphon looks at you intently, clearly smelling a familiar scent on your clothing. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='这头狮鹫似乎是被困住了。不过看上去，它应该能轻松地挣脱身上的束缚。' WHERE entry=17105; /* Text0_0: The gryphon appears to be trapped. It looks like it would be easily possible to break its bonds though. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='爸爸总是对我说，大家伙力气大，但速度慢……$b$b我相信爸爸一定没有见过这个家伙！' WHERE entry=17111; /* Text0_0: Dad always told me the big fellas hit hard, but that they\'re slow...$b$bI\'m pretty sure dad never met this guy! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='<黑角望向地狱的远方，然后又将注意力转回到你身上。>' WHERE entry=17112; /* Text0_0: <Blackhorn gazes out across the distant inferno, then turns his attention back to you.> */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='一块不显眼的大理石板。' WHERE entry=17115; /* Text0_0: An inconspicuous marble slab. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='一块不显眼的石板。' WHERE entry=17116; /* Text0_0: An inconspicuous stone slab. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='<这位巨大的远古半神仍然对你保持着警惕，但他已经像对待盟友一样和你说话了。>' WHERE entry=17117; /* Text0_0: <The enormous ancient remains wary of you, but speaks to you as an ally.> */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我是拉穆卡恒的纳顿亲王。尼斐塞特部族已经公然与其他托维尔为敌。$B$B请帮我逃出这里，这样我就能说服我的兄弟，也就是我们的国王向这些叛徒发动战争！' WHERE entry=17119; /* Text0_0: I am Prince Nadun of Ramkahen.  The Neferset tribe has turned against the other tol\'vir.$B$BHelp me escape so that I may lobby my brother, the king, to wage war against these traitors! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你一定要试试这种啤酒。' WHERE entry=17140; /* Text0_0: You\'ve got to try some of this beer. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='如果你不打算工作，那就离我们的发掘场远一些。' WHERE entry=17142; /* Text0_0: If you\'re not here to work, then please see yourself away from our excavation. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='嘿，帅哥！',Text0_1_loc4='嘿，帅哥！',Text1_0_loc4='还有地方吗，甜心？',Text1_1_loc4='还有地方吗，甜心？' WHERE entry=17143; /* Text0_0: Hey there, good lookin\'. */ /* Text0_1: Hey there, good lookin\'. */ /* Text1_0: You got room for one more, sugar? */ /* Text1_1: You got room for one more, sugar? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text2_0_loc4='跟我走吗？',Text2_1_loc4='跟我走吗？',Text3_0_loc4='一位淑女能够上马驰骋一番吗？',Text3_1_loc4='一位淑女能够上马驰骋一番吗？' WHERE entry=17143; /* Text2_0: Going my way? */ /* Text2_1: Going my way? */ /* Text3_0: Can a lady get a ride? */ /* Text3_1: Can a lady get a ride? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text4_0_loc4='马特克，你今天看上去很英俊。',Text4_1_loc4='马特克，你今天看上去很英俊。',Text5_0_loc4='哦，马特克，我能和你一起驰骋吗？',Text5_1_loc4='哦，马特克，我能和你一起驰骋吗？' WHERE entry=17143; /* Text4_0: You\'re looking very handsome today, Martek. */ /* Text4_1: You\'re looking very handsome today, Martek. */ /* Text5_0: Ooh, Martek, can I ride with you? */ /* Text5_1: Ooh, Martek, can I ride with you? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text6_0_loc4='马特克，你是我所知道的最勇敢的兽人。',Text6_1_loc4='马特克，你是我所知道的最勇敢的兽人。',Text7_0_loc4='救救我，马特克！我需要你！',Text7_1_loc4='救救我，马特克！我需要你！' WHERE entry=17143; /* Text6_0: Martek, you are the bravest orc I know. */ /* Text6_1: Martek, you are the bravest orc I know. */ /* Text7_0: Save me, Martek!  I need you! */ /* Text7_1: Save me, Martek!  I need you! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='这里的效率真高，你说呢？' WHERE entry=17148; /* Text0_0: This is quite an operation here, wouldn\'t you say? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='必须承认，我对这个野心勃勃的小狂徒有了些兴趣。$b$b我不会急于做出判断，但我要告诉你，我已经听到了一些令人不安的谣言。$b$b时间会告诉我，他的动机是否正当。' WHERE entry=17150; /* Text0_0: I must admit, I am intrigued by this ambitious little upstart.$b$bI\'m not rushing to judgement, mind you, but I\'ve heard some unsettling rumors.$b$bTime will tell if his motives are just. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你怎么会来找我们这些衰老又疲惫的沙漠狗子？' WHERE entry=17151; /* Text0_0: What brings you to a bunch of old, washed-up desert dogs like us? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我并不吃惊。$b$b我也不可能忽略这么多的问题……$b$b为什么一个考古发掘场里会有这么多武器？这与埋藏在地下的宝物有什么关系吗？这里的发掘人员到底效忠于谁？$b$b我还没有找到这些问题的答案。我想，我得自己去寻找真相。' WHERE entry=17152; /* Text0_0: I\'m not surprised.$b$bSo many questions, I cannot ignore...$b$bWhy all these weapons for an archaeological dig? And what is being done with the unearthed relics? Under what authority is the excavation being conducted?$b$bThe answers don\'t seem to be forthcoming. I\'ll just have to find out for myself, I suppose. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='白痴！$b$b快滚开！$b$b难道你看不出来，我正在集中精神吗？' WHERE entry=17153; /* Text0_0: Eediot!$b$bAvay vizh you!$b$bCan\'t you see zhat I am concentratink? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='听我说！朋友，举起望远镜！$b$b好好看看这里。$b$b要知道，在漫长的岁月里，这个地方一直被隐藏着。' WHERE entry=17155; /* Text0_0: I say! Raise a glass, my friend!$b$bTake in the sights here.$b$bThis entire region has been hidden away for ages, you know. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='看看他积聚的财富！$b$b他的手段经常会让我感到不舒服，但这个结果却是无法否认的……$b$b不要去想那些令人不快的事情了。要知道，这样也不礼貌。' WHERE entry=17156; /* Text0_0: Why, just look at the treasure he has accumulated!$b$bI\'m not always comfortable with his methods, but there\'s no denying the results...$b$bBest not to dwell upon unpleasant thoughts. It\'s bad manners, you know. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='好好想想，我亲爱的$g男孩:女孩;！$b$b一旦我们野心勃勃的小毛皮商发掘出足够的财宝，他就会成为艾泽拉斯最有影响力的角色。$b$b如果这一天到来，我们都会有一个令人满意的地位。' WHERE entry=17157; /* Text0_0: Speculation, my dear $gboy:girl;!$b$bOnce our eager little furrier has unearthed enough treasure, he\'ll be one of Azeroth\'s most influential figures.$b$bWe\'ll all be properly positioned when that comes to pass. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='不就是这里吗？$b$b与志同道合的伙伴一同探索这个世界从未被开发过的角落？$b$b还有什么能比这样更好的？' WHERE entry=17158; /* Text0_0: Now, isn\'t this the place to be?$b$bTouring unexplored corners of the world with likeminded fellows?$b$bWhat could be better? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='这就是那个大名鼎鼎的$r$c，嗯？$b$b如你所知，还有一个尚未被激活的方尖碑……$b$b当复原这古老装置的时机到来时，你会在那里吗？历史会记住你吗？$b$b这取决于你是否愿意合作！' WHERE entry=17166; /* Text0_0: So, zhis is zhe $r $c I\'ve heard so much about, hmm?$b$bAs you know, zhere is vone obelisk zhat has yet to be activated....$b$bVhen zhe time comes to restore zhis ancient mechanism, vhill you be zhere? Vill history remember you?$b$bZhat depends on your villingness to cooperate! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='说说你的情况，$r。',Text1_0_loc4='我们正在注意你，$r……' WHERE entry=17167; /* Text0_0: State your business, $r. */ /* Text1_0: Ve\'re vatchink you, $r... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text2_0_loc4='……一直在注意！' WHERE entry=17167; /* Text2_0: ...alvays vatchink! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='得知黑龙要与新卡加斯对抗，我像你一样感到惊讶。高恩非常顽固，拒绝任何人的帮助。$b$b即使这样，高阶考察者泰瑟兰·血望者还是要求我时刻注意新卡加斯的情况，以确保局势对我们不会太……糟糕。' WHERE entry=17169; /* Text0_0: I was as surprised as you to find the black dragonflight asserting its will against New Kargath.  Gorn is stubborn, and refuses help from anyone.$b$bEven so, High Examiner Bloodwatcher has asked me to watch from a distance, to make sure things do not become... ugly. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我们必须阻止塞拉赞恩的军队进攻巨石之炉。$B$B否则他们就有可能偷走世界之柱的中部残片。' WHERE entry=17170; /* Text0_0: We must keep Therazane\'s forces from attacking Stonehearth.$B$BIf they do, they will steal the middle fragment of the World Pillar. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我们钓鱼，我们睡觉，我们炸飞各种东西。还有什么生活能比这样更好？' WHERE entry=17172; /* Text0_0: We fish, we sleep, and we explode things.  What could be better than that? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='那个箱子就在废墟里。$b$b我们行动！' WHERE entry=17174; /* Text0_0: The coffer is just beyond these ruins.$b$bLet\'s go! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我们已经太久忽略了奥术的秘密。$B$B你是来学习这个秘密的吗？',Text0_1_loc4='我们已经太久忽略了奥术的秘密。$B$B你是来学习这个秘密的吗？' WHERE entry=17175; /* Text0_0: For too long we have ignored the secrets of the Arcane.$B$BAre you here to learn, as well? */ /* Text0_1: For too long we have ignored the secrets of the Arcane.$B$BAre you here to learn, as well? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我们已经太久忽略了奥术的秘密。$B$B可惜的是，它对你来说只能是个秘密。',Text0_1_loc4='我们已经太久忽略了奥术的秘密。$B$B可惜的是，它对你来说只能是个秘密。' WHERE entry=17176; /* Text0_0: For too long we have ignored the secrets of the Arcane.$B$BSadly, they will remain a secret to you. */ /* Text0_1: For too long we have ignored the secrets of the Arcane.$B$BSadly, they will remain a secret to you. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='感谢你救出了国王……还有王子，$n。' WHERE entry=17177; /* Text0_0: Thank you for rescuing the king... and the prince, $N. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你让我明白了朋友的意义，$n。' WHERE entry=17178; /* Text0_0: You\'ve taught me what it means to have friends, $N. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='我见证了你的成功，$n。你是你们一族的骄傲。' WHERE entry=17179; /* Text0_0: I see that you did it, $N. You\'re a credit to your race. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='抱歉，$c。$B$B你对奥术的掌握还不够强大，还无法理解传送门魔法。',Text0_1_loc4='抱歉，$c。$B$B你对奥术的掌握还不够强大，还无法理解传送门魔法。' WHERE entry=17180; /* Text0_0: Sorry, $c. $B$BYour grasp of the arcane isn\'t strong enough to understand portal magic. */ /* Text0_1: Sorry, $c. $B$BYour grasp of the arcane isn\'t strong enough to understand portal magic. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你也是一名奥术的研究者？$B$B我可以教导你传送门魔法的技艺，如果你想学的话。',Text0_1_loc4='你也是一名奥术的研究者？$B$B我可以教导你传送门魔法的技艺，如果你想学的话。' WHERE entry=17181; /* Text0_0: You too are a student of the arcane, yes?$B$BI can teach you about portal magic, if you wish to learn. */ /* Text0_1: You too are a student of the arcane, yes?$B$BI can teach you about portal magic, if you wish to learn. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='恐怕我没办法帮你，$r，但我相信凯琳·斯蒂文可以。',Text0_1_loc4='恐怕我没办法帮你，$r，但我相信凯琳·斯蒂文可以。' WHERE entry=17187; /* Text0_0: I\'m afraid I cannot help you, $r, but I am sure Khaelyn Steelwing can. */ /* Text0_1: I\'m afraid I cannot help you, $r, but I am sure Khaelyn Steelwing can. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='恐怕我没办法帮你，$r，但我相信乔吉亚可以。',Text0_1_loc4='恐怕我没办法帮你，$r，但我相信乔吉亚可以。' WHERE entry=17188; /* Text0_0: I\'m afraid I cannot assist you, $r, but I am certain Georgia can. */ /* Text0_1: I\'m afraid I cannot assist you, $r, but I am certain Georgia can. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你是否介意用你的暗影将太阳封锁一会儿？$b$b这样会很不错……',Text1_0_loc4='司克诺兹因为我们发了大财……但我们呢？！' WHERE entry=17189; /* Text0_0: Say, would you mind just blocking the sun with your shadow for a little while?$b$bThat\'d be great... */ /* Text1_0: Schnottz is making a fortune because of us... where\'s ours?! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text2_0_loc4='在这里工作实在是太热了——特别是还要穿着这身制服。',Text3_0_loc4='他们向我承诺过，可以在这里得到巨大的财富。$b$b这可真是个不错的笑话！' WHERE entry=17189; /* Text2_0: It\'s far too hot to work out here - especially in these uniforms. */ /* Text3_0: I was promised substantial wealth to come out here.$b$bWhat a joke! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text4_0_loc4='他们让我们像狗一样工作。我们却什么也没得到！',Text5_0_loc4='司克诺兹因为我们发了大财……但我们呢？！' WHERE entry=17189; /* Text4_0: They\'re working us like dogs and we\'re getting nothing to show for it! */ /* Text5_0: Schnottz is making a fortune because of us... where\'s ours?! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='你觉得哥培尔如果在这里，会怎么看你？嗯？',Text1_0_loc4='现在那个仪式完蛋了。你欠我一大笔债，$r。$b$b我会让你还的！' WHERE entry=17192; /* Text0_0: How do you zhink Gobbles vould feel about you if he vere here?$b$bHmm? */ /* Text1_0: After zhat ritual debacle, you owe me, $r.$b$bAnd I plan on collectink! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='听着，自从我们逃出来之后，我稍微庆祝了一下，喝了几杯。然后我一直在想……$b$b那些攻击我们的小人应该得到正义的惩罚！$b$b如果我们不为此做些事情，那么每一个没有准备就进入那个地方的探险家都会变成奴隶被卖掉，或者遭遇更可怕的事情！' WHERE entry=17193; /* Text0_0: Listen, I\'ve been doin\' a little celebratory drinkin\' since our escape, and I\'ve been thinkin\'...$b$bThose little men that jumped us need to be brought to justice!$b$bIf somethin\' ain\'t done, then every unsuspectin\' explorer who sets foot in this place is gunna get sold into slavery - or worse! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc4='这道传送门对面就是托尔巴拉德。',Text0_1_loc4='这道传送门对面就是托尔巴拉德。' WHERE entry=17194; /* Text0_0: Through this portal, Tol Barad awaits. */ /* Text0_1: Through this portal, Tol Barad awaits. */
